Ri ̀ fuu yi ̀ ɗi Yeesus Kiris man a ̀ Davit , man a ̀ Abiraham ɗi ri fɛlɛ :
Abiraham a ̀ yala ̀ Isag , Isag a ̀ yay Yakɔɓ , Yakɔɓ a ̀ yay lɛ , ri ̀ Zyuda ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓii ;
Zyuda a ̀ yay lɛ ri ̀ Farɛs ri ̀ Zara ɓɛɛ ̀ Tamaar , Farɛs a ̀ yay Ɛsirɔm , Ɛsirɔm a ̀ yay Aram ;
Aram a ̀ yay Aminadaɓ , Aminadaɓ a ̀ yay Naasɔn , Naasɔn a ̀ yay Salmɔn
Salmɔn ɓɛɛ ̀ Rahaɓ ɓɛ yay Boas , Boas ɓɛɛ ̀ Rut ɓɛ yay Oɓɛɛɗ , Oɓɛɛɗ a ̀ yay Isayii .
Isayii a ̀ yay ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi lɛ Davit ; ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi lɛ Davit ɗi yay Salomɔŋ ɓɛɛ ̀ gili U ̀ ri ̀ ;
Salomɔŋ a ̀ yay Roɓwam , Roɓwam a ̀ yay Aɓya , Aɓya a ̀ yay Asa ;
Asa a ̀ yay Yosafat , Yosafat a ̀ yay Zyoram , Zyoram a ̀ yay Ozyas ;
Ozyas a ̀ yay Zyoatam , Zyoatam a ̀ yay Akas , Akas a ̀ yay Ezekyas ;
Ezekyas a ̀ yay Manase , Manase a ̀ yay Amɔn , Amɔn a ̀ yay Yozyas .
Yozyas a ̀ yay lɛ , ri ̀ Yekonyas ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓii , ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔn ɓɛ Isirayɛl a Baɓilon .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ n ɗi ri ̀ Isirayɛl ɗin ̀ a Baɓilon nnɛ Yekonyas a ̀ yali Salatyɛl ; Salatyɛl a ̀ yay Zoroɓaɓɛl ;
Zoroɓaɓɛl a ̀ yay Aɓyud , Aɓyud a ̀ yay Elyakim , Elyakim a ̀ yay Azɔɔr ;
Azɔɔr a ̀ yay Saɗɔg , Saɗɔg a ̀ yay Akim , Akim a ̀ yay Elyud .
Elyud a ̀ yay Eleyazaar , Eleyazaar a ̀ yay Mataŋ , Mataŋ a ̀ yay Yakɔɓ ;
Yakɔɓ a ̀ yay Yoosɛɓ a ̀ yii Marii a ̀ nɛ a ̀ yala ̀ Yeesus a ̀ nɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ regi lɛ Kiris .
A ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓi Abiraham a ̀ kpaŋ ɓi Davit gba ̀ a ̀ yi ɓum yi ri yɛɛlɔɔ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ɗi ̀ yinin ̀ ; a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ n ɓi Davit a ̀ kpaŋ ɓi ri ̀ kɛ ̀ n ɗi ri ̀ Isirayɛl a Baɓilon , gba ̀ a ̀ yi ɓum n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ɗi ̀ yinin ̀ ; a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ a ̀ kpaŋ ɓi ri ̀ yalɛ ̀ n ɗi Kiris , gba ̀ a ̀ yi ɓum n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ɗi ̀ yinin ̀ .
Ri ̀ yalɛ ̀ n ɗi Yeesus Kiris ɗi ɓagha ̀ fɛlɛ : Marii a ̀ jɛɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ mɛ gherɛn Yoosɛɓ lɛ , ɓɛ ɓii ̀ wɔlɛɛ . Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ di ɓɛ ka wɔlɛn ɓi , nni Marii , a ̀ teka ̀ ɗyem ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu Kitɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay .
Yoosɛɓ a ̀ ki ̀ lɔni ̀ kii , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ syeesyee a ̀ mum ; nni yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kɔnga ̀ ɓi lɛ a ghani Marii ɓidan , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ fe ̀ ka ̀ lɛ a caɗ nyi lɛ ɗyɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ŋ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ gom .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ ti ri ̀ fe ̀ g a ̀ nɛn , innɛ Ŋwaa ̀ fi ̀ tom a Kan a ̀ re ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi a ɓi ̀ dɛ ̀ ndɛm ̀ , a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Yoosɛɓ , man a ̀ Davit , kɔ ̀ ɔ risi riteɗ ɗi Marii a ̀ giɓ wɔɔ ̀ , ɓisuulɛ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu Kitɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n Ki Nghay wɛɛ nki ̀ i lɛ a teɗ ɗyem ɗi a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɗyɔ .
A ̀ ɓii ̀ yali ̀ man a ̀ baŋi ̀ , u ̀ ki ro ̀ o ̀ nyi ɗii lɛ Yeesus , lɛ nnyɛɛ ɓii ̀ ko ̀ ri ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kii ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓyaa .
Ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ kɛɛ ɓa ɓi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ Kan a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓi ŋwɔm wu n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan lɛ :
Ghɛna ! Gɔ ̀ n i ̀ giɓ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ka yi ɓi ɓɛbaŋi ̀ i ̀ ɓii ̀ teri ̀ ɗyem , i ̀ yay man a ̀ baŋi ̀ , ɓɛ roo ̀ nyi ɗii lɛ Emanuɛl ; ɗii ɗi ̀ n ɗi ri azi lɛ : Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yoosɛɓ a ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi fi ̀ lo , a ̀ ki ̀ loŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a Kan a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi , a ̀ teɗ giy a mɛɛ mii .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , a ̀ yigha ̀ ɓi nyi kito ̀ n zɛy a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ yala ̀ man a ̀ baŋi ̀ , Yoosɛɓ a ̀ ro ̀ o ̀ lɛ Yeesus .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ yalɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Bɛtilɛhɛm ɓi zii ̀ Zyude , ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki Eroodɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m , nni ɓɛ ̀ yii ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ Pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ y ɓi ja ̀ ŋ i ̀ nɛ ŋ ̀ wos a kpagii , ɓɛ yuiy a Yorisalɛm
ɓɛ tɔg lɛ : Ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɗi ɗi n-yalɛɛ fɛ ɗi ri fe ? Ti ̀ i n ̀ ghɛɛ fyɛy fi man a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ri ̀ kpagi ̀ i ̀ ɗi ŋwos di fyɛɛ ̀ lo ̀ nlo ̀ m , fɔɔnnɛ ti ̀ yu ̀ u yi ̀ fɛ lɛ , ti ɓɔgsi nyi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi lɛ Eroodɛ ɗi woka ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ , ki ɓuu ̀ si ̀ nyi n ̀ to , ki ɓuu ̀ si ̀ girig ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ a Yorisalɛm .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ taŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ a ̀ tɔg ɓɔ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ Kiris a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ yalɛɛ .
Ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : A Bɛtilɛhɛm ɓi zii ̀ Zyude , lɛ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan a ka ̀ nga ̀ lɛ :
Wɔ ̀ Bɛtilɛhɛm , ɓi ki ̀ den ki zi ki a Zyuda , u ̀ yin loo maa ba ̀ n a ̀ zɛy ri ̀ zɛy ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ba ̀ n yi a Zyuda , lɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɔɔ i ̀ nnɛ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi ɗi ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sii kilɔ ̀ ŋ kɛm ̀ ki lɛ Isirayɛl , ɗi ɓii ̀ kpaŋi ̀ i ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Eroodɛ a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ min ɓɛyii ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛn ̀ a dwi ̀ ɗ , a ̀ tɔg ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ konag nyi ki ̀ kpaa ̀ fin innɛ fyɛy fin ̀ fi tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ lo ̀ m .
Nni a ̀ romga ̀ min ɓɔ a Bɛtilɛhɛm , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Kɛ ̀ ɛna ki ̀ kaa ̀ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ man a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ tiɓ-tiɓ , i ɓi ̀ ghɛɛ nyi , ɓi ̀ yu ̀ mɛ ̀ ki ̀ wogsii lɛ , mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kɛn ̀ girig nyi ki ̀ ɓɔgsii .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ woka ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ ɓi ̀ n , nni ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ , ɓɛ ki si ̀ gmɛn lɛ , fyɛy fi ɓɛ remzi ̀ gha ̀ y a ri ̀ kpagi ̀ i ̀ ɗi ŋwos , fi ti ɓɔ ɓii ̀ syo ̀ ŋsyoŋi bee , a kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ fi kɛnga ̀ ki ̀ rɛlii ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ man a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓagha ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ fyɛy fin ̀ , ɓɛ woka ̀ ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi naa , ɓɛ ghɛn man a ̀ m ̀ ɓwɛɗ ri ̀ Marii a ̀ jɛɛ , ɓɛ ɓag mɛ ̀ ɗu ɓi zi , ɓɛ ɓɔgsi ̀ man a ̀ nɛ ̀ n . Ɓɛ fumi ̀ min mɛtɛ ̀ g maa , ɓɛ fa nyi lɛ ; ri ̀ gol ri ̀ a ̀ ŋsaŋ ri ̀ mii ̀ r .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ a ɓi ̀ dɛ ̀ ndɛm ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ sugti yɛ ̀ ɛ Eroodɛ . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ suka ̀ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kaa ɓi bee i ̀ dɛŋ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ yii ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ di ɓɛ mɛ sug , nni ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a Kan a ̀ re ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ Yoosɛɓ a ɓi ̀ dɛ ̀ ndɛm ̀ , a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyoo , u ̀ teɗ lɛ ri ̀ maa man a ̀ nɛ , ri ̀ jɛɛ , u ̀ ghɛŋi ri ̀ ɓɔ a Egiɓtɛn , u ki kɔ ̀ ri wɔɔ , a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ kalii lɛ , u sugtii ̀ , ɓisuulɛ Eroodɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ kaakaa man a ̀ nɛ , lɛ a wey .
Nni Yoosɛɓ a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ aɗyoo , a ̀ teɗ lɛ ri ̀ maa man a ̀ nɛ ̀ n ri ̀ jɛɛ , ɓɛ ghɛŋi ̀ lɔŋ ri i ̀ ru wi ̀ n a Egiɓtɛn .
A ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ wɔɔ a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Eroodɛ a ̀ wugha ̀ , lɛ kɛɛ kilɛn lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Kan a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓi ŋwɔm wu n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan lɛ : Mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗegii man wɛm ̀ lɛ a kpaŋdɛn a Egiɓtɛn .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ Eroodɛ a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ ̀ yii ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ m ̀ pwa ̀ a nyi , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ woka ̀ bim lɛɛ ̀ gwey , a ̀ ki rom ɓum lɛ ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ ki ̀ cuusii ɓɔn ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ a Bɛtilɛhɛm a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓi ɓɔn ɓɛ be ̀ g yiɓɛɛ ̀ rɛn a ̀ sɛn , lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ yii ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ reɓka ̀ nyi , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki fyɛy fi tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ lo ̀ m .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ roozi ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ kpaa ɗi n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan Zyeremii ɗi lɛ :
Ɓɛ n ̀ wooghii ̀ di ɓi ̀ kiŋ ɓi rii ̀ a Rama , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ gh , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓa ̀ a ̀ si ̀ , Rasyɛl nnyɛɛ re ̀ nɗen ɓɔn ɓii , kɛ ̀ ɛ gherɛn lɛ mum a fɔɔ ̀ si nyi n ̀ ɗem ɓisuulɛ , ɓɔn ɓii ɓɛ mɛ cu ̀ u ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Eroodɛ a ̀ wugha ̀ , nni ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a Kan a ̀ re ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ Yoosɛɓ a ɓi ̀ dɛ ̀ ndɛm ̀ a Egiɓtɛn ;
a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyoo , u teɗ lɛ ri ̀ man a ̀ nɛ ri ̀ jɛɛ , u sugti ri ̀ ɓɔ ɓi zii ̀ Isirayɛl , lɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ kaaka ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ wey man a ̀ nɛ , ɓɛ mɛ cu ̀ u ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yoosɛɓ a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ aɗyoo , a ̀ teɗ lɛ ri ̀ man a ̀ nɛ ̀ n ri ̀ jɛɛ , ɓɛ sug ɓi zi i ̀ Isirayɛl .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , yɛ ̀ ɛ Yoosɛɓ a ̀ woka ̀ lɛ , Arikelawus yɛɛ n ̀ teri i ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ wu seŋi a ̀ nɛ lɛ Eroodɛ ɓi zii ̀ Zyude , nni a ̀ risi ̀ gha ̀ lɛ a kɛn ̀ ki ̀ kɔ ̀ rii wɔɔ . Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ reɓ nyi a ɓi ̀ dɛ ̀ ndɛm ̀ lɛ a kɛn ̀ ki ̀ kɔ ̀ rii a Galile .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ kɔ ̀ rii ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ dɛŋ ɗii lɛ Naazarɛt , lɛ kɛɛ kilɛn lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ loka ̀ ki ̀ kalii lɛ : Ɓɛ regii gɛ nyi lɛ muu Naazarɛt .
Ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ Zyaŋ Ba ̀ ɓtis a ̀ peegha ̀ y ɓi-reɓ wu a Zyude , a ̀ kaka ̀ li ̀ ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll .
A ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ ɓum lɛ : Lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛɛna mɛ ̀ rem lɛ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyoo ki ti ja ̀ ŋbog .
Zyaŋ yɛɛ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan Ezayii a ̀ ɓuga ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ roa ̀ nɛ a la ̀ alamɓɛ ̀ n yi ̀ ɓi-reɓ lɛ : Pe ̀ gsɛɛna bee yi Kan , ɓi ̀ rɛsa ̀ g yɔ lɛ saaɗ .
Zyaŋ a ̀ waatɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ki ɓɛ toŋi ri ̀ nyu ̀ ŋ yi sya ̀ mo , a ̀ si ̀ nɛ ̀ n ka ̀ nɗa a ̀ go ̀ o ̀ i ̀ nya ̀ m ɓi ki ̀ ɓon ; a ̀ ɗiɗi ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ta ̀ ta ̀ ɗ , ri ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ mɛ ilo ̀ o ̀ mɛ ɓɛ Pisii yi ̀ ɓi cog .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓumɓɛ a Yorisalɛm , ri ̀ ɓɛ ɓi zii ̀ Zyude bimiɗ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ɓi ko ̀ do ̀ bimiɗ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ wuɓsɛɛ Zyuridɛŋ , ɓɛ yuyu ̀ gha ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkii ;
ɓɛ kpakpa ̀ g ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓyaa , Zyaŋ a ̀ ki ɓa ̀ aɓaɓti ̀ ɓɔ ɓi n ̀ syo ̀ m wu lɛ Zyuridɛŋ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Zyaŋ a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ di Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ri Ɓɛ ̀ sa ̀ du ̀ syɛŋ lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛɛ ̀ yu ̀ yuiy a lɔ ̀ ŋkii lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓaɓti ɓɔ , nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Mini ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ pisɛɛ ɓi ̀ go ̀ m ɓɛ ! Ghɛn yɛɛ reɓi mi ̀ ni lɛ ɓi ghɛŋi ri ̀ baŋi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ɗi ɗi tii ̀ ?
Kikiina min ɓiɓan ɓi ɓyɛɛ resi lɛ ɓi ̀ mɛ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛn mɛre ̀ m .
Kɛ ̀ ɓi fe ̀ g lɛ , lɔŋ ri ̀ kpaa ɗi lɛ , Abiraham a ̀ ri ̀ seŋi wi ̀ s ɗi ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ . N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni lɛ : Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ ghaasi ̀ gɔ ̀ g yi ɓɔn ɓɛ Abiraham .
Fi ̀ seŋ fyɛɛ ti gi ̀ kɔmiɗ lɛ fi ̀ nɔ ̀ ŋziyɛn a gaŋ yi ɓite . Fɔɔnnɛ ki ̀ te kice ̀ m ki kaa wum ɓi ɓiɗu ̀ n ɓi syeesyee , ɓɛ ɓii ̀ rengii kɔ ɓɛ won ̀ ɓi ɗuu ̀ .
Mɛ ̀ ɛ m ̀ ɓa ̀ aɓaɓti ̀ mi ̀ ni ri ̀ mɛ ̀ nig lɛ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛɛ mɛ ̀ rem , ki ̀ ɓan kifog roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ mɛ ̀ ajɛ ̀ m a ̀ cee mɛ ̀ ɓi-te ̀ ɗ ; nyii ri mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓtii lɛ ri ̀ Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay , ri ̀ ɗuu . Mɛ ̀ n ̀ kpaŋi gi ̀ ɓi ɓi n ̀ koŋ wulɛ n ̀ sɔ ̀ ŋi ̀ nyi go ̀ o ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ .
A ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ tɛŋkɛlɛ mii ɓi ca ̀ g , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ fyɔni ̀ ki ̀ bog kii a ̀ foŋ ge ̀ ŋ i cag-cag ɓi ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɗ ; wɔ ̀ lɛ a ̀ tɔ ̀ n ɓi ̀ koroɗ ɓi ɗuu ɗi ɗyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɗimi .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ y a Galile a ̀ yu ̀ ɓi Zyuridɛŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Zyaŋ lɛ a ɓaɓti nyi .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Zyaŋ a ̀ ɓe ̀ nga ̀ nyi ki ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓtii a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Mɛ ̀ yaa ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ , n ̀ -yu ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɔɔ lɛ u ɓaɓti mɛ ̀ , nni lannɛ wɔ ̀ yɛɛ ki yuu ̀ yi ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Gherɛn lɛ kɛɛ kilɛn fɔlɔɔ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ lɛ , ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ ti ̀ roo ̀ zi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a tɔtɔ ̀ g . Fɔɔnnɛ Zyaŋ a ̀ ki ɓunɛ ̀ nga ̀ min .
Lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ɓaɓti ̀ gha ̀ Yeesus , a ̀ kpaŋ yi ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ nig , nni ɗyoo ɗi nɛmɓɛ ̀ nga ̀ a ̀ ghɛn di Nghay a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a sɛnsɛn yi yɛ ̀ ɛ kuu ̀ kuu ̀ , a ̀ yu ̀ yu ̀ y nyi ɓi nyoo .
Nni jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ y ɓi ɗyoo i ̀ kpaa lɛ : Roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ Man wɛm ̀ a ̀ nɛ n ̀ keesii , ɓi nyi nnɛ n ̀ foga ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n wɛ ̀ m bimiɗ .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn nnɛ N ̀ ghay a ̀ ke ̀ ngɛ ̀ ri ̀ Yeesus ɓi-reɓ lɛ Sata ̀ n a fee ̀ ghrɛn nyi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ghagsigha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ŋwos mɛtin mɛɓɛɛ ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ̀ tin mɛɓɛɛ ̀ wɔɔ kɛ ̀ ɛ ɗi com , nni za ̀ y i ̀ kɔ ̀ nga ̀ nyi .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n-ɓum a ̀ tyɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ tɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi ja ̀ ŋbog , a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : I u ̀ ri ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll kali gɔ ̀ g yi , yɛɛ ghay ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g .
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : A ̀ a ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓyɔ ri ̀ ɓyɔ ɓyɛɛ ri ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ mum a ghɛɓ , lɔŋ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ bimiɗ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ kpaŋii ̀ ɓi ŋwɔm wu Bɛ ̀ ll .
Nni Sata ̀ n a teka ̀ nyi , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ nyi ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tɛnɛn , a ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ nyi ɓi fi ̀ ran fi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll aɗyo ̀ o ̀ ,
a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : I u ̀ ri ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll lɛla ɓi zi , lɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓii ̀ kpaa ̀ ɓum ɓii ɓɛ titom lɛ , ɓɛɛ yu wɔ ̀ ki ̀ lɛ ̀ ŋlɛŋi ɓi ɓya ̀ g ɓyaa , lɛ kɔ ̀ ɔ tuusi iko ̀ o ̀ ɓi gɔ ̀ g .
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Ki ri girig ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ɔ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn Kan Bɛ ̀ ll wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Sata ̀ n a tɛ ̀ gti ̀ gha ̀ Yeesus lɛ leg a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ nyi ɓi coo do ̀ n aɗyoo a ̀ re ̀ si nyi ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ɓi ziinɛ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , ri ̀ ri ̀ kem ɗi ɓi ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓin ̀ .
A ̀ ki kpaa nyi lɛ : N ̀ ɗi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ faa ̀ ɓyom ɓi ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m di u ̀ ɓaagh mɛ ̀ mɛ ̀ ɗu asu , u ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ mɛ ̀ .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ nyi lɛ : Sata ̀ n , pɛ ̀ sɛn mɛ ̀ ɓi mis ! Lɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : U ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓɔgsii Kan Bɛ ̀ ll wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , lɔŋ nyi cɛ ̀ ncii nnɛ u ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ say .
Fɔɔnnɛ Sata ̀ n a ̀ caɗka ̀ min Yeesus . Ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓɛ yu nyi a nyoo , ɓɛ kiki ̀ nyi ti ̀ tom .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ woka ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ mɓani Zyaŋ , ɓɛ pii ̀ g ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y , nni a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Galile .
A ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Naazarɛt , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ kɔ ̀ rii a Kapɛrinawum a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n , ɓi ki ̀ den ki zi ki ɓɔn ɓɛ Zaɓulon ri ɓɛ Nɛftalii .
A ki ̀ gha ̀ fɔlɔɔ lɛ , a roo ̀ zi ri ̀ kpaa ɗi n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan Ezayii a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ :
Zii ̀ Zaɓulon ri ̀ i ̀ Nɛftalii , jaŋ yi yi ri ɓi be ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y , nsoo ̀ lɛ cɛcɛɗ ki Zyuridɛŋ , Galile a ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ a yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n !
Ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki ki ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔriyɛn ɓi biri ̀ m , ki n ̀ ghɛɛ coo kitɛɛtɛ ̀ n ; fɔɔnnɛ ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ki n ̀ lo ̀ mi a ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki ɓi biri ̀ m i ̀ ri ̀ wu ɓi ɗu ̀ m .
Ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ innɛ Yeesus a ̀ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ ɗi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ kaka ̀ li ̀ ɓum lɛ : Lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛɛna mɛ ̀ rem , lɛ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyoo ki ti ja ̀ ŋbog .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ gha ̀ ɓi be ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ nɛ a Galile nni a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ri ̀ geni ɗi lɛ ri ̀ Simɔn a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ n ̀ ɗegi ̀ lɛ Pyɛɛri ri ̀ Andire a ̀ geni di ɓɛɛ pi ̀ pig dam ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y lɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ i ̀ gh-dam .
Nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ tiina mɛ ̀ , di n ̀ ki lɛ ɓi ɓa ɓɛ ̀ syoŋi ̀ -ɓum .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ghaska ̀ ki ̀ naŋi ̀ dam yaa , ɓɛ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ nyi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ di ̀ gha ̀ ti ̀ bee ̀ bɛ ̀ y , nni a ̀ ghɛɛdi ̀ gha ̀ ti ̀ ri ̀ geni ɗi ̀ dɛŋ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ rɛn , lɛ ri ̀ Zyag ri ̀ Zyaŋ ɓɔn ɓɛ Zeɓede . Ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ki ̀ kɔm ri ̀ Zeɓede a ̀ seŋi wa ̀ a ̀ , ɓɛ ki pe ̀ eghpegsɛ ̀ n dam yaa , nni Yeesus a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ghaska ̀ ki ̀ rinii lɛ ri ̀ dam yaa , ri ̀ seŋi wa ̀ a ̀ , ɓɛ nɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ nyi .
Yeesus a ̀ rere ̀ ni ̀ gha ̀ zii ̀ Galile bimiɗ di a re ̀ resi ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi naa yi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n , a ̀ la ̀ a ̀ la ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll . A ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zi ̀ ti ̀ roɓ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ lɛm mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ri ̀ kem ɗii ɗi saagha ̀ ja ̀ ŋbimiɗ a Sirii , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ yuyu ̀ gha ̀ y nyi lɛ , ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ roro ̀ ɓka ̀ ti ̀ roɓ mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ ̀ kuu ri ̀ , ɓɛ ɓɛ wowo ̀ ka ̀ ri ̀ kɛŋ bee lɛ bee , ri ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roɓi ̀ ki ̀ ti ̀ s , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ sɛkɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ , Yeesus a ̀ ki wɔ ̀ ɔwɔɔ ̀ zi ̀ ɓɔ .
Ɓi ̀ tuu ɓi ɓum ɓi pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ y lɛ , ri ̀ a Galile , ri ̀ a ba ̀ n n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ , ri ̀ a Yorisalɛm , ri ̀ a Zyude , ri cɛcɛɗ ki Zyuridɛŋ , ɓi nɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ nyi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ɓi ̀ tuu ɓi ɓum ɓi ̀ n , nni a ̀ ɓɔka ̀ ɓi do ̀ n aɗyoo a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ ɓi zi , ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛ tyɛɛ ̀ tɛ ̀ n nyi a nyo ̀ o ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ ri ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g a ̀ kpaa lɛ :
Ma ̀ a ̀ gh ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yii lɛ ɓɛ ri nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g , ɓi mɛ ̀ ghay maa ɓisuulɛ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyoo ki ri ɓisu wa ̀ a ̀ .
Ma ̀ a ̀ gh ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ri ̀ misi ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ tam , lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri fɔɔsi ɓɔ mɛ ̀ rem .
Ma ̀ a ̀ gh ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri mɛ ̀ rem lɛ fyo ̀ oog , lɛ zi i ̀ ri wooghrɛn ri ɓɔ .
Ma ̀ a ̀ gh ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ri ̀ coo za ̀ y lɛ , di saaɗ a ́ a ɓaa , lɛ ɓɛ ɓii ̀ wurii .
Ma ̀ a ̀ gh ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ woki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛmbog nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g , ɓisuulɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri wog ɓɔ nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g .
Ma ̀ a ̀ gh ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri mɛ ̀ rem mɛ ̀ tɛnɛn , lɛ ɓɛ ri ghɛn Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ma ̀ a ̀ gh ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki lɛ , fyo ̀ oog a ɓa ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓum , lɛ ɓɛ ri reŋi ɓɔ lɛ ɓɔn ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ma ̀ a ̀ gh ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ tuutulɛ ̀ n ri ̀ mɛ ̀ tɔɓ ɓisuu saaɗ , a ̀ ri ̀ ren ɗi ɓiɓan , ɓisuulɛ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyoo ki ri ɓi ̀ su wa ̀ a ̀ .
Yiina lɛ , ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ma ̀ a ̀ gh di ɓum ɓɛɛ ̀ sɛɛsɛmgi ̀ mi ̀ ni , ɓɛ tɔtɔ ̀ ɓ mi ̀ ni , ɓɛ ki renɗen mini ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi nyoo za ̀ ɓ yi aɗyoo yi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ̀ su wɛ ̀ m .
Nya ̀ a ̀ nyaana , ɓi ̀ ki sa ̀ nsam ɓisuulɛ mɛ ̀ le ̀ ɓ min mɛ aɗyoo mɛ teghɛɛ lɛɛ ̀ gwey . Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓɛ kigha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ ɓɛ loka ̀ ki ̀ yu ̀ u ri ̀ mi ̀ ni .
Mi ̀ ni yɛɛ ri ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n ki ɓi ziinɛ , nni i ki ̀ ko ̀ n ki mɛ rɔ ̀ ɓ kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ti , cɛ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓɛ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ kɛɛ yɛɛ ̀ ti ? Ki rɔɓi lɔŋ lɛ , ɓɛɛ so ̀ ɓ kɔ ɓidan , ɓum ɓɛɛ nyɔɔ ̀ kɔ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ .
Mi ̀ ni yɛɛ ri ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ki ̀ ɓi ziinɛ . Ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ toŋɛn ɓi do ̀ n aɗyoo i ̀ yin lɛ , i ̀ nyamzɛ ̀ n .
Ɓaa ̀ ki ro ̀ o ̀ si ɓi lamɓa ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ kuɓsi nyi a ki ̀ bɔkɔ ̀ zi , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ sag lamɓa ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ saghi nyi ɓi ki ̀ rɛsi ̀ ki lamɓa ̀ aɗyoo , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpeŋzi ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓi naa .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ Ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn kin ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ lo ̀ mi ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓum ɓi le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ , i ɓɛ ghɛɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi syeesyee , ɓi ɓi ki ̀ ki ̀ ɓɛ kemzi ̀ Ta ̀ a ̀ ta wi ̀ n anɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ɗyoo ɓi ɗu ̀ m .
Kɛ ̀ ɓi fe ̀ g lɛ n ̀ -yu ̀ gha ̀ lɛ n-yogsi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll , nsoo ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɗi ɓɛkpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan , n ̀ -yu ̀ gha ̀ ɓi lɛ n ̀ -yogsi ̀ ɓyɔ , n ̀ -yu ̀ gha ̀ lɔŋ lɛ , n ̀ ɗoo ̀ zi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi mii ̀ .
N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki yɛ ̀ ɛ ɗyoo ri ̀ zi ɓi ri ɓii ̀ ɓaɓaa nsoo ̀ maa com a ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna a ̀ a pɛ ̀ sɛn ɓi , a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi mii ̀ ɓi ri ɓii ̀ ki ̀ lɛɛ .
Nni ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ sɛɛtii kibog ki ɓi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi , nsoo ̀ lɛ a ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɓum lɛ ɓɛɛ sɛɛti ɓyɔ , nnyɛɛ ri ɓii ̀ ghɛnɛɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ maa ŋwaa ̀ zɛy ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyoo , ki ̀ ɓan kifog roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ɓidɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓin ̀ , a ̀ ki re ̀ sag ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓeŋ ̀ ɓyɔ yɛɛ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ gi ̀ n i mum ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyoo .
Lɛ n ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni lɛ ; I ɓi ̀ ki ̀ i bi Bɛ ̀ ll mɛ ̀ wog a cee le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kila ̀ g , ɓya ̀ a ɗiŋi ɓi ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyoo .
Ɓi woka ̀ lɛ ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓin ɓɛ ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ɔ wey mum . Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ woli mum , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ ɓɛ yɔm ̀ nyi .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog mɛ ̀ n ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni lɛ : ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ woo ̀ gh bim ri geni , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ ɓɛ yɔm ̀ nyi . Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ sɛmi geni lɛ ki ̀ du ̀ ŋdu ̀ ŋ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ ɓɛ yɔm nyi ɓi sa ̀ ne ̀ di ̀ rɛŋ . Roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ reŋii geni lɛ ki ̀ ye ̀ g , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ɗuu ɗi fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Nni ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki u ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ ɓɔgsii Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ ki ̀ tuwe ɓi ri ̀ ku ̀ na , nnɛ u ̀ yitii lɛ goni a ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ ri ̀ bim ,
ka ca ̀ ra ki ̀ tuwe kɔɔ foo ɓi ŋwɔŋi ̀ wu riku ̀ na ɓi ka pe ̀ gsɛn yi ki ̀ ɓan ki lɛ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ ri ̀ goni , di fɔɔnnɛ u sugtii ̀ min ki faa ̀ ri ̀ fa ɗyɔɔ .
Wooghrɛn jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ lɛ fyɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛɛ ̀ mum wɔɔ ̀ a ̀ ki ̀ ɓan di ɓi kaka ɓi bee i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ m , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ fɔlɔɔ , di a ̀ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ faa ̀ ɓi ɓya ̀ g ɓi ɓɛyɔ ̀ mi ̀ -ɓum , ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ mi ̀ -ɓum ɓɛ ghagsi ̀ wɔ ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ , u ̀ ki ghay lɛ u ̀ ɗiŋii naa ̀ -za ̀ y .
N ̀ kalii wɔ ̀ ɓi saaɗ lɛ , wa ̀ a kpaŋ ɓi ̀ naa ̀ -za ̀ y i ̀ nɛn di ɓɛɛ ka tɔtɔg wɔ nsoo ̀ siisi ̀ bog a ̀ nɛ u leɓ .
Ɓi ̀ woka ̀ lɛ ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ɔ ki ̀ fisɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog mɛ ̀ n ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni lɛ , i mum a ̀ fiɓii giɓ a ̀ fe ̀ g lɛ a kɔri ̀ ri ̀ nyi , ŋwa ̀ anɛ ̀ n a yi lɛ a ̀ mɛ ki ̀ fisɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g ri ̀ giɓ anɛ ̀ n ɓi n ̀ ɗem wii ɓi ɗu ̀ m .
I ɗis ɗyɔɔ ɗi wee ̀ lem ɗi ri lɛ ɗi kɛɓti ̀ wɔ ̀ fi ̀ ɓa ̀ g , sɔgha ɗyɔ , u mag ̀ ɗyɔ fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ ; ɓisuulɛ , ki ri ki ̀ rɔɔ lɛ u ɗimzi ki ̀ ka ̀ ɓ kɔɔ kifog a ̀ cee lɛ wɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ bimiɗ u kɛn ̀ ɓi ɗuu .
I ca ̀ g kɔɔ ki wee ̀ lem ki ri lɛ ki kɛɓti ̀ wɔ ̀ fi ̀ ɓa ̀ g , rena kɔ u mag ̀ kɔ fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ ; lɛ ki ri ki ̀ rɔɔ lɛ u ɗimzi ki ̀ ka ̀ ɓ kɔɔ kifog a ̀ cee lɛ wɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ bimiɗ u kɛn ̀ ɓi ɗuu .
Ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : I mum a ̀ na ̀ ɓi giɓ wii ̀ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ nyi ki ̀ faa ̀ kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ re ̀ sii lɛ ɓɛ mɛ ghasɛ ̀ n .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog mɛ ̀ n ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni lɛ ; ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ na ̀ ɓi giɓ wii ̀ , di ki yin lɛ giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ ki ̀ i fi ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g , di a ̀ foŋi nyi ɓi nɗɛli wulɛ , a gha ̀ y n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ti ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g , nni ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki wɔli giɓ anɛ ɓɛ naɓi fɔlɔɔ , a ̀ ki ̀ i girig fi ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g .
Ɓi ̀ woka ̀ ti ̀ lɛ ɓɛ kali ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓis ɓɛ ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ɔ ka ̀ nɛn bɛ ̀ ɗ yi kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ su , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , u ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ roozii ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi u ̀ ka ̀ agh Kan u ̀ ka ̀ nɛ ̀ n bɛ ̀ ɗ lɛ u ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog mɛ ̀ n ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni lɛ ; kɛ ̀ ɓi ka ̀ nag gi bɛ ̀ ɗ , nsoo ̀ ri ̀ ɗyoo ɓisuulɛ wɔɔnnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔrii ,
nsoo ̀ ri ̀ zi lɛ mii ̀ nnɛ a ̀ rɛrɛsii mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ mii , nsoo ̀ ri ̀ Yorisalɛm , lɛ nnyɛɛ ri ba ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗigwey .
Kɔ ̀ ɔ ki ka ̀ nɛn girig bɛ ̀ ɗ ri n ̀ to wɔɔ ɓisuulɛ u ̀ yin lɛ u ̀ puɓsi ̀ nsoo ̀ lɛ u ̀ fii ̀ zi ̀ fyo ̀ ŋ nsoo ̀ fi ̀ fog .
Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ , i ɓi ̀ kpaa lɛ , ɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ɓa lɛ ɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , i ɓi ̀ kpaa lɛ a ̀ g , ki ɓa loŋ lɛ a ̀ g , lɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yimbog yi yi ɓii ̀ wo ̀ ŋwoŋi ti foo , yi rii ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Sata ̀ n .
Ɓi ̀ woka ̀ lɛ ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : I u ̀ tu ̀ si mum ɗis ɓɛ tus girig wɔ ̀ ɗis ; i u ̀ ɓɛɛgh mum ɗin , ɓɛ ɓɛg girig wɔ ̀ ɗin .
Ki ̀ ɓan ki ̀ fog mɛ ̀ n ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni lɛ , kɛ ̀ ɓi pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi mum ki ̀ ɓe ki a ̀ ki ̀ i mi ̀ ni ; i ̀ ŋwaa ̀ ɓoogh wɔ ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛn ɓi ri ̀ tam ɗi wee ̀ lem , lɛgsi ti ̀ nyi ɗimbog lɛ a ɓog mii ̀ .
I ŋwaa ̀ sɔmɛɛ wɔ ̀ lɛ a ɓatɛn bu ̀ ɓi yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ca ̀ ra nyi a teɗ lɛ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ga wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ mii ̀ .
I ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ ka ̀ ŋi wɔ ̀ lɛ u ̀ kɛɛghi kilo ̀ mɛɛ ̀ ti ̀ rɛ ̀ bog ri ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ g , ki ̀ ya ɓɛ ̀ kilo ̀ mɛɛ ̀ tɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ g win ̀ ɓɛɛ ̀ nyi .
I ŋwaa ̀ lɔni wɔ ̀ com , faa nyi kɔ ̀ ; kɔ ̀ ɔ ki yem mum ɓɔ ̀ ra di a ̀ tɔɔgh wɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ra .
Ɓi woka ̀ lɛ ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Keesi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ wubsɛɛ wɔ ̀ , u ̀ ɓe ̀ e ̀ zɛ ̀ n be ̀ na ̀ bena wɔɔ ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan ki ̀ fog mɛ ̀ n ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni lɛ , keesiina ɓɛ ̀ be ̀ na ̀ bena ɓin , ɓi ̀ ma ̀ ŋ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ cɛ ̀ ncɛm mini , ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓe ̀ eɓee ̀ zɛ ̀ n mi ̀ ni , ɓi ̀ ki ̀ ɓɔ ki ̀ rɔɔ , ɓi ̀ ki ɓɔ ̀ ŋzag Bɛ ̀ ll ɓisuu ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ yeeyee ̀ si ̀ mi ̀ ni , ɓɛ tɔtɔ ̀ ɓ mi ̀ ni ,
di fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓi ɓa ɓɔn ɓɛ Seŋi wi ̀ n anɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ɗyoo ɓi ̀ ɗu ̀ m , lɛ nyii ti a ̀ lo ̀ mza ̀ g ŋwos wii ɓisuu ɓiɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓum , ri ̀ ɓisuu ɓum ɓɛ syeesyee , a ̀ ki nɔsag ti bwey ɓisuu ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri lɛ saaɗ , ri ̀ ɓisuu ɓɛroɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓi ̀ tɛ ̀ ŋtɛ ̀ ŋ .
I ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ keesag mini ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ ɓi ̀ keesii ɓɔri ̀ ɓɔ , mɛ ̀ le ̀ ɓ aɗi mɛɛ ̀ mɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓoŋɓo ̀ ŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ? Nsoo ̀ ɓɛ ̀ teri ̀ -la ̀ mpoŋ ̀ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kila ̀ g girig fɔlɔɔ .
I ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓin ɓɔri ̀ ɓɔ ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ ɓi ̀ ti ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsa ̀ g , di ɓi ka ki bi kiɓan ki nyɔ ̀ n ; lɛ nsoo ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ gherɛɛ ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kila ̀ g girig fɔlɔɔ .
Ɓaana min ɓɛsyeesyee ɓɛ ɓum lɛ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Ta ̀ a ̀ ta wi ̀ n anɛ a ̀ ri ̀ aɗyoo nyii ri .
Konaaghna lɛ , ki ̀ say ki ɓi ki ̀ ki Bɛ ̀ ll kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi re ̀ eresɛ ̀ n ɓi mis mɛ ɓum , di ɓi ̀ ɓii ̀ ki mɛ ̀ mi mɛle ̀ ɓ yɛ ̀ ɛ Seŋi wi ̀ n anɛ a ̀ ri ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki u fafa ŋwaa ̀ nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g com , kɔ ̀ ɔ ɓog n ̀ keŋ lɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ ghɛn ̀ wɔ ̀ , fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛ fyɛɛ ̀ fyɛɛ ̀ ɓi ŋwɔm , i ̀ ghe ̀ y ɓi ɗu ̀ m ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kila ̀ g , ɓi naa yi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓa ̀ a ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ sɛsɛg ɓɔ . N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ , mɛ ̀ le ̀ ɓ maa mɛɛ ri lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki u fafa ŋwaa ̀ nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g com , ca ̀ g kɔɔ ki kimɛŋ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ki yii ̀ com ki ca ̀ g ki wee ̀ lem ki faa ;
fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ri ̀ fa ɗyɔɔ ɗi ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ a ri ̀ nyam ; nni Seŋi wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ ghɛngi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi a ri ̀ nyam , a ̀ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ le ̀ ɓi .
Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓi ki ̀ ki bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n , kɛ ̀ ɓi ki yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛ fyɛɛ ̀ fyɛɛ ̀ ɓi ŋwɔm i ̀ ghe ̀ y ɓi ɗu ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ keesa ̀ g ri ̀ ɓɔŋza ̀ g ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll mɛ ̀ rɛy , ɓi naa yi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓi be ̀ n yi ɓiɓa ̀ a ̀ lɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ see ̀ see ɓɔ . N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ ; ɓɛ ti ri ̀ mɛ ̀ le ̀ ɓ maa yɛɛ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ i u ̀ ti ɓii ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzaagh Bɛ ̀ ll , ɗiŋi ɓi ki ̀ den kɔɔ ki naa , u sim ̀ i ̀ suunaa , di u ɓɔŋzag Seŋi wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ anɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ a ri ̀ nyam i ̀ nɛ ̀ n , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ Ta ̀ a ̀ ta wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ anɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ ghɛngi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi a ri ̀ nyam a ̀ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ le ̀ ɓi .
I ɓi ɓɔ ̀ ɔɓɔŋza ̀ g Bɛ ̀ ll , kɛ ̀ ɓi ra ̀ ŋzi ki kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ su yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yii ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kila ̀ g . Lɛ ɓɔɔ ̀ fe ̀ ki lɛ , i ɓɛ ciɓtaagh ri ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓa ̀ g bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n ya ̀ a ̀ .
Kɛ ̀ ɓi pisɛn ɓɔ ɓi ki ̀ syɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ kin ̀ , ɓisuulɛ Seŋi wi ̀ n a yii com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ɓi kɔ ̀ nkɔ ̀ n , di ɓi ̀ ka tɔg gi ɓi nyi kɔ .
Ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzaagh Bɛ ̀ ll fɛlɛ : Ta ̀ a ̀ ta wi ̀ s a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ aɗyoo
ɗii ɗyɔɔ ɗyɛɛ ɓa ki ̀ ce ̀ li ̀ , ri ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɗyɔɔ ɗyɛɛ yu , ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗyɔɔ ɗyɛɛ kilɛn ɓi ziinɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ ɗyɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ikilɛ ̀ n aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
Faa ɓi ̀ si ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓi ɓi ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si ɓi ŋwos a gɛɛ ̀ nɛ .
Cenɛn ɓi ̀ si ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓeɓɛn ɓi ti ̀ mɛ ki ̀ , fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ si girig ti ̀ mɛ cenɛn ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ kigha ̀ ɓi ̀ si ki ̀ ɓe .
Kɔ ̀ ɔ gherɛn lɛ , ti kpi ɓi mɛ ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn ɓi ɗu ̀ m , lɔŋ pisi ɓi ̀ si ɓi ki ̀ ɓe , lɛ ri ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ , ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , ri ̀ ri ̀ kem ɓi ri ɓyom ɓyɔɔ fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ . A ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n
Lɛ i ɓi ̀ cenɛɛ ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓeɓtɛn ɓi ɓɛ kii mi ̀ ni Seŋi wi ̀ n anɛ aɗyoo a ̀ cenɛ ̀ n girig mi ̀ ni ;
ki ̀ ɓan kifog , i ̀ ɓi ̀ cenɛɛ ɓi ɓum ki ̀ ɓe ki ɓɛ kii mi ̀ ni . Seŋi wi ̀ n a ̀ a cenɛn ɓi mini , girig ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓin .
Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ki ̀ ce ̀ li ̀ ki ɓiɗila ̀ g kɛ ̀ ɓi ɓa yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi wowog bim , yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛ fyɛɛ ̀ fyɛɛ ̀ ɓi ŋwɔm i ̀ ghe ̀ y ɓi ɗu ̀ m , ɓɛɛ ti ɓɛ kaga ̀ g mɛ ̀ su lɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ yi lɛ , ɓɛ ri ɓi ki ̀ ce ̀ li ̀ ki ɓiɗila ̀ g . N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ , ɓɛ ti ri ̀ mɛ ̀ le ̀ ɓ maa .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki u ̀ ce ̀ lii ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g , foŋɗɛn ti ̀ ra ̀ a ̀ ree ɓi n ̀ to , u ̀ ki so ̀ o ̀ i ̀ su wɔɔ
fɔlɔɔ nnɛ wa ̀ a re ̀ si ɓi ɓum lɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ki ̀ ce ̀ li ̀ ki ɓiɗila ̀ g , lɔŋ Soŋi a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ a ri ̀ nyam cɛ ̀ ncii yɛɛ ri ɓii ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ . Nni Soŋi a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ ghɛngi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi a ri ̀ nyam a ̀ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ le ̀ ɓi riki ̀ ɗin ̀ .
Kɛ ̀ ɓi saasaɓta ̀ g i ̀ kum win fɛ ɓi ziinɛ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ Zye ̀ ɗ ri ̀ gee ̀ gee ɓi ti ɓi yogsa ̀ g wɔ , nsoo ̀ lɛ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɛ ̀ wiiwi ̀ i ̀ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ ɓɛki ̀ naa , ɓɛ yii wɔ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ saɓtaaghna i ̀ kum win ɓi ɗyoo ɓi ɗu ̀ m lɛ wɔɔ nnɛ Zye ̀ ɗ ri ̀ gee ̀ gee ɓi yin lɛ ɓi yogsi ̀ wɔ , nsoo ̀ ɓɛ ̀ wiiwi ̀ i ̀ ɓɛ yin lɛ ɓɛ ɓɛg ja ̀ ŋ wɔɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ yii ̀ wɔ .
Ɓisuulɛ , ja ̀ ŋ inɛ i ̀ kum wɔɔ wu ri wɔɔ nnɛ n ̀ ɗem wɔɔ wu ri ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ girig .
Ɗis ɗyɛɛ ri lamɓa ̀ a ̀ nɛ ɓi nyoo i ̀ mum ; i ɗis ɗyɔɔ ɗi ri lɛ syeesyee , nyoo yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ bimiɗ i ̀ ɓa lɛ kpere ̀ e ̀ ŋ ;
ki ̀ ɓan kifog i ɗis ɗyɔɔ ɗi yin lɛ syeesyee , nyoo yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ bimiɗ i ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ɓi biri ̀ m . Nni i ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ki ki ri ɓi wɔ ki ti biri ̀ m , biri ̀ m i ̀ nɛn i ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ te ̀ ghɛɛ i ̀ cee .
Mum a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ say ɓɛ ̀ masa ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ ɓisuulɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓe ̀ e ̀ zɛɛ bog , a ̀ keesi ̀ roa ̀ mbog ; nsoo ̀ lɛ a ̀ ra ̀ rɛ ̀ n ri ̀ bogtɛ ̀ n , a ̀ sɛɛti ̀ roa ̀ mbog . Ɓi ̀ yin lɛ ɓi ̀ say lɛ ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ fog .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki n ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni lɛ : mɛ ̀ rem min mɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ cɛɛcɛɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓiɗila ̀ g ɓi ɓyɛɛ ̀ mɛmɛni ɓyɛɓ ɓin nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓisuu ɓila ̀ a ̀ ɓi ɓyɛɛ lɔg nyoo yi ̀ n ; mɛ ̀ ɛ nti cɛɓ ki cee ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g , nyoo i ̀ cee ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ye ̀ e ̀ ?
Ghɛɛna ɓa ̀ ti ̀ i ̀ li ̀ ti aɗyoo ti ti ri lɛ , tyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ say dɛm , tyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ saŋ ɓiɗila ̀ g , tyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki nyam com ri ̀ com ɓi zaro ̀ , wɔ ̀ lɛ Seŋi wi ̀ n anɛ a ̀ ri ̀ aɗyoo a ̀ ti a ̀ fala ̀ g tyɔ ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g . Ɓi ̀ yii ɓi ̀ nya lɛ ri ̀ ɓa ɗin ɗi cee ɗi ti ̀ i ̀ li ̀ tin ̀ lɛ vɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ m ?
Ghɛn anɛ ɓi mi ̀ ni yɛɛ ri lɛ a ̀ ra ̀ ɓsi ̀ cɛɓ kii nsoo ̀ lɛsa ̀ g , lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ɓiisɛɛ ki ̀ ghɛ ̀ ghɛrii nɗem aɗyoo ?
Nni mɛ ̀ rem min mɛɛ ̀ cɛɛcɛɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɓi ɗu ̀ m ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki nwaa ̀ lɛ cɛ ? Fiɓiina yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓyaaɓi ɓi ɓi dɛm ɓi ti ɓi tɔɓki ̀ , ɓyaaɓi ɓi ti ɓyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ say , ɓyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ti ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ;
ki ̀ ɓan kifog , n ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni lɛ , nsoo ̀ Salomɔŋ nyimiɗ ɓi ri ̀ kem ɗii ɗice ̀ m , a ̀ waatɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ɓila ̀ a ̀ ɓi rɔɔtɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓyaaɓi ɓin ̀ .
I Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ti a ̀ rɛ ̀ gi ̀ ɓyaaɓi ɓi ɓi dɛm fɔlɔɔ , ɓyaaɓi ɓi ɓi ri lɛ , gɛɛ ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓa wɔɔ , ri ̀ duri ɓɛ pig ɓyɔ ɓi ɗuu , lannɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓi lɛ a ̀ waasii ɓi mini ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ , mi ̀ ni ɓumɓɛ maa ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n lɛsa ̀ g ɓɛ ?
Kɛ ̀ ɓi ghɛ ̀ ghɛri min mɛrem aɗyoo di ɓi kpaakpaa lɛ : Ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɗii ̀ cɛ , ti ̀ nɔ cɛ , nsoo ̀ lɛ , cɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓii ̀ waatɛɛ yɔ ?
Ɓyom ɓi ̀ n , ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yii bi Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛɛ ti ɓɛ raŋza ̀ g ɓyɔ ki ̀ kaakaa , wɔ ̀ lɛ Seŋi wi ̀ n anɛ a ̀ ri ̀ aɗyoo a ̀ yii lɛ ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ ri ̀ ɓyɔ .
Looghna ki ̀ kaa ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kii ri ̀ saaɗ wi ̀ i ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓyom ɓi ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ri mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ sagtɛɛ .
Fɔɔnnɛ kɛ ̀ ɓi ghɛ ̀ ri n ̀ ɗem aɗyoo ri ̀ ri ̀ duri , lɛ ri ̀ duri a ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u ri ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓii ; ŋ ̀ wos bimiɗ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ri ̀ ntɔɓ wi ̀ i ̀ .
Kɛ ̀ ɓi yɔ ̀ mgi ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓaa yɔ ̀ m ɓi girig mi ̀ ni .
Lɛ le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ yɔ ̀ mi ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛmbog innɛ ɓɛ ri mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ yɔ ̀ mi ; ve ̀ g i ̀ nɛ ɓi ̀ ti ɓi ̀ fe ̀ ki ̀ ɓum mii ̀ , yɛɛ ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ri mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ fe ̀ egh mii ̀ .
Lannɛ ki ̀ fɛfɛy ki ki ri goni ɓi ɗis kɛɛ ̀ ki u ̀ ghɛɛ , kɔ ̀ ɔ ghɛn nwɔ ̀ g wu wɔ ̀ ɓi ɗis ?
Nsoo ̀ lɛ , lannɛ u ̀ ri ̀ lɛ u ̀ kpaa goni lɛ : Ki ̀ ya m ̀ pisi wɔ ̀ ki ̀ fɛfɛy ki ki ri wɔ ̀ ɓi ɗis , kɔm ̀ lɛ n ̀ wɔ ̀ g wu ri ɓi ɗiŋkɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Wɔ ̀ ŋwaa ̀ fyɛɛ ̀ fyɛɛ ̀ ɓi ŋwɔm i ̀ ghe ̀ y ɓi ɗu ̀ m , ka logha ki ̀ pisii n ̀ wɔ ̀ g wu wɔ ̀ ɓi ɗis di Fɔɔnnɛ u konag ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ u pisi ki ̀ fɛfɛy ki ki ri ɓi ɗis ɗi goni .
Kɛ ̀ ɓi falag bu ɓyom ɓi ɓi ri ki ̀ ce ̀ li ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɓi ki teki ti ̀ caka tin ɓi pi ̀ g ɓɔn ɓɛ je ̀ e ̀ tyɔ , lɛ ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ nyɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghi ̀ tyɔ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ɓɛ ki lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛn yi lɛ ɓɛɛ ghaski mi ̀ ni .
Lonina fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ri mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ faa ̀ , kaana fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ɓii ̀ tanɛɛ , ɓooghna naa fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ri mi ̀ ni yɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ nɛmi ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ lɔni , nnɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ fala ̀ g . Roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ kaa , nnyɛɛ ti a ̀ ghɛngi ̀ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓoogh naa , nnɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ nɛmgi ̀ yɔ ̀ .
Ghɛn anɛ ɓi mi ̀ ni yɛɛ ri lɛ a ̀ fa man wii ̀ ki ̀ ɗun ki gɔ ̀ g di a lɔni nyi ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ?
Nsoo ̀ lɛ a ̀ fa nyi ki ̀ ɗyo ̀ s di a ̀ lɔni nyi ki ̀ zɛn ?
I mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓtɛɛ mɛ ̀ rem ɓɛ , ɓi ̀ yii ri ̀ fa ɗi ɓɔn ɓin ɓyom ɓi syeesyee , lannɛ Seŋi wi ̀ n anɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ɗyoo ɓi ɗu ̀ m yɛɛ ri ɓii ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓi kɛ ̀ ɛ fa ɓyom ɓi syeesyee a ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ lɔni nyi ɓyɔ .
Com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ɓi kɔ ̀ ngi lɛ di ɓum ɓaa ki ̀ i mi ̀ ni , mi ̀ ni girig , ki ̀ laaghna ɓɔ kɔ , lɛ fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ri ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɗi ɓiɗɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Moyis ri ̀ ɗi ɓɛkpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɗi ri .
Ɗiŋiina ɓisuunaa wu wu ri lɛ sɔgsɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ g ɓisuulɛ i ̀ suunaa wu wu ri wu ̀ fu ̀ u ̀ ghrɛn , ri ̀ bee inɛ i ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ gbɛ ̀ ŋɛn ɓyɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛkɛɛ ̀ zi ̀ mum a ri ̀ ɗyaŋ . Nni ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛɛ ̀ ki fyeefyee mii ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog i ̀ suunaa wu a cɛɓ , ri ̀ bee inɛ a cɛɓ , ɓi ri lɛ Sɔgsɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ g , nni ɓum lɛsa ̀ g ɓɛɛ ti ɓɛ tana ̀ g bee inɛ ̀ n .
Konaaghna ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ pwa ̀ a ̀ pwaa ̀ ; ɓɛ ti ɓɛ yula ̀ g mi ̀ ni a nyoo ɓɛ ̀ pa ̀ mɓɛn go ̀ o ̀ i ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , wɔ ̀ lɛ wɔɔ ɓiɗu ̀ m , ɓɛ ɓa ɓi ̀ monɗo ɓi ɓaaɓanɛ ̀ n .
Ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ ɓii ̀ yii ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ maa ; ɓaa ̀ kɛs bi gas ɓi ki ̀ twi ̀ ɗ ki keŋ , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki kɛs dii ɓi n ̀ ɗye ̀ m wu riwo ̀ m .
Syeesyee a ̀ ki ̀ te bimiɗ a ̀ ti a ̀ wumgi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɗu ̀ n ɓi syeesyee ; ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki kite ki wumgi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓiɗu ̀ n .
Syeesyee a ̀ ki ̀ te a yin lɛ a ̀ ɓa ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓiɗu ̀ n , fɔɔnnɛ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki kite ki yin girig lɛ ki ɓa ri ̀ ɓi ̀ syeesyee ɓi ɓiɗu ̀ n .
Ki ̀ te kice ̀ m ki kaa wum ɓi ɓiɗu ̀ n ɓi ̀ syeesyee , kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ reni , ɓɛ won ̀ ɓi ɗuu .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ ɗu ̀ n ɓyaa , ɓyɛɛ ri ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ ɓi yi ri ̀ kuu ɗi ɓum ɗi ɓɛ ri .
A ̀ a ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛɛ rereŋi mɛ lɛ : Kan , Kan ɓɛɛ ri ɓii ̀ ɗiŋii ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , lɔŋ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki ̀ i ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi Ta ̀ a ̀ ta wɛ ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ɗyoo ɓi ɗu ̀ m , nnyɛɛ ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ wɔɔ .
Ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ ri kpaa gɛ mɛ ̀ ɓi ŋ ̀ wos anɛ ̀ n lɛ : Kan , Kan a ̀ a ɓi ɗii ɗyɔɔ nnɛ ti ̀ kpaa ̀ kpa ̀ ŋzi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ? A ̀ a ri ̀ ɗii ɗyɔɔ nnɛ ti ̀ na ̀ na ̀ ɓka ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay ? Ti ki ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ɓi nya da ̀ m yi ɓiɓan lɛɛ ̀ gwey ri ̀ ɗii ɗyɔɔ ?
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ kalii gɛ ɓɔ lɛ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n lɛ , n ̀ ka yigha ̀ ɓi mini nsoo ̀ ŋwos bog , pɛ ̀ sɛɛna mɛ ̀ ɓi mis , mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓɛ !
Nni fɔlɔɔ nnɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ woogh ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi nkpaakpaa ɓi , a ̀ ki nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ɓyɔ a ̀ ɓii ̀ pisɛɛ ŋwaa ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ a ̀ toga ̀ mɛɛ mii ɓi ri ̀ ɓan aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ bwey i ̀ nɔgha ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ poɓɓo ɓɛ ɓɛngi ̀ , bɛ ̀ ɓ i ̀ fɛɓsi ̀ , ɓyom ɓi ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi roŋɗɛ ̀ n ɓi mɛɛ mɛn ̀ , mɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ kpi ̀ lag , lɛ mɛ ɓagha ̀ mɛ ̀ toŋɛn ɓi ri ̀ ɓan .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ woogh ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi nkpaakpaa ɓi , kɛɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ɓyɔ , a ̀ pisɛɛ ki ̀ du ̀ ŋdu ̀ ŋ ki mum ki ki toga ̀ mɛɛ ɓi sɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ bwey i ̀ nɔgha ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ poɓɓo ɓɛ ɓɛngi ̀ , bɛ ̀ ɓ i ̀ fɛɓsi ̀ , ɓyom ɓi ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi yu ki ̀ roŋɗɛɛ ɓi mɛɛ mɛn , nni mɛ kpila ̀ ka ̀ mɛ ki wa ̀ a ̀ rɛn syeesyee a ̀ ri ̀ wa ̀ a ̀ rɛ ̀ n .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ le ̀ gsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓii ɓin ̀ , ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ kuura ̀ ka ̀ ri ̀ kuu ɗii ɗi rire ̀ sa ̀ g ɗin ̀ ;
ɓisuulɛ , ri ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɗii ɗi ɓagha ̀ ɓi yɛ ̀ ɛ ɗi ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , nyii re ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ ka ̀ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll yɛɛ faa i ̀ te ̀ ɗ lɛ a ree ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɓum .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ sɛnga ̀ y ɓi do ̀ n , ɓi ̀ tuu ɓi ɓum ɓi nɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ nyi .
Nni kukwiy adɛŋ a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ nyi a nyoo , a ̀ ɓag mɛ ̀ ɗu ɓi zi di a kakali lɛ : Kan , i ̀ ki kɔni wɔ ̀ , u ̀ ri lɛ u ̀ ki ̀ lɛ , mɓa ti lɛ syeesyee ɓi nyoo yɛ ̀ m .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ na ̀ mga ̀ ca ̀ g , a ̀ ko ̀ m ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Ki kɔni mɛ ̀ , ɓaya lɛ syeesyee ɓi nyoo yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ . Nni ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ gha ̀ ska ̀ ki ̀ wɔ ̀ ni kwiy wii ̀ lɔŋ wɔɔ foo .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , Yeesus a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ɔ fe ̀ g ki ɓu ̀ ŋi mum ki ̀ ɓan ki , kɛ ̀ na lɔŋ , u resɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ , u ki fa rifa ɗi Moyis a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ falag di mum a ̀ wɔ ̀ ni kwiy , di ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗin ̀ ɗyɛɛ resi ɓɔ lɛ , u ̀ mɛ wɔ ̀ n .
