Yɛ ̀ ɛ gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ ̀ n i ̀ pani ̀ gha ̀ , nni a ̀ ɗiŋigha ̀ ɓi naa , a ̀ ɓan mutya ̀ a ̀ giɓ anɛ a ̀ wugha ̀ a ̀ nɛn ɓi ca ̀ g ; mutya ̀ a ̀ giɓ a pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ n aɗyoo .
