Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii lɛ : Mɛ ̀ saŋ mɛ ri mɛ ̀ te ̀ ghɛn , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say lɛsa ̀ g .
