Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ka to ̀ tog ri gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum , nni jɛɛ wi ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓii ɓɛ rɛli ̀ gha ̀ y ɓi dan , ɓɛ kaaka ̀ a ̀ lɛ di ɓaa to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛɛ ri ̀ nyi .
