Fɔɔnnɛ ɓyoo ɓi ̀ tuu ɓi ɓum ɓi taŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi a nyoo , le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ nyii ɓɔka ̀ ki ̀ kɔ ̀ rii ɓi ki ̀ kɔm , ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ rɛli ̀ i ̀ ɓi be ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y .
A kurɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓi da ̀ ɗki ̀ a ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ ɓɔ lɛ :
Ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ yɛɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ mi ̀ si boo i ̀ ɓyom ɓi dɛm ; nni yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ mi ̀ mi ̀ ska ̀ , ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ boo i ̀ dɛŋ i ̀ kpi ̀ ɓi bee aɗyoo , ti ̀ i ̀ li ̀ ti yu ti ɗi yɔ ̀ bimiɗ .
Ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ mbog i ̀ kpi ̀ ɓi ti ̀ cɔg ja ̀ ŋ inɛ zi i ɓi ̀ ɓka ̀ ɓi , i ̀ gha ̀ s ki ̀ ro ̀ o ɓisuulɛ zi i fɔmga ̀ ɓi ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ̀ n .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwos a ̀ kpaga ̀ y , a ̀ ɗigsi ̀ ɓyom ɓi ɓi roo ̀ gha ̀ ɓin ̀ , mɛ ̀ ɗye ̀ m mɛ womda ̀ g lɛ ɓi ɓagha ̀ ɓi ri ga ̀ ŋ .
Ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ boo i ̀ mbog i ̀ kpi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ ka ̀ rag ; ɓi ̀ ka ̀ rag ɓi tɔɓ , ɓi laata ̀ g boo i ̀ nɛ ̀ n , i ̀ wu .
Fɔɔnnɛ boo i ̀ dɛŋ i ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ kpi ̀ i ɓi syeesyee a ̀ zi . Yɛ ̀ ɛ i ̀ rɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ gha ̀ , i ̀ tɔɔ , i ̀ ki ̀ lɛ , n ̀ ɗye ̀ m wu , wu wum ɓi ̀ ɗu ̀ n mɛ ̀ tin mɛtan ̀ , wumbog ɓi ̀ ɗu ̀ n mɛ ̀ tin mɛraa , wudɛŋ ɓi ̀ ɗu ̀ n ri ̀ tin ɗi ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ree ̀ , a ̀ wog .
Nni ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ tyondɛ ̀ nga ̀ Yeesus a nyoo ɓɛ tɔg nyi lɛ : Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ u to ̀ tog ri ɓɔ ɓi da ̀ ɗki ̀ ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : Nto ̀ tog ri ɓɔ ɓi da ̀ ɗki ̀ lɛ mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɛ ki ri ki ̀ fayɛn lɛ ɓi yi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyoo ɓi ɓi ri ɓi ̀ nyamɛn , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ɓɛg wa ̀ a , ki yin ɓɔ ki ̀ fayɛn lɛ ɓɛɛ yi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓyom innɛ ɓɛ ɓii ̀ fatii lɛ a ɓa ri ̀ ɓyɔ lɛɛ ̀ gwey , wɔ ̀ lɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ com , innɛ ɓɛ ɓii ̀ ɓa ̀ tɛɛ maa ga ̀ ɓ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ nyi .
Azi anɛ n ̀ to ̀ tog ri ɓɔ ɓi da ̀ ɗki ̀ innɛ ̀ n lɛ kɛɛ ɓa lɛ nsoo ̀ ɓaa seese ̀ e ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ghɛn , nsoo ̀ ɓaa wowo ̀ g , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ wog , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki yi .
Fɔlɔɔ a ri ̀ ɓii ̀ roo ̀ zii ki ̀ ɓan ki Ezayii a ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ gha ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ ɓii ̀ konaagh ki rami ̀ mɛ ̀ ree ̀ lɛ syeesyee lɛ ɓi wog , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓya ̀ a ki wog ɓi com , ɓi ̀ konag ki zyɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ dii mis lɛ ɓi ghɛn ̀ , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓya ̀ a ki ghɛn ɓi .
Ɓisuulɛ nɗem wu ɓumɓɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki wu kɛsii ti ̀ ɓi , lɛ ɓɛ nki ̀ i lɛ , ɓɛ simgi ̀ mɛ ̀ ree maa , ɓɛ ki ɓuusi mis maa lɛ , mis maa mɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ di , mɛ ̀ ree ̀ maa mɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki wog ti , mɛ ̀ rem maa mɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki yi ki ̀ ɓan , lɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛn mɛrem lɛ n ̀ wɔɔ ̀ zi ɓɔ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ mi ̀ nii ri ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ma ̀ a ̀ gh lɛ , mis min mɛɛ ghɛɛghɛnɛ ̀ n , mɛ ̀ ree ̀ min mɛ woo ̀ ghwo ̀ o ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n .
N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ , ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan lɛɛ ̀ gwey ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ saaɗ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ za ̀ y i ̀ nɛ ɓɛɛ ghɛn ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi mi ̀ nii seesee ɓi , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ ɓi , ɓɔ ti ̀ ri ̀ za ̀ y i ̀ nɛ ɓɛɛ wog ɓiɓan ɓi mi ̀ nii wowog ɓi , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛ woka ̀ ɓi .
Nni wooghna min azi a ̀ nɛ ɓi da ̀ ɗki ̀ i ̀ m ̀ mi ̀ si ̀ boo i ̀ ɓyom .
I ŋwaa ̀ woogh di ɓɛɛ ̀ kakali ki ̀ ɓan ki kilɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , a ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓ kɛ ̀ ɛ yi com ki ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ : Ghe ̀ ghey a ̀ mum a ̀ yu ̀ ki ̀ pisii boo i ̀ nɛ ɓaa mi ̀ si ɓi nɗem wu ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n ; ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ boo i ̀ nɛ i ̀ kpi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi bee aɗyoo .
Roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ gha ̀ ɓka ̀ boo i ̀ ɓyom ɓi ti ̀ cɔg , nnyɛɛ ri ̀ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti lɛ , i a ̀ woogh jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ gha ̀ s yɔ ̀ ki gha ̀ ɓi ri ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ ;
ki ̀ ɓan ki ̀ fog jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓag ga ̀ ŋ ɓi n ̀ ɗem wi ̀ i ̀ ; i a ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi yɔ ̀ ɓi maa ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n , i mɛ ̀ tɔɓ ri ̀ n ̀ -yeesɛ ̀ n ɓi ghɛnɛɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkii ɓisuu jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛn , lɔŋ lɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɓtɛɛ fi ̀ ɓa ̀ g .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghaɓka ̀ boo i ̀ ɓyom ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓi ̀ ka ̀ rag yɛɛ ri roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ woogh jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , cɛɛ ̀ -n ̀ ɗem a ̀ cɛɓ ki ɓi ziinɛ , ɗi ̀ ri ̀ yɛ ̀ y ɗi ikum ɓi laata ̀ g jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛn , ɓi ki lɛ , yɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ wum ɓiɗu ̀ n .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ gha ̀ ɓka ̀ boo ɓi syeesyee a ̀ zi a ̀ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ woogh jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ ki wog com ki i ̀ kpaa ; ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ti a ̀ wumgi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɗu ̀ n fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ boo i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ n ̀ ɗye ̀ m wu , wu fa ɓi ̀ ɗu ̀ n mɛ ̀ tin mɛtan ̀ , wumbog ɓi ̀ ɗu ̀ n mɛ ̀ tin mɛraa , wudɛŋ ɓi ̀ ɗu ̀ n ri ̀ tin ɗi ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ teɗti ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ da ̀ ɗki ̀ i ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyoo ki pisɛɛ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ mis ̀ ka ̀ syeesyee a ̀ boo i ̀ ɓyom ɓi dɛm yii ̀ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ be ̀ na ̀ bena wii ̀ a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ y di ɓum ɓɛ ri ɓi fi ̀ lo , a ̀ mi ̀ s ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki caaɓi ɓi dɛm i ge ̀ ŋ i ̀ nɛ ̀ n , a ghaa ̀ gh .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ge ̀ ŋ inɛ ̀ n i ̀ rɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ gha ̀ , i ̀ tɔɔ , i ̀ fogi ̀ ɓi ̀ saa , ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki caaɓi ki ̀ roo ̀ girig .
Nni ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓɛ yugha ̀ nyi ki ̀ tɔɔ ̀ gh lɛ : Ta ̀ a ̀ ta , ɓi ̀ sii ̀ fe ̀ ki nya lɛ boo i ̀ syeesyee yɛ ̀ ɛnnɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ m ̀ mi ̀ si ̀ ɓi dɛm yɔɔ ̀ , nni ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki caaɓi kɔɔ ɓaa yi ̀ fe ?
Nni a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Be ̀ na ̀ bena wɛm ̀ a ̀ dɛŋ yɛɛ n ̀ ki ̀ i ki ̀ say kin ̀ ; fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ i ki kɔni wɔ ̀ , ti ri ̀ lɛ ti kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ru ̀ ɓii kiɓeɓta ̀ g ki caaɓi kin ̀ .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : A ̀ g , mɛ ̀ n ̀ gherɛɛ ɓi ; lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ru ̀ ruɓii caaɓi kin ̀ , ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ , ɓi ̀ ru ̀ ɓ lɛ ri ̀ ge ̀ ŋ mii ̀ .
Ca ̀ rina lɛ ri ̀ ge ̀ ŋ ri ̀ caaɓi kin ̀ ɓyɛɛ tɔɔ ̀ nɗaŋ , ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ mɛ ̀ saŋ nnɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ kalii ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say lɛ , ɓɛɛ ka ru ̀ ɓi kiɓeɓta ̀ g ki caaɓi kin ̀ , ɓɛ kagi kɔ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓiŋ lɛ ɓɛɛ tɔn , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ taŋzɛ ̀ n min ge ̀ ŋ ɓi zaro ̀ yɛ ̀ m .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ teɗti ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ da ̀ ɗki ̀ i ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyoo ki ri fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ za ̀ m i ̀ mu ̀ tari ̀ dɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ mum a ̀ teka ̀ , a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ y ɓi dɛm yii ̀ .
Za ̀ m i ̀ nɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓisɛɛ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ lɛsa ̀ g ɓi boo yi ɓite yice ̀ m , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , i i ̀ mɛ ro ̀ o ̀ i ̀ ceeghi ̀ ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓi dɛm , i ̀ ghay ki ̀ te ɓi le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ ti ̀ i ̀ li ̀ ti aɗyoo tyɛɛ yuyu ki ̀ toŋtoŋi ɓilaa ɓi myaɓ mii .
Yeesus a ̀ teɗti ̀ ti ̀ ɓɔ da ̀ ɗki ̀ i ̀ dɛŋ lɛ : Ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyoo ki ri ̀ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ nwi ̀ ɗ a ̀ nɛ giɓ a teri , a ̀ foŋ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ kilo ̀ ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ rin ̀ ɓɛraa lɛ di fa ̀ rin ̀ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n bimiɗ a nurɛ ̀ n .
Yeesus a ̀ kaka ̀ li ̀ gha ̀ gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi da ̀ ɗki ̀ ; a ̀ a n ̀ ti kɛ ̀ ɛ kpaa ɓɔ ki ̀ ɓan ki ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓ lɛ a ̀ teri ɓi ɓɔ da ̀ ɗki ̀ ,
lɛ a roozi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan a kpaagha ̀ lɛ : N ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ pinii ŋwɔm n ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n ɓi da ̀ ɗki ̀ , n ̀ ki wogsi ɓɔ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ɓagha ̀ a ri ̀ nyam a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ zi i kpi ̀ gha ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ca ̀ ɗka ̀ gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ ɓi naa . Nni ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛ tyoŋdɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi a nyoo , ɓɛ kpaa nyi lɛ : Re ̀ si ɓi ̀ si azi anɛ ɓi da ̀ ɗki ̀ i ̀ boo i ̀ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki caaɓi ki ki ɓagha ̀ ɓi dɛm .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ mi ̀ ska ̀ syeesyee a ̀ boo yɛɛ ri Man a ̀ mum .
Ziinɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ri dɛm inɛ ̀ n ; syeesyee a ̀ boo a ̀ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ wooghrɛɛ ri ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyoo ; boo i ̀ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki caaɓi i ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ wooghrɛɛ ri ̀ Ghe ̀ ghey a ̀ mum .
Be ̀ na ̀ bena anɛ a ̀ mi ̀ ska ̀ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki boo yɛɛ ri ̀ Sata ̀ n ; mɛ ̀ saŋ mɛɛ ri ri ̀ le ̀ g ɗi zi , ɓɛ ̀ saŋi ̀ -mɛ ̀ saŋ ɓɛɛ ri ɓum ɓɛ tito ̀ m .
Fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ ruɓki ̀ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki caaɓi lɛ ɓɛɛ pig kɔ ɓi ɗuu , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ki ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ŋwosi rile ̀ g ɗi zi .
Man a ̀ mum a ̀ romigɛy ɓum ɓii ɓɛ titom lɛ ɓɛɛ pisi lɛ , ri ̀ ɓyom ɓi kɛ ̀ ɛkɛɓti ̀ yɛ ̀ n ɓum fi ̀ ɓa ̀ g , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kii .
Ɓɛ pig lɛ , ri ̀ ɓyom ɓi ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe ɓɛn ̀ ɓi ki ̀ gɛ ̀ ŋ ki ̀ ɗu ̀ u ̀ ; ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓum ɓɛ re ̀ e ̀ reedɛɛ gɛ , di ɓɛɛ ̀ ŋa ̀ aŋaa ̀ di ̀ min .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓum ɓɛ saaɗ ɓɛ lo ̀ nlomi gɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ saa ki ŋwos , ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Seŋi wa ̀ a ̀ . Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ree ̀ a ̀ wog .
Ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyoo ki pisɛɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ kum wu wu ri wu ̀ nyamɛn ɓi dɛm i ̀ dɛŋ . I ŋwaa ̀ ghɛɛ wɔ a ̀ kona ̀ g ti ̀ wɔ ki ̀ nyami ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ woo ̀ gh ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ a ̀ kɛ ̀ n a ̀ ka ̀ ɓki ̀ ɓyom ɓii ɓicem , a ̀ ki la ̀ g dɛm inɛ ̀ n .
Ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyoo ki pisɛɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -du ̀ ne a ̀ nɛ a kaakaa ticaka ti syeesyee .
I a ̀ tanɛɛ fi ̀ caka fi fi ri fi ̀ kɛŋɛn lɛɛ ̀ gwey , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ka ̀ ɓkii ɓyom ɓii ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ la ̀ g fyɔ .
Ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyoo ki ri ti ̀ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ dam i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ piigh ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y , i ̀ koŋi ̀ i ̀ ɓi ̀ zɛn mɛ ̀ kuu lɛ mɛ ̀ kuu .
I dam i ̀ nɛ ̀ n i ̀ mɛ ron , ɓɛ syoŋ yi ̀ yɔ ̀ a cɛɗ ɓɛ kɔri ̀ min ɓi ri ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ngi ̀ ɗi ɓi ̀ zɛn ɓi syeesyee di ɓɛɛ foŋfoŋ ɓyɔ ɓi ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɗ , ɓɛ mag ɓi ɓeɓtakɛn .
