Nni Pyɛɛri a ̀ pɛ ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ a ̀ kpaa Yeesus lɛ : Re ̀ si ɓi ̀ si yɛ ̀ ɛ da ̀ ɗki ̀ i ̀ nɛn , i ̀ ri ̀ azi .
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Mi ̀ nii ri girig kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ?
Ɓi woogh ɓi lɛ i com ki ɗiŋii mum ɓi ŋwɔm , ki kɛn ̀ ɓi ɗu ̀ m , ki ki kpaŋ ɓi dan ?
Wɔ ̀ lɛ com ki ki kpaŋii ̀ ɓi ŋwɔm wu mum , ki pɛsɛɛ yi ̀ nyi ɓi n ̀ ɗem , com kin ̀ kɛɛ ti ki fogi ̀ mum ki ̀ syeg ɓi nyo ̀ o ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ , ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛyiti ̀ , ri fe ̀ g a ̀ ri ̀ wey ɗi mum , ri ̀ ti ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g , ri ̀ cɛɓ ki sa ̀ a ̀ saa , ri wii , ri ̀ ri ̀ sasa ̀ a ̀ gh ɗi ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi nyoo , ri ̀ ti ̀ fena ti Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓi ti ɓi pɛsa ̀ g yi ̀ ɓi nɗem wu mum .
Ɓyom ɓi ɓyɛɛ ̀ foŋfoŋ mum ki ̀ syeg ɓi nyoo ɓyɛɛ ri lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ; wɔ ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ɗi ɗi mum a ɗii ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g kɛ ̀ ɛ so ̀ o ̀ ɓya ̀ g , ɗi yin nyi ɓii ̀ foŋfoŋi kisyeg ɓi nyo ̀ o ̀ .
Yeesus a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ̀ n , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ɓi ki ̀ la ̀ na ̀ ki zi ki ja ̀ ŋbog ri ba ̀ n yi lɛ , ri ̀ Tiir ri ̀ Sidɔŋ .
Fɔɔnnɛ giɓ adɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a Kanaaŋ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ko ̀ do ̀ a ̀ nɛn , a ̀ yugha ̀ y , a ̀ kpaa Yeesus jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Kan , wogha mɛ ̀ nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g , wɔ ̀ Man a ̀ Davit ; ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki nghay kɛɛ ̀ yeeyee ̀ si ̀ gɔ ̀ n yɛ ̀ m ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Yeesus a ̀ mi ̀ nɛ ̀ n giɓ anɛ ̀ n ; ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛ tyoŋdɛ ̀ n nyi a nyoo , ɓɛ kpaa nyi lɛ : Na ̀ ɓa giɓ anɛ , ɓisuulɛ a nɔ ̀ ɔnɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ i ̀ ɓi ̀ si ajɛ ̀ m ri ̀ ki ̀ yoo ̀ yo ̀ o ̀ .
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : A ɓɔni jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓɛ Isirayɛl ɓɛ ɓɛ ɗimga ̀ ɓɔ ri ̀ ɓɔ , nnɛ ɓɛ romga ̀ y mɛ ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan ki ̀ fog giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ nyi ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ gh mɛ ̀ ɗu asu di a kpaakpaa lɛ : Kan , yu ɓa ̀ mɛ ki ̀ ghɛɓsii .
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : Ki rɔɔtɛɛ ɓi lɛ , ŋwaa teɗ ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓi ɓɔɓti , a fa ɓyɔ ri ̀ ɓɔni bu .
Giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Ki ri lɔŋ fɔlɔɔ Kan , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɔni bu ɓɛ ti ɓɛ ɗila ̀ g bubu ̀ ɓ yi yɛɛ ̀ ra ̀ a ̀ raa a teɓe ̀ re ̀ a ̀ ɓum ɓaa zi .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ min giɓ anɛ ̀ n lɛ : Wɔ ̀ giɓ anɛ , ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗyɔɔ ɗi teghɛɛ lɛɛ ̀ gwey , nni kɛɛ kilɛn lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗyɔɔ ɗi ri . Ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kɔm ̀ kin ̀ gɔ ̀ n yi ̀ i ̀ i gha ̀ ska ̀ ki ̀ wɔ ̀ ni .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ̀ n , a ̀ na ̀ ri ̀ be ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ nɛ a Galile , a ̀ ɓɔg ɓi do ̀ n aɗyoo , a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ ɓi zi .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ tuu ɓi ɓum ɓi yugha ̀ y nyi a nyoo , lɛ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ lɛnlɛ ̀ m , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɗyaŋɗya ̀ ŋ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ mu ̀ m-mu ̀ m , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ sɛkɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roroɓ ɓɛdɛŋ lɛɛ ̀ gwey ; ɓɛ foŋ nyi ɓumɓɛ ̀ n asu , a ̀ ki wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zag ɓɔ .
Gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ ̀ n i ̀ kuura ̀ ka ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ di ki ti lɛ , ɓɛ ̀ mu ̀ m-mu ̀ m ɓɛ toto ̀ g , ɓi ̀ sɛkɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓi wɔnwɔ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ lɛnlɛm ɓɛ kɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛ ̀ rɛy , ɓɛ ̀ ɗyaŋɗya ̀ ŋ ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ ghɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ n . Nni ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ kee ̀ ke ̀ mzi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ Isirayɛl .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ reŋigha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g i ̀ ki ̀ i mɛ ̀ ri ̀ gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ , ɓisuulɛ mɛ ̀ ru mɛɛ ti lɛ mɛraa , yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ri ̀ fɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ . Kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ com ki lɛ ɓɛɛ ɗi . Ki kɔni ɓi mɛ lɛ ncaɗ ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ za ̀ y , lɛ a ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ki kpi ̀ i ɓi bee .
Ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ kpaa Yeesus lɛ : Lannɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ti ̀ ki ̀ lɛ ti tanɛn bi ̀ rɛs fɛ , ɓi ki ̀ lɛŋ ki ja ̀ ŋ ki , le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ gɛmum a ̀ nɛ a ̀ te ̀ ghɛɛ a ̀ nɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ ɗi a ̀ wuri ̀ ?
Yeesus a ̀ tɔg ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ ri ̀ foo ri bi ̀ rɛs yaŋ ? Ɓɛ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Ɓi ̀ rɛs taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔɔ ɓi ̀ zɛn .
Yeesus a ̀ kali ̀ min gwi ̀ y i ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ kɔri ɓi zi .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ teka ̀ bi ̀ rɛs yi ki ̀ taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ zɛn ɓi ̀ n , a ̀ fa Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ɓɛki ̀ yɔ , a ̀ fa ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii , ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ kaɓsi ̀ yɔ ri ̀ gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ ̀ n .
Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɗigha ̀ ɓɛ wura ̀ g , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ tɛka ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓɛgha ̀ ɓi ɓi rɔ ̀ ɓta ̀ ka ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɗ taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ lɛ pisa .
Ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɗigha ̀ ɓyom ɓi ̀ n , ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ tɔɔsi ̀ m ɓɛnin , kɔ ̀ ɔ ɓa ̀ y lɛ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ri ̀ ɓɔɓti ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ghesɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓum lɛ ɓɛɛ suki , fɔɔnnɛ nyii ɓɔka ̀ ɓi ki ̀ kɔ ̀ m , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ɓi ki ̀ la ̀ na ̀ ki zi ki a Magadaŋ .
Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ sa ̀ du ̀ syɛŋ ɓɛ yugha ̀ y yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus lɛ ɓɛɛ fee ̀ ghrɛn nyi . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ tɔka ̀ nyi lɛ , a ki da ̀ m i ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ resi ɓɔ lɛ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wii wu rii ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Nni a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ ri ̀ la ̀ g lɛ , i cɛŋko ̀ ki kpaŋi ɓi ̀ kpaa lɛ , ɗyoo ɗi ɓii ̀ rɔɔtɛɛ , lɛ ɗi ri lɛ bɔŋbɔ ̀ rɔɔŋ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ duri i ri ̀ ɓii ̀ tani ̀ , ɓi ̀ kpaa lɛ , bwey i ̀ ɓii ̀ nɔɔ ̀ gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , ɓisuulɛ , ɗyoo ɗi ri ri ̀ ɓa ̀ ŋ ɗyɔ ti ̀ biri ̀ m ; ɓi ̀ yii ri ̀ re ̀ mi ̀ ɗi riɓa ɗi yɛ ̀ ɛ ɗyoo ɗi ri ɓi mis , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , kɛ ̀ ɓi yi rire ̀ mi ̀ ɗi ɓire ̀ mzɛna ̀ ɓi ɓi ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓi .
Gba ̀ a ̀ i ̀ ɓum i ̀ gɛɛ ̀ nɛ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ lɛ yɔ ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓum , i ̀ ki keesi tisɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g , yɛɛ ̀ tɔtɔg ki ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ ; ɓaa re ̀ si ɓi yɔ ̀ ki ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ kidɛŋ , i ki yin lɛ , ki Zyonas . Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ca ̀ ɗka ̀ ɓɔ , a ̀ ghaa ̀ gh .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ syaa ̀ sya ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ cɛcɛɗ ki riɓa ̀ y , ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ ɗimzɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ teɗ ɗi bi ̀ rɛs .
Yeesus a kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Konaaghna syeesyee a ̀ ri ̀ kona ̀ g ri ̀ nwi ̀ ɗ a Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ri ̀ a ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ sa ̀ du ̀ syɛŋ .
Nni ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ fefe ̀ ka ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ rem maa lɛ : Ɓaa ̀ yi ɓi a ̀ kpaa fɔlɔɔ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ tya ̀ a terii ̀ ɓi bi ̀ rɛs .
Yeesus a ̀ yigha ̀ com ki ɓɛ fefe ̀ ka ̀ kin ̀ , nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓi fe ̀ feg ɓi mɛ ̀ rem min lɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓya ̀ a terii ̀ ɓi bi ̀ rɛs innɛ n ̀ kpaa fɔlɔɔ , mi ̀ ni ɓum ɓɛ maa ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n lɛsa ̀ g ɓɛ ?
Yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ ɓi ̀ ka konag ɓi ki woo ̀ gh ? Ɓi yitii ti ̀ ɓi kitan ̀ ki bi ̀ rɛs ki ɓum ɓɛ ̀ tɔɔsi ̀ m ɓɛtan ̀ ɓɛ nɗii , ri ̀ ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɗ ɓi bi ̀ rɛs ɓi ɓi ̀ i n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɛgh di i ̀ mɛ rɔ ̀ ɓta ̀ g ?
Nsoo ̀ lɛ ki ̀ taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki bi ̀ rɛs ki ɓum ɓɛ ̀ tɔɔsi ̀ m ɓɛnin ɓɛ nɗii , ri ̀ ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɗ ɓi ɓi ̀ i n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɛgh di i ̀ mɛ rɔ ̀ ɓta ̀ g ?
Nni lannɛ ɓi ̀ woogh ɓi lɛ , a ̀ a ki ̀ ɓan ki bi ̀ rɛs kɛɛ ̀ ki ma ̀ a kpaa ̀ ? Konaaghna ri ̀ nwi ̀ ɗ a Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ sa ̀ du ̀ syɛŋ .
Nni ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ woka ̀ min lɛ , a ̀ a nwi ̀ ɗ anɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ fogi ɓi bi ̀ rɛs lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ nurɛn innɛ a kala ̀ g lɛ ɓɛɛ konag ri ̀ nyi , lɔŋ dɔgtɛ ̀ n i ̀ nɛ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ sa ̀ du ̀ syɛŋ ɓɛɛ ̀ re ̀ re ̀ si ̀ yɛɛ ̀ nɛ a kalag lɛ ɓɛɛ konag ri ̀ yɔ ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaga ̀ ɓi ko ̀ do ̀ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ ba ̀ n i ̀ Sezare i ̀ nɛ a Filiɓ , nni a ̀ tɔka ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii lɛ : Ɓum ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaaghi ɓaa ̀ lɛ , mɛ ̀ Man a ̀ mum mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ghɛn ?
Ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ ɓaka ̀ lɛ : Ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaaghi lɛ , u ̀ ri ̀ Zyaŋ Ba ̀ ɓtis , ɓɛmbog lɛ , Eli , ɓɛdɛŋ ti ̀ lɛ , Zyeremii nsoo ̀ lɛ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan adɛŋ .
Yeesus a ̀ tɔg ɓɔ lɛ : Mi ̀ ni yo ̀ g ? Ɓi kalag lɛ mɛ ̀ nɗi ghɛn ?
Simɔn Pyɛɛri a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : U ri ̀ Kiris , Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ cem .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ teɗti ̀ gha ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , a kpaa nyi lɛ : Wɔ ̀ Simɔn , man a ̀ Zyonas , u ̀ ri ̀ m ̀ ma ̀ ŋɛn , ɓisuulɛ , a ̀ a mum a ̀ mɛ ̀ mu ̀ u ̀ ri ̀ bwaɓ yɛɛ resii wɔ ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ , lɔŋ Seŋi wɛ ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ɗyoo ɓi ɗu ̀ m nnyɛɛ resii wɔ ̀ kɔ .
Nni mɛ ̀ n ̀ kalii wɔ ̀ lɛ , u ̀ ri ̀ gɔ ̀ g , nni mɛ ̀ m ̀ ɓii ̀ toŋi ̀ ki ̀ seŋi kɛ ̀ m ɓi gɔ ̀ g i ̀ nɛ ̀ n aɗyo ̀ o ̀ . Fɔɔnnɛ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu riwu ̀ waa ɓa ɓi ri bee i ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ yɛn com ɗi ̀ ki ̀ seŋi ki ̀ n .
Nɗi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ faa ̀ ti ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓa ̀ ti ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ com ki u ̀ ka ̀ ŋi fɛ ɓi ziinɛ , kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓɛ ri ka ̀ ŋ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , ki u ̀ fumii fɛ ɓi ziinɛ , kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓɛ ri fu ̀ mi aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
Nni a ̀ rɔ ̀ gsɛ ̀ nga ̀ min ɓɛyila ̀ g syeesyee a ̀ ri ̀ rɔ ̀ gsɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ kali ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ lɛ nyii ri Kiris .
Ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ innɛ Yeesus a ̀ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ kaka ̀ li ̀ ɗi ɓɛyila ̀ g ɓii lɛ : Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ , a kɛn ̀ a Yorisalɛm , a ghɛn ̀ mɛ ̀ tɔɓ lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ɓi ɓya ̀ g ɓi ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna . Ɓɛ ri wey nyi , a ̀ ki ghe ̀ mɓɛn ɓi ŋwos a ki ̀ raa .
Fɔɔnnɛ Pyɛɛri a ̀ teka ̀ nyi a dwi ̀ ɗ a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n nyi ri ̀ reɓ di a kpaakpaa lɛ : Kan , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ a gherɛn ɓi ; com kidɛŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ kin ̀ kaa ki ̀ ɓi wɔ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog Yeesus a ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ y a ̀ kpaa Pyɛɛri lɛ : Pɛ ̀ sɛn mɛ ̀ ajɛ ̀ m Sata ̀ n , u ki ̀ ki lɛ , u kɛɓti mɛ ̀ fi ̀ ɓa ̀ g , ɓisuulɛ mɛ ̀ yiti ̀ mɔɔ mɛ yin mɛyiti ̀ mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , mɛ ri lɔŋ mɛyiti ̀ mɛ ɓum .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii lɛ : I ki kɔ ̀ ni mum lɛ a nɔɔ ̀ ti mɛ ̀ , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ roo ̀ zɛɛ nyimiɗ , a ̀ tɛ ̀ g kɔrɔs wi ̀ i ̀ , a ̀ ki nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti mɛ .
Mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ kɔ ̀ ni lɛ a kamɛn ri ̀ cɛɓ kii , a ri ̀ kɔ ɓii ̀ ɗimzii ; wɔ ̀ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ ɗimzii cɛɓ kii lɛ mɛ ̀ , nnyɛɛ ri kɔ ɓii ̀ tanɛɛ ti .
Nni ki ghɛɓsii mum cɛ lɛ a fɔn ̀ ziinɛ bimiɗ , di a ̀ ɗimzii cɛɓ kii ? Cɛ ŋwaa ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ la ̀ g cɛɓ kii ri kɔ ?
Lɛ Man a ̀ mum a ̀ ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u ɓi ri ̀ kem ɗi Seŋi ri ̀ ɓum ɓii ɓɛ titom , nni fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ le ̀ ɓi mum n ̀ ce ̀ m lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗii ɗi ri .
N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ , ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri fɛ , ɓaa cuu ɓi , di ɓɛ ka ghɛn ɓi yɛ ̀ ɛ Man a ̀ mum a yu ̀ yuiy ɓi ri ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɗii .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru taa ̀ fog , Yeesus a ̀ teka ̀ lɛ ri ̀ Pyɛɛri , ri ̀ Zyaag ri ̀ Zyaaŋ a ̀ geni a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ ɓɔ ki ̀ pa ̀ s ɓi coo do ̀ n aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
A ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ ɓi mis dɛŋ , i ̀ su wii wu lonlo ̀ m yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwos , ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ɓii ɓi pupu ̀ ɓ lɛ sya ̀ ŋ-sya ̀ ŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn .
Ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ ghɛn di Moyis ri ̀ Eli ɓɛ ti ɓii ̀ to ̀ toogh ri ̀ nyi .
Nni Pyɛɛri a ̀ pɛ ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ a ̀ kpaa Yeesus lɛ : Kan , ki ri ki ̀ rɔɔ di , ti ̀ kɔ ̀ rii fɛ ; i ki kɔni wɔ ̀ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ toŋi ̀ ɓi ̀ laa fɛ ɓiraa lɛ ki ̀ fog ɓisu wɔɔ , ki ̀ fog ɓisuu Moyis , ki ̀ fog ɓisuu Eli .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pyɛɛri a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ka to ̀ tog fɔlɔɔ nni coo kikwi ̀ ɗ ki lo ̀ nlomɛn ki si ̀ gtɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ . Fɔɔnnɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ y ɓi ki ̀ kwi ̀ ɗ kin ̀ , i ̀ kpaa lɛ : Roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ Man wɛm ̀ a ̀ nɗem , ɓi nyi innɛ n ̀ foga ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n wɛ ̀ m bimiɗ , wooghna nyi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ woka ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ɓɛ kpi ̀ la ̀ g ɓi zi guɓu ̀ g , ɓɛ ruusi ̀ mɛ ̀ su ɓi zi , lɛ i ̀ ris wu ɓanga ̀ ɓɔ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ tyo ̀ ŋdɛ ̀ nga ̀ y ɓɔ a nyoo , a ̀ n ̀ yɛ ̀ ŋ ɓɔ , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Pɛ ̀ sɛɛna aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɓi risi .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ pɛsi ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ su aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , ɓɛ ghɛn lɔŋ Yeesus cɛ ̀ ncii .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ sɛnsɛ ̀ nga ̀ y do ̀ n , Yeesus a ̀ rɔ ̀ gsɛ ̀ n ɓɔ lɛ : Kɛ ɓi fe ̀ g ki kpaa ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓi ̀ ghɛɛ ki ̀ n a ̀ kpaŋ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Man a ̀ mum a ̀ ri ghe ̀ mɓɛn yi a ɓi ̀ loŋ .
Ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ tɔka ̀ nyi n ̀ tɔɔ ̀ tɔɔgh lɛ : Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓɛɛ kalag min lɛ , Eli a ̀ ka ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ yi ̀ ki ̀ yu ̀ u ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : Ki ri lɔŋ saaɗ lɛ Eli a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u lɛ a pɛɛ ̀ zi ki ̀ rɛsaagh ɓiɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi mɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , n ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni lɛ , Eli a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓum ɓɛ yiti ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ nyi , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ kigha ̀ ri ̀ nyi yɛ ̀ ɛ ki kɔnga ̀ ɓɔ .
Nni ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ yigha ̀ min lɛ , ki ̀ ɓan ki Zyaŋ Ba ̀ ɓtis kɛɛ ̀ ki a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kpaga ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum , ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ yu ̀ ki ̀ kpi ̀ i Yeesus asu , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ɗu , a ̀ kpaa lɛ :
Kan , wogha man wɛm ̀ nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g , a roro ̀ ɓ kiti ̀ s , ki ki yeeyee ̀ si ̀ nyi lɛɛ ̀ gwey ; a ̀ ti a ̀ kpi ̀ la ̀ g ɓi ɗuu , nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ nig .
Ma ̀ a yu ̀ u yi ̀ ri ̀ nyi a ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɔɔ , nni a ̀ a yaagh ɓɔ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zi ̀ .
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : Mi ̀ ni ɓumɓɛ , ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ , mi ̀ ni kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , mi ̀ ni ɓi ̀ ɗyoŋi ɓi ɓum ; n ̀ ɗi ɓii ̀ kɔ ̀ rii n ̀ ɗaŋ ri mi ̀ ni , n ̀ ki cenɛn mi ̀ ni n ̀ kpaŋ fin ? Yu ̀ unay mɛ ̀ fɛ ri ̀ mutya ̀ a ̀ nɛn .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ fwa ̀ a ̀ dɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki nghay , ki kpaŋ ɓi mutya ̀ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n , a ̀ gha ̀ s ki ̀ wɔ ̀ ni lɔŋ wɔɔ foo .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ Yeesus ɓɛ tyoŋdɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi a nyoo , ɓɛ tɔg nyi a dwi ̀ ɗ lɛ : Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki nghay kin ̀ kaa yaagh ɓi ̀ si ri ̀ na ̀ ɓ ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : Kaa yaagh mi ̀ ni ri ̀ na ̀ ɓ lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗin ɗi tɔɔ ɓi ̀ ; n ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ ; i ɓya ̀ a ri ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ te ̀ ghɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ za ̀ m i ̀ doŋ , di ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ , i ɓi ̀ kpaa do ̀ n i ̀ nɛ lɛ : Pɛ ̀ sɛn fɛ kɛ ̀ na fɛnii , i ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ n ; di com ki yin lɛ ki yag mi ̀ ni .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , lɔŋ bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ ki ̀ ce ̀ li ̀ ki ɓiɗila ̀ g ɓyɛɛ ti ɓi kila ̀ g lɛ , ri ̀ kuu ɗi kiɓeɓta ̀ g ki nghay ɗi ̀ n ɗyɛɛ kpaŋ ̀ .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ rere ̀ ni ̀ gha ̀ ziinɛ a Galile , Yeesus a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓɛ ɓii ̀ ka ̀ ɓi Man a ̀ mum ri ̀ ɓum ;
ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ wey nyi , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ŋwos a ki ̀ raa , a ̀ ɓii ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛɛ . Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki fagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g bim ɓi nɗem lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kpaga ̀ a Kapɛrinawum , ɓɛ ̀ teri ̀ -la ̀ mpoŋ ̀ a ̀ nɛ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛ tɔka ̀ Pyɛɛri lɛ : Nɗe ̀ sa ̀ g wi ̀ n a ̀ ti ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ pee la ̀ mpoŋ ̀ a ̀ nɛ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll ?
Pyɛɛri a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : A ̀ ti a ̀ peeghi ̀ . Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi naa , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ loka ̀ ki ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛɛ a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Simɔn ! Wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghɛɛ la ? Mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m mɛ ɓi ziinɛ mɛ ti mɛ tɔki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ghɛn la ̀ mpoŋ ̀ ? Ɓum ɓɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ gi ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ ke ̀ n ?
Pyɛɛri a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Ɓɛ ̀ ke ̀ n ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ tɔki ̀ . Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g Pyɛɛri lɛ : Fɔlɔɔ a re ̀ sii lɛ , ɓɔn ɓɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ ɓaa ̀ pee ɓi .
Ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ yugha ̀ Yeesus a nyoo , ɓɛ tɔg nyi lɛ : Ghɛn yɛɛ cee min ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyo ̀ o ̀ ?
Nni Yeesus a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ y maa ŋwɔɓti a ̀ rɛsi ̀ ɓɔ nyi ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m ,
a ̀ kpaa lɛ : N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ , i ɓi ̀ koɓsɛɛ ɓi lɛ ɓi ɓa fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɔɓti ɓɛsa ̀ g , ɓya ̀ a ɗiŋi ɓi ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki , mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ sɛɛdii nyimiɗ ɓi zi fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ maa mutya ̀ a ̀ nɛ , nnyɛɛ ri ɓii ̀ cee ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ i mum a ̀ gha ̀ ɓi maa ŋwɔɓti yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ɗii ɗyɛ ̀ m di mɛ ̀ nnɛ a ̀ gha ̀ ɓi .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , i ̀ ŋwaa ̀ kɛ ̀ ɓtii ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɔɔ ɓɔɓti ɓɛ ɓɛ gherɛɛ mɛ ̀ ɓɛ fi ̀ ɓa ̀ g , ki ɓa ti ̀ ki ̀ rɔɔ ɓisu wii lɛ , ɓɛɛ kaŋ ̀ nyi coo gɔ ̀ g i ̀ ki ̀ pɛn ɓi ki ̀ mi ̀ i ̀ gh , ɓɛɛ ɓimzi nyi ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y .
Nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g ri ̀ ziinɛ lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi kɛ ̀ ɛkɛɓti ̀ yɛ ̀ n ɓum ti ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓi ri mii ̀ . Ti ̀ ɓa ̀ g ti yin lɛ ti taŋ ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan ki ̀ fog , nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ ɓtii romum fi ̀ ɓa ̀ g .
I ca ̀ g kɔɔ nsoo ̀ lɛ i ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ wɔɔ ɓyɛɛ ti ɓi kɛɓta ̀ g wɔ ̀ fi ̀ ɓa ̀ g , rena ɓyɔ , u mag ɓyɔ fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ ; lɛ ki ri wɔ ̀ ki ̀ rɔɔ lɛ u ghɛn ̀ cɛɓ ri ̀ ca ̀ g kifo ̀ g , nsoo ̀ lɛ i ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ wufo ̀ g , a ̀ cee lɛ u kɛn ̀ ɓi ɗuu ɗi fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ri ̀ ɓya ̀ g ɓyɔɔ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , nsoo ̀ lɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ mɔɔ mɛce ̀ m .
I ɗis ɗyɔɔ ɗyɛɛ ti ɗi kɛɓta ̀ g wɔ ̀ fi ̀ ɓa ̀ g , sɔgha ɗyɔ , u mag ɗyɔ fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ , lɛ ki ri ̀ wɔ ̀ ki ̀ rɔɔ lɛ , u ghɛn cɛɓ di u ̀ ri ̀ ɗis ɗi ̀ fog a ̀ cee lɛ u kɛn ̀ ɓi ɗuu ɗi fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ri ̀ mis mɔɔ mɛce ̀ m .
Kɔ ̀ riina ɗyomzɛ ̀ n lɛ kɛ ̀ ɓi sɛɛti kibog ki ɓi ɓɔɓti ɓɛ . Lɛ n ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni lɛ , ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓaa ɓɛ rɛrɛlii ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi mis mɛ Seŋi wɛ ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
Lɛ Man a ̀ mum a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ ki ghɛɓsii ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɗimga ̀ .
Mi ̀ nii ghɛɛ la ̀ ? I ŋwaa ̀ ri ̀ ɗi ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ tin mɛtan ̀ , nnɛ i ̀ ɗimi bog , a ̀ yin nya lɛ a ̀ ca ̀ ɗ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yimbog mɛ ̀ tin mɛnin ɗi ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ɗi ̀ taa ̀ ni ̀ n , a ̀ ka kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ kaa ̀ i ̀ nɛ ya ̀ a ɗimi ?
I a ̀ tanɛɛ ti ̀ yɔ ̀ , n ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ , a ̀ ɓii ̀ woo ̀ gh ki ̀ rɔɔ ri ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ i ̀ nɛn a ̀ cee yi mɛtin mɛnin ɗi ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ɗi ̀ taa ̀ ni ̀ n yi yaa rɔ ̀ ɓi .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ Seŋi wi ̀ n a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ aɗyoo , a ̀ kɔ ̀ ni ɓi lɛ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɔɓti ɓɛ kɛɛ taŋ ̀ .
I goni a ̀ ki ̀ i ki ̀ ɓe , kɛ ̀ na , u reɓ nyi a mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ ; i a ̀ woogh deɓ yɔɔ , di u ̀ ru ̀ nɛɛ nyi .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ , i a ̀ ɓe ̀ ni ki ̀ woo ̀ gh deɓ yɔɔ , u ̀ reŋi ̀ ti ̀ mum bog nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓum ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ , lɛ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ kpaa ̀ rɛn di ɓɛ ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛ ri ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓɛraa .
I a ̀ ɓe ̀ e ̀ dii ti ̀ ɓɔ ki ̀ woo ̀ gh , u ̀ kali ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ki ̀ seŋi . I a ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓtii kɛ ̀ ɛ wog rikpaa ɗi kiseŋi , tera nyi fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yin n ̀ gherɛ ̀ n nsoo ̀ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ teri ̀ -la ̀ mpoŋ ̀ .
N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ ; com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ɓi ̀ ɓii ̀ ka ̀ ŋi fɛ ɓi ziinɛ , ɓɛ ri kɔ ɓii ̀ ka ̀ ŋi aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ɓi ̀ ɓii ̀ fu ̀ mii fɛ ɓi ziinɛ , ɓɛ ri kɔ ɓii ̀ fu ̀ mii aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
N ̀ kalii ti ̀ mi ̀ ni saaɗ a ̀ ri ̀ kali ̀ lɛ ; i ɓum ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ wooghrɛɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ fɛ ɓi ziinɛ , lɛ ɓɛɛ tɔg Ta ̀ a ̀ ta wɛ ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ aɗyoo com kidɛŋ , a ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ kɔ ɓii ̀ faa ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ , ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓum ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓɛraa ɓɛ taŋzɛɛ ɓi ɗii ɗyɛ ̀ m , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wa ̀ a ̀ .
Nni Pyɛɛri a ̀ tyo ̀ ŋdɛ ̀ nga ̀ Yeesus a nyoo , a ̀ tɔg nyi lɛ : Kan n ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ cenɛɛ geni wɛ ̀ m di a ̀ ki ̀ i mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ɓe gɛ ̀ n yaŋ ? N ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ n ̀ cenɛ ̀ n nyi lɔŋ gɛ ̀ n taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : N ̀ kalii ɓi wɔ lɛ lɔŋ gɛ ̀ n taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ; n ̀ kalii wɔ ̀ lɛ ; gɛ ̀ n mɛtin mɛraa ri ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ a ̀ kpaŋ , fɔlɔɔ gɛ ̀ n taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyoo ki ri fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗidɛŋ ɗi ɗi kɔnga ̀ lɛ ɗyɛɛ fiɓi ɓɛ ̀ pon ɓɛ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓii ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ nyi ri ̀ ɓɔ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ba ̀ li ̀ , nni ɓɛ yugha ̀ nyi ri ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say adɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ nyi ri ̀ pon a ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ mi ̀ li ̀ yɔŋ .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ri bee inɛ lɛ a ̀ le ̀ ɓ pon anɛ ̀ n , nni masa ̀ wi ̀ i ̀ a ki ̀ say a reɓsigha ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ kaɓ lɛ , ri ̀ nyi , ri ̀ giy , ri ̀ ɓɔn ɓii , ri ̀ ɓyom ɓii ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓisuu pon anɛ ̀ n .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say anɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi zi a ̀ ɓag ri ̀ fo ̀ m mɛ ̀ ɗu asu , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Masa ̀ ka cenɛn mɛ ̀ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ le ̀ ɓi mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɛ ̀ n mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g i ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ masa ̀ anɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say wii ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ cenɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi pon wii ̀ , a ̀ ca ̀ ɗ nyi lɛ a kɛn ̀ .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say anɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpaga ̀ , a ̀ tuusɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ reŋka ̀ ŋ wi ̀ i ̀ adɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ nyi ri ̀ pon a hɔnɗɛ ̀ ɗ . Nni a ̀ sɛnga ̀ ɓi roa ̀ nɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ɓan nyi a ɓɛ ̀ ɓoŋ di a kakali lɛ : Le ̀ ɓa mɛ ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɛ ̀ m .
Reŋka ̀ ŋ wi ̀ i ̀ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpi ̀ gha ̀ nyi a mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ , a ̀ yɛ ̀ gsi ̀ nyi ɓya ̀ g di a kakali lɛ : Ka cenɛn mɛ ̀ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ pee ̀ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say anɛ ̀ n a ̀ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi rikali ̀ ɗi reŋka ̀ ŋ wi ̀ i ̀ ɗin ̀ . Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi ki ̀ pi ̀ igh ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y , a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ roa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ le ̀ ɓka ̀ pon a ̀ nɛ ̀ n .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛmbog ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ki kɛŋ ɓɔ lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ki ̀ kpaa ̀ masa ̀ wa ̀ a ̀ , com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ki ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ masa ̀ wa ̀ a ̀ a romga ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ regii ̀ nyi n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say anɛ ̀ n , nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : Wɔ ̀ nki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say anɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ gɛn ; mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ cenɛɛ wɔ ̀ pon wɔɔ ̀ bimiɗ yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ u mɓɔ ̀ ŋzaagh mɛ ̀ lɛ , n ̀ cenɛn wɔ ̀ .
Wɔ ̀ ɔ n-yin lɛ u ̀ wog roŋka ̀ ŋ nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ woogh wɔ ̀ nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g ?
Nni masa ̀ wi ̀ i ̀ a woka ̀ bim , a ̀ kpaa ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓan ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say anɛ ̀ n , ɓɛɛ foŋ nyi ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y , a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ le ̀ gsii ki pee ̀ pon wii ̀ .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ Ta ̀ a ̀ ta wɛ ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ aɗyoo a ̀ ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i di mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ ɓi mi ̀ ni a ̀ cenɛɛ ɓi geni wi ̀ i ̀ ri nɗem wii wuce ̀ m .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ le ̀ gsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓin ̀ , nni a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Galile a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ɓi ki ̀ den ki zi ki a Zyude ki ki ri cɛcɛɗ ki Zyuridɛŋ .
Ɓi ̀ tuu ɓi ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwɛy ɓi nɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ nyi wɔɔ , a ̀ ki wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zi ɓyɔ .
Nni Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ nyi ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ fe ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ , ɓɛɛ puri nyi ca ̀ g ɓi ɗu ̀ m . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ tɔka ̀ nyi lɛ : Ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓis ɓi kpaa nya lɛ mum a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ na ̀ ɓ giɓ wii ̀ nsoo ̀ ɓi n ̀ too-kiɓan aɗi ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : Ɓi ka ɓala ̀ ɓi yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : A ri ̀ tumɛ ̀ n N ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ri ̀ giɓ ri ̀ baŋi ̀ ,
a ̀ ki kpaa lɛ : Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki baŋi ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ca ̀ rii ̀ lɛ ri ̀ seŋi ri ̀ jɛɛ , i ̀ ra ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɓɛɛ giy , ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ɓum ki ghay com ki ̀ fog .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓɛ yii ̀ di ɓum ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ , ɓɛ ti ̀ com ki ̀ fog . Mum a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi min ki ghasii com ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ra ̀ ri .
Nni Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ tɔka ̀ Yeesus lɛ : Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ Moyis a ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ min lɛ , ɓɛɛ falag giɓ kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ gasɛ ̀ n di ɓɛ ti nyi ɓii ̀ na ̀ ɓi ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : Moyis a ̀ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ , ɓi naɓkag ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓin , ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ te ̀ ri mɛ ̀ rem . Wɔ ̀ lɛ a ri ̀ tumɛ ̀ n , ki ɓagha ̀ ɓi ̀ fɔlɔɔ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog mɛ ̀ n ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni lɛ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ na ̀ ɓi giɓ wii ̀ , di ki yin lɛ giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ ki ̀ i fi ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g , i a ̀ wɔɔtii giɓ adɛŋ , di a ̀ ki ̀ i fi ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g .
Ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛ kpaa nyi lɛ : I fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ri ̀ ɓa ɗi baŋi ̀ ɗi ɓɛɛ gil ɗi ri , ki ɓa min kirɔɔ lɛ , mum kɛ ̀ ɛ wɛy giɓ .
Yeesus a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ yin lɛ ɓɛ wog ri ̀ kpaa ɗin ̀ , i ki cee ɓi lɛ , ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ki ri ki ̀ fayɛn lɛ ɓɛɛ wog ɗyɔ .
Ɓisuulɛ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ri wɔɔ , ɓɛ ri myɛg a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓi mu ̀ m mɛ ɓɛ ̀ jɛɛ ɓaa , ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓa lɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ kii ɓɔ fɔlɔɔ , ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛmbog , ɓɛ ghaasi ̀ ɓɔmiɗ myɛg ɓisuu kilɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyo ̀ o ̀ . Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ wog , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ woo ̀ gh .
Nni ɓum ɓɛ yugha ̀ y Yeesus ri ̀ ɓɔɓti ɓɛsa ̀ g , lɛ a saagh ɓɔ ɓya ̀ g ɓi nyoo , a ̀ ki ɓɔŋzi Bɛ ̀ ll ɓisu wa ̀ a ̀ , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛ nyɛɛdɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n .
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Ca ̀ rina ɓɔɓti ɓɛsa ̀ g , kɛ ̀ ɓi re ̀ g ɓɔ ri ̀ yu ̀ ɗi a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ , ɓisuulɛ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyo ̀ o ̀ ki ri ɓisuu ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɔ .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ lɛ , a ̀ mɛ saaghrag ɓɔ ɓya ̀ ɓ ɓi nyoo , a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ n a ̀ ghaa ̀ gh .
Ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ yɛɛ kɛnga ̀ Yeesus a nyoo a ̀ tɔg nyi lɛ : N ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g ! cɛ ki syeesyee kɛɛ ̀ ki n ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ kii ̀ ɓi ɗi lɛ mɓa ri ̀ cɛɓ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ u ̀ tɔɔgh mɛ ̀ lɛ nɗeɓ wɔ ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki syeesyee ? Syeesyee a ̀ mum a ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ bogtɛ ̀ n . Uu ̀ kɔ ̀ ni lɛ u ghɛn ̀ cɛɓ , ɓe ̀ ŋa ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ; ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ tɔg lɛ : Ɓi be ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ɔ wey mum , kɔ ̀ ɔ ki ̀ fisɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g , kɔ ̀ ɔ yii com ki mum , kɔ ̀ ɔ pwa ̀ a ̀ mum ki ̀ ɓan ɓi nyoo ;
u ̀ nyaasi ̀ soŋi ɓɛɛ ̀ gaa , u ̀ ki keesi romum a ̀ nɛ wɔ ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog yɛ ̀ ɛ wɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ .
Dɛli ̀ i ̀ mum i ̀ nɛ ̀ n i ̀ kpaa Yeesus lɛ : M ̀ mɛ ɓe ̀ ŋ ɓidɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓin ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m nni cɛ kidɛŋ kɛɛ ̀ ki n ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ti ̀ ki ̀ kii ̀ ?
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Uu ̀ kɔ ̀ ni lɛ u ̀ ɓa syeesyee a ̀ mum lɛ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ , kɛ ̀ na , u kaɓ ɓyom ɓyɔɔ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m u kaɓsi mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɛ mii ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sogha ̀ sogha fɔɔnnɛ u ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓa ri ̀ i ̀ kum aɗyo ̀ o ̀ . Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn u yu u nɔɔ ̀ ti mɛ ̀ .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ dɛli ̀ i ̀ nɛn i ̀ woka ̀ fɔlɔɔ , nni i ̀ ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ bim , ɓisuulɛ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ kum lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii lɛ : Nkalii mi ̀ ni saaɗ lɛ , ki ri ki ̀ te ̀ ete ̀ ɗ ki kiɓan lɛ guŋgum a ɗiŋi ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
N ̀ kalii ti ̀ mi ̀ ni lɛ , ki ri lɛ fɛnfɛn lɛ sya ̀ moo a ɗiŋi ɓi ɗyas ɗi ba ̀ a ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ cee lɛ guŋgum a ɗiŋi ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ woka ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ɓɛ kuura ̀ g lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ɓɛ kpaa lɛ : Ghɛn yɛɛ ri min lɛ a ̀ ghɛn cɛɓ ?
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ pɛɓsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki yin ɓi ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗi ɓum , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , com ki lɛ ki yaaghrɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ki ̀ ki yin .
Nni Pyɛɛri a ̀ teka ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ a ̀ kpaa Yeesus lɛ : Ghɛna lɛ , ɓi ̀ sii rini ̀ gha ̀ y ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ti ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ wɔ ̀ , mɛ ̀ le ̀ ɓ mis mɛ ri ̀ ɓaa gɛ cɛ ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ , yɛɛ Man a ̀ mum a ̀ kɔ ̀ rii gɛ ɓi-kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wii wu rila ̀ mi ̀ wu rikem , ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi sugtii gɛ ɓɛ ̀ nyɔɔnyɔn ɓɛ ɓyom , mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ɓi ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ , ɓi ̀ kɔ ̀ rii gɛ girig ɓi mɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ mɛ rila ̀ mi ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ mɛɓɛɛ ̀ , lɛ ɓi yɔm ̀ mɛ ̀ pwi ̀ ɗ mɛ Isirayɛl ntɛ ̀ ɗ ɗi ̀ mɛɓɛɛ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ rini ̀ gha ̀ y mɛɛ mii , nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓii ɓɛ ɓɛbaŋi ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ , nsoo ̀ seŋi , nsoo ̀ jɛɛ , nsoo ̀ giy , nsoo ̀ ɓɔn , nsoo ̀ zi yii , a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ fɔ ̀ ni ɓyom ɓidɛŋ ɓi ɓi cee ɓin ̀ , gɛ ̀ n hɔnɗɛ ̀ ɗ , a ̀ ki fɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ di cɛɓ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Ki ̀ gwey ki ̀ ɓi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ asu ki ɓaa gɛ ajɛ ̀ m ; ki ̀ gwey ki ɓi ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ajɛ ̀ m ; ki ghay ɓum ɓɛ bee ̀ bɛ ̀ y .
Ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyo ̀ o ̀ ki pisɛɛ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ dɛm adɛŋ , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ponga ̀ ki ̀ kaa ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ ki ̀ say ɓi dɛm yii ̀ .
Nni a ̀ wooghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ a ̀ teka ̀ ɓi ki ̀ say lɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ ɓii ̀ peeghii dola ̀ bog ɓi bimiɗ a ̀ ŋwos . Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ romga ̀ min ɓɔ a dɛm yii ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ taa ̀ ni ̀ n a ̀ kpaga ̀ , nni a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ di ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ kaatii ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say , a ̀ ghɛn ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ di ɓɛ rɛrɛrii ɓi ki ̀ ɓa ̀ a ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ com ki ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ .
A ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Kɛ ̀ ɛna ki ̀ sali ̀ ɓi dɛm yɛm ̀ , n ̀ ɗi mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ le ̀ ɓi yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ .
Ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ɓi dɛm . Nni ŋwaa ̀ dɛm anɛ ̀ n a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ di ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ kaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ toroɓ , ri ̀ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ mɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛraa , a ̀ rom ɓɔ a dɛm yii ̀ , a ̀ ka ̀ g lɔŋ ɓɔ mɛ ̀ le ̀ ɓ mɛ a ̀ ka ̀ ka ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛmbog .
Di mɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛtan ̀ a ̀ cɛŋko ̀ a ̀ ti ja ̀ ŋbog nni a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ di ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ kaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛdɛŋ , a ̀ tanɛ ̀ n ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ di ɓɛ rɛrɛrii girig ɓi ki ̀ ɓa ̀ a ̀ , a ̀ tɔg ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓi ̀ ghagsii bimiɗ a ̀ ŋwos fɛ , kɛ ̀ ɓi say ?
Ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ pɛɛ ̀ zi ̀ nyi lɛ : Mum a ̀ a reŋii ɓi ɓisi lɛ ti ki nyi ki ̀ say . Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Kɛ ̀ ɛna girig ki ̀ sali ̀ ɓi dɛm yɛm ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ cɛŋko ̀ ki kpaga ̀ , ŋwaa ̀ dɛm a kpaa ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ a m ̀ ɓe ̀ gi ̀ i ̀ kum wii lɛ : Regi ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , u fa ɓɔ mɛ ̀ le ̀ ɓ maa , u ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓi ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ siito ̀ n , u ̀ siitɛ ̀ n ɓi ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ n ̀ tonto .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ say mɛkɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛtan ̀ a ̀ cɛŋko ̀ ɓɛ yugha ̀ , ɓɛ peeghi ɓɔ dola ̀ , dola ̀ .
Yɛɛ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ loka ̀ ki ̀ teri ̀ ɓɛ yugha ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ teɗ mɛ ̀ le ̀ ɓ maa , ɓɛ feki ̀ lɛ , mɛ ̀ le ̀ ɓ maa mɛ ri ɓii ̀ cee ̀ mɛ ɓɛro ɓɛmbog ; ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ɓɛ fala ̀ ka ̀ lɔŋ ɓɔ dola ̀ , dola ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ teka ̀ ka ̀ dola ̀ i ̀ nɛn , ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ŋɔ ̀ ŋɔ ̀ ŋi ̀ ɗi ŋwaa ̀ dɛm ,
ɓɛ kpaa lɛ : Ɓumɓɛ ɓaa siitɛɛ yi ̀ ɓɛ , ɓɔɔ sali lɔŋ hawo ̀ bog , wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ki pee ɓɔ com ki ̀ fog ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si ɓɛ tya ̀ a cenɛɛ lɛ , ri ̀ ki ̀ fɔli , ri ̀ ri ̀ tɔ ̀ n ɓi bimiɗ a ̀ ŋwos !
Nni ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛn ̀ lɛ : Reŋka ̀ ŋ ! N ̀ ki ̀ i ɓi ̀ wɔ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki n ̀ ɗe ̀ m . Mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ti , tya ̀ a wooghrɛɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ lɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ pee ̀ dola ̀ ?
Wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ tera ɓa ̀ loo ̀ mɛ ̀ le ̀ ɓ mɔɔ , u ghaa ̀ gh wɔ ̀ com kɔɔ . Mɛ ̀ yɛɛ kɔni lɛ m ̀ pee ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say anɛ a ̀ a siitɛɛ ki ̀ yu ̀ u lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ m ̀ pee wɔ ̀ .
Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ̀ nya lɛ , n ̀ ki ri ̀ i ̀ kum wɛ ̀ m yɛ ̀ ɛ ki kɔni mɛ ̀ ? Gi ̀ n ki ɓeɓi wɔ ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗɔɔtɛɛ nɗem ?
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓum ɓɛ siito ̀ n ɓɛ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ɓum ɓɛ bee ̀ bɛ ̀ y , ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ bee ̀ bɛ ̀ y ɓɛ ghay ɓum ɓɛ siito ̀ n .
Di Yeesus a ̀ ti lɛ a ɓɔg a Yorisalɛm , a ̀ teka ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ a dwi ̀ ɗ , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ di ɓɛ ti ɓi bee lɛ :
Ti ̀ ɓɔɔgh yɛɛ lɛ a Yorisalɛm , ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɛ ɓii ̀ faa ̀ Man a ̀ mum ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna , ɓɛ ren lɛ , ɓɛɛ wey nyi
ɓɛ ki ri ̀ nyi ɓii ̀ ka ̀ ɓi ri ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓɛɛ ki lɛ ɓɛ fengi ̀ nyi , ɓɛ ɓog nyi ki ̀ to ̀ n , ɓɛ ki kpan nyi ɓi kɔrɔs ; ki ̀ ɓan kifog , a ̀ ɓii ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛɛ ɓi ŋwos a ki ̀ raa .
Fɔɔnnɛ jɛɛ ɓɔn ɓɛ Zeɓede a ̀ tyo ̀ ŋdɛ ̀ nga ̀ Yeesus a nyoo ri ɓɔn ɓii , a ̀ ɓag mɛ ̀ ɗu ɓi zi lɛ a tɔg nyi ki ̀ ɓan .
Yeesus a ̀ tɔg nyi lɛ : La yɛɛ ri ? Giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Gherɛn lɛ ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛm ̀ ki ɓɔɓti ki kɛɛ ki lɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓi wee ̀ lem , roa ̀ mbog a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓi ki ̀ mɛŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kɔɔ .
Yeesus a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ lɛ : Ɓi yii ɓi com ki ɓi tɔtɔg mɛ ki ̀ n . Ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ cenɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓi nɔ ɓeŋ a ̀ nɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ nɔɔ ̀ ? Ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓaa ̀ g lɛ : Ti ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ti ̀ nɔ .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ki ri lɔŋ saaɗ lɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ nɔɔ ̀ ɓeŋ wɛ ̀ m , ki ̀ ɓan kifog a ̀ a mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ kalii ghɛn yɛɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓii ̀ kɔ ̀ rii ɓi wee ̀ lem nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓi ki ̀ mɛŋ ; mɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ mɛn ̀ mɛ ri mɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ mɛ ɓumɓɛ Ta ̀ a ̀ ta a ̀ pe ̀ gsɛ ̀ nga ̀ mɔ ɓisu wa ̀ a ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛmbog n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛ woka ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ɓɛ wog bim ri ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ɓɔn ɓɛ Zeɓede .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi yii lɛ , mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m mɛ ɓilɔ ̀ ŋ mɛ ti mɛ pye ̀ ngi ̀ ɓum mis ɗi ̀ n ̀ ci ̀ i ̀ zɛ ̀ n ; ɓɛ ̀ rɛli-asu ɓaa ɓɛ lamɓa ̀ g ɓɔ , ɓɛ ceesa ̀ g gin mɔ ̀ ɔ .
