Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ki ɓii ̀ kɔ ̀ ni lɛ a ɓa mi ̀ ni n ̀ ɗɛli ̀ a ̀ nɛ asu , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ n ̀ kpa ̀ n win ̀ .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ Man a ̀ mum a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ziinɛ , a ̀ a lɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ kiki nyi ɓi ̀ say , a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ lɔŋ lɛ , a say ɓum , a ̀ ki fa cɛɓ kii lɛ , a kweɗ ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Yɛɛ ɓɛ pɛsɛnga ̀ y a Zyeriko , coo ki ̀ tuu ki ɓum ki nɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ Yeesus .
Nni ɓɛ ̀ ɗyaŋɗya ̀ ŋ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ rɛn ɓɛ ɓɛ kɔkɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ŋwɔŋi ̀ wu bee , ɓɛ woka ̀ lɛ Yeesus yɛɛ ri ɓi ri ̀ ghaa ̀ gh , ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ kpaa jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ lɛ : Wɔ ̀ Man a Davit , wogha ɓa ̀ ɓisi nyii ̀ ghnyi ̀ g Kan .
Gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛn i ̀ kpɔmdɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ lɛ , ɓɛɛ maa ̀ rɛn , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓɔɔ teŋzi ̀ ti ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ ɓɛ kpaakpaa lɛ : Wɔ ̀ Man a ̀ Davit wogha ɓa ̀ ɓisi nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g Kan !
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ rɛli ̀ gha ̀ , a ̀ regi ̀ ɓɔ , a ̀ tɔg lɛ : Ɓi ̀ kɔ ̀ ngi lɛ , n ̀ ki mi ̀ ni cɛ ?
Ɓɛ ̀ ɗyaŋɗyaŋ ɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kpaa nyi lɛ : Kan , ti kɔ ̀ ngi lɛ , ti ghɛnɛ ̀ n .
