Nni ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ , ɓɛ ki lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ ki .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ sugti ̀ gha ̀ y lɛ : ri ̀ jɛɛ a ̀ ja ̀ ɗki ri ̀ man wii ̀ , ɓɛ ghay ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ɓyaa ɓi ja ̀ ɗki yi ̀ n , ɓɛ kɔɔ ̀ si ̀ Yeesus mii ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
