Yeesus a ̀ ca ̀ ɗka ̀ ɓɔ , a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ n ɓi ba ̀ n , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ lali ̀ a Bɛtanii .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ suu ̀ su ̀ gti ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ba ̀ n ɗi ̀ sariwa , nni za ̀ y i ̀ kɔ ̀ nga ̀ nyi .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ n ̀ ɗye ̀ m wu fi ̀ gyee ɓi bee , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n wɔɔ ; ki ̀ ɓan kifog , a ̀ tanɛ ̀ n wɔ tyɛn ɗi ̀ tyɛn , a ̀ kpaa ri ̀ fi ̀ gyee a ̀ nɛn lɛ : Wa ̀ a wumdii gɛ ɓi kiɗu ̀ n nsoo ̀ ki ̀ fog . Lɔŋ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kɔm ̀ kin ̀ , n ̀ ɗye ̀ m wu fi ̀ gyee wu ghaska ̀ ki ̀ wii ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ɓɛ kuura ̀ g ; ɓɛ tɔg lɛ : Lannɛ n ̀ ɗye ̀ m wu fi ̀ gyee wu wu wii fɛlɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ghaagh ?
Yeesus a ̀ ba ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : N ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni saaɗ lɛ , i ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , ɓi ̀ ki ɓa kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ nyoey ɓi nɗem , ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ , ɓi ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki n ̀ ki ̀ i fi ̀ gyee a ̀ nɛ ki , ɓi ̀ ki ɓa ti kɔm ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ , i ɓi ̀ kpaa do ̀ n i ̀ nɛ lɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ pɛsɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ kɛn ̀ ki ̀ kpi ̀ i ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y , ki kilɛ ̀ n fɔlɔɔ .
Com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ɓi ̀ ɓii ̀ tɔɔ ̀ gh ri ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n , ɓi ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ri ̀ kɔ .
Yeesus a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , nni yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ re ̀ e ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ ka ̀ ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓan , nni ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ ɓɛ yugha ̀ nyi ki ̀ tɔɔ ̀ gh lɛ : U ki ̀ ki ɓiɓan ɓi ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu ghɛn ? Ghɛn yɛɛ ki faa wɔ ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ win ̀ ? Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ :
Mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ tɔg ɓa ̀ girig mi ̀ ni n ̀ tɔɔ ̀ tɔɔgh wufog , i ɓi ̀ ɓa ̀ agh mɛ ̀ wɔ , fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ kpaa min mini ja ̀ ŋ inɛ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu nki ̀ ki ɓiɓan mii ̀ wu rii ̀ mɛ ̀ .
Ba ̀ ɓtis i ̀ Zyaŋ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ nya ki ̀ ɓan ki Bɛ ̀ ll yɛɛ feka ̀ gi ̀ n i ̀ ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓum ɓɛɛ feka ̀ ? Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ fiɓi ̀ gha ̀ n ̀ tɔɔ ̀ tɔɔgh win ̀ wɔɔ ɓɔ ri ̀ ɓɔ , ɓɛ kpaa lɛ : I ti ̀ ɓa ̀ agh nyi lɛ ba ̀ ɓtis i ̀ nɛ ̀ n i ̀ ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki Bɛ ̀ ll yɛɛ feka ̀ y , a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si ɓii ̀ tɔɔ ̀ gh lɛ , nni ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓi ̀ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi yɔ ̀ ?
I ti ̀ ki ɓa ̀ agh lɛ : I ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki ̀ ɓum ɓɛɛ feka ̀ , ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ risii gwi ̀ y i ̀ nɛ , ɓisuulɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ gherɛɛ lɛ Zyaŋ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ɓaka ̀ Yeesus lɛ : Ɓi ̀ sii yii ɓi n ̀ ko ̀ o ba ̀ ɓtis i ̀ nɛ ̀ n i ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ fe ̀ g ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , n ̀ ko ̀ o ri ̀ fe ̀ g ɗi ɓum . Yeesus a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ girig mɛ ̀ n ̀ kpaa ɓi mini ɓi-te ̀ ɗ aɗi nnɛ nki ̀ ki ɓiɓan ɓi .
Mi ̀ nii ghɛɛ ki ̀ ɓan ki la ̀ ? Lɛ , ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ yɛɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ dɛli ̀ ɓii ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ , nni a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ roa ̀ ntonto , a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Man , kɛ ̀ na mɛ ̀ ki ̀ say a dɛm gɛɛ ̀ nɛ .
Man a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : N ̀ -yin ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ nkɛni . Wɔ ̀ lɛ ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ri ̀ na ̀ n ɗii a ̀ ki kɛ ̀ n a dɛm .
Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ man a ̀ ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , a ̀ rom girig nyi a dɛm yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ romga ̀ roa ̀ ntonto , ŋwɔɓti a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : Ta ̀ a ̀ ta , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ , wɔ ̀ lɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ ki kɛ ̀ n .
Nni ɓi ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ɓɔɓti kin ̀ , roa ̀ be yɛɛ kigha ̀ ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi seŋi ̀ ? Ɓum ɓɛ Yeesus a ̀ teka ̀ da ̀ ɗki ̀ i ̀ nɛn ɓɛ ɓaa ̀ g lɛ : Man a ̀ n ̀ tonto yɛɛ kigha ̀ ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi seŋi ̀ . Yeesus a ̀ ki kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni saaɗ a ̀ ri ̀ kpaa lɛ , ɓɛ ̀ teri ̀ -la ̀ mpoŋ ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛ riɓa ̀ mɓa ̀ ɓɛ loogh gɛ ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ mi ̀ ni .
Ɓisuulɛ , Zyaŋ a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin , a ̀ re ̀ si ̀ mi ̀ ni bee i ̀ saaɗ , kɛ ̀ ɓi gherɛn nyi , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓɛ ̀ teri ̀ -la ̀ mpoŋ ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛ riɓa ̀ mɓa ̀ ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi . Nni nsoo ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ ghɛnga ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ɓi ̀ ki lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi mɛrem lɛ ɓi gherɛn nyi .
Wooghna da ̀ ɗki ̀ idɛŋ yɛ ̀ ɛnɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ yɛɛ sala ̀ dɛm yii ̀ , a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ y vii ̀ nyɛ ̀ mii ̀ , a ̀ ce ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n dɛm inɛ ̀ n ri ̀ gari , a ̀ ki ̀ wayɗ ɓi dɛm inɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ki toŋ ɓyoo mɛɛ wɔɔ . Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ fagha ̀ yɔ ̀ ɓi rɛŋti ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ vii ̀ nyɛ ̀ i ̀ ɓa ̀ ga ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ kɛs , nni a ̀ pɛ ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ɓum , a ̀ rom yi ̀ a ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛ a ̀ ca ̀ ɗka ̀ dɛm ri ̀ ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ rom ga ̀ ɓ yi ̀ i ̀ i ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛn ̀ ɓɛ ɓanga ̀ ka ̀ ɓumɓɛ a romga ̀ y ɓɛn ̀ , ɓɛ ki lɛ , ɓɛ ɓog roa ̀ nɛ ki ̀ to ̀ n , ɓɛ wey roa ̀ mbog , ɓɛ ki rogi roa ̀ ki ̀ raa gɔ ̀ g .
Nni ŋwaa ̀ dɛm a pɛ ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ y ti ̀ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ , ɓɛ ɓɛ ceegha ̀ ɓɛ n ̀ tonto ɓi ba ̀ li ̀ , a ̀ romdi ̀ lɔŋ ɓɔ a ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛ a dɛm , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ki ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ka ki ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛ n ̀ tonto .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ siitɛ ̀ nga ̀ min ki pɛ ̀ sii man wii ̀ , a ̀ rom nyi a ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛn ̀ , ri ̀ fe ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ , ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ ni ̀ ŋi man wii ̀ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛn ̀ ɓɛ mɛɛ ghɛnga ̀ y man a ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ kpaa wɔɔ ɓɔ ri ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Nnyɛɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓi ri dɛm i seŋi ̀ , yu ̀ una ti wey nyi , di fɔɔnnɛ dɛm yɛ ̀ ɛ woo ̀ ghrɛn ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ɓanga ̀ min man a ̀ nɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ pig nyi jɛ ̀ m i ̀ gari , ɓɛ wey .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛm a ri ̀ ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u , cɛ kɛɛ ̀ ki a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i ri ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛ a ̀ reɓsɛ ̀ nga ̀ dɛm ɓɛn ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ ?
Nni ɓɛ ɓaka ̀ Yeesus lɛ : A ̀ ɓii ̀ cuusii ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓin ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓ , a ̀ ki teɗ dɛm yii ̀ , a ̀ fa yɔ ̀ ɓi rɛnti ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ̀ nyi ɓii ̀ falaagh ga ̀ ɓ yi ̀ i ̀ i ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g di be ̀ g i ̀ kpaŋi .
