Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki n ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni lɛ , ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ pisii kilɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll a lɔ ̀ ŋkin , ɓɛ fa kɔ ri ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki ki ri ɓii ̀ wumi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɗu ̀ n ɓi ɓi ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ri ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll .
Mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ kpi ̀ i ɓi gɔ ̀ g i ̀ nɛ , a ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓumɓuni mii ̀ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ i ̀ kpi ̀ i ɓi nyoo , i ̀ turi ̀ nyi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ woka ̀ da ̀ ɗki ̀ yin , nnɛ ɓɛ yigha ̀ min lɛ ɓɔɔ ̀ ɓɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ kaaka ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ bee inɛ ɓɛɛ ɓan nyi ; wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛ riri ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ tuu ɓi ɓum ɓi ɓi ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ , lɛ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ Yeesus a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan .
Yeesus a ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ ɓi da ̀ ɗki ̀ a ̀ kpaa lɛ :
Ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyo ̀ o ̀ ki pisɛɛ ri ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗidɛŋ ɗi ɗi reŋɗɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ sɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ ɓi ri ̀ wɛy ɗi dɛli ̀ yi ̀ i ̀ .
Ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗin ̀ ɗi romga ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say lɛ ɓɛɛ reŋii ̀ ɓumɓɛ a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ a ki ̀ sɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ kin ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kɔnga ̀ ɓi lɛ ɓɛɛ yu .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ romdi ̀ gha ̀ ti ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛdɛŋ a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Kaliina ɓumɓɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ nɗeŋii lɛ : M ̀ mɛ lamgi gɛcom ; ɓɛ ̀ sani ̀ nya ɓɛ ̀ m , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ tuwe ɓyɛm ̀ ɓi fɔmɛn ɓi ti ɓi ̀ wolɛn , ɓiɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ti ɓi ̀ pe ̀ gsɛn , yu ̀ una ki ̀ sɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ɓumɓɛ a ̀ reŋɗɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɛn ̀ ɓɛ sɛɛti ̀ gha ̀ nɗee ̀ ghreŋi wii ɓɛ ghaaghra ̀ g . Roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ n a dɛm yii ̀ , roa ̀ mbog a ̀ kɛ ̀ n nyi du ̀ ne .
Ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛmbog ɓɛ sɛn ɓi ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛ rifo ̀ m , ɓɛ ɓog ɓɔ , ɓɛ ki cuusi ɓɔ .
Nni ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi woka ̀ bim , ɗi rom ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓii ɓɛ cuusi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ woli ̀ -ɓum ɓɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ ki ɗigsi ba ̀ n ya ̀ a ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi kpaagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓii lɛ : Ɓyom ɓi kisɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ ɓi ti ɓi ̀ pe ̀ gsɛn , wɔ ̀ lɛ a ̀ a ɓumɓɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ nɗeŋii , ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ reŋii .
Nni kɛ ̀ ɛna ɓi mɛ ̀ tanag mɛ ɓiɓa ̀ a ̀ , ɓi reŋii ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓi ̀ tanɛɛ wɔɔ , ɓɛɛ yu ki ̀ sɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ kɛm ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓii ɓɛn ̀ , ɓɛ saa ̀ tɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓa ̀ a ̀ , ɓɛ taŋzɛ ̀ n ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ y , lɛ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓum , ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ syeesyee ; fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓɛ ̀ ke ̀ n ɓɛ ronga ̀ ɓi naa i ̀ ki ̀ sɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ lɛ pisa .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ y ɓi naa lɛ ɗyɛɛ ghɛn ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ke ̀ n , nni ɗi ghɛnga ̀ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ wɔɔ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ki riwɛy .
Ɗi tɔg ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ : Reŋka ̀ ŋ wɛ ̀ m ! Lannɛ wa ̀ a ki ̀ i lɛ u ɗiŋii ̀ fɛ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ki riwɛy ? Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ com ki a kpaa ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi kpaagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓii lɛ : Ka ̀ ŋina mɛ ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ lɛ , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ ri ̀ ɓya ̀ g , ɓi pig nyi ɓi biri ̀ m i ̀ nɛ ɓi dan , ja ̀ ŋ i ̀ nɛ ɓum ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ re ̀ eree ̀ dɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ŋaa ̀ ŋa ̀ a ̀ di ̀ min .
Ɓisuulɛ , ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ reŋiyɛn , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , lɛsa ̀ g ɓɛɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ nɛn .
Fɔɔnnɛ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ dwi ̀ ɗ lɛ ɓɛɛ ghɛn ̀ i ̀ ghe ̀ y wu ɓɛɛ wɔɔ ̀ si Yeesus ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi nyimiɗ a kalii .
Nni ɓɛ romga ̀ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓi n ̀ ɗaŋ waa ri ̀ ɓɛ ɓi n ̀ ɗaŋ wu Eroodɛ , lɛ ɓɛɛ kali Yeesus lɛ : N ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g , ti ̀ yii lɔŋ lɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a kpaakpaa saaɗ , a ̀ ki re ̀ resi ɓum bee inɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n kɛ ̀ ɛ risi bimiɗ a ̀ mum , ɓisuulɛ , u ̀ yin ɓii ̀ seesee riɓa ɗi mum .
Wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ kali ɓa ̀ ɓisi ̀ , nko ̀ o ɓi ri ̀ ghɛn ɗyɔɔ , ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓis ɓi gherɛɛ lɛ ti peeghi la ̀ mpoŋ ̀ ri ̀ Kaaza ?
Wɔ ̀ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ yigha ̀ lɛ ɓɛ purii nyi ca ̀ g yɛɛri ɓi ɗu ̀ m , nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Mi ̀ ni ɓum ɓɛ fyɛɛ ̀ fyɛɛ ̀ ɓi ŋwɔm i ̀ ghe ̀ y ɓi ɗu ̀ m ɓɛ ! Ɓi fe ̀ eghfee ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n mɛ ̀ lɛ cɛ ?
Re ̀ siina mɛ ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ peeghi ̀ la ̀ mpoŋ ̀ mii ̀ ; fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ceesi ̀ gha ̀ nyi mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɛ firaŋ ̀ .
A ̀ tɔg ɓɔ lɛ : Ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki , ri ̀ ɗii ɗi , ghɛn yɛɛ ri ri ̀ ɓyɔ ?
Ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓaa ̀ g lɛ : Kaaza yɛɛ ri ri ̀ ɓyɔ . Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ min ɓɔ lɛ : Pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ziina lɔŋ ɓyom ɓi Kaaza ɗi ̀ Kaaza , ɓi ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ɗi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ woka ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɗin ̀ , nni ɓɛ kuura ̀ ka ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ɓɛ caɗ Yeesus , ɓɛ ghaaghra ̀ g .
Ŋwos ance ̀ m a ̀ nɛn , Ɓɛ ̀ sa ̀ du ̀ syɛŋ ɓɛ ɓɛɛ kpaaghi lɛ , com kidɛŋ ki yin lɛ , ri ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓilo ̀ ŋ , ɓɛ yugha ̀ y Yeesus a nyoo , ɓɛ tɔg nyi lɛ :
Nɗe ̀ sa ̀ g ! Moyis a ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , i ŋwaa ̀ wii , kɛ ̀ ɛ ca ̀ ɗ man , geni a ̀ baŋi ̀ a ̀ teɗ n ̀ kpɔɓ wii , a ̀ yay ɓɔn ɗi ̀ wɔ ɓi ɗii ɗi geni a ̀ nɛ a ̀ wii .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ sii n ̀ ɗi ̀ fɛ ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓi ri ̀ geni ɗyaa , ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , baŋi ̀ ri ̀ baŋi ̀ . Roa ̀ nsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn a wɔlɛ ̀ nga ̀ , a ̀ ki wu ; yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ri man , nni a ̀ ca ̀ ɗka ̀ n ̀ kpɔɓ wii ri geni .
Fɔɔnnɛ geni a ̀ ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ a wugha ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ man roa ̀ ki ̀ raa gi ̀ rig ; a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ ɓi roa ̀ ki ̀ taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ ki ̀ taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ɓum ki ̀ n , nnɛ giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ wugha ̀ girig .
Nni ŋwosi righe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓilo ̀ ŋ , giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ɓaa gɛ gili ghɛ ̀ n anɛ ɓi ki ̀ taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ɓum ki ̀ n ? Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yii ɓii ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi pwa ̀ a ̀ rɛɛ ; ɓisuulɛ ɓi ki ̀ i lɛ , kɛ ̀ ɓi wog ɓiɓan ɓi ɓi ri ɓi ̀ ka ̀ nɛn , kɛ ̀ ɓi ki yi ite ̀ ɗ wu Bɛ ̀ ll .
Lɛ ŋwosi righe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓilo ̀ ŋ , ɓɛ ̀ baŋi ̀ ɓaa wɔɔti ɓi ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ , ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki wɔɔti ɓɛbaŋi ̀ ; ɓɔɔ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓaa gɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓɛ ɓɛ ri aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
Ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki righe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓiloŋ , ɓi ̀ ɓa ̀ la ̀ ɓi kiɓan ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ mi ̀ ni lɛ :
N ̀ ɗi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ Abiraham , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ Isag ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ Yakɔɓ ? Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ yin Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓi ̀ loŋ a ̀ ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ̀ cem .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum i ̀ wo ̀ ka ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓi Yeesus ɓin ̀ , ri ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ɗii ɗi komga ̀ ɓɔ mɛ ̀ rem .
Nni Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ taŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ di ɓɛ mɛ wog lɛ , Yeesus a ̀ a si ̀ mi Ɓɛ ̀ sa ̀ du ̀ syɛŋ ŋwɔm .
Fɔɔnnɛ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɔ , ki ki ɓagha ̀ coo n ̀ -yii ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna , ki yugha ̀ ki fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛɛ Yeesus ri ̀ ntɔɔ ̀ tɔɔgh lɛ :
N ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g , ɓi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , kibe kɛɛ cee ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Ki ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ki kɛɛ kalag lɛ : Keesi Kan Bɛ ̀ ll wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ri ̀ n ̀ ɗem wɔɔ wuce ̀ m , ri ̀ n ̀ ghay wɔɔ wuce ̀ m , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ yiti ̀ mɔɔ mɛce ̀ m .
Kɛɛ ri ki ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ki asu , ki ki cee ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓimbog ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ki kiɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ki pisɛɛ kin ̀ ki ri lɛ : Keesi romum a ̀ nɛ wɔ ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog yɛ ̀ ɛ wɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ .
Ɓi ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ɓidɔ ̀ gsɛna kin ̀ , nnɛ ri ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɗi Moyis ɗi ̀ ce ̀ m , ri ̀ mɛ ɓɛkpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan , mɛ sasaghii .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ taŋzɛn , Yeesus a ̀ tɔka ̀ ɓɔ n ̀ tɔɔ ̀ tɔɔgh lɛ :
Mi ̀ nii kpaaghi la ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki Kiris ? A ̀ ri ̀ man a ̀ ghɛn ? Ɓɛ ɓaka ̀ nyi lɛ : A ̀ ri ̀ man a ̀ Davit .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Nni lannɛ Davit a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ nyi lɛ Kan , di N ̀ ghay a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ faa nyi ɗyomzɛ ̀ n , yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ :
Kan a ̀ a n ̀ kpaa Kan wɛ ̀ m lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ri mɛ ̀ fɛ ɓi wee ̀ lem , a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ foŋi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ be ̀ na ̀ bena ɓɔɔ a mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ mɔɔ zi .
Nni i Davit a ̀ mɛ regi nyi lɛ Kan , lannɛ a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ ɓa ti ̀ man a ̀ Davit ?
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ lɛ a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi ntɔɔ ̀ tɔɔgh win ̀ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi . Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓi ŋwos anɛ ̀ n ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ ghɛɛsi ̀ gha ̀ ti ̀ ɓi lɛ a tɔg nyi n ̀ tɔɔ ̀ tɔɔgh .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii lɛ :
Ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ri Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ , ɓɛ ri ri n ̀ tɛ ̀ g wulɛ , ɓɛɛ resag ɓum ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Moyis .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ , ɓi ̀ wog , ɓi ̀ ki ɓe ̀ ŋ ɓiɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓɛ kpaa mi ̀ ni ; ki ̀ ɓan kifog , kɛ ̀ ɓi nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti mɛki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ maa , ɓisuulɛ , ɓɔɔ ̀ kakali ri ŋwɔm , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ com ki ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ .
Ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kagi ̀ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ iri ̀ ɗ ɓi mɛtɛ ̀ g di ɓɛɛ ̀ tɛ ̀ ɛghtɛgsi ̀ ɓumkifog , ɓɔmiɗ ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ gherɛn lɛ di ɓaa nyɛ ̀ ŋi mɛ ̀ tɛ ̀ g mɛn ̀ nsoo ̀ ri ̀ man a ̀ ca ̀ g .
Ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ɓi ri lɔŋ lɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ ghɛn bɔ ; ɓɛ ti ɓɛ sina ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ ka ̀ nɗa ɓɛ po ̀ gpo ̀ g ɓi mɛ ̀ to ri ̀ ɓi ɓya ̀ g , ɓɛ ki ra ̀ ɓsag mɛkeɓ maa mɛ ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ .
Ɓɛ ti ɓɛ keesa ̀ g mɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ mɛ asu , di ɓɛ kɛɛ ki ̀ sɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ , ɓi naa yi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ kɔra ̀ g ɓi mɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ mɛ n ̀ tonto .
Ki kɔngi ̀ girig ɓɔ lɛ , ɓɛɛ too ̀ to ̀ gsi ̀ ɓɔ ri ̀ coo nyaasɛ ̀ n ɓi gwi ̀ y , ɓɛ ki rereŋi ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ mi ̀ nii ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ki gherɛɛ lɛ , ɓɛɛ rereŋi mi ̀ ni lɛ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɓisuulɛ , ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ ri n ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g bog , minii ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ̀ ki ɓa ti ɓi ri ̀ geni .
Kɛ ̀ ɓi reŋi ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ fɛ ɓi ziinɛ lɛ ta ̀ a ̀ ta wi ̀ n , ɓisuulɛ , ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ Seŋi bog lɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
Kɛ ̀ ɓi ki gherɛn lɛ , ɓɛɛ reŋi mi ̀ ni lɛ , ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ si ̀ ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ ri n ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ si ̀ wi ̀ n bog nnyɛɛ ri lɛ Kiris .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ n ̀ ɗɛli ̀ -asu ̀ ɓi nɗaŋ win , a ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say win ̀ .
Mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓɔgsii nyimiɗ , ɓɛ ri nyi ɓii ̀ sɛɛ ̀ dii ; roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ sɛɛ ̀ dii nyimiɗ ɓi zi , ɓɛ ɓɔgsi ̀ nyi .
Nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ , fyɛɛ ̀ fyɛɛ ̀ ɓi ̀ ŋwɔm i ̀ ghe ̀ y ɓi ɗu ̀ m , ɓisuulɛ ɓi ghegheg ɓum lɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ɗiŋi ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyo ̀ o ̀ ; mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ kɛ ̀ ɓi ɗiŋi mii ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɓi ki gherɛn lɛ , ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ ɓɛɛ ɗiŋi mii ̀ , ɓɛɛ ɗiŋi ̀ . [
