Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ ɓɛ samga ̀ ka ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey , mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ tɔg nyi lɛ : Kan , mɛ ̀ nya gi ̀ n ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ tya ̀ a pu ̀ u ̀ sɛɛ ca ̀ g ɓɛɛ ̀ nyi taasa ̀ bog yɛɛ ri mɛ ̀ ɓii ̀ ka ̀ ɓi .
Man a ̀ mum a ̀ ɓii ̀ wii ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kanga ̀ lɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ wii ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ nyi ɓii ̀ ka ̀ ɓi ! Ki ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ rɔɔ ɓisuu ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ yalɛn .
Nni Zyudas a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ki ̀ tɔ ̀ kɔ ̀ kin ̀ , a ̀ teka ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Raɓi ̀ , mɛ ̀ nya gi ̀ n ? Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Wa ̀ a kpaa ̀ .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ɗiɗi ̀ gha ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ teka ̀ bi ̀ rɛs , a ̀ fa Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ɓɛg min yɔ ̀ , a ̀ fa ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Terina , ɓi ɗi , nyoo yɛ ̀ m yɛ ̀ ɛ lɛ .
Nni a ̀ teeti ̀ gha ̀ ɓeŋ , a ̀ mɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ g a ̀ fa Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ceesi nyi ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Nɔɔna ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m
ɓisuulɛ bwaɓ yɛm ̀ yɛɛ ri , bwaɓ yi ɓi ri ̀ ra ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɗi ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , yi yi ri ɓii ̀ kpaŋi ̀ ɓisuu ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ɓisuu ricenɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓiɓe .
Nni mɛ ̀ n ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni lɛ , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , ma ̀ a nɔti ɓi mɛrɔ ̀ g mɛ vii ̀ nyɛ ̀ , a ̀ kpaŋ ŋwos anɛ ti ̀ nɔtii gɛ nyɔɔnyɔn a ̀ ri ̀ nɔ lɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Seŋi wɛ ̀ m .
Ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ lɛ ɓɛ mɛ gha ̀ ɓ tyem ti ɓɛsam ̀ fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ɓɔka ̀ min ɓi do ̀ n i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ o ̀ li ̀ vyee .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g lɛ : Ɓi-ru wu gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ fi ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓisu win ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , lɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : N ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ woli ̀ m ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yii yice ̀ m yi saa ̀ tɛ ̀ n .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ ri ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗyɛm ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ loo ̀ gh ki ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ri mi ̀ ni a Galile .
Nni Pyɛɛri a ̀ teka ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : N ̀ soo ̀ wa ̀ a ri ̀ fi ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓisuu ɓisi ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , wa ̀ a ɓa ɓi fiɓa ̀ g ɓisu wɛ ̀ m .
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : N ̀ kalii wɔ ̀ ɓi saaɗ lɛ , ɓi-ru wɔm ̀ wu , u ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓii ̀ roo ̀ zɛɛ gɛ ̀ n yiraa , di n ̀ lem a ̀ zag a ka rɔŋ ɓi .
Pyɛɛri a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ nyi lɛ : N ̀ so ̀ o ̀ ki kpaŋi lɛ n ̀ wu ɓɛɛ wɔ ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ , ma ̀ a roo ̀ zɛn ɓi wɔ . Ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛmbog ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ girig fɔlɔɔ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓi ja ̀ ŋ ɗii lɛ Gɛsemane , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Kɔ ̀ riina fɛ , mɛ ̀ n ̀ ka kɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzaagh fɛnii .
Nni a ̀ teka ̀ lɛ ri ̀ Pyɛɛri , ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ɓɔn ɓɛ Zeɓede , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ wog ɗi n ̀ ɗemi-kɛŋɛn , ɗi ̀ i ̀ ris .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ min ɓɔ lɛ : N ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ɗemi-kɛŋɛn wu wu ri lɛ wu wey mɛ ̀ , nni rɔ ̀ ɓina fɛ , ɓi kɔri cem nɗaŋ , ri mɛ ̀ .
Nni a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ di ̀ gha ̀ asu lɛsa ̀ g , a ̀ kpi ̀ ɓi zi guɓu ̀ g , a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzi ̀ lɛ : Ta ̀ a ̀ ta wɛ ̀ m i bee ya ̀ a ri ̀ lɛ i ̀ ɓa , lɛ ɓeŋ a ̀ nɛ a raɓsɛn mɛ ̀ , nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ , kɔ ̀ ɔ ki ̀ rikɔ ̀ n ɗyɛm ̀ , lɔŋ ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗyɔɔ ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi ki ̀ ya .
Nni a ̀ sugtigha ̀ y a ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g , a ̀ tanɛ ̀ n di ɓaa cuu tilo ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ tɔka ̀ Pyɛɛri lɛ : Ɓi yin yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ ɓi ̀ cenɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓi kɔri cem ɗi mɛ ̀ bimiɗ a ̀ hawo ̀ ?
Kɔ ̀ riina cem , ɓi ̀ ki ɓɔ ̀ ɔɓɔ ̀ ŋzi ̀ lɛ , kɛ ̀ ɓi tanɛn ri mɛ ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn ; lɛ n ̀ ghay wu mum wu ri ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , nyoo i ̀ mɛ ̀ mu ̀ u ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ .
Ɓi gɛ ̀ n i ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , a ̀ ra ̀ ɓsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ti ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g , a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋza ̀ g lɛ : Ta ̀ a ̀ ta wɛ ̀ m , i ki ri lɔŋ lɛ ɓeŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ a pɛ ̀ sɛn ɓi di nnɔɔ ɓi nyi , ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗyɔɔ ɗyɛɛ kilɛn .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ sugti ̀ gha ̀ y a ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g a ̀ tanɛ ̀ n ti ̀ ɓɔ ɓi fi ̀ lo , lɛ fi ̀ lo fi ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓɔ ɓi mis .
Nni a ̀ ca ̀ a ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ , a ̀ ra ̀ ɓsɛ ̀ n ti ̀ , a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi gɛ ̀ n i ki ̀ raa , a ̀ ɓi ̀ i ̀ ti ̀ lɔŋ ɓiɓan ɓi a ̀ loka ̀ ki ̀ kpaa .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ sugti ̀ gha ̀ y a ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Mi ̀ nii ri lɔŋ ɓi fi ̀ lo , ɓi ̀ fɔɔ ̀ fɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ sɛ ̀ n ? Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki lɛ , ɓɛɛ fa Man a ̀ mum ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe kɛɛ kpaŋi lɛ .
Pɛ ̀ sɛɛna aɗyoo ti kɛn ̀ , lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ka ̀ kaɓ mɛ a ̀ tii ̀ .
Yeesus a ̀ kaka a ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ fɔlɔɔ , nni Zyudas a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ , a ̀ gha ̀ ska ̀ ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ . A ɓagha ̀ y ri ̀ coo kituu ki ɓum ki ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ romga ̀ y ; ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ yugha ̀ y lɛ ri ̀ ga ̀ fa ̀ g , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ geŋ .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ka ̀ ɓka ̀ nyi a ̀ fagha ̀ ɓɔ ki ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓi ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ di n ̀ lɔ ̀ ri , ɓi ̀ yi lɛ nnyɛɛ ri , ɓi ̀ ɓan .
Fɔɔnnɛ Zyudas a ̀ gha ̀ ska ̀ ki ̀ tyo ̀ ŋdɛɛ Yeesus a nyoo , a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Raɓi ̀ , n ̀ to ̀ gsii wɔ ̀ , a ̀ ki lɔ ̀ ɗ nyi .
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Reŋka ̀ ŋ wɛ ̀ m ! Ki ̀ ya com ki wa ̀ a yu ̀ u ki ̀ ki ̀ i . Ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ yuiy min , ɓɛ sɛn ɓi Yeesus , ɓɛ ɓan .
Ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ Yeesus , ki nimɓɛ ̀ nga ̀ , ki sɔŋi ̀ i ̀ ga ̀ fa ̀ g ɓi ɗyaŋ , ki kpɛɛ ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say a n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ -ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey , i ̀ ree ̀ wu lɛy .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : Pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ga ̀ fa ̀ g yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓi ɗyaŋ , lɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ teri ga ̀ fa ̀ g , ɓɛ ɓii ̀ wii ̀ lɛ ga ̀ fa ̀ g .
U ̀ yii ɓi lɛ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ , i n ̀ tɔɔgh Ta ̀ a ̀ ta wɛ ̀ m lɛ , a ghɛɓsi mɛ ̀ , a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ rom yi ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓigomi ̀ nɛ ɓi ̀ tuu lɛ ɓi ̀ tuu .
Lannɛ ri ̀ kali ̀ ɗi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ɗi ri min ɓii ̀ roni ̀ ? Lɛ kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a kalag lɛ , ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ lɛɛ fɔɔlɔɔ .
Ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ innɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ tuu ki ɓum ki ̀ n lɛ : Ɓi ̀ ghɛɛ mɛ ̀ lɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ zyaa ̀ zyaa , nni ɓi ̀ yu ̀ u yi ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ga ̀ fa ̀ g ri ̀ ɓi ̀ geŋ lɛ ɓi ɓan ̀ mɛ ̀ ? Kɔm ̀ lɛ , mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗi ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛ ̀ ŋwos ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m n ̀ ɗe ̀ e ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɓum , kɛ ̀ ɓi ki ɓan ̀ mɛ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ fɔlɔɔ lɛ di ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ kanga ̀ ɓyɛɛ ron ̀ . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ rini ̀ gha ̀ nyi ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , ɓɛ ghɛŋɗa ̀ g .
Ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓanga ̀ Yeesus ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ ri ̀ nyi yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ -ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey a ̀ nɛ lɛ Kayif ; wɔɔ nnɛ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓɛ taŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ .
Pyɛɛri a ̀ nɔɔnɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ nyi fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ , a ̀ kpaŋ ɓi n ̀ lɛmɓog wu n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ -ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey , a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ lɛ , a ̀ ghɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri ɓii ̀ Syɔni ̀ .
Ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey , ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓi sa ̀ ne ̀ di ̀ rɛŋ , ɓɛ kaaka ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓɛpwa ̀ a ̀ ki ɓɛɛ tiri Yeesus ɓi ɗi lɛ ɓɛɛ wey nyi .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ ɓi kiɓan ki ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ lɛ ɓɛ kpaa , nsoo ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ rɛli ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ feg ki ̀ pwaa ̀ Yeesus ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi nyo ̀ o ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ bee ; fɔɔnnɛ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ siitɛ ̀ nga ̀ y ki ̀ yu ̀ u ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ , ɓɛ kpaa lɛ :
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ a n ̀ kpaa lɛ : N ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ n ̀ wa ̀ a ̀ naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , n ̀ ki pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi yɔ ̀ ki toŋi ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛraa .
Nni n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ -ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey a pɛ ̀ sɛn ̀ ga ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ a ̀ tɔg Yeesus lɛ : Ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ kpaa ki ɓɛ raɗ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ yo ̀ g , u ̀ yin ɗi com ki ɓa ̀ ghɛn ɓɔ ?
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Yeesus a ̀ maama ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ lɔŋ . Nni n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ -ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey a ̀ tɔgti ̀ gha ̀ nyi lɛ : Ɓi ɗii ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ cencem n ̀ tɔɔgh lɛ u ̀ kali ɓi ̀ si u ̀ ki ka ̀ nɛn bɛ ̀ ɗ n ̀ ko ̀ o wɔ ̀ yɛɛ ri Kiris Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Wa ̀ a kpaa ̀ . Nni n ̀ ki kpaatii mi ̀ ni lɛ , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , ɓi ̀ ri ghɛn Man a ̀ mum di a ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔrii ɓi wee ̀ lem a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wuce ̀ m , ɓi ̀ ki ghɛɛ ̀ di nyi di a yu ̀ yuiy aɗyoo ɓi ɓi ̀ kwi ̀ ɗ .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ -ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey a ̀ woka ̀ bim , a ̀ gha ̀ ski ̀ ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ɓi a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɓyɔ ɓi nyoo , a ̀ ki kpaa lɛ : Ɓi ̀ woogh ɓi yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ fengii Bɛ ̀ ll , ti ̀ yin lɛ ti ̀ kaati ̀ ɓɛ ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛdɛŋ , lɛ mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ ɓi ̀ woogh ti ̀ fena ti a ̀ fengii Bɛ ̀ ll , nni ɓi ̀ kpaa la ?
Ɓum ɓɛmbog ɓɛ ɓaa ̀ g lɛ : A ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ wey .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ tuugha ̀ ka ̀ Yeesus ti ̀ tyɛɛ ̀ ɓisu , ɓɛ ki rogi nyi ɓi ̀ kam ; ɓɛro ɓɛmbog ɓɛ ɓoɓog nyi mɛ ̀ ɓɛn di ɓɛɛ kpaakpaa lɛ :
Me ̀ sii , re ̀ mi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓoogh wɔ ̀ , u kali ɓi ̀ si .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Pyɛɛri a ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓi n ̀ lɛm ̀ ɓog fɔɔnnɛ giɓ adɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say a ̀ yugha ̀ y nyi a ̀ nyoo , a kpaa lɛ : Wɔ ̀ ɔ n ̀ ɗi ̀ gi ̀ ri ̀ g ɓi n ̀ ɗaŋ wu Yeesus a ̀ nɛ a Galile .
Ki ̀ ɓan ki ̀ fog Pyɛɛri a ̀ roo ̀ zɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ɓi mis mɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : N ̀ -yii ɓi com ki u kɔ ̀ nkɔn kin ̀ lɛ u kpaa ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ nkɛni a ri ̀ ɗigi ̀ ɗi gari , giɓ adɛŋ a ̀ ghɛn nyi , a ̀ kpaa ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ lɛ : ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ a n ̀ ɗi ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ ri Yeesus a ̀ nɛ a Naazarɛt .
Nni Pyɛɛri a ̀ roo ̀ zɛ ̀ nga ̀ ti ̀ nyi , a ̀ ka ̀ nɛ ̀ n bɛ ̀ ɗ , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : N ̀ -yii ɓi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ maa ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ , nni ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ ɓɛ tyoŋdɛ ̀ nga ̀ y ɓɛ kpaa Pyɛɛri lɛ : Ki ri lɔŋ saaɗ lɛ , u ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓumɓɛ ̀ n , ɓisuulɛ , ri ̀ to ̀ to ̀ g ɗyɔɔ ɗi resii fɔlɔɔ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Pyɛɛri a ̀ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ka ̀ a ̀ ka ̀ na ̀ g ɗi bɛ ̀ ɗ , di a kpaakpaa lɛ , i m ̀ pwa ̀ a , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ cɛ ̀ m mɛ ̀ ; n ̀ -yii ɓi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n . N ̀ lem a ̀ zag a ghaa ̀ gh ki ̀ rɔŋi ̀ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kɔm ̀ kin ̀ .
Nni Pyɛɛri a ̀ yi ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ min yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ , u ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓii ̀ roo ̀ zɛɛ gɛ ̀ n yiraa , di n ̀ lem a ̀ zag a ̀ ka rɔŋ ɓi ; fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpaga ̀ gari a ̀ re ̀ n a ̀ si ̀ gta ̀ g .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ duri i tanga ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ ɓɛ taŋzɛ ̀ n ki ̀ tɔ ̀ kɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ wey Yeesus .
Ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ mɛ ka ̀ ŋ nyi bɛn , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi yɛ ̀ ɛ gɔmi ̀ na ̀ a ̀ nɛ lɛ Pilat .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Zyudas a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ka ̀ ɓka ̀ Yeesus a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ reni lɛ ɓɛɛ wey nyi , n ̀ ɗem wii wu fa nyi bɛ ̀ lɛn , a ̀ lemgi ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗii a ̀ ki sugtii ̀ ki ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zii tiraŋ ̀ ri ̀ tin ɗi ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ti ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ fagha ̀ nyi ,
a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ki ̀ i ki ̀ ɓe lɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ka ̀ ɓi bwaɓ yi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ ɓe ; nni ɓɛ ɓaka ̀ nyi lɛ : Ki ̀ ɓan kis ki yin mii ̀ , wɔ ̀ nnɛ ki seesee .
Zyudas a ̀ ɗyɛɛgha ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ kpaŋ a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ su ̀ rɛɛ .
Ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ɓɛ ɓadɛ ̀ nga ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ki kpaa lɛ : Ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓis ɓi gherɛɛ ɓi lɛ , ti teɗ ri ̀ kuu ɗi mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni ɗin ̀ , ti ɓutɛn ɓi mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɛ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , lɛ mɛ ri ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɛ bwaɓ .
Ɓɛ nyolɛ ̀ nga ̀ , ɓɛ yɔɔsi ̀ ŋwɔm wufog lɛ ɓɛɛ teɗ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɛ ̀ n , ɓɛɛ laa ̀ g ki ̀ den ki zi mii ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ -ye ̀ ŋi ̀ -fyo ̀ o ̀ , kɛɛ ɓa dɛm i zɔ ̀ ŋ i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ke ̀ n ɓɛ ɓum .
Kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓɛ roo ̀ gha ̀ dɛm inɛ ̀ n lɛ dɛm i bwaɓ a ̀ kpaŋ gɛɛ ̀ nɛ .
Fɔɔnnɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan a ̀ nɛ lɛ Zyeremii a ̀ kpaagha ̀ i ̀ ronga ̀ ; lɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Ɓɛ teka ̀ ti ̀ raŋ ̀ ri ̀ tin ɗi ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ , ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni i ̀ nɛ ɓɔn ɓɛ Isirayɛl ɓɛ renga ̀ ɓi n ̀ to wi ̀ i ̀ ,
ɓɛ ki fa mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɛ ̀ n ɓi ri ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ sɛ ̀ n ɗi dɛm i n ̀ -ye ̀ ŋi ̀ -fyo ̀ o ̀ , lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Kan a ̀ siŋdɛ ̀ nga ̀ mɛ ̀ .
Yeesus a ̀ rɛli ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ m ɓi mis mɛ gɔmi ̀ na ̀ ; gɔmi ̀ na ̀ a ̀ tɔg nyi lɛ : U ̀ ri ̀ nya ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ? Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : Wɔ ̀ yɛɛ kpaa .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ , a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓi com ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ɓɛgwey ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ rara ̀ ɗ ri ̀ nyi .
Nni Pilat a ̀ tɔka ̀ min lɛ : U ̀ woogh ɓi ɓiɓan ɓi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ kpaa ɓi ɓɛ ra ̀ ɗ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ ?
Yeesus a ̀ mi ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , gɔmi ̀ na ̀ a ̀ kuura ̀ g lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Ɓi ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ ti Paska ̀ ti ̀ ce ̀ m , gɔmi ̀ na ̀ a ̀ a n ̀ ti a ̀ ca ̀ ɗki ̀ ki ̀ mbu ̀ ŋ ki ̀ fog , ki ɓum ɓɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ ɓɛ tɔɔgh lɛ , a caɗ .
Ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ , ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ ɓum lɛ ̀ ɛgwey ɓɛ yi ̀ gha ̀ , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ mbu ̀ ŋ ɗii lɛ : Ɓaraɓas .
Nni Pilat a ̀ tɔka ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ taŋzɛn lɛ : Ghɛn innɛ ɓi kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ ncaɗ mi ̀ ni , Ɓaraɓas gi ̀ n Yeesus a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɗii lɛ Kiris ?
Pilat a ̀ tɔka ̀ fɔlɔɔ lɛ a ̀ yigha ̀ lɔŋ saaɗ lɛ , ɓɛ sɔmɛ ̀ nga ̀ Yeesus ɓi n ̀ ɗemi-ya ̀ aka aɗyoo .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pilat a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ kaka ɓi naa ̀ -ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ m , nni gil a romga ̀ y mum lɛ a kpaa nyi lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ɔ gha ̀ ɓ gaa i ̀ nɛ ɓi saaɗ a ̀ mum a ̀ nɛ ̀ n , lɛ ɓi-ru wu gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , ɓi ̀ dɛ ̀ ndɛm ɓyaa yeesii mɛ ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓisu wi ̀ i ̀ .
Ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ toosi ̀ gha ̀ gɛmum a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ tɔg Pilat lɛ a caɗ Ɓaraɓas , Yeesus i ̀ nnɛ ɓɛɛ wey .
Nni gɔmi ̀ na ̀ a ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ , a ̀ tɔg ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ɓum ki , ghɛn innɛ ɓi kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ ncaɗ ? Ɓɛ ɓaa ̀ g lɛ : Ɓaraɓas .
Pilat a ̀ tɔgti ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Nghas ̀ min la ri Yeesus a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɗii lɛ Kiris ? Ɓɔɔ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓaa ̀ g lɛ : Ɓɛɛ kpan ̀ nyi ɓi kɔrɔs .
Gɔmi ̀ na ̀ a ̀ tɔgti ̀ lɛ : Ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki kiɓan aɗi kɛɛ ̀ ki a ̀ ki ̀ i ? Ɓɛ syaadi ̀ ti ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ lɛ : Ɓɛɛ kpan ̀ nyi ɓi kɔrɔs .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pilat a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ , mɛ ̀ tɔɔ ̀ gtɔɔgh mii mɛ ghɛɓsii ɓi com , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ki ̀ yoo ̀ yo ̀ o ̀ kɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ nkɛn asu n ̀ kɛ ̀ nkɛnɛn , nni a ̀ teka ̀ mɛ ̀ nig , a ̀ so ̀ gtɛ ̀ n ɓya ̀ g ɓi mis mɛ gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : N ̀ -yin lɛ , n ̀ teɗ ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ki ɓi bwaɓ yi saaɗ a ̀ mum a ̀ nɛ , ki ̀ ɓan kii ki seesee lɔŋ mini .
Nni ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ɓaka ̀ lɛ : Bwaɓ yii yɛɛ kɛn ̀ ɓi ̀ si ɓi n ̀ to , lɛ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si ri ̀ ɓɔn ɓis .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ca ̀ ɗka ̀ min ɓɔ Ɓaraɓas , a ̀ reɓsi ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓog Yeesus ɓi ki ̀ to ̀ n , a ̀ fa min ɓɔ nyi lɛ ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ nyi ki ̀ kpani ̀ ɓi kɔrɔs .
Ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ gɔmi ̀ na ̀ ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ ri ̀ Yeesus ɓi naa i ̀ gɔmi ̀ na ̀ , n ̀ ɗaŋ waa wuce ̀ m wu kɔmzɛ ̀ n nyi .
Ɓɛ sɔŋi ̀ Yeesus ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ , ɓɛ waasi ̀ nyi ri ̀ ga a ̀ mɓa ̀ ŋ lɛ pɔɔŋ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ toga ̀ ta ̀ m a ̀ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ɓɛ waasi ̀ nyi ɓi n ̀ to , ɓɛ teɗ ki ̀ syo ̀ ŋ , ɓɛ fa nyi ɓi ca ̀ g ki wee ̀ lem , ɓɛ ɓag min nyi mɛ ̀ ɗu asu , ɓɛ fee ̀ fe ̀ ngi ̀ nyi ɗi ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa lɛ : Ti ̀ to ̀ gsii wɔ ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ tuutu ̀ u ̀ gha ̀ nyi ti ̀ tyɛɛ ̀ , ɓɛ teɗ ki ̀ syo ̀ ŋ , ɓɛ ɓoo ̀ ɓo ̀ ki ̀ nyi ɓi n ̀ to .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ di ɓɛ mɛ fengi nyi fɔlɔɔ , nni ɓɛ sɔŋi ̀ gha ̀ nyi ri ̀ ga a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ waasi ̀ gha ̀ nyi , ɓɛ pɛɛ ̀ zi ̀ nyi ̀ ki ̀ waasii ɓila ̀ a ̀ ɓii , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ min ɗi nyi lɛ ɓɛɛ kpan ɓi kɔrɔs .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kpaŋkpa ̀ ŋga ̀ y ɓi naa i ̀ gɔmi ̀ na ̀ , nni ɓɛ tuusɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a Sirɛn ɗii lɛ Simɔn , ɓɛ kaŋ ̀ nyi lɛ a tɛg kɔrɔs a ̀ Yeesus .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kpaga ̀ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ lɛ Gɔlgɔta , yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ , ja ̀ ŋ i ki ̀ tɛtɛg ki n ̀ to ,
nni ɓɛ fagha ̀ nyi mɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ g mɛ ɓɛ ɓiga ̀ ri ̀ com ki lo ̀ lolɛn lɛ a nɔ ; yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ɓoɓti ̀ gha ̀ mɔ , a ̀ ɓe ̀ n ki ̀ nɔɔ ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kpanga ̀ nyi ɓi kɔrɔs , nni ̀ ɓɛ ɓoka ̀ n ̀ tɔ ̀ ŋ lɛ ɓɛɛ kaɓɓɛn ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ɓii . Ki kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ fɔlɔɔ lɛ kɛɛ ɓa lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan a kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Ɓɛ kaɓɓɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ɓyɛm ̀ , ɓɛ ɓog n ̀ tɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi jɔmpa ̀ s wɛ ̀ m .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ kɔri ̀ gha ̀ wɔɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓeŋɓeŋ nyi .
Ɓɛ kanga ̀ n ̀ too-kiɓan wu ɓɛ wola ̀ nyi mii ̀ , ɓi ki ̀ ɓoŋ ɓɛ foŋ nyi kɔ a n ̀ to ; azi anɛ ɓɛ wola ̀ nyi mii ̀ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ lɛ : Roa ̀ nɛ nnyɛɛ ri Yeesus , ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n .
Ɓɛ kpanga ̀ ɓɛ ̀ zyaa ̀ zyaa ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ ɗi Yeesus ; roa ̀ nɛ nyi ɓi wee ̀ lem , roa ̀ nɛ ɓi ki ̀ mɛŋ .
Ɓɛ ̀ ghaa ̀ gh-bee ɓɛ fee ̀ fe ̀ nga ̀ ka ̀ nyi , di ɓɛɛ ̀ ghegheri ɗi mɛ ̀ to .
Ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ lɛ : Wa ̀ a ̀ nɛ u kalag lɛ , u ̀ ri ̀ lɛ u ̀ wa ̀ a ̀ ghi ̀ naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , u ̀ ki pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi yɔ ̀ kitoŋi ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛraa , ghɛɓsi min wɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ , i u ̀ yii lɛ u ̀ ri ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , sɛnay ɓi kɔrɔs a ̀ nɛ ̀ n .
Ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ wɔwɔ ̀ la ̀ girig nyi di ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa lɛ :
A ̀ a n ̀ ghɛɛghɛ ̀ ɓsi ̀ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ , wɔ ̀ lɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa ri bee inɛ , a ghɛɓsi nyimiɗ , a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi Isirayɛl , nni a sɛn yi ̀ ɓi kɔrɔs di ti gherɛn nyi .
A ̀ fagha ̀ n ̀ tyweeyi wii ri Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ kpaa lɛ nyii ri ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ; nni ti ghɛn ̀ min n ̀ ko ̀ o Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ , a ̀ gherɛ ̀ n lɛ a ghɛɓsi nyi ɓigomi ̀ nɛ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ zyaa ̀ zyaa ɓɛ ɓɛ kpanga ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ ɗi nyi , ɓɛ sɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ mgi ̀ gha ̀ girig nyi .
Biri ̀ m i ̀ sigtɛ ̀ nga ̀ zi bimiɗ , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n toroɓ , a ̀ kpaŋ mɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛraa .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛraa a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ ti ja ̀ ŋbog , nni Yeesus a ̀ nya ̀ mga ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : < < Eli Eli , lama saɓagtani ! > > Yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ : Bɛ ̀ ll wɛ ̀ m , Bɛ ̀ ll wɛ ̀ m , wa ̀ a rinii mɛ ̀ lɛ cɛ ?
Ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ ɓɛ woka ̀ com ki Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ , ɓɛ kpaa lɛ : A rereŋi Eli .
Lɔŋ wɔɔ foo , ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɔ ki kɛnga ̀ y ki ̀ teri ̀ dɛ ̀ ɓ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ree , ki ɓam ̀ yɔ ̀ ɓi ki ̀ syo ̀ ŋ , ki nɔg ɓi ɓi ̀ kpaakpam ɓi mɛrɔ ̀ g , ki nam ̀ Yeesus lɛ a ̀ nɔ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛmbog ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Ka ca ̀ ra , ti ghɛn ̀ n ̀ ko ̀ o Eli a ̀ ri ̀ nyi ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u kighɛɓsii .
Yeesus a ̀ nya ̀ mdi ̀ gha ̀ ti ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , a ̀ maasi ̀ min .
Fɔɔnnɛ coo kila ̀ a ̀ ki ̀ ki ɓagha ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , ki lani ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ la ̀ na ̀ ɓiɓɛɛ ̀ , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n yi ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , a ̀ kpaŋ azi ; zi i nyɛ ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ n , mɛ ̀ ɓan mɛ lanla ̀ n .
Zɔ ̀ ŋ yi ŋwarɛ ̀ nga ̀ , ɓi ̀ loŋ ɓi ɓum ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ɓɛ ɓɛ cuugha ̀ ɓi ghemɓɛ ̀ nga ̀ ,
ɓi kpagi ̀ i ̀ ɓi zɔ ̀ ŋ , ɓi ɗiŋi ̀ ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tɛnɛn ; ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ ri ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi Yeesus ɓi ki re ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ a ki ̀ gwey ki ɓum .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ , ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋɓeŋi Yeesus ri ̀ ɓɔ ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ di zi i nyɛ ̀ ŋɗɛɛ , ɓɛghɛɛdi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓimbog ɓi ɓi kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓin ̀ , nni ɓɛ risi ̀ gha ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ɓɛ kpaa lɛ : Yeesus a ̀ a n ̀ ɗi ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ta ̀ a ̀ kaa ̀ .
Ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ lɛ ̀ ɛgwey , ɓɛ rɛli ̀ gha ̀ y fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ , ɓɛ seese ̀ e ̀ yi ̀ ; ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛ ɓɛ kɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ gha ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ ri Yeesus a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n a Galile , lɛ ɓɛɛ ghɛɛ ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɓsi ̀ nyi ti ̀ tom .
Marii Madelɛn ri ̀ Marii a ̀ jɛɛ Zyag ɓɛɛ Yoosɛɓ , ri jɛɛ ɓɔn ɓɛ Zeɓede ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛn ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ cɛŋko ̀ ki kpaga ̀ , guŋgum a mum a ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a Arimate ɗii lɛ Yoosɛɓ , a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ y , lɛ nyi girig a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ -yila ̀ g a ̀ Yeesus .
Nni a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Pilat , a ̀ lɔn nyi ki ̀ loŋ ki Yeesus , Pilat a ̀ kpaa lɛ ɓɛɛ fa nyi kɔ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yoosɛɓ a ̀ teka ̀ ki ̀ loŋ kin ̀ a ̀ lɔg kɔ ri ̀ aloya ̀ a ̀ nyɔn
a ̀ kɛ ̀ n min kɔ ki ̀ nɔ ̀ ŋzii ɓi zɔ ̀ ŋ i ̀ nyɔn i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ soɓka ̀ nyi ɓi ri ̀ ɓan ; fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ɓiŋzi ̀ gha ̀ coo gɔ ̀ g ɓi ŋwɔm wu zɔ ̀ ŋ , a ̀ si ̀ m yɔ ̀ mii ̀ , a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ n a ̀ ghaa ̀ gh .
Marii Madelɛn , ri ̀ Marii a ̀ mbog ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ , ɓɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔriyɛn yi ɓɛg a ̀ mbog , ɓɛ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ i ̀ mis ri ̀ zɔ ̀ ŋ .
Ɓi duri tana , yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ ɓi ŋwos anɛ a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɓka ̀ go ̀ n inɛ ɓɛ m ̀ ɓuŋa ̀ g Saɓa ̀ t mii ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey , ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ ɓaka ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Pilat
ɓɛ kpaa nyi lɛ : Gɔmi ̀ na ̀ a ̀ gwey , ti ̀ yitii lɛ pwa ̀ a ̀ pwaa ̀ a ̀ mum a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ a n ̀ kpaa di a ̀ kaka cem lɛ : Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru mɛraa , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛɛ yi a ɓi ̀ loŋ .
Kali min , ɓɛɛ ɓeŋ ̀ ɓeŋ zɔ ̀ ŋ a ̀ kpaŋ mɛ ̀ ru mɛraa kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ fɔlɔɔ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u ki fyaasii kiloŋ kii lɛ ɓɛɛ tumɛn ri ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ lɛ : A ̀ a ghe ̀ mɓɛɛ . Ri ̀ kuu ɗi pwa ̀ a ̀ ɗin ̀ ɗi ɓii ̀ ɓeɓtɛɛ ɗi cee ɗi n ̀ tonto .
Pilat a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ n kɛ ̀ ɛna , ɓi woŋzi ɓɔ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ri ̀ lɛ ɓɛ , ɓe ̀ ŋ zɔ ̀ ŋ lɛ syeesyee .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ min , ɓɛ kona ̀ g ki ̀ rɔ ̀ mi gɔ ̀ g i ̀ nɛ ɓi ŋwɔm wu zɔ ̀ ŋ , ɓɛ ki rɛsi ɓɛsuja ̀ a ̀ wɔɔ lɛ , ɓɛɛ ɓeŋ ̀ ɓeŋ yɔ ̀ .
Ɓi jɛ ̀ m i ̀ Saɓa ̀ t , ŋwosi sɔnɗi lɛ ɓuɓ , Marii Madelɛn ri ̀ Marii a ̀ mbog ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ zɔ ̀ ŋ .
Nni ɓɛ sigmɛ ̀ nga ̀ di zi i mɛ nyɛ ̀ ŋɗɛn ri i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , lɛ ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a Kan a ̀ sɛnga ̀ y , a ̀ yu ̀ ki ̀ ɓiŋzii gɔ ̀ g , a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ mii ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
Ŋwaa ̀ fi ̀ tom a ̀ n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ lo ̀ nlo ̀ mga ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋ ̀ wa ̀ aŋ ̀ wa ̀ ɗ , ki ̀ la ̀ a ̀ kii ki pupuɓ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ dɛ ̀ ɓ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ risi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ni ̀ i ̀ ghni ̀ ŋdɛ ̀ n lɛ kpa ̀ g-kpa ̀ g-kpa ̀ g , ɓɛ rɔɓ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ loŋ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ , a ̀ kpaa ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛn ̀ lɛ : Kɛ ̀ ɓi risi , lɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yii lɛ ɓi kaakaa Yeesus a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ n ̀ kpani ɓi ̀ kɔrɔs .
A ̀ yii ̀ di fɛ , a ̀ a ghe ̀ mɓɛɛ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ , yu ̀ unay , ɓi ghɛn ̀ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ a ̀ a nɗi ̀ n ̀ nɔ ̀ nɔŋiyɛn .
Nni kɛ ̀ ɛna lɛ fyɛ ̀ ɗ , ɓi kpaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii lɛ , a ̀ a ghe ̀ mɓɛɛ a ɓi ̀ loŋ , a ̀ loloogh ri ̀ mi ̀ ni a Galile , wɔɔ nnɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ nyi ɓii ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ ; ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki maa ̀ ri ̀ lɛ n ̀ kpaa ̀ mi ̀ ni .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ a zɔ ̀ ŋ lɛ fyɛ ̀ ɗ , mɛ ̀ rem mɛ ̀ ronɛn lɛ : ri ̀ i ̀ ris , ri ̀ coo kinya ̀ a ̀ , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ki ̀ kpaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ree .
Lɔŋ wɔɔ foo , nni Yeesus a ̀ gha ̀ ska ̀ ki yu ̀ u ki tulɛɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛn ̀ , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : N ̀ to ̀ gsii mi ̀ ni ! Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ tyoŋdɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi a nyoo , ɓɛ ɓan ̀ nyi ɓi mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ , ɓɛ ɓɔgsi ̀ nyi .
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa min ɓɔ lɛ : Kɛ ̀ ɓi risi ; kɛ ̀ ɛna ki ̀ kpaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓɛ ̀ m lɛ ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ a Galile , wɔɔ nnɛ ɓɛ ri mɛ ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛn ̀ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ di ɓɛ kaka ɓi bee , nni ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi nɗaŋ wu ɓɛsuja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓeŋɓe ̀ ŋga ̀ zɔ ̀ ŋ , ɓɛ sugti ̀ gha ̀ y ɓi ba ̀ n , ɓɛ kpaa ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ki kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ mɛ taŋzɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ toki ̀ , nni ɓɛ fagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛn ̀ ɓyoo mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni ;
ɓɛ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ghagsii ɓɔlɛ lɛ , ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓaa yu ̀ u ki ̀ fyaasii kiloŋ kii ri i ̀ ru , di ɓi ̀ sii ri ɓi fi ̀ lo .
Nni i gɔmi ̀ na ̀ a ̀ woogh ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ , ti ̀ yii yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ ri kpaa nyi ɓi ɗi lɛ kɛ ̀ ɓi ɓa ri ki ̀ ɓan .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ teka ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni , ɓɛ ki lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ reɓka ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ ki ; fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ sa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpaŋ gɛɛ ̀ nɛ .
Nni ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ kintɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ bog ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ a Galile ɓi do ̀ n i ̀ nɛ Yeesus a ̀ reɓka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ wɔɔ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ nyi , ɓɛ ɓɔgsi ̀ nyi , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ nyoey ɓi nɗem .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ tyo ̀ ŋdɛ ̀ nga ̀ y , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓaa fa mɛ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wuce ̀ m lɛ ri ̀ ɓi ɗyoo ɓiɗu ̀ m , ri ̀ ɓi ziinɛ .
Kɛ ̀ ɛna ! ɓi ki lɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛɛ ɓa ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛm , ɓi ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓti ̀ ɓɔ ɓi ɗii ɗi Seŋi , ri ̀ Man , ri ̀ Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ;
ɓi ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɓɔ ri ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋ ɗi ɓiɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi nsiŋdɛ ̀ nga ̀ mi ̀ ni ; ɓi ̀ ki yi lɛ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ nɗaŋ ri mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ ŋwos ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ kpaŋ ɓi ri ̀ le ̀ g ɗi zi .
Ri ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɗi Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ Yeesus Kiris Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan Ezayii lɛ : Ghɛna , n ̀ ɗomi wɔ ̀ mum Wɛm ̀ a ̀ fi ̀ tom bee ̀ bɛ ̀ y , lɛ a pegsɛn wɔ ̀ bee .
Jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ roa ̀ nɛ a la ̀ alamɓɛ ̀ n yi ̀ ɓi-reɓ lɛ : pe ̀ gsɛɛna bee yi Kan ɓi rɛsa ̀ g yɔ lɛ saaɗ .
Nni Zyaŋ a ̀ peegha ̀ y ɓi-reɓ , a ̀ ɓa ̀ a ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓti ̀ ɓum a ̀ ki la ̀ alamɓɛ ̀ n lɛ , ɓum , ɓɛɛ ɓɛɛ lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛn mɛ ̀ rem , ɓɛ ̀ ɓaɓtɛ ̀ n , fɔɔnnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a cenɛn mi ̀ ni ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓyaa .
Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓi zii ̀ Zyude , ri ̀ ɓɛ a Yorisalɛm , ɓɛ pɛɛ ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ y di ɓɛɛ ̀ yu ̀ yuiy a lɔ ̀ ŋkii , nyii ki ɓa ̀ aɓaɓti ̀ ɓɔ ɓi n ̀ syo ̀ m wulɛ Zyuridɛŋ , di ɓɛ mɛ kpa ̀ ki ɓiɓe ɓyaa .
Zyaŋ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ki ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ki ɓɛ tiŋi ri nyu ̀ ŋ yi sya ̀ moo , a ̀ ŋirɛ ̀ n ka ̀ nɗa a ̀ go ̀ o ̀ ɓi ki ̀ ɓon , a ̀ ki ɗiɗi lɛ , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ta ̀ ta ̀ ɗ , ri ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ mɛ ilo ̀ o ̀ wu ɓɛ pisii yi ̀ ɓi cog .
A kaka ̀ li ̀ gha ̀ ɓum lɛ : Roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ mɛ ̀ ajɛ ̀ m , a ̀ cee mɛ ̀ ɓi-te ̀ ɗ , n ̀ kpaŋi ɓi ɓi n ̀ koŋ wulɛ n ̀ laŋi , n ̀ fu ̀ mi ̀ mɛ ̀ ɗig mii mɛ go ̀ o ̀ .
Mɛ ̀ , m ̀ ba ̀ ɓtii mi ̀ ni ri ̀ mɛ ̀ nig , ki ̀ ɓan kifog nyii ri mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓtii ri Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Ngha ̀ y .
Lɔŋ ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ̀ n , Yeesus a ̀ pɛsɛnga ̀ y a Naazarɛt , ɓi kiden ki zi ki a Galile a ̀ yu ̀ y , Zyaŋ a ̀ ki ɓa ̀ ɓti nyi ɓi Zyuridɛŋ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaŋkpa ̀ ŋga ̀ y ɓi mɛ ̀ nig , nni a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ di ɗyoo ɗi nɛmɓɛɛ , Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ki sɛnsɛ ̀ n yi ̀ nyi ɓi nyoo fɛ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ kuu ̀ kuu ̀ .
Jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ki ɓɔ ̀ ɓ yi aɗyoo lɛ : U ̀ ri Man wɛm ̀ a ̀ n ̀ ɗem , ɓi wɔ ̀ nnɛ n ̀ foŋi ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ kɛm ̀ ki ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , nni Nghay a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ gha ̀ ska ̀ ki ̀ tinii Yeesus lɛ a kɛn ̀ ɓi-reɓ .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ghagsigha ̀ mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ̀ tin mɛɓɛɛ ̀ ɓi-reɓ win ̀ , Sata ̀ n a fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n nyi wɔɔ . A ̀ ghɛghɛ ̀ ɓka ̀ wɔɔ ri nya ̀ m yi ɓi cog , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓɛ kiki ̀ gha ̀ nyi ti ̀ tom .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ di ɓɛ mɛ ɓan Zyaŋ , Yeesus a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Galile , a ̀ kaka ̀ li ̀ Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
A ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ ɓum lɛ : Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ , ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll ki mɛ tyɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ tɛn yi ; lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛɛna mɛ ̀ rem , ɓi gherɛn Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ghagha ̀ ghi ̀ ya ̀ ɓi n ̀ wɔŋi ̀ wu riɓa ̀ y a ̀ nɛ a Galile , nni a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ɓɛ ̀ -Simɔn ɓɛɛ ̀ Andire a ̀ geni di ɓɛɛ ̀ pi ̀ pig dam ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y , lɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ i ̀ gh-dam .
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ tiina mɛ ̀ , di n ̀ ki lɛ ɓi ɓa ɓɛ ̀ syo ̀ ŋi ̀ -ɓum .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ghaska ̀ ki ̀ ca ̀ ri dam yaa , ɓɛ nɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ nyi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ di ̀ gha ̀ ti ̀ asu lɛsa ̀ g , nni a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ Zyag , man a ̀ Zeɓede ɓɛɛ Zyaŋ a ̀ geni ; ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ri ̀ pe ̀ gsɛ ̀ n ɗi dam yaa ɓi ki ̀ kɔm ɓiɗu ̀ m .
