Ɓaa ̀ ki foŋ ɓi mɛrɔ ̀ g mɛ nyɔn ɓi ɓi ̀ tu ̀ g ɓi ɓiren , ɓisuulɛ mɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ g mɛ ri ɓii ̀ weeyii ɓiren , mɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ g ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ren ɓi ɗyaŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m . Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ fogi mɛrɔ ̀ g mɛ nyɔn ɓi ɓi ̀ ren ɓi nyɔ ̀ n .
Ŋwosi Saɓa ̀ t a ̀ dɛŋ , Yeesus a ̀ ghagha ̀ ghi ̀ ya ̀ ɓi dɛmi nyas . Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ghagha ̀ ghi ̀ ya ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ so ̀ so ̀ ri ̀ ɗi nyas .
Nni Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ tɔka ̀ Yeesus lɛ : Ghɛna ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɔɔ ! Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki kiɓan ki ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓis ɓi ree ̀ gh lɛ mum kɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ŋwosi Saɓa ̀ t ?
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɓaka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ ka ɓala ̀ ɓi com ki Davit a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ , yɛ ̀ ɛ za ̀ y i ̀ kɔ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ri ̀ nyi ri ̀ ɓum ɓii , nyi kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ com ki ɗiyɛn ?
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki Aɓyatar a ̀ ɓagha ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey , a ̀ ɗi bi ̀ rɛs yi ɓum ɓɛ fagha ̀ ɓisuu Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ ki teɗ ga ̀ ɓ , a ̀ fa ɓum ɓii , kɔm ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓyɛɛ kpaaghi lɛ lɔŋ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ cɛ ̀ ncaa ɓɛɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɗii ̀ bi ̀ rɛs yin ̀ .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛn ̀ lɛ : Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ rɛsi ̀ gha ̀ Saɓa ̀ t ɓi ki ̀ rɔɔ ki mum , wɔ ̀ lɛ a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ɓi mum lɛ a ɓa n ̀ kpa ̀ n a go ̀ n inɛ ̀ n .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ Man a ̀ mum a ̀ la ̀ mii girig Saɓa ̀ t .
Yeesus a ̀ sugti ̀ gha ̀ ki ɗiŋii ɓi naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n . Ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ ri ca ̀ g ki ɓɔmɛn ,
ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ , ɓɛ pɛɛ ̀ zi ̀ mis ri ̀ Yeesus lɛ ɓɛɛ ghɛn ̀ , n ̀ ko ̀ o a ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zii ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n ŋwosi Saɓa ̀ t , di ɓɛɛ sɔmɛn nyi .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ mum a ̀ nce ̀ m lɛ : Pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyoo , u rɛli foo ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ tɔka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓis ɓi gherɛɛ nya lɛ mum a ki ki ̀ rɔɔ gi ̀ n ki ̀ ɓe ŋwosi Saɓa ̀ t ? Lɛ mum a ghɛɓsi romum gi ̀ n , a wey nyi ŋwosi Saɓa ̀ t ? Ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ minɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa ̀ g ntɔɔ ̀ tɔɔgh wii .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ kɛɛ ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ mis ɓi ɓumɓɛ ̀ n di a wowog bim , ri ̀ n ̀ ɗemi-kɛŋɛn ɓi ki ̀ te ̀ ri kaa ki n ̀ ɗem , a ̀ kpaa min ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ca ̀ g kiɓɔmɛn lɛ : Na ̀ ma ca ̀ g kɔɔ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a na ̀ m ca ̀ g kii kin ̀ , ki sugti ̀ lɛ syeesyee .
Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ kpaga ̀ , ɓɛ ghas ki ̀ ki ̀ i righa ̀ da ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ga ̀ ŋgam ɓɛ Eroodɛ , lɛ ɓɛɛ ghɛn ̀ lannɛ ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ ki lɛ ɓɛɛ wey Yeesus .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓi be ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y , coo kituu ki ɓum ki nɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ nyi ; ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ y a Galile ri ̀ a Zyude
ri ̀ a Yorisalɛm , ri ̀ a Idume , ri ̀ cɛcɛɗ ki Zyuridɛŋ ri ̀ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ ko ̀ do ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛ wuɓsɛɛ ba ̀ n yi lɛ , ri ̀ Tiir ri Sidɔŋ ; ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ yuyu ̀ gha ̀ Yeesus a nyoo , lɛ ɓɛ woka ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi a ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii lɛ , ɓɛɛ yu nyi ri maa ki ̀ kɔm , lɛ gwi ̀ y i ɓum i ̀ nɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ turi nyi .
Ɓisuulɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓii ̀ roroɓi ɓɛ kpikpi ̀ gha ̀ nyi ɓi nyoo lɛ ɓɛɛ kom nyi .
Ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay ɓi ɓala ̀ ka ̀ lɛ , i ɓi ghɛɛ Yeesus , ɓi ɓag nyi mɛ ̀ ɗu asu , ɓi ki syan jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : U ̀ ri Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ a ̀ ɓa ̀ ŋzi ̀ gha ̀ mis lɛɛ ̀ gwey , a ̀ re ̀ re ̀ g ɓyɔ lɛ byɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ lɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ yi nyi .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɓɔka ̀ min ɓi do ̀ n aɗyoo , a ̀ regi ̀ ɓumɓɛ a ̀ kɔ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ a reŋi , ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kɛn ̀ nyi a nyoo .
A ɓɔ ̀ n min ɓum n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ ɓi ɓumɓɛ ̀ n lɛ a kɛɛ ̀ ghag ri ̀ ɓɔ , a ̀ ki rom ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ ki ̀ kakalii Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
A ̀ fagha ̀ ɓɔ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ , ɓɛɛ nanaɓ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay .
Ɓumɓɛ a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ nga ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ lɛ : Ri ̀ Simɔn a ̀ nɛ Yeesus a ̀ a n ̀ kpɔgi ̀ lɛ Pyɛɛri
ri ̀ Zyag , man a ̀ Zeɓede ɓɛɛ Zyaŋ a ̀ geni , ɓɛ Yeesus a n ̀ kpɔgii lɛ : Bwanɛrigɛs , yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ , ɓɔn ɓɛ baa ̀ ba ̀ n ;
ri ̀ Andire , ri ̀ Filiɓ , ri ̀ Batelemi , ri ̀ Matyoo , ri ̀ Tomas , ri ̀ Zyag man a ̀ Alfe , ri ̀ Tadee , ri ̀ Simɔn a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a Kana ;
ri Zyudas Iskariyot ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ka ̀ ɓka ̀ Yeesus .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , nni ɓɛ sugti ̀ gha ̀ y a mɛɛ , coo gu ̀ l i ̀ ɓum i ̀ taŋzɛ ̀ n ti ̀ le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ri bee inɛ ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ ɗi ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ naa ̀ -ɓum i ̀ Yeesus i woka ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ nni ɓɛ yugha ̀ nyi ki ̀ teri ̀ lɛ ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ nya m ̀ ɓu ̀ u ̀ sɛn .
Ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓɛ ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ y a Yorisalɛm , ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ girig lɛ : A ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki nghay ki lɛ Bɛlzeɓul , a na ̀ naɓ ɓiɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu Bɛlzeɓul a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi ɓiɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ , a kpaa ɓɔ ɓi da ̀ ɗki ̀ lɛ : Lannɛ Sata ̀ n a ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ na ̀ ɓti ̀ nyimiɗ ?
Ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ɓum ɓɛ mii ̀ ɓɛ lanɛɛ , ɓɛ ram wɛ ̀ y ɓɔ ri ̀ ɓɔ , ki ti ki cuughi ̀ .
Naa ̀ -ɓum i ̀ nɛ ɓum ɓɛ mii ̀ ɓɛ ramzɛɛ wɛ ̀ y ɓɔ ri ̀ ɓɔ , i ̀ yin lɛ i ̀ kɛ ̀ n bee ̀ bɛ ̀ y ;
i Sata ̀ n a pɛ ̀ sɛɛ , a ̀ ram wɛ ̀ y ri nyimiɗ , di a ̀ ti yɛɛ lɔɔ ri n ̀ la ̀ nag ; ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kii ki yii ̀ di lɛ ki kɛn ̀ asu ki ɓaɓa ̀ , di ki ɓi nyi ki lee ̀ gh .
Ŋwaa ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ ɓi naa ̀ ki ̀ te ̀ ete ̀ ɗ ki mum , a ̀ sa ̀ ŋ i ̀ kum wu roa ̀ nɛ ̀ n , di a ̀ loogh ɓi nyi ki ̀ ka ̀ ŋi bɛn ; i a ̀ mɛ ka ̀ ŋ nyi bɛn , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ sa ̀ ŋ min ɓyom ɓi roa ̀ nɛ ̀ n .
N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓii ̀ cenɛɛ ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓyaa ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , ri ̀ ti ̀ fena tice ̀ m ti ɓɛ fenga ̀ ka ̀ nyi ;
ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓaa cenɛɛ gɛ ɓi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ fengii Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay nsoo ̀ ŋwos bog , ɓisuulɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n mii ̀ a ̀ ki ̀ i ki ̀ ɓe ki a ̀ kɔ ̀ rii gɛ ri ̀ kɔ fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓum fɔlɔɔ lɛ , ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki nghay .
Jɛɛ Yeesus ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓii , ɓɛ yugha ̀ y , ɓɛ rɛri ̀ ɓi dan , ɓɛ rom mum lɛ a reŋii ̀ nyi .
Ɓum ɓɛ kɔri ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ kɔmzɛ ̀ n nyi , nni ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : Gaa , ri ɓɛ ̀ goni ɓɛɛ tɔtɔg wɔ fɛnii ɓi dan .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ lɛ : Ghɛn yɛɛ ri jɛɛ wɛ ̀ m , ɓɛ ̀ ghɛn ɓɛɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓɛ ̀ m ?
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ mis ɓi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ kɔmzɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi ɓɛ ̀ n , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Jɛɛ wɛ ̀ m ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓɛ ̀ m , ɓɛɛ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ tɛ ̀ n lɛ ;
ɓisuulɛ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki ̀ i ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , nnyɛɛ ri geni wɛ ̀ m a ̀ baŋi ̀ , nsoo ̀ lɛ a ̀ giɓ nsoo ̀ lɛ jɛɛ wɛ ̀ m .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ti ̀ ri ̀ re ̀ e ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɗi ɓum ɓi be ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y . Coo kituu ki ɓum ki taŋzɛ ̀ n nyi a nyoo le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ a ̀ ɓɔka ̀ ɓi ki ̀ kɔm a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ nig , gɛ mum a ̀ nɛ ̀ n bimiɗ a ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓ yi ̀ a cɛɗ .
Yeesus a ̀ re ̀ e ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ ɓi ̀ ɓan lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓi da ̀ ɗki ̀ , nni ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ a ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ :
Wooghna ! Nsali ̀ -dɛm odɛŋ yɛɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ mi ̀ si boo i ̀ ɓyom ɓi dɛm .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ mi ̀ mi ̀ ska ̀ , ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ boo i ̀ dɛŋ i ̀ kpi ̀ ɓi bee aɗyoo , ti ̀ i ̀ li ̀ ti yu , ti ɗi yɔ ̀ bimiɗ .
Ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ mbog i ̀ kpi ̀ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ i ti ̀ cɔg i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓka ̀ ɓi , i ̀ gha ̀ s ki ̀ ro ̀ o ɓisuulɛ ziinɛ ̀ n i ̀ fɔmga ̀ ɓi .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwos a kpaga ̀ y ɓyom ɓi ɗig , mɛ ̀ ɗye ̀ m mɛ wom ̀ da ̀ g lɛ ɓi ɓagha ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ga ̀ ŋ .
Nni ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ mbog i ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ kpi ̀ i ɓi ɓi ̀ ka ̀ rag , yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ ka ̀ rag ɓi tɔɓka ̀ , ɓi laata ̀ g yɔ ̀ , i ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓ yɛ ̀ kɛɛ wum .
Nni boo i ̀ dɛŋ i kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ kpi ̀ i ɓi syeesyee a ̀ zi , i ̀ ro ̀ o ̀ , i ̀ tɔɔ , i ̀ ki wum lɛ , nɗye ̀ m wu wu yii ɓi ̀ ɗu ̀ n ri ̀ tin ɗi ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ , wu wu yii ɓi ̀ ɗu ̀ n mɛ ̀ tin mɛ ̀ ra , wu wu yii , ɓi ̀ ɗu ̀ n mɛ ̀ tin mɛtan ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaati ̀ gha ̀ lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ree ̀ , mɛ lɛ a ̀ wog , a ̀ wog .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ dɛga ̀ , nni ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ nyi ja ̀ ŋbog , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi ri ̀ tɔg ɗi mɛtɔɔ ̀ gtɔɔgh ɓi da ̀ ɗki ̀ yi a ̀ tete ̀ ka ̀ .
Nni a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Mi ̀ nii ɓɛ ki ri ki fayɛn lɛ ɓi yi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ɓagha ̀ ɓi ̀ nyamɛn ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll ; ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛmbog ɓɛɛ ̀ wowog lɔŋ ɓiɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m yɛ ̀ ɛ da ̀ ɗki ̀
lɛ kɛɛ ɓa lɛ , nsoo ̀ ɓaa seese ̀ e ̀ lɛ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ghɛn , ɓɛ ri ki wog lɛ syeesyee , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ yi , lɛ di ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓa lɛ ɓɛ lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n mɛ ̀ rem , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki cenɛn ɓɔ ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓyaa .
