Nni Yeesus a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ŋmɛ ̀ nga ̀ y ajɛ ̀ m a ̀ ghɛn ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ fwa ̀ a ̀ dɛ ̀ n ɗi Pyɛɛri di a kpaakpaa lɛ : Pɛ ̀ sɛn mɛ ̀ ajɛ ̀ m Sata ̀ n , ɓisuulɛ , mɛ ̀ yiti ̀ mɔɔ mɛ yin mɛ ̀ yiti ̀ mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , mɛ ri ̀ lɔŋ mɛyiti ̀ mɛ ɓum .
Nni a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ min lɛ ri ̀ gu ̀ l i ̀ ɓum ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : I mum a ̀ kɔ ̀ ni lɛ a nɔɔ ̀ ti mɛ ̀ , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ roo ̀ zɛɛ nyimiɗ , a ̀ tɛ ̀ gsɛ ̀ n kɔrɔs wi ̀ i ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ mɛ ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ kɔ ̀ ni lɛ a kamɛ ̀ n ri ̀ cɛɓ kii , a ̀ ri ̀ kɔ ɓii ̀ ɗimzii , wɔ ̀ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɗimzii cɛɓ kii ɓisu wɛ ̀ m , ri ̀ ɓisuu Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ , nnyɛɛ ri kɔ ɓii ̀ ghɛɓsii .
Ki ̀ ghɛɓsii mum cɛ lɛ , a fɔn ̀ ziinɛ bimiɗ , di a ̀ ɗimzii cɛɓ kii ?
Ŋwaa ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ kwe ̀ ɗ cɛɓ kii ri cɛ ?
Ɓisuulɛ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓii ̀ woo ̀ gh n ̀ too ̀ ri ̀ ɗ , nsoo ̀ lɛ a ̀ wog ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓyɛm ̀ n ̀ too ̀ ri ̀ ɗ ɓi gba ̀ a ̀ i ̀ ɓum i ̀ gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ti ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g , Man a ̀ mum a ̀ woogh gɛ girig nyi n ̀ too ̀ ri ̀ ɗ , ŋwos anɛ a ̀ yu ̀ u gɛ ɓi ri ̀ kem ɗi Seŋi wi ̀ i ̀ , n ̀ ɗaŋ ri ɓum ɓii ɓɛ titom ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ tɛnɛn .
Nni a ̀ kpaati ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ɓum i ̀ dɛŋ i ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ̀ fɛ , ya ̀ a wu ɓi di i ̀ ka ghɛn ɓi yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll ki yu ̀ u yi ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru taa ̀ fog , Yeesus a ̀ teka ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ Pyɛɛri , ri ̀ Zyag , ri ̀ Zyaŋ , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ɓɔ cɛ ̀ ncaa ɓi coo do ̀ n aɗyoo , a ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n ɓɔ ɓi mis dɛŋ .
Ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ɓii ɓi lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ̀ puɓ ɓi lonlo ̀ m lɛ syaŋ ̀ syaŋ ̀ , le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ziinɛ a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ puɓsi ̀ ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ fɔlɔɔ .
Ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ ghɛn di Moyis ri ̀ Eli ɓɛ ti ɓii ̀ to ̀ toogh ri Yeesus .
Nni Pyɛɛri a ̀ pɛ ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ a ̀ kpaa Yeesus lɛ : Raɓi ̀ , ki ri ki ̀ rɔɔ di ti ̀ kɔ ̀ rii fɛ ̀ , ti ̀ toŋ ɓi ̀ laa ɓiraa lɛ , kifog ɓisu wɔɔ , ki ̀ fog ɓisuu Moyis , ki ̀ fog ɓisuu Eli .
A yigha ̀ ɓi ̀ com ki a kpaa ̀ , lɛ i ̀ ris wu ɓanga ̀ ɓɔɔ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Fɔɔnnɛ ki ̀ kwi ̀ ɗ ki sigtɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ , jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ ki kpaŋ yi ɓi ki ̀ kwi ̀ ɗ kin ̀ lɛ : Roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ man wɛm ̀ a ̀ nɛ n ̀ keesa ̀ g , wooghna nyi .
Lɔŋ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kɔm ̀ kin ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ mɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ti ̀ mis fɛlɛ asu waa ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ di ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ , lɔŋ Yeesus cɛ ̀ ncii nnɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ nyi .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ sɛnsɛ ̀ nga ̀ y do ̀ n , Yeesus a ̀ rɔ ̀ gsɛ ̀ n ɓɔ lɛ , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ kpaa mum com ki ɓaa ghɛɛ ̀ , a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Man a ̀ mum a ̀ ri ghe ̀ mɓɛn a ɓi ̀ loŋ .
Ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ ɓega ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛn ɓi mɛ ̀ rem , ɓɛ ki nyoonyolɛ ̀ n wɔɔ ɓɔ ri ̀ ɓɔ , di ɓɛɛ tɔɔtɔɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n lɛ , ri ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi a ɓi ̀ loŋ ɗi ri yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ cɛ ?
Nni ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ tɔka ̀ Yeesus lɛ : Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kpaaghi ̀ lɛ , Eli a ̀ ka ri ̀ ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : Eli a ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ ɓii ̀ loo ̀ gh ki ̀ yu ̀ u lɛ a pegsag ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , nni lannɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ Man a ̀ mum a ̀ ɓii ̀ woo ̀ gh mɛ ̀ tɔɓ lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ɓɛ ki sɛɛti nyi ?
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Eli a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ , ɓɛ ki ki ̀ ri ̀ nyi yɛ ̀ ɛ ki kɔnga ̀ ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ ki , lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ɓi ̀ ɓɛg wi ̀ i ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kpaga ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ ghɛn di coo gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum i ̀ kɔ ̀ mi ɓɔ , ɓɛ ki nyoonyolɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna .
Lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ gu ̀ l i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ ̀ n i ̀ soɓka ̀ mis ɓi Yeesus , i ̀ mughi ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ree lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ yu nyi ki ̀ to ̀ gsii .
Yeesus a ̀ tɔka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi nyoonyolɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ɓɔ ɓi ki ̀ ɓan aɗi ̀ ?
Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ki ̀ tuu ki ɓum ki ̀ n , a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ nyi lɛ : N ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g , ma ̀ a yu ̀ u yi ̀ ri ̀ ŋwɔɓti wɛ ̀ m a ̀ baŋi ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɔɔ . A ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki ̀ n ̀ ghay ki ki pɛɛ ̀ zii nyi mu ̀ m-mu ̀ m .
Ja ̀ ŋbimiɗ i ̀ nɛ ki sɛni ɓi nyi , ki roŋ nyi ɓi zi , ŋwɔɓti a ̀ fuu ̀ fu ̀ u ̀ si ̀ ti ̀ tyɛɛ ̀ di a ŋa ̀ aŋaa ̀ di ̀ min , a ̀ na ̀ rɛ ̀ n lɛ saɗ-sa ̀ a ̀ ɗ . Ma ̀ a ɓɔ ̀ ŋzaagh ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɔɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ naa ̀ ɓ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki n ̀ ghay kiŋce ̀ m , ki ̀ ɓan kifog kaa yaagh ɓɔ ri ̀ na ̀ ɓ .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Mi ̀ ni boo i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ , i ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ kɔ ̀ rii n ̀ ɗaŋ ri mi ̀ ni a ̀ kpaŋ fin ? N ̀ ki ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ cenɛɛ a ̀ kpaŋ fe ? Yu ̀ unay mɛ ̀ fɛ ri ̀ ŋwɔɓti a ̀ nce ̀ m .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ yugha ̀ y ri ̀ nyi ; lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwɔɓti a ̀ roga ̀ mis ɓi Yeesus , ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki nghay ki ghas nyi ki ̀ na ̀ rii , a ̀ kpi ̀ ɓi zi , a ̀ sɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ gɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ n di a fuufuu ̀ si ̀ ti ̀ tyɛɛ ̀ .
Yeesus a ̀ tɔg min seŋi ŋwɔɓti a ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ : Ki mɛ finɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ com ki ki tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi ? Roa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : Ki tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi lɔŋ ɓi ri ̀ ŋwɔɓti ̀ .
Ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki nghay ki ti ki ɓoki ̀ nyi ɓi ɗuu nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ nig lɛ kɛɛ wey nyi . Nni i u ̀ ri ̀ lɛ u ̀ ki ̀ com ki ̀ dɛŋ ɓisu wii , ghɛɓsi ɓi ̀ si , wogha ɓa ̀ ɓisi nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g .
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ : U kpaaghi mɛ lɛ i u ̀ ri ̀ lɛ u ̀ ki ̀ com kidɛŋ , lɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yii ɓi lɛ ki ̀ ɓan ki ki ri lɛ ki yaaghrɛ ̀ n di ŋwaa ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ki yin ?
Fɔɔnnɛ seŋi ̀ ŋwɔɓti ̀ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ gha ̀ ska ̀ ki ̀ kpaa jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : N ̀ gherɛɛ ! Yu ɓa ̀ mɛ ki ̀ ghɛɓsii ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ɗi lɛ ɗi ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ di ɓum ɓɛ ti ɓii ̀ su ̀ usuu ̀ rɛ ̀ n yi ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ree , nni a ̀ fwa ̀ a ̀ dɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki nghay a ̀ kpaa kɔ lɛ : Ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki nghay ki ki ti ̀ ki pɛɛza ̀ g ɓum ɓɛ ̀ lɔlɔg ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ mu ̀ m-mu ̀ m , n ̀ kalii wɔ ̀ lɛ , kpaŋa ɓi ŋwutya ̀ a ̀ nɛ , kɔ ̀ ɔ ki ɓi ̀ i ̀ ti ti ki ̀ ɗiŋii ɓi nyi .
Nni ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki nghay ki ɓoka ̀ ŋwɔɓti ɓi zi ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , ki faŋi ̀ di kɛɛ ̀ kuukugsɛ ̀ n , ŋwutya ̀ a ̀ ma ̀ a ̀ ghra ̀ g yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ loŋ , ɓi le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ fefe ̀ ka ̀ lɛ a ̀ wii .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɓanga ̀ nyi ɓi ca ̀ g , a ̀ pɛ ̀ si ̀ nyi aɗyoo , ŋwutya ̀ a ̀ ki rɛli mɛrɛ ̀ y .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi naa , nni ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛ tɔka ̀ nyi di ɓaa rɔ ̀ ɓ ɓɔ ri ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki nghay ki ̀ n kaa yaagh ɓi ̀ si ri ̀ na ̀ ɓ ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : Lɔŋ bɔŋ ̀ zɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛti i ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g lɛ ri ̀ kuu ɗi nghay ɗi ̀ n ɗyɛɛ kpaŋ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ foo , ɓɛ syaa ̀ zii ̀ Galile , ki kɔnga ̀ ɓi Yeesus lɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ yi lɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi jaŋ ̀ inɛ ̀ n ;
ɓisuulɛ a ̀ re ̀ re ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓiɓan , a ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓɛ ɓii ̀ ɓani ̀ Man a ̀ mum , ɓɛ fa ri ̀ ɓum , ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ wey nyi ; wɔ ̀ lɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛɛ ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru mɛraa .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ yi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi azi anɛ ɓi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ i ̀ nɛn , ɓɛ ki risi nyi ri ̀ tɔg .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ a Kapɛrinawum , yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi naa , nni a ̀ tɔka ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g lɛ : Cɛ ɓya ̀ a nyoonyo ̀ lɛ ̀ n mii ̀ bee bimiɗ ?
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛ minɛ ̀ n nyi , ɓisuulɛ ɓɛ kaa ̀ ka ̀ rɛ ̀ nga ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ yi ghɛn anɛ ɓi ɓɔ yɛɛ cee ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛmbog .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓi zi , a ̀ reŋi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : I mum a ̀ kɔ ̀ ni lɛ a ̀ ɓa n ̀ ɗɛ ̀ li ̀ -asu ̀ , a terɛn nyimiɗ yɛ ̀ ɛ siito ̀ n a ̀ mum ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ ki ɓa n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say a ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Nni a ̀ teka ̀ maa ŋwɔɓti , a ̀ rɛsi ̀ ɓɔ nyi ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ lɔ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɗ nyi a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ :
Mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ gha ̀ ɓi maa ŋwɔɓti yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ nɛ ri ̀ ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ ɓisu wɛ ̀ m a yi lɛ mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ nnɛ a ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ; nni ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ gha ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ , a yi lɛ , a ̀ a mɛ ̀ nnɛ a ̀ gha ̀ ɓi , a ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ romga ̀ y mɛ ̀ .
Nni Zyaŋ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ Yeesus lɛ : N ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g , tya ̀ a ghɛɛ di ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a na ̀ naɓ ɓiɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay ri ̀ ɗii ɗyɔɔ , nni tya ̀ a re ̀ egh nyi lɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ ki fɔlɔɔ , lɛ a ̀ ti kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa ɓi nɗaŋ wis .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Kɛ ̀ ɓi re ̀ g nyi , ɓisuulɛ mum a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki ̀ i da ̀ m ri ̀ ɗii ɗyɛ ̀ m , a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n lɔŋ mɛ ri ̀ to ̀ to ̀ g ɗi kiɓe lɔŋ wɔɔ foo .
Ɓisuulɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yin ɓii ̀ ɗu ̀ u ̀ ɗuu ri ɓi ̀ si , a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ga ̀ m yi ̀ s .
N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ faa ̀ gi ̀ ras i ̀ mɛ ̀ nig mɛnɔyɛn lɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ Kiris , a ̀ a mɛ ̀ m ɓi mɛle ̀ ɓ mɛ mii ̀ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ i mum a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɓtii ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɔɔɓɔɓti ɓɛ ɓɛ gherɛɛ mɛ ̀ ɓɛ fiɓa ̀ g , ki ɓa ti ̀ ki ̀ rɔɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ suŋ nyi coo gɔ ̀ g i ̀ ki ̀ pɛn ɓi ki ̀ mi ̀ i ̀ gh , di ɓɛɛ pig nyi ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n .
I ca ̀ g kɔɔ kɛɛ ri lɛ kɛɛ kɛɓti wɔ ̀ fi ̀ ɓa ̀ g , rena kɔ , lɛ ki ri wɔ ̀ ki ̀ rɔɔ lɛ u ghɛn cɛɓ di u ̀ ri ̀ ca ̀ g ki ̀ fog a ̀ cee lɛ u kɛn ̀ ɓi ki ̀ gɛ ̀ ŋ ki ɗuu ɗi fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ri ̀ ɓya ̀ g ɓyɔɔ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m . [
Jaŋ i ̀ nɛ zye ̀ ɗ yi ti yɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ wu , ɗuu ɗyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɗimi . ]
I i ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ wɔɔ wɛɛ ri lɛ wɛɛ kɛɓti wɔ ̀ fi ̀ ɓa ̀ g rena wɔ , lɛ ki ri ̀ wɔ ̀ ki ̀ rɔɔ lɛ u ghɛn ̀ cɛɓ di u ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ wufog a ̀ cee lɛ u kɛn ̀ ɓi ki ̀ gɛ ̀ ŋ ki ɗuu ɗi fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ mɔɔ mɛce ̀ m , [
ja ̀ ŋ i ̀ nɛ zye ̀ ɗ yi ti yɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ wu , ɗuu ɗyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɗimi . ]
I ɗis ɗyɔɔ ɗyɛɛ ri lɛ ɗyɛɛ kɛɓti wɔ ̀ fi ̀ ɓa ̀ g , sɔgha ɗyɔ , lɛ ki ri wɔ ̀ ki ̀ rɔɔ lɛ u ɗiŋi ɓi ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll ɗi u ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ fi ̀ ɗyaŋ a ̀ cee lɛ u kɛn ̀ ɓi ki ̀ gɛ ̀ ŋ ki ɗuu ɗi fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ri ̀ mis mɔɔ mɛce ̀ m ,
ja ̀ ŋ inɛ zye ̀ ɗ yi ti ̀ yɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ wu , ɗuu ɗyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɗimi .
Ɓisuulɛ mum bimiɗ a ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n ɓi nyoo lɛ ɗuu .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ foo lɛ a kɛn ̀ a Zyude , a ̀ ki ̀ sya ̀ a ̀ Zyuridɛŋ . Ɓi ̀ tuu ɓi ɓum ɓi taŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ ti ̀ nyi a nyoo , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ti ̀ ɓɔ ri ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ a n ̀ ti a ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g .
Fɔɔnnɛ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ yugha ̀ nyi ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛɛ , ɓɛ tɔg nyi lɛ : Ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓis ɓi gherɛɛ nya lɛ mum a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ na ̀ ɓ giɓ wii ̀ ?
Nni Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Moyis a ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ mi ̀ ni lɛ ɓi kilag la ?
Ɓɔɔ ɓaa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Moyis a ̀ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ baŋi ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ falag giy kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ nɛ lɛ a ghasɛɛ ri ̀ nyi , fɔɔnnɛ i ̀ ki na ̀ ɓ min nyi .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Moyis a ̀ kpaagha ̀ fɔlɔɔ ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ te ̀ ri mɛ ̀ rem .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ a ri ̀ tumɛ ̀ n , yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ baŋi ̀ ri ̀ giɓ ;
ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki baŋi ̀ i ̀ ɓii ̀ ca ̀ rii ̀ lɛ ri ̀ seŋi ri ̀ jɛɛ , i ̀ ra ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɓɛɛ giy ;
ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ɓum ki sug com ki ̀ fog , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓɛ yii ̀ di ɓum ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ , ɓɛ ti lɔŋ com ki ̀ fog .
Fɔɔnnɛ mum kɛ ̀ ɛ ghasi com ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ra ̀ ri .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kpaga ̀ a mɛɛ , nni ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ tɔgti ̀ gha ̀ Yeesus mɛ ̀ tɔɔ ̀ tɔɔgh ɓi ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ .
Nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : I mum a ̀ na ̀ ɓi giy , a ̀ ki wɔɔti giɓ adɛŋ di a ̀ ki ̀ i fi ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ɗi lɛ ri ̀ nyi ri ̀ gil a n ̀ tonto .
I giɓ a ɓe ̀ ni yii a ̀ wɛy ti ̀ roa ̀ dɛŋ , di a ̀ ki ̀ i fi ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g .
Ɓum ɓɛ yugha ̀ y Yeesus ri ̀ ɓɔɓti ɓɛsa ̀ g lɛ a kom ̀ ɓɔ , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ nyɛɛdɛ ̀ n ɓumɓɛ ̀ n .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ki ɓeɓ nyi , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ca ̀ rina ɓɔɔɓɔɓti ɓɛɛ yuiy a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ ɓisuulɛ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ki ri ̀ ɓisuu ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɔ .
N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ɓi kilɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ maa ŋwɔɓti , a ̀ a ɗiŋi ɓi mii ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ lɔ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɗka ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ , a ̀ ma ̀ gi ̀ ɓɔ , ɗi a sasaghi ɓɔ ɓya ̀ g ɓi nyo ̀ o ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ghaa ̀ gh , nni ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ pwaŋi ̀ gha ̀ y ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ree , a ̀ yu ̀ nyi ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ gh mɛ ̀ ɗu asu , a ̀ tɔg nyi lɛ : Syeesyee a ̀ n ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g , cɛ kɛɛ ̀ ki n ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ɓi ɗi lɛ n ̀ fɔ ̀ n lol a cɛɓ ?
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ u ̀ reŋii mɛ ̀ lɛ syeesyee a ̀ mum ? Ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ yin syeesyee a ̀ mum di ki yi ̀ n lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll cɛ ̀ ncii .
U ̀ yii ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ɔ wey mum , kɔ ̀ ɔ ki ̀ fisɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g , kɔ ̀ ɔ yii com ki mum , kɔ ̀ ɔ pwa ̀ a ̀ mum ki ̀ ɓan ɓi nyoo , kɔ ̀ ɔ ki ̀ mum ki ̀ ɓe , nyaasi soŋi ɓɛɛ ̀ gaa .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : N ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g , n ̀ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋ ɗi ɓidɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓin ̀ , di n ̀ kaka ki ̀ keŋ ki mum .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ seese ̀ e ̀ gha ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ keesi ̀ nyi , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ min nyi lɛ : Com kɛɛ ̀ ka kaakaa ̀ rɛ ̀ n wɔ ̀ ki ̀ fog , kɛɛ ri lɛ , u kɛn ̀ , u kaɓ ɓyom ɓyɔɔ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , u kaɓsi mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɛ mii ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sogha ̀ sogha , fɔɔnnɛ u ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ kum ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyo ̀ o ̀ ; ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , u yu , u nɔɔ ̀ ti mɛ ̀ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ woka ̀ fɔlɔɔ , a ̀ ɓeɓsi ̀ i ̀ su , a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ n a ̀ ghaa ̀ gh ri ̀ bim , ɓisuulɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ kum lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kɛɛ ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ mis ɓi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ nyi ja ̀ ŋbog a ̀ kpaa ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii lɛ : Ki tee ̀ sɛɛ lɛɛ ̀ gwey lɛ ɓɛ ̀ guŋgum ɓɛɛ ɗiŋi ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ woka ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ɓɛ kuura ̀ g . Yeesus a ̀ ki pɛ ̀ si ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓɔn ɓɛm , ki tee ̀ sɛɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ lɛ mum a ɗiŋi ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyoo .
Ri ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ ɗi sya ̀ moo a ɗiŋi ɓi ɗyas ɗi ba ̀ a ̀ ta ̀ , ɗi ri ti ̀ lɛ fɛnfɛn ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ɗi ̀ ŋi ̀ ɗi guŋgum a ɗiŋi ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyoo .
Ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ kuura ̀ ka ̀ ti ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey a ̀ cee fɔlɔɔ , ɓɛ tɔɔ ̀ ghtɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n wɔɔ ɓɔ ri ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ghɛn yɛɛ ri min lɛ a ̀ ghɛn cɛɓ ?
Nni a ̀ pɛɓsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki cee i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu mum , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , com ki lɛ ki yaaghrɛ ̀ n ki yin .
Nni Pyɛɛri a ̀ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi ri ̀ kpaa lɛ : U ̀ ghɛɛ ! ɓi ̀ sii rini ̀ gha ̀ y ɓyom ɓis ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , ti ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ wɔ ̀ .
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ , mum a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ naŋ yi ̀ lɛ ri ̀ mɛɛ mii , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni , ri ̀ seŋi ̀ , ri ̀ jɛɛ , ri ̀ ɓɔn ɓii nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ den ɓii ɓi zi ɓisu wɛ ̀ m , ri ̀ ɓisuu Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ ,
a ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓ lɛ a ̀ fɔ ̀ ni ɓi ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ti ka ghɛghɛɓ ki mii ̀ ɓyom hɔnɗɛ ̀ ɗ ɓi ri ̀ kuu ɗi com ɗi ̀ ce ̀ m ɗi a ̀ naga ̀ y lɛ ri ̀ gɛ mɛɛ , ɓɛ ̀ geni , ɓɛ ̀ jɛɛ , ɓɔn , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ den ɓi ̀ zi , a ̀ ɓu ̀ tɛ ̀ n mɛ ̀ tɔɓ mɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki nyi mii ̀ ɓisuu righerɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ki teɗ cɛɓ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ mɛɛ ̀ yu ̀ yuiy .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ bee ̀ bɛ ̀ y ɓɛ ɓii ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓi ajɛ ̀ m , ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ajɛ ̀ m ɓɛ syoŋ ̀ bee .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi bee inɛ ɓi ri ̀ ɓɔg a Yorisalɛm , Yeesus yɛɛ syoŋsyo ̀ ŋga ̀ ɓɔ bee . Ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ riighriki ̀ , nsoo ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ nɔɔ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ , ɓɛ riri ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ girig . Nni Yeesus a ̀ teka ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ rɛn a dwi ̀ ɗ , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓɔ ri ̀ kpaa ɗi ɓiɓan ɓi ɓi ri nyi ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i .
A ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi ɗi ti ̀ rɛrɛrii ɗi , ti ̀ ɓɔɔgh yɛɛ lɛ a Yorisalɛm , wɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ɓii ̀ ka ̀ ɓi Man a ̀ mum ɓi ɓya ̀ g ɓi ɓɛpi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ri ̀ ɓi ɓya ̀ g ɓi ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ; ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ren lɛ ɓɛɛ wey nyi , ɓɛ ki ceesi nyi ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yii ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ri ̀ nyi ɓii ̀ fengii , ɓɛ tuutu ̀ u ̀ nyi ̀ ti ̀ tyɛɛ ̀ ɓi nyoo , ɓɛ ɓog nyi ki ̀ to ̀ n , ɓɛ wey nyi , wɔ ̀ lɛ ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru mɛraa , a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛɛ yi a ɓi ̀ loŋ .
Ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ɓɔn ɓɛ Zeɓede lɛ ri ̀ Zyag ri ̀ Zyaŋ ki yugha ̀ Yeesus a nyoo , ki kpaa nyi lɛ : Nɗe ̀ sa ̀ g , ti kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ u ki ɓi ̀ si com ki ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ tɔɔ ̀ gh wɔ ̀ .
Yeesus a ̀ tɔg ɓɔ lɛ : Cɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ ki ɓi kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ n ̀ ki mi ̀ ni ?
Ɓɛ kpaa nyi lɛ : Yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ɓi ki ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ kɔɔ ki rikem , u gherɛn lɛ ti kɔri lɛ roa ̀ nɛ wɔ ̀ ɓi wee ̀ lem , roa ̀ nɛ wɔ ̀ ɓi ki ̀ mɛŋ .
Yeesus a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi yii gi ̀ ɓi rikuu ɗi kiɓan ɗi ɓi tɔtɔg ɗin ̀ ; ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ cenɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓi nɔ ɓeŋ a ̀ nɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ nɔɔ ̀ , nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓaɓti mi ̀ ni ri ̀ kuu ɗi ba ̀ ɓtis ɗi ɓɛ ri mɛ ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓtii ?
Ɓɛ ɓaa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Ti ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ti ̀ cenɛ ̀ n . Yeesus a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ki ri lɔŋ saaɗ lɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ nɔɔ ̀ ɓeŋ a ̀ nɛ mɛ ̀ m ̀ ɓii ̀ nɔɔ ̀ , ɓɛ ki ɓa ̀ ɓti mini ri ̀ kuu ɗi ba ̀ ɓtis ɗi ɓɛ ri mɛ ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓtii ;
ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ki ̀ ɓan ki lɛ mum a kɔri mɛ ̀ ɓi wee ̀ lem nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓi ki ̀ mɛŋ , ki yin kiɓan kɛm ̀ ; mɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ mɛn mɛ ri ̀ ɓisuu ɓumɓɛ mɛ ri mɛ ̀ pe ̀ gsɛn ɓisu wa ̀ a ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ ntɛ ̀ ɗ ki ɓɛyila ̀ g kimbog ki woka ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ , mɛ ̀ rem maa mɛ ɓeɓtɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ -Zyag ɓɛɛ ̀ Zyaŋ .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔɔ ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ yii lɛ , ɓumbɛ ɓɛro ɓum ɓɛ ti ɓɛ regi ̀ lɛ mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m mɛ ɓilɔ ̀ ŋ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ pyengi ̀ ɓum mis ri ̀ n ̀ cii ̀ zɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ ̀ rɛli ̀ -asu ɓaa , ɓɛ ceesa ̀ g gin mɔ ̀ ɔ ri ̀ ri ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɗi ɓɔ .
Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ki ɓaa ̀ fɔlɔɔ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n . Ki ̀ ɓan ki ̀ fog , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ kɔ ̀ ni lɛ a ɓa n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say a ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛmbog .
