Lɔŋ m ̀ bobog a ̀ mum a ̀ nɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛm a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ mɛ rɔ ̀ ɓ ri nyi a ̀ ɓagha ̀ lɔŋ lɛ man wii ̀ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ keesi ̀ gha ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey ; nyi nnɛ a ̀ siitɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ romi ̀ a ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛ ɓi dɛm yii ̀ , a ̀ fe ̀ ki ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ kuuraagh man wii ̀ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛ wɔrɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɛ kpaa lɛ : Roa ̀ nɛ yɛɛ ri ɓii ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓi ri dɛm i seŋi ̀ ; yu ̀ una , ti wey nyi di dɛm yɛ ̀ ɛ woo ̀ ghrɛn ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ɓanga ̀ min man a ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓɛ wey , ɓɛ mag ki ̀ loŋ kii jɛ ̀ m i ̀ gari i dɛm .
Nni n ̀ tɔɔ ̀ tɔɔgh wu ri lɛ : Cɛ kɛɛ ̀ ki ŋwaa ̀ dɛm a ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i ? Ŋwaa ̀ dɛm a ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u , a ̀ cuusi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛn ̀ a ̀ ki reɓsɛn dɛm ri ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ lɛ ɓɛɛ sasay .
Ɓi ̀ ka ɓala ɓi ̀ nya yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : Gɔ ̀ g i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ̀ toŋi ̀ -mɛɛ ɓɛ maka ̀ , yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ghala ̀ gɔ ̀ g i ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ konag ki ̀ le ̀ mi n ̀ tɔn a ̀ mɛɛ ?
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki ɓagha ̀ y yɛ ̀ ɛ Kan , ki ki ri ̀ da ̀ m i ̀ ki ̀ ɓan i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ki ̀ lɛɛ ɓi ̀ si ɓi mis .
Mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m mɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n mɛ kaaka ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ bee inɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓan ̀ Yeesus , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ɓɛ risi ̀ gha ̀ gu ̀ l i ̀ ɓum ; ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ Yeesus a ̀ teka ̀ da ̀ ɗki ̀ i ̀ nɛn ɓi ɓɔ , nni ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ , ɓɛ ghaaghra ̀ g .
Ɓɛ rom lɛ ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛdɛŋ ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓi n ̀ ɗaŋ wu Eroodɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus lɛ ɓɛɛ wɔɔ ̀ si nyi ɓi ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓii .
Nni ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ yugha ̀ y , ɓɛ kpaa nyi lɛ : N ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g , ti yii lɔŋ lɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a kpaakpaa saaɗ , u ̀ ki ti kɔ ̀ ɔ risi mum , ɓisuulɛ , wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yin ɓii ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔnɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ɗi mum , u re ̀ resi ɓum bee inɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ . Nni kali ɓi ̀ si n ̀ ko ̀ o ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓis ɓi gherɛɛ lɛ ti pee ̀ ghi la ̀ mpoŋ ̀ ri ̀ Kaaza ; ki ri ka ̀ ŋbɛn lɛ ti pee ̀ gi ̀ n ki yin ka ̀ ŋbɛn ?
Yeesus a ̀ yigha ̀ lɛ ɓɛ purii nyi ca ̀ g ɓi ɗu ̀ m yɛɛ ri , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ tɔka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓi fe ̀ eghfee ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n mɛ ̀ ? Yu ̀ unay mɛ ̀ fɛ ri ̀ fi ̀ raŋ ̀ nghɛn ̀ .
Nni ɓɛ yugha ̀ y nyi ri ̀ fi ̀ raŋ ̀ , a ̀ tɔg ɓɔ lɛ : Ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki ghɛn kɛɛ ri lɛ mii ̀ ? Ɗii ɗi ghɛn ɗyɛɛ ki ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ ? Ɓɛ ɓaa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Ɓi ri yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ , ri ̀ ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki Kaaza , ri ̀ ɗii ɗi ̀ i ̀ .
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa min ɓɔ lɛ : Pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ziina ɓyom ɓi Kaaza ri ̀ Kaaza , ɓi ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll . Ɓɛ kuura ̀ ka ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ fɔlɔɔ .
Ɓɛ ̀ sa ̀ du ̀ syɛŋ ɓɛ ɓɛɛ kpaaghi lɛ , com kidɛŋ ki yin lɛ ri ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓilo ̀ ŋ , ɓɛ yugha ̀ y Yeesus a nyoo , ɓɛ tɔg nyi lɛ :
N ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g , Moyis a ̀ ka ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ti kilag lɛ ; i ge ̀ ni mum a ̀ wii a ̀ ca ̀ ɗ giɓ di a ̀ ka yin ɗi man ɗi ̀ nyi , geni ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ wii a ̀ nɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ wɔli ̀ n ̀ kpɔɓ wii , a ̀ yay ɓɔn ri ̀ wɔ ɓi ɗii ɗi geni .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ki kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ; ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ri ̀ geni ɗyaa ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , baŋi ̀ ri ̀ baŋi ̀ . Roa ̀ n ̀ tonto a ̀ wɔlɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ki wu kɛ ̀ ɛ ca ̀ ɗ man ;
geni a ̀ ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ a ̀ teɗ n ̀ kpɔɓ wii , nyi girig a ̀ wu , kɛ ̀ ɛ ca ̀ ɗ man , ki kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ ti ̀ fɔlɔɔ ri roa ̀ ki ̀ raa ,
ri ̀ ɓɛro ɓɛmbog ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , nsoo ̀ mum bog a ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓɔ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , a ̀ ca ̀ ɗka ̀ ɓi ̀ man ri ̀ giɓ anɛ ̀ n . Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ ki ̀ taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ɓum ki ̀ n , nnɛ giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ wugha ̀ girig .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛ kitaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛn ɓɛ wɔla ̀ giɓ anɛ ̀ n ɓɔɔ ̀ ce ̀ m , nni a ̀ ɓaa gɛ gili ghɛn anɛ ɓi ̀ ɓɔ ŋwosi righe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓiloŋ ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ pwa ̀ a ̀ rɛɛ , ɓisuulɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ yii ɓi nya ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , kɛ ̀ ɓi ki yi ite ̀ ɗ wu Bɛ ̀ ll .
Lɛ ŋwosi righe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓilo ̀ ŋ , ɓɛ ̀ baŋi ̀ ɓaa wɔɔti ɓi ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ , ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ wɔɔti ɓɛbaŋi ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓɔɔ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓaa gɛ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓɛ ɓɛ ri aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
Ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki righe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓiloŋ ki ɓi tɔtɔ ̀ g , ɓi ̀ ɓala ̀ ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ Moyis ja ̀ ŋ i ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi ɓi ki ̀ twi ̀ ɗ lɛ : N ̀ ɗi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ Abiraham , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ Isag , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ Yakɔɓ ?
Ki re ̀ sii lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ yin Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓi ̀ loŋ , a ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri cem ; ɓi ri ̀ ɓi ri ̀ na ̀ n lɛ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ .
Ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna kidɛŋ ki wowo ̀ ka ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ nyoo ̀ nyo ̀ lɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n , ki ki ghɛn lɛ Yeesus a ̀ kona ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ ki ̀ ɓa ̀ agh . Nni a ̀ tyɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ tɛ ̀ nga ̀ y , a ̀ tɔg Yeesus lɛ : Ki ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna kibe kɛɛ cee ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ lɛ : Ki ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ki asu kɛɛ ̀ ki lɛ : Wɔ ̀ Isirayɛl , wogha lɛ Kan Bɛ ̀ ll wi ̀ s nnyɛɛ ri lɔŋ Kan cɛ ̀ ncii .
Fɔɔnnɛ keesi Kan Bɛ ̀ ll wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ri ̀ n ̀ ɗem wɔɔ wuce ̀ m , ri ̀ n ̀ ghay wɔɔ wuce ̀ m , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ yiti ̀ mɔɔ mɛce ̀ m , ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wɔɔ wuce ̀ m .
Ki kiɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ri lɛ : Keesi romum a ̀ nɛ wɔ ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ wɛ ̀ ɛmi ̀ ɗ ; ki ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ki ̀ dɛŋ ki ̀ ki cee ɓin ̀ , ki yii ̀ di .
Nni n ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna anɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpaagha ̀ Yeesus lɛ : Raɓi ̀ , com ki u ̀ kpaa ki ri mii ̀ , lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ bog fɔɔnnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ dɛŋ i ̀ yii ̀ di ;
ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ , mum a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ keesii Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ nɗem wii wuce ̀ m , ri ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗii ɗice ̀ m , ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wii wuce ̀ m , a ̀ ki keesi ti romum a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ nyi ja ̀ ŋbog yɛ ̀ ɛ nyimi ̀ ɗ ; ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗin ̀ ɗi rɔɔtɛɛ ɗi cee ɓi ̀ tuwe ɓi mum a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ tɔ ̀ ngi ̀ ɓisuu Bɛ ̀ ll , nsoo ̀ ɓyom ɓi a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ fu ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ a ɓɔgsi Bɛ ̀ ll mii ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓa ̀ agh ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ri ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n , nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : U ̀ ra ̀ ɓsɛɛ ɓi kilɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll ; ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ ghɛɛsi ̀ gha ̀ ti ̀ ɓi lɛ a tɔg ti nyi ntɔɔ ̀ tɔɔgh .
Yeesus a ̀ teka ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓum ri ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɗi ɓiɓan ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ tɔg lɛ : Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kpaaghi ̀ lɛ Kiris a ̀ ri ̀ man a ̀ Davit ?
Davit nyimiɗ a kpaagha ̀ , di Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ki mɛ fa nyi ɗyomzɛ ̀ n lɛ : Kan a ̀ a n ̀ kpaa Kan wɛ ̀ m lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ri mɛ ̀ fɛ ɓi wee ̀ lem a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ ghaasii ɓɛ ̀ be ̀ na ̀ bena ɓɔɔ com ki rɛsakɛn mɛko ̀ o ̀ mɔɔ mii ̀ .
I Davit nyimiɗ a reŋii nyi lɛ Kan , Lannɛ ki kɛɛ ̀ dii ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ lɛ a ɓa ti man wii ̀ ? Coo gu ̀ l i ̀ ɓum i ̀ wowo ̀ ka ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Yeesus a ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ ɓi n ̀ ɗem .
Nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓum ɓɛ a ̀ re ̀ e ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɛn ̀ lɛ : Konaaghna ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ keesa ̀ g ri ̀ rere ̀ ni ̀ ɗi ja ̀ ŋ di ɓɛ waataagh ɓyoo ɓɛ ̀ ka ̀ ɓa ̀ , ɓɛ kɔngi ̀ girig lɛ ɓɛɛ too ̀ to ̀ gsi ̀ ɓɔ ri ̀ coo nyaasɛ ̀ n ɓi gwi ̀ y .
Ki rɔɔghi ̀ ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ kɔri ɓi mɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ mɛ asu di ɓɛ kɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ sɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ , ɓɛ ki teki mɛkɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ mɛ bee ̀ bɛ ̀ y ɓi naa yi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n .
Ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ fog ɓɛɛ ti ɓɛ pumza ̀ g mɛ ̀ kpɔɓ mɛ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ , ɓɛ ki ki ̀ lag ɓyoo bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ sɛsɛg ɓɔ . Ɓɛ ri teri gɛ ki ̀ te ̀ ete ̀ ɗ ki pɔnɔsi ̀ ki ki ɓaa gɛ fɔlɔɔ lɛ yoɓ .
Yeesus a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ , a fa mis ri ̀ fi ̀ kɔrɔŋ fi ɓɛ n ̀ pi ̀ ki ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɛ bɔgsi ̀ mii ̀ a ̀ seese ̀ e ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ tuu ɓi ɓum ɓi pipi ̀ ka ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni ; ɓɛ ̀ guŋgum lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ suu ̀ su ̀ u ̀ ri ̀ ɓyoo mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni .
Nni maa n ̀ kpɔɓ a giɓ a yu ̀ gha ̀ y girig , a ̀ pi ̀ g ɓɔɔ tiraŋ ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ rɛn ɓɛ kpaŋɛn dola ̀ yiɓɛɛ ̀ ɓi fi ̀ kɔrɔŋ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ regi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : N ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ , ri ̀ fa ɗi maa n ̀ kpɔɓ a giɓ anɛ ɗi cee ri mum bimiɗ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ pii ̀ gh mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni ɓi fi ̀ kɔrɔŋ ;
