Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓi do ̀ n i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ olivyee , a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ mis ri ̀ naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll nni ɓɛ ̀ -Pyɛɛri ri ̀ Zyag ri ̀ Zyaŋ ri ̀ Andire ɓɛ tɔka ̀ nyi a dwi ̀ ɗ lɛ :
