Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ɓi dɛm , kɛ ̀ ɛ sugtii ri ̀ jɛ ̀ m lɛ a teɗ ri ̀ ga .
Nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛ me ̀ m , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gɛɓyɛ ̀ y ɓɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ̀ n .
Ɓɔ ̀ ŋzaaghna Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ lɛn ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ bu ̀ ma ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ̀ n mɛ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ kuu ɗi n ̀ tɔɓ ɗi ɗi ka ghɛnɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi , a tumɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ɗyoo ri ̀ zi , a ̀ kpaŋ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ ; ri ̀ kuu ɗi n ̀ tɔɓ ɗi ̀ n ɗi ki ghɛnɛɛ gɛ ti ̀ ɓi ɓi ziinɛ .
I Kan Bɛ ̀ ll kɛ ̀ ɛ ghaɓi mɛru mɛ ̀ n , di nsoo ̀ mum bog a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ ghɛɓ ; ki ̀ ɓan kifog a ̀ ghaɓi ̀ gha ̀ mɔ ɓisuu ɓum ɓii ɓɛ a ̀ rɔ ̀ tɛ ̀ nga ̀ .
I ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni lɛ , Kiris a ̀ ri ̀ fɛ nsoo ̀ lɛ fɛnii , kɛ ̀ ɓi wog ;
ɓisuulɛ ɓɛ ̀ -kiris ɓɛ ɓɛpwa ̀ a ̀ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pwa ̀ a ̀ pwaa ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛkpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u , ɓɛ kiki ̀ lɛ ri ̀ da ̀ m yi ɓiɓan ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ koŋnyoo ɓɛ ɓiɓan ɓi le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ , i kaa ri ̀ lɛ ki kilɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ syoŋ ̀ nsoo ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ nɛn .
N ̀ loogh mi ̀ ni ki ̀ wogsii ɓiɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , kɔ ̀ riina ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ̀ n ki ̀ ghɛnɛɛ .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛru ɓi ̀ n , ki ̀ saa ki ŋwos ki ri kpi ̀ i gɛ ɓiri ̀ m , ŋwii kɛ ̀ ɛ lo ̀ mdi .
Tyɔɛy ti ̀ kɔɔ ̀ kɔ ̀ sɛ ̀ n yi ̀ aɗyoo , di tyɛɛ ̀ kpi ̀ kpi ̀ , mɛ ̀ te ̀ ɗ mɛ ɓi ɗyoo mɛ nyɛŋɗɛ ̀ n .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓum ɓɛ ghɛɛ gɛ ɗi Man a ̀ mum a ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ kwi ̀ ɗ ri ̀ coo ite ̀ ɗ , ri ̀ ri ̀ gwey .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ romi gɛ min ɓum ɓii ɓɛ titom ɓi ɓɛ ̀ tum ɓɛ zi ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m lɛ ɓɛɛ taŋzɛn ɓum ɓii ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ nɛn ɓi zi bimiɗ .
Terina ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ɓi n ̀ ɗye ̀ m wu fi ̀ gyee . Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ɓɛ ghɛɛ di myaɓ mɛɛ ̀ wo ̀ owomzɛ ̀ n , tyɛn ti tɔtɔ ̀ ɓ , ɓɛ ti ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g lɛ bwey yi yuu ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ sɛn .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ mi ̀ ni girig , ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ yii lɛ Man a ̀ mum a ̀ ti ja ̀ ŋbog ɗi ̀ ri ̀ yu ̀ di ɓi ̀ ghɛɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m .
N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ , bɔ ̀ ɓ i ɓum i ̀ nɛ ya ̀ a le ̀ g ɓi bimiɗ di ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ka kilɛn ɓi .
Ɗyoo ri ̀ zi ɓi ri ɓii ̀ le ̀ egh , ki ̀ ɓan ki ̀ fog ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓyɛm ̀ ɓyaa le ̀ g ɓi .
Ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ yii ɓi go ̀ n nsoo ̀ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ ; nsoo ̀ ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓɛ aɗyoo , nsoo ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓɔ a ̀ yii ɓi go ̀ n inɛ ̀ n , lɔŋ Ta ̀ a ̀ ta cɛ ̀ ncii yɛɛ yii .
Konaghna , ɓi ̀ ki ɓa cem , lɛ ɓi ̀ yii ɓi fin innɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓii ̀ kpaŋi ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki ri ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , a ̀ ca ̀ ɗ mɛɛ mii , a ̀ reɓsa ̀ g ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓii ri ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say lɛ , ri ̀ a ̀ nɛn mii ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ su wii wu kisay , a ̀ ki siitag m ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -i ̀ suunaa lɛ , a kɔri cem .
Fɔɔnnɛ kɔ ̀ riina cem , lɛ ɓi ̀ yii ɓi fin innɛ ŋwaa ̀ mɛɛ a ɓii ̀ kpaŋi ̀ . A ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ kpaŋ cɛŋko ̀ , nsoo ̀ lɛ ri ̀ n ̀ ɗem-iru ̀ , nsoo ̀ lɛ di ɓɛ ̀ lem ɓaa rɔ ̀ ŋ , nsoo ̀ lɛ sariwa ;
ɓi ̀ kona ̀ g lɛ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa lɛ a ̀ kpaŋ lɛ vua ̀ s , a ̀ tanɛ ̀ n mi ̀ ni di ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓi fi ̀ lo .
Ki ̀ ɓan ki n ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni ki , n ̀ kpaa kɔ ɓisuu ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m : Kɔ ̀ riina cem .
Ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ ti Paska ̀ ti ɓɛnki ̀ la ̀ g bi ̀ rɛs kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ nwi ̀ ɗ mii ̀ ti ɓagha ̀ di tyaa rɔ ̀ ɓ mɛru mɛɓɛɛ ̀ , nni ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓɛ kaaka ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ bee inɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓan ̀ Yeesus a ri ̀ nyam ɓɛɛ wey nyi .
Lɛ ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ki ki ̀ lɛɛ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ , lɛ ki ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u yi ri ̀ ki ̀ yoo ̀ yo ̀ o ̀ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɓagha ̀ a Bɛtanii ɓi naa i ̀ Simɔn a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ kukwiy , nni giɓ adɛŋ a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ y di Yeesus a ɗiɗi ɓiɗila ̀ g , giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓagha ̀ y ri ̀ ɓeŋ a ̀ nɛ a ɓagha ̀ n ̀ soɓɛn ri ri ̀ kuu ɗi gɔ ̀ g ɗi ŋwe ̀ rim-ŋwe ̀ rim , ɓeŋ a ̀ nce ̀ m a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ ɗonɛn ri ɓi ̀ syeesyee ɓi tira ̀ a ̀ re , ɓi ɓi ɓagha ̀ ɓi ̀ kɛŋɛn lɛɛ ̀ gwey ; fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ weeya ̀ ka ̀ ɓeŋ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n , a ̀ su ̀ u ̀ ri ̀ Yeesus ti ̀ ra ̀ a ̀ re ɓi n ̀ to .
Nni ki ɓeɓka ̀ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ , ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ŋwɔ ̀ ŋwɔ ̀ ŋi ̀ di ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa lɛ , ki ghɛɓsii cɛ lɛ a yogsi ti ̀ ra ̀ a ̀ re fɛlɛ ̀ ?
Tya ̀ a ri ̀ lɛ ti cee ɓɛ ̀ tɔɔsi ̀ m ɓɛraa , di ɓɛ kaɓi tyɔ , ɓɛ fa mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɛ mii ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sogha ̀ sogha ; ɓɛ kpɔmdɛ ̀ nga ̀ giɓ anɛ ̀ n lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ca ̀ rina giɓ anɛ , ɓi ki ̀ ki nyi fɔlɔɔ lɛ cɛ ? A ̀ ki ̀ i syeesyee a ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ɓisu wɛ ̀ m .
Lɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sogha ̀ sogha ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , ɓi ̀ ki ri ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ ki ̀ ɓɔ ki ̀ rɔɔ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ɓi ̀ kɔ ̀ ni , ki ̀ ɓan ki ̀ fog mɛ ̀ ma ̀ a ɓa ɓi ri mi ̀ ni ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m .
Giɓ anɛ a ̀ ki ̀ i ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ri ̀ nyi . A ̀ loogh mɛ ̀ ki ̀ siŋii tira ̀ a ̀ re ɓi ri ̀ ɓo ̀ m ɗi ɓɛ ri mɛ ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓo ̀ mi .
N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ , ja ̀ ŋbimiɗ i ̀ nɛ Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ kaaka ̀ lɛɛ gɛ ɓi ziinɛ bimiɗ , ɓɛ kpaakpaa gɛ girig ki ̀ ɓan ki giɓ anɛ a ̀ ki ̀ i ki , ɓɛ yii ̀ yi ̀ ta ̀ g nyi mii ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Zyudas Iskariyot , ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ Yeesus n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ , a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey lɛ a kaɓ ɓɔ Yeesus .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ woka ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ɓɛ nyaa ̀ rɛ ̀ n lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ɓɛ ki ka ̀ g nyi lɛ , ɓɛ ri nyi ɓii ̀ faa ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni . Fɔɔnnɛ Zyudas a ̀ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ min rikaaka ̀ a ̀ ɗi kirɔŋiɗ ki lɛ a fa ɓɔ Yeesus .
Ŋwos a n ̀ tonto a ̀ nɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ɓɛ nki ̀ la ̀ g bi ̀ rɛs ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ foŋ nwi ̀ ɗ mii ̀ , innɛ ɓɛ ŋweeyi ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ i ̀ Paska ̀ ; ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ Yeesus ɓɛ tɔka ̀ nyi lɛ : Fe nnɛ u kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ ti ̀ kɛn ̀ wɔ ̀ ki ̀ pe ̀ gsɛɛ ɓiɗila ̀ g ɓi Paska ̀ ?
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ romga ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Kɛ ̀ ɛna ɓi ba ̀ n , ɓi ̀ ɓii ̀ tuusɛɛ ri ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ di a ̀ tɛ ̀ tɛɛgh be ̀ e ̀ i mɛ ̀ nig , ɓi nɔɔ ̀ ti nyi ,
naa i ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ mii ̀ ɓii ̀ ɗiŋii , ɗiŋiina girig wɔɔ , ɓi kpaa ̀ ŋwaa ̀ mɛɛ lɛ : N ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g lɛ ki ̀ den ki naa ki nyii ri ɓii ̀ ɗii Paska ̀ mii ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii kin ̀ ki ri fe yɔ ?
A ̀ ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ re ̀ sii coo ki ̀ den ki naa ɓi mɛɛ aɗyoo , ki ̀ pe ̀ gsɛn ri ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , wɔɔ nnɛ ɓi ̀ ɓii ̀ pe ̀ gsɛɛ ɓiɗila ̀ g ɓi Paska ̀ .
Nni ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ ɓɛ kpaŋ ɓi ba ̀ n , ɓɛ tanɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ , ɓɛ pegsɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓi Paska ̀ wɔɔ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ cɛnko ̀ ki kpaga ̀ , Yeesus a ̀ yu ̀ y ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kɔri ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g , nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : N ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ , ki ̀ bog ki ɓi mi ̀ ni ki kɛɛ ̀ ɗiɗi nɗaŋ ri mɛ ̀ , ki ri mɛ ̀ ɓii ̀ ka ̀ ɓi .
Nni ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ samga ̀ ka ̀ , ri ̀ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n mii ̀ a ̀ tɔg nyi lɛ , mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ri nya yɔ ̀ ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ki ̀ bog ki ɓi mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ki ̀ ntɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ , ki ti ɗiɗi taasa ̀ bog , ri ̀ kɔ kɛɛ ̀ ri .
Man a ̀ mum a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ wii ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kanga ̀ lɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ wii ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan ki ̀ fog nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ nyi ɓii ̀ ka ̀ ɓi , ki ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ rɔɔ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n kɛ ̀ ɛ yalɛn .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ɗiɗi ̀ gha ̀ , nni Yeesus a ̀ teka ̀ bi ̀ rɛs , a ̀ fa Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ɓɛg min yɔ ̀ , a ̀ fa ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Terina , nyoo yɛ ̀ m yɛ ̀ ɛ ri lɛ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ teɗti ̀ gha ̀ ɓeŋ , a ̀ fa ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g di a ̀ mɛ ka fa Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n , nni ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ nɔgha ̀ ɓeŋ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Bwaɓ yɛm ̀ yɛɛ ri lɛ , bwaɓ yi ri ̀ ra ̀ rɛn ɗi lɛ ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ ɓum , yɛɛ ri ɓii ̀ kpaŋi ̀ ɓisuu ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ : Ma ̀ a nɔti ɓi mɛrɔ ̀ g mɛ vi ̀ inyɛ ̀ a ̀ kpaŋ ŋwos anɛ n ̀ nɔtii gɛ mɔ , nyɔɔnyɔn a ̀ ri ̀ nɔ , ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ mɛ gha ̀ ɓ tyem , ɓɛ ɓɔg min ɓi do ̀ n i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ o ̀ livyee .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii lɛ : Mi ̀ nii ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ ɓtɛɛ fiɓa ̀ g lɛ , ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : N ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ woli ̀ m ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yii yi saa ̀ tɛ ̀ n jaŋ ̀ bimiɗ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ ri ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗyɛm ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ loloogh ri mi ̀ ni a Galile .
Pyɛɛri a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Nsoo ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓaa kɛ ̀ ɓtɛɛ fi ̀ ɓa ̀ g , mɛ ̀ ma ̀ a kɛ ̀ ɓtɛn ɓi .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : N ̀ kpaa wɔ ̀ ɓi saaɗ lɛ : Ɓi ru wu gɛɛ ̀ nɛ wu , u ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓii ̀ roo ̀ zɛɛ gɛ ̀ n yiraa , di n ̀ lem a ̀ zag a ̀ ka rɔŋ ɓi gɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , Pyɛɛri a ̀ sii ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɓi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi ̀ i ̀ i ̀ nɛ lɛ : Nsoo ̀ kaa kpaŋi lɛ , n ̀ wu ɓɛɛ ̀ wɔ ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ , ma ̀ a roo ̀ zɛn ɓi ̀ wɔ . Ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛmbog ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ kpaati ̀ girig fɔlɔɔ .
Nni ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ min ɓi ja ̀ ŋ i ̀ dɛŋ ɗii lɛ Gɛsemane , Yeesus a ̀ kpaa ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii lɛ : Kɔ ̀ riina fɛ , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ka ki ̀ ki bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ Pyɛɛri ri ̀ Zyag ri ̀ Zyaŋ lɛ ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ nyi ki ̀ foŋi ̀ , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ wog ɗi n ̀ ɗemi-kɛŋɛn ɗi ̀ i ̀ ris ,
Nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : N ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ɗemi-kɛŋɛn wu wu ri lɛ , wu wey mɛ ̀ ; nni rɔ ̀ ɓina foo , ɓi kɔri cem .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ di ̀ gha ̀ asu lɛsa ̀ g , a ̀ kpi ̀ ɓi zi ri mɛ ̀ ɗu , a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ , i kaa ri ̀ lɛ ki kilɛ ̀ n lɛ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki kɛɛ raɓsɛn nyi ,
a ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ lɛ : Ta ̀ a ̀ ta wɛ ̀ m , u ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ u ̀ ki ̀ com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ; ki ̀ ya lɛ ɓeŋ a ̀ ri ̀ wu a ̀ nɛ a ra ̀ ɓsɛn mɛ ̀ ; nsoo ̀ n ̀ kpaa fɔlɔɔ , ki ̀ ya ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗyɔɔ , a ̀ a ɗiŋkɛ ̀ m .
Nni a ̀ sugti ̀ gha ̀ y ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ , a ̀ tanɛ ̀ n ɓɔ di ɓaa cuu tilo ̀ , a ̀ kpaa Pyɛɛri lɛ : Simɔn , u ̀ lali yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ ri ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ u kɔri cem bimiɗ a ̀ hawo ̀ ɗyaa yaagh wɔ ̀ wa ?
Kɔ ̀ riina cem , ɓi ̀ ki ɓɔ ̀ ɔɓɔŋza ̀ g Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ kɛ ̀ ɓi tanɛn ri mɛ ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn . Ɓisuulɛ n ̀ ghay wu mum wu ri ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ ki ̀ ɓan kifog nyoo i ̀ ɓa kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ .
Nni a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ di ̀ gha ̀ ti ̀ ɓɔ fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ a ɓɔ ̀ ŋzi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ ɓi ̀ i ̀ ti ̀ ti ̀ lɔŋ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi a ̀ loka ̀ ki ̀ kpaa ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ sugti ̀ gha ̀ y ti ̀ ri ̀ jɛ ̀ m , a ̀ tanɛ ̀ n ti ̀ lɔŋ ɓɛyila ̀ g ɓi fi ̀ lo , lɛ fi ̀ lo fi ronga ̀ ɓɔ mis , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa ri ̀ com ki kpaayɛn .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ sugti ̀ gha ̀ y ti ̀ ɓi gɛ ̀ n i ki ̀ raa , nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , lalina ̀ lɛ ɓi fɔɔ ̀ sɛn ; ki ̀ lee ̀ gh , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ , ɓi ghɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ɓii ̀ ka ̀ ɓi Man a ̀ mum ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe .
Pɛ ̀ sɛɛna aɗyoo , ti kɛn ̀ lɛ , roa ̀ nɛ a ka ̀ kaɓ mɛ a ̀ tii ̀ .
Yeesus a ̀ kaka a ̀ to ̀ to ̀ g fɔlɔɔ , Zyudas a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ɗi ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ s ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ . A ɓagha ̀ y ri ̀ ki ̀ tuu ki ɓum ki ki yugha ̀ y lɛ ri ̀ ga ̀ fa ̀ g ri ̀ ɓi ̀ geŋ ; ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛɛ romga ̀ y ɓɔ .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ka ̀ ɓka ̀ ɓɔ Yeesus a ̀ wooghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ , lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓi ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ di n ̀ lɔ ̀ ri , ɓi ̀ yi lɛ nnyɛɛri , ɓi ɓan ̀ , ɓi kɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ nyi , ɓi ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋ nyi ̀ lɛ syeesyee .
Lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Zyudas a ̀ kpaga ̀ , a ̀ gha ̀ s ki ̀ tyo ̀ ŋdɛɛ Yeesus a nyoo , a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Raɓi ̀ !
A ̀ lwɛ ̀ ɗ nyi . Ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ sɛn min ɓi Yeesus , ɓɛ ɓan nyi .
Nni ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ Yeesus , ki sɔni ̀ gha ̀ y ga ̀ fa ̀ g ɓi ɗyaŋ , ki ɓog n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say a n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey , i ̀ ree ̀ wu lɛy .
Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n lɛ : Ɓi ̀ ghɛɛ mɛ ̀ lɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ zyaa ̀ zyaa , nni ɓi yu ̀ u yi ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ga ̀ fa ̀ g ri ̀ ɓi ̀ geŋ lɛ ɓi ɓan ̀ mɛ ̀ ?
Mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ lɔŋ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛ ̀ ŋwos ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , n ̀ ɗe ̀ e ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɓum , kɛ ̀ ɓi ki ɓan mɛ ; ki ̀ ɓan kifog ki kilɛɛ fɔlɔɔ lɛ , ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ri ɓi ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ɓyɛɛ ron ̀ .
Nni ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ tuɓi ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ree , ɓɛ rini ̀ Yeesus .
Dɛli ̀ i ̀ dɛŋ i ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ Yeesus n ̀ ɗyeɓɓɛn sa ̀ nja ̀ nyi ri ̀ nyi , nni ɓɛ ɓanga ̀ yɔ ̀ ,
i ̀ naŋ sa ̀ nja ̀ , i ̀ ghaa ̀ gh ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ree ki ̀ to ̀ n zɛy .
Ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓanga ̀ Yeesus ɓɛ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ nyi yɛ ̀ ɛ nkɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ , wɔɔ nnɛ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓɛ taŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ .
Pyɛɛri a ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ y Yeesus fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ a ̀ kpaŋ ɓi n ̀ lɛmɓog wu nkɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n-ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say , a wowo ̀ g ɗuu .
Ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey , ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓi Sa ̀ ne ̀ di ̀ rɛŋ ɓɛ kaaka ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki lɛ ɓɛɛ wey Yeesus mii ̀ , ɓɛ kɛɛ ̀ ki ghɛ ̀ n .
Ɓisuulɛ ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ pwaapwa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ nyi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi nyoo , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ wɔɔsɛn .
Ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ rɛli ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ pwa ̀ a ̀ nyi ki ̀ ɓan ɓi nyoo , ɓɛ kpaa lɛ :
Ti ̀ i n ̀ woogh di a kpaakpaa lɛ , a ɓii ̀ wa ̀ a ̀ ghii naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛ ɓum ɓɛ toga ̀ i ̀ nɛ , a ̀ toŋdi ̀ i ̀ dɛŋ ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛraa mum kɛ ̀ ɛ foŋ ca ̀ g mii ̀ .
Nsoo ̀ ɓi n ̀ to wu sɔmi ̀ na ̀ win ̀ , jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi ɓumɓɛ ̀ n yi ɓagha ̀ dɛŋ dɛ ̀ ŋ dɛŋ .
Nni n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n-ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ aɗyoo ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ da ̀ , a ̀ tɔg Yeesus lɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ kpaa la ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ kpaa ki , ɓɛ raɗ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ ?
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Yeesus a ̀ mi ̀ nɛ ̀ nga ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa ̀ g . Nni n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n-ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ ɓi ̀ i ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ nyi ki ̀ tɔɔ ̀ gh lɛ wɔ ̀ yɛɛ ri ̀ Kiris , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɔgsa ̀ g ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : N ̀ ɗi ̀ Kiris , ɓi ̀ ki ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɛ Man a ̀ mum di a ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔrii ɓi wee ̀ lem a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wuce ̀ m , a ̀ ki yu ̀ yuiy ɓi ɓi ̀ kwi ̀ ɗ ɓi aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n-ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ ska ̀ ka ̀ ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ɓi a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɓyɔ ɓi nyoo , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Ti ̀ ɓii ̀ kaatii ti ɓɛ ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛdɛŋ lɛ cɛ ?
Mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ ɓi ̀ woogh yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ fengii Bɛ ̀ ll , nni ɓi ̀ kpaa la ? Ɓum ɓɛmbog ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ fagha ̀ Yeesus zɔɔ , ɓɛ kpaa lɛ , ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ wey nyi .
Ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi ri ̀ tuutu ̀ u ̀ ɗi tityɛɛ ̀ , ɓɛ kiki ̀ lɛ , i ɓɛ lɔɔgh nyi ki ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ɓi mis , ɓɛ ɓoo ̀ ɓo ̀ ki ̀ nyi ɓi ̀ kam di ɓɛɛ tɔtɔg nyi lɛ : Re ̀ mi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓoogh wɔ ̀ . Ɓi ɗi lɛ ɓɛɛ ghaɓ nyi , ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛ togsi ̀ gha ̀ nyi ri ̀ tyɛn ti mɛɓɛn .
