n ̀ ɗem wii wu nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g wɛɛ ghɛnag ɓi gba ̀ a ̀ yi ̀ ce ̀ m , a ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ni ̀ gi nyi .
