Marii a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛɛ Eliisaɓɛt , nunu ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ ŋwii ɓara , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ suka ̀ min .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki lɛ Eliisaɓɛt a yas ̀ ki kpaga ̀ , nni a ̀ yala ̀ man a ̀ baŋi ̀ .
Ɓumɓɛ a ̀ wɔŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ mɛɛ ri bɔ , ri ̀ ɓɔɔseŋi ɓii ɓɛ woka ̀ lɛ Kan a ̀ a n ̀ ɗe ̀ sii nyi geesɛ ̀ n yi ̀ i ̀ lɛ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ nyaa ̀ rɛ ̀ n n ̀ ɗaŋ ri nyi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ man a ̀ kpaga ̀ mɛ ̀ ru taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , nni ɓɛ yugha ̀ ri ̀ nyi lɛ ɓɛɛ kɛ ̀ ɗ , ɓɛ rere ̀ ŋi ̀ nyi lɛ Zakarii , ɓi ɗii ɗi ̀ seŋi wi ̀ i ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , jɛɛ a ̀ pɛ ̀ si ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : E ̀ e e ̀ e ! A ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ i ɓaa ɗii lɛ Zyaŋ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ ɓi boo yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ a ̀ ka ɓagha ̀ ɓi ɗii fɔlɔɔ .
