Nni wɔ ̀ man a ̀ nɛ , ɓum ɓɛ ri regag wɔ lɛ : N ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan a Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ teŋmɛɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ve ̀ g , ɓisuulɛ u ̀ ɓii ̀ syo ̀ ŋi Kan bee , lɛ u log ki ̀ pe ̀ gsɛɛ bee yii ̀ ,
u ̀ ki ki ̀ lɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kii ɓɛɛ yi lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ko ̀ ri ɓɔ , lɛ a ̀ mɛ cenɛn ɓɔ ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓyaa .
Lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll wi ̀ s a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ɗonɛn ri coo geesɛ ̀ n , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ri rom yi ɓi ̀ si ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ki aɗyoo , ki ki ri fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ baso i ̀ ŋwos
lɛ kɛɛ kpeŋzi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓi biri ̀ m , ri ̀ ɓi ki ̀ fi ̀ i ̀ ki riwu ̀ , ki kɛɛ ̀ si ̀ ɓi ̀ si ɓi bee i ̀ cɛɓ ki fyo ̀ oog .
