Ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ , kaaza a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɗii lɛ Ogus , a ̀ lami ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓay ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓi zi bimiɗ .
