nni a ̀ yala ̀ man wi ̀ i ̀ a ̀ n ̀ tonto baŋi ̀ , a ̀ lɔki ̀ nyi ri ̀ ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ , a ̀ nɔ ̀ ŋzi ̀ nyi ɓi ki ̀ ɓɛrɛ ki ɓi ̀ tuwe ɓi n ̀ ɗila ̀ g mii ̀ lɛ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɛ kɔri ̀ mii ̀ i ̀ ɓati ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ɓi naa ̀ -ɓɛ ̀ ke ̀ n .
Ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kɔm ̀ kin ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ be ̀ ŋi ̀ -jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓɛ n ̀ laayi ̀ cɛm a dɛm , ɓɛ ɓeŋɓe ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ tuwe ɓyaa .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a Kan a ̀ resɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ , ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ki rigwey ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ki ceŋzɛ ̀ n ɓɔ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ risi ̀ gha ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Kɛ ̀ ɓi risi ̀ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ i ̀ mi ̀ ni ri ̀ syeesyee a ̀ ɓɔlɛ ̀ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ faa ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki ̀ ce ̀ m coo kinya ̀ a ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ rem .
Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ : n ̀ ghɛɓsi ̀ ɓum a ̀ yalɛɛ gɛɛ ̀ nɛ ɓi ̀ su wi ̀ n , ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ Davit , nnyɛɛ ri Kiris Kan .
Nni ki ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ ki ki ri mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ re ̀ sii nyi ki ri lɛ , ɓi ̀ ɓii ̀ tanɛɛ man a ̀ m ̀ ɓwɛɗ n ̀ lɔkakɛn , n ̀ nɔ ̀ ŋziyɛn ɓi ki ̀ ɓɛrɛ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ sigmɛ ̀ nga ̀ di ki ̀ tuu ki ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓɛ aɗyoo ki mɛ yu ̀ ki tanɛɛ roa ̀ n ̀ tonto , ɓɛ ɓɔɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ gsi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll di ɓɛɛ kpaakpaa lɛ ;
Ri ̀ kem ɗyɛɛ ki Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ɗyoo ɓi ɗu ̀ m , fyo ̀ oog a ̀ ɓa ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓi ziinɛ ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ keesii .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓɛ sugti ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ ɓɔɔgh aɗyoo , nni ɓɛ ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓɛ rɔɓka ̀ ki ̀ kpaa wɔɔ ɓɔ ri ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ti kɛ ̀ ɛna a Bɛtilɛhɛm , ti ghɛn ki ̀ ɓan ki kaa ki ̀ lɛɛ wɔɔ , kɛɛ ̀ ki Kan a ̀ a wogsii ɓi ̀ si .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ wɔɔ ri mɛ ̀ ree , ɓɛ tanɛ ̀ n Marii ri ̀ Yoosɛɓ , ri ̀ maa man a ̀ nɛ ̀ n n ̀ nɔ ̀ nɔŋiyɛn ɓi ki ̀ ɓɛrɛ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ man a ̀ nɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ kpaa ɗi ɓiɓan ɓi ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ ɓi ki ̀ ɓan kii .
Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ woka ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓɛ ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ ɓin ̀ , ɓɛ kuura ̀ ka ̀ ɓyɔ .
Marii a ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋɓe ̀ ŋga ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ ki fe ̀ feg ɓyɔ ri ̀ n ̀ ɗem .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓɛ sugti ̀ gha ̀ di ɓɛɛ ɓɔɔɓɔgsi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓɛ kee ̀ ke ̀ mzi ̀ nyi ri ̀ tyem ɓisuulɛ , ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ , ɓi ɓagha ̀ com ki ̀ fog ri ̀ ɓi ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ .
Ɓi mɛ ̀ ru taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ghɛɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ kɛ ̀ ri man , innɛ ɓɛ roo ̀ gha ̀ nyi ɗii lɛ Yeesus ; ɗii ɗi ̀ n ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a ̀ fagha ̀ , di jɛɛ a ̀ ka teɗ ɓi ɗyem ɗii .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki zo ̀ ghɛ ̀ n inɛ Yoosɛɓ ɓɛɛ ̀ Marii ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ lɛɛ ki kpaga ̀ , lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri ɓi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Moyis , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ ri ̀ man a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a Yorisalɛm , lɛ ɓɛɛ resi nyi ɓi mis mɛ Kan ,
lɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ɓi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Kan lɛ : Man a ̀ baŋi ̀ bimiɗ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ man a ̀ n ̀ tonn ̀ to , ɓɛ ̀ yali ̀ ɓii ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ nyi ki ̀ faa ̀ ri ̀ Kan ;
ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ fu ̀ nɛɛ ɓɛ ̀ kuu ̀ kuu ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ , nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ sɔ ̀ m ɓɛ ko ̀ oko ̀ s ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ , lɛ fɔɔnnɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ɓi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Kan .
Ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ̀ n , ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ a Yorisalɛm ɗii lɛ Simeyɔŋ , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ syeesyee a ̀ mum , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ a nti a ̀ risa ̀ g Bɛ ̀ ll ; a ̀ ɓoŋɓo ̀ ŋga ̀ go ̀ ri i ̀ Isirayɛl , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay .
Nni Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ki re ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ nyi lɛ , a ̀ a wu ɓi di a ̀ ka ghɛn ɓi Kiris a ̀ nɛ Kan a ̀ ɓii ̀ romi ̀ i ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Simeyɔŋ a ̀ yugha ̀ y ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll yɛ ̀ ɛ Nghay a ̀ tini ̀ gha ̀ y nyi ; nni ɓɛ ̀ yali ̀ ɓɛ Yeesus ɓɛ yuyu ̀ gha ̀ y ri ̀ man waa ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ roo ̀ zi ri ̀ kpaa ɗi ɓi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll .
Fɔɔnnɛ Simeyɔŋ a ̀ gha ̀ ɓka ̀ man a ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓi ɓya ̀ g ɓii , a ̀ fa Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ kem a ̀ kpaa lɛ :
Ta ̀ a ̀ ta , u ̀ ti lɛ u ̀ ca ̀ ɗ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say wɔɔ lɛ , a sug ri ̀ n ̀ ɗem ɓi ɗu ̀ m ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ mɛ roozi n ̀ ka ̀ g wɔɔ .
Ɓisuulɛ mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ n ̀ ɗuusii mis ɓi nghɛɓsi ̀ -ɓum a ̀ nɛ u ̀ romii ̀
nyi nnɛ u ̀ pe ̀ gsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi mis mɛ ɓilɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m .
A ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ki kii ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ɓi ziinɛ ɓyɛ yi wɔ ̀ , ki ki fa Isirayɛl a ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kɔɔ rikem .
Seŋi ri ̀ jɛɛ Yeesus ɓɛ rɔɓka ̀ myɔm ɓi ̀ kpaŋ , ɓɛ keg ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Simeyɔŋ a ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ ɓisuu man a ̀ nɛ ̀ n .
Fɔɔnnɛ Simeyɔŋ a ̀ ma ̀ ga ̀ ɓɔ , a ̀ kpaa Marii a ̀ jɛɛ man lɛ : Man a ̀ nɛ A ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ ɓumɓɛ a Isirayɛl lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛɛ kɛɓtɛn fi ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛmbog ɓɛ ɓa kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ bɛ ̀ lɛn ; a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ roa ̀ nɛ a konag ki ̀ re ̀ sii yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛ ɓee ̀ zɛɛ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ,
Wɔɔmiɗ anɛ , u ̀ ɓii ̀ woo ̀ gh n ̀ ɗemi-kɛŋɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ mɛ ̀ yiti ̀ mɛ mɛ ri ̀ ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓi mɛ ̀ rem mɛ ɓii ̀ yilɛɛ .
Giɓ adɛŋ ɗii lɛ Ana , gɔ ̀ n i ̀ Fanuɛl , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓi ri ̀ pwi ̀ ɗ ɗi Azɛr a ɓati ̀ gha ̀ girig n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan a Bɛ ̀ ll . A ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ mɛ ru ̀ n lɛɛ ̀ gwey ; a ̀ ghɛɓka ̀ be ̀ g taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓɛ wɔlɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɛɛ ̀ nyi ɓi ri ̀ gɔ ̀ n ɗii .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓka ̀ n ̀ kpɔɓ ; yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ min di a ̀ ti be ̀ g mɛ ̀ tin mɛnin ri ̀ be ̀ g yinin , nni a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ suu ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ki ̀ say lɛ , ri ̀ i ̀ ru ri ̀ ŋwos ; a ̀ a n ̀ ti a ̀ ce ̀ la ̀ g ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n lɛɛ ̀ gwey , a ̀ ki ɓɔ ̀ ɔɓɔŋza ̀ g .
Nni giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ y girig ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kɔm ̀ kin ̀ , a ̀ tum ri ̀ fa ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ kem , a ̀ ki kpaakpaa ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓoŋɓo ̀ ŋga ̀ go ̀ ri i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓisuu Yorisalɛm ki ̀ ɓan ki Yeesus .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ yali ̀ ɓɛ Yeesus ɓɛ legsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓɛ ghɛɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Kan ɓyɛɛ ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ , nni ɓɛ sugti ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ nyi a Galile , ɓi ban i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ kɔkɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ wɔɔ lɛ Naazarɛt .
Fɔɔnnɛ man a ̀ nɛn a tɔɔtɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ gha ̀ a ̀ ki te ̀ etee ̀ sɛ ̀ n ; a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n lɛɛ ̀ gwey , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki keekee ̀ si ̀ nyi .
Ɓɛ ̀ yali ̀ ɓɛ Yeesus ɓɛ n ̀ ti ɓɛ kɛngi ̀ ki ̀ ɗii ̀ Paska ̀ a Yorisalɛm be ̀ g yi ̀ ce ̀ m .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ ti be ̀ g n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ yiɓɛɛ ̀ , nni ɓɛ kɛɛdi ̀ gha ̀ lɔŋ Paska ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ n ̀ kɛ ̀ ngi ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ ti leka ̀ , nni ɓɛ suka ̀ , wɔ ̀ lɛ Yeesus a ̀ man waa ̀ a ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓ yi ̀ a Yorisalɛm ɓɔ ɓɔ kɔɔ ̀ yi .
Di ɓɛ mɛ kɛɛ ̀ ghi bimiɗ a ŋwos , ɓɛ fefe ̀ g lɛ Yeesus a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ki ̀ tuu ki ɓum ki ɓɛ kɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ kɔ , nni ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi ri ̀ kaa , di ɓɛɛ tɔtɔg nyi ri ̀ ɓɔɔseŋi ɓaa , ri ̀ ɓisɛn ɓyaa .
Ɓaa rɔ ̀ ɓ ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ghɛn nyi , nni ɓɛ sugti ̀ gha ̀ min a Yorisalɛm di ɓɛɛ ̀ tɔtɔ ̀ g .
Ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛɓɛɛ ̀ nnɛ ɓɛ tanɛɛ nyi ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll n ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔriyɛn ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , a ̀ tɔtɔ ̀ g ɓɔ mɛ ̀ tɔɔ ̀ ghtɔɔgh , a ̀ ki wowog riɓa ̀ g ɗyaa .
Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ wowo ̀ ka ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓii ɓɛ kuura ̀ ka ̀ coo ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗii , ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɗi a ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ yali ̀ ɓii ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ nyi , ɓɛ kuura ̀ g lɛɛ ̀ gwey , nni jɛɛ a ̀ tɔka ̀ nyi lɛ : Man wɛm ̀ , u ̀ yeesii ɓa ̀ ɓisi fɛlɛ lɛ cɛ ? Ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ri ̀ soŋi tya ̀ a ti ̀ mɛ ̀ rem aɗyo ̀ o ̀ lɛ ti kaakaa wɔ .
Nni a ̀ ɓaka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓya ̀ a kaakaa mɛ ̀ ? Ɓya ̀ a yii ɓi lɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ nkiki ɓiɓan ɓi Seŋi wɛ ̀ m ?
Ki ̀ ɓan ki ̀ fog , ɓɛ yigha ̀ ɓi ̀ azi anɛ ɓi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ i ̀ nɛ ̀ n .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ sugti ̀ gha ̀ min ri ɓɔ a Naazarɛt , a ki ̀ ki ̀ ɓɔ mɛ ̀ wog ; jɛɛ a ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋɓe ̀ ŋga ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi n ̀ ɗem .
Yeesus a ̀ tɔɔtɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ gha ̀ , ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗii ɗi tee ̀ ghte ̀ ghɛ ̀ n , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kee ̀ ke ̀ e ̀ si ̀ nyi , ɓum ɓɛ ki keekee ̀ si ̀ nyi girig .
Di Ti ̀ ɓɛr a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗigwey a ti ɓe ̀ g n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ yitan ̀ ɓi ri ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki Pɔŋs-Pilat a ̀ ɓaa gɔmi ̀ na ̀ a ̀ nɛ a Zyude , Eroodɛ a ̀ la ̀ lami ̀ Galile , geni a ̀ nɛ lɛ Filiɓ nyii lala ̀ mi ̀ ɓi ̀ den ɓi zi ɓi lɛ , ri ̀ Iture ri ̀ Tirakonit , Lizanyas nyii lala ̀ mi ̀ Abilɛn
An ri ̀ Kayif ɓɔɔ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ; nni Zyaŋ a ̀ man a ̀ Zakarii a ̀ woka ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll di a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi-reɓ .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ rere ̀ ni ̀ ɗi ko ̀ do ̀ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ Zyuridɛŋ , di a la ̀ alamɓɛ ̀ n lɛ , ɓum ɓɛɛ lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛn mɛ ̀ rem , ɓɛ ɓaɓta ̀ g , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a cenɛn ɓɔ ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓyaa .
Lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi a ̀ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan Ezayii lɛ : Jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛn i ̀ ri ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ roa ̀ nɛ a la ̀ alamɓɛ ̀ n yi ̀ ɓi-reɓ lɛ : Pe ̀ gsɛɛna bee yi Kan bi ̀ rɛsa ̀ g yɔ lɛ saaɗ .
Ɓɛ ɓii ̀ roozaagh ɓigbɔ ̀ g ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , ɓɛ ɓu ̀ gsi ̀ lɛ ri ̀ do ̀ n ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ke ̀ eke ̀ y , ɓɛ ki rɛsag ti ɓɛ ̀ kɔna ̀ ɓɛ bee , ɓɛ tii ̀ ghgɛ ̀ n girig bee yi yi ri ri ̀ mɛ ̀ gbeŋ .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ mum bimiɗ a ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɛ go ̀ ri i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ɓum ɓɛ yuyu ̀ gha ̀ y yɛ ̀ ɛ Zyaŋ ɓi ̀ tuu lɛ ɓi ̀ tuu , lɛ a ɓa ̀ ɓti ɓɔ , nyii ki kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ pisɛɛ ɓi ̀ go ̀ m ɓɛ ! Ghɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ reɓi mi ̀ ni lɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ ghɛŋi ̀ ri ̀ baŋi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ɗi ɗi rii ̀ ?
Nni ki ̀ ina min ɓiɓan ɓi ɓyɛɛ resi lɛ , ɓi ̀ mɛ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛn mɛrem ; kɛ ̀ ɓi kpaakpaa ɓi mɛ ̀ rem min lɛ : Abiraham a ̀ ri ̀ seŋi wi ̀ s a n ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ; ɓisuulɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ ki ̀ lɛ gɔ ̀ g yi yɛɛ ghas ̀ ɓɔn ɓɛ Abiraham , mɛ ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ kpaa mi ̀ ni .
Ɓi kiŋce ̀ m , fi ̀ seŋ fi ti a ɓi ̀ te zi lɛ , ki ̀ te kice ̀ m ki kii ɓii ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓi kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ wum ɓiɗu ̀ n ɓi syeesyee , ɓɛ ɓii ̀ kpɛ ̀ ɛ kɔ , ɓɛ wo ̀ n kɔ ɓi ɗuu .
Nni gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ ̀ n i ̀ tɔka ̀ nyi lɛ : Cɛ kɛɛ ̀ ki ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ min ki ki ̀ i ?
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ɓiɓɛɛ ̀ , a fa ge ̀ ni a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɔ ki ̀ fog ; ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓyom ɓi ɗiyɛn , a yiti ge ̀ ni a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ com .
Ɓɛ ̀ teri ̀ -la ̀ mpoŋ ̀ ɓɛ yugha ̀ y girig lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓaɓti ɓɔ , nni ɓɛ tɔka ̀ nyi lɛ : N ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g , cɛ ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ?
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ɓaka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Kɛ ̀ ɓi sagtɛn com ɓi ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɛ la ̀ mpoŋ ̀ i ̀ nɛ ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ tɔɔ ̀ gh .
Ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ tɔka ̀ girig nyi lɛ : Ɓi ̀ si yo ̀ g , cɛ kɛɛ ̀ ki ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ? A ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Kɛ ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓa ̀ tag mum com ɓi-te ̀ ɗ , kɛ ̀ ɓi ki sɔmag mum di a ̀ ki ̀ i ɓi kiɓan ki ɓeɓtɛn ; nya ̀ a ̀ rɛɛna ri ̀ mɛ ̀ le ̀ ɓ mɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ leɓki ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓi ki ̀ say kin .
Ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki ɓoŋɓo ̀ ŋga ̀ ri ̀ dya ̀ ɓɛn , ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ feki ̀ nya lɛ Zyaŋ nnyɛ ̀ ɛ ri Kiris .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔɔ ̀ ce ̀ m lɛ : Mɛ ̀ ɛ m ̀ ɓa ̀ aɓaɓti ̀ mi ̀ ni ri ̀ mɛ ̀ nig , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ cee mɛ ̀ ɓi-te ̀ ɗ a ̀ tii ̀ , n ̀ kpaŋi gi ̀ ɓi ɓi n ̀ koŋ wulɛ m ̀ fu ̀ mi ̀ n ̀ ɗig wii wu go ̀ o ̀ . Nnyɛɛ ri mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓtii ri Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay , ri ̀ ɗuu .
