Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n , nni a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ a mɛɛ mɛ Simɔn , a ̀ tanɛ ̀ n jɛɛ gili Simɔn di a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ fɛɓ ɓi nyoo lɛɛ ̀ gwey ; fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ tɔka ̀ Yeesus lɛ a ghɛɓsi nyi .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ loŋmɛ ̀ nga ̀ giɓ anɛ ̀ n ɓi nyoo , a ̀ fwa ̀ a ̀ dɛ ̀ n ki ̀ fɛɓ ki ki ɓagha ̀ nyi ɓi nyoo ki ̀ n , ki ̀ fɛɓ ki le ̀ g , giɓ a gha ̀ s ki ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ aɗyoo , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓyom ɓi ki ̀ yɛn lɛ a kaa ̀ ɓɔ .
Di ŋwos a mɛ nɔ ̀ ŋi ̀ , ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roroɓ mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ ̀ kuu , ɓɛ yugha ̀ y nyi ri ̀ ɓɔ , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ sasa ̀ ghi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ ɓya ̀ g ɓi nyoo , a wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zi ̀ ɓɔ .
Ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay ɓi kpaŋkpa ̀ ŋga ̀ girig ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓi nyoo , di ɓyɛɛ ̀ syaasyaa ̀ dɛ ̀ n ɓi kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ lɛ : U ̀ ri ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , wɔ ̀ lɛ Yeesus kɛ ̀ ɛ fa ɓyɔ bee i ̀ nɛ lɛ , ɓyɛɛ too ̀ ghrɛn , ɓisuulɛ ɓi yigha ̀ lɛ nnyɛɛ ri Kiris .
A ̀ faŋi ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɛŋ ki ja ̀ ŋ sariwa lɛ ɓuɓ ; nni ɓi ̀ tuu ɓi ɓum ɓi tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi ri ̀ kaa , yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi tanɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi , ɓɛ kɔn ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ cɛɛ ̀ zi nyi kɛ ̀ ɛ ghaghi a ̀ ca ̀ ɗ ɓɔ .
Ki ̀ ɓan ki ̀ fog Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ , n ̀ ghagsi Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ba ̀ n yimbog , lɛ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ romga ̀ y mɛ ̀ mii ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kaka ̀ li ̀ gha ̀ ɓum Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ ɓi naa yi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n yi a Galile .
Ŋwos adɛŋ , Yeesus a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi n ̀ wɔŋi ̀ wu riɓa ̀ y a ̀ nɛ a Zyenezarɛt , fɔɔnnɛ gwi ̀ y i ̀ kɔ ̀ mzɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi , ɓum ɓɛ tyɔɔ ̀ tyɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ rɛ ̀ n , lɛ ɓɛɛ wog ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ,
nni a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ɓi ̀ kɔm ɓiɓɛɛ ̀ ɓi be ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y . Ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ i ̀ gh-dam ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɓyɔ , ɓɛ sɛnga ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ cug dam yaa .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ɓɔka ̀ ɓi ki ̀ kɔm ki ̀ fog , ki ki ɓagha ̀ ki Simɔn , a ̀ tɔg Simɔn lɛ , a raɓsɛn ti ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ be ̀ n i ̀ mɛ ̀ nig lɛsa ̀ g ; nni a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ min ɓi ki ̀ kɔm , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɗi gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ le ̀ gsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ , nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ Simɔn lɛ : Tyɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ti ki ̀ kɔm ɓi dim i ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y , ɓi pi ̀ g dam wɔɔ , ɓi ɓan ɓi ̀ zɛn .
Simɔn a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : N ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g , tya ̀ a lali cem ɓi dam i ̀ m ̀ pi ̀ ghɛn , tyɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ɓan com , nni n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ pi ̀ igh dam lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ wɔ ̀ yɛɛ kpaa .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ pika ̀ dam , nni ɓɛ ɓanga ̀ ɓi ̀ zɛn lɛɛ ̀ gwey le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ dam yaa yi tuu ̀ tu ̀ nɛ ̀ nga ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ reŋigha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓaa ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ki ̀ kɔm kimbog ri ̀ kuriɓa ̀ ɓ lɛ ɓɛɛ yu ɓɔ ki ̀ gheŋzii ritu ̀ g ɗi ɓi ̀ zɛn ; ɓɛ yuis ̀ , ɓɛ roo ̀ zi ̀ ɓi ̀ zɛn ɓi ɓi ̀ kɔm ɓi kiɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ ɓi tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓim .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Simɔn Pyɛɛri a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ fɔlɔɔ , nni a ̀ ɓaka ̀ Yeesus mɛ ̀ ɗu asu , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Kan , pɛ ̀ sɛn mɛ ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog , ɓisuulɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe .
A kpaagha ̀ fɔlɔɔ lɛ , i ̀ ris wu ɓanga ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ Simɔn , ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ , ɓisuulɛ ɓɛ ɓanga ̀ ɓi ̀ zɛn lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
I ̀ ris wu ɓaadi ̀ gha ̀ girig ɓɔn ɓɛ Zeɓede ɓɛ kiɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ lɛ ri ̀ Zyag ri ̀ Zyaŋ ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ reŋka ̀ ŋ ɓɛ Simɔn . Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ Simɔn lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ɔ risi , a ̀ tumɛɛ gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , ɓum ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓwemɓwemi ɓi sig a ̀ ɓi ̀ zɛn .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ sugtigha ̀ y ri ̀ ɓi ̀ kɔm a cɛɗ , nni ɓɛ ca ̀ ɗka ̀ ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ nɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ Yeesus .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ̀ ba ̀ n i ̀ dɛŋ , nni ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ kwiy a ̀ ɗyɛɛrɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyoo bimiɗ a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ nyi , a ̀ kpi ̀ nyi a mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ , a ̀ ɓag i ̀ su ɓi zi , a ̀ ɓɔŋzi ̀ nyi lɛ : N ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g , i ki kɔni wɔ ̀ , ki ̀ ya ɓa ̀ lɛ mɓati lɛ syeesyee ɓi nyoo yɛ ̀ m .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ na ̀ mga ̀ ca ̀ g , a ̀ ko ̀ m nyi , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Ki kɔni mɛ ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ɓati lɛ syeesyee ɓi nyoo yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ; kwiy a gha ̀ s nyi ki ̀ le ̀ egh ɓi nyo ̀ o ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ siita ̀ ka ̀ nyi lɛ : Kɔɔ ɓu ̀ ŋ mum ki ̀ ɓan ki , wɔ ̀ lɛ , kɛ ̀ na ki re ̀ sɛɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ , u funɛn com ɓisuu zo ̀ ghɛ ̀ n yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Moyis a ̀ ka ̀ nga ̀ , ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗin ̀ ɗyɛɛ resi ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m lɛ u ̀ mɛ wɔ ̀ n .
Ri ̀ kem ɗi Yeesus ɗi kɛnkɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɔŋ asu di ɗyɛɛ ̀ sa ̀ a ̀ sa ̀ a ̀ . Ɓum ɓɛ nti ɓɛ taŋza ̀ g ɓyoo gwi ̀ y lɛ ɓɛɛ wowog ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓii , ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ , a wɔɔ ̀ zi ɓɔ ti ̀ roɓ tyaa .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog Yeesus nyii n ̀ ti a ̀ kɛ ̀ ngi ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ lɛŋ ɓi jaŋ , a ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n wɔɔ .
Ŋwos adɛŋ , Yeesus a ̀ re ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ ka ̀ ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll nni Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓɛ ɓɛ pɛsɛnga ̀ y ɓi ɓɔɔ ɓilɔ ̀ ŋ ɓɛ a Galile , ri ̀ ɓɛ a Zyude ri ̀ ɓɛ a Yorisalɛm ɓɛ kɔkɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ wɔɔ . I ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu Bɛ ̀ ll wu wu ɓagha ̀ ɓi Kan wu kiki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , a wɔɔ ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zi ̀ ɓum .
Nni ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ tɛka ̀ y mum a ̀ nɛ a ̀ yiti ̀ gha ̀ ɓi rikɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓi kon , ɓɛ kaaka ̀ a ̀ bee inɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɗiŋi ri ̀ nyi ɓi naa , di ɓɛɛ ŋɔŋzi Yeesus nyi asu .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ ɓi bee inɛ ɓɛɛ ɗiŋzi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ gwi ̀ y i ̀ ceegha ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ɓɔka ̀ ri ̀ nyi a bwe ̀ y , ɓɛ rɔŋzi ̀ i ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓi ɗyas n ̀ ka ̀ ŋɛn ɓi kon , ɓɛ ki sɛɛdii nyi asuu Yeesus , ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓum .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓumɓɛ ̀ n , nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ : Tɛɛnɛ , ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓyɔɔ ɓi ti ɓi ̀ cenɛn .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓumɓɛ lɛ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ŋwɔ ̀ ŋwɔ ̀ ŋi ̀ di ɓɛɛ fe ̀ feg ɓi mɛ ̀ rem maa lɛ ghɛn yɛɛ ri lɛ a ̀ cenɛ ̀ n ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓe , i ki cee ɓi lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll cɛ ̀ ncii ?
Yeesus a ̀ yigha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ fe ̀ g ɓaa , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ tɔka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ mɛyiti ̀ mɛn ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ rem ?
Ri ̀ ri ̀ kpaa ɗi ̀ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓyɔɔ ɓi ti ɓi ̀ cenɛn , ri ̀ ɗi lɛ pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyo ̀ o ̀ u kɛɛghi , ɗibe ɗyɛɛ ri lɛ fyɛ ̀ ɗ ?
Nkɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ ɓi yi lɛ , Man a ̀ mum a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ a ̀ cenɛ ̀ n ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓe fɛ ɓi ziinɛ . Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ min kisɛkɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ lɛ : Nkpaa wɔ ̀ lɛ : Pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , u teɗ kon wɔɔ ̀ u kɛn ̀ a mɛɛ .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ gha ̀ ska ̀ ki pɛ ̀ sɛɛ aɗyoo ɓi mis mɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ teɗ kon anɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ mii ̀ n ̀ nɔ ̀ nɔŋiyɛn , a ̀ ro ̀ ŋi ̀ bee inɛ a mɛɛ mii , di a fafa Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ kem .
Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ kuura ̀ ka ̀ , ɓɛ ki keekemzi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll . Iris wu ronga ̀ ɓɔ ɓi nɗem ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ lɛ , ti ̀ ghɛɛ ɓɛ ̀ koŋnyoo ɓɛ ɓiɓan ɓi ŋwos a gɛɛ ̀ nɛ .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , Yeesus a ̀ kpaga ̀ ɓi dan a ̀ ghɛn n ̀ teri ̀ -la ̀ mpoŋ ̀ a ̀ dɛŋ ɗii lɛ Levi , di a ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔrii a-kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wii wu kisay . Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : Nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti mɛ ̀ .
Nni Levi a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , a ̀ ca ̀ ɗ ɓyom ɓii ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ nyi .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ Yeesus a mɛɛ mii , a ̀ taŋzɛ ̀ n coo kisɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ : Ɓɛ ̀ teri ̀ -la ̀ mpoŋ ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɗiɗi ̀ gha ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ ri ɓɔ .
Nni Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ŋwɔ ̀ ŋwɔ ̀ ŋi ̀ di ɓɛɛ tɔtɔg ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ Yeesus lɛ : Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓi ki ̀ ki lɛ , ɓi ̀ ɗiɗi ̀ , ɓi ̀ ki nɔnɔ n ̀ ɗaŋ ri ɓɛ ̀ teri ̀ -la ̀ mpoŋ ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓɛ ̀ roroɓ ɓɛɛ ti ɓɛ ɓala ̀ g ɗi ̀ za ̀ y i ̀ dɔgta ̀ , a ̀ a ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ̀ lɛ syeesyee .
N ̀ -yu ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ki reŋii ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri lɛ saaɗ , lɛ ɓɛɛ lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛn mɛ ̀ rem , lɔŋ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ n ̀ -yu ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ reŋii .
Ɓum ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ Yeesus lɛ : Ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓidɛŋ , ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ Zyaŋ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ cela ̀ g ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g , ɓɛ kiki ̀ bɔŋzɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ girig , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛnkɔɔ ɓɔɔ ɗiɗi ̀ , ɓɛ ki nɔnɔ ( ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ) .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ ri ̀ nya lɛ ɓi ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ si ̀ ɓɛ ̀ reŋka ̀ ŋ ɓɛ n ̀ wɔli ̀ giɓ za ̀ y , di n ̀ wɔli ̀ giɓ a kaka ri ̀ ɓɔ ?
Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓatɛn ɓɔ n ̀ wɔli ̀ giɓ ki tii ̀ , mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ̀ n mɛɛ ̀ mɛ ɓɛ ri ce ̀ li ɓiɗila ̀ g mii ̀ .
Nni a ̀ teɗti ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ da ̀ ɗki ̀ lɛ : Ɓaa ̀ gha ̀ s ɓi zyo ̀ na ̀ i ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ a ̀ i ̀ nyɔn ɓɛ raɗki ̀ ki kitu ̀ g mii ̀ , i ̀ ɓɛ kii fɔlɔɔ , ki nyɔn ki tu ̀ nɛ ̀ n , ɓyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki wɔɔsɛn lɛ ri ̀ zyo ̀ na ̀ i ̀ nyɔn , ri ̀ ki ̀ tu ̀ g ki kila ̀ a ̀ .
Ɓaa ̀ ɓe ̀ ni ɓi mɛrɔ ̀ g mɛ nyɔn ɓi ɓi ̀ tu ̀ g ɓi ɓiren , lɛ mɛ ri ɓii ̀ ki weeyii ɓi ̀ ren , mɛ soɓɓa ̀ g , ɓi ̀ ren ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɗyoŋ ;
ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ foŋi ̀ mɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ g mɛ nyɔn ɓi ɓi ̀ ren ɓi nyɔ ̀ n .
Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ mɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ŋwɔm ɓi ti ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ ti mɛrɔ ̀ g , a ̀ ti kɛ ̀ ɛ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ di mɛ mɛ kaka nyɔn , lɛ mɛ abɛ ̀ y mɛɛ rɔɔtɛɛ ɓi ri ̀ ghɛn ɗii .
Ŋwosi Saɓa ̀ t a ̀ dɛŋ , Yeesus a ̀ ghagha ̀ ghi ̀ ya ̀ ɓi dɛmi nyas , ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛ kɛɛnkɛ ̀ n di ɓɛɛ so ̀ sori nyas , ɓɛ pyepye ̀ g ri ̀ ɓya ̀ g di ɓɛɛ ɗiɗi ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ tɔka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓi ki ̀ ki ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi mum a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ki ki ̀ i ŋwosi Saɓa ̀ t ?
Nni Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ ka ɓala ̀ ɓi kiɓan ki Davit a ki ̀ gha ̀ ŋwos adɛŋ di za ̀ y i ̀ kɔ ̀ ni lɛ , ri ̀ nyi ri ̀ ɓum ɓii ?
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Davit a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ teɗ bi ̀ rɛs yi ɓɛ fagha ̀ ɓisuu Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛ ɗi yɔ ri ̀ ɓum ɓii , kɔm ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ cɛ ̀ ncaa ɓɛɛ ɓagha ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ ɗi bi ̀ rɛs yin ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaati ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Man a ̀ mum a ̀ la ̀ mii Saɓa ̀ t .
Ɓi go ̀ n i Saɓa ̀ t i ̀ dɛŋ , Yeesus a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n i ̀ dɛŋ , a ̀ tum ɗi ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɗi ɓum ; nni ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ , ca ̀ g ki wee ̀ lem ki ̀ ɓɔmɛn .
Ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ fifi ̀ ɓi ̀ gha ̀ nyi lɛ fyɛɛyi , lɛ ɓɛɛ ghɛn ̀ n ̀ ko ̀ o a ̀ ɓii ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zii mum ŋwosi Saɓa ̀ t , lɛ ɓɛ kaaka ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓɛɛ ɓanɛn mii lɛ ɓɛɛ sɔmɛn nyi .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , Yeesus a ̀ yigha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ fe ̀ g ɓaa , nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ŋwaa ̀ ca ̀ g kiɓɔma ̀ lɛ : Pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , u rɛli fɛ ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓum ; nni ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , a ̀ rɛli ̀ wɔɔ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ tɔka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Kaliina ɓa ̀ mɛ , ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓis ɓi kalii lɛ , ɓi go ̀ n i Saɓa ̀ t , mum a ki ki ̀ ɓe gi ̀ n ki ̀ rɔɔ ? Lɛ a ghɛɓsi mum gi ̀ n , a caɗ nyi lɛ a wu ?
Nni Yeesus a seese ̀ e ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔɔ ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ kpaa min ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ : Na ̀ ma ca ̀ g kɔɔ , ŋwaa ̀ na ̀ m , ca ̀ g ki gha ̀ s ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ lɛ syeesyee .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ woka ̀ bim , ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ nyoo ̀ nyo ̀ lɛ ̀ n ɓi com ki ɓɛ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i Yeesus .
Ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ innɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɓɔka ̀ ki ɓɔ ̀ ŋzaagh ɓi do ̀ n aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , a ̀ ghagsi ̀ i ̀ ru wu ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ri ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ɓi duri tana , a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ̀ , a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ n ɓum mii ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ , a ̀ ro ̀ o ̀ ɓɔ ɗii lɛ , ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom .
Ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ lɛ : Ri ̀ Simɔn a ̀ nɛ a ̀ roo ̀ gha ̀ lɛ Pyɛɛri , ri ̀ Andire a ̀ geni , ri ̀ Zyag , ri ̀ Zyaŋ , ri ̀ Filiɓ ri ̀ Batelemi ,
ri ̀ Matyoo , ri ̀ Tomas , ri ̀ Zyag a ̀ man a ̀ Alfe , ri ̀ Simɔn a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ Zelot
ri ̀ Zyudɛ a ̀ man a ̀ Zyag , ri ̀ Zyudas Iskariyot a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki ghala ̀ lɛ a ̀ tɔ ̀ kɛɛ Yeesus .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ sɛnga ̀ y ri ̀ ɓɔ , a ̀ rɛli ̀ ɓi lɛ ̀ gsi ̀ , ja ̀ ŋ inɛ coo gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii i ɓagha ̀ , ri ̀ gɛ mum a ̀ nɛ a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ y a Zyude , ri ̀ a Yorisalɛm , ri ̀ ɓi be ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ nɛ a Tiir , ri ̀ Sidɔŋ .
Ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ yugha ̀ y lɛ ɓɛɛ wowog ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓi Yeesus , a ̀ ki wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zi ɓɔ ti ̀ roɓ tyaa , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay ɓi yee ̀ ye ̀ e ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ , ɓɛ wɔnga ̀ girig .
Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ kaaka ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ ko ̀ m nyi , ɓisuulɛ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wudɛŋ wu kpaŋkpa ̀ ŋga ̀ y nyi ɓi nyoo , wu wɔɔ ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zi ̀ ɓɔɔ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ pɛɓsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ma ̀ a ̀ gh ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sogha ̀ sogha ɓisuulɛ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll ki ri kiŋki ̀ n .
Ma ̀ a ̀ gh ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ɓi wowog za ̀ y ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ ɓii ̀ wurii ! Mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ɓi re ̀ nɗen ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , ma ̀ a ̀ gh ri ̀ mi ̀ ni lɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ wɔ ̀ li .
I ɓum ɓɛ ɓee ̀ zɛɛ mi ̀ ni , ɓɛ ɓe ̀ n mi ̀ ni , ɓɛ sɛmgi ̀ mi ̀ ni , ɓɛ ki ren mini ɗii ɓi n ̀ ɗaŋ waa , ɓisuu Man a ̀ mum , ɓi ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ma ̀ a ̀ gh .
Nya ̀ a ̀ nyaana , ɓi ̀ ki sa ̀ nsam ɓi ŋwos anɛ ̀ n , lɛ mɛ ̀ le ̀ ɓ min mɛ aɗyoo mɛ teghɛɛ lɛɛ ̀ gwey ; lɛ fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓaa ɓɛ ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ tɔtɔ ̀ ɓka ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ guŋgum , lɛ mi ̀ nii ti ri ̀ ga ̀ ɓ yi ̀ n i ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ !
Nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ɓi ̀ mɛ wura ̀ g ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , lɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ wog za ̀ y ! Nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ɓi wɔ ̀ wɛy ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , lɛ ɓi ̀ bii ̀ ɓaa ri ̀ n ̀ ɗemi-kɛŋɛn ɓi ̀ ki re ̀ n .
Nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g ri ̀ mi ̀ ni , di ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛɛ ̀ sɛsɛg mini , lɛ fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓaa ɓɛ ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ sɛsɛ ̀ ka ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pwa ̀ a ̀ pwaa ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛkpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ , n ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ɓi wowog mɛ lɛ , keesiina ɓɛ ̀ be ̀ na ̀ bena ɓin , ɓi ̀ ki ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓe ̀ eɓee ̀ zɛ ̀ n mi ̀ ni ki ̀ rɔɔ .
Ma ̀ ŋina ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ cɛmgi ̀ mi ̀ ni , ɓi ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋza ̀ g ɓisuu ɓɛroɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ tɔtɔɓ mini .
I mum a ̀ ɓoogh wɔ ̀ ɓi ri ̀ tam ɗi kimɛŋ , fati nyi ɗi wee ̀ lem ; i ŋwaa ̀ ɓa ̀ tɛɛ wɔ ̀ ri ̀ ga , ca ̀ ra nyi a tee ̀ ti bu ̀ ɓi yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ lɔni wɔ ̀ com , faa nyi kɔ ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓa ̀ tɛɛ wɔ ̀ com , kɔ ̀ ɔ tɔg nyi lɛ a pɛɛ ̀ zi wɔ ̀ kɔ .
Ki ̀ ɓan ki ki kɔni wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ kilag wɔ ̀ , wɔ ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g girig ɓɔ kɔ ̀ .
I ɓi keesii lɔŋ lɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ keesii mi ̀ ni , ki ̀ ɓan ki kuurakɛn kaa ɓa ɓi a lɔ ̀ ŋkin , lɛ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe ɓɛ ti ɓɛ keesa ̀ g girig ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ keesii ɓɔ .
I ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kila ̀ g mi ̀ ni ki ̀ rɔɔ ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ ɓi ̀ ti ɓi ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g ki ̀ rɔɔ , di ɓi ̀ ka ki ɓi kiɓan ki kuurakɛn , lɛ n ̀ soo ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe , ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kila ̀ g fɔlɔɔ .
I ɓumɓɛ ɓi ̀ yii lɛ ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ leɓ mi ̀ ni pon ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ ɓi ̀ ti ɓi ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ra ̀ g ɓyom , ki ̀ ɓan kidɛŋ ki kuurakɛn ki yin foo , lɛ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe ɓɛ ti ɓɛ ɓɔra ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe ɓyom lɔŋ lɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɔ ɓyɔ ɓii ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zii .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , keesiina ɓɛ ̀ be ̀ na ̀ bena ɓin , ɓi ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ɓɔ ki ̀ rɔɔ , ɓi ̀ ki ɓɔ ̀ rag ɓum ɓyom , kɛ ̀ ɓi mi ̀ ngi tityɛɛ lɛ , ɓɛ ri mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zii ɓyɔ . I ɓi ̀ ki ̀ i fɔlɔɔ , mɛ ̀ le ̀ ɓ min mɛ ri ɓii ̀ te ̀ ghɛɛ , ɓi ̀ ki ɓa ɓɔn ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ teŋmɛɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ve ̀ g ɓisuulɛ , nyii rila ̀ g ri ̀ geesɛ ̀ n ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a ɓɛ ̀ te ̀ nten ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ri ̀ gɛn .
Ɓaana ri ̀ n ̀ ɗem wu nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Seŋi wi ̀ n a ri ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ɗem wu nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g .
Kɛ ̀ ɓi ɓa ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ mi ̀ ɓum fɔɔnnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ a yɔ ̀ m ɓi ̀ mini ; kɛ ̀ ɓi fa ɓum zɔɔ , fɔɔnnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ a fa ɓi mini zɔɔ ; cenɛɛna ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓin , fɔɔnnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ cenɛɛ .
Faana ɓum ɓyom fɔɔnnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ girig mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ faa ̀ ɓi coo ve ̀ g i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ɗonɛn lɛ pisa , i ̀ ki ɓa n ̀ nɔ ̀ rakɛn , i ̀ ra ̀ a ̀ ra ̀ a ̀ ; ve ̀ g i ̀ nɛn yɛɛ ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ri wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ su ̀ u ̀ rii ɓyom ɓi ɓa ̀ m a ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ a ̀ kɔɔ ; ɓisuulɛ ve ̀ g i ̀ nɛ u ̀ ti u ̀ fe ̀ ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓyom mii ̀ , yɛ ̀ ɛnɛ ɓɛ ri girig wɔ ̀ ɓyɔ ɓii ̀ fe ̀ egh mii ̀ .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ teeti ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ da ̀ ɗki ̀ i ̀ dɛŋ lɛ : Ɗyaŋɗya ̀ ŋ a ̀ ri ̀ nya lɛ a ̀ ɓan roɗyaŋɗya ̀ ŋ ɓi ki ̀ geŋ , ɓɛ rɔɓ lɛ ɓɛ kpii ɓi ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ri ̀ ɓee ?
N-yila ̀ g a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ cee n ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g wi ̀ i ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , i a ̀ kpaŋzɛɛ cilag kii , a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ ɓa yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g wi ̀ i ̀ .
Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ u ̀ ghɛɛ ki ̀ fɛfɛy ki ki ri ɓi ɗis ɗi goni , kɔ ̀ ɔ ghɛn n ̀ wɔ ̀ g wu wu ri ɓi ɗin ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ?
Nsoo ̀ lɛ : Lannɛ u ̀ ri ̀ lɛ u ̀ kpaa goni lɛ , maaso ̀ ŋ , ki ̀ ya m ̀ pisi wɔ ̀ ki ̀ fɛfɛy ki wɔ ̀ ɓi ɗis , kɔm ̀ lɛ u ̀ ghɛɛ ɓi nwɔ ̀ g wu wu ri ɓi ɗin ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ? Wɔ ̀ ŋwaa ̀ fyɛy fyɛy ɓi ŋwɔm i ̀ ghe ̀ y ɓi ɗu ̀ m ! Ka pisi n ̀ wɔ ̀ g wu wu ri wɔ ̀ ɓi ɗis , di fɔlɔɔ nnɛ u konag ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ u pisi ki ̀ fɛfɛy ki ki ri ɓi ɗis ɗi goni .
Syeesyee a ̀ ki ̀ te a maa ̀ wum ɓi ɓiɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓiɗu ̀ n , n ̀ soo ̀ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki kite , ki yin lɛ ki wum ɓi ̀ syeesyee ɓi ɓiɗu ̀ m .
Lɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ yilag kite kice ̀ m ɓi ɓi ̀ ɗu ̀ n ɓi kɔ . Ŋwaa ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ kɔs dii ɓi n ̀ ɗye ̀ m wu gay , n ̀ soo ̀ lɛ a ̀ kɔs gin ɓi nɗye ̀ m wu keŋ .
Syeesyee a ̀ mum a ̀ ti a ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi syeesyee lɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ syeesyee a ̀ n ̀ ɗem ; ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki mum ki kila ̀ g ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓeɓtɛn lɛ , ki ri ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki n ̀ ɗem , lɛ ŋwɔm wu mum wɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa kiɓan ki ki roni nyi n ̀ ɗem .
Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓi rereŋi mɛ lɛ Kan , Kan , kɛ ̀ ɓi ki ki ̀ com ki n ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni ?
N ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ n ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni lɛ , mum bimiɗ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ yu ̀ u a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ , a ̀ wog ri ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɗyɛm ̀ , a ̀ ki nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ɗyɔ ,
a ̀ pisɛɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ki ̀ toŋ ki mɛɛ ; a ̀ timga ̀ zi , a ̀ kpaŋ ɓi ri ̀ ɓan a ̀ ghɛ ̀ lɛ ̀ n yi ̀ ki ̀ toŋ mii ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ ; yɛ ̀ ɛ don yi mɛnig yi kpaga ̀ , poɓɓo a ̀ yu ̀ ki ̀ roŋdɛɛ ɓi mɛɛ mɛn ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , mɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ nyɛ ̀ ŋɗɛn , lɛ mɛ ɓagha ̀ mɛ ̀ toŋɛn lɛ syeesyee .
Nni wɔ ̀ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ woogh ri ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɗyɛm ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɛ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ɗyɔ , a ̀ pisɛɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ saghi ̀ gha ̀ mɛɛ mii ɓi m ̀ bume aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɛ tim lɛ a ghɛlɛn yi ̀ ki ̀ toŋ ɓi zi i nteɗ . Yɛ ̀ ɛ poɓɓo a ̀ roŋɗɛ ̀ nga ̀ mii ̀ , mɛ ghas ki ̀ kpi ̀ laagh , mɛ waa ̀ rɛ ̀ n mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ le ̀ gsi ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ kalii ɓiɓan ɓi a ̀ ɓagha ̀ lɛ a kpaa gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum ɓɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Kapɛrinawum .
Muu Ro ̀ mɛŋ a ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n-ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say anɛ a ̀ keesi ̀ gha ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey ; nni n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say anɛ ̀ n a ̀ roro ̀ ɓka ̀ , di a ̀ ti ɓii ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔkɔɔ ̀ si ̀ .
