Lɛ mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ kɔmɛɛ mɛ ̀ ; n ̀ ki ɓa ti ri ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛɛ ; i n ̀ kpaa adɛŋ lɛ kɛ ̀ na ! a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ; n ̀ ki kpaati ambog lɛ a yu , a ̀ yu ̀ ; n ̀ soo ̀ ma ̀ a kpaa n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say wɛm ̀ lɛ , ki ̀ ya fɛlɛ , a ̀ ki ̀ fɔlɔɔ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ woka ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n-ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓin ̀ , a ̀ kuura ̀ ka ̀ nyi ; fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ni ̀ mɓɛ ̀ nga ̀ a ̀ fa mis ri ̀ gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Mi ̀ ni ɓum , n ̀ soo ̀ a Isirayɛl , n ̀ ka ghɛnga ̀ ɓi mum a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ coo ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ ɗi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ .
Nni ɓumɓɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n-ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ romga ̀ y , ɓɛ sugti ̀ gha ̀ a mɛɛ mii , ɓɛ tanɛ ̀ n lɛ , n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say anɛ a ̀ roro ̀ ɓka ̀ a ̀ mɛ wɔ ̀ n .
Ɓi duri tana , Yeesus a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ min ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ dɛŋ ɗii lɛ Nayin . A ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ lɛ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii , ri ̀ coo kituu ki ɓum .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ ti ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ i ̀ suunaa wu ɓi ri ̀ ɗi ̀ ŋɗa ̀ g ɗi ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛn , nni ɓɛ kɛnkɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ ɓomi ki ̀ loŋ ki mum ; mum a ̀ nce ̀ m a ̀ ɓagha ̀ m ̀ bobog a ̀ man a ̀ n ̀ kpɔɓ wu giɓ wudɛŋ . Ɓumɓɛ ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛn , lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ kɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zɛ ̀ nga ̀ y n ̀ ɗaŋ ri ̀ n ̀ kpɔɓ win ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Kan a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ giɓ anɛ ̀ n , a ̀ wog nyi nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g , a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ɔ re ̀ nɗen .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ tyoŋdɛ ̀ nga ̀ , a ̀ ko ̀ m fi ̀ kɔrɔŋ fi kilo ̀ n ; ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ tɛtɛ ̀ ka ̀ fyɔ ɓɛ rɛli ̀ , Yeesus a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Dɛli ̀ i ̀ mum , n ̀ kpaa wɔ ̀ lɛ , pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyo ̀ o ̀ !
Nni ki ̀ loŋ ki pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ki tumɛn ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ , Yeesus a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ nyi ri ̀ jɛɛ .
Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ , ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ koŋnyo ̀ o ̀ . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ kee ̀ ke ̀ mzi ̀ gha ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ lɛ : Coo n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan a ghɛnɛɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkis , ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ yu ̀ u ki ̀ ghɛɓsii kilɔ ̀ ŋ kii .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ sa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ɓi zi i ̀ Zyude bimiɗ , ri ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓidɛŋ ɓi ɓi ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ nunu ̀ g .
Ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ Zyaŋ ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ nyi ki ̀ kpaa ̀ gɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan anɛ ̀ n .
Fɔɔnnɛ Zyaŋ a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ , a ̀ rom ɓɔ yɛ ̀ ɛ Kan , lɛ ɓɛɛ tɔg nyi lɛ : Wɔ ̀ yɛɛ ri nya roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ yu ̀ u gi ̀ n , ti ɓoŋ ̀ ɓoŋ ti ̀ roa ̀ dɛŋ ?
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kpaga ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus , ɓɛ kpaa nyi lɛ : Zyaŋ Ba ̀ ɓtis yɛɛ romii ̀ ɓi ̀ si lɛ , ti ̀ tɔg wɔ ̀ lɛ : Wɔ ̀ yɛɛ ri nya roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ yu ̀ u , gi ̀ n ti ɓoŋ ̀ ɓoŋ ti ̀ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ ?
Ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kɔm ̀ kin ̀ , Yeesus a ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roroɓ lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ lɛnlɛm , ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay , a ̀ ki ki ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ ̀ ɗyaŋɗya ̀ ŋ lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ ghɛnɛ ̀ n ti ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓumɓɛ Zyaŋ a ̀ romga ̀ y ɓɛn ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkii lɛ : Kɛ ̀ ɛna ki ̀ kpaa ̀ Zyaŋ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ̀ ghɛɛ , ri ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ woogh ; ɓyɛɛ ri lɛ : ɓɛ ̀ ɗyaŋɗya ̀ ŋ ɓɛ ghɛɛghɛnɛ ̀ n ti ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ lɛnlɛm ɓɛ kɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ lɛ syeesyee , ɓɛ ̀ kukwiy ɓɛ tee ̀ te ̀ e ̀ ti ̀ syeesyee a ̀ nyoo , ɓɛ ̀ lɔlɔg ɓɛ woo ̀ wo ̀ o ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n , ɓi ̀ loŋ ɓi ̀ ghee ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n , Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ kaa ̀ ka ̀ lɛ ̀ n a ɓɛ ̀ sogha ̀ sogha .
Nni ma ̀ a ̀ gh ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ a kɛ ̀ ɓtɛn ɓi fiɓa ̀ g lɛ mɛ ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛ fi ̀ tom ɓɛ Zyaŋ ɓɛ sugti ̀ gha ̀ , nni Yeesus a ̀ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓum ri ̀ kpaa ɗi kiɓan ki Zyaŋ , a ̀ tɔg ɓɔ lɛ : Cɛ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓi ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ ɓi-reɓ ? Ki ̀ syo ̀ ŋ ki fɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ fɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ a nyɛ ̀ ɛnyɛŋzi ̀ gi ̀ n ?
Nni cɛ ɓi kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ , ɓaa ̀ yi ɓi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ɗɛ ̀ ŋɗɛn lɛ syeesyee ? Ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ ŋɗɛn , lɛ syeesyee ɓɛ ki ghɛghɛɓ ɓi-kum , ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kɔra ̀ g ɓi mɛɛ mɛ mɛfo ̀ m .
Nni cɛ ɓi ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ min ki ghɛɛ ̀ ? N ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ? Ɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ! N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni lɛ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓi ghɛnga ̀ a ̀ nɛn a ̀ cee gi ̀ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan .
Ɓisuulɛ Zyaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ roa ̀ nɛ ɓɛ kanga ̀ ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ : Ghɛna n ̀ ɗomi mum wɛm ̀ a ̀ fi ̀ tom wɔ asu lɛ a pegsɛn wɔ ̀ bee .
N ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni lɛ , ɓi ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ yalɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ɗu ̀ m ɗi giɓ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ cee Zyaŋ a ̀ yin ; ki ̀ ɓan kifog siito ̀ n a mum a ̀ nɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ cee nyi .
Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ wowo ̀ ka ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓi Zyaŋ , n ̀ soo ̀ ɓɛ ̀ teri ̀ -la ̀ mpoŋ ̀ , ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ saaɗ ; kɛɛ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ , Zyaŋ a ɓaɓti ɓɔ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓenga ̀ fe ̀ g a ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ nyi ɓisu waa , yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ɓenga ̀ ki ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ lɛ Zyaŋ a ɓaɓti ɓɔ .
Nni n ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ n ̀ fe ̀ g ɓa ̀ gba ̀ a ̀ i ̀ ɓum i ̀ gɛɛ ̀ nɛ ri ̀ cɛ ? I ̀ pisɛɛ ɓa ̀ ri ̀ kuu ɗi ɓum aɗi ?
I ̀ pisɛɛ ɓɔɔɓɔɓti ɓɛ ɓɛ kɔkɔ ̀ rii ɓi n ̀ lɛm ̀ ɓog ; ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ kaka ̀ li ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓaa lɛ : Ti ̀ mɛ ki ̀ lɛ , ti ̀ ɓog mi ̀ ni mɛ ̀ keŋ , kɛ ̀ ɓi ɗyen , ti ̀ kɛɛ ̀ gh mi ̀ ni ki ̀ ɓa ̀ a ̀ si ̀ ki riwu ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɓi ki re ̀ n .
Lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Zyaŋ Ba ̀ ɓtis a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ɗi bi ̀ rɛs , kɛ ̀ ɛ ki nɔ mɛrɔ ̀ g , mi ̀ ni lɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki n ̀ ghay .
Man a ̀ mum a ̀ yu ̀ y , a ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ lɛ , a ̀ ɗiɗi ̀ , a ̀ nɔnɔ ̀ , mi ̀ ni lɛ : A ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ɗii com , a ̀ ki ɓa ti kinɔɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ g , nyi ti ̀ ri ̀ ghan ɗi ɓɛteri ̀ -la ̀ mpoŋ ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ɗi mɛ ghɛnɛn lɛ ɗi ri lɛ saaɗ a ɓɔn ɓii .
Fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ adɛŋ yɛɛ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ Yeesus lɛ a kɛn ̀ ki ̀ ɗii ̀ a mɛɛ mii , fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi naa i ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g .
Nni n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe a giɓ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛn a ̀ woka ̀ y lɛ , Yeesus a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ɓyom ɓi ɗiyɛn a mɛɛ mɛ Fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n ; fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ yugha ̀ y ri ̀ ɓeŋ a ̀ ti ̀ ra ̀ a ̀ re n ̀ ɗonɛn lɛ pisa ,
a ̀ rɛli ̀ Yeesus ajɛ ̀ m fɛlɛ ̀ a mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ mii , a ̀ re ̀ nɗe ̀ n le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ misi ̀ mii mɛ ɓwaŋzi ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ mɛ Yeesus . Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ tɔ ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ mɔ ri ̀ tyo ̀ ŋ tii , a ̀ lɛ ̀ ŋlɛ ̀ ŋ mɔ a ̀ ki sisiŋi mɔ ti ̀ ra ̀ a ̀ re .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ Yeesus a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ fɔlɔɔ , a ̀ fe ̀ g ɓi n ̀ ɗem wii lɛ : I Yeesus a ̀ a ri ̀ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan , di a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ , a yi lɛ , giɓ anɛ a ko ̀ mkom nyi a ̀ nɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki giɓ .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ : Simɔn , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki lɛ n ̀ kpaa wɔ ̀ , roa ̀ nɛn a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ nyi lɛ : Nɗe ̀ sa ̀ g to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛn !
Ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ tɔtɔ ̀ ka ̀ ɓum ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pon , roa ̀ nɛ , ɓɛ ̀ hɔnɗɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛtan ̀ , roa ̀ mbog , dola ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ .
