Ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki ̀ ce ̀ m , ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ yuyu ̀ gha ̀ y ɓɛn ̀ , yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay .
