Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay ɓi kpaga ̀ ɓi nyoo a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋza ̀ ka ̀ Yeesus lɛ , nyii nɔɔ ̀ ti a ̀ nɛ ̀ n , wɔ ̀ lɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɓe ̀ e ̀ dɛ ̀ ng , a ̀ kpaa ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ :
Sugha a mɛɛ mɔɔ , u kpaa ɓum ɓɔɔ com ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ a ki ̀ i wɔ ̀ ; fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ suka ̀ min , a ̀ la ̀ a ̀ la ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n com ki Yeesus a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ nyi ba ̀ n bimiɗ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ suka ̀ y ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɗi a ̀ ɓagha ̀ y cɛcɛɗ ki riɓa ̀ y , nni gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum i ̀ gha ̀ ɓka ̀ nyi , ɓisuulɛ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓoŋɓo ̀ ŋga ̀ nyi .
Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ ɗii lɛ Zyayirus , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ a ̀ nɛ ɓi naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n , a ̀ yugha ̀ y Yeesus a nyoo , a ̀ kpi ̀ nyi a mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ , a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzi ̀ nyi lɛ a yu a mɛɛ mii ,
ɓisuulɛ , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ lɔŋ maa man bog , a ̀ nce ̀ m giɓ , di a ̀ ti be ̀ g n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ yiɓɛɛ ̀ ; nni man ance ̀ m a ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ . Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ kɛ ̀ nkɛ ̀ nga ̀ wɔɔ , gwi ̀ y i ̀ si ̀ i ̀ si ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ nyi lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
