Fɔɔnnɛ giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ ce ̀ ga ̀ y Yeesus ajɛ ̀ m , a ̀ ko ̀ m ri ̀ keɓ ɗii ɗi kila ̀ a ̀ , bwaɓ yi yi kpaŋkpa ̀ ŋga ̀ nyi yi ghas ki ̀ renɛɛ lɔŋ wɔɔ foo .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ tɔka ̀ lɛ : Ghɛn yɛɛ komi mɛ ̀ lɔɔ ? Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ti ɓii ̀ rooroo ̀ zɛ ̀ n , nni Pyɛɛri a ̀ ɓaka ̀ nyi lɛ : N ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g , ɓum ɓɛɛ ceŋzɛɛ wɔ ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ ki si ̀ isii ̀ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ .
