Yɛ ̀ ɛ giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ , ki ̀ ɓan ki a ̀ a ki ̀ i ki yii ̀ di a ri ̀ nyam , nni a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ kpi ̀ i Yeesus a mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ di a ni ̀ ighniŋdɛ ̀ n , a ̀ kpaa nyi ɓi mis mɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓisuucɛ nnɛ a ̀ a ko ̀ mi nyi , ri ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ a gha ̀ si ki ̀ wɔ ̀ ni lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ a ko ̀ mi nyi .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ min nyi lɛ : Gɔ ̀ n yɛ ̀ m ! ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗyɔɔ ɗi ghɛɓsii wɔ ̀ , kɛ ̀ na lɛ fyo ̀ oog !
Yeesus a ̀ kaka a ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ giɓ anɛ ̀ n fɔlɔɔ , nni mum a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ y a mɛɛ mɛ nla ̀ mi ̀ a ̀ nɛ ɓi naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ ŋzɛn , a ̀ yu ̀ ki ̀ kpaa lɛ : Zyayirus , gɔ ̀ n yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ i ti ki ̀ loŋ , kɔ ̀ ɔ yeesi ti n ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g zɛy .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , Yeesus a ̀ woka ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpaagha ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ Zyayirus lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ɔ risi ! Lɔŋ n ̀ tyweeyi wɛɛ ̀ wu ɓaya ri ̀ wɔ , di gɔ ̀ n yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa ri ̀ cɛɓ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kpaga ̀ a mɛɛ mɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ̀ lɛ , ɓum ɓɛɛ ɗiŋi ɓi naa n ̀ ɗaŋ ri nyi , i ki cee ɓi lɛ , ri ̀ Pyɛɛri ri ̀ Zyaŋ ri ̀ Zyag , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yali ̀ man a ̀ nɛ ̀ n , ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ a ̀ ca ̀ ɗka ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɗiŋi ̀ .
Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ rɔŋɗɔ ̀ ŋga ̀ ɓi ̀ kiŋ di ɓɛɛ ̀ sa ̀ asarɛ ̀ n ri ̀ n ̀ ɗemi-kɛŋɛn ɓisuu man a ̀ nɛ ̀ n . Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ min ɓɔ lɛ : Kɛ ̀ ɓi re ̀ nɗen , a wii ɓi , a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi fi ̀ lo .
Ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ fenga ̀ ka ̀ nyi , lɛ ɓɛ yigha ̀ saaɗ lɛ mutya ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ loŋ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog Yeesus a ̀ ɓanga ̀ man a ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓi ca ̀ g , a ̀ kpaa jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ lɛ : Mutya ̀ a ̀ nɛ pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
Nghay wu ŋwɔɓti wu sugti ̀ i ̀ , a ̀ gha ̀ s ki ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , Yeesus a ̀ tɔg min lɛ ɓɛɛ fa nyi ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g .
Ɓɛ ̀ yali ̀ man a ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kuura ̀ ka ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey , wɔ ̀ lɛ Yeesus a ̀ siita ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ kpaa mum ki ̀ ɓan ki ki kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ kin ̀ .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ taŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ , a ̀ fa ɓɔ ite ̀ ɗ wu na ̀ ɓɛn ɓiɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , ri ̀ wulɛ ɓɛɛ wɔɔ ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roroɓ .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ romga ̀ ɓɔ lɛ , ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ ki la ̀ alam ̀ ɓɛ ̀ n Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛ ki wɔ ̀ ɔwɔɔ ̀ zi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roroɓ .
Nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Kɛ ̀ ɓi ɓanɛn com yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi kɛ ̀ nkɛ ̀ n , kɛ ̀ ɓi teɗ nsoo ̀ ki ̀ geŋ , nsoo ̀ ɓa ̀ m , nsoo ̀ com kiɗiyɛn , nsoo ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni , nsoo ̀ ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ɓiɓɛɛ ̀ .
Naa bimiɗ i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ghaɓi mi ̀ ni wɔɔ , kɔ ̀ riina ɓi naa i ̀ nɛ ̀ n , a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ri ̀ wɔɔ ɓii ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ ɓi ghaa ̀ gh .
Ja ̀ ŋ bimiɗ i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ beni mi ̀ ni ki ̀ gha ̀ ɓi , ku ̀ rina ku ̀ ru ̀ ɓu a ̀ nɛ mi ̀ ni ɓi mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ di ɓi ̀ ti ɓii ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ nce ̀ m , ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗin ̀ ɗyɛ resi zɛ ̀ ɗ yaa ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛn ̀ ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ , ɓɛ rereni ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ di ɓɛɛ ̀ kakali ɓum Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ , ɓɛ wɔɔ ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zi ̀ ɓum ja ̀ ŋbimiɗ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Eroodɛ a ̀ woka ̀ gɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan bimiɗ a ̀ nɛ Yeesus a ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ a ̀ nɛn , ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗi ɗim nyi , ɓisuulɛ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ lɛ : Zyaŋ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n yɛɛ ghem ̀ ɓɛɛ yi ̀ a nyɔ ̀ ɛ ̀ y .
Ɓum ɓɛmbog lɛ Eli a ̀ nɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ resɛɛ ti ̀ ; ɓɛdɛŋ ti ̀ lɛ , ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ abɛ ̀ y kɛɛ ghemɓɛɛ yi ̀ a nyɔ ̀ ɛ ̀ y .
Fɔɔnnɛ Eroodɛ a ̀ tɔɔ ̀ ghtɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ɗem lɛ : Mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ yɛɛ kpaagha ̀ lɛ , ɓɛɛ ren n ̀ to wu Zyaŋ ; nni roa ̀ nɛ ri ̀ kem ɗyɛɛ ̀ pa ̀ pas mɛ a ̀ nɛ , nyi ri ɓa ̀ ghɛn ? Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kaaka ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ bee inɛ lɛ a ghɛn ̀ Yeesus .
Nni ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ Yeesus a ̀ romga ̀ ɓɛ sugti ̀ gha ̀ y , ɓɛ kpaa nyi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓɛ kigha ̀ y , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ syo ̀ ga ̀ ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ ki ̀ pa ̀ s ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ dɛŋ ɗii lɛ Bɛdsayida .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ tuu ɓi ɓum ɓi woka ̀ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ , nni ɓi nɔɔta ̀ ka ̀ nyi wɔɔ , Yeesus a ̀ gha ̀ ɓ ɓɔ lɛ syeesyee , a ̀ kpaakpaa ɓɔ ɓɔlɛ ̀ a ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ ki wɔ ̀ ɔwɔɔ ̀ zi ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ kɛŋ ɓi nyo ̀ o ̀ .
Di ŋwos a ti ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ nkɛni , nni ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ tyɛɛ ̀ tɛ ̀ nga ̀ y , ɓɛ kpaa nyi lɛ : Kali gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ lɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ kɛn ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ri ̀ ɓi jɛ ̀ m yi ɓilɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ɓi ri fɛ ja ̀ ŋbog , ɓɛɛ kaa ̀ fi ̀ lo , ri ̀ com ki ɓɛ ri ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ɗi , ɓisuulɛ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ com .
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : Mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ , faana ɓɔ ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ; wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛn ̀ ɓɛ kpaa nyi lɛ : Ti ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ fɛ lɛ bi ̀ rɛs yitan ̀ , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ zɛn ɓi ̀ ɓɛɛ ̀ ; ti ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ti ̀ lam ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m di ti ̀ ɓa tii yi ̀ nya ki ̀ laa ̀ gh ɓiɗila ̀ g ɓidɛŋ ɓisu wa ̀ a ̀ .
Ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ nunu ̀ g ɓum ɓɛ ̀ tɔɔsi ̀ m ɓɛtan ̀ . Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ siina ɓɔ ɓi ̀ gwi ̀ y ɓi gwi ̀ y ; gwi ̀ y bog ɓum mɛ ̀ tin mɛɓɛɛ ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ .
Nni ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ , ɓɛ kɔɔ ̀ si ̀ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi zi .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ teka ̀ bi ̀ rɛs yi kitan ̀ yin ̀ , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ zɛn ɓi kiɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , a ̀ ɓegsi ̀ mis aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , a ̀ fa Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ɓɛki ̀ bi ̀ rɛs , a ̀ syo ̀ ngi ̀ ɓi ̀ zɛn , a ̀ fa min ɓyom ɓi ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii , lɛ ɓɛɛ kaɓsi gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ ̀ n .
Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɗi ̀ gha ̀ , ɓɛ wura ̀ g ɓɛ ki taŋzɛn ɓi ̀ ɓɛgha ̀ ɓi ɓi rɔ ̀ ɓta ̀ ka ̀ ɓi ron ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɗ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ ɓiɓɛɛ ̀ .
Ŋwos adɛŋ , di Yeesus a ki ̀ ki bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n ki ̀ pa ̀ s nɗaŋ ri ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii nni a ̀ tɔka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Gɛ ɓi ̀ tuu ɓi ɓum a ̀ nɛ a fe ̀ ki ɓaa ̀ lɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ghɛn ?
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ ɓaka ̀ nyi lɛ : Ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛɛ kpaaghi lɛ , u ̀ ri ̀ Zyaŋ Ba ̀ ɓtis , ɓɛmbog lɛ , wɔ ̀ yɛɛ ri Eli , ɓɛmbog ti ̀ lɛ , u ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓiɓan ɓɛ abɛ ̀ y , ki ki ghemɓɛɛ yi ̀ a nyɔ ̀ ɛ ̀ y .
Nni a ̀ tɔgti ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ ɓi kpaaghi lɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ghɛn ? Fɔɔnnɛ Pyɛɛri a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ nyi lɛ : U ̀ ri ̀ Kiris a ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ romii ̀ .
