Nni ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ ̀ n , ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ syanga ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ lɛ : N ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g ! ku ̀ ru ̀ g m ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzaagh wɔ ̀ , pɛɓsɛn ɓa ̀ mɛ ŋwɔɓti wɛ ̀ m a ̀ nɛ , ɓisuulɛ nnyɛɛ ri lɔŋ maa m ̀ bobog wɛ ̀ m a ̀ man .
