Ŋwosi Saɓa ̀ t , Yeesus a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi naa i ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ , ɗidɛŋ , lɛ a ɗi ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ ɓɛ fifi ̀ ɓi ̀ gha ̀ Yeesus lɛ syeesyee ; ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ roro ̀ ɓka ̀ fi ̀ roɓ fi mi ̀ kakɛn mɛko ̀ o ̀ , a ̀ rɛrɛ ̀ li ̀ gha ̀ nyi asu .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ , a ̀ tɔg ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi kpaa nya lɛ , ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ wɔɔ ̀ zi ̀ mum ŋwosi Saɓa ̀ t gi ̀ n ɓɛ yin lɛ ɓɛ wɔɔ ̀ zi ̀ ?
Ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ minɛ ̀ n nyi . Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ teka ̀ roro ̀ ɓ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n , a ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zi ̀ nyi a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ a sug .
Nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ min ɓumɓɛ ̀ n lɛ : Ghɛn anɛ ɓi mi ̀ ni yɛɛ ri lɛ a ̀ ki ̀ lɛ , i man wii ̀ nsoo ̀ lɛ sani ̀ nya wi ̀ i ̀ a kpi ̀ i ɓi ri ̀ ɓee ŋwosi Saɓa ̀ t , a ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓ kɛ ̀ ɛ ru ̀ nɛn lɛ a sɔŋi nyi lɔŋ wɔɔ foo ?
Ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ ɓi ŋwɔm wu ɓa ̀ ghɛn nyi n ̀ tɔɔ ̀ tɔɔgh win ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ seese ̀ e ̀ gha ̀ di ɓum ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ nɓɔn mɛkɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ mɛ syeesyee , nni a ̀ teka ̀ ɓɔ da ̀ ɗki ̀ i ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ kpaa lɛ :
I mum a ̀ reŋii wɔ ̀ a ki ̀ sɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ ki riwɛy , kɔ ̀ ɔ kɛ ̀ n ki kɔ ̀ rii ɓi-kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu asu , lɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ cee wɔ ̀ ɓi nkoŋ a ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ ɓa girig n ̀ ɗeŋiyɛn a ki ̀ sɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ kin ̀ ;
ɓi le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ reŋii mi ̀ nii ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ yu ̀ wɔ ̀ ki ̀ kpaa ̀ lɛ , u nɛm ŋwaa ̀ mbog a ̀ nɛ ̀ n i ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ to wu ri wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ ri ̀ ri ɓi ri ̀ kɛ ̀ n ɗi u ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ki kɔ ̀ rii ɓi-kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu ajɛ ̀ m .
Nni ki ̀ lag lɛ i mum a ̀ reŋii wɔ ̀ ɓi ki ̀ sɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ u ̀ kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ kɔ ̀ rii ɓi-kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu ajɛ ̀ m di fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ reŋii wɔ ̀ a ki lɛ , i a ̀ yu ̀ u yi ̀ , a ̀ kpaa wɔ ̀ lɛ , Ceeya ki ̀ kɔ ̀ rii fɛlɛnii asu . Ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗin ̀ ɗi ri wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ faa ̀ ri ̀ mum ɓi mis mɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ri a ki ̀ sɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ kin ̀ .
Mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓɔgsii nyimiɗ innɛ ɓɛɛ ɓii ̀ sɛɛ ̀ dii , wɔ ̀ lɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ sɛɛ ̀ dii nyimiɗ ɓi zi , innɛ ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ ɓɔgsii .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ girig ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ nyi a mɛɛ mii lɛ : I u ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ki ̀ sɛ ̀ nɛ nsoo ̀ ri ̀ ŋwos , nsoo ̀ cɛŋko ̀ , kɔ ̀ ɔ reŋɗɛn lɛ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ reŋka ̀ ŋ ɓɔɔ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓɔɔ , nsoo ̀ boo yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ i ɓum , nsoo ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ba-go ̀ ŋzɛn ɓɔɔ , ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ri ̀ i ̀ kum ɓisuulɛ ɓɔ girig ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ reŋi ̀ wɔ ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkaa , ɓɛ leɓ wɔ ̀ ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓi u ̀ fagha ̀ ɓɔ .
Ki ̀ lag lɔŋ lɛ , i u ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ki ̀ sɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ , u ̀ reŋɗɛ ̀ n lɛ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sogha ̀ sogha ri ̀ ɓi ̀ wɔ ̀ g ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ lɛnlɛm , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɗyaŋɗya ̀ ŋ .
Fɔɔnnɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ma ̀ a ̀ gh ɓisuulɛ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ yin ɗi i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ ɓɛ leɓ wɔ ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗin ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ u ̀ teri gɛ mɛ ̀ le ̀ ɓ ŋwosi righe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓilo ̀ ŋ ɗi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri lɛ saaɗ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɗiɗi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛn ̀ ri ̀ Yeesus ki woka ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓin ̀ , ki kpaa nyi lɛ : Ma ̀ a ̀ gh ri ̀ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɗii gɛ ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g a ki ̀ sɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ ki ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ nyi lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ yɛɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi coo kisɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ , a ̀ ki regi ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey a ki ̀ sɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ kin ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ki ̀ sɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ ki ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ tumɛɛ ki kpaga ̀ , nni a ̀ romga ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say wii ̀ lɛ a kɛn ̀ ki ̀ reŋii ɓumɓɛ a ̀ reŋɗɛ ̀ nga ̀ , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Yu ̀ unay , ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ti ɓi ̀ pe ̀ gsɛn .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓaka ̀ y n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say anɛ ̀ n lɛ , bee inɛ ɓɔɔ yu i ̀ nɛ ̀ n i ̀ yin , roa ̀ ntonto a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Mɛ ̀ ɛ nla ̀ agh dɛm , nni n ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ yɔ ̀ ki ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ , ku ̀ ru ̀ g cenɛn mɛ ̀ .
