Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ tuu ɓi ɓum ɓi nɔɔ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ Yeesus , nni a ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ y a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ :
I mum a ̀ yu ̀ u a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ , a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ ɓa n ̀ -yila ̀ g wɛ ̀ m di a ̀ keesii ɓi mɛ , a ̀ cee le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ a ̀ keesii lɛ , ri ̀ seŋi ̀ , ri ̀ jɛɛ , ri ̀ giy , ri ̀ ɓɔn ɓii , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓii ɓɛ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ri ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛbaŋi ̀ , nsoo ̀ cɛɓ kii kɔmiɗ .
Fɔɔnnɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ tɛ ̀ ɛgh ɓi kɔrɔs wi ̀ i ̀ , a ̀ ki nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti mɛ a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ ɓa n ̀ -yila ̀ g wɛ ̀ m .
