Fɔɔnnɛ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓɛ ŋwɔŋwɔ ̀ ŋi ̀ gha ̀ di ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a gha ̀ ghaɓ ɓiɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓum lɛ syeesyee , a ̀ ki ɗiɗi nɗaŋ ɗi ɓɔ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ teka ̀ ɓɔ da ̀ ɗki ̀ i ̀ nɛ .
Ghɛn anɛ ɓi mi ̀ ni yɛɛ ri lɛ a ̀ ki ̀ lɛ , i a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yii mɛtin mɛtan ̀ , nni bog i ̀ ɗimi , kɛ ̀ ɛ ca ̀ ɗ yi yi rɔɓi mɛ ̀ tin mɛnin ri ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ taa ̀ ni ̀ n ɓi-reɓ a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ kaa ̀ ki ̀ bog ki kaa ɗimi a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ri ̀ kɔ ɓii ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ ?
I a ̀ mɛ tanɛn yɔ ̀ , a ̀ saa ̀ gh yɔ ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ laŋ ri ̀ coo kinya ̀ a ̀ ,
i a ̀ kpaŋi a mɛɛ mii , a ̀ taŋzɛ ̀ n lɛ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ reŋka ̀ ŋ ɓii , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ba-go ̀ ŋzɛn ɓii a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ti nya ̀ a ̀ rɛɛna n ̀ ɗaŋ ɓisuulɛ ma ̀ a ghɛɛ ̀ dii ti ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛ i ̀ i nɗimi .
N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni lɛ , ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ ki ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ girig fɔlɔɔ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , di n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe bogtɛ ̀ n a ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛɛ n ̀ ɗem , ki cee ki ki ri ɓisuu ɓum mɛ ̀ tin mɛnin ri ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ taa ̀ ni ̀ n , ɓɛ ɓɛ ri lɛ saaɗ , ɓɛ ki ghɛɓsii ɓi com lɛ ɓɛɛ lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛn ti ̀ mɛ ̀ rem .
Nsoo ̀ lɛ i giɓ adɛŋ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ dola ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ , nni dola ̀ bog i ̀ ɗimi , a ̀ a ro ̀ o ̀ si ɓi nya lamɓa ̀ a ̀ fyɛn naa , a ̀ kona ̀ g ki ̀ kaa ̀ dola ̀ i ̀ nɛn a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ri ̀ yɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ ?
I a ̀ mɛ ghɛn yɔ ̀ , a ̀ reŋi ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ reŋka ̀ ŋ ɓii , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ ɓɔ , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ti nya ̀ a ̀ rɛɛna n ̀ ɗaŋ lɛ maa ghɛɛdii mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɛ ̀ m mɛ mɛ nɗimi .
N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni lɛ , ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ ki ri girig fɔlɔɔ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓumɓɛ titom ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓisuu n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe bog a ̀ nɛ a ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛɛ n ̀ ɗem .
Yeesus a ̀ teeti ̀ ɓɔ da ̀ ɗki ̀ lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ yɛɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɔn ɓɛ ɓɛbaŋi ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ .
Nni roa ̀ siito ̀ n a ̀ kpaagha ̀ seŋi lɛ : Ta ̀ a ̀ ta , faa mɛ ̀ ga ̀ ɓ yɛ ̀ m i ̀ i ̀ kum . Fɔɔnnɛ Seŋi a ̀ ka ̀ ɓsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ i ̀ kum wii .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɔɔ mɛru ɓɛ ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ , roa ̀ siito ̀ n anɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓadɛ ̀ n ɓyom ɓii ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ kwe ̀ ɗ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ , a ̀ yogsa ̀ g i ̀ kum wii wɔɔ ɓi cɛɓ ki ko ̀ o ̀ koo .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ le ̀ gsi ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ yogsaagh ikum wii , fɔɔnnɛ coo za ̀ y ki kpigha ̀ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kin ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa ti ri com ki lɛ a ̀ ghɛɓ mii ̀ .
Nni a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ ɗiŋii kisa ̀ y yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kin ̀ ; roa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ rom nyi lɛ a kɛn ̀ nyi ki ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi je ̀ e ̀ a dɛm .
A ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ za ̀ y i ̀ nɛ lɛ di a ̀ a ɗii ɓyom ɓi je ̀ e ̀ yi n ̀ ti yi ɗila ̀ g , wɔ ̀ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ lɛ a fa nyi ɓyɔ kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ sugti ̀ gha ̀ ɓi nyimiɗ , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ sasay seŋi wɛ ̀ m ɓɛ ri ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g lɛɛ ̀ gwey , mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yu ̀ ki ̀ wuwii za ̀ y fɛ .
M ̀ ɓii ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ , n ̀ sugti ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Ta ̀ a ̀ ta wɛ ̀ m , n ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Ta ̀ a ̀ ta ! N ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ ɓe ɓi san a ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ ɓi san a ̀ nɛ a ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋkɔɔ ,
fɔɔnnɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ti ̀ ɓi lɛ , ɓɛɛ reŋi ti ̀ mɛ ̀ lɛ man wɔɔ ̀ , tera mɛ ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɔɔ .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ a ̀ kɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ seŋi . Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ kakay fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ , nni seŋi a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ y nyi , a ̀ tuɓi ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ree , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n nyi ki ̀ siighrɛɛ ɓi nyoo , a ̀ lɔ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɗ nyi .
Man a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Ta ̀ a ̀ ta , n ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ ɓe ɓi san a ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ ɓi san a ̀ nɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɔɔ , nni ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ti ̀ ɓi lɛ ɓɛɛ reŋi ti ̀ mɛ ̀ lɛ man wɔɔ ̀ .
Nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ seŋi a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓii lɛ : Terinas ̀ mɛ ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ki ki ɓiisɛɛ ki ̀ rɔɔtɛɛ lɛ fyɛ ̀ ɗ , ɓi fa nyi a waa ̀ tɛn ; a ̀ kpaa ti ̀ ɓɔ lɛ . Waasiina nyi bɔŋ ɓi mana ̀ ca ̀ g , ɓi ̀ waasi ̀ ti ̀ nyi ɓɛ ̀ siripa ̀ s ɓi mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ .
Ɓi yuiy ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓwɛɗ ki sani ̀ nya ki ki ri ki ̀ fɔmɛn , ɓi wey kɔ , ti ɗi di ti nya ̀ a ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ man wɛm ̀ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ wugha ̀ nni a ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛɛ , man a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɗimga ̀ nni ti ̀ ghɛɛdii nyi .
Fɔlɔɔ a ɓaa , di dɛli ̀ i ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n i ̀ n ̀ tonto i ̀ kakas ̀ a dɛm . Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ i ̀ susu ̀ ka ̀ y di i ̀ ti ɓii ̀ kpaŋi ̀ a mɛɛ , nni i ̀ woka ̀ y lɛ ri ̀ gom i ̀ ɓyom ɓi ɓoɓoghɛn , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ dɛli ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say a seŋi a ̀ dɛŋ , a ̀ tɔg nyi ɓisuucɛ nnɛ gom i ̀ ri ̀ a mɛɛ mɛ seŋi ?
N ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say a ɓa ̀ g dɛli ̀ i ̀ nɛn lɛ : Goni a ̀ sughii , nni Soŋi a ̀ woli man a ̀ sani ̀ nya a ̀ n ̀ fɔmɛn ɓisuu man , lɛ a ̀ kpaŋdii nyi ɓi ɓya ̀ g di a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ syeesyee ɓi nyo ̀ o ̀ .
Nni dɛli ̀ i ̀ nɛ ̀ n i ̀ woka ̀ bim , i ̀ ɓe ̀ n ki ̀ ɗiŋii ɓi naa , seŋi a ̀ kpaŋ yi ̀ nyi ki ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzaagh lɛ a ɗiŋi ɓi naa .
Man a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpaa min seŋi lɛ : Ghɛna ! Be ̀ g gɛɛ ̀ nɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ ba ̀ li ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ maa ̀ sasa ̀ y wɔ ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɛ nsɛɛti wɔ nsoo ̀ ŋwos bog , nni u ̀ ka fagha ̀ ɓi mɛ nsoo ̀ bwiy lɛ n ̀ ɗi ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ reŋka ̀ ŋ ɓɛm , di ti nya ̀ a ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , yɛ ̀ ɛ man wɔɔ ̀ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ a sughii nyaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yogsaghii ̀ i ̀ kum wɔɔ ri ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ , ɓɛ riɓa ̀ mɓa ̀ , u ̀ teɗ man a ̀ sani ̀ nya a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ fɔmɛn , u ̀ wey nyi .
Seŋi a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Man wɛm ̀ , wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m fɔɔnnɛ com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki wooghrɛɛ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , kaa ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɔŋ lɛ , ti nyaa ̀ rɛn , ɓisuulɛ goni a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ wugha ̀ nni a ̀ sugtii yi ̀ ɓi cɛɓ , a ̀ ɗimga ̀ , nni ti ̀ ghɛɛdii nyi .
Yeesus a ̀ kpaati ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g lɛ : Guŋgum adɛŋ yɛɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ mum a ̀ nɛ a ̀ a m ̀ ɓe ̀ gi ̀ nyi i ̀ kum . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a yooyogsi ̀ nyi i ̀ kum .
Nni a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n , a ̀ tɔg nyi lɛ : Ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓum ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa ki ɓɛ rara ̀ ɗ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ ki ri la ? Re ̀ si mɛ ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ u kɛ ̀ ɛkɛɛ ̀ si ̀ i ̀ kum wɛm ̀ ɓisuulɛ , wa ̀ a ɓe ̀ ŋdi ɓi wɔ .
Fɔɔnnɛ m ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -i ̀ kum anɛ ̀ n a ̀ fe ̀ ka ̀ ɓi nɗem wii lɛ : M ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ɓa ̀ la yɛ ̀ ɛ masa ̀ wɛ ̀ m a ̀ kpaa lɛ mɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ m ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋdi ̀ ikum wii ? Mɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ n ̀ say dɛm , n ̀ ki wowog n ̀ too ̀ ri ̀ ɗ lɛ nlɔ ̀ n ̀ lɔn ɓum ɓyom ɓi ki ̀ ɓa ̀ a ̀ .
N ̀ -yii yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i , lɛ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛɛ ghaɓ mɛ ̀ lɛ syeesyee a mɛɛ maa di ɓɛ pisii mɛ ̀ ɓi ki ̀ say ki riɓe ̀ ŋ ɗi ikum .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ masa ̀ wi ̀ i ̀ ri ɓɛ ̀ pon lɛ bog bo ̀ g bog a ̀ tɔg roa ̀ ntonto lɛ : Wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ri ̀ masa ̀ wɛ ̀ m ri ̀ pon a cɛ ?
Roa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : Pon wɛm ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kpɛm ɓɛ mɔɔgh mɛ ̀ tin mɛtan ̀ . Nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ roa ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ : Tera kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ pon wɔɔ ̀ , u kɔri ɓi zi lɛ fyɛ ̀ ɗ , u kan ̀ mii ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ kpɛm ɓɛ mɔɔgh mɛ ̀ tin mɛɓɛɛ ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , a ̀ kpaa ti ̀ roa ̀ mbog lɛ : Ɓɛɛ tɔtɔg wɔ cɛ ? Roa ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ : Mɛ ̀ ku ̀ ti ̀ mɛ ba ̀ a ̀ zi ̀ mɛ ̀ tin mɛtan ̀ , nni m ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -i ̀ kum a kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : Ka ̀ na ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ a pon lɛ mɛ ̀ ku ̀ ti ̀ mɛ ̀ tin mɛnin .
Masa ̀ a ̀ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki m ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -i ̀ kum anɛ ̀ n a ̀ sɛka ̀ nyi lɛ , a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ri ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n lɛɛ ̀ gwey . Fɔlɔɔ a re ̀ sii lɛ , ɓumɓɛ ɓi cɛɓ ki ziinɛ ɓɛ wom ̀ zaagh ɓi cɛɓ ki lɛ ri ̀ ɓɔ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓum a ̀ cee ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓi ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaati ̀ gha ̀ lɛ : N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni lɛ , kaana lɛ ɓi ɓa ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ghan ri ̀ i ̀ kum wu kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ̀ kpaa ̀ , mɔ yɛɛ ri mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ɓi naa i ̀ fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ di i ̀ kum win ̀ wu yii ̀ di mi ̀ ni ɓi ca ̀ g .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ɓɔɔ ɓyom ɓɛsa ̀ g lɛ syeesyee , ri ̀ ntyweeyi a ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ɓigwey lɛ syeesyee . Roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ɓi ɓɔɔ ɓyom ɓɛsa ̀ g lɛ syeesyee , a ̀ a yi ɓi riɓe ̀ ŋ ɗi gi ̀ n yi ɓyom lɛ syeesyee ri ̀ ntyweeyi .
Nni i ɓi ̀ mɛ rɔ ̀ ɓ kɛ ̀ ɓi yi riɓe ̀ ŋ ɗi ikum wu kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ̀ kpaa fɛlɛ ri ̀ n ̀ tyweeyi , ghɛn yɛɛ ri mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ faa ̀ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ i ̀ kum lɛ ɓi ɓeŋ ̀ ?
Ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ i ɓi ̀ re ̀ sii lɛ ɓi ̀ yin ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ tyweeyi ̀ ɓi ɓyom ɓi ɓɛgan , ɓaa fa ɓi mini ɓiŋkin ɓi mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ .
Lɛ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say bog a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ say ɓɛ ̀ masa ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ ɓisuulɛ , a ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓe ̀ e ̀ zɛɛ bog , a ̀ keesi ̀ roa ̀ mbog ; nsoo ̀ lɛ a ̀ ra ̀ rɛ ̀ n ri ̀ masa ̀ bog , a ̀ naŋ a ̀ mbog . Ɓi ̀ yin ɗi i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ ɓi say lɛ ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ fog .
Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ ɓɛ n ̀ keesa ̀ g mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni ɓɛ wowo ̀ ka ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m di ɓɛɛ ̀ wɔ ̀ wɛy Yeesus .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ kaakaa lɛ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛɛ ghɛn ̀ mi ̀ ni lɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ saaɗ ɓɛ ɓum , wɔ ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ yii mɛ ̀ rem min . Fɔɔnnɛ com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ki ri gi ̀ n i com ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓum , ki ri com ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓe ̀ e ̀ zɛɛ lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Ri ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ɗi ɓidɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Moyis ri ̀ ɗi ɓɛkpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɗi kigha ̀ ki ̀ say a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Zyaŋ Ba ̀ ɓtis a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ . Nni a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ , a ̀ kpaŋ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll a kaakalɛ ̀ n a ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , fɔɔnnɛ mum bimiɗ a kaakaa lɛ a ɗiŋi ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kin ̀ ɓi-te ̀ ɗ .
Ki ri lɛ fyɛ ̀ ɗ lɛ , ɗyoo ri ̀ zi ɓyɛɛ sili ̀ a ̀ cee lɛ maa ki ̀ ka ̀ ŋga a ̀ dɛŋ a pɛsɛn ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna .
I mum a ̀ na ̀ ɓi giɓ wii ̀ , a ̀ wɔɔti ̀ a ̀ dɛŋ , di a ̀ ki ̀ i fi ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g . Nni fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ wɔli giɓ anɛ yii a ̀ na ̀ ɓi a ̀ ki ̀ i girig fi ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g .
Mum a ̀ dɛŋ yɛɛ ɓagha ̀ guŋgum , a ̀ waata ̀ g ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ɓi syeesyee , ɓi ki ɓa ɓila ̀ a ̀ ɓi mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni ; fɔɔnnɛ ŋwos anɛ aɗyoo bimiɗ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ghɛghɛ ̀ ɓka ̀ ɓi ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ a ̀ ki ki ̀ ki ɓyoo ɓisɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ .
Nni maa nyi ̀ inyi ̀ g a ̀ mum lɛ Lazaari , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓɛɛ nyoo bimiɗ , a ̀ a n ̀ nɔ ̀ ŋɗa ̀ g asuunaa wu guŋgum anɛ ̀ n .
A ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ za ̀ y i ̀ nɛ lɛ di a ̀ a ɗii nsoo ̀ bubu ̀ ɓ yi yi raara ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ a teɓe ̀ re ̀ a ̀ guŋgum anɛ ̀ n zi , a ̀ a lɔŋ ri ̀ ɓa ɗi ̀ n ɗyɔ ri ̀ ɗyɔ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , bu yi m ̀ pɛ ̀ sa ̀ g ti ̀ i ̀ , yi yu ki ̀ lɛɛlɛɛ ɓiɓɛɛ ̀ ɓii ɓin ̀ .
Nni maa nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g a ̀ mum a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ wugha ̀ , ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓɛ teɗ nyi , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ nyi ki ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ sii ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ Abiraham . Yɛ ̀ ɛ guŋgum anɛ ̀ n a ̀ wugha ̀ girig , ɓɛ ɓom ̀ nyi .
Nni wɔɔ a nyɔ ̀ ɛ ̀ y nnɛ a ̀ ɓegsi ̀ gha ̀ mis , di ri ̀ kɛŋ ɗyɛɛ ̀ pye ̀ npyen nyi mis , a ̀ ghɛn yi ̀ lɔŋ Abiraham fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ , ɓɛɛ ̀ Lazaari n ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔriyɛn nyi ɓi n ̀ wɔŋi ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ nya ̀ mga ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ lɛ : Ta ̀ a ̀ ta Abiraham , wogha ɓa ̀ mɛ nyi ̀ ghnyi ̀ g , u rom yi ̀ Lazaari , a nɔg yi ̀ mana ̀ ca ̀ g ɓi mɛ ̀ nig , a yɔɔ ̀ si mɛ ̀ ɓi ri ̀ lema ̀ g , di ɗyɛɛ ki yɛ ̀ ɛ ɗi fɔli , lɛ n ̀ wowog rikɛŋ lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓi ɗuu ɗi ̀ .
Nni Abiraham a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ nyi lɛ : Man wɛm ̀ , yiti ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki u ̀ wowo ̀ ka ̀ ga ̀ ɓ yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ i ki ̀ rɔɔ di u ̀ kaka ɓi cɛɓ , Lazaari nyii wowo ̀ ka ̀ mɛ ̀ tɔɓ ; nni ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki , nyii ti ɓii ̀ fɔɔfɔɔ ̀ sɛ ̀ n fɛ , wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wowo ̀ g ri ̀ kɛŋ .
Ɓi kiŋce ̀ m , coo bɛŋ i ̀ ri ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ nɛ lɛ , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si ri ̀ mi ̀ ni , lɛ di ɓumɓɛ fɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkis ɓɛ ɓɛ kɔni lɛ ɓɛɛ yu foo , nsoo ̀ ɓɛ foo a lɔ ̀ ŋkin ɓɛ ɓɛ kɔni lɛ ɓɛɛ yu fɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkis , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa ri bee inɛ ɓɛɛ syaayi ̀ .
Nni guŋgum anɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpagha ̀ lɛ : Ta ̀ a ̀ ta Abiraham m ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzaagh min wɔ lɛ , u rom ̀ Lazaari ɓi naa yɛ ̀ m i ̀ ɓum , lɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓɛ ɓɛbaŋi ̀ ɓɛtan ̀ .
A kɛn ̀ ɓɔ ki ̀ wogsii ɓiɓan ɓi , di ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ yu ̀ girig ɓi ja ̀ ŋ i ri ̀ kɛŋ i ̀ nɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi mii ̀ i ̀ nɛ .
Abiraham a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : Ɓɛ ̀ goni ɓɛ ri lɛ , ɓɔ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Moyis , ɓɔ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kaa ̀ ta ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛkpaŋzi ̀ -ɓiɓan , ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ woo ̀ gh ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ guŋgum a kpaati ̀ gha ̀ lɛ : Ta ̀ a ̀ ta Abiraham : E ̀ e e ̀ e ! Lɔŋ i mum a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ fɛ a nyɔ ̀ ɛ ̀ y a ̀ kɛ ̀ n a lɔ ̀ ŋkaa , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛɛ mɛre ̀ m .
Abiraham a ̀ ɓa ̀ gti ̀ nyi lɛ : I ɓɛ ̀ goni ɓɛ yin lɛ ɓɛ wog ri ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ɗi Moyis ri ̀ ɗi ɓɛkpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan , nsoo ̀ mum a ̀ a ghe ̀ mɓɛɛ yi ̀ fɛ a nyɔ ̀ ɛ ̀ y , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ɓɔ ki ̀ kpaa ̀ ki ̀ ɓan , ɓaa gherɛn ɓi .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g lɛ : Ɓum ɓɛ yin lɛ ɓɛ rɔɓ lɛ ɓɛ kɛɓtɛɛ ɓi fiɓa ̀ g , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛkɛɓti ̀ ɓum ti ̀ ɓa ̀ g .
Ki ri ki ̀ rɔɔ ɓisu wii lɛ ɓɛɛ kaŋ ̀ nyi coo gɔ ̀ g i ̀ ki ̀ pɛn ɓi ki ̀ mi ̀ i ̀ gh , di ɓɛɛ pig nyi ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n a ̀ cee ɗi lɛ a kɛɓti ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɔɓti ɓɛ fi ̀ ɓa ̀ g .
Kɔ ̀ riina ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ri ̀ mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ ! I goni a ̀ ki ̀ i wɔ ̀ ki ̀ ɓe , re ̀ si nyi zɛ ̀ ɗ yii ̀ , i a ̀ gherɛɛ yɔ ̀ , a ̀ lemgi ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗii , u ̀ cenɛ ̀ n nyi .
Nni aa ̀ na ̀ ni ɓi ̀ ɓan taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri wɔ ̀ ɓi nwos bog , innɛ a ̀ sugtii yi ̀ wɔ ̀ a nyoo fɔlɔɔ gɛ ̀ n taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , a ̀ gherɛ ̀ n a ̀ ki lemgi zɛ ̀ ɗ yii ̀ , u ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ nyi ki ̀ cenɛɛ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ Kan lɛ : Te ̀ gsi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗis .
Nni Kan a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : I ɓya ̀ ari ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi ɗi ri lɛ ɗi teghɛ ̀ n lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ za ̀ m i ̀ nyas , di ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ , ɓi ̀ kpaa ki ̀ te ki lɛ : Pɛ ̀ sɛn fɛ , u kɛn ̀ ki ̀ ɓɛlɛɛ ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n , ki ̀ te kin ̀ ki ki fɔlɔɔ .
Ghɛn anɛ ɓi mi ̀ ni yɛɛ ri lɛ a ̀ ki ̀ lɛ i a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a sasay nyi ɓi dɛm , nsoo ̀ lɛ a ɓe ̀ ŋɓeŋ nyi ɓi ̀ tuwe , a ̀ kpaa roa ̀ nɛ ̀ n di a ̀ sughii ̀ a dɛm lɛ yu ki ̀ ɗii lɛ fyɛ ̀ ɗ .
Com ki a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ kpaa nyi ki ri lɛ : Pe ̀ gsɛn ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g , u ̀ ki cenɗɛn ɓila ̀ a ̀ , di u yu mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ka ̀ a , u ̀ ɓoŋ lɛ , n ̀ ka ɗi , n ̀ nɔ , fɔɔnnɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ siitɛn min girig ki ̀ ɗii ̀ , u ̀ nɔ .
Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi nya lɛ , a fa n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say wii ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n lɛ , roa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ a ki ̀ i ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi a ̀ a kpaa nyi lɛ a ki ?
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ , mi ̀ ni girig , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓi ̀ mɛ ki ̀ ɓiɓan ɓi ɓɛ tɔɔgh mi ̀ ni lɛ ɓi ki , ɓi ̀ kpaa lɛ : Ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛ zɛɛri ̀ zɛy , lɛ ki ̀ ɓan ki kaa ri ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ si yɛɛ ki , kɛɛ ̀ ki tya ̀ a ki ̀ i .
Ɓi ri ̀ kɛ ̀ n ɗi a Yorisalɛm , Yeesus a ̀ fyeegha ̀ ɓi bee inɛ i ̀ ghaghii ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ nɛ lɛ ri ̀ Samari , ri ̀ Galile .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi maa ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ a ̀ dɛŋ , nni ɓɛ ̀ kukwiy ntɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛ yugha ̀ nyi ki ̀ ɓoŋi ̀ , ɓɛ rɛli ̀ i ̀ fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ , ɓɛ kpaa jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ :
Yeesus , n ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g ! Wogha ɓi ̀ si nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ɓɔ , nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Kɛ ̀ ɛna ki ̀ re ̀ sɛɛ ɓi mis mɛ ɓɛpi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey . Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ , nni ɓɛ sigmɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ɓɛ mɛ wɔ ̀ n .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɔ ki ghɛnga ̀ lɛ ki mɛ wɔ ̀ n , ki sugti ̀ gha ̀ y ri ̀ jɛ ̀ m di kɛɛ ɓɔɔɓɔgsi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
A ̀ kpi ̀ gha ̀ Yeesus a mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ , a ̀ ruusi ̀ i ̀ su ɓi zi , a ̀ fa nyi ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n . Ŋwaa ̀ nce ̀ m a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a Samari .
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa min lɛ : Ɓɛ ̀ kukwiy ɓɛ kin ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ɓaa wɔ ̀ ni ɓi nya ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛce ̀ m ? Nni ki ̀ taa ̀ ni ̀ n kim ̀ bog ki ri fe ?
Lɔŋ n ̀ ke ̀ n a mum a ̀ nɛ yaa yitii , ɓi ɓɔɔ ̀ ce ̀ m , lɛ a sugtii ̀ ki ̀ kemzii Bɛ ̀ ll .
Nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ min ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ : Pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , u kɛn ̀ , ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗyɔɔ ɗi ghɛɓsii wɔ ̀ .
Nni Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ tɔka ̀ Yeesus lɛ fin innɛ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll ki ri ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u ? A ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : Ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll kaa yu ̀ ɓi , ɓi ri ̀ kuu ɗi riyu ̀ ɗi lɛ , ɓum ɓɛ ghɛn ɗi ̀ mis .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓaa reɓ ɓi lɛ , kɛɛ ̀ ki fɛ , nsoo ̀ lɛ kɛɛ ̀ kinii , ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ yii ̀ lɛ , ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll ki ri ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n .
Nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g lɛ : Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki tii ̀ , ki ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ri ̀ za ̀ y i ̀ nɛ lɛ , di ɓya ̀ a ghɛɛ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ Man a ̀ mum , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓya ̀ a ki ghɛn ɓi .
Ɓɛ ri mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ kpaa ̀ lɛ innɛnii , nsoo ̀ lɛ innɛ fɛ ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɓi kɛ ̀ n wɔɔ , kɛ ̀ ɓi mɛŋ wɔɔ ri mɛ ̀ ree .
Fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ ŋwa ̀ ɗ a ̀ ti a ̀ ŋwa ̀ ɗki ̀ , a ̀ kpeŋzi ̀ ɗyoo ɗi ̀ ce ̀ m , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ Man a ̀ mum a ̀ ɓaa gɛ ɓi ŋwosi risugti ̀ i ̀ ɗii .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ a ka log kiwoo ̀ gh ri ̀ kɛŋ lɛɛ ̀ gwey , gba ̀ a ̀ i ̀ ɓum i ̀ gɛɛ ̀ nɛ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ɓe ̀ n nyi .
Lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ Nowe , fɔɔlɔɔ nnɛ ki ɓii ̀ ki ̀ lɛɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ Man a ̀ mum a ̀ ɓii ̀ sugtii yi .
Ɓum ɓɛ kiki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , di ɓɛɛ ̀ ɗi di ɓɛɛ ̀ nɔ , ɓɛ wɔwɛy ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ , ɓɛ fafa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gɔ ̀ n a mɛ ̀ wɛy , ɓɛ yin-yi ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ dɛli ̀ ɓaa ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ , a ̀ kpaŋ ŋwos anɛ Nowe a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ki ̀ kɔm , don i yu ̀ , i ̀ cuusi ̀ ɓɔ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ki ̀ ɓan ki ki kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ Lɔt , ki ki ̀ lɛɛ gɛ ti ̀ , ɓum ɓɛ kiki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ɗiɗi ̀ , ɓɛ nɔnɔ ̀ , ɓɛ la ̀ lag , ɓɛ ki ka ̀ ka ̀ ɓ ɓyom , ɓɛ ɓɛɓɛ ̀ y ɓyom , ɓɛ ki tootoŋɗɛ ̀ n mɛɛ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ŋwos anɛ Lɔt a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Sɔdɔm ɗuu ri ̀ n ̀ du ̀ si ɓi nɔnɔ ̀ gha ̀ y ɓi ɗyoo yɛ ̀ ɛ bwey , ɓi cuusi ̀ ɓɔ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ki ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ lɔŋ com ki ̀ fog ŋwos anɛ Man a ̀ mum a ̀ ri re ̀ sɛɛgɛs ̀ .
Ŋwos anɛ ̀ n , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓaa gɛ ɓi bwe ̀ y aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɛ sɛɛdii lɛ a teɗ ɓyom ɓii ɓi naa ; nsoo ̀ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓaa gɛ ɓi dɛm , kɛ ̀ ɛ sugtii ̀ a mɛɛ .
Yitiina gili Lɔt .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ kaa gɛ bee inɛ lɛ a ghɛɓsi cɛɓ kii , a ̀ ɗimzii gɛ kɔ . Fɔɔnnɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɗimzii gɛ cɛɓ kii nnyɛɛ ki ɓatii gɛ ri ̀ kɔ .
N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni lɛ : Ki ɓaagɛ ɓi-ru wi ̀ n lɛ , i ɓum ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ nɔnɔŋii ɓyomɓilɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ fog , ɓɛ teɗ bog roa ̀ mbog a ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓ .
Ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ wɔwɔ ̀ g ɓyom nɗaŋ , ɓɛ teɗ bog , bog a ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓ .
