Fɔɔnnɛ Zasye a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , a ̀ kpaa Kan lɛ : Kan , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ ka ̀ ɓi ikum wɛm ̀ ga ̀ ɓ yiɓɛɛ ̀ , n ̀ fa ga ̀ ɓ bog ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sogha ̀ sogha . I n ̀ teka ̀ mum dola ̀ bog ɓi ki ̀ co ̀ o ̀ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi ɓii ̀ le ̀ ɓi dola ̀ yinin ̀ .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : Go ̀ ri i ̀ ɗiŋii ɓi naa i ̀ nɛ gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , ɓisuulɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ girig do ̀ o ̀ yi ̀ Abiraham .
Ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ Man a ̀ mum a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , a kaa ̀ a ̀ ki ghɛɓsi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɗimɛn .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛ wowo ̀ ka ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓin ̀ , nni Yeesus a ̀ teeti ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ da ̀ ɗki ̀ i ̀ dɛŋ ɓisuulɛ , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ Yorisalɛm , ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ ɓum ɓɛ fefe ̀ ka ̀ lɛ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kɔm ̀ kin ̀ .
Nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ min lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ man a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kemi ̀ nnyɛ ̀ ɛ kɛnga ̀ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ lɛ a ɓɔg yi ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m wɔɔ , di a sugtii ̀ min ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kii .
Fɔnnɛ a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓii ntɛ ̀ ɗ , a ̀ ka ̀ ɓsi ̀ ɓɔ ti ̀ raŋ ̀ ti gol n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Rɔ ̀ ɓina ki ̀ ki ̀ kii du ̀ ne ri ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɛ , ɓi yaa ̀ si mɔ , a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ sugtii yi .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kii ɓɛ ɓee ̀ ɓe ̀ e ̀ zɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi , nni ɓɛ romga ̀ ɓum ɓɛɗɛŋ di nyii mɛ kɛ ̀ n , lɛ ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ ki ̀ kpaa ̀ wɔɔ lɛ , ɓɔɔ kɔni ɓi lɛ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a lami ɓɔ .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ suka ̀ y di a ̀ mɛ ɓɔg yi ri ̀ fo ̀ m , nni a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛ a ̀ fagha ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ n , lɛ ɓɛɛ resi nyi cɛ kɛɛ ̀ ki mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɛ rɔɓka ̀ ki ̀ yali ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ roa ̀ ntonto a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ y a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Ta ̀ a ̀ ta , fi ̀ raŋ ̀ fyɔɔ fi gol fi n-yali tidɛŋ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ .
Ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi kpaa n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say anɛ ̀ n lɛ : Ki rɔɔtɛɛ , u ̀ ri ̀ syeesyee a ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say , yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ re ̀ sii mɛ ̀ lɛ u ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say a n ̀ tyweeyi ɓi ɓɔɔ ɓiɓan ɓɛsa ̀ g , n ̀ ɗɛsii wɔ ̀ n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ .
Nni roa ̀ ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ a yu ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ , a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Ta ̀ a ̀ ta , fi ̀ raŋ ̀ fyɔɔ fi n ̀ -yali ti ̀ raŋ ̀ tidɛŋ titan ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpaati ̀ gha ̀ roa ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ : N ̀ ɗɛsii wɔ ̀ n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ba ̀ n yitan ̀ .
Nni roa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ yu ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Ta ̀ a ̀ ta , fi ̀ raŋ ̀ fyɔɔ fyɛɛ ̀ fi , n ̀ ka ̀ ga ̀ fyɔ ɓi ki ̀ la ̀ a ̀ , n ̀ nyam ,
ɓisuulɛ , n ̀ ɗisi ̀ gha ̀ wɔ ̀ , lɛ u ̀ nyɛni lɛɛ ̀ gwey ; u ̀ ti u ̀ teki ̀ com ki u ̀ nɔ ̀ ŋzii ɓi , u ̀ ki sagi com ki u ̀ ɓɛ ̀ li ɓi .
Nni ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗin ̀ ɗi kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : N-yɔm ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓi ri ̀ kpaa ɗyɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ; u ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say ! U ̀ yigha ̀ lɔŋ lɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ nyɛni lɛɛ ̀ gwey , lɛ n ̀ ti n ̀ teki ̀ com ki n ̀ nɔ ̀ ŋzii ɓi , n ̀ ki sagi ki m ̀ ɓɛ ̀ li ɓi !
Nni ɓi cɛ nnɛ u ̀ nyamga ̀ ɓi mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɛ ̀ m a baŋ ̀ lɛ , i n ̀ sughii ̀ n ̀ teɗ mɔ wɔɔ lɛ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ yaa ̀ yali ̀ mii ̀ ?
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ lɛ : Ɓa ̀ tɛɛna nyi fi ̀ raŋ ̀ fin ̀ , ɓi fa fyɔ ri ̀ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ti ̀ raŋ ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ .
Ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kpaa nyi lɛ : Ta ̀ a ̀ ta ŋwaa ̀ nɛ u kalag lɛ ti fa , a ̀ ti ri ̀ ti ̀ raŋ ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ .
Nyii pɛɛ ̀ zi ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni lɛ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓyom innɛ ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ fatii , roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ com , ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ ɓa ̀ tɛɛ lɛ ri ̀ maa ga ̀ ɓ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ nyi mii ̀ .
Ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a ɓɛ ̀ be ̀ na ̀ bena ɓɛm , ɓɔɔ kɔnga ̀ ɓi lɛ n ̀ lami ɓɔ , nni yu ̀ unay fɛ ri ̀ ɓɔ , ɓi sii ̀ ɓɔ ɓɛ ̀ ɓoŋ foo ɓi mis mɛ ̀ m .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ fɔlɔɔ , nni a ̀ syo ̀ ga ̀ ɓɔ bee lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓɔg a Yorisalɛm .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ mɛ wuɓsɛn ɓilɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi lɛ , ri ̀ Bɛtfazee ri ̀ Bɛtanii ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ do ̀ n i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ nɗegi ̀ lɛ do ̀ n i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ o ̀ li ̀ vyee , nni a ̀ romga ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ ,
a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Kɛ ̀ ɛna ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki ki rii ̀ mi ̀ ni kinii asu , i ɓi ̀ kpaŋi wɔɔ , ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ tanɛɛ man a ̀ ja ̀ ɗki a ̀ nɛ mum a ̀ ka ɓoka ̀ ɓi mii ̀ n ̀ suŋɛn , ɓi fumii ̀ nyi ɓi yuis ̀ ri ̀ nyi .
I mum a ̀ tɔɔgh mi ̀ ni lɛ ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓi ̀ fu ̀ mii man a ̀ ja ̀ ɗki a ̀ nɛ ̀ n , ɓi ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Kan a kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ ti kɛn ̀ nyi ri ̀ yɔ ̀ .
Nni ɓumɓɛ Yeesus a ̀ romga ̀ ɓɛn ̀ ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ , ɓɛ tanɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ri lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ fufu ̀ mi ̀ gha ̀ man a ̀ ja ̀ ɗki a ̀ nɛ ̀ n nni ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ nyi ɓɛ tɔka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓi fu ̀ fumi man a ̀ ja ̀ ɗki a ̀ nɛ ̀ n ?
Ɓɔɔ ɓaa ̀ g lɛ : Kan a kɔ ̀ ngi lɛ ti kɛn ̀ nyi ri ̀ yɔ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ Yeesus ri ̀ man a ̀ ja ̀ ɗki a ̀ nɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ ghas ̀ ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ mii ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , ɓɛ ɓɔgsi ̀ nyi mii ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ kɛ ̀ nkɛ ̀ nga ̀ , ɓum ɓɛ ghagha ̀ la ̀ ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ɓyaa ɓi bee aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ mɛ wuɓsɛn Yorisalɛm , ɓi ri ̀ sɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɗi do ̀ n i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ o ̀ li ̀ vyee , nnɛ ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ ki ɓanga ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ , ɓisuu da ̀ m yi ɓiɓan yice ̀ m yi ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ .
Ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ lɛ : Bɛ ̀ ll a maŋ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi ɗi yuu yi ̀ ɓi ɗii ɗi Kan , fyo ̀ oog a ̀ ɓa ɓi ɗyoo ɓi ɗu ̀ m , ri ̀ kem ɗyɛɛ ki Bɛ ̀ ll .
Fɔɔnnɛ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ Yeesus lɛ : N ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g , simi ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɔɔ ɓɛɛ maa ̀ rɛn .
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : N ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni lɛ , i ɓɛ maarɛɛ , gɔ ̀ g yi kpagsɛ ̀ n .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ mɛ wuɓsɛn ba ̀ n , nni a ̀ soɓka ̀ mis ɓi yɔ ̀ , a ̀ tum ri ̀ re ̀ n ɓisuu ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛ ̀ n , a ̀ kpaa lɛ :
I wɔ ̀ girig wa ̀ a ri ̀ lɛ u ̀ yi com ki ki ri lɛ ki fa wɔ ̀ fyo ̀ oog ɓi ŋwos a gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , nni fe ! Com ki ̀ n ki ri wɔ ̀ ki ̀ nyamɛn ɓi le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ kɔ ̀ ɔ ghɛn kɔ .
Mɛ ̀ ru mɛdɛŋ mɛ ri ɓii ̀ ghɛnɛɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɔɔ , mɛ ɓɛ ̀ be ̀ na ̀ bena ɓɔɔ ɓɛ ri wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ ce ̀ ŋzɛɛ ri gari , ɓɛ ki ghegsag wɔ ; ɓɛ ri wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ faa ̀ ri ̀ baŋi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɓɛg ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ɓɛ ɓii ̀ ɓu ̀ gsii lɛ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ , ri ̀ ɓɔn ɓɔɔ , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ca ̀ a ̀ ti gɔ ̀ g i ̀ dɛŋ m ̀ ɓasɛn ɗi yimbog ɓisuulɛ , u ̀ yigha ̀ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ wɔ ̀ ki ̀ ghɛɓsii mii ̀ .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ na ̀ ɓ ɗi ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -fye ̀ e ̀ ,
a ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ , naa yɛ ̀ m i ̀ ri ɓa naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n . Wɔ ̀ lɛ mi ̀ nii mɛ ghaasi yɔ ̀ naa i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ wiiwi ̀ i ̀ .
Yeesus a ̀ a nti a ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛ ̀ ŋwos ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll . Nni ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ri ̀ mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m mɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓɛ kaaka ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ bee inɛ ɓɛɛ wey nyi .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ɓɛ yigha ̀ ɓi lannɛ ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ ki ɓisuulɛ , ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ɓagha ̀ mɛ ̀ ree ̀ mɛ ̀ ramɛn ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Yeesus a ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ .
Ŋwos adɛŋ , di Yeesus a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ri ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɗi kilɔ ̀ ŋ , a ̀ ki kpaakpaa Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , nni ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ peegha ̀ y ,
ɓɛ tɔg nyi lɛ : Kali ɓi ̀ si ! Ɓi-te ̀ ɗ aɗi nnɛ u ki ̀ ki ɓiɓan , nsoo ̀ lɛ ghɛn yɛɛ faa wɔ ̀ ri ̀ kuu ɗi ite ̀ ɗ ɗin ̀ ?
Nni a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ girig n ̀ tɔg mi ̀ ni n ̀ tɔɔ ̀ tɔɔgh .
Kaliina mɛ ̀ , ba ̀ ɓtis i ̀ Zyaŋ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ y nya yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll gi ̀ n , a ɓum ?
Fɔɔnnɛ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ fiɓi ̀ gha ̀ n ̀ tɔɔ ̀ tɔɔgh win ̀ wɔɔ ɓɔ ri ̀ ɓɔ , ɓɛ kpaa lɛ : I ti ̀ ɓa ̀ agh nyi lɛ ba ̀ ɓtis i ̀ Zyaŋ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ y yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si ɓii ̀ tɔɔ ̀ gh lɛ , nni ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓi ̀ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi yɔ ̀ ?
I ti ̀ ɓa ̀ agh nyi lɛ , i ̀ ɓagha ̀ y a ɓum , ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ri ɓi ̀ si ɓii ̀ rogii gɔ ̀ g lɛ , ki gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ nɗem wu ̀ ce ̀ m lɛ , Zyaŋ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ɓaka ̀ nyi lɛ ɓɔɔ yii ɓi fe nnɛ ba ̀ ɓtis i ̀ Zyaŋ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ y .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ min ɓɔ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ girig , mɛ ̀ n ̀ kpaa ɓi mini ɓi-te ̀ ɗ aɗi nnɛ nki ̀ ki ɓiɓan ɓi .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , nni a ̀ teeti ̀ gha ̀ ɓum da ̀ ɗki ̀ lɛ , ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ yɛɛ sala ̀ dɛm i vii ̀ nyɛ ̀ , a ̀ foŋ yɔ ̀ ɓi rɛnti ̀ , a ̀ fa yɔ ̀ ri ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓɛɛ sasay mii ̀ , nyii kɛn ̀ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kidɛŋ a ̀ finɛ ̀ n yi ̀ wɔɔ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki mɛ ̀ saŋ ki kpaga ̀ , nni a ̀ romga ̀ y n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say adɛŋ a ɓumɓɛ a ̀ foga ̀ ɓi dɛm , lɛ ɓɛɛ rom ̀ nyi ga ̀ ɓ yi ̀ i ̀ i ɓyom . Ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ reɓsɛ ̀ nga ̀ dɛm ri ɓɔ , ɓɛ kula ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓɛ romga ̀ y a ̀ nɛn , ɓɛ pɛɛ ̀ zi ̀ nyi ri ̀ jɛ ̀ m ɓya ̀ g zɛy , yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛm .
Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛm a romdi ̀ gha ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say adɛŋ , ɓɛ kuuti ̀ nyi , ɓɛ ki sɛmgi nyi , ɓɛ pɛɛ ̀ zi ̀ ti ̀ nyi ri ̀ jɛ ̀ m ɓya ̀ g zɛy .
Ŋwaa ̀ dɛm a romdi ̀ ti ̀ i ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say ɓi gɛ ̀ n i ki ̀ raa ; ɓɛ ̀ sali ̀ ɓi dɛm ɓɛ kpɛɛghi ̀ ti ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say anɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ki na ̀ ɓ nyi .
Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛm a tɔka ̀ min lɛ : N ̀ ghay ɓa ̀ la ? N ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ romi ̀ man wɛm ̀ a ̀ n ̀ ɗem , ɓaa ̀ yi ɓi , nyi nnɛ ɓɛ ri nya ɓii ̀ risii .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ sali ̀ ɓi dɛm ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ y man a ̀ nɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ ghɛn ɓi ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗyaa lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓi ri dɛm inɛ yɛɛ ri lɛ , nni ti wolina nyi di dɛm yɛ ̀ ɛ woo ̀ ghrɛn ɗi ̀ ɓi ̀ si .
Nni ɓɛ kpaŋzi ̀ gha ̀ nyi ɓi dɛm , ɓɛ ki wey nyi . Ɓigomi ̀ nɛ ̀ n , cɛ kɛɛ ̀ ki ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓii ̀ ghali ̀ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ a ̀ fagha ̀ dɛm ri ɓɔ ?
Ŋwaa ̀ dɛm a ri ̀ ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u , a ̀ cuusi ̀ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ ki fa dɛm inɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ . Yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki woka ̀ ri ̀ kpaa ɗi Yeesus ɗin ̀ , ki kpaa lɛ : Kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa ɓaa ̀ fɔlɔɔ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ pɛɓsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ ri ̀ azi lɛ cɛ ? Gɔ ̀ g i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ̀ toŋi ̀ -mɛɛ ɓɛ maka ̀ , yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ti gɔ ̀ g i ̀ nɛ i ̀ le ̀ nlemi n ̀ tɔn a ̀ mɛɛ .
Nni mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ kpi ̀ i ɓi gɔ ̀ g i ̀ nɛn , a ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓumɓuni , fɔɔnnɛ gɔ ̀ g i ̀ nɛn i ̀ ɓii ̀ turii mum bimiɗ a ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ kpi ̀ i ɓi nyo ̀ o ̀ .
Ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓɛ kaaka ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ bee inɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓan ̀ nyi , ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kɔm ̀ kin ̀ , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛ risi ̀ gha ̀ ɓum ɓɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ lɛ , ɓɛ yigha ̀ lɛ ɓisu waa nnɛ Yeesus a ̀ teka ̀ da ̀ ɗki ̀ i ̀ nɛn .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ fifi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɗi Yeesus lɛ tintɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ŋ , ɓɛ ki rom yi nyi ɓum ɓɛ mɛwooghrag , ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ki lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ yuu ̀ nyi ki ̀ tɔɔ ̀ gh saaɗ a ̀ ki ̀ ɓan lɛ ɓɛɛ wog n ̀ ko ̀ o a ̀ nɛ ̀ si jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , di ɓɛɛ ɓan nyi , ɓɛɛ fa nyi ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ mi ̀ -ɓum , ri ̀ gɔmi ̀ na ̀ .
Nni ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ tɔka ̀ Yeesus n ̀ tɔɔ ̀ tɔɔgh lɛ : N ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ z ɓi ̀ sii yii lɔŋ lɛ , u ̀ ri ̀ roa ̀ nɛ a ki ̀ ki lɛ , a ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ saaɗ , a ̀ ki re ̀ resi ɓum saaɗ , kɛ ̀ ɛ fiɓi riɓa ɗi mum ; u ki re ̀ resi ɓum bee inɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi saaɗ .
Ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓis ɓi gherɛɛ nya lɛ ti pee ̀ ghi la ̀ mpoŋ ̀ ri ̀ Kaaza gi ̀ n , tyɛ ̀ ki peeghi ?
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Yeesus a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ ɓɛ purii nyi ca ̀ g ɓi ɗu ̀ m yɛɛri , nni a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ :
Re ̀ siina mɛ ̀ fi ̀ raŋ ̀ ; ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki ghɛn , ri ̀ ɗii ɗi ghɛn , ɓyɛɛ ri lɛ mii ̀ ? Ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓaa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Ɓi ri yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ , ri ̀ ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki Kaaza , ri ̀ ɗii ɗii ̀ .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ min ɓɔ lɛ : Pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ziina ɓyom ɓi Kaaza ri ̀ Kaaza , ɓi ̀ fa Bɛ ̀ ll ɓinki ̀ i ̀ .
Ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi lɛ ɓɛ wɔɔsi ̀ nyi ɓi ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓii ɓi a ̀ to ̀ to ̀ ka ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓum ɓɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ ; wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛ kuura ̀ ka ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɗi a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ , ɓɛ mam .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓi nɗaŋ wu Ɓɛ ̀ sa ̀ du ̀ syɛŋ ɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaaghi lɛ , ɓi ̀ loŋ ɓi yin lɛ ɓi ghemɓɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ yugha ̀ Yeesus a nyoo ɓɛ tɔg nyi lɛ :
N ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g , ki ̀ ɓan ki Moyis a ̀ ka ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ti kilag ki ri lɛ i ge ̀ ni mum a ̀ wii , a ̀ ca ̀ ɗ giɓ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ man , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ wɔli ̀ giɓ anɛ ̀ n , a ̀ yay ɓɔn ri ̀ nyi ɓisuu geni a ̀ nɛ a ̀ a ŋwii .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ri ̀ geni ɗyaa ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ; roa ̀ ntonto a ̀ wɛy giɓ , a ̀ ki wu di ɓɛ ka yin ɗi man .
Geni a ̀ ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , ri ̀ roa ̀ ki ̀ raa ɓɛ wɛy n ̀ kpɔɓ win ̀ .
Nni ki kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ fɔlɔɔ ɓi ki ̀ taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ɓum ; ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ cuu , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ca ̀ ri man .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m nnɛ giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ wugha ̀ girig .
Nni ŋwosi righe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓiloŋ giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓaa gɛ ɓa ̀ gili ghɛn anɛ ɓi ɓumɓɛ kitaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛn ̀ , yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yii ɓii ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓumɓɛ ɓi cɛɓ ki ti ̀ kaka mii ̀ ki , ɓɛ ti ɓɛ wɔla ̀ g ,
ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ki ghɛnɛɛ gɛ lɛ , ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ teri ̀ ga ̀ ɓ ɓi nyɔɔnyɔn a ̀ cɛɓ ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ ri ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓiloŋ , ɓaa wɔlɛn ti ɓi ,
ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki wu ti , lɛ ɓɛ ri ɓaa gɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛ titom , ɓɛ ki ɓa ɓɔn ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ , ɓɛ mɛ ghe ̀ mɓɛn yi a ɓi ̀ loŋ .
Ki ̀ ɓan ki righe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓiloŋ kɛɛ ̀ ki Moyis a ̀ ɓu ̀ ŋi ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ yɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa kitwi ̀ ɗ ki ki ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ɗo ̀ o ̀ wu ɗuu ; wɔɔ nnɛ a ̀ reŋii Kan lɛ : Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ Abiraham , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ Isag , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ Yakɔɓ .
Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ yin Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓi ̀ loŋ , a ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri cem , lɛ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ri cem lɛ nyi .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓaka ̀ nyi lɛ : N ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g , u ̀ konaagh ki ̀ kpaa ̀ .
Nni ɓɛ ghɛɛsi ̀ gha ̀ ti ̀ ɓi lɛ ɓɛɛ tɔg ti nyi n ̀ tɔɔ ̀ tɔɔgh .
Yeesus a ̀ tɔka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Lannɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ kpaa lɛ , Kiris a ̀ ri ̀ Man a ̀ Davit ?
Davit nyimiɗ a kalag ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ sam ̀ lɛ : Kan a ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ Kan wɛ ̀ m lɛ , kɔ ̀ ri mɛ ̀ fɛ ɓi wee ̀ lem ,
a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ ghaasii ɓɛ ̀ be ̀ na ̀ bena ɓɔɔ ki ̀ ɓoŋ ki u rɛsag mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ mii ̀ .
Nni i Davit a ̀ mɛ reŋi nyi lɛ Kan , lannɛ nyii ri lɛ a ̀ ɓa ti ̀ man wii ̀ ?
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ tuu ki ɓum ki wowo ̀ ka ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Yeesus a ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ , nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii lɛ :
Ɓi ̀ kona ̀ g ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ keesa ̀ g ri ̀ rere ̀ ni ̀ ɗi zi ri ɓyoo ɓɛ ̀ ka ̀ ɓa ̀ , ki kɔngi ̀ ɓɔ lɛ , ɓɛɛ too ̀ to ̀ gsi ̀ ɓɔ ri ̀ coo nnyaasɛ ̀ n ɓi gwi ̀ y , ɓɛ ki keesag mɛkɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ mɛ asu ɓi naa yi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ a ɓi ̀ sɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ .
Ɓɛ ti ɓɛ pumza ̀ g naa yi mɛkpɔɓ mɛ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ , di ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ɓyoo bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n lɛ , ɓum ɓɛɛ ghɛn ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ri ɓi ̀ syeesyee ɓi ɓum ; ɓɛ ɓii ̀ teri ̀ ri ̀ kuu ɗi pɔnɔsi ̀ ɗi ɗi tee ̀ sɛɛ lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ pi ̀ ka ̀ mis , nni a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ di ɓɛ ̀ guŋgum ɓɛɛ ̀ pi ̀ pig bɔgsi ̀ ɓi fi ̀ kɔrɔŋ fi ɓɛ m ̀ pi ̀ ki ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɛ bɔgsi ̀ mii ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ girig maa sogha ̀ sogha a n ̀ kpɔɓ wu giɓ di a pi ̀ pig ɓɔɔ tiraŋ ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ .
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa lɛ : N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ , maa nkpɔɓ a giɓ anɛ a ̀ pi ̀ igh bɔgsi ̀ a ̀ cee ɓum ɓɛm ̀ bog ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ɓisuulɛ ɓaa pi ̀ igh ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni i ̀ nɛ ya ̀ a yii ̀ di ɓɔ ri ̀ ki ̀ say , wɔ ̀ lɛ giɓ anɛ nyaa pi ̀ igh ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ com bimiɗ i ̀ nɛ a ̀ a ri ̀ ri ̀ yɔ ̀ , i ̀ nɛ a ̀ a ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ a ̀ ghɛɓ mii ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ lɛ naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ɗɛ ̀ ŋɛn ri ɓi ̀ syeesyee ɓi gɔ ̀ g , ri ̀ ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓum ɓɛ fafa ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , nni Yeesus a ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ lɛ :
Mɛ ̀ ru mɛdɛŋ mɛ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ mɛ ɓya ̀ a ghɛɛ ̀ di ɓi nsoo ̀ di gɔ ̀ g bog i ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ sasaghiyɛn ɓi i ̀ dɛŋ i ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓ lɛ ɓɛ ɓigtii ɓi yɔ ̀ , ɓi ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓi seesee ɓi .
Nni ɓɛ tɔka ̀ nyi lɛ : N ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g ! fin innɛ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki ɓii ̀ ki ̀ lɛɛ ? Ki ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ aɗi kɛɛ ri ɓii ̀ re ̀ sii lɛ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki ti ja ̀ ŋbog ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ lɛ ̀ n ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : Ɓi ̀ kona ̀ g lɛ mum kɛ ̀ ɛ ye ̀ gsi mini , ɓisuulɛ ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ ɓii ̀ yu ̀ yuu ri ɗii ɗyɛ ̀ m , ri ̀ a ̀ nɛn mii ̀ a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ri Kiris , ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ti ja ̀ ŋbog ; kɛ ̀ ɓi nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ɓɔ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ woo ̀ gh di ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa ɓiɓan ɓi mɛ ̀ y , ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓu ̀ u ̀ si ̀ ki ɓi ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ , kɛ ̀ ɓi risi , lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ loo ̀ gh ki ̀ re ̀ sɛɛ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog a ̀ a ri ̀ le ̀ g ɗi zi ɗyɛɛ ri lɔɔ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ .
Nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ min ɓɔ lɛ : Ki ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ lɛ , ɓumɓɛ ɓi tum a zi anɛ ɓɛ ram wɛ ̀ y ri ɓɛ ɓi tum a zi ambog , ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki ki ram wɛ ̀ y ri kim ̀ bog ;
ki ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ lɛ ri ̀ foo ri ̀ foo zi i nyɛ ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ n ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi tiroɓ ɓi ri ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ , ri ̀ za ̀ y , ɓɛ ̀ koŋnyoo ɓɛ ɓiɓan ri ̀ ɓyoo ɓife ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ɓi ɓii ̀ re ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ɗyoo .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ di ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ka ghɛnɛn ɓi , ɓɛ ri mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ ɓangii , ɓɛ ki mi ̀ ni mɛ ̀ tɔɓ ; ɓɛ ri mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ faa ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ rɛli ̀ -asu ɓɛ ɓi naa yi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓɛɛ yɔm ̀ mi ̀ ni , ɓɛ ki pi ̀ g mini ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y ; ɓɛ ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ri mi ̀ ni a ɓɛ ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ri ̀ a ɓɛ ̀ gɔmi ̀ na ̀ ɓisu wɛ ̀ m .
Fɔlɔɔ a ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ , ɓi lom ̀ ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ɓi ki ̀ ɓan kɛm ̀ .
Com ki ɓi foŋ ̀ ɓi n ̀ to ki ri lɛ , kɛ ̀ ɓi log ki fe ̀ feegh lannɛ ɓi ̀ ɓii ̀ yɔ ̀ mi ,
ɓisuulɛ mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ yɛɛ ri mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ faa ̀ n ̀ kpaa ̀ ri ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n , ɓi ɓi ri ɓii ̀ yaa ̀ gh ɓɛ ̀ be ̀ na ̀ bena ɓin , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ di ŋwɔm .
Nsoo ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yali ̀ ɓin , nsoo ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓin , nsoo ̀ boo yi ̀ n i mum , nsoo ̀ ɓɛ ̀ reŋka ̀ ŋ ɓin ɓɛ ri mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ ka ̀ ɓi , ɓɛ ki cuusi kigwey ki ɓi mi ̀ ni .
Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ri mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ ɓe ̀ e ̀ zɛɛ ɓisu wɛ ̀ m .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , nsoo ̀ fyo ̀ ŋ fi ɓi nto wu wa ̀ a ̀ dɛŋ fyaa ta ̀ ŋ ɓi .
Ki ̀ si ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ kin kɛɛ ri ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ ɓi ghɛɓsi ɓyɛɓ ɓin .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɛ di mɛ ̀ raŋ mɛ wɛ ̀ y maa kɔ ̀ mzɛn Yorisalɛm , ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ yii ̀ lɛ , Yorisalɛm a ̀ yu ̀ u ki ̀ wa ̀ a ̀ rɛɛ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ a Zyude , ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ghɛŋii , ɓi do ̀ n aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓi ba ̀ n ɓi ɗu ̀ m , ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ , ɓɛ ɓi dɛm , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɗiŋi ti ɓi ba ̀ n .
Ɓisuulɛ mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ̀ n mɛ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ mɛ ̀ ru mɛ rɔ ̀ ŋɗɔ ̀ ŋ , mɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓi ri ɓi ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ɓi ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ lɛɛ .
Nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛ mem , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gɛɓyɛ ̀ y ɓɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ̀ n , ɓisuulɛ nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g i ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ , fɔɔnnɛ bim inɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki ri ̀ yɔ ̀ i ̀ ri re ̀ sɛ ̀ n .
Ɓɛ ri ɓɔ ɓii ̀ cuusii ri ga ̀ fa ̀ g , ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓidɛŋ ɓi ɓangi ̀ ɓɔ ɓi ri ̀ kpa ̀ n , ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ sasa ̀ ɓ Yorisalɛm ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ , a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓum ɓɛ ̀ n ki ri ɓii ̀ le ̀ egh .
Ɓi ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ɓi ɓii ̀ re ̀ sɛɛ lɛ , ri ̀ ɓi ki ̀ saa ki ŋwos , ri ̀ ɓi ŋwii , ri ̀ ɓi tyɔɛy ; fɛ ɓi zi , coo-ris wu ri ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i ɓilɔ ̀ ŋ di ɓi woogh , ri ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɗi riɓa ̀ y a ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n , ri ̀ gom i ̀ ɓi ̀ kus .
