N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ , bɔ ̀ ɓ i ɓum i ̀ nɛ ya ̀ a le ̀ g ɓi bimiɗ di ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ka kilɛn ɓi .
Ɗyoo ri ̀ zi ɓi ri ɓii ̀ le ̀ egh , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓyɛm ̀ ɓyaa le ̀ g ɓi .
Ɓi ̀ kona ̀ g ri ̀ mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ , lɛ ɓi ̀ sɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ zɛ ̀ ŋ ɓi mɛrɔ ̀ g ri ̀ ri ̀ cɛɛ ̀ cɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɗi nɗem ɓyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ fa mɛrem min i ̀ ɓwɛɗ ; di ŋwos anɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri si ̀ ɗ mini n ̀ si ̀ rɛn .
Ɓisuulɛ ŋwos anɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓii ̀ si ̀ i ̀ dii ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓi ziinɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ dam i ̀ ti i ̀ si ̀ i ̀ da ̀ g ɓi ̀ zɛn .
Fɔɔnnɛ kɔ ̀ riina cem , ɓi ̀ ki ɓɔ ̀ ɔɓɔŋza ̀ g ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , lɛ ɓi ɓa ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ ɓi cee ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ri ɓii ̀ ki ̀ lɛɛ , ɓi ̀ ki kpaŋ ɓi mis mɛ Man a ̀ mum mɛ ̀ rɛy .
Yeesus a ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ŋwos a ̀ re ̀ e ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ i ̀ ru , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ lali ̀ ɓi do ̀ n i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ o ̀ li ̀ vyee .
Nni ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓɛ n ̀ ti ɓɛ kɛngi ̀ nyi a nyo ̀ o ̀ ri ̀ sariwa , lɛ ɓɛɛ wowog ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi a kaka ̀ li ̀ gha ̀ .
Ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ ti ɓɛ n ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g bi ̀ rɛs , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ foŋ nwi ̀ ɗ mii ̀ , tyɛɛ ̀ ti ɓɛɛ ̀ regi lɛ Paska ̀ , ti kɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ gha ̀ y .
Ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓɛ kaaka ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ bee inɛ ɓɛɛ wey Yeesus , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓɛ riri ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ɓum ɓɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ .
Sata ̀ n a ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi nɗem wu Zyudas a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ndegi ̀ lɛ Iskariyot , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Zyudas a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ wooghrɛɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m mɛ ɓɛsuja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛ m ̀ be ̀ gi ̀ naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓi-ghe ̀ y wu a fa ɓɔ Yeesus .
Ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ woka ̀ ki ̀ rɔɔ , ɓɛ kag ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ri nyi ɓii ̀ faa ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni .
Zyudas a ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ kaa ɗi kirɔŋiɗ ki lɛ a fa ɓɔ Yeesus yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ yi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwos a riki ̀ ɗi bi ̀ rɛs i ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ nwi ̀ ɗ , a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ woli ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ i ̀ Paska ̀ a ̀ kpaga ̀ ,
Yeesus a ̀ romga ̀ lɛ ri ̀ Pyɛɛri ri ̀ Zyaŋ a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Kɛ ̀ ɛna ɓi ̀ si ki ̀ pe ̀ gsɛɛ ɓiɗila ̀ g ɓi Paska ̀ .
Ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ tɔg nyi lɛ : Fe nnɛ u kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ ti pegsɛn ɓyɔ ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ yii ! Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ ɓii ̀ ɗiŋii ɓi ba ̀ n , ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ tuusɛɛ ri ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ ɗi a ̀ tɛ ̀ tɛɛgh be ̀ e ̀ i mɛ ̀ nig , nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ tiina nyi a mɛɛ mɛ a ̀ ri ̀ mii ̀ ɓii ̀ ɗiŋii ,
ɓi kpaa ̀ ŋwaa ̀ mɛɛ lɛ , n ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g lɛ : Ɓi ki ̀ den ki naa kibe nnɛ nyii ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɗii ̀ Paska ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ?
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ re ̀ sii coo kiden ki naa ɓi mɛɛ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ ki ̀ pe ̀ gsɛn . Wɔɔ nnɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ lami ̀ ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓi Paska ̀ .
Nni ɓɛ ̀ -Pyɛɛri ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ , ɓɛ tanɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ , ɓɛ ki lam ɓiɗila ̀ g ɓi Paska ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki riɗi ki kpaga ̀ , nni Yeesus a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓi zi nɗaŋ ri ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii lɛ ɓɛɛ ɗi .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ki mɓiisɛɛ mɛ ̀ ki ̀ kɔ ̀ ni lɛ , n ̀ ɗi Paska ̀ a ̀ nɛ n ̀ ɗaŋ ɗi mi ̀ ni di n ̀ ka wog ɓi rikɛŋ .
Lɛ ̀ , n ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni lɛ , ma ̀ a ɗi ti ɓi Paska ̀ a ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ azi anɛ mii ̀ a ̀ ki ̀ lɛɛ gɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll .
Nni a ̀ teka ̀ ɓeŋ a ̀ mɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ g a ̀ fa Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Terina ɓeŋ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ceesɛn nyi di ɓi sa ̀ sa ̀ g ;
lɛ , n ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni lɛ a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , ma ̀ a nɔti ɓi mɛrɔ ̀ g mɛ vii ̀ nyɛ ̀ a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll ki ri ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ teka ̀ bi ̀ rɛs , a ̀ fa Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ɓɛg yɔ ̀ , a ̀ fa ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Nyoo yɛ ̀ m yɛ ̀ ɛ ri lɛ ; yɛ ̀ ɛ ri n ̀ fayɛn ɓisu wi ̀ n , ki ̀ laaghna ki ̀ ɓan ki , ɓi ̀ yita ̀ g mɛ ̀ .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ a ̀ teka ̀ girig ɓeŋ , ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ ri ̀ ɗi , a ̀ fa ɓɔ a kpaa lɛ : Ɓeŋ a ̀ nɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ nyɔɔnyɔn a ̀ ri ̀ ra ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɗi lɛ , ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ ɓum , ɓi bwaɓ yɛm ̀ yi yi ɗyoŋi ɓisu wi ̀ n .
Nni ɓi ̀ ghɛɛ ! Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ a tɔ ̀ kɛɛ mɛ ̀ , a ɗiɗi fɛ n ̀ ɗaŋ ri mɛ ̀ .
Man a ̀ mum a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ wii ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fe ̀ ka ̀ lɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ wii ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g ri ̀ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ nyi ɓii ̀ ka ̀ ɓi .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ tɔɔ ̀ ghtɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n wɔɔ ɓɔ ri ̀ ɓɔ lɛ , ghɛn anɛ ɓi nɗaŋ waa yɛɛ ri ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i rikuu ɗi kiɓan yɛ ̀ ɛ ɗin ̀ ?
Nni ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ ɓigti ̀ gha ̀ ɓyoo nyoey lɛ ɓɛɛ yi ghɛn anɛ ɓi nɗaŋ waa nnɛ ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛm ̀ bog .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m mɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ mɛ ti mɛ lamɓa ̀ g ɓyɔ mɛ ciɓta ̀ g ; ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ tuturi ɓilɔ ̀ ŋ ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓin ̀ ɓi ti ɓi kpaaghi ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ɓɔ ki ̀ rɔɔ .
Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ki ɓaa ̀ fɔlɔɔ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n , wɔ ̀ lɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ n ̀ ɗɛli ̀ -asu ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ terɛɛ nyimi ̀ ɗ yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwɔɓti , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a la ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ , a ̀ ɓa yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kpa ̀ n a ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛm ̀ bog .
Ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔrii ɓi teɓe ̀ re ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ɗi ɗi ɓiɗila ̀ g ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ka ̀ a ̀ kaa nyi ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g , roa ̀ be yɛɛ cee roa ̀ mbog ? Mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ti nya lɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ɗiɗi yɛɛ cee ! Nni mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ min ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say !
Mi ̀ ni yɛɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ n ̀ si ̀ i ̀ rɛɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ nɔɔ ̀ ti mɛ ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn mɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ tuutu ̀ lɛ ̀ n ri ̀ mɔ .
