Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ tɔgti ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ ɓi gɛ ̀ n i ki ̀ raa lɛ : Ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki kiɓan aɗi kɛɛ ̀ ki ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki ̀ i ? Lɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ ghɛɛ ɓi kiɓan ki a ̀ ki ̀ i ki ki ri lɛ ɓɛ wey nyi mii ̀ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ tɔɔ ̀ gh lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓog nyi ɓi ki ̀ to ̀ n , fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ca ̀ ɗ min nyi .
