Mɛ ̀ ghan mɛ Yeesus mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛ ɓɛ kɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ nyi , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n a Galile , ɓɛ rɛli ̀ gha ̀ y fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ ɓɛ seese ̀ e ̀ com ki ki kii ̀ ki ̀ lɛ ̀ nga ̀ .
Ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ntaŋzɛn wu rila ̀ mi ̀ , wu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɗii lɛ Yoosɛɓ , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ syeesyee a ̀ n ̀ ɗem , a ̀ ki ɓa ŋwaa ̀ saaɗ .
