Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ lɔni ̀ ki ̀ loŋ ki Yeesus ri ̀ Pilat .
A ̀ kɔ ̀ si ̀ i ̀ kɔ ɓi kɔrɔs , a ̀ lɔki ̀ kɔ ri ̀ aloya ̀ , a ̀ nɔ ̀ ŋzi ̀ kɔ ɓi zɔ ̀ ŋ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ soɓɛn ɓi ri ̀ ɓan , i ̀ ki ɓa zɔ ̀ ŋ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɗi ɓɛ ka ɓom ̀ ɓi mum mii ̀ abɛ ̀ y .
