ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɔ ɗii lɛ Kileyopas ki ɓaa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Wɔ ̀ yɛɛ ri nya ki ̀ bog ki mum ki a Yorisalɛm , ki ki yii ɓi kiɓan ki ki nki ̀ lɛɛ wɔɔ ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ?
Yeesus a ̀ tɔg ɓɔ lɛ : Ki ̀ ɓan aɗi kɛɛ nki ̀ lɛɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ? Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ɓaka ̀ nyi lɛ : Ki ̀ ɓan ki ki nki ̀ i Yeesus a ̀ nɛ a Naazarɛt , a ̀ nɛ mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ mii ri ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓii , ɓi nɗe ̀ resii lɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ te ̀ ete ̀ ɗ ki n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ ɓi mis mɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ ki ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓis ɓɛgwey ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɓis ɓɛ nka ̀ ɓi nyi ri ̀ gɔmi ̀ na ̀ lɛ a ren ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ wey nyi , ɓɛ ki kpan nyi ɓi kɔrɔs .
Ɓi ̀ sii nti ri ̀ dya ̀ ɓɛn lɛ , nnyɛɛ ɓii ̀ ghɛɓsii Isirayɛl ; nni ri ̀ gɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan anɛ ̀ n bimiɗ , ɓɛ ̀ ŋwos ɓɛɛ ti lɛ ɓɛraa yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki nki ̀ lɛɛ .
Nni wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓi nɗaŋ wis ɓɛɛ ɓu ̀ u ̀ sii ɓi ̀ si lɛ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ ; lɛ ɓaa poni a zɔ ̀ ŋ sariwa lɛ ɓuɓ ,
ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ghɛn kiloŋ kii ɓi zɔ ̀ ŋ nni ɓaa yu ̀ u ɓi ̀ si ki ̀ kpaa ̀ lɛ ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓaa re ̀ sɛɛ yi ̀ ɓɔ , ɓɛ ki kpaa ɓɔ lɛ , Yeesus a ̀ ri ̀ cem .
Ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ tya ̀ a ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ ɓaa kɛ ̀ ɛ a zɔ ̀ ŋ , ɓɛ tanɛ ̀ n lɛ ki ri yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓaa kalii , ki ̀ ɓan kifog kɛ ̀ ɓɛɛ ̀ ghɛn Yeesus nyimiɗ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ min ɓɔ lɛ : Mi ̀ ni ɓum ɓɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ mɛ ̀ rem mɛ ti mɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ fyaŋzi ki gherɛɛ ɓiɓan ɓi ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ ,
ɓi ̀ yii ɓi lɛ Kiris a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ woo ̀ gh mɛ ̀ tɔɓ fɔlɔɔ ɓi ɗi lɛ a ɗiŋi ɓi ri ̀ kem ɗii ?
Nni a ̀ kona ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ ki ̀ re ̀ sii ɓiɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓi ɓagha ̀ ɓi ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ɓisu wi ̀ i ̀ , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓi ɓɛ ̀ kaa ̀ ta ̀ ɓɛ Moyis a ̀ kpaŋ ɓi ɓɛ ɓɛkpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kpaga ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛn ̀ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ nkɛni , Yeesus a ̀ ki ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ a kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ a kɛɛ ̀ di bee ̀ bɛ ̀ y .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ sii ̀ rɛ ̀ n nyi ri ̀ tɔtɔ ̀ g lɛ : Ti rɔɓ fɛ , ŋwos aa ma ̀ g ɓilɛ ̀ y , i ̀ ru wu ki yu ̀ u ki ̀ fini ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi naa lɛ a kɔri ri ̀ ɓɔ .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g n ̀ ɗaŋ ri ɓɔ , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ teka ̀ bi ̀ rɛs , a ̀ fa Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ɓɛg yɔ ̀ a ̀ fa ɓɔ .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ mis maa mɛ ŋwarɛ ̀ nga ̀ min , ɓɛ yiti ̀ nyi , ki ̀ ɓan kifog a ̀ sili ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ ɓi mis .
Nni ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛn ̀ ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ wɔɔ ɓɔ ri ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki a ̀ a to ̀ toogh ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si ɓi bee , a ̀ tɛɛ ̀ tɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ ɓi ̀ si ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ri ɓi ̀ ka ̀ nɛn , mɛ ̀ rem mis maa nyɛ ̀ ŋɗɛɛ ɓi mu ̀ m .
Nni ɓɛ ghaska ̀ ki ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ , ɓɛ sugti ̀ a Yorisalɛm , ɓɛ tanɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ ki n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ bog ɓɛ ̀ taŋzɛ ̀ n nɗaŋ ri ɓɛ ̀ reŋka ̀ ŋ ɓaa ,
di ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa lɛ , ki ri lɔŋ saaɗ lɛ Kan a ̀ a ghe ̀ mɓɛɛ , Simɔn a ̀ a ghɛɛ nyi ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɔɔ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ ki ̀ ɓan ki kaa ki ̀ i ɓɔ ɓi bee inɛ a Emayus , ri ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓaa re ̀ mii Yeesus di a ̀ mɛ ɓɛg bi ̀ rɛs .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ fɔlɔɔ , nni Yeesus nyimiɗ a gha ̀ ska ̀ ki ̀ rɛlii ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wa ̀ a ̀ a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Fyo ̀ oog a ɓa ri ̀ mi ̀ ni .
Nni ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ risi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ni ̀ i ̀ ghni ̀ ŋdɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓɛ fefe ̀ ka ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ghɛɛ n ̀ ghay .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog Yeesus a ̀ tɔka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɓu ̀ u ̀ sɛn , ɓi ̀ ki ɓa ti ri nywey ɓi nɗem ?
Ghɛɛna lɛ ri ̀ ɓya ̀ g ɓyɛm ̀ , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ mɛm ̀ , mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ yɛɛ ri lɛ , ko ̀ mina min mɛ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ghɛn ̀ lɛ , n ̀ ghay waa ̀ ɓa ɓi ri nyoo , nsoo ̀ ɓi ̀ woɓ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ɓyɔ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi seese ̀ e ̀ .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ fɔlɔɔ , nni a ̀ re ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ ri ̀ ɓya ̀ g ɓii ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ mii .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ di ɓɛ ka gherɛn ɓi , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓɛ wowo ̀ g ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ , ɓɛ ki kuurag lɛɛ ̀ gwey , Yeesus a ̀ tɔka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ yin fɛ ri ̀ com ki ɗiyɛn ?
Nni ɓɛ fagha ̀ nyi ki ̀ den ki kizɛn ki tɔ ̀ nɛn .
Yeesus a ̀ teɗ ki ̀ zɛn ki ̀ n a ̀ ɗi kɔ ɓi mis maa .
Nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ ghɛɛ ki ̀ ɓan ki n ̀ kpaagha ̀ mi ̀ ni di n ̀ kaka ri ̀ mi ̀ ni lɛ : Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓi ri ɓi ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ɓisu wɛ ̀ m ɓi ɓɛ ̀ kaa ̀ ta ̀ ɓɛ Moyis ri ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛkpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan , ri ̀ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ sam ɓyɛɛ kilɛn ?
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ nɛmga ̀ min ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗyaa , lɛ ɓɛɛ wog ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ri ɓi ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
A ̀ ki kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : Kiris a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ woo ̀ gh ri ̀ kɛŋ , a ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n a ɓi ̀ loŋ ɓi ŋwos a ki ̀ raa .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n a Yorisalɛm , a ̀ kpaŋ ɓi ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ kpaakpaa kiɓan ki lɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛn mɛ ̀ rem di Bɛ ̀ ll a cenɛn ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓyaa ɓi ɗii ɗi ̀ i ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛ ɓi ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ romi ̀ i ̀ com ki Ta ̀ a ̀ ta wɛ ̀ m a ̀ ka ̀ ka ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓi ̀ ka ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓi ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛ a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ i teri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu wu rii ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
Yeesus a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ Bɛtanii , a ̀ na ̀ m ɓya ̀ g , a ̀ ma ̀ ŋ ɓɔ .
Nni ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki a ̀ ma ̀ ŋma ̀ ŋga ̀ ɓɔ ki ̀ n , kɛɛ ̀ ki a ̀ ghasɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ , a ̀ ɓɔg aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
Ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ mɛ kemzi nyi , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ sugti ̀ gha ̀ a Yorisalɛm di ɓɛɛ ̀ wowog kinya ̀ a ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ lɔŋ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , ɓɛ fafa ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ kem .
A ri ̀ tumɛ ̀ n , Jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ , nni Jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛɛ ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , Jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ ki ɓagha ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
I ɓagha ̀ ɓɛɛ ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ri ̀ tumɛ ̀ n .
Jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ kigha ̀ ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , nni ɓi ɓyom ɓi ɓi kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ , kidɛŋ ki kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ .
Cɛɓ ki ɓagha ̀ ɓi Jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛn , cɛɓ ki ̀ n ki ki fafa ɓum ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn .
Ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ki lomlo ̀ m ɓi biri ̀ m , biri ̀ m yɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki teɗ kɔ .
Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ romga ̀ y ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ ɗii lɛ Zyaŋ .
Nnyɛɛ yugha ̀ y fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ a ̀ ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn lɛ di ɓum ɓɛɛ gherɛn lɛ ri ̀ kpaa ɗii .
Nyii ɓagha ̀ ɓi kitɛɛtɛn , ki ̀ ɓan kifog a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ y lɛ a kpaa ̀ ɓum ki ̀ ɓan ki kitɛɛtɛn .
Jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛn i ̀ ɓagha ̀ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn , ki ki yugha ̀ ɓi ziinɛ lɛ kɛɛ kpeŋzi ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ziinɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ki ̀ gha ̀ ziinɛ , wɔ ̀ lɛ ziinɛ i ̀ yiti ̀ gha ̀ ɓi yɔ ̀ .
I ̀ yugha ̀ a ɓum ɓii , ɓum ɓii ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki gha ̀ ɓ yɔ ̀ ;
wɔ ̀ lɛ i ̀ fagha ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ghaɓka ̀ kɔ , ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ n ɗii ɗi yɔ ̀ , i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ ɓɛɛ ɓa ɓɔn ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ghala ̀ ɓi ɓɔn ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ nyoo i ̀ mɛ ̀ mu ̀ u ̀ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɔn ɓɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ ̀ yala ̀ g , lɔŋ Bɛ ̀ ll yɛɛ fagha ̀ ɓɔ cɛɓ ki nyɔn .
Fɔɔnnɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ ghala ̀ mum a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghɛɓka ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ s , n ̀ ɗonɛn , ri ̀ geesɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ saaɗ , ti ̀ ki ghɛnga ̀ ri ̀ kem ɗii , ri ̀ kem ɗi ̀ n ɗi ki ɓa ɗi mbobog a ̀ Man a ̀ nɛ a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ y yɛ ̀ ɛ Seŋi ̀ .
Zyaŋ a ̀ rɛli ̀ gha ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ki ̀ ɓan kii , a ̀ la ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n lɛ : Nnyɛɛ ri ŋwaa ̀ nɛ n ̀ kpaagha ̀ mi ̀ ni lɛ : Roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ mɛ ̀ ajɛ ̀ m , a ̀ loka ̀ y ri ̀ mɛ ̀ , ɓisuulɛ nyii ɓagha ̀ di mɛ ̀ n ̀ ka yin .
Ɓi ̀ sii ̀ ce ̀ m ti ̀ mɛ teɗ ɓɛma ̀ a ̀ gh ɓɛ ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ɗii ɗi a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ɗonɛn , a ̀ saa ̀ sa ̀ gta ̀ g ɓi ̀ si geesɛ ̀ n .
Ɓisuulɛ , ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi falɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ Moyis , geesɛ ̀ n ri ̀ saaɗ ɓi yuiy ri ̀ Yeesus Kiris .
Mum a ̀ ka ghɛnga ̀ ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll , lɔŋ m ̀ bobog a ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ Seŋi yɛɛ kigha ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ yi nyi .
Fɛlɛ nnɛ Zyaŋ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ a Yorisalɛm ɓɛ romga ̀ y ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ levi ̀ t lɛ ɓɛɛ tɔg nyi lɛ : Wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ri ̀ ghɛn ?
A ̀ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ pwa ̀ a ̀ , a ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yin Kiris .
Nni ɓɛ tɔka ̀ nyi lɛ : Wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ri ̀ min ghɛn ? Wɔ ̀ yɛɛ ri Eli gi ̀ n ? Zyaŋ a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : E ̀ e e ̀ e . U ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan anɛ ̀ n ? Zyaŋ lɛ : A ̀ g .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ tɔka ̀ nyi lɛ : Wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ki ri ̀ min ghɛn ? Ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ sugtii ki kpaa ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓaa romii ̀ ɓi ̀ si ri ̀ ɓa ̀ g . Wɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ kali ɓi ̀ si ! Wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ri ̀ ghɛn ?
Nni Zyaŋ a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ roa ̀ nɛ a la ̀ alam ̀ ɓɛ ̀ n ɓi-reɓ lɛ pe ̀ gsɛɛna bee i ̀ Kan , lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan Ezayii a ̀ kpaagha ̀ .
Ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ romga ̀ y ɓɛn ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Zyaŋ , ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ .
Nni ɓɛ tɔgti ̀ gha ̀ nyi lɛ : I wɔ ̀ ki yin Kiris , nsoo ̀ lɛ Eli , nsoo ̀ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan , ɓisuucɛ nnɛ u ɓa ̀ aɓaɓti ̀ ɓum ? Zyaŋ a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ :
Mɛ ̀ ɛ mɓa ̀ aɓaɓti ̀ ɓum ri ̀ mɛ ̀ nig , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ ri ̀ foo ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n , a ̀ nɛ ɓi ̀ yii ɓi ; nyi yɛɛ rii ̀ mɛ ̀ ajɛ ̀ m .
Mɛ ̀ n ̀ wuɓsɛɛ gi ̀ ɓi nkoŋ wulɛ n ̀ fu ̀ mi ̀ n ̀ ɗig wii wu go ̀ o ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Bɛtanii , cɛcɛɗ ki Zyuridɛŋ , ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ Zyaŋ a ̀ ɓa ̀ a ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓti ̀ gha ̀ ɓum .
Ɓi duri tana , Zyaŋ a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ di Yeesus a ̀ tii ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkii , a ̀ kpaa lɛ man a ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a pipisi kiɓe ki ɓum ɓi ziinɛ yɛɛ ri lɛ .
Nnyɛɛ ri roa ̀ nɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kpaa lɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ mɛ ̀ ajɛ ̀ m , a ̀ loka ̀ y mɛ ̀ bee ̀ bɛ ̀ y , ɓisuulɛ nyii ɓagha ̀ di mɛ ̀ n ̀ ka yin .
Mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yigha ̀ ɓi nyi , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , n ̀ -yu ̀ gha ̀ y lɛ mɓaɓti ɓum ri ̀ mɛ ̀ nig , lɛ di Isirayɛl a ̀ a yii nyi .
Zyaŋ a ̀ kpaati ̀ gha ̀ lɛ n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ di N ̀ ghay a sɛnsɛn yi aɗyoo yɛ ̀ ɛ kuu ̀ kuu ̀ , a ̀ yu ̀ nyi ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ lii ɓi nyo ̀ o ̀ .
Mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yigha ̀ ɓi nyi , wɔ ̀ lɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ romga ̀ y mɛ ̀ lɛ mɓa ̀ a ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓti ̀ ɓum ri ̀ mɛ ̀ nig , a ̀ kpaagha ̀ mɛ ̀ lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ di N ̀ ghay a ̀ sɛnii ̀ , ɓi nyoo a ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓ ɓi nyi , roa ̀ nɛ ̀ n yɛɛ ɓii ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓtii ɓum ri ̀ Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay .
Mɛ ̀ n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ kpaagha ̀ mii ̀ lɛ , nnyɛɛ ri Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ɓi duri tana , Zyaŋ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ kaka wɔɔ ri ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ di Yeesus a ghagha ̀ a ̀ gh , nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Man a ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll innɛ .
Ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kii ki ɓɛyila ̀ g ki woka ̀ com ki a ̀ kpaagha ̀ , ki ki nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti Yeesus .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ y , a ̀ ghɛn lɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔnɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ i ̀ nyi , nni a ̀ tɔka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Cɛ ɓi kaaka ̀ a ̀ ? Ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kpaa nyi lɛ : Raɓi ̀ , yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ n ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g , fennɛ u ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔrii ?
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Yu ̀ unay , di ɓi ghɛn ̀ . Nni ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ga ̀ ɓɛ ghɛn ja ̀ ŋ inɛ a ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ , ɓɛ ratɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ghagsii ŋwos anɛ ̀ n ri nyi , ki ɓagha ̀ nunu ̀ g mɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛnin a ̀ ŋwos nkɛ ̀ nɛn .
Andire a ̀ geni Simɔn Pyɛɛri a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓum ɓɛ kiɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛ woka ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki Zyaŋ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ , ɓɛ nɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ Yeesus .
Andire a ̀ nɛn a ̀ loka ̀ ki ̀ tanɛɛ ri Simɔn a ̀ geni , a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Tya ̀ a ghɛɛ Me ̀ sii , yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ Kiris .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ syo ̀ ga ̀ Simɔn yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus . Yeesus a ̀ fiɓi ̀ nyi a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Simɔn , man a ̀ Zyonas ɓɛ ri wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ reŋɗaagh lɛ Sefas , yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ Pyɛɛri .
Ɓi duri tana Yeesus a ̀ ɓeka ̀ lɛ a kɛn ̀ a Galile , nni a ̀ tanɛ ̀ nga ̀ Filiɓ a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti mɛ ̀ .
Filiɓ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a Bɛdsayida , ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ -Andire ɓɛɛ ̀ Pyɛɛri .
Fɔɔnnɛ Filiɓ a ̀ tuusɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ Natanayɛl , a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Tya ̀ a ghɛɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ki ̀ ɓan kii ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Moyis ri ̀ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ kaa ̀ ta ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛkpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan , nnyɛɛ ri Yeesus a ̀ man a ̀ Yoosɛɓ a ̀ nɛ a Naazarɛt .
Nni Natanayɛl a ̀ kpaagha ̀ Filiɓ lɛ : Cɛ ki cem kɛɛ ri lɛ ki kpaŋ yi ̀ a Naazarɛt ? Fɔɔnnɛ Filiɓ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : Yuiy u ghɛn ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ di Natanayɛl a yu ̀ yuiy nyi a nyoo nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Natanayɛl a ̀ ri ̀ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ muu Isirayɛl a ̀ nɛ a ̀ yin ɗi mɛ ̀ ɗyɔg .
Nni Natanayɛl a ̀ tɔka ̀ Yeesus lɛ : Wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yii mɛ ̀ fe ? Yeesus a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ nyi lɛ : Ma ̀ a ghɛɛ wɔ ̀ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki wa ̀ a ri ̀ a nɗye ̀ m wu fi ̀ gyee zi , di Filiɓ a ̀ ka reŋii ɓi wɔ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Natanayɛl a ̀ kpaagha ̀ min Yeesus lɛ : Raɓi ̀ , u ̀ ri ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , u ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi Isirayɛl .
Yeesus a ̀ ba ̀ g nyi lɛ : Yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kalii wɔ ̀ lɛ ma ̀ a ghɛɛ wɔ ̀ a nɗye ̀ m wu fi ̀ gyee zi , nnɛ u ̀ gherɛɛ , u ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ghɛɛ ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓidɛŋ ɓi ɓi teghɛɛ ɓi cee fɔlɔɔ .
N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ kpaa lɛ , ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ di ɗyoo ɗi nɛmɓɛɛ , ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛ ɓɔɓɔ ̀ g ɓɛ sɛnsɛ ̀ n Man a ̀ mum a nto .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru mɛraa , ki ̀ sɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ ki riwɛy ki ɓagha ̀ a Kana , ɓi zi i ̀ Galile , jɛɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ .
Ɓɛ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ girig Yeesus ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii a ki ̀ sɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ kin ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ g mɛ leka ̀ , nni jɛɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : Ɓɛ yii ̀ di ri mɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ g .
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Giɓ anɛ , cɛ kɛɛ ri lɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ ? Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kɛm ̀ ki ka kpaŋ ɓi .
Jɛɛ a ̀ kpaa ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say lɛ : Ki ̀ ina com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki a ̀ ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ kalii .
Be ̀ e ̀ yi mɛnig yi yi ɓagha ̀ yi ̀ ye ̀ ŋɛn ɗi gɔ ̀ g , yi ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ taa ̀ fog ; be ̀ e ̀ yin ̀ yi ɓagha ̀ foo lɛ , yɛɛ ghɛɓsi ɓisuu ɓisyɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓi ritɛn ɓi ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ; bog i ̀ ɓagha ̀ lɛ i ̀ kpaŋ ɓɛ ̀ kpɛm ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓɛraa .
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Roo ̀ ziina mɛ ̀ nig ɓi be ̀ e ̀ yi , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ roo ̀ za ̀ ka ̀ mɛ ̀ nig mii ̀ , lɛ pisa .
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓɔ ̀ rina min mɔ , ɓi kɛn ̀ ki ̀ faa ̀ n ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ si ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi kisɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ nyi ri ̀ mɔ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ si ̀ -ki ̀ sɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ a ̀ ɓoɓti ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ nig mɛ mɛ ɓagha ̀ mɛn ̀ di maa ghay mɛrɔ ̀ g , kɛ ̀ ɛ yi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ mɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ g mɛn ̀ mɛ ɓaa yi ̀ , kɔm ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓwɛɗka ̀ y mɛ ̀ nig ɓɔɔ yigha ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ wɔlɛ ̀ nga ̀ a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛɛ ̀ loki ki ̀ faa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ke ̀ n mɛrɔ ̀ g mɛ syeesyee , ɓɛ siitɛ ̀ n ɓɔ ki ̀ faa ̀ mɛ ɓeɓtɛn di ɓaa ŋwagi ̀ ; ki ̀ ɓan kifog wɔ ̀ wa ̀ a ɓe ̀ ŋɓeŋi mɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ g mɛ syeesyee a ̀ kpaŋ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ Yeesus a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ da ̀ m yi ̀ i ̀ i n ̀ tonto a Kana , ɓi zi i ̀ Galile , a ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ri ̀ gwey ɗii , ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛ ki gherɛn nyi .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , nnɛ a ̀ sɛnga ̀ a Kapɛrinawum n ̀ ɗaŋ ri jɛɛ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii , ɓɛ ghagsi ̀ lɔŋ ɓɔɔ mɛru wɔɔ lɛsa ̀ g .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ ti Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ti lɛ Paska ̀ ti kɛɛkɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ gha ̀ y , nni Yeesus a ̀ ɓɔka ̀ a Yorisalɛm .
A ̀ tanɛ ̀ n di ɓɛ ri ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ka ̀ ɓi ̀ sani ̀ nya , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ka ̀ ɓi ̀ bwiy , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ka ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kuu ̀ kuu ̀ , ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ceecen ̀ ɗi ̀ yɛ ̀ n ɓum mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ki ̀ lɛ ̀ nga ̀ n ̀ kpas ri ̀ ɓi ̀ sɔŋ , nni a ̀ na ̀ ɓka ̀ ɓɔ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ na ̀ ɓki ̀ girig lɛ ri ̀ bwiy yaa , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sani ̀ nya ɓaa ; a ̀ tya ̀ ŋzi ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ cee ̀ ce ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ gha ̀ ɓum mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni , a ̀ tyɔki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ teɓe ̀ re ̀ ɓaa ;
a ̀ ki kpaa ɓɛ ̀ ka ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kuu ̀ kuu ̀ lɛ : Pisiina ɓyom ɓi fɛ ! Kɛ ̀ ɓi ghaasi naa i ̀ Seŋi wɛ ̀ m mɛɛ mɛ fye ̀ e ̀ .
Nni Ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛ yiti ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : N ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ naa yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ a ̀ ɓuni mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗem .
Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ teka ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ tɔg nyi lɛ : Da ̀ m i ̀ be yɛɛ ̀ nɛ u ̀ ri ̀ lɛ u ̀ ki ̀ , lɛ u resi ɓi ̀ si lɛ , u ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ u ki yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ ki ̀ i yi ̀ lɔɔ ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : Wa ̀ a ̀ ghiina na-Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛ mpɛɛ ̀ zi yɔ ̀ ki toŋi ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛraa .
Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ pɛɛ ̀ zi ̀ nyi lɛ : Naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ toga ̀ be ̀ g mɛ ̀ tin mɛɓɛɛ ̀ ri ̀ be ̀ g taa ̀ fog , yɛɛ ̀ nɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zii kitoŋi ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛraa ?
Wɔ ̀ lɛ naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛ Yeesus a ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ , i ̀ ɓagha ̀ nyoo yi ̀ i ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ nga ̀ y a nyɔ ̀ ɛ ̀ y , ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛ yiti ̀ lɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ fɔlɔɔ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ri ɓi ̀ ka ̀ nɛn , ɓɛ ki gherɛn ti ki ̀ ɓan ki Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ kin ̀ .
Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki Yeesus a ̀ ɓagha ̀ a ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ ti a Paska ̀ Yorisalɛm , ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi , yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ da ̀ m yi ɓiɓan yi a ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Yeesus a ̀ tyweeya ̀ ka ̀ ɓi ɓɔ ɓisuulɛ , a ̀ yigha ̀ ɓɔ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ,
ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ , ki ghɛɓsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi nyi com lɛ ɓɛɛ ka re ̀ si nyi ri ̀ ɓa ɗi mum , lɛ nyimiɗ a yigha ̀ com ki mum a fe ̀ feg ɓi n ̀ ɗem ɓi ɗu ̀ m .
Nni ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ ɓi nɗaŋ wu Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɗii lɛ Nikodɛm , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɛ ̀ lem ɓɛ ɓum ɓɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ,
a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus ri ̀ i ̀ ru a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Raɓi ̀ , ti ̀ yii lɛ , u ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g a ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll yɛɛ romii ̀ ɓisuulɛ , ŋwaa ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ ki ̀ da ̀ m yi ɓiɓan yɛ ̀ ɛ yi wɔ ̀ ɔ ki ̀ ki yi , di Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ yin a lɔ ̀ ŋkii .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ nyi lɛ : N ̀ kpaa wɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ kpaa lɛ , i mum a ̀ yalɛɛ ti ̀ ɓi nyɔɔnyɔn a ̀ ri ̀ yalɛ ̀ n , a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ ghɛn ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll .
Fɔɔnnɛ Nikodɛm a ̀ tɔka ̀ nyi lɛ : Lannɛ mum a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ yalɛ ̀ nti ̀ di a ̀ ti n ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ? A ̀ ri ̀ nya lɛ a ̀ sugti ̀ ɓi ɗu ̀ m ɗi jɛɛ a ̀ yalɛ ̀ nti ̀ ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : N ̀ kpaa wɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ kpaa lɛ , i mum a ̀ yalɛɛ ɓi ri mɛ ̀ nig ri ̀ N ̀ ghay , a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll .
Lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yalɛɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ mu ̀ u ̀ , a ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ mum a ̀ mɛ ̀ mu ̀ u ̀ , roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yalɛɛ ri ̀ N ̀ ghay a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ghay .
Fɔɔnnɛ kɔ ̀ ɔ kuurag lɛ ma ̀ a kpaa wɔ ̀ lɛ , ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ ɓi ɓii ̀ ti ki ̀ yalɛɛ .
Bɛ ̀ ɓ i ̀ ti i ̀ fɛɓsag ja ̀ ŋ inɛ i ̀ kɔni , wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wowo ̀ g lɔŋ lɛ ri ̀ fiŋfi ̀ ŋ kɔ ̀ ɔ yi fennɛ i ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ yi ̀ , nsoo ̀ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ yɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ nkɛ ̀ n . Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ mɛ yalɛn ri N ̀ ghay a ̀ ri ̀ .
Nni Nikodɛm a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ nyi lɛ : Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki ri lɛ ki kilɛ ̀ n di ki ɓaɓaa la ̀ ?
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Wɔ ̀ lɔŋ nɗe ̀ sa ̀ g a ̀ nɛ a Isirayɛl , kɔ ̀ ɔ ki yi ɓiɓan ɓi ?
N ̀ kpaa wɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ kpaa lɛ , ɓi ̀ sii ̀ kpaakpaa ɓiɓan ɓi ti ̀ yii , ti ̀ ki tɛɛtɛɛ ̀ zi ̀ ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ti ̀ ghɛnga ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog kɛ ̀ ɓi kɔ ̀ n lɛ di ɓya ̀ a teri ri ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ɗis .
I ɓi ̀ ti kɛ ̀ ɓi gherɛn di n ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ziinɛ , lannɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ min ɓii ̀ gherɛɛ di n ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi aɗyo ̀ o ̀ ?
Ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ ka ɓɔka ̀ ɓi aɗyo ̀ o ̀ i ki cee ɓi lɛ Man a ̀ mum a ̀ nɛ a ̀ sɛnga ̀ y aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
Fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Moyis a ̀ pɛ ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ nyoo ɓi ki ̀ geŋ aɗyoo ɓi-reɓ , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ girig lɛ , ɓɛɛ pɛsi Man a ̀ mum aɗyoo ,
lɛ di mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ gherɛɛ nyi , a ̀ ɓa ri ̀ cɛɓ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ keesi ̀ gha ̀ ziinɛ a ̀ pya ̀ ŋda ̀ g fɔlɔɔ nnɛ a ̀ fagha ̀ m ̀ bobog wi ̀ i ̀ a Man lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ gherɛɛ nyi kɛ ̀ ɛ wu , a ɓa lɔŋ ri cɛɓ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ romga ̀ y ɓi Man wii ̀ ɓi ziinɛ lɛ a fa yɔ ̀ bɛ ̀ lɛn , a ̀ romga ̀ y lɔŋ nyi lɛ a ghɛɓsi yɔ ̀ .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ gherɛɛ nyi a ̀ yii ̀ di ri bɛ ̀ lɛn wɔ ̀ lɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ gherɛɛ ɓi nyi yɛɛ ti ri ̀ bɛ ̀ lɛn ɓisuulɛ , a ̀ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi mbobog a ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Bɛ ̀ lɛn i ri ̀ n ̀ to lɛ : Ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ki yugha ̀ y ɓi ziinɛ , ɓum ɓɛ ki keesi biri ̀ m a ̀ cee ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ki ̀ n , lɛ mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ maa mɛ ɓagha ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓeɓtɛn .
Lɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ki ̀ ki kiɓe , a ̀ ti a ̀ ɓe ̀ e ̀ za ̀ g ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn , kɛ ̀ ɛ ki yu ̀ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ki ri , lɛ i ̀ ris wulɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓii ɓyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki kpagi dan .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi saaɗ , nnyɛɛ ti a ̀ yu ̀ la ̀ g ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ki ri , lɛ ɓɛɛ ghɛn ̀ lɛ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n lɛ , a ki ̀ ki ɓiɓan yɛ ̀ ɛ kɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ngi Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , Yeesus a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓi zii ̀ Zyude ; a ̀ ghagsi ̀ gha ̀ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n wɔɔ ri ɓɔ , a ̀ ki ɓa ̀ aɓaɓti ̀ ɓum .
Zyaŋ girig a ̀ ɓa ̀ a ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓti ̀ gha ̀ ɓum a Enɔŋ , ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ Salim lɛ mɛ ̀ nig mɛ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ lɛɛ ̀ gwey . Nni ɓum ɓɛ kɛnkɛ ̀ nga ̀ wɔɔ lɛ a ɓaɓti ɓɔ .
Lɛ ki ɓagha ̀ di ɓɛ ka pig ɓi Zyaŋ ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y .
Nni nyoey yi kpigha ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ Zyaŋ , ri ̀ muu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki ritɛn , ɓi ɓi ̀ syɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓi righerɛ ̀ n ɗi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Zyaŋ ɓɛ kpaa nyi lɛ : Raɓi ̀ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓi ̀ i nɗi ̀ ri ̀ nyi cɛcɛɗ ki Zyuridɛŋ , a ̀ nɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ ntɛɛzsii ɓi ̀ si ri ̀ ɓa ɗii , a ̀ ti girig ɓii ̀ ɓa ̀ aɓaɓti ̀ ɓum , fɔɔnnɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛɛ ̀ su ̀ usuu ̀ rɛ ̀ n a lɔ ̀ ŋkii .
Nni Zyaŋ a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Mum a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ ɓa ri ̀ com kidɛŋ , ki ki yin ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ faa nyi .
Mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ lɛ , n ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ , a ̀ a mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ri Kiris , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ɓɛ romga ̀ y mɛ ̀ lɛ nsyoŋ ̀ yi ̀ nyi bee .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ giɓ , yɛɛ ri yii giɓ ; wɔ ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ghan ɗi yii giɓ ɗi ɗi ri wɔɔ ɗi ti ɗi nyaa ̀ ra ̀ g yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ , lɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ yii giɓ inɛ ɗyɛɛ ̀ wowo ̀ g . Ri ̀ kuu ɗi kinya ̀ a ̀ ɗin ̀ ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ n ̀ ɗonɛn ri ɗyɔ ̀ .
Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ nyii ɓɔɓɔg , mɛ ̀ nsisi ̀ li ̀ .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ yi ̀ aɗyoo , a ̀ teŋmɛɛ a ̀ cee ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ; roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ yi ̀ ɓi ziinɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓi ziinɛ , fɔɔnnɛ a ki kpaakpaa ɓiɓan ɓi ɓi ziinɛ . Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ yi ̀ a ɗyoo ,
ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ri ̀ ɓi a ̀ woka ̀ ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓi a re ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ; nni mum a ̀ ki teri ɓi rire ̀ si ̀ ɗii ɗin ̀ .
I mum a ̀ ki teri ri ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ɗii , di a ̀ gherɛɛ yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ti a ̀ kpaaghi ̀ saaɗ .
Ɓisuulɛ , roa ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ romga ̀ y , a kakali ɓiɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ; lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ti a ̀ roo ̀ za ̀ g nyi ri ̀ Nghay wi ̀ i ̀ lɛ pisa .
Seŋi a ̀ keesii Man , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ fagha ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓya ̀ g ɓii .
Nni mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ gherɛɛ Man , a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ cɛɓ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ; ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ woogh ɓi nyi , a ̀ a ghɛn ɓi cɛɓ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ri ̀ baŋi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ɗi kaka nyi ɓi nyo ̀ o ̀ .
Yeesus a ̀ woka ̀ lɛ ɓɛ nkalii Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ lɛ nyii ̀ syo ̀ ŋsyoŋ ɓum a ̀ cee Zyaŋ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓa ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii , a ̀ ki ɓa ̀ aɓaɓti ̀ ɓɔ ;
wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi saaɗ a ̀ ri ̀ kpaa , Yeesus nyimiɗ a ɓa ̀ a ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓti ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ɓum , lɔŋ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛɛ ɓa ̀ a ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓti ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Zyude a ̀ sugti ̀ a Galile .
Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ , a fyee ̀ a Samari .
Nni a ̀ kpaga ̀ ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ dɛŋ i ̀ nɛ a Samari ɗii lɛ Sikar , ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ dɛm inɛ Yakɔɓ a ̀ fagha ̀ man wii ̀ a ̀ nɛ lɛ Yoosɛɓ .
Ki ̀ ɗig ki Yakɔɓ ki ɓagha ̀ ɓi dɛm inɛ ̀ n ; Yeesus a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓi nwɔŋi ̀ wu kiɗig kin ̀ , di a ̀ mɛ fɔy rikɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ; ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ nunu ̀ g toroɓ .
Fɔɔnnɛ giɓ anɛ a Samari a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ roo ̀ gh mɛ ̀ nig , Yeesus a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Faa mɛ ̀ mɛ ̀ nig mɛ nɔyɛn .
Lɛ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ ghii ̀ ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓi ba ̀ n .
Nni giɓ anɛ a Samari a ̀ nɛn a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ nyi lɛ : Lannɛ wɔ ̀ muu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , u ̀ lɔni mɛ ̀ mɛ ̀ nig mɛ nɔyɛn , kɔm ̀ lɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ giɓ anɛ a Samari ? Lɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi lɛ ɓɛ wooghrɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ ɓumɓɛ a Samari .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ giɓ anɛ ̀ n lɛ : I wa ̀ a yii ri ̀ fa ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , u ̀ ki yi roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ lɔni wɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ nig mɛ nɔyɛn , di wɔ ̀ yaa ri ̀ lɛ , u ̀ lɔn nyi mɛ ̀ nig mɛ noyɛn , di a ̀ a ki faa wɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ nig mɛ cɛɓ .
Nni giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : Kan , wɛ ̀ ɛnɛ ̀ n kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ com ki lɛ u ̀ rog mɛ ̀ nig mii ̀ , ki ̀ ɗig ki ki ri ̀ ki ̀ rimɛn , nni mɛ ̀ nig mɛ cɛɓ mɛ ri wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ yi ̀ fe ?
U fe ̀ feg lɛ wɔ ̀ yɛɛ cee seŋi wi ̀ s a n ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ anɛ lɛ Yakɔɓ , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ fagha ̀ ɓi ̀ si ki ̀ ɗig ki , nyimiɗ , ri ̀ ɓɔn ɓii , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ tuwe ɓii , ɓɛ nɔ girig kɔ ̀ ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ nɔɔ mɛ ̀ nig mɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ ti lɔŋ ɓii ̀ woo ̀ gh ki ̀ nɔli .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ nɔɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ nig mɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi ɓii ̀ faa ̀ , a ̀ a wogtii gɛ ɓi kinɔli . Lɛ mɛ ̀ nig mɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi ɓii ̀ faa ̀ mɛn ̀ , mɛ ri ɓii ̀ ghali ̀ n ̀ sim a ̀ cɛɓ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓi nɗem wii .
Nni giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : Kan , faa mɛ ̀ mɛ ̀ nig mɛn ̀ , di ki ̀ nɔli kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ti mɛ , kɛ ̀ ɛ nki yu ̀ ti kiroo ̀ gh mɛ ̀ nig fɛ .
Yeesus a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ nyi lɛ : Kɛ ̀ nay ki ̀ reŋii yii wɔɔ ̀ , di u sugtii ̀ fɛ .
Nni giɓ a ɓa ̀ ka ̀ nyi lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yin ɗi yii . Yeesus a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ u ̀ kpaa saaɗ yɔɔ ̀ kalii lɛ u ̀ yin ɗi yii ;
ɓisuulɛ , u ̀ ti mɛ ̀ wɛy mɛtan ̀ , nni ŋwaa ̀ nɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ nyi ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , a ̀ yin yii wɔɔ ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ wa ̀ a kpaa i ̀ ri ̀ mii ̀ .
Nni giɓ a kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : Kan ! N ̀ ghɛɛ lɛ , u ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan .
Ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓis ɓɛ mɓɔgsaagh Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi do ̀ n i ̀ nɛ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog mi ̀ nii kpaaghi ̀ lɛ , a Yorisalɛm nnɛ ɓum ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓɔgsaagh Bɛ ̀ ll .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : Giɓ anɛ ! Gherɛn ri ̀ kpaa ɗyɛ ̀ m , lɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki rii ̀ , ki ɓya ̀ a ɓɔgsi ti ɓi Ta ̀ a ̀ ta ɓi do ̀ n i ̀ nɛ , nsoo ̀ lɛ a Yorisalɛm .
Lɛ mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔɔɓɔgsi ̀ com ki ɓi ̀ yii ɓi , ɓi ̀ sii ̀ ɓɔɔɓɔgsi ̀ com ki ti ̀ yii , lɛ go ̀ ri i ̀ ɓum i ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ yi ̀ a Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki tii ̀ , kiŋce ̀ m ki mɛ ki kpaŋ , ki ɓɛ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛ ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ ɓɔgsii Ta ̀ a ̀ ta ri ̀ nghay , ri ̀ saaɗ . Ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɔɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ gsi ̀ nyi fɔlɔɔ ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ Ta ̀ a ̀ ta a kaaka ̀ a ̀ .
Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ Nghay , fɔɔnnɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɔɔɓɔgsi ̀ nyi ɓɛɛ ɓɔgsi nyi ri ̀ nghay , ri ̀ saaɗ .
Fɔɔnnɛ giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpaagha ̀ Yeesus lɛ : N ̀ -yii lɛ Me ̀ sii a ̀ ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɗii lɛ Kiris . Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ri yu ̀ , a ̀ ri kali ɓisi ɓiɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m .
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa min nyi lɛ : Mɛ ̀ a ̀ nɛ nto ̀ tog anɛ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ , mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ri Me ̀ sii .
Ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ innɛ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ Yeesus ɓɛ sugti ̀ gha ̀ y , ɓɛ kuura ̀ g yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ nyi di a to ̀ tog ri giɓ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɔ ki ghɛɛsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi lɛ , kɛɛ tɔg nyi lɛ , la yɛɛ ri ? Nsoo ̀ lɛ cɛ kɛɛ ̀ ki u kpaakpaa ri giɓ anɛ ?
Nni giɓ a ca ̀ ɗka ̀ be ̀ e ̀ yii ̀ i ̀ mɛ ̀ nig , a ̀ sugti ̀ ɓi ba ̀ n , a ̀ kpaa ɓumɓɛ wɔɔ lɛ :
Yu ̀ una ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ a kpaa mɛ ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi m ̀ mɛ ki ̀ , ɓaa ̀ yi ɓi nnyɛɛ ri Kiris .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓum ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ y ɓi ba ̀ n , ɓɛ yu ja ̀ ŋ inɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɓagha ̀ .
Ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ nɛn , ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛ ɓɔɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzi ̀ gha ̀ nyi , di ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa lɛ : Raɓi ̀ , ɗiya ɓa ̀ maa com .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : N ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓidɛŋ ɓi nɗi , ɓi mi ̀ nii yii ɓi ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ tɔɔ ̀ ghtɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ wɔɔ ɓɔ ri ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ a ri ̀ nya lɛ , a ̀ yu ̀ y nyi ri ̀ com ki ɗiyɛn gin ̀ ?
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓyɛm ̀ ɓi ri lɛ nki ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ romga ̀ y mɛ ̀ , n ̀ ki le ̀ gsi kisay ki a ̀ fagha ̀ mɛ ̀ .
Mi ̀ nii ti ɓi ̀ kpaaghi ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ ŋwii ɓaa rɔ ̀ ɓ ɓɛnin lɛ mɛ ̀ saŋ mɛɛ tumɛn . Nni mɛ ̀ n ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni lɛ , pi ̀ ighna mis ɓi ghɛn ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓyom ɓyaa te ̀ ɗ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ dɛm lɛ , ɓɛɛ saŋ .
N ̀ saŋi ̀ -mɛ ̀ saŋ a ̀ mɛ teɗ mɛle ̀ ɓ mii , a ̀ ki taŋzɛn ɓiɗu ̀ n ɓisuu cɛɓ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , lɛ di m ̀ ɓɛ ̀ li ̀ -ɓyom ri ̀ n ̀ saŋi ̀ -mɛ ̀ saŋ , ɓɛɛ nyaa ̀ rɛn n ̀ ɗaŋ .
Ɓisuulɛ da ̀ ɗki ̀ i ̀ nɛ lɛ , i mum bog a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ li , roa ̀ mbog a ̀ saŋ , i ̀ ri ̀ saaɗ .
N ̀ ɗomga ̀ mi ̀ ni lɛ ɓi kɛn ̀ mɛ ̀ saŋ ɓi dɛm inɛ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛɛ sala ̀ , mi ̀ nii ki ɗiŋi ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɔɔ mɛ say kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛ ̀ tɔɓ .
Ɓumɓɛ a Samari lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛn , ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ Yeesus , ɓi ri ̀ kpaa ɗi giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ a kpaa mɛ ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi m ̀ mɛ ki ̀ .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓumɓɛ a Samari ɓɛ yugha ̀ y nyi a nyoo , ɓɛ ɓɔŋza ̀ g nyi lɛ a kɔri a lɔ ̀ ŋkaa . Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ ghagsi ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ ru mɛɓɛɛ ̀ wɔɔ .
Ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓisuu ɓiɓan ɓi Yeesus nyimiɗ a kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ giɓ anɛ ̀ n lɛ , a ̀ a ri ̀ kpaa ɗyɔɔ ɗyɔ ri ̀ ɗyɔ ɗyɛɛ kii ̀ lɛ ti gherɛn . Ti ̀ gherɛɛ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ lɛ ɓi ̀ sii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ ti ̀ woogh ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓii , ti ̀ ki yi lɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ N ̀ ghɛɓsi ̀ -ziinɛ a ta ̀ a ̀ kaa ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ ru mɛ kiɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ̀ mɛ ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ , nni Yeesus a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ wɔɔ lɛ a kɛn ̀ a Galile .
Lɛ nyimiɗ a kali ̀ gha ̀ lɛ : N ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan a maa ̀ kem ɓi ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kii .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kpaga ̀ a Galile , ɓumɓɛ wɔɔ ɓɛ ghaɓ nyi lɛ syeesyee , lɛ ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ a Yorisalɛm , ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ ti Paska ̀ , lɛ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ga ̀ girig ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ tin ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ sugti ̀ gha ̀ min a Kana , ɓi zi i ̀ Galile , ja ̀ ŋ inɛ a ̀ ghaasi ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ nig mɛrɔ ̀ g . N ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n-ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ rifo ̀ m adɛŋ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ a Kapɛrinawum , nni man wii ̀ a ̀ baŋi ̀ a ̀ roro ̀ ɓka ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ woka ̀ lɛ , Yeesus a ̀ a m ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ yi ̀ a Zyude , a ̀ yu ̀ a Galile , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi a nyoo , a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋza ̀ g nyi lɛ , ɓɔɔ sɛn ̀ a Kapɛrinawum , a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a wɔɔ ̀ zi man wii ̀ a ̀ baŋi ̀ , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ ti ɓii ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔkɔɔ ̀ si ̀ .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : Mi ̀ nii ri lɔŋ lɛ , i ɓi ̀ ghɛɛ ɓi da ̀ m yi ɓiɓan , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ koŋnyoo ɓɛ ɓiɓan , kɛ ̀ ɓi gherɛn .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n-ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ nyi lɛ : Kan yuiy ɓa ̀ a mɛɛ mɛm ̀ di ŋwɔɓti wɛ ̀ m a ̀ ka maasi ɓi .
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Kɛ ̀ na man wɔɔ ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ cem . Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ kpaa ɗi Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi ɗi ̀ n , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ a ̀ kɛ ̀ n .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ sɛnsɛ ̀ nga ̀ a mɛɛ , nni ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓii ɓɛ yugha ̀ nyi ki ̀ ɓoŋi ̀ ɓi bee , ɓɛ kpaa nyi lɛ : Man wɔɔ ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ cem .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ tɔka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Fin innɛ nyoo yi ̀ i ̀ ya ̀ a sa ̀ a ̀ mɛɛ ? Ɓɛ ɓag ̀ nyi lɛ : I ̀ i nsa ̀ a ̀ mɛɛ ri ̀ ŋ ̀ ko ̀ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɗi ̀ fog .
Fɔɔnnɛ seŋi man a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ yiti ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki Yeesus a ̀ a nkpaa nyi lɛ : Man wɔɔ ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ cem . Nni a ̀ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ Yeesus ri ̀ ri ̀ mɛɛ ɗii ɗice ̀ m .
Da ̀ m i ̀ nɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓagha ̀ da ̀ m i ̀ ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ inɛ Yeesus a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ a Galile , di a ̀ ɓaa yi ̀ a Zyude .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ , fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɓɔka ̀ a Yorisalɛm .
A Yorisalɛm , coo kiɗig kidɛŋ ki ri wɔɔ , ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ ri ̀ ɗigi ̀ ɗi ɓi ba ̀ n ɗi lɛ , i ̀ suunaa wu jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ɓɛ regi ̀ kɔ ɓi ki ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ki Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n lɛ : Bɛtzata ; ki ̀ ɗig kin ̀ ki ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ tuu ̀ tuu mɛtan ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ tuu ɓi ɓɛroroɓ ɓi nɔɔ ̀ nɔ ̀ ŋdɛ ̀ nga ̀ a ɓɛ ̀ tuu ̀ tuu ɓɛ ̀ n zi , lɛ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɗyaŋɗya ̀ ŋ , [ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ lɛnlɛm , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ wɔ ̀ g , ɓɛ ɓoŋɓo ̀ ŋ lɛ mɛ ̀ nig mɛɛ nyɛŋ ̀ ɗɛn .
Lɛ ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a ̀ a nti a ̀ sɛngi ̀ i ̀ ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓidɛŋ ɓi ki ̀ ɗig kin ̀ , a ̀ nyɛ ̀ ŋzi ̀ mɛ ̀ nig ; fɔɔnnɛ ki mɓala ̀ g lɛ , i mɛ ̀ nig mɛ mɛ nyɛ ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ n , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ loogh mii ̀ ki ̀ kpi ̀ i , a ̀ a soo roro ̀ ɓ ri ̀ kuu ɗi firoɓ aɗi , a ̀ wɔ ̀ n . ]
Nni roro ̀ ɓ a ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ di a ̀ mɛ finɛn ɓi fi ̀ roɓ , be ̀ g ri ̀ tin ɗi ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ taa ̀ raa .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ nyi n ̀ nɔ ̀ nɔŋiyɛn , a ̀ ki yi lɛ , a ̀ mɛ finɛn ɓi-kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ win ̀ , nni a ̀ tɔka ̀ nyi lɛ : U kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ di wa ̀ a wɔ ̀ ni ?
Roro ̀ ɓ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Kan , n ̀ -yin ɗi mum a ̀ nɛ lɛ , a ̀ pi ̀ g mɛ ̀ ɓi ki ̀ ɗig , di mɛ ̀ nig mɛ mɛ nyɛŋ ̀ ɗɛ ̀ n ; lɛ ki ti lɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki mɛ ̀ ɛ nka yeeghyee ̀ ghkɛ ̀ n lɛ nkpi ɓi ki ̀ ɗig , ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ log ri ̀ mɛ ̀ .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : Pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , u teɗ kon wɔɔ ̀ , u kɛɛ ̀ ghi .
Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ gha ̀ ska ̀ ki ̀ wɔ ̀ ni , a ̀ teɗ kon wii ̀ , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ . Ŋwos anɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ŋwosi Saɓa ̀ t .
Nni Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓɛ wɔɔ ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ a ̀ nɛn lɛ : Ŋwosi Saɓa ̀ t yɛɛ ri lɛ . Ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓis ɓi gherɛɛ ɓi lɛ , u tɛg kon wɔɔ ̀ .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ a wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zii mɛ ̀ , a ̀ a kpaa mɛ ̀ lɛ : Tera kon wɔɔ ̀ , u kɛɛ ̀ ghi .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ tɔka ̀ min nyi lɛ : Ri ̀ kuu ɗi mum aɗi ɗyaa kpaa wɔ ̀ lɔɔ lɛ tera kon wɔɔ ̀ , u kɛɛ ̀ ghi ?
Wɔ ̀ lɛ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓɛ wɔɔ ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ a ̀ nɛn a ̀ yigha ̀ ɓi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi fɔlɔɔ , lɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ mɛ ɗim ɓi gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , Yeesus a ̀ tanɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : U ̀ ghɛɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ mɛ wɔ ̀ n , kɔ ̀ ɔ ki ̀ ti kiɓe , di u ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ tulɛɛ ri n ̀ tɔɓ wudɛŋ wu wu cee fɔ ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ kpaa ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n lɛ Yeesus yaa wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zii nyi .
Kɛɛ ̀ ki Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ nɔɔ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ Yeesus , lɛ a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ŋwosi saɓa ̀ t .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Seŋi wɛ ̀ m a ka sasa ̀ y a ̀ kpaŋ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , mɛ ̀ n ̀ sasa ̀ y girig .
Ɓi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛn nnɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ tee ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ti ̀ nyoo ɓi ri ̀ kaaka ̀ a ̀ ɗi bee inɛ ɓɛɛ wey nyi , a ̀ a lɛ ri ̀ yogsi ̀ ɗi a ̀ yoo ̀ yo ̀ gsi ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ ce ̀ li ̀ ki Saɓa ̀ t ɗyɔ ri ̀ ɗyɔ , lɔŋ ɓisuulɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ Seŋi wi ̀ i ̀ , a ̀ foŋɗɛn nyimiɗ ɓi nɗɛli wu Bɛ ̀ ll .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ min ɓɔ , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : N ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ kpaa lɛ Man a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kidɛŋ ri ̀ nto wi ̀ i ̀ , a ki ̀ ki lɔŋ ɓiɓan ɓi a seese ̀ e ̀ di Seŋi a ki ̀ ki ̀ . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Seŋi a ki ̀ ki ̀ , ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓi Man girig a ki ̀ ki ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ Seŋi a ̀ keesii Man , a ̀ ti a ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g nyi com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki a ki ̀ ki ̀ . A ̀ ki ri ̀ nyi ɓii ̀ re ̀ sii ɓiɓan ɓi ɓi cee fɔlɔɔ , lɛ ɓi kuu ̀ rag .
Lɛ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Seŋi a ̀ ti a ̀ ghe ̀ mza ̀ g ɓi ̀ loŋ , a ̀ fa ɓyɔ cɛɓ , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ Man a ̀ ti a ̀ fala ̀ g girig ɓumɓɛ a ̀ kɔ ̀ ni cɛɓ .
Seŋi a ̀ yin ɓii ̀ renɗeni ɓiɓan ɓi ɓum , wɔ ̀ lɛ Man innɛ a ̀ fagha ̀ ri ̀ ren ɗi ɓiɓan ɗice ̀ m ,
lɛ di ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛɛ nyaa ̀ si Man lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ nyaanyaa ̀ si ̀ Seŋi . I mum a ̀ nyaasii ɓi Man , di a ̀ nyaasii ɓi Seŋi a ̀ nɛ a ̀ romga ̀ y nyi .
N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ kpaa lɛ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ woogh jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yɛ ̀ m , a ̀ ki gherɛn roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ romga ̀ y mɛ ̀ , a ̀ ti ri ̀ cɛɓ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ . A ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ yu ̀ a ri ̀ ren ɗi ɓiɓan , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , a ̀ mɛ pɛ ̀ sɛn yi ɓi ri ̀ wu , a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ ɓi cɛɓ .
Nkpaa mi ̀ ni kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ kpaa lɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki rii ̀ , kiŋce ̀ m kɛɛ ti lɛ , kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓi ̀ loŋ ɓi ɓii ̀ woo ̀ gh jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ woo ̀ gh jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi ̀ i ̀ , ɓɛ ɓii ̀ ghɛɓi ̀ .
Lɛ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Seŋi a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu fayɛn cɛɓ , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , Man a ɓa girig ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu fayɛn cɛɓ .
A ̀ fagha ̀ nyi i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ a yɔm ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓum lɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ Man a ̀ mum .
Nni kɛ ̀ ɓi kuurag kiɓan kin ̀ ; ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki tii ̀ , ki ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓi zɔ ̀ ŋ ɓɛ ɓii ̀ woo ̀ gh jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi ̀ i ̀ , ɓɛ kpagi ̀ i ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ kigha ̀ ki ̀ rɔɔ , ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ ghemɓɛɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ teɗ cɛɓ ; ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ kigha ̀ ki ̀ ɓe , ɓɛ ghemɓɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓɛɛ teɗ bɛ ̀ lɛn .
Mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yin ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ kii kiɓan kidɛŋ ri ̀ nto wɛ ̀ m , nɗenɗen ɓiɓan lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ nwowo ̀ g , fɔɔnnɛ ri ̀ ren ɗyɛ ̀ m ɗi ɓiɓan ɗi ri lɛ saaɗ lɛ , n ̀ -yin ɓii ̀ kaakaa rikɔ ̀ n ɗyɛm ̀ , nkaakaa lɔŋ rikɔ ̀ n ɗi roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ romga ̀ y mɛ ̀ .
I mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ yaa ri ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ki ̀ ɓan kɛm ̀ , di com ki n ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ n ̀ kpaa ki yin lɛ ki wooghrɛ ̀ n .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ yɛɛ ri wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ki ̀ ɓan kɛm ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ -yii lɛ , com ki a kpaakpaa ɓi san wɛ ̀ m ki ri saaɗ .
Ɓi ̀ romga ̀ ɓum yɛ ̀ ɛ Zyaŋ , Zyaŋ a ̀ re ̀ si ̀ mi ̀ ni saaɗ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ɗyɛ ̀ m .
Ɓi san wɛ ̀ m , a ̀ a mum yɛɛ ri wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ɗyɛ ̀ m , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , n ̀ kpaa lɔŋ fɔlɔɔ lɛ , di ɓi ɓa ri ̀ cɛɓ .
Zyaŋ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ lamɓa ̀ a ̀ nɛ a ro ̀ o ̀ ro ̀ o ̀ , a ̀ kpee ̀ kpe ̀ ŋzi ̀ ja ̀ ŋ , nni ki kɔnga ̀ mi ̀ ni lɛ ɓi nyaa ̀ rɛn ri ̀ ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn kii ɓi maa ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n .
N ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ a ̀ nɛ a re ̀ resi kiɓan kɛm ̀ , a ̀ cee ri ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ɗi Zyaŋ a ̀ re ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ , nnyɛɛ ri ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Ta ̀ a ̀ ta a ̀ fagha ̀ mɛ ̀ lɛ nki . Ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓyɛɛ ̀ re ̀ resi lɛ Ta ̀ a ̀ ta yɛɛ romga ̀ y mɛ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Ta ̀ a ̀ ta nyimiɗ anɛ a ̀ romga ̀ y mɛ ̀ , a ̀ re ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ girig ki ̀ ɓan kɛm ̀ ; ŋwos adɛŋ , ɓi ̀ ka woka ̀ ɓi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi ̀ i ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɓi ki ghɛn i ̀ su wi ̀ i ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓii ɓi yin mini ɓi nɗem , lɛ ɓi ̀ gherɛɛ ɓi roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ romga ̀ y .
Ɓi fifiɓi mɛka ̀ ni ̀ mɛ kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , lɛ ɓi fe ̀ feg lɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ ka ̀ ni ̀ mɛn ̀ nnɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ri ̀ cɛɓ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ . Mɛ ̀ ka ̀ ni ̀ mɛn ̀ mɔ yɛɛ ̀ ki re ̀ resi kiɓan kɛm ̀ .
Nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ɓi ̀ kɔ ̀ ni ɓi lɛ di ɓya ̀ a yu ̀ u yi ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ lɛ ɓi ghɛn ̀ cɛɓ .
N ̀ -yin ɓii ̀ kaakaa rikem a ɓum .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ n ̀ -yii mi ̀ ni , n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ yin mini ɓi mɛ ̀ rem .
N ̀ -yu ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ɗii ɗi Seŋi wɛ ̀ m kɛ ̀ ɓi kɔ ̀ n lɛ ɓi ghaɓ mɛ ̀ , wɔ ̀ lɛ , i ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ yu ̀ u ɓi ɗii ɗii ɗi nyimiɗ , nyi nnɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ gha ̀ ɓi .
Lannɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , di ɓi faafa ̀ lɛ ̀ n ri ̀ kem mi ̀ ni ri ̀ mi ̀ ni , kɛ ̀ ɓi kaa rikem ɗi ɗi rii ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll cɛ ̀ ncii ?
Kɛ ̀ ɓi fe ̀ g lɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ sɔmɛɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Ta ̀ a ̀ ta ; ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ sɔmɛɛ , nnyɛɛ ri Moyis a ̀ nɛ ɓi ̀ fagha ̀ n ̀ tyweeyi ri nyi ,
ɓisuulɛ i ɓi ̀ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ Moyis , di ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ gherɛ ̀ n mɛ ̀ , lɛ ki ̀ ɓan kɛm ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki a ̀ ka ̀ nga ̀ .
Nni i ɓi ̀ gherɛɛ ɓi ɓiɓan ɓi a ̀ ka ̀ nga ̀ , lannɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ gherɛɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ n ̀ kpaa ?
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , Yeesus a ̀ sya ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ cɛcɛɗ ki riɓa ̀ y a ̀ nɛ a Galile , a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ nɗegi ̀ ti ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ nɛ a Tiɓeriyaadɛ .
Fɔɔnnɛ coo kituu ki ɓum ki nɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ nyi , lɛ ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ da ̀ m yi a ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ roroɓ ɓɛ a ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ ɓɔka ̀ ɓi do ̀ n aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ wɔɔ ɓi zi , ri ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii .
Fɔlɔɔ a ɓagha ̀ di ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ ti Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ti lɛ Paska ̀ ti ti ja ̀ ŋbog .
Yeesus a ̀ pi ̀ ka ̀ mis , a ̀ ghɛn coo kituu ki ɓum , di kɛɛ ̀ yu ̀ yuiy nyi a nyoo , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ tɔka ̀ Filiɓ lɛ : Fennɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ti ̀ la ̀ g bi ̀ rɛs i ̀ nɛ lɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛɛ ɗi ?
Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ fɔlɔɔ lɛ , a fee ̀ ghrɛn Filiɓ lɛ , nyimiɗ a yigha ̀ com ki a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i .
Nni Filiɓ a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ nyi lɛ : Nsoo ̀ bi ̀ rɛs i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ hɔnɗɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛ ɓɛtɔɔsi ̀ m ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ , i ̀ yin lɛ i ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ n lɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ ɗi maa ki ̀ ɓɛgha ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ -yila ̀ g wi ̀ i ̀ adɛŋ a ̀ nɛ lɛ Andire , geni Simɔn Pyɛɛri a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ :
Maa ŋwɔɓti a ̀ baŋi ̀ a ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ ri ̀ fɛ lɛ , ri ̀ bi ̀ rɛs yitan ̀ yi ɓɛ kii ri ̀ ri ̀ kuu ɗi ge ̀ ŋ ɗilɛ ɔri ̀ zɛ ̀ , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ zɛn ɓiɓɛɛ ̀ , nni ɓi ri lɛ ɓi ki cɛ ri gɛ mum a ̀ nɛ ?
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ siina ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓi zi . Ɓyaaɓi ɓi ɓagha ̀ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ̀ n lɛɛ ̀ gwey , nni ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kɔri ̀ gha ̀ min ɓi zi , ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ nunu ̀ g ɓum ɓɛ ̀ tɔɔsi ̀ m ɓɛtan ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ teka ̀ bi ̀ rɛs , a ̀ fa Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ka ̀ ɓsi ̀ yɔ ̀ ri ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ ɓɛn ̀ ; fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ fati ̀ gha ̀ girig ɓɔ ɓi ̀ zɛn ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ kɔnkɔ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɗi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ wura ̀ ka ̀ , nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii lɛ : Taŋ ̀ zɛɛna ɓi ̀ ɓɛgha ̀ ɓi bi ̀ rɛs ɓi ɓi rɔɓtaagh lɛ com kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɗyoŋ .
Nni ɓɛ ɓadɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓɛgha ̀ ɓi bi ̀ rɛs ɓi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɗi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ caɗka ̀ , ɓɛ roo ̀ zi ̀ ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɗ ntɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ ɓiɓɛɛ ̀ ; ɓi bi ̀ rɛs yi kitan ̀ yi yi ɓagha ̀ yin ̀ yi ki ̀ yɛn ɗi ɔri ̀ zɛ ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ da ̀ m i ̀ ki ̀ ɓan inɛ ̀ n , nni ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan anɛ ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ lɛ , a ̀ ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u ɓi ziinɛ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ yigha ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ti ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ , ɓɛɛ ɓan nyi , ɓɛɛ ɓɔgsi nyi ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɓi-te ̀ ɗ , nni a ̀ gha ̀ ghi ̀ gha ̀ a ̀ ɓɔgti ̀ ɓi do ̀ n cɛ ̀ ncii .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ cɛŋko ̀ ki kpaga ̀ , nni ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛ sɛnga ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y .
Ɓɛ ɓɔg ɓi ki ̀ kɔm lɛ ɓɛɛ syaa ̀ cɛcɛɗ ki riɓa ̀ y a Kapɛrinawum ; biri ̀ m i ̀ kpi ̀ gha ̀ di Yeesus a ̀ ka tanɛn ɓi lɔŋ ɓɔ .
Fɔɔnnɛ bɛ ̀ ɓ i ̀ fɛɛ ̀ fɛ ̀ ɓsi ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ pi ̀ pi ̀ g ɓi ̀ kus .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ di ɓɛ mɛ fye ̀ e ̀ riɓa ̀ y fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ kilo ̀ mɛɛ ̀ tɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛtan ̀ nsoo ̀ lɛ taa ̀ fog , nni ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ y Yeesus di a kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛɛ yi ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , a ̀ yu ̀ yu ̀ y ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ ki ̀ kɔm , i ̀ ris wu ɓan ɓɔ .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ri , kɛ ̀ ɓi risi .
Ɓɛ mɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , ɓɛɛ teɗ nyi ɓi ki ̀ kɔm , nni ki ghaska ̀ ki ̀ lomi ̀ ɓi be ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɛ kɛnkɛ ̀ nga ̀ .
Ɓi duri tana , ki ̀ tuu ki ɓum ki ki rɔɓka ̀ y cɛcɛɗ ki riɓa ̀ y , ki ghɛnga ̀ lɛ , ki ̀ kɔm ki ̀ fog kɛɛ nɗi ̀ wɔɔ . Nni Yeesus a ̀ a nki ɓɔɔgh ɓi ɓi ki ̀ kɔm kiŋce ̀ m n ̀ ɗaŋ ri ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii , lɔŋ ɓɔ yɛɛ nkɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ki ̀ kɔm ki ̀ n cɛ ̀ ncaa .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ kɔm ɓidɛŋ ɓi ɓagha ̀ y a Tiɓeriyaadɛ , ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɛ ɗigha ̀ bi ̀ rɛs , di Kan a ̀ mɛ fa Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ nsoo ̀ Yeesus nsoo ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii , a ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi wɔɔ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɔmiɗ ɓɛ ɓɔka ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ kɔm ɓi ̀ n , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ki ̀ kaa ̀ Yeesus a Kapɛrinawum .
Ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ga ̀ nyi ki ̀ tanɛɛ cɛcɛɗ ki riɓa ̀ y , ɓɛ tɔg nyi lɛ : Raɓi ̀ , wɔ ̀ ɔ n-yu ̀ u fɛ ̀ fin ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : N ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ kpaa lɛ , a ̀ a ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ i nghɛɛ da ̀ m nnɛ ɓi kaakaa mɛ ; ɓi kaakaa mɛ lɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ i nɗii bi ̀ rɛs ɓi ̀ wura ̀ g .
Kɛ ̀ ɓi say ɓisuu ɓiɗila ̀ g ɓi ɓi ri lɛ ɓi ɗyoŋ , salina ɓisuu ɓiɗila ̀ g ɓi ɓi ri lɛ ɓi kɔri ̀ a ̀ kpaŋ ɓi cɛɓ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓi Man a ̀ mum a ̀ ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ faa ̀ , lɛ nyi nnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll Seŋi a ̀ foga ̀ ki ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ ki rila ̀ mi ̀ ɗii ɓi nyi .
Nni ɓɛ tɔka ̀ Yeesus lɛ : Ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ i cɛ ɓi ɗi lɛ ti say ɓisuu ɓiɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a kɔ ̀ nkɔ ̀ n ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : Ki ̀ say ki Bɛ ̀ ll ki ri lɛ , ɓi gherɛn roa ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ romga ̀ y .
Nni ɓɛ tɔka ̀ nyi lɛ : Da ̀ m i ̀ ki ̀ ɓan aɗi yɛɛ ̀ nnɛ u ̀ ki ̀ i , i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ lɛ , i ti ̀ ghɛɛ , ti ̀ gherɛ ̀ n wɔ ̀ ? Ki ̀ say aɗi kɛɛ ̀ ki wɔ ̀ ɔ ki ̀ ki ̀ ?
Ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓis ɓɛ ɗigha ̀ mana ̀ ɓi-reɓ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : A ̀ fagha ̀ ɓɔ bi ̀ rɛs i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ aɗyoo lɛ ɓɛɛ ɗi .
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ , a ̀ a Moyis yɛɛ fagha ̀ mi ̀ ni bi ̀ rɛs i ̀ nɛ i ̀ sɛnga ̀ y aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog Seŋi wɛ ̀ m yɛɛ faa mi ̀ ni kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ bi ̀ rɛs a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
Lɛ bi ̀ rɛs i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ ri ̀ bi ̀ rɛs i ̀ nɛ i ̀ sɛnii ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , i ̀ ki fa ziinɛ cɛɓ .
Nni ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ min nyi lɛ Kan , falag ɓi ̀ si bi ̀ rɛs i ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m .
Yeesus a ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ bi ̀ rɛs i ̀ cɛɓ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yu ̀ u a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ za ̀ y , ya ̀ a kɔɔdii gɛ ɓi nyi . Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki gherɛɛ mɛ ̀ , ki ̀ nɔli kaa kitii gɛ ɓi nyi .
N ̀ ki kpaagha ̀ mi ̀ ni fɔlɔɔ , ɓi ̀ ghɛn mɛ ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɓi ki gherɛn .
Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ Ta ̀ a ̀ ta a ̀ faa mɛ ̀ , ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ , nni ma ̀ a ki kpaŋzi ɓi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yu ̀ u yi ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ ɓi ɗyɔ ̀ m .
Ɓisuulɛ , n ̀ sɛnga ̀ y ɓi aɗyoo lɛ nki ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗyɛm ̀ , n ̀ sɛnga ̀ y lɔŋ lɛ nki ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ romga ̀ y mɛ ̀ .
Nni ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ romga ̀ y mɛ ̀ ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi : Lɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ nɗimzi nsoo ̀ mum bog , ɓi ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ a ̀ fagha ̀ mɛ ̀ . N ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɔŋ ɓɔ ki ̀ ghe ̀ mzii , ɓi siito ̀ n a ŋwos .
Lɛ ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi Seŋi wɛ ̀ m ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi : Lɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghɛɛ Man , a ̀ ki gherɛn nyi , a ɓa ri ̀ cɛɓ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , mɛ ̀ n ̀ ki ghe ̀ mzii gɛ nyi ɓi siito ̀ n a ŋwos .
Fɔɔnnɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ŋwɔŋwɔ ̀ ŋi ̀ gha ̀ nyi lɛ , a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ bi ̀ rɛs i ̀ nɛ i ̀ sɛnga ̀ y aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
Ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ lɛ : A ̀ a Yeesus a ̀ man a ̀ Yoosɛɓ yɛɛ ri lɛ ? Ti ̀ yii lɛ ri ̀ seŋi ri ̀ jɛɛ , nni lannɛ a kpaaghi ɓigomi ̀ nɛ lɛ , nyii ri bi ̀ rɛs i ̀ nɛ i ̀ sɛnga ̀ y aɗyo ̀ o ̀ ?
Yeesus a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Kɛ ̀ ɓi ŋwɔ ̀ ŋwɔŋi , mi ̀ ni ri ̀ mi ̀ ni .
Mum a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ yu ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ di Ta ̀ a ̀ ta a ̀ nɛ a ̀ romga ̀ y mɛ ̀ a ̀ syo ̀ ŋii ̀ ɓi nyi , mɛ ̀ n ̀ ki ghe ̀ mzii gɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n mii ̀ ɓi siito ̀ n a ŋwos .
Ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan lɛ : Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ re ̀ saagh ɓɔ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , fɔɔnnɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ woka ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Ta ̀ a ̀ ta , a ̀ ki teɗ rire ̀ sa ̀ g ɗii , nnyɛɛ ri lɛ a ̀ yu ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ .
Fɔlɔɔ a re ̀ sii ɓi lɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ ka ghɛnga ̀ Ta ̀ a ̀ ta , lɔŋ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ y yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll yɛɛ ghɛnga ̀ Ta ̀ a ̀ ta cɛ ̀ ncii .
N ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ kpaa lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ gherɛɛ mɛ ̀ , a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ cɛɓ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ri bi ̀ rɛs i ̀ cɛɓ .
Ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓin ɓɛ ɗigha ̀ mana ̀ ɓi-reɓ , ɓɛ ki cuu .
Lɔŋ bi ̀ rɛs i ̀ nɛ i ̀ sɛnga ̀ y aɗyoo , yɛɛ ̀ nɛ , lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɗii yɔ ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɛ wu ̀ .
N ̀ ɗi ̀ bi ̀ rɛs i ̀ cencem i ̀ nɛ i ̀ sɛnga ̀ y aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɗii bi ̀ rɛs i ̀ nɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɓi ̀ fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ . Bi ̀ rɛs i ̀ nɛ m ̀ ɓii ̀ faa ̀ i ̀ nɛ ̀ n , yɛ ̀ ɛ ri nyoo yɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ faa ̀ , lɛ ziinɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa ri ̀ cɛɓ .
Ɓi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛn , Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ nyoo ̀ nyo ̀ lɛ ̀ n ɓɔ ri ̀ ɓɔ , ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ lɛ : Lannɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ fa ɓi ̀ si nyoo yi ̀ i ̀ lɛ ti ɗi yɔ ̀ ?
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : N ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ , i ɓi ̀ ɗii ɓi nyoo i ̀ Man a ̀ mum , kɛ ̀ ɓi ki nɔ bwaɓ yii , ɓi ̀ yin lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓa ri ̀ cɛɓ ki kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɗii nyoo yɛ ̀ m , a ̀ ki nɔ bwaɓ yɛm ̀ , a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ cɛɓ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ghe ̀ mzii nyi ɓi siito ̀ n a ŋwos .
Lɛ nyoo yɛ ̀ m i ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓi kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ , bwaɓ yɛm ̀ , kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ com ki nɔyɛ ̀ n .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɗii nyoo yɛ ̀ m , a ̀ nɔ bwaɓ yɛm ̀ , a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ɗa ̀ rɛn ɗi mɛ ̀ , mɛ ̀ girig n ̀ ɗa ̀ rɛn ɗi nyi .
Fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Ta ̀ a ̀ ta a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ cem a romga ̀ y mɛ ̀ , mɛ ̀ n ̀ ki ɓa ri cɛɓ lɛ nyi , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɗii mɛ ̀ , a ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɓi ̀ lɛ mɛ ̀ .
Bi ̀ rɛs i ̀ nɛ i ̀ sɛnga ̀ y aɗyoo yɛ ̀ ɛ ri lɛ ; i ̀ yin yɛ ̀ ɛ i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓin ɓɛ ɗigha ̀ ɓɛ cuu ; nni ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɗii bi ̀ rɛs i ̀ nɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɓi ̀ fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi , yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ re ̀ e ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ ka ̀ ɓum ɓi naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n i ̀ nɛ a Kapɛrinawum .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ woka ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓin ̀ , nni ki ̀ gwey ki kali ̀ gha ̀ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓi ɓi tee ̀ sɛɛ , ghɛn yɛɛ ri lɛ a ̀ cenɛ ̀ n ɓyɔ ri ̀ wowo ̀ g ?
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ yigha ̀ ɓi nɗem wii lɛ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛɛ ̀ ŋwɔ ̀ ŋwɔŋi nyi ɓi ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ , nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki kɛɓtii mi ̀ ni fi ̀ ɓa ̀ g ?
I ɓi ̀ ki ghɛɛ Man a ̀ mum di a ɓɔɓɔg aɗyoo ja ̀ ŋ inɛ a ̀ ka ɓagha ̀ , ki ɓa min la ?
N ̀ ghay wɛɛ ̀ fafa cɛɓ , mɛ ̀ mu ̀ u ̀ mɛ yin ɗi gɛɓsɛ ̀ n . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ma ̀ a kpaa mi ̀ ni ɓi ri ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Nghay , ri ̀ ɓi cɛɓ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n ɓɛ gherɛɛ ɓi . Lɛ a ri ̀ tumɛ ̀ n Yeesus a ̀ yigha ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi , ri ̀ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi ki ̀ ka ̀ ɓi .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Ki ̀ ɓan ki kɛɛ ̀ ki n ̀ kpaagha ̀ mi ̀ ni mii ̀ lɛ mum a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ yu ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ di Ta ̀ a ̀ ta a ̀ faa ɓi nyi fe ̀ g a ̀ nɛ ̀ n .
A ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ ghaaghra ̀ ka ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ti nyi .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ min ɓɛyila ̀ g ɓɛ kin ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ rɛn lɛ : Mi ̀ nii kɔni ɓi lɛ ɓi ghaa ̀ rag girig ?
Simɔn Pyɛɛri a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ nyi lɛ : Kan , ti ̀ ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ghɛn ? U ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi cɛɓ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ti ̀ mɛ gherɛ ̀ n , ti ̀ ki yi lɛ wɔ ̀ yɛɛ ri roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tenɛn a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ y yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Yeesus a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ ɛ nti mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ɓɔnga ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ntɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ ? N ̀ soo ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ki ̀ bog ki ɓi mi ̀ ni ki ri Sata ̀ n .
Zyudas a ̀ man a ̀ Simɔn Iskariyot innɛ a ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ lɔɔ lɛ nnyɛɛ ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ , ki ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi ki ̀ ka ̀ ɓi .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , Yeesus a ̀ rere ̀ ni ̀ gha ̀ zii ̀ Galile lɛ a ̀ kɔ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi lɛ a kɛn ̀ ki ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛɛ a Zyude , lɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kaaka ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ wey nyi .
Ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ ti Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ti lɛ ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ ti ɓilaa ti ɓagha ̀ di ti ti ja ̀ ŋbog .
Nni ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓɛ Yeesus ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : Pɛ ̀ sɛn fɛ , u kɛn ̀ a Zyude , di Ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɔɔ ɓɛɛ ghɛn ̀ girig ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi u ki ̀ ki fɛ .
Mum a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan a ri ̀ nyam di a kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ ɓɛɛ yi nyi . Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ u ki ̀ ki ɓiɓan yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi , kpaŋzi ɓyɔ mum bimiɗ a yi wɔ ̀ .
Lɛ nsoo ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓii ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi nyi .
Yeesus a ̀ kali ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kɛm ̀ ki ka kpaŋ ɓi , mi ̀ ni yɛɛ ri ri ̀ syeesyee a ̀ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ziinɛ i ̀ yin lɛ i ̀ ɓe ̀ e ̀ zɛ ̀ n mi ̀ ni wɔ ̀ lɛ mɛ ̀ ɛnɛ yɛɛ ̀ ɓe ̀ eɓee ̀ zɛ ̀ n , lɛ n ̀ ti n ̀ kala ̀ g lɛ , mɛ ̀ ki ̀ kii mɛ yɔ ̀ mɛ rɔɔtɛɛ ɓi ̀ .
Mi ̀ nii ɓɔɔghna ɓi kɛn ̀ ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ , ɓi san wɛ ̀ m , mɛ ̀ n ̀ ka yin ɓii ̀ ɓɔɓɔɔgh wɔɔ lɛ , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kɛm ̀ ki ka ghɛɛ ̀ sɛn ɓi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ fɔlɔɔ , nni a ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓka ̀ a Galile .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ di ɓɛ mɛ ɓɔg a ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ , nni nyimiɗ a ɓɔka ̀ girig wɔɔ , wɔ ̀ lɛ a ̀ ɓɔka ̀ ɓi ɓi mɛ ̀ ta ̀ na , lɔŋ a ri ̀ nyam nnɛ a ̀ ɓɔka ̀ .
Nni Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kaaka ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ nyi ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ di ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa lɛ : A ̀ ri ̀ fe ?
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓi gwi ̀ y i ̀ nɛn ɓɛ ruru ̀ mi ̀ gha ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓi ki ̀ ɓan kii . Ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛdɛŋ lɛ : A ̀ ri ̀ syeesyee a ̀ mum ; ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛmbog lɛ : A ̀ g ! A na ̀ anaa ̀ zi ̀ gi ̀ kɔm ̀ ɓum bee .
Nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ , mum a ̀ ghɛɛsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi lɛ a ɓuŋ nyi fɛlɛ lɛ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ɓi mɛ ̀ ree ̀ mɛ ɓum lɛ ɓɛ riri ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ ti ɓagha ̀ di ti ti ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m , Yeesus a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ tum ri ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɗi ɓum .
Nni Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kuu ̀ ku ̀ u ̀ ghra ̀ ka ̀ ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ lɛ : Ki ɓaa la lɛ , a yi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ri ɓi ̀ ka ̀ nɛ ̀ n , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ fɛ a ̀ yilaagh ɓyɔ ?
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi nɗe ̀ eresa ̀ g ɓi , ɓi yin ɓiɓan ɓyɛm ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ , ɓi ri lɔŋ ɓiɓan ɓi roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ romga ̀ y mɛ ̀ .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ kɔ ̀ ni lɛ a ki ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll yɛɛ ri ɓii ̀ yii ̀ n ̀ ko ̀ o ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓi nɗe ̀ re ̀ si ̀ , nko ̀ o ɓiŋkɛ ̀ m ɓi mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a kpaakpaa ɓiɓan ɓii ɓi nyimiɗ yɛɛ ̀ kaakaa rikem ɗii , wɔ ̀ lɛ roa ̀ nɛ a kaakaa rikem ɗi roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ romga ̀ y nyi , nnyɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa saaɗ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ki ɓa ri ki ̀ ɓan kidɛŋ ki ki ri ki ̀ tɛ ̀ ŋtɛ ̀ ŋ .
Mɛ ̀ ɛ nti Moyis a ̀ fagha ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ki ̀ ɓan kifog , nsoo ̀ wa ̀ a ̀ dɛŋ u ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ɓi ɓidɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓin ̀ ; nni ɓi kaakaa lɛ ɓi wey mɛ ̀ lɛ cɛ ?
Nni gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum i ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ nyi lɛ : U ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki nghay ; ghɛn yɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ a wey wɔ ̀ ?
Yeesus a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ki ̀ i lɔŋ kiɓan kifog , kɛɛ n ̀ kegsii mi ̀ ni lɛ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ɓi ̀ ti ɓi ̀ kɛ ̀ ɗki ̀ mum ŋwosi Saɓa ̀ t lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Moyis yɛɛ fagha ̀ mi ̀ ni i ̀ te ̀ ɗ ɓisuu kɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ n ; nsoo ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki yin lɛ Moyis yɛɛ kpaga ̀ y ri ̀ nyi , lɔŋ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓin ɓɛ ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛɛ loka ̀ ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ nyi .
I ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ kɛ ̀ ɗ ŋwɔɓti ŋwosi Saɓa ̀ t , fɔlɔɔ kɛ ̀ ɛ ki yogsi ɓidɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Moyis , nni lannɛ ɓi woki bim ri mɛ ̀ lɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zii mum lɛ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ ŋwosi Saɓa ̀ t ?
Kɛ ̀ ɓi teki ɓiɓan ɗyoo ri ̀ ɗyoo , ɓa ̀ kiina ki ̀ ɓan yɛ ̀ ɛ saaɗ a kɔ ̀ nkɔ ̀ n .
Ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ a Yorisalɛm ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ lɛ a ̀ a ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ kaakaa lɛ ɓɛɛ wey yɛɛ ri lɛ ?
Nni ghɛɛna min yɛ ̀ ɛ a to ̀ tog lɛ fwa ̀ afwa ̀ a ̀ y ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓum , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki kpaa nyi com . Ɓɛ ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɓis ɓɛ mɛ konag nya ki ̀ yii ̀ lɛ nnyɛɛ ri Kiris gi ̀ n ?
Ɓi ̀ sii yii ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ yi ̀ , wɔ ̀ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Kiris a ̀ ri yu ̀ mum a ̀ a yi ɓi fennɛ a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ yi ̀ .
