Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ kpaa lɛ , mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ki ̀ ki kiɓe , a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ kpa ̀ n a ki ̀ ɓe .
N ̀ kpa ̀ n a maa ̀ ɓa ɓi lɔŋ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓi naa i ̀ ɓum ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , ki ̀ ɓan kifog man a ̀ nɛ ɓi naa i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ ̀ n , nnyɛɛ ri ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓi naa i ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m .
Fɔɔnnɛ i Man yɛɛ ghaasii mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ kan , ɓi ̀ ɓa ɓɛ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛ ̀ kan .
N ̀ -yii lɛ , ɓi ̀ ri ̀ boo i ̀ mum yi ̀ Abiraham , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ɓi kaakaa lɛ ɓi wey mɛ ̀ lɛ , ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓyɛm ̀ ɓi ghɛɛ ɓi ikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ rem min .
Mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kpaakpaa ɓiɓan ɓi n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Seŋi wɛ ̀ m ; mi ̀ nii ̀ yɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki lɔŋ ɓiɓan ɓi seŋi wi ̀ n a ̀ kpaagha ̀ mi ̀ ni .
Nni ɓɛ ɓaka ̀ nyi lɛ : Abiraham yɛɛ ri seŋi wi ̀ s . Yeesus a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : I ki ri saaɗ lɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔn ɓɛ Abiraham , ki ̀ ina min ɓiɓan ɓi nyii kigha ̀ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki , ɓi kaakaa lɛ ɓi wey mɛ ̀ . M ̀ o ̀ a ̀ nɛ n ̀ kpaagha ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi n ̀ woka ̀ y ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , com ki Abiraham a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ɓi .
Ɓi ki ̀ ki ɓiɓan ɓi seŋi wi ̀ n a ki ̀ la ̀ g ? Nni ɓɛ ɓaka ̀ nyi lɛ : Ti ̀ yin ɓɔn ɓɛ ti ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g , ti ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ Seŋi bog lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa lɛ : I kaa ri ̀ saaɗ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll yɛɛ ri Seŋi wi ̀ n , di ɓi ̀ keesii mɛ ̀ ; lɛ ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll nnɛ n ̀ fuu yi ̀ , wɔɔ nnɛ n ̀ ki ɓagha ̀ y ; n ̀ -yu ̀ gha ̀ y ɓi ri nto wɛ ̀ m , lɔŋ nyi yɛɛ romga ̀ y mɛ ̀ .
Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓi ̀ woogh ɓi kito ̀ ki ̀ kɛm ̀ ? Lɛ ɓi ̀ yin lɛ ɓi ̀ wog jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yɛ ̀ m .
Sata ̀ n yɛɛ ri seŋi wi ̀ n fɔɔnnɛ ɓi kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ di ɓya ̀ a ki ̀ i ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi seŋi wi ̀ n . A ɓalag n ̀ woli ̀ -ɓum a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n a ri ̀ tumɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ki ka rɛli ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ɓi saaɗ nsoo ̀ ŋwos bog , ɓisuulɛ , saaɗ a maa ̀ ɓa ɓi a lɔ ̀ ŋkii ; ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki a pwa ̀ a ̀ pwaa ɓum , lɔŋ com ki ki rii ̀ nyi ɓi nɗem kɛɛ ̀ ki a kpaakpaa ɓɔ , lɛ a ̀ ri ̀ pwa ̀ a ̀ pwaa ̀ , a ̀ ki ɓa ti seŋi ɓɛ ̀ pwa ̀ a ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ gherɛɛ ɓi mɛ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ nkpaakpaa saaɗ .
Ghɛn anɛ ɓi mi ̀ ni yɛɛ ri lɛ a ̀ re ̀ si ̀ nsoo ̀ maa ri ̀ na ̀ n ɓi cɛɓ kɛ ̀ m lɛ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ? I mɛ ̀ n ̀ ki kpaa saaɗ , ɓi cɛ nnɛ ɓi ̀ gherɛɛ ɓi mɛ ?
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ mum a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , a woki jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ; nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ yin ɓum ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , nnɛ ɓi ̀ woogh ɓi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi ̀ i ̀ .
Nni Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓaka ̀ nyi lɛ : Ki ri lɔŋ saaɗ yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ i nkpaa lɛ , u ̀ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a Samari , u ̀ ki ɓa ti ri ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki nghay .
Yeesus a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ lɛ : N ̀ -yin ɗi ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki nghay , ki ̀ ɓan kifog nkeekem ̀ zi ̀ Seŋi wɛ ̀ m , mi ̀ nii ki so ̀ osoo ̀ ti ̀ mɛ ̀ .
Mɛ ̀ n-yin ɓii ̀ kaakaa rikem ɗyɛ ̀ m , ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ yɛɛ ̀ kaakaa ɗyɔ , nnyɛɛ ̀ ki yɔ ̀ myɔm ɓum .
N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ kali ̀ lɛ : I ŋwaa ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓyɛm ̀ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ wii gɛ ɓi .
Nni Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : Ɓigomi ̀ nɛ ti ̀ yii lɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki nghay . Abiraham a ̀ wugha ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ cuu girig , wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ki kpaa lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓyɛm ̀ a ̀ wii gɛ ɓi .
Wɔ ̀ yɛɛ cee Abiraham a ̀ seŋi wi ̀ s anɛ a ̀ wugha ̀ ? Ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ ɓɛ cuugha ̀ girig ? Wɔ ̀ ɔ fe ̀ feg lɛ u ̀ ri ̀ cɛ ?
Nni Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ lɛ : I ma ̀ a ɓɔɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ gsɛ ̀ n di ri ̀ kem ɗyɛ ̀ m ɗi ri ɗi zɛy ri ̀ zɛy . Nni Seŋi wɛ ̀ m a ̀ nɛ ɓi kalag lɛ a ̀ ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll wi ̀ n yɛɛ ̀ ɓɔɔɓɔgsi ̀ mɛ ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ ki yii ɓi nyi ; mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yii nyi . I n ̀ kpaa lɛ n ̀ -yii ɓi nyi , di n ̀ ɗi ̀ pwa ̀ a ̀ pwaa ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ mi ̀ ni . Kiɓan kifog mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yii nyi , mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ki ɓe ̀ ŋɓeŋ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi ̀ i ̀ .
Abiraham a ̀ seŋi wi ̀ n a nya ̀ a ̀ rɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ fe ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ , a ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɛ ŋwos wɛm ̀ , a ̀ ki ghɛnga ̀ nyi a ̀ wog ki ̀ rɔɔ lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Nni Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : Wɔ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ be ̀ g mɛ ̀ tin mɛɓɛɛ ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ , u ̀ ki kpaa lɛ u ̀ ghɛnga ̀ Abiraham ?
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ , di Abiraham a ̀ ka yin , mɛ ̀ m ̀ ɓagha ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ pɛsa ̀ ka ̀ gɔ ̀ g lɛ ɓɛɛ rogi nyi , wɔ ̀ lɛ Yeesus a ̀ nyamzɛ ̀ nga ̀ a ̀ kpaŋ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ghagha ̀ ghi ̀ ya ̀ , nni a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ yalɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ti ̀ ɗyaŋ .
Ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛ tɔg nyi lɛ : Raɓi ̀ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yalɛ ̀ nga ̀ fɛlɛ ri ̀ ti ̀ ɗyaŋ lɛ nyimiɗ yɛɛ kigha ̀ ki ̀ ɓe gi ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ yali ̀ ɓii ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : Ki yin lɛ nyimiɗ , nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ yali ̀ ɓii ɓɛɛ kigha ̀ ki ̀ ɓe , wɔ ̀ lɛ ki ri lɔŋ fɔlɔɔ lɛ , di mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll mɛɛ ghɛnɛn a lɔ ̀ ŋkii .
Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ ti ki ɓi ̀ say ɓi roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ romga ̀ y mɛ ̀ , di ŋwos a kaka , lɛ i ̀ ru wɛɛ ̀ yu ̀ yuiy , wɛɛ ̀ wu mum a ̀ a ɓa ti ɓi ri bee inɛ a ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ say mii ̀ .
Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki n ̀ kaka ɓi ziinɛ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ki ɓi ziinɛ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ fɔlɔɔ , nni a ̀ tuugha ̀ ti ̀ tyɛɛ ̀ ɓi zi , a ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ tɔ ̀ tɔ ̀ ɓ ri ̀ ti ̀ tyɛɛ ̀ tii , a ̀ siŋi ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓi mis ,
a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Kɛ ̀ na ki ̀ so ̀ o i ̀ su ɓi ki ̀ ɗig ki a Silowe ; ɗii ɗi ̀ n ɗi ri azi lɛ : N ̀ ɗomɛn . Nni ɗyaŋɗya ̀ ŋ a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ , a ̀ so ̀ o ̀ i ̀ su , a ̀ sugti ̀ i ̀ di a ̀ mɛ ghɛnɛ ̀ n .
Ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ woŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ mɛɛ ri ɓɔ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ nghɛngi ̀ nyi abɛ ̀ y di a lɔnlɔn ɓyom ɓi bee , ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ lɛ : A ̀ a ŋwaa ̀ nɛ yɛɛ nti a ̀ kɔ ̀ ra ̀ g fɛ a ̀ lɔnlɔ ̀ n ɓum ɓyom ?
Ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ lɛ nnyɛɛ ri , ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛmbog lɛ a ̀ g ! A ̀ a nyi yɛɛ ri , lɔŋ ki ̀ pisɛn kii kɛɛ ri . Wɔ ̀ lɛ nyimiɗ a ki kpaakpaa lɛ : Lɔŋ mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ri .
Nni ɓɛ tɔka ̀ min nyi lɛ : Mis mɔɔ maa ghɛnɛɛ di ki ɓaa la ̀ ?
Nni a ̀ ɓaka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ regi lɛ Yeesus yaa tɔɓi zi , a ̀ siŋi ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓi mis , a ̀ kpaa mɛ ̀ lɛ : Kɛ ̀ na ki ̀ so ̀ o i ̀ su ɓi Silowe . Fɔɔnnɛ ma ̀ a kɛ ̀ ɛ , n ̀ so ̀ o ̀ i ̀ su , n ̀ ghɛnɛ ̀ n .
Nni ɓɛ tɔka ̀ nyi lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ ri ̀ fe ? Nyii pɛɛ ̀ zi ̀ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yii ɓi .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ga ̀ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ka ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ti ̀ ɗyaŋ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ .
Kɔɔ ki ɓagha ̀ foo lɛ , ŋwosi Saɓa ̀ t nnɛ Yeesus a ̀ tɔɓka ̀ zi , a ̀ ki ̀ lɛ , mis mɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n mɛɛ ghɛnɛn .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ tɔka ̀ girig ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ , a kali ɓɔ lannɛ kaa ki ̀ lɛɛ lɛ a ghɛnɛn . Nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : A ̀ a siŋii mɛ ̀ ki ̀ tɔ ̀ tɔ ̀ ɓ ɓi mis , n ̀ so ̀ o ̀ i ̀ su , nnɛ nghɛɛghɛnɛ ̀ n lɛ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ yi ̀ ɓi yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓisuulɛ a ̀ ce ̀ lii ɓi Saɓa ̀ t . Ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛmbog ɓɛ tɔg lɛ : Lannɛ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe a ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ ki ̀ mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ da ̀ m yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ?
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ghasɛ ̀ nga ̀ ga ̀ ɓ yiɓɛɛ ̀ ; ɓɛ tɔgti ̀ ɗyaŋɗya ̀ ŋ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ : Ɓi ɓɛg wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ kpaa la ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ a ki ̀ i lɛ mis mɔɔ mɛɛ ghɛnɛn ? Nni ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ ghɛɛ lɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan .
Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ka ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ti ̀ ɗyaŋ nni a ̀ mɛ ghɛnɛ ̀ n , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ di ɓɛ ka reŋii ɓi ɓɛyali ̀ ɓii .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ tɔka ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yali ̀ ɓii lɛ : Man win ̀ a ̀ nɛ ɓi kpaaghi lɛ a ̀ yalɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ti ̀ ɗyaŋ yɛɛ ri lɛ ? Nni lannɛ a ̀ ti ɓii ̀ ghɛnɛɛghɛnɛ ̀ n ɓigomi ̀ nɛ ?
Ɓɛ ̀ yali ̀ ɓii ɓɛ ɓaa ̀ g lɛ : Ɓi ̀ sii yii lɛ man wi ̀ s yɛɛ ri lɛ , a ̀ ki yalɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ti ̀ ɗyaŋ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ti ̀ yii ɓi com ki ki kii ̀ lɛ a ghɛnɛn , tyɛ ̀ ki ki yi nsoo ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ a ŋwa ̀ ri nyi mis . Tɔɔghna nyi , a ̀ ti n ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓi le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ki ̀ ɓan ki ki seesee nyi .
Ɓɛ ̀ yali ̀ ɓii ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ fɔlɔɔ ɓisuulɛ , ɓɛ riri ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ; ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ di ɓɛ mɛ wooghrɛn jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ lɛ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ gherɛɛ lɛ Yeesus a ̀ ri ̀ Kiris , ɓɛ ren nyi ɗii ɓi naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ kigha ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ yali ̀ ɓii ɓɛɛ kpaa lɛ : A ̀ ti n ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn , tɔɔghna nyi .
Fɔɔnnɛ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ y ti ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ka ɓagha ̀ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ti ̀ ɗyaŋ , ɓɛ kpaa nyi lɛ : Kali saaɗ ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ sii yii lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe .
Nni ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yii ɓi nko ̀ o a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe ; com ki mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yii ki ri lɛ , m ̀ ɓalag ri ti ̀ ɗyaŋ , nni m ̀ mɛ ghɛnɛn ɓigomi ̀ nɛ .
Ɓɛ tɔka ̀ nyi lɛ : Cɛ kɛɛ ̀ ki a ̀ a ki ̀ i wɔ ̀ ? Lannɛ a ̀ a ki ̀ i lɛ mis mɔɔ mɛɛ ghɛnɛ ̀ n ?
A ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : Ma ̀ a kpaa mi ̀ ni ki ̀ ɓan ki , kɛ ̀ ɓi kɔ ̀ n lɛ ɓi wog . Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓi kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ ɓi wogti kɔ ? Ɓi kɔ ̀ nkɔn girig lɛ ɓi ɓa ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ?
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ sɛmga ̀ ka ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ kpaa nyi lɛ : Wɔ ̀ yɛɛ ri n ̀ -yila ̀ g wi ̀ i ̀ , ɓi ̀ sii ri ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ Moyis .
Ti ̀ yii lɛ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ Moyis ; wɔ ̀ lɛ roa ̀ nɛ , ti ̀ yii ɓi fennɛ a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ yi ̀ .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : Ki ̀ ɓan ki ki yeesɛɛ ri ̀ wog ki ri lɛ , mi ̀ nii yii ɓi fennɛ a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ yi ̀ , wɔ ̀ lɛ nyaa ki ŋwa ̀ ri mɛ ̀ mis !
Ti ̀ yii lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ti kɛ ̀ ɛ wog bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n yi ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , a ̀ ti a ̀ woki ̀ bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n yi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ kuuraagh nyi , a ̀ ki ki ̀ lag rikɔ ̀ n ɗii .
Ti ̀ ka woka ̀ ɓi di ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa lɛ , ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ mɛ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ mis mɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yalɛɛ ri ̀ ti ̀ ɗyaŋ mɛɛ ghɛnɛ ̀ n .
I ŋwaa ̀ nɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓay yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , di a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ ki ̀ com .
Nni ɓɛ ɓaka ̀ nyi lɛ : Wa ̀ a ̀ nɛ u ̀ yalɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ki ̀ ɓe wɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ bimiɗ , wɔ ̀ yɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ u resag ɓi ̀ si ? Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ naɓka ̀ nyi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ woka ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ nna ̀ ɓi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n , nni a ̀ tuusɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ nyi , a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : U ̀ gherɛɛ nya Man a ̀ mum ?
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ nyi lɛ : Nnyɛɛ ri ghɛn Kan , yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ n ̀ gherɛ ̀ n nyi ?
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : U ̀ mɛ ghɛn ance ̀ m , nyimiɗ yɛɛ ̀ ki to ̀ tog lɛ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Kan n ̀ gherɛɛ ; a ̀ ɓag mɛ ̀ ɗu ɓi zi , a ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ nyi .
Yeesus a ̀ kali ̀ min nyi lɛ : N ̀ -yu ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ziinɛ lɛ ri ̀ ren ɗi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɗyɛɛ ghɛnɛn le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ , ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ri ̀ ti ̀ ɗyaŋ ɓɛɛ ghɛnɛn , ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ghɛɛghɛnɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɗiŋi ̀ ti ̀ ɗyaŋ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ ɓɛ woka ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓin ̀ , ɓɛ tɔg nyi lɛ : Ɓi ̀ sii ri nya girig ri ̀ ti ̀ ɗyaŋ ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : I ɓya ̀ a ri ̀ ri ̀ ti ̀ ɗyaŋ , di ɓi ̀ yin ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓa ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓe ; nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi kpaakpaa lɛ ɓi ghɛɛghɛnɛ ̀ n , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ki ̀ ɓe kin ki kaka .
N ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ kpaa lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ fyee ɓi asuunaa lɛ a ɗiŋi ɓi ki ̀ laa ki jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog a ̀ ɓɔg gari ɓi ja ̀ ŋ idɛŋ a ̀ ɗini ̀ ɓi ki ̀ laa , a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ nyi wiiwi ̀ i ̀ , nyi ti ̀ zyaa ̀ zyaa .
Lɔŋ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɗiŋii asuunaa yɛɛ ri syeesyee a ̀ m ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yin ̀ .
M ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -i ̀ suunaa a ̀ nɛm ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n i ̀ suunaa lɛ a ɗiŋi , jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yii yi wog jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi ̀ i ̀ ; a ̀ ki regi jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yii lɔŋ ɓi mii , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ yɔ ɓidan .
I a ̀ mɛ kpaŋzi jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yii yice ̀ m , a ̀ syo ̀ ŋ yɔ bee , yɔɔ nɔɔ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ nyi lɛ , yi yii jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi ̀ i ̀ .
Yi yin lɛ yi nɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ n ̀ ke ̀ n a mum , ki ̀ ɓan kifog yi ri ɓii ̀ ghɛŋii nke ̀ n a mum fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ lɛ yi remzii ɓi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi ɓɛ ̀ ke ̀ n .
Yeesus a ̀ teka ̀ ɓɔ da ̀ ɗki ̀ i ̀ nɛn , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ wog kiɓan ki a kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaati ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : N ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ kpaa lɛ mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ri i ̀ suunaa wu gari i ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ loka ̀ y ki ̀ yu ̀ u ri mɛ ̀ , ɓɛ ri , ɓɛ ̀ wiiwi ̀ i ̀ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ zyaa ̀ zyaa . Wɔ ̀ lɛ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yi woka ̀ ɓi rikpaa ɗya ̀ a ̀ .
Mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ri i ̀ suunaa , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ fyee a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ a ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ cɛɓ . A ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ , a ̀ kpaŋ a ̀ ki tanɛn ɓiɗila ̀ g .
Wiiwi ̀ i ̀ a ̀ ti a ̀ yu ̀ la ̀ g lɔŋ lɛ , a yii ̀ , a ̀ wey , a ̀ ki cuusi . Ɓi mɛ ̀ , mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yu ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yɛɛ ɓa ri ̀ cɛɓ , yi ki ɓa ri kɔ lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ri syeesyee a ̀ m ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ . Syeesyee a ̀ m ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ a falag cɛɓ kii ɓisuu jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yii .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ɓe ̀ ŋɓeŋ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ leɓ nyi , kɛ ̀ ɛ ki ɓa mɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓa lɛ yiŋkii , a ̀ ti a ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g lɛ , i a ̀ ghɛɛ n ̀ gɔn , a ̀ rini ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , a ̀ la ̀ n . N ̀ gɔn a ̀ yu ̀ ki ̀ ɓangii jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , a ̀ san yɔ .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ti a ̀ la ̀ ngi ̀ fɔlɔɔ ɓisuulɛ , a ki ̀ ki kisay ɓisuu mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni , n ̀ ɗem wii wɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ kɛsi ri jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ri syeesyee a ̀ m ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ . N ̀ -yii jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yɛm ̀ , jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yɛm ̀ yi ki yii mɛ ̀ ,
lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Ta ̀ a ̀ ta a ̀ yii mɛ ̀ , mɛ ̀ n ̀ ki yi Ta ̀ a ̀ ta ; mɛ ̀ n ̀ ki faa cɛɓ kɛ ̀ m ɓisuu jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yɛm ̀ .
N ̀ ɗi ̀ ti ̀ ri ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yidɛŋ yi yi ka yin ɓi ki ̀ laa ki . Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ nteɗ yi ̀ girig yɔ ; yi ri ɓii ̀ woo ̀ gh jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yɛ ̀ m , fɔɔnnɛ ki ̀ tuu ki jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ki ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ki ̀ fog , m ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ a ̀ ɓa bog .
Ta ̀ a ̀ ta a ̀ keesii mɛ ̀ ɓisuulɛ , n ̀ faa cɛɓ kɛ ̀ m lɛ di nki teeti kɔ .
Mum a ̀ ɓa ̀ tɛɛ ɓi mɛ cɛɓ , lɔŋ mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ yɛɛ faa kɔ ̀ . N ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ nfa kɔ , n ̀ ki ɓa ti ri i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ n ̀ teeti ̀ kɔ ̀ ; ki ̀ ɓan ki Seŋi wɛ ̀ m a ̀ reɓsi ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ lɛ nki kɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ n .
Fɔɔnnɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ghasɛ ̀ nga ̀ ti ̀ ga ̀ ɓ yiɓɛɛ ̀ ɓisuu ɓito ̀ ki ̀ ɓin ̀ .
Ki ̀ gwey ki ɓi ɓɔ ki kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ lɛ : Yeesus a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki nghay , a ̀ ki ɓa ti ndu ̀ ŋɛn , ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓi wowog ɓiɓan ɓii ?
Ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛmbog ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓi yin ɓito ̀ ki ̀ ɓi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki nghay . Ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki nghay ki ri nya lɛ ki ŋwaɗ mis mɛ ɓɛɗyaŋɗyaŋ ?
Ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ ti go ̀ n inɛ ɓɛ fagha ̀ naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ti ɓagha ̀ a Yorisalɛm , ki ɓagha ̀ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ bu ̀ ma ̀ .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ gha ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi tuu ̀ tuu anɛ ɓɛ nɗegi ̀ lɛ , tuu ̀ tuu a Salomɔŋ .
Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ taŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi a nyoo , ɓɛ kpaa nyi lɛ : U kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ mɛ ̀ rem mɛɛ ɗii ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ si ɓi mu ̀ m a ̀ kpaŋ ɓigomi ̀ be ? Nko ̀ o wɔ ̀ yɛɛ ri Kiris , kali ɓi ̀ si lɛ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ ɓaka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : M ̀ mɛ kpaa mini , kɛ ̀ ɓi gherɛn . Ɓiɓan ɓi nki ̀ ki ɓi ɗii ɗi Seŋi wɛ ̀ m , ɓyɔ yɛɛ re ̀ resi rikuu ɗi mum ɗi n ̀ ɗi ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ɓi ̀ gherɛɛ ɓi lɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ yin jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yɛm ̀ .
Jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yɛm ̀ yi ti yi woki ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yɛ ̀ m , mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yii yɔ , yɔɔ ki ti yi nɔɔ ̀ ta ̀ g mɛ ̀ .
N ̀ ti n ̀ fala ̀ g yɔ cɛɓ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ya ̀ a wu ɓi nsoo ̀ ŋwos bog , mum a ̀ ki yin lɛ a ̀ ɓa ̀ tɛ ̀ n yɔ ɓi ca ̀ g kɛm ̀ .
Seŋi wɛ ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ fagha ̀ mɛ ̀ yɔ , a ̀ cee ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , fɔɔnnɛ mum a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ ɓa ̀ tɛ ̀ n yɔ ɓi ca ̀ g ki Ta ̀ a ̀ ta .
Ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ri ̀ Ta ̀ a ̀ ta , ti ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ mum bog .
Fɔɔnnɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓadɛ ̀ nga ̀ ti ̀ gɔ ̀ g lɛ ɓɛɛ rogi nyi .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaati ̀ gha ̀ min ɓɔ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ ɛ nki ̀ i ɓɛ ̀ gɛn ɓɛ ɓiɓan lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓi mis min , ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu Ta ̀ a ̀ ta , nni ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ , kibe kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓi ̀ ti mɛ ̀ ɓii ̀ rogii gɔ ̀ g mii ̀ ?
Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓag nyi lɛ : Ti ̀ yin lɛ ti ̀ rogi ̀ wɔ ̀ gɔ ̀ g ɓi syeesyee a ̀ ki ̀ ɓan anɛ u ̀ ki ̀ i , wɔ ̀ lɛ tii rogi ̀ wɔ ̀ gɔ ̀ g ɓisuu zɛɛtɛn yi u ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ yɔ ɓi san a ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓisuulɛ , wɛ ̀ ɛnɛ lɔŋ mum , u ̀ ki kɔ ̀ n lɛ u terɛn wɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ?
Nni Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ki yin kika ̀ nɛn ɓi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓin lɛ : Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ bɛ ̀ ll ?
Ti ̀ yii lɛ mum a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ pisi ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ; nni i mɛ ̀ ka ̀ ni ̀ mɛ regii ɓumɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ lɛ bɛ ̀ ll ,
mi ̀ nii kali ̀ roa ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ nga ̀ a ̀ rom yi ̀ lɛ a ̀ sɛɛtii Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓisuulɛ ma ̀ a kalii lɛ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ?
I n ̀ ki rɔ ̀ ɓi kɛ ̀ ɛ nki ̀ ɓisay ɓi Seŋi wɛ ̀ m , ɓi ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓ kɛ ̀ ɓi gherɛn mɛ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , i nki ̀ ki ɓisay ɓii , nsoo ̀ ɓya ̀ a gherɛɛ ɓi mɛ , gherɛɛna ɓyɔ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ , ɓi ̀ yi , ɓi ̀ ki ghɛn lɛ Ta ̀ a ̀ ta a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ , mɛ ̀ ɓi Ta ̀ a ̀ ta .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ mɛɛ ̀ kaati ̀ gha ̀ bee inɛ ɓɛɛ ɓan ̀ nyi ; wɔ ̀ lɛ Yeesus a ̀ sɔtɛ ̀ n ɓɔ ɓi ɓya ̀ g .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ di ̀ gha ̀ cɛcɛɗ ki Zyuridɛŋ , ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ Zyaŋ a ̀ ka ɓa ̀ a ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓti ̀ gha ̀ ɓum , a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ wɔɔ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ yugha ̀ y nyi a nyoo , ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ lɛ : Zyaŋ a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ɓi da ̀ m nsoo ̀ bog , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi Zyaŋ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ a ̀ ra ̀ ɗ ɗi ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓagha ̀ saaɗ .
Nni ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ Yeesus .
Ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ ɗii lɛ Lazaari , yɛɛ roro ̀ ɓka ̀ ; a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a Bɛtanii , ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki ɓɛ-Marii ɓɛɛ ̀ Maata a ̀ geni .
Marii a ̀ nɛn yɛɛ sisi ̀ ŋi ̀ gha ̀ Kan ti ̀ ra ̀ a ̀ re , a ̀ ki tɔ ̀ si nyi mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ ri tyo ̀ ŋ tii ; nni geni Marii a ̀ baŋi ̀ yɛɛ roro ̀ ɓka ̀ lɔɔ lɛ Lazaari .
Ri ̀ geni ɗi ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɗin ̀ , ɗi romga ̀ mum lɛ a kali Yeesus lɛ : Kan , mum wɔɔ ̀ a ̀ nɛ u keesa ̀ g , a ̀ yin cem .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ woka ̀ fɔlɔɔ , nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Fi ̀ roɓ fi ̀ n fi yin nyi ɓii ̀ wowoli , fi ri ɓisuu rikem ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , lɛ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a teɗ ri ̀ kem ɓi fi ̀ roɓ fi ̀ n .
Yeesus a ̀ keesi ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ Maata ri ̀ geni a ̀ giɓ , ri ̀ Lazaari girig .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ woka ̀ lɛ Lazaari a ̀ yin cem , a ̀ laati ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ ru mɛɓɛɛ ̀ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn nnɛ a ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii lɛ : Ti sugtiina a Zyude .
Ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ kpaa nyi lɛ : Raɓi ̀ , ki ka finɛn ɓi yɛ ̀ ɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ m ̀ mɛɛ ̀ rogi wɔ gɔ ̀ g , wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ki kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ di lɛ u sugti wɔɔ ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ ɛ nti ŋwos a ri ̀ la ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ hawo ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ ɓiɓɛɛ ̀ ? I mum a kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛɛ ri ŋwos , a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ ɓa ̀ gtɛ ̀ n , ɓisuulɛ a seesee kitɛɛtɛn ki ɓi ziinɛ .
