Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ fɔlɔɔ , nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Reŋka ̀ ŋ wi ̀ s Lazaari a ̀ a nlali , ki ̀ ɓan kifog n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ nyi ki ̀ ghe ̀ mzii .
Ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛ kpaa lɛ : Kan i ki ri lɛ a ̀ a nlali di a ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ lɛ syeesyee .
Ri ̀ wu ɗi Lazaari ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi a ̀ kpaagha ̀ , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɔɔ feki ̀ nya lɛ fi ̀ lo fi zɛy fyɛɛ ̀ fi a ̀ kpaa .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n lɛ : Lazaari a ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ loŋ .
Nni ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ ki ri mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ronɛn ɓi nɗem ɓisu win lɛ , mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ -yin wɔɔ , fɔlɔɔ yɛɛ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ ɓi gherɛn . Wɔ ̀ lɛ ti kɛ ̀ ɛna ja ̀ ŋ inɛ a ̀ ri ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Tomas a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ nɗegi ̀ lɛ , Didim , a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛmbog lɛ : Ti kɛ ̀ ɛna girig , ti wu nɗaŋ ɗi nyi .
