Yeesus a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ri ri ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓiloŋ , ri ̀ cɛɓ ; ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ gherɛɛ mɛ ̀ , a ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ri ̀ cɛɓ nsoo ̀ a ̀ a wi ̀ i ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ghɛghɛ ̀ ɓ a ̀ ki gherɛn mɛ , a ̀ a wu ɓi ; u ̀ gherɛɛ nya ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ?
Maata a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : Ɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ Kan ! n ̀ gherɛɛ lɛ wɔ ̀ yɛɛ ri Kiris , Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ yu ̀ u ɓi ziinɛ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Maata a ̀ kpaagha ̀ fɔlɔɔ , nni a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ reŋii geni a ̀ giɓ anɛ lɛ Marii , a ̀ kɔ ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ n nyi a dwi ̀ ɗ lɛ : N ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g a ̀ ri ̀ fɛ , a ki regi wɔ .
Lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Marii a ̀ woka ̀ fɔlɔɔ , a ̀ gha ̀ s ki ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus .
Lɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ ka ɗiŋi ɓi ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ kaka ja ̀ ŋ inɛ Maata a ̀ tulɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ nyi .
Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi naa ri ̀ Marii ɓɛ fɔɔfɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ si ̀ nyi nɗem , ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ lɔŋ di a ̀ mɛ pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyoo lɛ fo ̀ os , a ̀ kpaŋ ɓi ɗyɔ ̀ m ; fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ nɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ nyi , ɓɛ feki ̀ lɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ re ̀ ni a zɔ ̀ ŋ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Marii a ̀ kpaga ̀ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɓagha ̀ , a ̀ ghɛn Yeesus , a ̀ kpi ̀ nyi a mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ , a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Kan i wɔ ̀ ɔ nɗi ̀ fɛ , di geni wɛ ̀ m a ̀ a ŋwii ɓi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ di Marii a re ̀ nɗe ̀ n , Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ y n ̀ ɗaŋ ri nyi ɓɛ renɗe ̀ n girig , nni nyi ̀ inyi ̀ g i ̀ ɓanga ̀ nyi lɛɛ ̀ gwey , n ̀ ɗem wu nyɛŋɗɛ ̀ n nyi ɓiɗu ̀ m ,
a ̀ tɔg lɛ : Fe nnɛ ɓi ̀ i mɓo ̀ mi nyi ? Ɓɛ ɓaa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Kan yuiy u ghɛn ̀ .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ re ̀ nga ̀ .
Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kpaa min lɛ : Ghɛɛna yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ a nti a ̀ keesa ̀ g nyi .
Ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ dɛŋ i ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓɔ i ̀ kpaa lɛ : Nyi a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ŋwa ̀ ɗka ̀ ɗyaŋɗya ̀ ŋ mis , a ̀ a yin lɛ a ̀ ki ̀ lɛ Lazaari kɛ ̀ ɛ wu ?
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ɗem wu Yeesus wu nyɛŋɗɛ ̀ nga ̀ ti ̀ ɓi ɗu ̀ m , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n a zɔ ̀ ŋ . Zɔ ̀ ŋ i ̀ nce ̀ m i ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ tuɓɛn ɓi gɔ ̀ g ɓɛ simi ̀ gɔ ̀ g i ̀ dɛŋ a ŋwɔm .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Pisiina gɔ ̀ g i ̀ nɛ ɓi ŋwɔm wu zɔ ̀ ŋ . Maata , a geni Lazaari a ̀ nɛ a ̀ wugha ̀ , a ̀ kpaa Yeesus lɛ : Kan , a ̀ ti ɓii ̀ nu ̀ nnumi ; lɛ mɛ ̀ ru mɛnin gɛɛ ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ mɓo ̀ mi nyi .
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Ma ̀ a kpaa wɔ ̀ lɛ i u ̀ gherɛɛ u ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɛ ri ̀ gwey ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll !
Nni ɓɛ pisi ̀ gha ̀ gɔ ̀ g i ̀ nɛn , Yeesus a ̀ ɓegsi ̀ mis aɗyoo , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Ta ̀ a ̀ ta n ̀ to ̀ gsaagh wɔ ̀ ɓisuulɛ , wa ̀ a ɓa ̀ agh bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ m .
Ɓi ɓɛg wɛ ̀ m , n ̀ -yii lɛ u ̀ ti u ̀ ɓa ̀ ki ̀ bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n yɛm ̀ ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , ki ̀ ɓan kifog n ̀ kpaa fɔlɔɔ ɓisuu ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri fɛ , lɛ di ɓɛɛ gherɛn lɛ wɔ ̀ yɛɛ romga ̀ y mɛ ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ fɔlɔɔ , nni a ̀ pɛ ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Lazaari kpaŋay .
Fɔɔnnɛ ki ̀ loŋ ki kpaga ̀ y , ɓya ̀ g ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ ɓi ̀ ka ̀ gakɛn ri ɓɛ ̀ ɓanɗas , i ̀ su wu ̀ ka ̀ ŋɛn ɗi sa ̀ nja ̀ . Yeesus a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Fu ̀ miina nyi , ɓi caɗ nyi a kɛn ̀ .
Ki ̀ gwey ki ɓi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɛ yuyu ̀ gha ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Marii , ɓɛ ghɛn ki ̀ ɓan ki Yeesus a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ kin ̀ , ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ dɛŋ i ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓɔ i ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ , i ̀ kpaa ɓɔ ki ̀ ɓan ki Yeesus a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ taŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ Sa ̀ ne ̀ di ̀ rɛŋ ɓɛ kpaa lɛ : Ti ki la ? Lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ki ̀ ki da ̀ m lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
