Ɓigomi ̀ nɛ ti ̀ mɛ yi lɛ u ̀ yii ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ , ki ghɛɓsii ɓi com lɛ mum a tɔg wɔ ̀ n ̀ tɔɔ ̀ tɔɔgh . Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ti ̀ gherɛɛ mii ̀ lɛ u ̀ ɓagha ̀ y yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓigomi ̀ nɛ nnɛ ɓi ̀ mɛ gherɛ ̀ n ?
Ɓi ̀ ghɛɛ ! Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki rii ̀ , kiŋce ̀ m ki mɛ kpaŋ , kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓi ̀ ɓii ̀ tya ̀ ŋzɛɛ , mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ bee yii ̀ , ɓi ca ̀ ɗ mɛ ̀ cɛ ̀ ncɛm ; nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ , n ̀ -yin cɛ ̀ ncɛm , lɛ Ta ̀ a ̀ ta a ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛɛ ̀ mɛ ̀ .
Mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ lɛ , ɓi ɓa ri ̀ fyo ̀ oog a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ . Ɓi ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ -yeesɛ ̀ n ɓi ziinɛ nni si ̀ i ̀ riina mɛ ̀ rem , mɛ ̀ m ̀ mɛ yag ziinɛ ɓi-te ̀ ɗ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ , nni a ̀ ɓegsi ̀ gha ̀ mis aɗyoo , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Ta ̀ a ̀ ta , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki mɛ kpaŋ , kemzi Man wɔɔ ̀ , di Man wɔɔ ̀ a kemzi girig wɔ ̀ .
Fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ fagha ̀ nyi i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu lɛ a lami ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ fa ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ u ̀ fagha ̀ nyi cɛɓ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Cɛɓ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ki ri lɛ , ɓɛɛ yi wɔ ̀ , lɛ wɔ ̀ yɛɛ ri m ̀ bobog a ̀ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓɛ ki yi Yeesus Kiris , roa ̀ nɛ u ̀ romga ̀ y .
Mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kemzii wɔ ̀ ɓi ziinɛ , n ̀ le ̀ gsi ̀ ki ̀ say ki u ̀ fagha ̀ mɛ ̀ lɛ nki .
Nni ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , Ta ̀ a ̀ ta wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ kemzi mɛ ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ wɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ , ri ̀ ri ̀ kem ɗi m ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɗyɔ ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ wɔ ̀ , di ziinɛ i ̀ ka yin .
N ̀ ɗe ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ɗii ɗyɔɔ a ɓumɓɛ u ̀ fagha ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓi ziinɛ ; ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓum ɓɔɔ , nni u ̀ fagha ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓɔ , ɓɛ ki ɓe ̀ ŋ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , ɓɛ mɛ yi lɛ , ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi u ̀ fagha ̀ mɛ ̀ , ɓi rii ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɔɔ .
Ɓisuulɛ n ̀ fagha ̀ ɓɔ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi u ̀ fagha ̀ mɛ ̀ , ɓɛ ghaɓ ɓyɔ , ɓɛ ki konag ki yii ̀ lɛ , m ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ y a lɔ ̀ ŋkɔɔ , ɓɛ ki gherɛn lɛ wɔ ̀ yɛɛ romga ̀ y mɛ ̀ .
Ɓisu waa nnɛ m ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋza ̀ g . N ̀ -yin ɓii ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɔɓɔ ̀ ŋzi ̀ ɓisuu ziinɛ , m ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzii ɓisuu ɓɛroɓɛ u ̀ fagha ̀ mɛ ̀ , ɓisuulɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛnkɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Com kɛm ̀ ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ri kiŋkɔɔ , fɔɔnnɛ kiŋkɔɔ kice ̀ m ki ri girig kiŋkɛ ̀ m . Ɓi ɓɔ nnɛ ri ̀ kem ɗyɛ ̀ m ɗyɛɛ ̀ re ̀ eresɛ ̀ n .
Mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yii ̀ di ti ɓi ziinɛ , ɓɔ yɛɛ rɔɓi ɓi ziinɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yu ̀ u a lɔ ̀ ŋkɔɔ . Ta ̀ a ̀ ta a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tɛnɛn , ɓe ̀ ŋa ɓumɓɛ u ̀ fagha ̀ mɛ ̀ ri ̀ ɗii ɗyɔɔ , lɛ di ɓɛɛ ɓa ɓɛ ̀ ra ̀ rɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ sii ri ɓɛ ̀ ra ̀ rɛn lɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ .
Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki mɛ ̀ ɛ nɗi ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ , mɛ ̀ ɛ mɓe ̀ ŋɓeŋi ɓɔ , ɓi ̀ ɗii ɗyɔɔ , mɛ ̀ ɛ nka ̀ aka ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ ɓɔ , nsoo ̀ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɔ kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɗyaŋ ; i ki cee ɓi lɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ ɗyaŋi ̀ lɛ mɛ ̀ ka ̀ ni ̀ mɛɛ ron ̀ .
Nni ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , n ̀ -yu ̀ u a lɔ ̀ ŋkɔɔ ; n ̀ ki kpaa ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki n ̀ kaka ɓi ziinɛ , lɛ di ɓɛɛ ɓa ri ̀ ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ .
N ̀ fagha ̀ ɓɔ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓyɔɔ , fɔɔnnɛ ziinɛ i ̀ ɓe ̀ e ̀ zɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛ yin ɓumɓɛ ɓi ziinɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yin ŋwaa ̀ nɛ fɛ ɓi ziinɛ .
M ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzii ɓi wɔ lɛ u pisi ɓɔ ɓi ziinɛ , mɓɔ ̀ ŋza ̀ g lɔŋ wɔ lɛ , u lɛgsi ɓɔ ki ̀ ɓe .
Ɓɛ yin ɓumɓɛ fɛ ɓi ziinɛ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yin ŋwaa ̀ nɛ fɛ ɓi ziinɛ .
Ki ̀ ya lɛ ri ̀ saaɗ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ɓɛɛ ɓa ɓum ɓɔɔ ; ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓyɔɔ ɓi ri saaɗ .
Fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ romga ̀ y mɛ ̀ ɓi ziinɛ , mɛ ̀ girig mɛ ̀ ɛ nɗomi ɓɔ ɓi ziinɛ .
Mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ mɓe ̀ eɓeŋɗɛ ̀ n ntɛnɛn lɛ ɓɔ , lɛ di ɓɔ girig ɓɛɛ ɓa ɓɛ ̀ tɛnɛn ɓi saaɗ ɓi ɗu ̀ m .
M ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzii ɓi wɔ ɓisu waa lɔŋ cɛ ̀ ncaa , m ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzii wɔ ̀ girig ɓisuu ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓii ̀ gherɛɛ mɛ lɛ ri ̀ ghagsi ̀ ɗyaa ɗi ɓɔlɛ ̀ a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɔ ɓii ̀ ghagsii .
M ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzii wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓa ɓɛ ̀ ra ̀ rɛn ki ̀ byɔg ki ̀ fog Ta ̀ a ̀ ta , yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ , mɛ ̀ ɓi wɔ ̀ , ki ̀ ya lɛ ɓɔ girig ɓɛɛ ɓa ɓɛ ̀ ra ̀ ren ɓi ɓi ̀ si di fɔɔnnɛ ziinɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ gherɛn lɛ , wɔ ̀ yɛɛ romga ̀ y mɛ ̀ .
Mɛ ̀ n ̀ fagha ̀ ɓɔ ri ̀ kem ɗi u ̀ fagha ̀ mɛ ̀ , lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓa ɓɛ ̀ ra ̀ rɛn kibyɔg ki ̀ fog yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ si .
Mɛ ̀ ɓi ɓɔ , wɔ ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ , lɛ di ɓɛɛ ɓa ɓɛ ̀ ra ̀ rɛn lɛ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ ki ̀ byɔg ki ̀ fog , ziinɛ i ̀ ki yi lɛ wɔ ̀ yɛɛ romga ̀ y mɛ ̀ , nni n ̀ keesi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ yɛ ̀ ɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ keesi ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ .
Ta ̀ a ̀ ta kɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ nkɔn mɛ lɛ , ja ̀ ŋ inɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ , ɓumɓɛ u ̀ fagha ̀ mɛ ̀ , ɓɛɛ ɓa girig wɔɔ nɗaŋ ri mɛ ̀ , di ɓɛɛ ghɛn ̀ ri ̀ kem ɗyɛ ̀ m ɗi u ̀ fagha ̀ ɓisuulɛ u ̀ keesi ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ di ziinɛ i ̀ ka kilɛn ɓi .
Ta ̀ a ̀ ta a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ saaɗ , ziinɛ i ̀ yigha ̀ ɓi wɔ , lɔŋ mɛ ̀ yɛɛ yigha ̀ wɔ ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ ki yi lɛ wɔ ̀ yɛɛ romga ̀ y mɛ ̀ .
N ̀ ɗe ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ ɗii ɗyɔɔ , m ̀ ɓii ̀ ki re ̀ sii ti ɓɔ ɗyɔ lɛ di n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ nyi ɓisu wɛ ̀ m a ɓa a lɔ ̀ ŋkaa , mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ m ̀ ɓa a lɔ ̀ ŋkaa .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ , nni a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ cɛcɛɗ ki maa n ̀ syo ̀ m a ̀ nɛ lɛ Sedirɔŋ . Ɓɛ ɗiŋi ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓi dɛm idɛŋ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ .
Zyudas a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi ki ̀ ka ̀ ɓi a yigha ̀ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ̀ n , lɛ Yeesus ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛ nti ɓɛ taŋza ̀ g wɔɔ .
Nni Zyudas a ̀ teka ̀ lɛ ri ̀ nɗaŋ wu ɓɛsuja ̀ a ̀ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓɛ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ romga ̀ y , a ̀ yu ̀ y ri ̀ ɓɔ wɔɔ ɓi dɛm inɛ ̀ n . Ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ y lɛ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ lamɓa ̀ , ri ̀ ti ̀ ŋwɔki ̀ ri ̀ ɓyom ɓi ribaŋi ̀ .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ yigha ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓi ghɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi ki ̀ tanɛɛ , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ tyɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ tɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ a nyoo , a ̀ tɔg ɓɔ lɛ : Ghɛn innɛ ɓi kaaka ̀ a ̀ ?
Ɓɛ ɓaa ̀ g lɛ : Ti kaakaa Yeesus a ̀ nɛ a Naazarɛt . Yeesus a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ ɛ nɛ . Zyudas a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ka ̀ ɓka ̀ nyi a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ mɛ ̀ rɛy .
Lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ ɛ nɛ , ɓɛ sugti ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ jɛ ̀ m ɓɛ kpila ̀ g ɓi zi .
Yeesus a ̀ tɔgti ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ghɛn innɛ ɓi kaaka ̀ a ̀ ? Ɓɛ ɓaa ̀ g lɛ : Ti kaakaa Yeesus a ̀ nɛ a Naazarɛt .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ma ̀ a kalii mi ̀ ni lɛ , mɛ ̀ ɛ nɛ . I ki ri lɛ mɛ ̀ nnɛ ɓi kaaka ̀ a ̀ , ca ̀ rina ɓum ɓɛmbog ɓɛn ̀ , ɓɛɛ ghaa ̀ gh .
A ̀ kpaagha ̀ fɔlɔɔ lɛ kɛɛ ɓa lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ ɛ nɗimzii ɓi nsoo ̀ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓumɓɛ u ̀ fagha ̀ mɛ ̀ .
Nni Simɔn Pyɛɛri a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ga ̀ fa ̀ g ɓi ɗyaŋ , a ̀ sɔŋi ̀ gha ̀ y yɔ ̀ a ̀ kpɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say a ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi ɓɛpi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ syaŋ nyi i ̀ ree ̀ wu wee ̀ lem . N ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say a ̀ n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɗii lɛ Malkus .
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa Pyɛɛri lɛ : Pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ga ̀ fa ̀ g ɓi ɗyaŋ . Mɛ ̀ m ̀ ɓii ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓi kɛ ̀ ɛ nnɔ ɓeŋ a ̀ nɛ Ta ̀ a ̀ ta a ̀ fagha ̀ mɛ ̀ lɛ nnɔ ?
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ɗaŋ wu ɓɛsuja ̀ a ̀ win ̀ , ri ̀ N ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n wa ̀ a ̀ , ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɛ mɓe ̀ gi ̀ naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛ ɓanga ̀ Yeesus , ɓɛ kaŋ ̀ nyi bɛn .
Ɓɛ ka kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi yɛ ̀ ɛ Ann ; lɛ Ann a ̀ ɓagha ̀ seŋi gili Kayif . Kayif a ̀ nce ̀ m yɛɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi ɓɛpi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓi be ̀ g i ̀ nɛn .
Nyi yɛɛ ki reɓka ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n lɛ , ki ri ki ̀ rɔɔ lɛ mum a wu bog ɓisuu kilɔ ̀ ŋ .
Simɔn Pyɛɛri ri ̀ n ̀ -yila ̀ g a ̀ dɛŋ , ɓɛ nɔɔ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ Yeesus . Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi ɓɛpi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɗi yigha ̀ n ̀ -yila ̀ g a ̀ nɛ ̀ n , nyii ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛɛ ̀ Yeesus ɓi nlɛmɓog wu rifo ̀ m ɗi ɓɛpi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Pyɛɛri a ̀ rɔɓka ̀ ɓi dan , ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ i ̀ suunaa . Nni n ̀ -yila ̀ g a ̀ mbog a ̀ nɛ a ̀ yisɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi bɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ kpaga ̀ y , a ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n ɓɛɛ ̀ giɓ anɛ a ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋɓe ̀ ŋga ̀ i ̀ suunaa , a ̀ ɗiŋzi ̀ min Pyɛɛri .
Nni giɓ anɛ a ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋɓe ̀ ŋga ̀ i ̀ suunaa a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ tɔka ̀ Pyɛɛri lɛ u ̀ ri ̀ girig ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ wa ? Pyɛɛri a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : A ̀ g , n ̀ -yin n-yila ̀ g wi ̀ i ̀ .
Ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛ rɛrɛ ̀ li ̀ gha ̀ wɔɔ , di ɓɛɛ ̀ wowog ɗuu ɗi ɓɛ ghɛŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ki ̀ fɛɓ ki ɓagha ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ kii . Pyɛɛri a ̀ rɛrɛ ̀ li ̀ gha ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ ri ɓɔ , a ̀ wowo ̀ g girig ɗuu .
Nni ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi ɓɛpi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɗi tɔka ̀ Yeesus ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓi ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi a ̀ ti a ̀ re ̀ e ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɓɔ .
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ to ̀ toogh lɛ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓi ziinɛ . Mɛ ̀ nɗe ̀ resii ɓum ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi naa yi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , ja ̀ ŋ yi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ti ɓɛ taŋza ̀ g , kɛ ̀ ɛ nki kpaa kiɓan kidɛŋ a ri ̀ nyam .
Nni lannɛ mɛ ̀ ɛnɛ u tɔtɔg mɛtɔɔ ̀ ghtɔɔgh ? Tɔgha ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ nwowoogh ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi mɛ ̀ ɛ nkpaakpaa , ɓɛɛ kpaa ̀ wɔ ̀ com ki mɛ ̀ ɛ nkpaa ɓɔ , lɛ ɓɛ yii ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi mɛ ̀ ɛ nkpaakpaa .
