Ki kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ fɔlɔɔ lɛ , di jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ a resi ri ̀ kuu ɗi riwu ̀ ɗi a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ wii ̀ , yɛ ̀ ɛ ron .
Nni Pilat a ̀ sugti ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ ɗiŋii ɓi ki ̀ kpana ̀ ki ɓɛyɔ ̀ m , a ̀ reŋi ̀ Yeesus , a ̀ tɔg nyi lɛ : U ̀ ri ̀ nya ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ?
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Wɔ ̀ yɛɛ kpaa ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ gi ̀ n , ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛɛ kalii wɔ ̀ fɔlɔɔ ɓɛ raɗ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ?
Pilat a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ muu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n gi ̀ n ? Ɓumɓɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kɔɔ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ɓɔ yaa yu ̀ u ri ̀ wɔ ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ , nni ki ̀ ɓan aɗi kɛɛ ̀ ki wɔ ̀ ɔ nki ̀ i ?
