Pilat a ̀ tɔg nyi lɛ : Yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m wa ? Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : U ̀ kpaa mii ̀ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m . Mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yalɛ ̀ nga ̀ , n ̀ ki yu ̀ ɓi ziinɛ lɛ ntɛɛ ̀ zag ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi saaɗ , fɔɔnnɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ saaɗ , a ̀ ti a ̀ woki ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yɛ ̀ m .
Nni Pilat a ̀ tɔka ̀ nyi lɛ : Saaɗ innɛ cɛ ? Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ fɔlɔɔ , nni a ̀ kpaŋdi ̀ gha ̀ , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ja ̀ ŋ inɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ ghɛɛ ɓi kiɓan ki ɓeɓtɛn ki ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki ̀ i .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri mi ̀ ni ki ̀ syɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ lɛ , ncaɗ mi ̀ ni ki ̀ mbu ̀ ŋ ki ̀ fog ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ ti Paska ̀ , nni ki kɔni mi ̀ ni lɛ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi ncaɗ gi ̀ n ?
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ti ̀ ri ̀ kpaa jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : E ̀ e e ̀ e a ̀ a nyi , lɔŋ Ɓaraɓas innɛ u caɗ . Kɔlɛ Ɓaraɓas a ̀ ɓagha ̀ zyaa ̀ zyaa .
Nni Pilat a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ min ɗi Yeesus a ̀ reɓsi ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ nyi ki ̀ to ̀ n .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ toga ̀ min ta ̀ m a ̀ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ɓɛ saa ̀ gh Yeesus ɓi nto , ɓɛ waasi ̀ nyi ki ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ki ɓa ̀ ŋ .
Ɓɛ tyɛɛ ̀ tɛ ̀ n nyi a nyoo di ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa lɛ : Ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , ti ̀ to ̀ gsii wɔ ̀ , ɓɛ ɓoo ̀ ɓo ̀ ki ̀ nyi mɛ ̀ ɓɛn .
Nni Pilat a ̀ kpaŋdi ̀ gha ̀ y , a ̀ kpaa Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n lɛ : Ghɛɛna , n ̀ ti lɛ , nkpaŋzii ̀ mi ̀ ni nyi ; ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ yii ̀ lɛ , n ̀ ghɛɛ ɓi kiɓan ki ɓeɓtɛn ki a ̀ ki ̀ i , ki ki ri lɛ ɓɛ sɔmɛ ̀ n nyi mii ̀ .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaga ̀ y min . A ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ta ̀ m a ̀ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓi nto , ri ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ki ɓa ̀ ŋ ɓi nyoo , Pilat a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ghɛɛna ! mum innɛ ̀ n .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ nyi , ɓɛ kpaa jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Kpana nyi ɓi kɔrɔs , kpana nyi ɓi kɔrɔs . Pilat a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ terina nyi , ɓi kpan ̀ nyi ɓi kɔrɔs . Ɓi ɓɛg wɛ ̀ m , mɛ ̀ n ̀ ghɛɛ ɓi kiɓan ki ɓeɓtɛn ki a ̀ ki ̀ i , ki ki ri lɛ ɓɛ sɔmɛ ̀ n nyi mii ̀ .
Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓaa ̀ g Pilat lɛ : Ti ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna , nni ki ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ kpaaghi lɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ wii ̀ ɓisuulɛ a ̀ a nɗɛ ̀ ŋii ki ̀ kpaa ̀ lɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pilat a ̀ woka ̀ ti ̀ jɛɛ i ̀ nɛn , a ̀ risi ̀ ti ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey ,
fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ti ̀ ɓi ki ̀ kpana ̀ ki ɓɛyɔ ̀ m , a ̀ tɔg Yeesus lɛ : Wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ fuu yi ̀ fe ? Wɔ ̀ lɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓi nyi , Pilat a ̀ kpaa min nyi lɛ :
Mɛ ̀ nnɛ u ̀ mi ̀ nɛɛ ? U ̀ yii ɓi lɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ , n ̀ ca ̀ ɗ wɔ ̀ , nsoo ̀ lɛ n ̀ kpan ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓi kɔrɔs ?
