A ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ , Pilat a ̀ kaaka ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ bee inɛ lɛ a caɗ nyi , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : I u ̀ ca ̀ ri ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n di u ̀ yin righan ɗi Kaaza , lɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ kalii lɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m , a ̀ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ɗu ̀ u ̀ ɗuu ri Kaaza .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pilat a ̀ woka ̀ fɔlɔɔ , nni a ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ gha ̀ y Yeesus a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ ɓi-kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu riren ɗi ɓiɓan , ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɛ nɗegi ̀ lɛ pa ̀ vee ̀ , ɓi ri ̀ ebi ̀ reegh lɛ Gaɓata .
Ŋwos anɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ŋwos anɛ ɓɛ pee ̀ ghpe ̀ gsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ ti Paska ̀ di ki ti nunu ̀ g toroɓ , Pilat a ̀ kpaa Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n lɛ : Ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗin ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛ teŋzi ̀ gha ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ kpaa lɛ : A wu , a wu , kpana nyi ɓi kɔrɔs . Pilat a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ , mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kpan ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗin ? Ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ɓɛ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Ɓi ̀ sii yin ɗi ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗiɗɛŋ i ki yin lɛ Kaaza .
Nni Pilat a ̀ fagha ̀ min ɓɔ Yeesus lɛ ɓɛɛ kpan ɓi kɔrɔs . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ teka ̀ nyi , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi .
Yeesus a ̀ tɛ ̀ tɛ ̀ ka ̀ kɔrɔs wi ̀ i ̀ nyimiɗ ɓi ɗi lɛ ɓɛɛ pɛsɛn ɓi ba ̀ n , ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɛ nɗegi ̀ lɛ ki ̀ tɛtɛg ki nto , yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ɓi ri ̀ ebi ̀ reegh lɛ Gɔlgɔta .
Wɔɔ nnɛ ɓɛ kpanga ̀ nyi ɓi Kɔrɔs n ̀ ɗaŋ ri ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ , lɛ roa ̀ nɛ nyi ɓi ki ̀ mɛŋ , roa ̀ mbog nyi ɓi wee ̀ lem , Yeesus ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wa ̀ a ̀ .
Pilat a ̀ ka ̀ nga ̀ girig ɓi ki ̀ ɓoŋ , ɓɛ ɓaa ̀ ti ̀ kɔ ɓi kɔrɔs . Mɛ ̀ ka ̀ ni ̀ mɛn ̀ mɛ ɓagha ̀ lɛ : Yeesus a ̀ nɛ a Naazarɛt , ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n .
Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ ɓala ̀ ki ̀ ɓoŋ kin ̀ , lɛ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɛ kpanga ̀ Yeesus i ̀ ɓagha ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ ba ̀ n . Ki ̀ ɓoŋ kin ̀ ki ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ , ri ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ebi ̀ reegh , ri ̀ ɓi ri ̀ gi ̀ rɛg , ri ̀ ɓi ri ̀ la ̀ tɛŋ .
Ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ɓɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ Pilat lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ɔ ka ̀ n lɛ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , ka ̀ na lɛ , a ̀ a nkpaa lɛ , nyii ri ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n .
Nni Pilat a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ki m ̀ mɛ ka ̀ n , ki ti ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn .
Ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ mɛ kpan Yeesus ɓi kɔrɔs , ɓɛ teɗ ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ɓii , ɓɛ kaɓsi ̀ ɓyɔ ga ̀ ɓ yinin , suja ̀ a ̀ bimiɗ a ̀ teɗ ga ̀ ɓ bog ; ɓɛ teka ̀ girig jɔmpa ̀ s wi ̀ i ̀ , a ̀ nce ̀ m a ̀ ɓagha ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ja ̀ ŋ i n ̀ ɗa ̀ rɛn , a ̀ ɓa n ̀ toŋɛn lɛ ɗyɔɔg , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n aɗyoo , a ̀ kpaŋ azi .
