Ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛ lɛ : ri ̀ jɛɛ Yeesus , ri ̀ geni jɛɛ Yeesus , ri ̀ Marii a ̀ gili Kileyopas , ri ̀ Marii Madelɛn , ɓɛ rɛrɛ ̀ li ̀ gha ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ kɔrɔs a ̀ Yeesus .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ jɛɛ , a ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ di ̀ ti ̀ n ̀ -yila ̀ g a ̀ nɛ a ̀ a nkeesa ̀ g n ̀ ɗɛrɛliyɛn ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ jɛɛ wi ̀ i ̀ , nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ jɛɛ lɛ : Giɓ anɛ , man wɔɔ ̀ nnɛ ̀ n lɔɔ .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ -yila ̀ g a ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ : Gaa nnɛ ̀ n lɔɔ . A ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ , n ̀ -yila ̀ g a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ teka ̀ jɛɛ Yeesus a mɛɛ mii .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ yigha ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi mɛ kpaŋzɛ ̀ n , nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Ki ̀ nɔli kɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki mɛ , lɛ di ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ri ɓi ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ɓyɛɛ ron ̀ .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ teka ̀ y dɛ ̀ ɓ ɓɛ nɔg ɓi ɓi ̀ kpama ̀ ɓi mɛrɔ ̀ g ɓi ɓi ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ ɓi ki ̀ bɔkɔ ̀ kidɛŋ , ɓɛ ɓam ̀ yɔ ̀ ɓi ki ̀ geŋ , ɓɛ namzi ̀ nyi a ŋwɔm .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ syo ̀ ga ̀ ɓi ̀ kpama ̀ ɓi mɛrɔ ̀ g ɓin ̀ , nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi roni . Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ tuŋzi ̀ gha ̀ nto a ̀ maasi ̀ .
Ŋwos anɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ŋwosi jumɓa , di Saɓa ̀ t a ̀ ri ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ duri . Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kɔnga ̀ ɓi lɛ ɓi ̀ loŋ ɓyɛɛ rɔɓ fɔlɔɔ ɓikpanɛn ɓi kɔrɔs a ̀ kpaŋ ɓi Saɓa ̀ t , lɛ Saɓa ̀ t a ̀ nɛn a ̀ ɓagha ̀ coo go ̀ n i ki ̀ ce ̀ li ̀ . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ tɔka ̀ Pilat lɛ a fa ɓɔ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ ɓɛɛ ɓwingi ɓɔ mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ , ɓɛ ki kɔ ̀ sag yi ɓɔ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ kɔrɔs .
Nni ɓɛsuja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ yugha ̀ ɓɛ ɓungi ̀ mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ mɛ kibog ki ɓi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ kpanga ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ ri Yeesus , ɓɛ ɓungi ̀ ti ̀ mɛ roa ̀ mbog .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kpaga ̀ ɓi Yeesus , ɓɛ tanɛ ̀ n lɛ a ̀ mɛ wu ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓwingi nyi mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ki tuɓka ̀ nyi be ̀ n ɗi ̀ ri ̀ kɔ ̀ ŋ , mɛ ̀ nig ri ̀ bwaɓ ɓi ghas ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a kpaakpaa ɓiɓan ɓi , a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ɓyɔ ( ri ̀ mis ) . Nni com ki a kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ ki ri saaɗ , nyimiɗ a yii lɛ , a kpaakpaa saaɗ lɛ , di mi ̀ ni girig ɓi gherɛn .
Ki kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ fɔlɔɔ lɛ , kɛɛ ɓa yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ nsoo ̀ ki ̀ woɓ kii kifog , ɓaa ɓun ɓi .
Ki ri ti ̀ ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ɓi ja ̀ ŋ idɛŋ lɛ ɓɛ ri pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zii gɛ mis ri ̀ roa ̀ nɛ ɓɛ tuɓka ̀ be ̀ n .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , Yoosɛɓ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a Arimate , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ -yila ̀ g a ̀ Yeesus a ri ̀ nyam lɛ a ̀ riri ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n . Nni a ̀ tɔka ̀ Pilat i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ a teɗ ki ̀ loŋ ki Yeesus , Pilat a ̀ gherɛ ̀ n . Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ , a ̀ teɗ ki ̀ loŋ ki Yeesus .
Nikodɛm a ̀ nɛ a ̀ loka ̀ ki ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus ɗi ̀ i ̀ ru , a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ y gi ̀ rig ; a ̀ ɓanɛ ̀ n yi ̀ bu ̀ tag i ɓyom ɓi ɓi ɓagha ̀ lɛ ɓi kpaŋ ɓɛ ̀ kilo ̀ ri ̀ tin ɗi ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ , ɓi ɓagha ̀ mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ tira ̀ a ̀ re mɛ lɛ : ri ̀ mii ̀ r , ri ̀ a ̀ lo ̀ wɛs .
Nni ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ɓum ki ̀ n ki teka ̀ min kiloŋ ki Yeesus , ɓɛ kagi ̀ kɔ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɓandas , di ɓɛɛ ̀ mi ̀ misi tira ̀ a ̀ re mii ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ nki ̀ la ̀ g di ɓɛ ti ɓii ̀ ɓo ̀ mi mum .
Dɛm idɛŋ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɛ kpanga ̀ Yeesus ɓi kɔrɔs , nni zɔ ̀ ŋ i ̀ nyɔn i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ di ɓɛ ka ɓom ̀ ɓi mum mii ̀ , i ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi dɛm inɛ ̀ n .
Mii ̀ nnɛ ɓɛ ɓomga ̀ Yeesus , ɓisuulɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ di ɓɛ ti ɓii ̀ ɓu ̀ uɓuŋɛ ̀ n Saɓa ̀ t , ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ , zɔ ̀ ŋ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ ja ̀ ŋbog .
Ŋwosi sɔnɗi ̀ sariwa , Marii Madelɛn a ̀ ponga ̀ a zɔ ̀ ŋ ri ̀ ti ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ rii ̀ , a ̀ ghɛn lɛ , gɔ ̀ g i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ŋwɔm wu zɔ ̀ ŋ i ̀ ti m ̀ pisiyɛn .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ree , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ lɛ ri ̀ Simɔn Pyɛɛri , ri ̀ n ̀ -yila ̀ g a ̀ mbog a ̀ nɛ Yeesus a ̀ a nkeesa ̀ g , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓaa pisii Kan ɓi zɔ ̀ ŋ , nni ti ̀ yii ɓi fennɛ ɓaa foŋi nyi .
Nni Pyɛɛri ɓɛɛ ̀ n ̀ -yila ̀ g a ̀ mbog ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɛ kɛn ̀ a zɔ ̀ ŋ .
Ɓɔɔ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ kɛnkɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɗi ̀ mɛ ̀ ree , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , n ̀ -yila ̀ g a ̀ mbog a ̀ fya ̀ ga ̀ Pyɛɛri ɓi mɛ ̀ ree , a ̀ log ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ a zɔ ̀ ŋ ɗi ̀ nyi .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ laŋmɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ a tɛg wɔɔ ɓi ɗu ̀ m , a ̀ ghɛn ɓɛ ̀ ɓanɗas ɓɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ nɔŋiyɛn , wɔ ̀ lɛ a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ɓi zɔ ̀ ŋ .
Nni Simɔn Pyɛɛri a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ y nyi ajɛ ̀ m a ̀ kpaga ̀ , a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ ɓi zɔ ̀ ŋ , a ̀ ghɛn ɓɛ ̀ ɓanɗas ɓɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ nɔŋiyɛn ,
ki ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ki ki ɓagha ̀ Yeesus ɓi nto , kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓa ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɓanɗas , kɔɔ ɓa ki ̀ takakɛn fɔlɔɔ ki nɔ ̀ ŋziyɛn yi ki ̀ pa ̀ s .
Nni n ̀ -yila ̀ g a ̀ mbog a ̀ nɛ a ̀ loka ̀ ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ a zɔ ̀ ŋ , a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ girig , a ̀ ghɛn a ̀ ki gherɛn .
