Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ rɛsi ̀ gha ̀ min ɓum ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ lɛ ri ̀ Yoosɛɓ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɗii lɛ Ɓarisaɓas , nyinnɛ ɓɛ nkpɔgi ̀ ti ̀ lɛ Yustus , ri ̀ Matyas .
Nni ɓɛ ɓɔŋzi ̀ gha ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛ kpaa lɛ : Kan , wɔ ̀ yɛɛ yii mɛ ̀ rem mɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , re ̀ si ɓi ̀ si ghɛn innɛ u ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ni ɓi ɓum ɓɛ kiɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ
lɛ a teɗ i ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu nkɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom wu Zyudas a ̀ a nca ̀ ri , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ teri ̀ wu wu nghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ri ̀ nyi .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ pika ̀ n ̀ tɔ ̀ ŋ ri ̀ mii maa , n ̀ tɔ ̀ ŋ a ̀ kpi ̀ ɓi ɗii ɗi Matyas , ɓɛ ɓas min nyi ri ̀ ki ̀ ntɛ ̀ ɗ ɗi ̀ bog ki ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom kimbog .
Ŋwosi Pa ̀ ŋte ̀ kot , ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ taŋzɛn ja ̀ ŋbog .
Nni ɓɛ sigmɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ , gom i ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ aɗyoo , i ̀ ɓa yɛ ̀ ɛ gom i ̀ coo bɛ ̀ ɓ ki kɛɛ ̀ fɛɛfɛɓsi ̀ , ki yu ki ̀ roni ̀ naa i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ mii ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ ɓyom yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ ro ̀ o ̀ mɛ ɗuu , ɓince ̀ m ɓi ̀ ghasakɛn dɛŋ-dɛ ̀ ŋ-dɛŋ di ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɓɛli ɓɔ ɓi nyo ̀ o ̀ .
Ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓa min ɓɛronɛn ri Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay , ɓɛ ki to ̀ tog ɓito ̀ ki ̀ ɓidɛŋ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Nghay a ̀ fafa ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu lɛ ɓɛɛ toto ̀ g .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɛ falɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ girig a Yorisalɛm , di ɓɛ pɛsaagh yi ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓi ziinɛ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ gom i ̀ nɛ ̀ n i ̀ ki ̀ lɛ ̀ nga ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ɓum ɓɛ ghɛŋmɛ ̀ n yi ̀ nni yɛ ̀ ɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓumɓɛ ̀ n a ̀ woogh di ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ɓɛɛ ̀ to ̀ tog kito ̀ ki ̀ kii , ɓɛ rɔɓ lɛ re ̀ e ̀ ree .
Ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ kuura ̀ ka ̀ ɓɛ rɔɓ myɔm ɓi ̀ kpaŋ . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ tɔɔ ̀ tɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔri ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Nti ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ to ̀ tog ɓɛ , ɓɛ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ a Galile ?
Nni cɛ kɛɛ kii ̀ lɛ , mum bimiɗ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ si a wowog di ɓɛɛ ̀ to ̀ tog kito ̀ ki ̀ kii ?
A ̀ tumɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓɛ ̀ -Paritɛ , ɓɛ ̀ -Mɛɛɗɛ , ɓɛ ̀ -Elamit , ɓumɓɛ a Mɛzopotamii , ri ɓɛ a Zyude ri ̀ ɓɛ a Kapados , ri ̀ ɓɛ a Pɔŋ , ri ̀ ɓɛ a Azii ,
ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ a Firizii , ri ̀ ɓɛ a Paŋfilii , ri ̀ ɓɛ a Egiɓtɛn , ri ̀ ɓɛ ɓi , ki ̀ den ki zi ki a Liɓii ki ki wo ̀ ŋzɛɛ ri ̀ Sirɛn , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ y a Rom , a ̀ teɗ lɛ , Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɔmiɗ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpaŋ lɛ ,
ɓumɓɛ a Kirɛɗɛ , ri ̀ ɓɛ a Araɓii , cɛ kɛɛ kii lɛ , ti wowog yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ kakali da ̀ m yi ɓiɓan yi Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓis ?
Ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ kuura ̀ ka ̀ ; ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗi ɗim ɓɔ , ɓɛ tɔɔ ̀ tɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n ɓɔmiɗ lɛ : Ri ̀ kuu ɗi kiɓan aɗi ɗyɛɛ ̀ ri lɛ ?
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ wɔwɔ ̀ la ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ ŋwaŋɛn mɛrɔ ̀ g lɛ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ .
Nni Pyɛɛri a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ aɗyoo ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ bog , a ̀ kpaa ɓumɓɛ ̀ n jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Mi ̀ ni Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ mini ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓi kɔ ̀ kɔrii a Yorisalɛm , ramina mɛ ̀ ree , ɓi wog ki ̀ ɓan ki nki ̀ ki lɛ , nkpaa ̀ mi ̀ ni :
Ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ŋwaŋi ɓi mɛrɔ ̀ g yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi fe ̀ feg lɔɔ , lɛ mɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ taa ̀ ni ̀ n a ̀ sariwa yɛɛ kaka lɛ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , Bɛ ̀ ll yɛɛ roozii jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi ̀ i ̀ inɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓi ŋwɔm wu n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan wii ̀ a ̀ nɛ lɛ Zyuwɛl lɛ :
Ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ siito ̀ n , n ̀ ɗomigɛy N ̀ ghay wɛ ̀ m ɓi mum bimiɗ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ dɛli ̀ ɓin ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gɔ ̀ n ɓin ɓɛ ɓaa ̀ gɛ ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɔn ɓin ɓɛ ghɛnghɛ ̀ n da ̀ m yi ɓiɓan ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu Nghay a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓi ̀ dɛ ̀ ndɛm ɓi kiki ̀ ɓi ̀ tu ̀ g ɓin ɓi ɓum .
Ɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ! ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ̀ n nfoŋi gɛ N ̀ ghay wɛ ̀ m ɓi ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛm lɛ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛbaŋi ̀ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ lɛ ɓɛɛ kpaŋzi ɓi ̀ ɓan .
Nɗi ki ̀ i gɛ lɛ da ̀ m yi ɓiɓan yɛɛ resɛn ɓi ɗyoo ɓi ɗu ̀ m , ɓɛ ̀ koŋnyoo ɓɛ ɓiɓan ɓɛ kilɛ ̀ n ɓi ziinɛ ; ri ̀ bwaɓ , ri ̀ ɗuu , ri ̀ fi ̀ sili ̀ ɓi ɓaa gɛ ;
ŋ ̀ wos a ̀ suu gɛ ɓi mis yɛ ̀ ɛ biri ̀ m , ŋwii a ̀ lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n m ̀ ɓa ̀ ŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ bwaɓ , di go ̀ n i ri ̀ yu ̀ ɗi Kan i ̀ ka kpaŋ ɓi , yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ɓaa gɛ coo ŋwos a ri ̀ kem ɗii .
Fɔɔnnɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ reŋii gɛ ɗii ɗi Kan lɛ a ghɛɓsi nyi a ̀ ghɛɓi gɛ .
Mi ̀ ni ɓumɓɛ a Isirayɛl , wooghna ki ̀ ɓan ki nki ̀ ki lɛ , nkpaa ̀ mi ̀ ni : Yeesus a ̀ nɛ a Nazarɛt a ̀ a nɗi ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ a n ̀ ɗe ̀ sii mi ̀ ni lɛ , nnyɛɛ romga ̀ y nyi , ɓi da ̀ m yi ɓiɓan , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ koŋnyoo ɓɛ ɓiɓan , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ ɓi a ̀ fagha ̀ nyi i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ a ki ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ ɓi ̀ yii .
Yeesus a ̀ nɛn innɛ ɓɛ nka ̀ ɓi lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ kaliyɛn , lɔŋ yɛɛ ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fe ̀ ka ̀ ɓi coo ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗii , nyi nnɛ ɓi ̀ i nkpani ɓi kɔrɔs aɗyoo , ɓi ̀ ki fa nyi ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe lɛ ɓɛɛ wey .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ a n ̀ ghe ̀ mzii nyi , a ̀ fu ̀ mi ̀ nyi bɛn yi riwu ̀ , lɛ ki n-yin lɛ ki kilɛ ̀ n lɛ , ri ̀ wu ɗyɛɛ ghaatɛn yi ̀ ri ̀ nyi .
Lɛ Davit a ̀ ɓu ̀ ga ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kii yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : N ̀ seese ̀ e ̀ gha ̀ lɔŋ Kan mɛ ̀ asu ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , ɓisuulɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓi wee ̀ lem lɛ m ̀ ɓa kɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ni ̀ ŋdɛ ̀ n .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki n ̀ ɗem wɛ ̀ m wu roni ri ̀ ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ , ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓyɛm ̀ ɓi ki ɓa ɓikpakpag ɓi kinya ̀ a ̀ ; nsoo ̀ nyoo yɛ ̀ m i ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ fɔɔsɛɛ lɛ fyo ̀ oog ri ̀ n ̀ tyweeyi wu n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ wɔ .
Lɛ , wa ̀ a rini ɓi n ̀ ghay wɛ ̀ m a n ̀ yɔ ̀ ɛ ̀ y i ̀ suu ̀ ce ̀ m , kɔ ̀ ɔ ki gherɛn lɛ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say wɔɔ ̀ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tɛnɛn a ɓwɛy ɓi zɔ ̀ ŋ .
U ̀ re ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ bee i ̀ cɛɓ , fɔɔnnɛ ri ̀ ɓa ɗi u ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog , ɗi ri fa mɛ coo kinya ̀ a ̀ .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ n ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni lɛ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Davit a ̀ seŋi wis a n ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ lɛ : A ̀ wugha ̀ , ɓɛ ki ɓo ̀ m nyi , zɔ ̀ ŋ yi ̀ i ̀ i ri ̀ fɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkis a ̀ kpaŋ gɛɛ ̀ nɛ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan a ̀ ki yi n ̀ ka ̀ g wu Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ka ̀ ka ̀ nyi a ̀ ka ̀ nɛ ̀ n bɛ ̀ ɗ lɛ , a ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ sii gɛ do ̀ o ̀ yi ̀ i ̀ idɛŋ ɓi-kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wii wu rila ̀ mi ̀ ,
ri ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi Kiris ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi a ̀ loka ̀ lɔɔ ki ghɛɛ ̀ , a ̀ ki kpaa lɛ : Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ a rini ɓi nyi a nyɔ ̀ ɛ ̀ y , kɛ ̀ ɛ ki ca ̀ ɗ lɛ nyoo yi ̀ i ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓwɛy ɓi zɔ ̀ ŋ .
Yeesus a ̀ nɛ ̀ n nnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ a n ̀ ghe ̀ mzii , ɓi ̀ sii ̀ ce ̀ m ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛ ɓi ri ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗii .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ a mɓɔɔ ki kɔ ̀ rii ɓi wee ̀ lem a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , Seŋi a ̀ a nfaa nyi Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ki a ̀ ka ̀ ka ̀ , kɛɛ ̀ ki a ̀ romii ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi seesee lɛ , ɓi ̀ ki wowog .
Davit a ̀ ɓɔka ̀ ɓi aɗyoo ki ̀ ɓan kifog nyimiɗ a kalag lɛ : Kan Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ka ̀ ligha ̀ Kan wɛ ̀ m lɛ , kɔ ̀ ri mɛ ̀ fɛ ɓi wee ̀ lem
a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ ghaasii ɓɛ ̀ be ̀ na ̀ bena ɓɔɔ com ki , u rɛsag mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ mii ̀ .
Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ a Isirayɛl ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ yii ̀ syeesyee a ̀ ri ̀ yi lɛ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ a n ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ , Yeesus a ̀ nɛ ɓi ̀ i nkpani ɓi kɔrɔs aɗyoo a ɓa lɛ nyi Kan wis , nyi Kiris .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ woka ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓi Pyɛɛri ɓin ̀ , ɓi ɗiŋi ̀ ɓɔ ɓi n ̀ ɗem lɛ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ , nni ɓɛ tɔka ̀ Pyɛɛri ri ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ɓɛm ̀ bog lɛ : Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , ki ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ min lɛ ti ki la ?
Pyɛɛri a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : Lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛɛna mɛ ̀ rem , mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ ɓi mi ̀ ni a ̀ ki ɓa ̀ ɓtɛn ɓi ɗii ɗi Yeesus Kiris fɔɔnnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a cenɛn ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓin , a ̀ ki fa mini Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay .
Lɛ n ̀ ka ̀ g wu Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ka ̀ ka ̀ wu ri ɓisu win , ri ̀ ɓisuu ɓɔn ɓin , wu ki ɓa ti ɓisuu ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ti ̀ ra ̀ ɓ , ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ Kan Bɛ ̀ ll wi ̀ s a ̀ regiigɛy ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ nɛ ki kɔ ̀ ni gɛ nyi lɛ a regii ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Pyɛɛri a ̀ re ̀ re ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ saaɗ , a ̀ ki rereɓ ɓɔ ri ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yidɛŋ yi a ̀ kpaati ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ nwe ̀ e : Pɛ ̀ sɛɛnas ̀ lɛfyɛ ̀ ɗ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓi ri ̀ ɗim ɓi ɗu ̀ m .
Ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ kpaa ɗi Pyɛɛri ɗin ̀ ɓɛ ɓaɓta ̀ ka ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ i ̀ sagtɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , i ̀ ɓagha ̀ nunu ̀ g ɓum ɓɛ ̀ tɔɔsi ̀ m ɓɛraa .
Ɓɛ sii ̀ rɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ri ̀ wowo ̀ g ɗi rire ̀ sa ̀ g ɗi ɓɛkɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom , ri ̀ ɓi cɛɓ ki rigeni , ri ̀ ɓi ri ̀ cusa ̀ g ɗi bi ̀ rɛs , ri ̀ ɓi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n .
I ̀ ris wu ɓanga ̀ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓɔ , lɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ɓɛ kiki ̀ gha ̀ da ̀ m yi ɓiɓan ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ koŋnyoo ɓɛ ɓiɓan , lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ byɔg ki ̀ fog , ɓyom ɓyaa ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓa bu ̀ tag .
Ɓɛ kaka ̀ ɓka ̀ lɛ : Ri ̀ ɓi ̀ den ɓyaa ɓi zi , ri ̀ ɓyom ɓyaa , ɓɛ kaa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɓɛ ̀ n mɔɔ ̀ ni mɛ mii ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , mum bimiɗ a ̀ teki ̀ ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ri ̀ nyi .
Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ n ̀ ti ɓɛ taŋza ̀ g ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll ŋwos bimiɗ , ɓɛ ɗiɗi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓyaa n ̀ ɗaŋ ɓi naa yaa ɓɛ ɗiɗi ̀ ɓyɔ ri ̀ ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ , ri ̀ n ̀ ɗem wu risɛɛ ̀ dɛ ̀ n .
Ɓɛ mɓɔgsa ̀ g Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ki keekee ̀ si ̀ ɓɔ , fɔɔnnɛ Kan a ̀ te ̀ e ̀ ghte ̀ gsi ̀ gha ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ waa ɓɛ ŋwos ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ki kɔnga ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ a ghɛɓsi .
Pyɛɛri ɓɛɛ ̀ Zyaŋ ɓɛ ɓɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ka ̀ a naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n i ̀ mɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛraa a ̀ ŋwos n ̀ kɛ ̀ nɛn .
Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ yalɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ lɛm , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ . Ɓɛ ̀ ŋwos ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , ɓɛ n-yu ̀ la ̀ g nyi ki ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ sii asuunaa wu naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll wu ɓɛ n ̀ ɗegi ̀ lɛ : Rɔɔrɔɔ , lɛ a lɔn ̀ lɔn ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ɗiɗiŋi ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll ɓyom .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ ri ̀ Pyɛɛri ri ̀ Zyaŋ di ɓɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ nkɛn lɛ ɓɛɛ ɗiŋi ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ lɔnga ̀ ɓɔ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni .
Pyɛɛri ri ̀ Zyaŋ ɓɛ ruusi ̀ gha ̀ mis ɓi nyi ɓɛ fiɓi ̀ nyi lɛ fyɛɛɛyi , Pyɛɛri a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ pɛɓsɛn ɓi ̀ si .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ seese ̀ e ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ tɔ ̀ ntɔ ̀ n a ̀ fe ̀ ki ̀ nya lɛ ɓɛ ri nyi ɓii ̀ faa ̀ com .
Pyɛɛri a ̀ Kpaa min nyi lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n-yin ɗi mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni nsoo ̀ gol lɔŋ com ki n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ kɔ kɛɛ ̀ ki n ̀ faa wɔ ̀ : Ɓi ɗii ɗi Yeesus Kiris a ̀ nɛ a Nazarɛt pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyoo u kɛɛ ̀ ghi !
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ɓanga ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓi ca ̀ g ki wee ̀ lem a ̀ pɛ ̀ si ̀ nyi mɛ ̀ rɛy . Lɔŋ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kɔm ̀ kin ̀ , mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ mii , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ le ̀ ŋiɗ mii ɓi ghas ki ̀ teri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ ;
lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ lɛla ̀ gɛ ̀ n bog lɛ doɓta ̀ , a ̀ rɛli mɛ ̀ rɛy a ̀ ghagsɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ . Nni a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ -Pyɛɛri ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll di a kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , a ̀ lɛɛ ̀ lɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ tɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ki keekemzi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Mum bimiɗ a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ gha ̀ di a ɓɔɔɓɔgsi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n yɛɛ nti a ̀ kɔ ̀ ra ̀ g asuunaa wu naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll wu lɛ Rɔɔrɔɔ a ̀ lɔnlɔ ̀ n ɓum ɓyom , nni ɓɛ risi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ki kuurag kiɓan ki ki kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ kin ̀ bi cɛɓ ki ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n , yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Ŋwaa ̀ nce ̀ m a ̀ nɛn a ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ tɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɛ ̀ -Pyɛɛri ɓɛɛ ̀ Zyaŋ , nni ki yeesi ̀ gha ̀ ɓum ri ̀ wog ɓɛ ghɛŋmɛ ̀ n ɓɔ a nyoo ɓi tuu ̀ tuu anɛ ɓɛ nɗegi ̀ lɛ tuu ̀ tuu a ̀ Salomɔŋ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pyɛɛri a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ fɔlɔɔ , nnɛ a ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n lɛ : Mi ̀ ni ɓumɓɛ a Isirayɛl , ɓi cɛ nnɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ri mɛ ̀ kuu ̀ kuugh ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki ? Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓi fifiɓi ɓisi lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ kali lɛ ti ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sii ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wis , nsoo ̀ lɛ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ falɛ ̀ n ɗis ɗi ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ?
Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ Abiraham , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ Isag , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ Yakɔɓ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓis yɛɛ faa n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say wii ̀ a ̀ nɛ lɛ Yeesus ri ̀ kem . Yeesus a ̀ nɛn nnɛ ɓi ̀ i nka ̀ ɓi , ɓi ki roo ̀ zɛn nyi ɓi mis mɛ Pilat a ̀ nɛ a ̀ a m ̀ mɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ lɛ di a ̀ a ca ̀ ri nyi .
Ɓi ̀ i nɗoo ̀ zɛɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ a nɗi ̀ n ̀ tɛnɛn a ̀ ki ɓa ti lɛ saaɗ , ɓi tɔg Pilat lɛ a caɗ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ a nɗi ̀ n ̀ woli ̀ -ɓum .
Ɓi ̀ i ki ̀ i lɛ ɓɛɛ wey ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ la ̀ mii cɛɓ , nyi nnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ a n ̀ ghe ̀ mzii yi ̀ a ɓi ̀ loŋ ; ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛ ɓi ri ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗii .
N ̀ tyweeyi wu ti ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ wɔ ɓi ɗii ɗi Yeesus wɛɛ kii lɛ , ɗii ɗi ̀ n ɗyɛɛ fa mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ mɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓi yii a ̀ nɛ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi seese ̀ e ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ tyweeyi wu ɓi Yeesus wɛɛ kii lɛ , a wɔn ̀ lɛ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi seesee lɔɔ ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Nni ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓɛ ̀ m , n ̀ -yii lɛ ɓi ̀ i n ̀ ki ̀ i fɔlɔɔ lɛ , ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɓin ɓi ̀ i n-yii ɓi ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ɓi bee inɛ ̀ n nnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ a n ̀ doo ̀ zii ki ̀ ɓan ki a ̀ loka ̀ ki kpaa ̀ ɓi myɔm mɛ ɓɛkpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ajɛ ̀ m lɛ : Kiris a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ gɛ ki ̀ woo ̀ gh ri ̀ kɛŋ .
Nni lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛɛna min mɛrem , ɓi sugtii ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , di fɔɔnnɛ a tii ̀ si ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓin .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ Kan a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ romi ̀ i ̀ ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓi rifɔɔsɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ romi ̀ i ̀ n ̀ ghɛɓsi ̀ -ɓum , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ pe ̀ gsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓisu wi ̀ n . Nnyɛɛ ri ̀ Yeesus Kiris .
Yeesus a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ka ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔrii aɗyoo , a ̀ kpaŋ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zii ki rɛsii ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi mɛ ̀ rɛli mɛ ɓyɔ , lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kpaagha ̀ fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ ɓi myɔm mɛ ɓɛkpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓii ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ tɛnɛn .
Fɔɔnnɛ Moyis a ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ lɛ : Kan Bɛ ̀ ll wi ̀ n a ̀ romii ̀ gɛ mi ̀ ni n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓaa gɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ , a ̀ ki ̀ ɓa ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kin , ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ woo ̀ gh com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki a ̀ kalii gɛ mi ̀ ni .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ sɛɛtii gɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan anɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ pisii gɛ nyi ɓi ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɓum ɓɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ , ɓɛ ki wey nyi .
Ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓɔɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɓsɛ ̀ nga ̀ , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n yi ̀ ɓi Samuɛl , ɓɛ ɓuga ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Mi ̀ ni yɛɛ ri ɓɔn ɓɛ ɓɛkpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan , ɓi ̀ ki ɓa ti ɓɔn ɓɛ ɓi ɓee i ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ renga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓi ̀ n , yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ Abiraham lɛ : M ̀ ma ̀ ŋi gɛ naa yi ɓum yi ̀ ce ̀ m yi ɓi ziinɛ ɓi jɛ ̀ m i ̀ do ̀ o ̀ yɔɔ .
Mi ̀ ni yɛɛ ri ɓumɓɛ asu ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ nga ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say wii ̀ ɓisu waa , a ̀ rom yi ̀ nyi , lɛ a maŋ ̀ mi ̀ ni , di a ki lɛ mum bimiɗ a ̀ nɛ ɓi mi ̀ ni a ca ̀ ɗ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓii ɓi mɛki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ .
Ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ , ri ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ sa ̀ du ̀ syɛŋ ɓɛ yugha ̀ y di ɓɛ ̀ -Pyɛɛri ɓɛɛ ̀ Zyaŋ ɓɛɛ ̀ ka to ̀ tog ri ɓum ɓɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ .
Nni ɓɛ woka ̀ bim yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ tanɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ -Pyɛɛri ɓɛɛ ̀ re ̀ resi ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓɛ ɓuŋɓu ̀ ŋ ki ̀ ɓan ki ri ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi Yeesus , ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓiloŋ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ɓanga ̀ ɓɔ ɓɛ pig ɓɔ ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y lɛ ɓɛɛ kɔri wɔɔ a ̀ kpaŋ ɓi duri-tana , lɛ cɛŋko ̀ ki ɓagha ̀ di ki ti .
Nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ki ̀ gwey ki ɓi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ woka ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ki gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n i ̀ kpaga ̀ nunu ̀ g ɓum ɓɛ ̀ tɔɔsi ̀ m ɓɛtan ̀ .
Ɓi duri-tana , ɓɛ ̀ la ̀ nlam ɓɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓaa , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓɛ taŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Yorisalɛm
ɗi ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n-ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey a ̀ nɛ ̀ lɛ Ann , ri ̀ Kayif , ri ̀ Zyaŋ , ri ̀ Alɛgsaŋdirɛ ri ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓi naa ̀ -ɓum i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ rɛsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ -Pyɛɛri ɓɛɛ ̀ Zyaŋ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wa ̀ a ̀ , ɓɛ tɔg ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi-te ̀ ɗ aɗi , n ̀ soo ̀ lɛ ̀ ɓi ɗii ɗi ̀ ghɛn innɛ ɓi ̀ i nwɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zii ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n ?
Nni Pyɛɛri , n ̀ ɗonɛn ri Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki N ̀ ghay , a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ a Isirayɛl ,
yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ mɛ tɔg ɓisi gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓi ki ̀ rɔɔ ki ki ̀ sɛkɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ ki mum ki ntanɛɛ ri ̀ kɔ , lɛ ti resi yɛ ̀ ɛ ki mɓaa lɛ a wɔn ̀ ,
ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ yii ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Isirayɛl ki yi girig lɛ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ rɛrɛlii mi ̀ ni asu fɛlɛ lɛ syeesyee ɓi nyoo yi ̀ i ̀ , lɛ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu ɗii ɗi Yeesus Kiris a ̀ nɛ a Nazarɛt , a ̀ nɛ ɓi ̀ i nkpani ɓi kɔrɔs aɗyoo , nyi nnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ a n ̀ ghe ̀ mzii yi ̀ a ɓi ̀ loŋ .
Yeesus a ̀ ri ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ gɔ ̀ g i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ̀ toŋi ̀ -mɛɛ ɓɛ maka ̀ , yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ghala ̀ ki ̀ le ̀ mi ̀ ki n ̀ tɔn a ̀ mɛɛ .
Mum a ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ri ̀ cɛɓ lɛ nyi , ɓisuulɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ ɓi ɓum ɗii ɗidɛŋ fɛ ɓi ziinɛ ɗi ɗi ri ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ , ɗi fa ɓi ̀ si cɛɓ .
Ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yɔɔ ̀ yɔ ̀ mzi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ -Pyɛɛri , ɓɛ kuura ̀ ka ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ , Pyɛɛri ri ̀ Zyaŋ ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓag ɓɔ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ ris ɓi n ̀ ɗem , ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ di ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓum ɓɛ zɛy ɓɛ ɓɛ yigha ̀ ɓi su ̀ kuru ̀ , ɓɛ yi min lɛ , ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ kɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ gha ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ ɗi Yeesus .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ wɔ ̀ nga ̀ a ̀ nɛn a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓɔ ɓi nwɔŋi ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ rɔɓka ̀ ɓɛ kɛɛ ̀ yi com ki ɓɛɛ pɛɛ ̀ zi ɓɛ ̀ -Pyɛɛri .
Nni ɓɛ tɔka ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ ka kpaŋzi ɓɔ ɓi ɗyɔ ̀ m di ɓɔɔ rɔ ̀ ɓ ki ̀ nyolɛɛ ɓɔri ̀ ɓɔ , lɛ ɓɛɛ teɗ bimiɗ a ̀ n ̀ ɗɛli ɓi ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ .
Ɓɛ tɔɔ ̀ tɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ : Ti ki la ri ɓumɓɛ ? Lɛ , ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ a Yorisalɛm ɓɛ mɛ yi lɛ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n lɛ , ɓɔ yɛɛ nki ̀ i da ̀ m i ̀ ki ̀ ɓan i ̀ nɛ , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ sii ki yin lɛ ti ̀ teɗ nyoey lɛ ɓɔ yɛɛ nki ̀ i ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ .
Nni ɓi ɗi lɛ ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓiisɛn ki sa ̀ a , ti rɔ ̀ gsɛɛna ɓɔ lɛ , i ɓɛ kpaatii mum ki ̀ ɓan ki ki rarɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ ɗii ɗi Yeesus di ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ ti ̀ min ɓɔ , ɓɛ ree ̀ g ɓɔ i ̀ suu ̀ ce ̀ m lɛ , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓu ̀ ŋdi ɗii ɗi Yeesus , ɓɛ kɛɛ ̀ ki re ̀ resiti ɓum ɗii din ̀ .
Ɓɛ ̀ -Pyɛɛri ɓɛɛ ̀ Zyaŋ ɓɛ ɓaa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : Ghɛɛna mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ , n ̀ ko ̀ o ki ri lɛ saaɗ ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ , ti ki mi ̀ ni mɛ ̀ wog a ̀ cee Bɛ ̀ ll .
Lɛ ɓi ̀ sii yin lɛ ti ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓ lɛ ti ̀ kpaa ɓi kiɓan ki ti ghɛnga ̀ , ti ̀ ki wog .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ mzi ̀ -ɓɔ , ɓɛ sagɛ ̀ nga ̀ ti ̀ ɓɔ , ɓɛ ki caɗ min ɓɔ , di ɓɛ mɛ rɔɓ ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ yi yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛɛ pɔnɔ ̀ si ɓɔ ɓisuulɛ , ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki kee ̀ ke ̀ mzi ̀ gha ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓisuu da ̀ m i ̀ ki ̀ ɓan inɛ ̀ n .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ wɔ ̀ nga ̀ da ̀ m i ̀ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ n a ̀ nɛn , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a mɛ cee be ̀ g mɛ ̀ tin mɛɓɛɛ ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ caɗka ̀ y ɓɛ ̀ -Pyɛɛri ɓɛɛ ̀ Zyaŋ , ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ ki ̀ tanɛɛ ɓɛgeni ɓaa , ɓɛ kali ɓɔ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓɛ rɔgsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ lɛ , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ti .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ woka ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ nni ɓɔɔ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ pɛsi ̀ gha ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ ɓɛ ɓɔŋzi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ : Kan , wɔ ̀ yɛɛ kigha ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ɗyoo , ri ̀ zi , ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓi ri mii ̀ ;
wɔ ̀ yɛɛ kpaagha ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu Kitɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay , ɓi ŋwɔm wu seŋi wi ̀ s Davit a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say wɔɔ ̀ lɛ : Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓɛ ̀ nyu ̀ u ̀ ghnyu ̀ u ̀ gh ɓɛ ri fɛlɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ? Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi taŋzɛɛ ɓi ̀ tɔ ̀ kɔ ̀ ɓi zɛy ri ̀ zɛy ?
Mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m mɛgwey mɛ ɓi ziinɛ mɛ ramii ̀ wɛ ̀ y , mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m mɛ sa ̀ gsa ̀ g mɛ ɓasɛ ̀ n yi ̀ ki ̀ byɔg ki ̀ fog lɛ mɛɛ ɗuu ̀ ri ̀ Kan , ri ̀ Me ̀ sii wii ̀ .
Ɓi saaɗ , ɗi ̀ Eroodɛ ri ̀ Pɔŋs-Pilat ɓɛ mɓasɛɛ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ke ̀ n , ri mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ a Isirayɛl ɓi ban i ̀ nɛ , lɛ ɓɛɛ ɗuu ̀ ri ̀ Yeesus a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say wɔɔ ̀ a ̀ n ̀ tɛnɛn a ̀ nɛ u ̀ rɛsi ̀ gha ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi u ̀ loka ̀ ki ̀ fe ̀ egh ɓi-te ̀ ɗ wɔɔ , ri ̀ ɓi ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗyɔɔ lɛ ɓi ri ɓii ̀ ki ̀ lɛɛ , ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓi ɓɛ nɗoo ̀ zii lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Nni ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , Kan , ghɛna yɛɛ ̀ ɓɛɛ ̀ sa ̀ asagɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ si , di ̀ u fa ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɔɔ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ , ɓɛɛ ghagsi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ghɛɛsii kice ̀ m .
Na ̀ mas ̀ ca ̀ g kɔɔ lɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ ̀ wɔ ̀ nwɔn ti ̀ roɓ , ɓɛ ̀ koŋnyoo ri da ̀ m yi ɓiɓan ɓi kii ̀ ki ̀ lɛ ̀ n ɓi ɗii ɗi Yeesus a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say wɔɔ a ̀ ntɛnɛn .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ legsi ̀ gha ̀ bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n ya ̀ a ̀ inɛ ̀ n , mɛɛ mɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ ɓɛtaŋzɛn mɛ nyɛŋɗɛ ̀ nga ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ronga ̀ ri ̀ Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay , ɓɛ ki ghaaghagsi ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ ntyweeyi ɓi n ̀ ɗem .
N ̀ ɗaŋ wu ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n wu ɓagha ̀ n ̀ ɗem wu ̀ fog , ɓɛ ̀ fe ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ fog , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓɔ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ lɛ a ̀ kali ̀ lɛ ɓyom ɓi a ̀ ri ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓyɔ ɓi ri ɓiŋkii cɛ ̀ ncii , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓyom ɓyaa ɓi ɓagha ̀ ɓisu waa ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ɓɛkɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ ɓum ki ̀ ɓan ki righe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi Kan Yeesus ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ lɛɛ ̀ gwey , fɔɔnnɛ coo geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ ronga ̀ a ɓɔɔ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ yɛɓɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi com ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wa ̀ a ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ dɛm , ri ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ mɛɛ ɓɛ kaka ̀ ɓka ̀ ɓyom ɓi ̀ n , ɓɛ yuyu ̀ ri ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɛ mii ̀
ɓɛ fafa ̀ mɔ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom , ɓɛ kaɓsa ̀ g mɔ yɛ ̀ ɛ mum bimiɗ a teɗ ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɗi nyi ...
Yoosɛɓ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi boo i ̀ ɓum i ̀ Levi i ̀ nɛ ɓi ban i ̀ nɛ lɛ Siipirɛ , nyi nnɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ɓɛ nkpɔgi ̀ lɛ Ɓarinaɓas , yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ -mɛ ̀ fegsɛn ,
a ̀ ka ̀ ɓka ̀ dɛm inɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ yɔ ̀ , a ̀ yu ̀ ki ̀ faa ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɛ mii ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ ɗii lɛ , Ananyas ɓɛɛ ̀ Safira a ̀ giy ɓɛ Kaɓka ̀ ki ̀ den kaa ki zi .
Nni Ananyas a ghaɓi ̀ gha ̀ ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ki faa ̀ ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ mbog ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ; giy a yigha ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Pyɛɛri a ̀ kaligha ̀ Ananyas lɛ : Ananyas , Sata ̀ n a ra ̀ gɛɛ ɓa ̀ wɔ ri n ̀ ɗem fɛlɛ lɛ cɛ yɔ ? U ̀ pwa ̀ a Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay u ̀ nyam ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni i ̀ nɛ ɓi kiden ki zi ki wɔ ̀ ɔ n ̀ ka ̀ ɓi ?
Yɛ ̀ ɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ nka kaɓ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ̀ n , i ̀ i n ̀ ɗi ̀ ja ̀ ŋ yɔɔ ̀ , yɛ ̀ ɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ nki ka ̀ ɓi yɔ ̀ , mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɛ mii ̀ mɛ ri ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɔɔ , nni fe ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ u ki ri ̀ kuu ɗi kiɓan ɗi u ̀ ki ̀ i ɗi , a ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ wɔ ̀ fe ? Yiti lɛ : A ̀ a ɓum ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ u ̀ pwa ̀ a , lɔŋ Bɛ ̀ ll innɛ u ̀ pwa ̀ a .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Ananyas a ̀ woka ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓi Pyɛɛri ɓin ̀ , nni a ̀ kpi ̀ gha ̀ , a ̀ wu . Fɔɔnnɛ coo iris wu ɓanga ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ woka ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ .
Ɓɛ ̀ dɛli ̀ ɓɛ ɓum ɓɛ yugha ̀ y ri ̀ com ki lɛ , ɓɛɛ lɔg kiloŋ kii mii ̀ , ɓɛ pɛsi ̀ min kɔ , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ki ̀ ɓo ̀ mi .
Di ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kaa ghaa ̀ gh fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ hawo ̀ ɓɛraa , nnɛ gili Ananyas a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ y , kɛ ̀ ɛ yi com ki ki kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ .
Nni Pyɛɛri a ̀ tɔka ̀ nyi lɛ : Kali ɓa ̀ mɛ , mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m mɛ ɓi zi inɛ ɓi ̀ i nka ̀ ɓi mɛɛ ri lɛ ? Giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : Ɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɔ yɛɛ ri lɔɔ mɛce ̀ m .
Nni Pyɛɛri a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : Cɛ kɛɛ yaa ki ̀ i lɛ ɓi woo ̀ ghrɛn jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ lɛ , ɓi fee ̀ ghrɛn Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ki Kan ? Ghɛna , ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓomii ̀ yii wɔɔ ̀ ɓɛɛ ti lɛ asuunaa , ɓɛɛ teɗ wɔ ̀ girig .
Bi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kɔm ̀ kin ̀ innɛ a ̀ gha ̀ ska ̀ ki ̀ kpi ̀ i a mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ mɛ Pyɛɛri , a ̀ wu . Ɓɛ ̀ dɛli ̀ ɓɛ ɓum ɓɛ ɗiŋi ̀ i ̀ , ɓɛ tanɛ ̀ n nyi ki ̀ loŋ , ɓɛ pɛsi ̀ nyi , ɓɛ kɛn ki ̀ ɓo ̀ mi ɓi n ̀ wɔŋi ̀ wu zɔ ̀ ŋ i ̀ yii wii ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ coo iris wu ɓanga ̀ ki ̀ seŋi ki ̀ ce ̀ m ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ woka ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ .
Ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ɓɛ kiki ̀ gha ̀ da ̀ m , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ koŋnyoo ɓɛ ɓiɓan lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ . Ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ n ̀ ti ɓɛ rɛla ̀ g n ̀ ɗaŋ ɓi tuu ̀ tuu a ̀ nɛ ɓisuunaa wu naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll wu Salomɔŋ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghɛɛsi ̀ gha ̀ lɛ a rarɛn ɗi ̀ ɓɔ , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ̀ , nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ ɓum ɓɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ ɓɛ sɛsɛ ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Fɔɔnnɛ ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yuyu ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ gherɛɛ Kan , lɛ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɗi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ baŋi ̀ i ̀ ɓɔɓɔ ̀ ka ̀ mɓɔɓɔghɛn .
Nni ɓɛ yuyu ̀ gha ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roroɓ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓa ̀ a ̀ , ɓɛ nɔŋza ̀ g ɓɔ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ kon ri ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ra ̀ lɛ , i Pyɛɛri a ̀ ti ɓii ̀ ghaghii , nsoo ̀ ci ̀ i ̀ ziŋ kii ki kom roa ̀ dɛŋ .
Ɓi ̀ tuu ɓi ɓum ɓi ɓi ba ̀ n yi ɓi mɛ ̀ wɔŋi ̀ , ɓi yuyu ̀ y a Yorisalɛm ɗi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roroɓ , ɗi ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay ɓi yee ̀ ye ̀ e ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ , ɓɛ ki wɔ ̀ ɔwɔɔ ̀ zi ̀ ɓɔ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ m ̀ ɛn ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey , ri ɓumɓɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ , ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi n ̀ ɗaŋ wu Ɓɛ ̀ sa ̀ du ̀ syɛŋ ɓɛ woka ̀ bim lɛɛ ̀ gwey ri ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom .
Ɓɛ ɓangi ̀ ɓɔ , ɓɛ pig ɓɔ ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y .
Nni ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a ̀ Kan a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ ru , a ̀ nɛmgi ̀ mɛ ̀ suunaa mɛ naa ̀ -za ̀ y , a ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom , a ̀ ki kali ɓɔ lɛ :
Kɛ ̀ ɛna ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓi kakali ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓi komi cɛɓ ki .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ woka ̀ fɔlɔɔ , nni ɓɛ ponga ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ n ɓum ɗi ̀ re ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ɗi ɓiɓan ɓin ̀ . Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey , ri ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ wii wu ɓum ɓɛ yugha ̀ y , ɓɛ reŋɗɛ ̀ n n ̀ taŋzɛn wu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n wu lɛ Sa ̀ ne ̀ di ̀ rɛŋ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ a Isirayɛl , ɓɛ rom min ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ yi ̀ ki ̀ teri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ kpaga ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ tanɛn ɓɔ wɔɔ , nni ɓɛ sugti ̀ gha ̀ y ki ̀ kalii ɓumɓɛ ɓi Sa ̀ ne ̀ di ̀ rɛŋ lɛ :
Ti ̀ tanɛɛ yi ̀ lɔŋ naa ̀ -za ̀ y n ̀ ɗogakɛn lɛ gba ̀ g-gba ̀ a ̀ g . Ɓɛ ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ naa ̀ -za ̀ y ɓɛ ̀ rɛrɛliyɛn lɔŋ a mɛ ̀ suunaa wɔ ̀ lɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ŋwa ̀ ri mɛ ̀ suunaa , tyɛ ̀ ki tanɛn mum ɓi ɗu ̀ m nsoo ̀ bog .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll ɗi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ɓɛ woka ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ki yeesi ̀ ɓɔ lannɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ɓɛ kigha ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ sili ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y . Ɓɛ tɔɔ ̀ tɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n lɛ : Ki ̀ ɓan ki ki ri ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ la ?
Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ y ɓɔ ki ̀ kalii lɛ : Ɓi ̀ ghɛɛ , ɓumɓɛ ɓi ̀ i n ̀ foŋi ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y , ɓɛ ri ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ri ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɗi ɓum .
Nni n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ , ɓɛ teɗ yi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom , lɛ tɛ ̀ tɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , lɛ ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɔmiɗ ɓɛ riri ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ɓum ɓɛ ri ɓɔ ɓii ̀ rogii gɔ ̀ g .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ yugha ̀ y ri ̀ ɓɔ a Sa ̀ ne ̀ di ̀ rɛŋ , n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓɔ ri ̀ tɔg ɗi mɛtɔɔ ̀ tɔɔgh
a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ti ti ̀ i n ̀ ɗɔ ̀ gsɛɛ mi ̀ ni syeesyee a ̀ ri ̀ rɔ ̀ gsɛ ̀ n lɛ , kɛ ̀ ɓi re ̀ si ti mum ɗii di ̀ n ? Nni ghɛɛna com ki ɓi ̀ ki ̀ i , ɓi ̀ sa ̀ a ̀ tii ri ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ɗin ̀ ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ Yorisalɛm bimiɗ , ɓi ki ̀ kɔ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ di ɓya ̀ a saghii ɓi ̀ si ri ̀ wu ɗi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓi n ̀ to .
Nni Pyɛɛri ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ɓɛ ɓaka ̀ lɛ : Bɛ ̀ ll nnɛ mum a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ i mɛwog , a ̀ cee ɓum .
Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓi ̀ s a ̀ a n ̀ ghe ̀ mzii Yeesus a ̀ nɛ ɓi ̀ i n ̀ woli di ɓi kpani ɓi kɔrɔs .
Nyi nnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ a m ̀ pɛ ̀ sii aɗyoo , ri ̀ wee ̀ lem wi ̀ i ̀ , lɛ a ɓa lɛ , nyi ri ̀ fo ̀ m , nyi n ̀ ghɛɓsi ̀ -ɓum a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ nɛmi ̀ Isirayɛl bee i ̀ nɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛn mɛ ̀ rem di Bɛ ̀ ll a cenɛn ɓɔ ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓyaa .
Ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si , ri ̀ Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ a n ̀ ɗomii ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki nyi mɛ ̀ wog .
Fɔɔnnɛ bim i ki ̀ gha ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓi n ̀ taŋzɛn win ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ woka ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓin ̀ , ɓɛ feg lɛ ɓɛɛ cuusi ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ,
wɔ ̀ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ ɓi n ̀ ɗaŋ wu Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɗii lɛ Gamalyɛl , n ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ kuura ̀ ka ̀ , a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ aɗyoo ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ Sa ̀ ne ̀ di ̀ rɛŋ , a ̀ tɔg lɛ ɓɛɛ ka kpaŋzi ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ɓidan .
A ̀ kpaa min ɓum ɓɛ n ̀ taŋzɛn lɛ : Mi ̀ ni ɓumɓɛ a Isirayɛl , konaaghna ri ̀ com ki ɓi fe ̀ feg kin ̀ lɛ ɓi ki ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ;
lɛ , ki ka finɛn ɓi ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ lɛ Tedas a ̀ peegha ̀ y fɛ a ̀ ye ̀ e ̀ ghye ̀ gsi ̀ ɓum lɛ nyii ri ̀ bimiɗ a ̀ mum a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛ nɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ nyi nunu ̀ g ɓum ɓɛ ̀ hɔnɗɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛnin , nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ wola ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ nɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ nyi ɓɛ sani ̀ , com ki ɓɛ mɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ kɔɔ duŋɛ ̀ n fɔlɔɔ .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ Tedas , ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ki ̀ lɛ ̀ nga ̀ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a Galile lɛ Zyudas a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ y , a ̀ syo ̀ ŋ ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey , nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ wooti ̀ gha ̀ nyi , ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ a ̀ syo ̀ ga ̀ ɓɛn ̀ ɓɛ sani ̀ .
Nni mɛ ̀ n ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni ɓigomi ̀ nɛ lɛ : kɛ ̀ ɓi fifiɓi ti ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓumɓɛ , ca ̀ rina gi ̀ ɓɔ , ɓɛɛ ghaagh ; ɓisuulɛ i ki ri lɛ mum yɛɛ faa bɔ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗin ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ kaa ghay ɓi .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , i Bɛ ̀ ll yɛɛ n ̀ faa ɓɔ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗin ̀ , ɓya ̀ a ghɛn ɓi bee inɛ lɛ ɓi yogsi ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ . Konaaghna lɛ , kɛ ̀ ɓi ki ram wɛ ̀ y ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓum ɓɛmbog ɓɛ sɛka ̀ ri ̀ kpaa ɗi Gamalyɛl ɗin ̀ , nni ɓɛ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ y ti ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom , ɓɛ ɓog ɓɔ ɓi ki ̀ to ̀ n , ɓɛ rɔgsɛ ̀ n ɓɔ lɛ , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ kpaati ɓum ki ̀ ɓan ki Yeesus , ɓɛ ki ca ̀ ɗ min ɓɔ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ y a Sa ̀ ne ̀ di ̀ rɛŋ ɗi ̀ coo ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ ɓi nɗem lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ a n ̀ ghɛɛ lɛ , ki ri ̀ syeesyee a ̀ kiɓan lɛ , ɓɔɔ ghɛn mɛ ̀ tɔɓ lɛ , ɗii ɗi Yeesus .
Nni fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ fɔla ̀ ɓi rire ̀ si ̀ , ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ghagsi ̀ ɗi Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ Yeesus Kiris ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , ɗi ̀ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ naa ɓaa ɓɛŋwos ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ , yɛ ̀ ɛ ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n i ̀ te ̀ e ̀ ghte ̀ ghɛ ̀ nga ̀ nni ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ toto ̀ ka ̀ ri ̀ gi ̀ rɛg ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ cɛɛ ̀ cɛ ̀ mdɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓɛroɓɛ ɓɛ toto ̀ ka ̀ ki ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ki Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , ɓisuulɛ ɓɛ n ̀ ti ɓɛ ɗimza ̀ g mɛ ̀ kpɔɓ maa ɓi ka ̀ ɓ a ̀ ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ n ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ ŋwos ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ɗi ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ taŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ ristɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ kpaa lɛ : Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi lɛ , ti caɗ ri ̀ ghagsi ̀ ɗi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , lɛ ti kaa ̀ ka ̀ ɓsi ̀ ɓum ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g .
Fɔɔnnɛ mi ̀ ni ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ni ɓum taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m win ̀ , ɓɛ ɓum ɓɛ yii lɛ , ɓɛ rɔɔtaagh ɓi ̀ syɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ɓɛ ki ɓa ɓɛronɛn ɗi ̀ Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay , ri ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n , ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ ti fa ki ̀ say ki rika ̀ ɓsi ̀ ɗi ɓiɗila ̀ g .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ sii ri ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ asu , ti ̀ si ̀ i ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɓi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ghagsi ̀ ɗi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Fe ̀ g a ̀ nɛn a ̀ kɔ ̀ nga ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ wu ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n wu ̀ ce ̀ m nni ɓɛ ɓɔnga ̀ min lɛ , ri ̀ Ityɛn a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ coo righerɛ ̀ n a ̀ ki ɓati n ̀ ɗonɛn ri Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay , ri ̀ Filiɓ , ri ̀ Pikɔɔri , ri ̀ Nikanɔɔri , ri ̀ Timɔŋ , ri ̀ Parimenas , ri ̀ Nikola a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ a Aŋtyos , a ̀ ki lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛn a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n .
Nni ɓɛ yugha ̀ y ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ kitaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , ɓɛ resi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom , ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom , ɓɛ ɓɔŋza ̀ g Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓɛ ki saaghra ̀ g ɓɔ ɓya ̀ g ɓi nyo ̀ o ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ asu di yɛ ̀ ɛ sa ̀ a ̀ sa ̀ a ̀ , ɓa ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n i ̀ ki ɓɔg lɛɛ ̀ gwey a Yorisalɛm , ki ̀ gwey ki ɓɛpi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ki ki foŋ n ̀ tyweeyi ɓi Yeesus .
Ityɛn a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ ɗonɛn lɛ , ri ̀ geesɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ koŋnyoo ɓɛ ɓiɓan , ri ̀ da ̀ m yi ɓiɓan ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ɓum i ̀ dɛŋ i ̀ nɛ ɓi naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n , i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ naa i ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ka ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kpa ̀ n , ɓɛ nyoo ̀ nyo ̀ lɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ Ityɛn , ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi lɛ : ri ̀ Sirɛn ri ̀ Alɛgsaŋdirii , ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ a Silisii , ri ̀ ɓɛ a Azii .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi lɛ , ɓɛ yagsa ̀ g Ityɛn ɓi nyoey , ɓisuulɛ , nyii toto ̀ ka ̀ ri ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗi Kitɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ki fafa ̀ gha ̀ nyi .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ laki ̀ ya ̀ ɓum lɛ ɓɛɛ kpaa ̀ lɛ : Ti ̀ i nwoogh di Ityɛn a feefengi ̀ Moyis , a ̀ fee ̀ fe ̀ ngi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ɓɛ kigha ̀ lɛ ɓum ɓɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna , ɓɛɛ wog bim , ɓɛ yu ɓɛ sɛn ɓi Ityɛn , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi a Sa ̀ ne ̀ di ̀ rɛŋ .
Ɓɛ kɛɛ ̀ di ̀ wɔɔ ri ɓɛ ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓɛ pwaapwa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ Ityɛn ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi nyoo di ɓɛɛ kpaakpaa lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ri ̀ fen ɗi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Moyis .
Ti ̀ i n ̀ woogh di a kakali lɛ : Yeesus a ̀ nɛ a Nazarɛt a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ wa ̀ a ̀ ghii ja ̀ ŋ inɛ , a ̀ ki cenɗag ɓidɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Moyis a ̀ fagha ̀ ɓi ̀ si .
Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ki ̀ kpana ̀ ki ɓɛyɔ ̀ m ɓɛ pɛɛzi ̀ gha ̀ mis di ̀ Ityɛn , ɓɛ ki ghɛn lɛ i ̀ su wii wɛɛ ̀ lo ̀ nlom yɛ ̀ ɛ wu ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a Bɛ ̀ ll .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ kɔmɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey a ̀ tɔka ̀ min lɛ : Ki ri nya saaɗ fɔlɔɔ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kpaa ?
Ityɛn a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : Mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓɛ ̀ m , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓɛ ̀ m , ramina mɛ ̀ ree ɓi konag ki ̀ woo ̀ gh lɛ : Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ keŋke ̀ mi ̀ a ̀ re ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Abiraham a ̀ seŋi wi ̀ s a n ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki a ̀ ɓagha ̀ a Mɛzopotamii , di a ̀ ka kɛn ɓi ki kɔ ̀ rii a Haraŋ .
A ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Pɛ ̀ sɛn ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kɔɔ , u ki ghasɛn ɗi naa yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ i ɓum , u kɛn ̀ ki ̀ kɔ ̀ rii ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki n ̀ ɗi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ re ̀ sii .
Nni Abiraham a ̀ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ min ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki lɛ Kalde , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ kɔ ̀ rii a Haraŋ . Wɔɔ nnɛ ki ɓaa lɛ , seŋi wi ̀ i ̀ a ̀ mɛ wu , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ , a syaa ̀ yi ̀ ɓi ki ̀ la ̀ na ̀ ki zi ki ɓi ̀ ri ̀ mii ̀ ki gɛɛ ̀ nɛ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ ɓi nyi nsoo ̀ maa ki ̀ den a ̀ ja ̀ ŋ a ̀ nɛ a woo ̀ ghrɛn ɗi ̀ nyi ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ̀ n , nsoo ̀ maa zyo ̀ na ̀ a ̀ zɛy ri ̀ zɛy , wɔ ̀ lɛ , a ̀ ka ̀ ka ̀ nyi lɛ , a ̀ ri faa gɛ nyi zi inɛ ̀ n , lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ woo ̀ ghrɛn ri ̀ nyi ̀ nsoo ̀ nyaa ki yii ̀ di , do ̀ o ̀ yii yi rɔɓ ri ̀ yɔ ̀ ; Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ Abiraham n ̀ ka ̀ g win ̀ fɔlɔɔ di a ̀ ka yin ri ma ̀ n .
Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : Do ̀ o ̀ yɔɔ yi kɔ ̀ rii gɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kidɛŋ , wɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ghaasii gɛ yɔ ɓɛ ̀ kpa ̀ n , ɓɛ ki tɔɓ yɔ , be ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ hɔnɗɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛnin .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki ki ghaasii gɛ ɓɔ ɓɛ ̀ kpa ̀ n kin ̀ , lɔŋ mɛ ̀ yɛɛ yɔ ̀ mi gɛ kɔ ; ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn ɓɛ ri pɛ ̀ sɛɛ gɛ wɔɔ , ɓɛ yu mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ɓɔɔɓɔgsi ̀ fɛ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ i ̀ nɛ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ Abiraham kɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɓi si ̀ g a ̀ ki ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ ki bee inɛ a ̀ renga ̀ ɓɛɛ ̀ nyi . Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ yali min Isag , a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɗ nyi ɓi mɛ ̀ ru taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ . Isag a ̀ yay Yakɔɓ , a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɗ girig nyi , Yakɔɓ a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɗki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓis ɓɛ ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ɗi ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓis ɓɛ ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ɗem wu ya ̀ aka ri Yoosɛɓ a ̀ geni wa ̀ a ̀ , nni ɓɛ ka ̀ ɓka ̀ nyi a Egiɓtɛn .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ga ̀ m ɗi ̀ nyi , a ̀ kwe ̀ ɗ nyi ɓi mɛ ̀ tɔɓ mii mɛce ̀ m ; a ̀ fagha ̀ nyi ɗyomzɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ki ki ̀ lɛ Farawɔŋ , ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi a Egiɓtɛn , ɗyɛɛ kee ̀ si nyi , ɗi ki ɓɔgsi nyi gɔmi ̀ na ̀ a Egiɓtɛn , ri ̀ ɓi naa yi ̀ i ̀ bimiɗ .
Fɔɔnnɛ coo za ̀ y i ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki a Egiɓtɛn ki ̀ ce ̀ m ri ̀ ki a Kanaaŋ . Ntɔɓ wu ceegha ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓis , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ghɛɛ ̀ di com ki ɗiyɛn .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yakɔɓ a ̀ woka ̀ lɛ ge ̀ ŋ i ̀ ri ̀ a Egiɓtɛn , nni a ̀ romga ̀ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓis wɔɔ , ɓi gɛ ̀ n i n ̀ tonto .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kɛɛdi ̀ gha ̀ wɔɔ ɓi gɛ ̀ n i ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , Yoosɛɓ a ̀ ki ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓɛɛ remi nyi , fɔɔnnɛ Farawɔŋ a ̀ yigha ̀ min ri ̀ fuuyi ̀ ɗi Yoosɛɓ .
Nni Yoosɛɓ a ̀ romga ̀ min lɛ ɓɛɛ teɗ yi ̀ , Yakɔɓ a ̀ seŋi , ri ̀ naa yi ̀ i ̀ i ɓum i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓum mɛ ̀ tin mɛraa ri ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ɗi ̀ ɓɛtan ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yakɔɓ a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ min a Egiɓtɛn wɔɔnnɛ nyimiɗ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓis ɓɛ ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn , ɓɛ cuugha ̀ .
Nni ɓɛ tɛka ̀ ɓi ̀ loŋ ɓyaa , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓyɔ a Sikɛm , ɓɛ ɓom ɓyɔ ɓi zɔ ̀ ŋ i ̀ nɛ Abiraham a ̀ la ̀ ka ̀ wɔɔ n ̀ la ̀ ghɛn , ri ɓɔn ɓɛ Emɔɔr .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a roo ̀ zi n ̀ ka ̀ g wu a ̀ ka ̀ ka ̀ Abiraham ki kɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ gha ̀ y , ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɓum ɓis ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ a Egiɓtɛn i ̀ te ̀ e ̀ ghte ̀ ghɛ ̀ nga ̀ , ɓɛ ki yaayay ti
a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗiɗɛŋ ɗi ɗi yigha ̀ ɓi Yoosɛɓ ɗi teka ̀ ri ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ a Egiɓtɛn .
Ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗin ̀ ɗyɛɛ ɓee ̀ ɓe ̀ e ̀ zɛ ̀ nga ̀ boo yi ̀ s ɓi mɛ ̀ ghe ̀ y ɗi ki tɔ ̀ ɓ ɓɔ le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ , ɓɛ n ̀ ka ̀ gi ̀ ɓɔ lɛ , ɓɛɛ maa ̀ g ɓɔn ɓaa , lɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ghɛɓ .
Ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ innɛ Moyis a ̀ yalɛɛ ; a ̀ ɓagha ̀ rɔɔrɔɔ a ̀ man a ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ Keesi ̀ gha ̀ ; ɓɛ ̀ yali ̀ ɓii ɓɛ ɓega ̀ nyi naa ri ̀ naa , a ̀ kpaŋ ɓɛ ̀ ŋwii ɓɛraa .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ rini ̀ gha ̀ nyi , fɔɔnnɛ gɔ ̀ n i ̀ Farawɔŋ i ̀ ɓadɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi , i ̀ tɔɔsi ̀ nyi lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ man wii ̀ .
Ɓumɓɛ a Egiɓtɛn ɓɛ resa ̀ ka ̀ Moyis ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kaa ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ te ̀ ete ̀ ɗ ki mum lɛ , ri ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓii , ri ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ mii .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kpaga ̀ be ̀ g mɛ ̀ tin mɛɓɛɛ ̀ lɛ rinɗim , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ɓeka ̀ lɛ a kɛn ̀ ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ ɓɔn ɓɛ Isirayɛl ɓɛ ɓɛgeni ɓii .
Yɛɛ ̀ Moyis a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ di muu Egiɓtɛn a yeeyeesi ̀ ge ̀ ni wi ̀ i ̀ adɛŋ , nni a ̀ ka ̀ mga ̀ geni a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ yeeye ̀ e ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ a ̀ nɛn ; ɓi ɗi lɛ a rɔŋ ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ , a ̀ wola ̀ muu Egiɓtɛn a ̀ nce ̀ m .
A ̀ fe ̀ fe ̀ ka ̀ lɛ , ɓɔn ɓɛ Isirayɛl ɓɛ ɓɛge ̀ ni ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗin ̀ lɛ , nyi nnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ romii ̀ lɛ a ghɛɓsi ɓɔ , wɔ ̀ lɛ , ɓɔɔ ghɛnga ̀ ɓi kiɓan kin ̀ fɔlɔɔ .
Nni ɓi duri tana , Moyis a ̀ tanɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔn ɓɛ Isirayɛl ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ , di ɓɛɛ ̀ ɗu ̀ u ̀ ɗu ̀ u ̀ , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ɓɔ ki ̀ ghasii , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ cɛ kɛɛ ri ɓa ̀ lɛ , mi ̀ ni ɓi ri ̀ geni , ɓi ̀ ki ciicii ̀ zɛ ̀ n ti ̀ mi ̀ ni ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ?
Fɔɔnnɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ cii ̀ ci ̀ i ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ ge ̀ ni a ̀ mbog a ̀ fenga ̀ ka ̀ Moyis , a ̀ ki tɔg nyi lɛ : Ghɛn yɛɛ nkpaa kɔm wɔ ̀ lɛ , u yu ɓi ̀ si ki ̀ la ̀ mii , u ̀ ki yɔ ̀ myɔm ɓiɓan ɓis ?
U kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ u wey mɛ ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ n ̀ woli muu Egiɓtɛn ri ̀ ŋko ̀ ?
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Moyis a ̀ woka ̀ fɔlɔɔ , nni a ̀ ghɛŋi ̀ gha ̀ , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ nyamzɛɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki lɛ Maɗyaŋ , wɔɔnnɛ a ̀ yala ̀ ɓɔn ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ be ̀ g mɛ ̀ tin mɛɓɛɛ ̀ , nnɛ ŋ ̀ waa ̀ fi ̀ tom a ̀ resɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi ɓi-reɓ wu do ̀ n i ̀ Sinayi i ̀ ri ̀ wɔɔ ; a ̀ ɓagha ̀ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗo ̀ o ̀ wu ɗuu wu wɛɛ ̀ ro ̀ o ̀ roo ɓi ki ̀ tywi ̀ ɗ .
Moyis a ̀ kuughra ̀ ka ̀ ri ̀ kuu ɗi com ɗi a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ɗin ̀ nni yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ mɛɛ ̀ tyo ̀ ŋdɛ ̀ nga ̀ wɔɔ , a ̀ wog di jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Kan i ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛɛ , i ̀ kpaa lɛ :
Mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓɔɔ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ Abiraham , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ Isag , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ Yakɔɓ , nni Moyis a ̀ risi ̀ gha ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ghɛɛsi ti ri ̀ seese ̀ e ̀ wɔɔ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Kan a ̀ ka ̀ li ̀ gha ̀ Moyis lɛ : Sɔ ̀ ŋi ɓɛ ̀ siripa ̀ s ɓɔɔ , ɓisuulɛ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ u ̀ rɛrɛrii mii ̀ i ̀ nɛ ̀ n , i ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ce ̀ li ̀ .
Mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ghɛɛ mɛ ̀ tɔɓ mɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ kɛm ̀ ki ki ri a Egiɓtɛn , n ̀ ki wog bemeg yaa , fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ sɛnii lɛ n ̀ ghɛɓsi ̀ ɓɔ . Nni ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki , yu , n ̀ ɗom wɔ ̀ a Egiɓtɛn .
Moyis nyimiɗ a ̀ nɛ ɓɔn ɓɛ Isirayɛl ɓɛ ɓenga ̀ , ri ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ inɛ lɛ : Ghɛn yɛɛ m ̀ ɓɔgsii wɔ ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi yɔ ̀ myɔmɛn ɓisi ? Innɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ romga ̀ lɛ , a lami ɓɔ , a ̀ ki kwe ̀ ɗ ɓɔ ɓi ri ̀ kpa ̀ n , lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ɓi ki ̀ twi ̀ ɗ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi .
Nnyɛɛ kpaŋzi ̀ gha ̀ y ɓɔn ɓɛ Isirayɛl a Egiɓtɛn di a ki ̀ ki ɓɛ ̀ koŋnyoo ɓɛ ɓiɓan ri ̀ da ̀ m yi ɓiɓan a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n a Egiɓtɛn a ̀ kpaŋ ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ m ̀ ɓa ̀ ŋ ri ̀ ɓi reɓ be ̀ g mɛ ̀ tin mɛɓɛɛ ̀ .
Lɔŋ Moyis a ̀ nɛ ̀ n yɛɛ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔn ɓɛ Isirayɛl lɛ : Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ romii ̀ gɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ ɓi boo yi ̀ n i ɓum , lɛ a ɓa n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki taŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi-reɓ , Moyis yɛɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ nɛ lɛ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓis ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom anɛ a ̀ to ̀ to ̀ ka ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi ɓi do ̀ n i ̀ Sinayi . Nnyɛɛ ghaɓka ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi Bɛ ̀ ll yi yi ri cem lɛ a ghagsi mi ̀ ni yɔ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓis ɓɛ nɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ ɓi deɓ yii , ɓɛ ɓenga ̀ yɔ , ɓɛ kɔn ̀ lɛ , di ɓaa sugtii a Egiɓtɛn :
Lɛ ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ Arɔn lɛ : Syagha ɓi ̀ si bɛ ̀ ll yi yɛɛ syogi ɓi ̀ si bee ɓisuulɛ , ɓi ̀ sii yii ɓi com ki ki n ̀ ki ̀ i Moyis a ̀ nɛ a ̀ a n ̀ kpaŋzii yi ̀ ɓi ̀ si a Egiɓtɛn .
Nni ɓɛ syaka ̀ min man a ̀ sani ̀ nya ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ ɓɛ funɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ tuwe ɓi ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ kin ̀ , ɓɛ ki nya ̀ a ̀ rɛn lɛɛ ̀ gwey ri com ki ɓɔmiɗ ɓɔ yɛɛ syaka ̀ ri ̀ ɓya ̀ g ɓyaa .
Fɔɔnnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ lɔ ̀ ghi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ jɛ ̀ m , a ̀ ca ̀ ɗ ɓɔ lɛ , ɓɛɛ ɓɔɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ gsi ̀ tyɔɛy ti aɗyoo , fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ kanga ̀ lɛ : Mi ̀ ni ɓɔn ɓɛ Isirayɛl , ɓi be ̀ g mɛ ̀ tin mɛɓɛɛ ̀ yi ɓi ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓi-reɓ , mɛ ̀ ɛnɛ ɓi ̀ ɓɔɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ gsi ̀ gha ̀ nya lɛ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ tuwe ri ̀ i ̀ kum ?
E ̀ e e ̀ e ki ̀ cu ̀ ma ̀ ki bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛ lɛ Mɔlɔg ri ̀ ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki fyɛy fi bɛ ̀ ll yi ̀ n i ̀ nɛ lɛ Refan ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ tɛ ̀ ka ̀ , ɓi ̀ syag ɓi ̀ nu ̀ n ɓin ̀ lɛ ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓi ɓi ɓɔɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ gsi ̀ ; ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki n ̀ ɗi ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ki naŋi ̀ fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ , Baɓilon a ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓ fɛ ajɛ ̀ m .
Ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓis ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ cu ̀ ma ̀ ki ki ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ ki lɛ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wa ̀ a ̀ . Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ to ̀ to ̀ ka ̀ ri ̀ Moyis a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ ɓɛn ̀ ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ toŋi ̀ ki ̀ cu ̀ ma ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ kuu ɗi nyii resi ̀ gha ̀ a ̀ nɛn .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓis ɓɛ ɓɛ rɔɓka ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ cu ̀ ma ̀ kin ̀ ɓɛ teka ̀ kɔ , ɓɛ ɗiŋi ̀ ri ̀ kɔ ɓi zi i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ɓatɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ sansa ̀ nga ̀ ɗi ɓɔɔ tii ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Yooswa a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ ; ki ̀ cu ̀ ma ̀ kin ̀ ki kɔri ̀ gha ̀ wɔɔ a ̀ kpaŋ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki Davit a ̀ ɓɔka ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m .
Davit a ̀ nɛ ̀ n yɛɛ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ keesii nyi fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ tɔka ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ Yakɔɓ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ nyi Davit nyii toŋ ̀ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n mɛɛ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , Salomɔŋ yɛɛ toga ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll mɛɛ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ teŋmɛɛ a ̀ cee , a maa ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ɓi kɔmiɗ ɓi mɛɛ mɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ toŋi .
Ɓisuulɛ Kan a kpaaghi lɛ , ɗyoo ɗyɛɛ ri i ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wɛm ̀ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ , zii ̀ ɓa ja ̀ ŋ i ri ̀ rɛsa ̀ g ɗyɛm ̀ ɗi mɛko ̀ o ̀ , nni ri ̀ kuu ɗi mɛɛ aɗi ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi ɓi ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓii ̀ toŋi ̀ ? Nsoo ̀ lɛ ri ̀ kuu ɗi ̀ ja ̀ ŋ ɗi la ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ n ̀ fɔɔsa ̀ g wɔɔ ?
A ̀ a mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ yɛɛ ki ̀ gha ̀ ɓyom ɓin ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ?
Mi ̀ ni ɓum ɓɛ n ̀ too ̀ te ̀ ɗ ɓɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ , mi ̀ ni kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛ ̀ rem , mi ̀ ni ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ lɔg , fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ɗu ̀ u ̀ ɗuu ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ɗi ̀ Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay , ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓin ɓɛ ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn .
N ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan abe nnɛ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓin ɓɛ rɔɓka ̀ lɛ ɓɛ tɔɓi ɓi ̀ ? Ɓɛ cuusi ̀ gha ̀ kɔm ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ woo ̀ wo ̀ gsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓum ri ̀ yu ̀ ɗi m ̀ bobog a ̀ mum a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ saaɗ . Nni ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , ŋwaa ̀ nce ̀ m a ̀ nɛn innɛ ɓi ̀ mɛ ki ̀ lɛ , ɓi ̀ tɔ ̀ kɛ ̀ n , ɓi ki wey .
Mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ɓi gha ̀ ɓka ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ɓya ̀ g ɓi ɓum ɓɛ titom kɛ ̀ ɓi ki ɓe ̀ ŋ ɓyɔ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓi Sa ̀ ne ̀ di ̀ rɛŋ ɓɛ woka ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓi Ityɛn ɓin ̀ bim i naasa ̀ g ɓɔ , ɓɛ tum ri ̀ ŋa ̀ a ̀ ŋa ̀ a ̀ di ̀ ɗi min lɛ bim inɛ ɓɛ woka ̀ ri ̀ Ityɛn .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Ityɛn a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ ɗonɛn ɗi Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay , nni yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ pɛɓsɛ ̀ nga ̀ aɗyoo , a ̀ ghɛn ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ki rigwey ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ Yeesus n ̀ ɗɛrɛliyɛn ɓi wee ̀ lem a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ,
fɔɔnnɛ a kali ̀ gha ̀ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ ghɛɛ ! Mɛ ̀ ɛ ntaataa ɗyoo ɗi ̀ nɛmɓɛn , Man a ̀ Mum a ̀ rɛrɛ ̀ li ̀ ɓi wee ̀ lem a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɔɔ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ kuu ̀ gha ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo , ɓɛ simgi ̀ ɓya ̀ g ɓi mɛ ̀ ree ̀ , ɓɛ suu ̀ rɛ ̀ n Ityɛn ɓi nyoo .
Ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ ɗi ba ̀ n , ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ n nyi ri ̀ rogi ̀ ɗi gɔ ̀ g lɛ ɓɛɛ wey nyi . Ɓɛ ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛ ɓi ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ɓɛ reɓsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ɓyaa ri dɛli ̀ i ̀ mum i ̀ dɛŋ ɗii lɛ Sol .
Ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓɛ roo ̀ ro ̀ ga ̀ ka ̀ Ityɛn gɔ ̀ g mii , nyii ɓɔɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋza ̀ ka ̀ lɛ : Kan Yeesus , tera nghay wɛ ̀ m .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi zi ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ɗu , a ̀ nyam jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ , Kan , cenɛn ɓɔ ki ̀ ɓe ki ! Yɛɛ ̀ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ fɔlɔɔ , nni a ̀ maasi ̀ gha ̀ .
Sol a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ ri ̀ wey di ɓɛ wola ̀ Ityɛn ɗi ɓagha ̀ syeesyee a ̀ ki ̀ ɓan . Ŋwos a ̀ n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛn , wɛ ̀ y wu pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ y ɓisuu kiseŋi ki ki ɓagha ̀ a Yorisalɛm , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ saa ̀ tɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ɓɔɔ ba ̀ n ɓɛ a Zyude , ri ̀ ɓɛ a Samari , lɔŋ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom cɛ ̀ ncaa ɓɛɛ rɔɓka ̀ a Yorisalɛm .
Ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ falɛn ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓomga ̀ Ityɛn , ɓɛ ki re ̀ n nyi lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ , ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Sol nyii kɛnkɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɔŋ asu a ̀ tɔtɔ ̀ ɓ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ; a ̀ ɗiɗi ̀ ŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ naa , di a Kpaakpa ̀ ŋzi ̀ i ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɗi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ baŋi ̀ ɓi-te ̀ ɗ a ̀ ki foŋfoŋ ɓɔ ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y .
Ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɛ Saa ̀ tɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɛn ̀ , ɓɛ Kɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ gha ̀ ja ̀ ŋ lɛ ja ̀ ŋ di ɓɛɛ ̀ ghaaghagsi ̀ ɓum Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Filiɓ a ̀ Sɛnga ̀ ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ dɛŋ i ̀ nɛ a Samari a ̀ kaka ̀ li ̀ ɓumɓɛ wɔɔ kiɓan ki n ̀ ghɛɓsi ̀ ɓum .
Ɓi ̀ tuu ɓi ɓum lɔŋ n ̀ ɗem wu ̀ fog , ɓi sii ̀ rɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ri ̀ wog ɗi ɓiɓan ɓi Filiɓ a ̀ Kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ , ɓisuulɛ ɓɛ wowo ̀ ka ̀ , ɓɛ Ki seesee da ̀ m yi ɓiɓan yi a ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ .
Ɓi Saaɗ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓi Kpaŋkpa ̀ ŋga ̀ ɓi ɓumɓɛ ɓi ɓagha ̀ mii ̀ di ɓyɛɛ ̀ Syaasyaa ̀ dɛ ̀ n jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo , ɓi ̀ sɛkɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ lɛnlɛm ɓɛ wɔnga ̀ ka ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛn ɓɛ nyaa ̀ rɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ lɛ Simɔn a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛn abɛ ̀ y , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -maji ̀ g ; a ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi lɛ ɓumɓɛ a Samari ɓɛɛ Kuuku ̀ u ̀ ra ̀ g , a ̀ ki ye ̀ eghyegsi ̀ ɓum lɛ nyii ri ki ̀ te ̀ ete ̀ ɗ ki mum .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ Kuura ̀ ka ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓi ɓɔɓti ɓɛsa ̀ g a ̀ Kpaŋ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn di ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa lɛ : Roa ̀ nɛ yɛɛ ri i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu Bɛ ̀ ll wu ɓɛɛ ̀ regi lɛ , i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wugwey .
Ɓɛ kuura ̀ ka ̀ fɔlɔɔ ri nyi lɛ , ki ɓagha ̀ di kaa finɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓii ɓi maji ̀ g ɓi kee ̀ ghke ̀ gsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓum .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ Filiɓ a ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ , Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ a ̀ ɗii ɗi Yeesus Kiris , fɔɔnnɛ ɓum ɓɛ ɓaɓta ̀ ka ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ baŋi ̀ .
N ̀ soo ̀ Simɔn nyimiɗ , a ̀ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ girig , a ̀ ki ɓa ̀ ɓtɛn , a ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ Filiɓ , a ̀ kuu ̀ ku ̀ u ̀ ghra ̀ g da ̀ m ɗi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ koŋnyoo ɓɛ ɓiɓan ɓɛ a ̀ seese ̀ e ̀ gha ̀ di roa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ki ̀ ki ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ɓɛ ɓɛ rɔɓka ̀ y a Yorisalɛm , ɓɛ woka ̀ lɛ ɓum ɓɛ a Samari ɓɛ ghaɓi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ syeesyee , nni ɓɛ romga ̀ lɛ ri ̀ Pyɛɛri ri ̀ Zyaŋ wɔɔ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kpaga ̀ a Samari , ɓɛ ɓɔŋza ̀ ka ̀ ɓisuu ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ wɔɔ , lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a fa ɓɔ Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay .
Ɓisuulɛ , Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Ngha ̀ y ki ɓagha ̀ di ki ka sɛn yi ɓi nsoo ̀ ɓi ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɔ ; ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ lɔŋ yɛɛri di ɓɛ ti ɓɛ ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓtakɛn ɓi ɗii ɗi Kan Yeesus .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ -Pyɛɛri ɓɛɛ ̀ Zyaŋ ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ ri ̀ sasa ̀ a ̀ gh ɗi ɓya ̀ g ɓi nyoo , ɓɛ teɗ min Kitɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Ngha ̀ y .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ Simɔn a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ɓɛ ti lɛ i ɓɛ saghii mum ɓya ̀ g ɓi nyoo , a ̀ ɓa ri ̀ Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Ngha ̀ y , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ sɔ ̀ ŋi ̀ gha ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni lɛ a fa ɓɔ .
Ri ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ a nwɔm lɛ : Faana mɛ ̀ girig i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ n ̀ saghii ɓya ̀ g ɓi nyoo , a ̀ ɓa ri ̀ Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Ngha ̀ y .
Nni Pyɛɛri a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ nyi lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓa gi la ri ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɔɔ mɛnce ̀ m , yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ fe ̀ egh lɛ u ̀ ri ̀ lɛ u ̀ la ̀ g ri ̀ fa ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni ,
lɛ u ̀ yin gi ri ̀ ga ̀ ɓ nsoo ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓi ki ̀ say ki , lɛ nɗem wɔɔ wu yin lɛ saaɗ ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Koɓsɛn fe ̀ g a ̀ m ̀ ɓeɓtɛn anɛ u ̀ ri ̀ a ̀ nɛn ɗi ̀ nyi , u ̀ ki ɓɔ ̀ ŋzi Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ , a cenɛn wɔ ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki u ̀ mɛɛ ̀ fe ̀ g kin ̀ di a ̀ kɔ ̀ ni .
Ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛyiti ̀ ɓi roni wɔ ̀ n ̀ ɗem lɛ pisa , ki ̀ ɓe ki ki ghaasii wɔ ̀ n ̀ kpa ̀ n .
Nni Simɔn a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzaghna Bɛ ̀ ll ɓisu wɛ ̀ m lɛ , ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ̀ kalii ɓi ̀ n ɓyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ kpaŋ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ -Pyɛɛri ɓɛɛ ̀ Zyaŋ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ di ɓaa re ̀ sag ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓɔɔ yigha ̀ , ɓi rarɛ ̀ n ri ̀ Yeesus , ɓɛ ki kali ti ɓɔ Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ Kan , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ Sugti ̀ gha ̀ a Yorisalɛm di ɓɛɛ ̀ kakali ɓumɓɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi a Samari Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ .
Ŋwaa ̀ fi ̀ tom a Kan a ̀ kpaagha ̀ Filiɓ lɛ : Pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyoo , u nɔɔ ̀ ti bee inɛ i ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ yi ̀ a Yorisalɛm i ̀ sɛn a Gaza , ɓum ɓɛ ti ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ fyee ti ɓi bee ince ̀ m .
Nni Filiɓ a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ , a ̀ gha ̀ s ki ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ , nni a ̀ pi ̀ ka ̀ mis , a ̀ ghɛn ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ nyi asu , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ŋwɛg , nyi ti ̀ coo n ̀ sasa ̀ li ̀ a ̀ Kaŋɗas giɓ anɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m a Etyopii , nyi ti ̀ baŋ-masa ̀ a ̀ giɓ anɛ ̀ n . A ɓagha ̀ y ki ̀ ɓɔgsii Bɛ ̀ ll a Yorisalɛm .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n yɛɛ susu ̀ ka ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔriyɛn ɓi calig di a ɓa ̀ ɓay kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan Ezayii .
Fɔɔnnɛ Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ki kali ̀ gha ̀ Filiɓ lɛ : Pi ̀ gha mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ , u ̀ tanɛn calig kinii .
Nni Filiɓ a ̀ Cɛ ̀ ɓti ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ ree , a ̀ tanɛ ̀ n calig ki ̀ n , a ̀ wog min yɛ ̀ ɛ muu Etyopii a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓa ̀ la ̀ kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan Ezayii . Filiɓ a ̀ tɔg nyi lɛ : Tɛɛnɛ , u wowog nya com ki u ɓa ̀ ɓay kin ̀ ?
Nni ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ Filiɓ lɛ : Lannɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ n ̀ wog com ki mɓa ̀ ɓa ̀ y di ɓɛ tɛɛ ̀ zii ɓi mɛ kɔ ? Nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ Filiɓ lɛ a ɓɔg yi ̀ ɓi calig , a kɔri nyi ɓi nwɔŋi ̀ .
Ki ̀ den ki a ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓa ̀ la ̀ ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ nɛn ki ɓagha ̀ lɛ : A ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓka ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ tuwe ki ɓɛɛ kɛ ̀ nkɛn ɗi kɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ gheg ̀ ɓoŋ , a ̀ ki maarag lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ man a ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ a ̀ nɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ caacaa nyu ̀ ŋ . Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓka ̀ fɔlɔɔ , kɛ ̀ ɛ pini nsoo ̀ ŋwɔ ̀ m .
Ɓɛ sooti ̀ gha ̀ nyi , ɓɛ ki n ̀ yuŋzag nyi , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ lɛ a ̀ lo ̀ e ̀ y ki ̀ ɓan kii ; ɓɛ ̀ ghɛn ɓɛɛ ri ɓu ̀ ŋ lɛ a ̀ ca ̀ ri boo i ̀ mum , yɛ ̀ ɛ cɛɓ kii ki ti ki ̀ ti ̀ i ̀ siyɛn ɓi ziinɛ ?
Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ tɔka ̀ Filiɓ lɛ : Ku ̀ ru ̀ g , kali ɓa ̀ mɛ , ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan a kpaa ɓi ̀ n ɓi seesee ghɛn , nyimiɗ gi ̀ n ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ ?
Nni Filiɓ a ̀ pɛ ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ y min kito ̀ ki ̀ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓa ̀ la ̀ , a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kona ̀ ka ̀ nyi ki ̀ tɛɛ ̀ zii Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ Yeesus .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kɛɛdi ̀ gha ̀ ti ̀ bee ̀ bɛ ̀ y , nni ɓɛ kpaga ̀ ɓi ki ̀ ra ̀ a ̀ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ tɔg Filiɓ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ nig mɛɛ ̀ mɛ , cɛ kɛɛ regtii lɛ kɔ ̀ ɔ ɓa ̀ ɓti mɛ ?
Filiɓ a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : I u ̀ gherɛɛ ri ̀ n ̀ ɗem wɔɔ wuce ̀ m n ̀ ɗi lɛ m ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓti ̀ wɔ ̀ ; ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Ɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , n ̀ gherɛɛ lɛ Yeesus Kiris a ̀ ri ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Nni ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ tɔka ̀ m ̀ pusi ̀ calig lɛ a rɛli . Ɓɛ sɛn min ɓɛɛ ̀ Filiɓ , ɓɛ ɗiŋi ̀ ɓi ki ̀ ra ̀ a ̀ , Filiɓ a ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓti ̀ min nyi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kpaga ̀ y a cɛɗ , Nghay a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ tɛ ̀ g Filiɓ a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ɗi nyi , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n kɛ ̀ ɛ ghɛɛ ̀ di nyi ; nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ , muu Etyopii a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ghagsi ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɗii di a nya ̀ a ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ .
Filiɓ a ̀ si ̀ gmɛ ̀ nga ̀ di a ̀ ti a Azɔt , a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ n wɔɔ , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n a Sezare , a ̀ kaka ̀ li ̀ ɓum Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓi ba ̀ n yi ̀ ce ̀ m yi a ̀ ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi bee .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ sol a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ kaka ri ̀ coo n ̀ ɗem wu ri ̀ gɛn wulɛ , a cuu ̀ cu ̀ u ̀ si ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ Kan , nni a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey ,
a ̀ tɔg nyi ɓɛ ̀ kaa ̀ ta ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛ faa nyi I ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ , a kɛn ̀ a Damas , i a ̀ tanɛɛ ɓum ɓi naa yi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n , nsoo ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ nsoo ̀ ɓɛ ̀ baŋi ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔnɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ bee i Kan , a ɓangii ̀ ɓɔ a ki sug yi ri ̀ ɓɔ a Yorisalɛm ɓɛ ̀ ka ̀ gakɛn .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ nkɛni a Damas , di a ̀ ti ɓii ̀ wuuwuɓsɛ ̀ n ba ̀ n , nni a ̀ si ̀ gmɛ ̀ nga ̀ di ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ki mɛ la ̀ n yi ɗyoo lɛ ŋwa ̀ a ̀ ɗ , ki ceŋzɛ ̀ n nyi .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi zi a ̀ wog di jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ kpaakpaa nyi lɛ : Sol , Sol wɔ ̀ , ɓisuucɛ nnɛ u tɔtɔɓ mɛ fɛlɛ ̀ ?
Sol a ̀ tɔg lɛ : Kan , wɔ ̀ ghɛn wɔ ̀ yɛɛ ri ? Jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ nyi lɛ : Mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ri Yeesus a ̀ nɛ u tɔtɔ ̀ ɓ ki ri wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ n ̀ tɔɓ lɛ u ki ti n ̀ too ̀ te ̀ ɗ di mɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ŋ mɛɛ ̀ roorogi ̀ wɔ ̀ . Nni Sol a ̀ risi ̀ gha ̀ , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ni ̀ i ̀ ghni ̀ ŋdɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Kan nni wɔ ̀ ɔ kɔ ̀ ngi lɛ nki la ? Kan a ̀ ɓa ̀ g min nyi lɛ :
Pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyoo , u ɗiŋi ɓi ba ̀ n , wɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ri wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ kpaa ̀ com ki u ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ i .
Ɓumɓɛ Sol a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ gha ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ ri ɓɔ , ɓɛ rɛli ̀ gha ̀ , i ̀ ris wu mamzi ̀ ɓɔ , ɓisuulɛ , ɓɛ wowɔka ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ ri yɔ ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ghɛn ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ to ̀ to ̀ ka ̀ .
Nni Sol a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ aɗyoo , wɔ ̀ lɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ ghɛnɛnti nsoo ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ mis mii mɛ ɓagha ̀ mɛ ̀ ŋwa ̀ rɛn . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ɓanga ̀ nyi ɓi ca ̀ g , ɓɛ kɛɛ ̀ si ̀ nyi a ̀ kpaŋ a Damas .
A ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ru mɛraa , kɛ ̀ ɛ ghɛnɛn , kɛ ̀ ɛ ɗi , kɛ ̀ ɛ nɔ .
N ̀ gherɛ ̀ n a ̀ dɛŋ ɗii lɛ Ananyas a ̀ ɓagha ̀ a Damas , nyi nnɛ Kan a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ dɛ ̀ ndɛm a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Ananyas wɔ ̀ ! Roa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Kan , mɛ ̀ ɛnɛ lɛ .
Kan a ̀ kpaa ti ̀ nyi lɛ : Pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyoo , u kɛn ̀ ɓi bee i ̀ mɛ ̀ rɛy , u kpaŋ a mɛɛ mɛ Zyudas , u tɔg ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ wɔɔ lɛ Sol , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ yalɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Tarisi a ̀ nce ̀ m a ki ̀ ki bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n ɓigomi ̀ nɛ ;
nni ɓi bɔŋ ̀ zɛ ̀ n i ̀ nɛn , ki kii ̀ yi ̀ nyi fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ dɛ ̀ ndɛm lɛ a ̀ ghɛɛ yi ̀ mum ɗii lɛ Ananyas di a ̀ ɗiŋii yi ̀ ɓi naa yi ̀ i ̀ , a ̀ ki saagh nyi ɓya ̀ g ɓi nyoo lɛ di a ghɛnɛn ti ̀ .
Ananyas a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : Kan , m ̀ mɛ wog di ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛɛ sɛsɛg rigɛn ɗi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ a nki ̀ i ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ a Yorisalɛm .
Nni ɓi ɗi a ̀ ri ̀ ɗi fɛ , ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ɓɛ nfaa nyi i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ a ɓangi ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ rereŋi ɗii ɗyɔɔ , a ̀ ki fogi ɓɔ ɓi ɓi ̀ sɔŋ .
Nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ , Kan a ̀ kpaati ̀ gha ̀ Ananyas lɛ : Kɛ ̀ na lɔŋ ɓisuulɛ , Sol a ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ com ki kisay ki n ̀ sɔnɛɛ . A ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ re ̀ resii ɗii ɗyɛ ̀ m ɓi ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ɓɛ yii ɓi mɛ wɔɔ , ri ̀ a mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m , ri ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓɔn ɓɛ Isirayɛl .
Mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ n ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi ɓii ̀ re ̀ sii mɛtɔɓ mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m mɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ woo ̀ gh ɓisu wɛ ̀ m .
Fɔɔnnɛ Ananyas a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ min wɔɔ ; nni yɛɛ ̀ a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi naa i ̀ nɛ Sol a ̀ ɓagha ̀ mii ̀ , a ̀ saagh nyi ɓya ̀ g ɓi nyoo a ki kpaa nyi lɛ : Geni wɛ ̀ m Sol , Kan Yeesus a ̀ nɛ a ̀ a n ̀ ɗe ̀ sɛɛ yi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓi bee di u yu ̀ yuiy fɛ , yɛɛ romii ̀ mɛ ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɔɔ , lɛ mɛ ̀ nsaagh wɔ ̀ ɓya ̀ g ɓi nyoo di wɔ ̀ ɔ ghɛnɛn ti ̀ , u ̀ ki ɓa nɗonɛn ɗi Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay .
Lɔŋ ɓi gom yɔ ̀ miɗ inɛ ̀ n , ɓyom ɓidɛŋ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ ɓaaɓaa ɓi ɓi ̀ zɛn ɓi ɓaaghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ y ɓi mis mɛ Sol , ɓi kpi ɓi zi , a ̀ ghɛnɛ ̀ n ti ̀ min , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ aɗyoo , ɓɛ ɓaɓti ̀ nyi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ɗigha ̀ ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g , i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu yuti ̀ nyi ɓi nyoo . A ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ti ̀ ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ a Damas .
Nni a ̀ ghagsɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɔŋ wɔɔ foo ɗi ri ̀ kaka ̀ li ̀ ɗi ɓum ɗii ɗi Yeesus ɓi naa yi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n , a ̀ la ̀ a ̀ la ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n lɛ : Yeesus a ̀ ri ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ wowo ̀ ka ̀ di a kpaakpaa fɔlɔɔ , ɓɛ Kuura ̀ ka ̀ , ɓɛ tɔtɔ ̀ g lɛ : A ̀ a ŋwaa ̀ nɛ yɛɛ n ̀ -yee ̀ ye ̀ e ̀ si ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛɛ kpɔŋkpɔŋ ɗii ɗi Yeesus a Yorisalɛm ? A ̀ nce ̀ m aa ̀ n-yuyuu yi ̀ ɓi fɛ ri ̀ fe ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ , a ɓangi bɔ , a fogi ɓɔ ɓi ɓi ̀ sɔŋ , di a kɛn ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓɔ a ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ?
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog Sol a ̀ kɛ ̀ nkɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɔŋ asu , a ̀ ki si ̀ isii ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɓi ri ̀ re ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ɗi ɓum lɛ ɓɛɛ yi saaɗ lɛ Yeesus a ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ Kiris ; Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ a Damas ɓɛ rɔɓka ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ Sol .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru i ̀ ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ ti ̀ foo , Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ wɔrɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓɔɔ wey Sol .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , Sol a ̀ yigha ̀ ki ̀ tɔ ̀ kɔ ̀ kaa ɓisuulɛ ɓɛ ramga ̀ ka ̀ nyi a mɛ ̀ suunaa mɛ ba ̀ n lɛ ɓɛɛ wey nyi , ɓɛ beŋ ̀ mɔ lɛ ri ̀ i ̀ ru ri ̀ ŋwos .
Nni ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛ teka ̀ nyi ɓi-ru wudɛŋ , ɓɛ kaŋ ̀ nyi ɓi ki ̀ kpoŋ , ɓɛ ɓɔg gari ɗi nyi lɛ ɓɛɛ sɛɛ ̀ di nyi ri ̀ n ̀ ɗig ɓɛg a ̀ mbog .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Sol a ̀ kpaga ̀ a Yorisalɛm , nni a ̀ kaagha ̀ bee i ̀ nɛ a rarɛn ɗi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ riri ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ nyi , lɛ ɓɛ ɓiisɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi kigherɛɛ lɛ a ̀ ti n ̀ -yila ̀ g .
Fɔɔnnɛ Ɓarinaɓas a ̀ teka ̀ Sol a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ nyi a ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ yɛ ̀ ɛ Sol a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ Kan ɓi bee i ̀ nɛ a Damas ri ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Kan a ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi , nni a ̀ kpaati ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ ri ̀ kuu ɗi n ̀ tyweeyi ɗi Sol a ̀ a n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ɗyɔ a Damas di a kakali ɓum ɗii ɗi Yeesus .
A ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ innɛ Sol a ̀ ɓasɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ , ɓɛ kiki ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ ɓɔg , ɓɛ sɛn n ̀ ɗaŋ di ɓɛɛ ̀ re ̀ resi ɓum ɗii ɗi Kan ri ̀ n ̀ tyweeyi ɓi nɗem .
Sol a ̀ kuu ̀ ku ̀ rɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɗi ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɛ n ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ri ̀ gi ̀ rɛg , a ̀ ki nyoonyolɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ ɓɔ , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɔɔ kaaka ̀ a ̀ bee inɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ wey nyi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓɛ Sol ɓɛ righerɛn ɓɛ woka ̀ fɔlɔɔ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi a Sezare ; yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kpaga ̀ wɔɔ , ɓɛ ca ̀ ɗ nyi lɛ a ghaa ̀ gh a Tarisi .
Ki ̀ seŋi ki ɓagha ̀ lɛ fyo ̀ oog , ɓi zi i ̀ Zyude bimiɗ , a Galile ri ̀ a Samari ; ki ̀ seŋi ki tete ̀ ka ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , ki kiki ̀ Kan mɛ ̀ wog , ki ki te ̀ eghteghɛ ̀ n ri ̀ n ̀ ghɛɓsɛn wu Kitɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay .
Pyɛɛri a ̀ rere ̀ ni ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ lɔŋ ki ̀ ce ̀ m , nni nwos adɛŋ , a ̀ sɛnga ̀ a Lida lɛ a ghɛn ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ tanɛ ̀ nga ̀ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ wɔɔ ɗii lɛ Enee n ̀ nɔ ̀ nɔŋiyɛn ɓi kon . Ki ɓagha ̀ di ki ti be ̀ g taa ̀ raa yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi zi , lɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛn .
Nni Pyɛɛri a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ : Enee wɔ ̀ , Yeesus Kiris a ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zii wɔ ̀ , pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyoo , u pegsɛn ɓyom ɓilɔ ̀ ŋ ɓyɔɔ . Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ gha ̀ ska ̀ ki ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ aɗyoo .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ a Lida , ri ̀ ɓɛ ɓi-reɓ wu lɛ Sarɔn ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n , nni ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ Kan .
Giɓ adɛŋ yɛɛ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ gherɛ ̀ n a Zyope ɗii lɛ Taɓita yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ Dorikas ; a ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ rɔɔ lɛɛ ̀ gwey a ̀ ki ghɛɛghɛɓsi ̀ ɓum ɓɛ nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g .
Ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ̀ n , nni a ̀ roɓka ̀ , a ̀ ki wu . Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ wuɓsi ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ loŋ kii , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ kɔ ki ̀ nɔ ̀ ŋzii ɓi ki ̀ den ki naa ɓi mɛɛ mɛ aɗyoo .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ a Zyope ɓɛ woka ̀ lɛ Pyɛɛri a ̀ ri ̀ a Lida , Lida a ̀ nɛn a ̀ ra ̀ ɓsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi loo ̀ ri ̀ Zyope , nni ɓɛ romga ̀ ɓum ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ ki ̀ kpaa ̀ Pyɛɛri lɛ : Ku ̀ ru ̀ g yuis ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkis , kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ lɛ ̀ mzii ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ , a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ ɓɔ . Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kpaga ̀ wɔɔ , ɓɛ ɓɔg ɗi ̀ nyi ɓi ki ̀ den ki naa ki ɓi mɛɛ aɗyoo , mɛ ̀ kpɔɓ mɛce ̀ m mɛ tyoŋdɛ ̀ n nyi a nyoo di mɛɛ ̀ re ̀ nɗe ̀ n ɓɛ rere ̀ si ̀ nyi lɛ , ri ̀ bu ̀ ɓa ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ka ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓɛ Dorikas a ̀ rara ̀ ɗka ̀ di a ̀ kaka cem .
Nni Pyɛɛri a ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ gha ̀ min ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓidan , a ̀ ɓag mɛ ̀ ɗu ɓi zi , a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋza ̀ g Bɛ ̀ ll , ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn a ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n min ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ ki ̀ loŋ a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Taɓita wɔ ̀ , pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyoo ! Nni a ̀ ŋwa ̀ ɗka ̀ min mis a ̀ ghɛn Pyɛɛri , a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ n ki ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Pyɛɛri a ̀ ɓan nyi ɓi ca ̀ g , a ̀ pɛ ̀ si ̀ nyi mɛ ̀ rɛy . A ̀ regi ̀ i ̀ min lɛ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ri ̀ mɛ ̀ kpɔɓ , a ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ɓɔ nyi , ɓɛ ghɛn lɛ a ̀ ti cem .
Ba ̀ n i ̀ Zyope bimiɗ i ̀ woka ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ , ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ ki gherɛn Kan .
Pyɛɛri a ̀ finɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Zyope le ̀ g a ̀ dɛŋ , a ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ lɛ Simɔn a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -go ̀ o ̀ .
Ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ a Sezare ɗii lɛ Kɔrinɛy , a ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ tin mɛtan ̀ ɓi n ̀ ɗaŋ wu ɓɛsuja ̀ a ̀ wu a Italii .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ falɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi righerɛ ̀ n , a ̀ a nki risa ̀ g Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ ri ̀ nyi ɗi ̀ ri ̀ mɛɛ ɗii ɗice ̀ m , a ̀ ki fafa Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g ɓyom lɛɛ ̀ gwey , a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋza ̀ g Bɛ ̀ ll ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ŋwos adɛŋ , di mɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛraa a ̀ ŋwos n ̀ kɛ ̀ nɛn a ̀ tii ̀ , Kɔrinɛy a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ dɛ ̀ ndɛm di ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɗiŋii yi ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkii , a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Kɔrinɛy wɔ ̀ !
Nni a ̀ fiɓi ̀ gha ̀ ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom lɛ fyɛɛɛyi , a ̀ risi ̀ , a ̀ tɔg nyi lɛ : La yɛɛ ri Kan ? Ŋwaa ̀ fi ̀ tom a ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ a n ̀ gha ̀ ɓi lɛ , ri ̀ bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n yɔɔ , ri ̀ gɛ ɓyom a ̀ nɛ u ̀ ti u ̀ fafa ̀ ɓum ɓɛ nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ɗimzɛɛ ɓi wɔ .
Rom ɓum a Zyope ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , lɛ ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ ki ̀ teri ̀ i ̀ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ wɔɔ , ɗii lɛ Simɔn a ̀ nɛ ɓɛɛ kpɔgi ti ̀ lɛ Pyɛɛri .
A ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔrii yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ lɛ Simɔn n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -go ̀ o ̀ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ toŋi ɓi nwɔŋi ̀ wu ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n .
Lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a ̀ nɛ a ̀ to ̀ to ̀ ka ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi a ̀ ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ , Kɔrinɛy a ̀ gha ̀ s ki ̀ reŋii ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓii ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ a ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ gha ̀ , suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ falɛn ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ;
fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ ki ̀ ɓan kice ̀ m ki ki ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ a ̀ ki rom min ɓɔ a Zyope .
Ɓi duri tana , yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kɛnkɛ ̀ nga ̀ , di ɓɛ mɛ wuɓsɛn ba ̀ ni ̀ Zyope , Pyɛɛri a ̀ ɓɔka ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n ɓi mɛɛ aɗyoo di toroɓ a ̀ ti ja ̀ ŋbog .
Nni za ̀ y i ̀ kɔ ̀ nga ̀ Pyɛɛri , a ̀ kɔ ̀ n lɛ a ɗi com ; ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓɛ kiki ̀ gha ̀ nyi ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g , nnɛ a ̀ si ̀ gmɛ ̀ nga ̀ di a ̀ mɛ cɛɛnɛn mis ɓi ̀ kpaŋ .
A ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ɗyoo ɗi ̀ nɛmɓɛn a ̀ ki ghɛn di com ki rii ̀ wɔɔ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ coo sa ̀ nja ̀ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ keɓ mɛsugakɛn , ki sɛnsɛ ̀ n yi ̀ ɓi zi .
Ɓyom ɓi ɓagha ̀ ɓi sa ̀ nja ̀ a ̀ nɛn lɛ : Nya ̀ m yi kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛɛyɛn mɛko ̀ o ̀ mɛnin mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , ri ̀ yi wɔwɔghɛn ɗi ̀ ɗu ̀ m , ri ̀ ti ̀ i ̀ li ̀ ti aɗyoo mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Pyɛɛri a ̀ wog di jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ dɛŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ kpaakpaa nyi lɛ : Pyɛɛri ! Pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyoo , u ̀ wey nyam foo bog di u ɗi .
Nni Pyɛɛri a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ lɛ : A ̀ g , Kan ! Mɛ ̀ n ̀ ka ɗigha ̀ ɓi com ki ki ri ɓaa , nsoo ̀ ki ki ri ki ̀ syeg ŋwos adɛŋ .
Fɔɔnnɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛn i ̀ kpaati ̀ gha ̀ nyi ɓi gɛ ̀ n i ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ɔ ki ̀ lɛ : Com ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kpaa lɛ ki ri kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ syeg , wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ kpaa lɛ , ki ri ri ̀ ki ̀ syeg .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki ɓii ̀ tɛ ̀ nga ̀ fɔlɔɔ gɛ ̀ n yiraa , ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn nnɛ sa ̀ nja ̀ a ̀ nɛn a ̀ sugti ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ ɓɔɔ ̀ gh aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki Pyɛɛri a ̀ kaakaa lɛ , a yi azi anɛ ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ kin ̀ , kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓumɓɛ Kɔrinɛy a ̀ romga ̀ y ɓɛ tɔtɔghii ̀ mɛɛ mɛ Simɔn , ɓɛ yu , ɓɛ rɛli ̀ asuunaa ,
ɓɛ regi ̀ ɓum , ɓɛ tɔg ɓɔ lɛ : A mɛɛ mɛ innɛ Simɔn a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kpɔgi ̀ lɛ Pyɛɛri a ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔrii wa ?
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pyɛɛri a ̀ ɓagha ̀ lɔŋ ɓii ̀ fe ̀ feegh ki ̀ ɓan ki a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ , nni Nghay a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : Wɛɛ ̀ nnɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ tɔtɔg lɛ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛraa .
Pɛ ̀ sɛn , u sɛn ɓi zi , u ̀ kɛn ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ , kɔ ̀ ɔ risi , ɓisuulɛ mɛ ̀ yɛɛ nɗomii ̀ ɓɔ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Pyɛɛri a ̀ sɛnga ̀ min , a ̀ tanɛ ̀ n ɓumɓɛ ̀ n , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ ! Mɛ ̀ ɛ nɛ lɛ , mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓi kaaka ̀ a ̀ , nni ɓi ̀ yu ̀ u yi ̀ fɛ ɓi n ̀ to wu kiɓan aɗi ?
Nni ɓɛ ɓaka ̀ nyi lɛ : Ti ̀ yu ̀ u yi ̀ fɛ lɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ nɛ lɛ Kɔrinɛy yɛɛ romii ̀ ɓi ̀ si a lɔ ̀ ŋkɔɔ , a ̀ nce ̀ m a ̀ ri ̀ saaɗ a ̀ mum a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ risa ̀ g Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ ki ri ̀ ti ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛɛ ̀ Sɛsɛ ̀ g ; ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ a n ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ a regii ̀ wɔ ̀ a mɛɛ mii , a wog jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ u ̀ ri ̀ lɛ u ̀ kpaa nyi .
Nni Pyɛɛri a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɗiŋi ɓi naa , a ̀ reɓ ɓɔ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɛɛ la ̀ y ; ɓi duri tana nnɛ ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ . Ɓɛ ̀ ge ̀ ni ɓii ɓɛ righerɛ ̀ n ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ a Zyope ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ga ̀ nyi ki ̀ foŋi ̀ .
Nni ŋwos anɛ a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɓka ̀ a ̀ nɛn nnɛ ɓɛ kpaga ̀ a Sezare , Kɔrinɛy a ̀ ɓoŋɓo ̀ ŋga ̀ ɓɔ lɛ ri ̀ naa yi ̀ i ̀ i ̀ ɓum , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ghan mii mɛ a ̀ reŋɗɛ ̀ nga ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pyɛɛri a ̀ kpaga ̀ wɔɔ , Kɔrinɛy a ̀ kɛ ̀ n nyi ki gha ̀ ɓi , a ̀ kpi nyi a ̀ mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ lɛ a fa nyi bɔgsɛ ̀ n .
Nni Pyɛɛri a ̀ ɓanga ̀ nyi lɛ a pɛsi nyi aɗyoo di a kpaakpaa lɛ : Pɛ ̀ sɛn yi ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ lɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ girig romum yɛ ̀ ɛ wɔ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi naa di ɓɛɛ ̀ to ̀ tog lɔŋ lɛ ri ̀ nyi ri ̀ Kɔrinɛy , a ̀ tanɛ ̀ n ɓum lɛ ku ̀ nag ku ̀ nag ,
a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ yii lɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ri ɗi ̀ coo n ̀ siŋdɛn wudɛŋ lɛ , mum waa ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ra ̀ rɛn ɗi muu cee-ri ̀ kuu , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ɗiŋi naa i ̀ roa ̀ nɛ ̀ n , nni ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ a n ̀ ɗe ̀ sii mɛ ̀ lɛ , n ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ti ̀ ɓi ki ghɛɛ ̀ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ lɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ syeg , kɛ ̀ ɛ nki ce ̀ li ti mum lɛ , a ̀ yin ntɛnɛn ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ -yu ̀ u yi ̀ mii ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ti ̀ ka ̀ na ɓi ̀ n ̀ ɗee ̀ ghreŋi wu wa ̀ a regii mɛ ̀ ; nkɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ , di ma ̀ a yii n ̀ to wu kiɓan wu wa ̀ a regii mɛ ̀ mii ̀ .
Nni Kɔrinɛy a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ lɛ : Gɛɛ ̀ nɛ mɛ ̀ ru mɛraa nnɛ mɛ nki ̀ kii bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n ɓi ki ̀ den kɛ ̀ m ki naa ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ mɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛraa a ̀ ŋwos . Nni mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ si ̀ gmɛ ̀ ɛ di mum a ̀ mɛ rɛli mɛ asu , ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ɓii ɓi lo ̀ nlo ̀ m lɛ syaŋ ̀ syaŋ ̀ a ̀ kpaa mɛ ̀ lɛ :
Kɔrinɛy Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ a nwoogh bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , a ̀ ki yiti gɛ ɓyom a ̀ nɛ u ̀ ti u ̀ fafa ̀ ɓum ɓɛ nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g .
Nni rom ɓum a Zyope ɓɛɛ regii ̀ Simɔn a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kpɔgi ̀ lɛ Pyɛɛri a yuiy ; a ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔrii yɛ ̀ ɛ Simɔn a ̀ m ̀ pe ̀ gsɛ ̀ n-go ̀ o ̀ ɓi be ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n .
Fɔɔnnɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ ngha ̀ si ki ̀ romi ̀ i ̀ ɓum lɛ ɓɛɛ yu wɔ ̀ ki ̀ reŋii . U ̀ konaagh yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ yu ̀ u yi ̀ . Nni ɓigomi ̀ nɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ yɛɛ lɛ ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , lɛ ti wog com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki Kan a ̀ a kpaa lɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ kali ɓi ̀ si .
Pyɛɛri a ̀ pɛ ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ min ɓito ̀ ki ̀ , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Ɓi saaɗ n ̀ konaagh ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ gɛɛ ̀ nɛ lɛ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ yin ɗi n ̀ ɗe ̀ e ̀ wu n ̀ ɗem
n ̀ ki ghɛɛ ̀ di lɛ , mum bimiɗ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ risii Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ki ̀ ki ɓiɓan ɓi saaɗ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ nyi ɓii ̀ keesii a ̀ a soo ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki be .
Fɔɔnnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ romga ̀ y jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ a ɓɔn ɓɛ Isirayɛl lɛ ɓɛɛ yi lɛ , fyo ̀ oog a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ nɛ lɛ ri ̀ nyi ri ̀ ɓum , ɓi jɛ ̀ m i ̀ Yeesus Kiris a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ;
ɓi ̀ yii ki ̀ ɓan ki ki nki ̀ lɛɛ ɓi zii ̀ Zyude bimiɗ , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n yi ̀ a Galile ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ ba ̀ ɓtis i ̀ nɛ Zyaŋ a ̀ la ̀ a ̀ la ̀ mɓɛ ̀ nga ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ yii lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ nga ̀ Yeesus a ̀ nɛ a Nazarɛt a ̀ rom yi ̀ nyi Kitɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay kii , a ̀ ki fa nyi i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wuce ̀ m , fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ gha ̀ ja ̀ ŋ bimiɗ a ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ɓum ki ̀ rɔɔ , di a wɔ ̀ ɔwɔɔ ̀ zi ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ri ̀ kpa ̀ n ɗi Sata ̀ n ɓisuulɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi .
Ɓi ̀ sii ri ɓɛ ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ɓi zi i ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ri ̀ a Yorisalɛm , nni Yeesus a ̀ nɛ ̀ n innɛ ɓɛ n ̀ woli di ɓɛ kpani ɓi kɔrɔs .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ ghe ̀ mzi ̀ nyi ɓi ŋwos a ki ̀ raa , a ̀ ki fa nyi i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ , a resɛn a ɓum .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ a ̀ a ɓum a ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m nnɛ a ̀ re ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ , lɔŋ a ɓɛ ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ loka ̀ ki ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ni . A ɓi ̀ si ɓumɓɛ ti ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , ti ̀ ɗi , ti ̀ ki nɔ nɗaŋ ɗi ̀ nyi di a ̀ mɛ ghemɓɛn yi a ɓi ̀ loŋ .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ reɓsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ si lɛ ti ghaa ̀ gha ̀ gsi ̀ ɓum Ɓɔlɛ wi ̀ i ̀ , ti ̀ ki si ̀ i ̀ rag ɓɔ ki ̀ resii lɛ , nnyɛɛ ri ̀ roa ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ rɛsi ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , a ̀ ri yu ̀ ki reni ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ kaka cencem , ri ̀ ɓi ɓɛ ɓɛ mɛ wu ̀ .
Yeesus a ̀ nɛ ̀ n nnɛ ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓuga ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ ɗii ɗii nnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ cenɛɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ gherɛɛ nyi ɓi ̀ ɓe .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pyɛɛri a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ka to ̀ tog a ŋwɔm fɔlɔɔ , nni Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ki sɛnga ̀ y ki ɗiŋi ̀ ɓi ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ wowo ̀ ka ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓii ɓin ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ y n ̀ ɗaŋ ɗi Pyɛɛri , ɓɛ kuura ̀ ka ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey , yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ faa ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay .
Ɓɛ wowo ̀ ka ̀ di ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛɛ ̀ to ̀ tog ɓi ̀ ke ̀ neke ̀ ne ̀ ɓi ɓito ̀ ki ̀ , ɓɛ kpaa ̀ kpa ̀ gsɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ kem ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll . Nni Pyɛɛri a ̀ kpaagha ̀ min lɛ :
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ mɛ teɗ Kitɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ sii teka ̀ , nni cɛ kɛɛ ri ɓii ̀ re ̀ gtii lɛ , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓti ɓɔ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ nig ?
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ min lɛ , ɓɛɛ ɓaɓti ɓɛn ̀ ɓi ɗii ɗi Kan Yeesus Kiris . Ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ki tɔg nyi lɛ , a kɔri ti ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkaa , ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru .
Ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓaa ɓɛ righerɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɛ kɔkɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ a Zyude ɓɛ woka ̀ lɛ , ɓumɓɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ kuu mɛm ̀ bog ɓɛ n ̀ gha ̀ ɓi girig jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pyɛɛri a ̀ sugti ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ ɓɔɔ ̀ gh a Yorisalɛm , ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ n nyi ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ y .
Ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ lɛ : Wɔ ̀ ɔ nɗiŋii ɓi naa yi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , u ̀ ki ɗi n ̀ ɗaŋ ri ɓɔ ?
Fɔɔnnɛ Pyɛɛri a ̀ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ ri ̀ tɛɛ ̀ zi ̀ ɗi kiɓan ki a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ki ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ :
Yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ Zyope di nki ̀ ki bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n , nni ki nki ̀ i mɛ ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ dɛ ̀ ndɛm lɛ : n ̀ ghɛɛ ri ̀ kuu ɗi coo sa ̀ nja ̀ ki ̀ sugakɛn ɓi mɛ ̀ keɓ mɛ kini ̀ n aɗyoo , ki yuyu ̀ y mɛ ̀ a nyo ̀ o ̀ .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ konaagh ki ̀ si ̀ ŋii sa ̀ nja ̀ a ̀ nce ̀ m , n ̀ ghɛn mii ̀ ɓi ɗu ̀ m lɛ : Ri ̀ nya ̀ m yi ɓi ziinɛ yi yi ri mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ mɛnin , ri ̀ nya ̀ m yi ɓi cog , ri ̀ yi wɔwɔghɛn ɗi ̀ ɗu ̀ m , ri ̀ ti ̀ i ̀ li ̀ ti aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
Nni nwoki ̀ , di jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ dɛŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ kpaakpaa mɛ lɛ : Pyɛɛri wɔ ̀ ! Pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyoo , u wey nya ̀ m bogtɛ ̀ n ɓi nya ̀ m yi , u ɗi .
Fɔɔnnɛ m ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , a ̀ g ! Kan , ɓi cɛɓ kɛ ̀ m ki ̀ ce ̀ m , n ̀ ka foga ̀ ɓi com ki ki ri ki ̀ ce ̀ li ̀ , nsoo ̀ lɛ ki ki ri ki ̀ syeg ɓi ŋwɔm wɛ ̀ m .
Nni jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛn i kpaati ̀ gha ̀ ɓi gɛ ̀ n i ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ lɛ , com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kpaa lɛ ki ri ̀ ki ̀ tɛnɛn , wɔ ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ kpaa lɛ , ki ri ri ̀ ki ̀ syeg .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ɓii ̀ tɛɛ fɔlɔɔ gɛ ̀ n yiraa , nni sa ̀ nja ̀ a ̀ sugti ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ ɓɔɔ ̀ gh aɗyoo ri ̀ ɓyom ɓi ̀ n .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn nnɛ ɓumɓɛ a Sezare ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛraa ɓɛ peetɛ ̀ nga ̀ y a mɛɛ mɛ m ̀ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ , lɛ ɓɛ romii ̀ ɓɔ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ .
Nni Nghay a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kpaagha ̀ mɛ ̀ lɛ : Sugtɛn ɗi ̀ ɓɔ , kɔɔ ̀ foŋ tika ̀ na . Ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓɛ ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ mɛ ̀ ki ̀ foŋi ̀ a Sezare , ti ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ ɓi naa i ̀ Kɔrinɛy .
Kɔrinɛy a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ si ri ̀ kpaa yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ di ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ yu ̀ u a mɛɛ mii , a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Rom ɓum a Zyope , lɛ ɓɛɛ reŋii ̀ Simɔn a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kpɔgi ̀ lɛ Pyɛɛri
nyɛɛ ri wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ kpaa ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ri ɓii ̀ ghɛɓsii lɛ , ri ̀ wɔ ̀ , ri ̀ naa yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ i ̀ ɓum bimiɗ
Lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ m ̀ mɛɛ ̀ pini ̀ gha ̀ ŋwɔm lɛ n ̀ too ̀ ghrɛn , Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ki sɛn yi ̀ ɓi ɓɔ , lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki sɛnga ̀ y girig ɓi ɓi ̀ si a ri ̀ tumɛ ̀ n .
Fɔɔnnɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ -yitii min jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ Kan a ̀ ka ̀ li ̀ gha ̀ lɛ : Zyaŋ a ̀ ɓa ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ nig , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin , ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓtɛɛ ri Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ mɛ fa ɓɔ com ki a ̀ fagha ̀ ɓi ̀ si ɓɛ ti ̀ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ Yeesus Kiris , nni mɛ ̀ ɛnɛ ghɛn anɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ , n ̀ ki ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗidɛŋ ?
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ woka ̀ ɓito ̀ ki ̀ ɓin ̀ , nnɛ ɓɛ kɔri ̀ gha ̀ lɛ fyo ̀ oog , ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ kemzi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll di ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa lɛ : Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ mɛ nɛm girig ɓumɓɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ kuu mɛm ̀ bog bee inɛ lɛ , ɓɛɛ lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛn mɛ ̀ rem , di ɓɛɛ ɓa ri ̀ cɛɓ .
N ̀ tɔɓ wu ɓɛ tɔtɔ ̀ ɓka ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓɛ wola ̀ Ityɛn , wu ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛɛ saa ̀ tɛn . Fɔɔnnɛ ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ dɛŋ i ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Fenisii , ri ̀ ɓi ki ̀ ri ̀ ŋ ki riɓa ̀ y ki lɛ Siipirɛ , ri ̀ a Aŋtyos , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , lɔŋ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɔ ri ̀ ɓɔ ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Nni ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n i ̀ dɛŋ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ a Siipirɛ , ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ a Sirɛn , ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ a Aŋtyos , ɓɔɔ toto ̀ ka ̀ girig ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ Gi ̀ rɛg , ɓɛ kpaakpaa ɓɔ Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ Kan Yeesus .
I ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu Kan wu ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ , kɛɛ kigha ̀ ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey lɛ ɓɛɛ lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛn mɛ ̀ rem , ɓɛɛ gherɛn Kan .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓi ki ̀ seŋi ki a Yorisalɛm ɓɛ woka ̀ gom i ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ romga ̀ Ɓarinaɓas a Aŋtyos .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kpaga ̀ wɔɔ , a ̀ ghɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ re ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ a ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛn ̀ , a ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ rɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ki toni ɓɔ lɛ : Si ̀ i ̀ rɛɛna lɔŋ ɓi Kan Yeesus , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ rem min mɛce ̀ m .
Ɓi saaɗ , Ɓarinaɓas a ̀ ɓagha ̀ syeesyee a ̀ mum , n ̀ ɗonɛn ɗi Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay , a ̀ ki gherɛn Bɛ ̀ ll lɛɛ ̀ gwey , fɔɔnnɛ ɓa ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey i ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ Kan .
Nni Ɓarinaɓas a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ min a Tarisi , a ̀ teɗ yi ̀ Sol .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ tanɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi wɔɔ , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ a Aŋtyos ɓɔɔ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ kɔri ̀ wɔɔ bimiɗ a ̀ be ̀ g , ɓɛ sasa ̀ y bas ri ̀ ki ̀ seŋi ki wɔɔ , ɓɛ ki re ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ ka ̀ coo ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll . Nni wɔɔ a Aŋtyos nnɛ ɓɛ tɔmga ̀ ki ̀ ro ̀ o ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɗii ɗi lɛ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ ristɛ ̀ n .
Ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ y a Yorisalɛm , ɓɛ sɛn a Aŋtyos .
Fɔɔnnɛ , ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɔ , ɗii lɛ Agaɓus , ki pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ aɗyoo , ki kali ̀ ɓum ri ̀ i ̀ teɗ wu Kitɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay lɛ , coo za ̀ y i ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i ɓi zi bimiɗ wɔ ̀ lɛ i ̀ ki ki ̀ gha ̀ , ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki Kiloodɛ a ̀ ɓaa ri ̀ fo ̀ m .
Nni ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ renga ̀ lɛ , mum bimiɗ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓɔ , a syɔɔ ̀ ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ com i ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ ghɛn , lɛ ɓɛɛ ghɛɓsi ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓaa ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ a Zyude mii ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kigha ̀ fɔlɔɔ , nni ɓɛ romga ̀ min Sol ɓɛɛ ̀ Ɓarinaɓas ri ̀ ɓyom ɓi ̀ n lɛ , ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ ɓyɔ ki ̀ faa ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ a Zyude .
Ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi lɛ Eroodɛ ɗi tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ tɔtɔ ̀ ɓ ɗi ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓi ki ̀ seŋi ki ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ wey Zyag a ̀ geni Zyaŋ ri ̀ ga ̀ fa ̀ g .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗin ̀ ɗi rɔɔgha ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ reɓsi ̀ gha ̀ ti ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓan ̀ Pyɛɛri ; ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki ɓagha ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ n ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g bi ̀ rɛs kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ nwi ̀ ɗ .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ Eroodɛ a ̀ ɓanga ̀ Pyɛɛri , a ̀ lɔg nyi , a ̀ foŋ ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛnin ɓɛnin gwi ̀ y yinin lɛ , ɓɛɛ ɓeŋ ̀ ɓeŋ nyi ri ̀ fe ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ , i ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ ti Paska ̀ ti ghaghii , ɓɛ yɔ ̀ m ki ̀ ɓan kii di ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki kɔkɔ ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ .
Ɓɛ ɓeŋɓe ̀ ŋga ̀ Pyɛɛri ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y , nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ n ̀ ɗaŋ wu ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n wu ɓɔɔɓɔ ̀ ŋza ̀ g Bɛ ̀ ll ɓisu wii ri i ̀ te ̀ ɗ .
Di ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ m ɓɛ Pyɛɛri ɓaa rɔ ̀ ɓ lɛ ri ̀ duri , a ̀ lala ̀ la ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ , n ̀ ka ̀ ŋɛn ɗi mɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ŋi mɛɓɛɛ ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛm ̀ bog ɓɛ ɓeŋ ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋ mɛ ̀ suunaa mɛ naa ̀ -za ̀ y .
Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a Kan a ̀ kpaga ̀ y lɛ vwa ̀ s ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ki kpeŋzi ̀ ki ̀ den ki naa ki Pyɛɛri a ̀ ɓagha ̀ mii ̀ . Nni ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom anɛ ̀ n a ̀ ghe ̀ mzi ̀ gha ̀ Pyɛɛri di a ̀ nyɛ ̀ ŋi nyi ɓi tum , a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyoo lɛ fyɛ ̀ ɗ , fɔɔnnɛ mɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ŋi mɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ mɔ ɓi ɓya ̀ g , mɛ fumɓɛ ̀ nga ̀ .
Ŋwaa ̀ fi ̀ tom a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Si ̀ nɛn ka ̀ nɗa , u ̀ ki waatɛn ɓɛsiripa ̀ s ɓɔɔ , Pyɛɛri a ̀ ki ̀ lɔŋ fɔlɔɔ ; nni a ̀ kpaati ̀ gha ̀ nyi lɛ , waatɛn ki ̀ la ̀ a ̀ u nɔɔ ̀ ti mɛ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Pyɛɛri a ̀ kpaga ̀ y , a ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ nyi kɛ ̀ ɛ yi lɛ com ki ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a yu ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i kin ̀ ki ɓagha ̀ saaɗ a ̀ ki ̀ ɓan , nyii feki ̀ lɔŋ lɛ ɓi ̀ dɛ ̀ ndɛm ɓyɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki nyi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ceegha ̀ ki ̀ tuu ki ɓɛsuja ̀ a ̀ ki n ̀ tonto , ɓɛ ceeti ̀ ki kiɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , nni ɓɛ kpaga ̀ asuunaa wu wu ɓagha ̀ wu ̀ ki ̀ yɛn ɗi bɔŋ , wu ki seesee ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ ɓi ba ̀ n . I ̀ suunaa wi ̀ n wu nɛmɓɛ ̀ nga ̀ wɔmiɗ di ɓɔɔ ti wɔɔ ja ̀ ŋbog . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ kpaga ̀ ɓi dan ɓɛ fyee ɓi ki ̀ ɓa ̀ a ̀ ki ̀ dɛŋ , nni ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a ̀ gha ̀ ska ̀ ki ̀ rinii Pyɛɛri , a ̀ ghaa ̀ gh .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pyɛɛri a ̀ sugti ̀ gha ̀ min ɓi nyimiɗ , a ̀ kpaa lɛ , n ̀ konaagh min ki ghɛɛ ̀ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ lɛ , Kan a ̀ a romii ̀ mum wii ̀ a ̀ fi ̀ tom , a ̀ sɔri ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓi ɓya ̀ g ɓi Eroodɛ , a ̀ ki lɛgsi mɛ mɛ ̀ tɔɓ mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m mɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ n ̀ fe ̀ feegh lɛ n ̀ ghɛn .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pyɛɛri a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ lɛ fyo ̀ oog , a ̀ fe ̀ g , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ rɔ ̀ ŋi ̀ gha ̀ bee inɛ a mɛɛ mɛ Marii a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ jɛɛ Zyaŋ a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ nkpɔgi ̀ lɛ Marikus , ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ taŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ wɔɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓɔŋzag .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pyɛɛri a ̀ ɓoka ̀ i ̀ suunaa , nni giɓ adɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say ɗii lɛ Roodɛ a ̀ yugha ̀ y lɛ a woo ̀ ghrag .
Nni a ̀ re ̀ mi ̀ gha ̀ Pyɛɛri ɓi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , a ̀ wog ki ̀ rɔɔ : Kɛ ̀ ɛ ka ŋwa ̀ ɗ nyi naa , ki ̀ ɓan kifog a ̀ sugti ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ree lɛ a kali ɓum lɛ ; Pyɛɛri yɛɛ ri asuunaa .
Ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kpaa nyi lɛ : U ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ duŋɛn ? Wɔ ̀ lɛ nyii sii ̀ rɛ ̀ n lɔŋ lɛ , ki ̀ ɓan ki nyaa kpaa ki ri saaɗ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ min lɛ : n ̀ ghay wu Pyɛɛri wɛɛ ri ̀ nya lɛ wu ɓa , nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ Pyɛɛri a ̀ kɛ ̀ nkɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɔŋ asu ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓoɓo ̀ g ɗi naa . Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ŋwaɗka ̀ naa , ɓɛ ghɛn nyi , ɓɛ kuura ̀ g lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Pyɛɛri a ̀ maasi ̀ ɓɔ ri ̀ ca ̀ g , a ̀ ki kali ɓɔ yɛ ̀ ɛ Kan a ̀ kpaŋzi yi ̀ nyi ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y , a ̀ kpaa ti ̀ ɓɔ lɛ , kaliina Zyag ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓis ɓɛmbog ki ̀ ɓan ki , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpaga ̀ , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ja ̀ ŋ idɛŋ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ duri i ̀ tanga ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan ki yeesi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ , ɓɛ rɔɓ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛ ̀ kanikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ɓɛ tɔtɔ ̀ g lɛ : Nni Pyɛɛri a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓaa la ̀ ?
Eroodɛ a ̀ tɔka ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ kaa ̀ Pyɛɛri , nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ rɔɓka ̀ kɛ ̀ ɓɛɛ ̀ ghɛn nyi , ɓɛ yɔmzi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ nce ̀ m , Eroodɛ a ̀ ki reɓsi lɛ ɓɛɛ cuu ̀ si bɔ . Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Zyude a ̀ kɛ ̀ n a Sezare , a ̀ ghagsi ̀ ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru wɔɔ .
Eroodɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi paa ̀ zi ̀ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ a Tiir , ri ̀ ɓɛ a Sidɔŋ , nni ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ wooghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ y jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ nyi ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ . Ɓɛ ɗiŋi da ̀ ŋ ri ̀ Bilastus a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ ɓi gari yii ̀ . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ tɔka ̀ nyi lɛ ɓɔɔ pe ̀ gsɛn paa ̀ zi ̀ wa ̀ a ̀ , ɓisuulɛ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kaa ki n ̀ laka ̀ g ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki rifo ̀ m .
Ŋwos anɛ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki ɓagha ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ ikilɛ ̀ n Eroodɛ a ̀ waatɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ɓii ɓi rifo ̀ m , a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ki ̀ nuugh , a ̀ ki tumɛn ɓito ̀ ki ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki kpaagha ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ dɛŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ to ̀ tog lɔɔ , a ̀ a mum yɛɛ ri .
Lɔŋ wɔɔ foo , ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a Kan a ̀ ɓog nyi ɓisuulɛ a ̀ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ fa nyi ri ̀ kem ɗi ɗi ghɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ fa Bɛ ̀ ll . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛgɛn ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi ri ̀ ɗiɗi ̀ ɓi ɗu ̀ m , a ̀ wu .
Nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ , jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ asu i ̀ sa ̀ a ̀ sa ̀ a ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ Ɓarinaɓas ɓɛɛ ̀ Sol ɓɛ le ̀ gsi ̀ gha ̀ fi ̀ tom fi ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ a Yorisalɛm , nni ɓɛ sugti ̀ gha ̀ ; ɓɛ ɓasɛ ̀ n yi ̀ ɗi ̀ Zyaŋ a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ nkpɔgi ̀ lɛ Marikus .
Ɓi ki ̀ seŋi ki a Aŋtyos , ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɗi ̀ ɓyoo ɓɛre ̀ sa ̀ g su ̀ kuru ̀ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ . Ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ lɛ : ri ̀ Ɓarinaɓas ri ̀ Simeyɔŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓati ̀ gha ̀ ɗii lɛ ŋwaa ̀ -n ̀ fin , ri ̀ Lusyus a ̀ nɛ a Sirɛn ri ̀ Manaɛŋ a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ tɔɔsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ gɔmi ̀ na ̀ a ̀ nɛ lɛ Eroodɛ , ri ̀ Sol .
Ŋwos adɛŋ a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi ɗii ɗi Kan , ɓɛ ki ce ̀ li ɓiɗila ̀ g ɓi ŋwos a ̀ nce ̀ m a ̀ nɛn , Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ki kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ ! Pisiina mɛ ̀ ɓum ɓɛ lɛ ri ̀ Ɓarinaɓas , ri ̀ Sol , lɛ ɓɛɛ ki ki ̀ say ki n ̀ ɗegi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ ki .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ kigha ̀ lɛ , ɓaa ce ̀ li ɓiɗila ̀ g , ɓɛ ɓɔŋza ̀ g Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓɛ ki saaghrag ɓɔ ɓya ̀ g ɓi nyoo , ɓɛ ca ̀ ɗ min ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ ghaa ̀ gh .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ki romga ̀ Sol ɓɛɛ ̀ Ɓarinaɓas fɔlɔɔ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ sɛnga ̀ a Silisii , wɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ɓɔka ̀ ki ̀ kɔm lɛ ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ a Siipirɛ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kpaga ̀ a Salamin , ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ ɓum Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi naa yi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n yi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ; ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɗi ̀ Zyaŋ lɛ a ghɛɛ ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɓsi ̀ ɓɔ .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , di ɓaa sya ̀ a ̀ kiri ̀ ŋ ki riɓa ̀ y ki ̀ ce ̀ m , nni ɓɛ kpaga ̀ a Pafos , wɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ tanɛ ̀ nga ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -maji ̀ g a ̀ dɛŋ ɗii lɛ Bari-Yeesus , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ muu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ki ye ̀ eghyegsi ̀ ɓum lɛ nyii ri n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ghan ɗi gɔmi ̀ na ̀ a ̀ nɛ lɛ , Sɛrizyus-Paolus , gɔmi ̀ na ̀ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ŋwaa ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ Ɓarinaɓas ɓɛɛ ̀ Sol lɛ , a ̀ kɔ ̀ nkɔ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ a wog ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll .
Nni Elimas , yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -maji ̀ g ɓi ri ̀ gi ̀ rɛg , nyii ramzɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ baŋi ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ -Ɓarinaɓas ɓɛɛ ̀ Sol , a ̀ kaaka ̀ a ̀ bee inɛ lɛ gɔmi ̀ na ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ gherɛn Bɛ ̀ ll .
Fɔɔnnɛ Sol a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓati ̀ gha ̀ ɗii lɛ , Pol a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ ɗonɛn ri Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ; a ̀ fiɓi ̀ gha ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ fyɛɛɛyi
a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Wɔ ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ , u ̀ ri ̀ lɛ , wɔ ̀ coo ghe ̀ ghes ̀ , wɔ ̀ ɓe ̀ e ̀ ɓee ̀ , man a ̀ Sata ̀ n anɛ lɛ wɔ ̀ , be ̀ na ̀ bena a ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi saaɗ , u ̀ yin ɓi ̀ i ̀ rɛɛrɛɛ ̀ si ̀ ri ̀ yoo ̀ yo ̀ gsi ̀ ɗi bee yi Kan yi yi ri lɛ saaɗ ?
Ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , yiya lɛ Kan a ̀ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ pɔnɔsii , u ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɗiŋii tiɗyaŋ , fɔɔnnɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ finɛɛ maa ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kɔ ̀ ɔ ghɛɛ ̀ di kisaa ki ŋwos . Nni mis mii mɛ ghaska ̀ ki ̀ ɓuli ̀ , biri ̀ m i ̀ sigtɛ ̀ n nyi , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ gbɔ ̀ mgbɔ ̀ m di a kaakaa ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ɓan nyi ɓi ca ̀ g , a kɛɛ ̀ si nyi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ gɔmi ̀ na ̀ a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ , nni a ̀ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓisuulɛ , dɔgtɛ ̀ n i ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi seesee Kan , i ̀ ko ̀ mga ̀ nyi n ̀ ɗem lɛ syeesyee .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pol ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ reŋka ̀ ŋ ɓii ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Pafos , ɓɛ teɗ ki ̀ kɔm lɛ ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ a Pɛrizɛ a ̀ nɛ a Paŋfilii Zyaŋ nyii ghasɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ , a ̀ sugti a Yorisalɛm .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Pɛrizɛ , ɓɛ ghagsi ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɗyaa , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ a Aŋtyos a ̀ nɛ a Pisidii . Nni ɓɛ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi naa i ̀ bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n i ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , ŋwosi Saɓa ̀ t ɓɛ kɔri ɓi zi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ le ̀ gsi ̀ gha ̀ ki ɓa ̀ li kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Moyis ri ̀ ɓi a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan , nni ɓɛ ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n ɓɛ romga ̀ mum lɛ a kali ɓɛ ̀ -Pol lɛ : Bɔɔsoŋ ! i ̀ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ deɓ yidɛŋ yi ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ fa ɓum , to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛɛna ɓigominɛ .
Nni Pol a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ aɗyoo , a ̀ maasi ̀ ɓum ɗi ̀ ca ̀ g , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Mi ̀ ni ɓɔn ɓɛ Isirayɛl ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ɓi risag Bɛ ̀ ll , ramina mɛ ̀ ree ̀ !
Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki lɛ Isirayɛl , a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓis , a ̀ ki ki ̀ lɛ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kin ̀ kɛɛ tɔɔ ̀ , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ a Egiɓtɛn , ajɛ ̀ m inɛn nnɛ a ̀ pisi ̀ gha ̀ y ɓɔ wɔɔ ri i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wii .
A ̀ mɛni ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ ɓi-reɓ nunu ̀ g be ̀ g mɛ ̀ tin mɛɓɛɛ ̀ .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ cuusi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓi zii ̀ Kanaaŋ , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ fagha ̀ zi yaa ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓis .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki finɛ ̀ nga ̀ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ be ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ hɔnɗɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛnin , ri ̀ be ̀ g mɛ ̀ tin mɛɓɛɛ ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ . Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ ɓɔ ɓɛ ̀ reni ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɔ yɛɛ kɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan a ̀ nɛ lɛ Samuɛl .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ tɔka ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓa ri ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m , nni Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ ɓɔ Saul , man a ̀ Kis a ̀ nɛ ɓi ri ̀ pwi ̀ ɗ ɗi Bɛŋzyamɛŋ , nnyɛɛ lami ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ be ̀ g mɛ ̀ tin mɛɓɛɛ ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ pisi ̀ gha ̀ Saul , a ̀ fa ɓɔ Davit lɛ nnyɛɛ ɓa ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗyaa . Davit a ̀ nɛ ̀ n innɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ sɛka ̀ a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Mɛ ̀ ɛ nghɛɛ Davit , man a ̀ lzayii , a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ kuu ɗi mum ɗi nɗem wɛ ̀ m wu n ̀ fe ̀ feegh , nnyɛɛ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i ɓiɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi n ̀ kɔ ̀ ni lɛ a ki .
Ɓi do ̀ o ̀ yi Davit a ̀ nɛ ̀ n nnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ Yeesus a yalɛn fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ghɛɓsi ̀ lsrayɛl , lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ nyimiɗ a ka ̀ ka ̀ .
Di Yeesus a ̀ ka yu ɓi , Zyaŋ a ̀ rere ̀ ŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓumɓɛ a Isirayɛl lɛ ɓɛɛ lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛn mɛ ̀ rem , ɓɛ ɓaɓta ̀ g .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Zyaŋ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ ti ɓii ̀ le ̀ gsii ki ̀ say kii , nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ , a ̀ a mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ri ̀ roa ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓoŋɓo ̀ ŋ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ mɛ ̀ ajɛ ̀ m , nnyɛɛ ri ri ̀ kuu ɗi mum ɗi mɛ ̀ n ̀ kpaŋi ɓi ɓi n ̀ koŋ wulɛ , n ̀ fu ̀ mi ̀ n ̀ ɗig wii wu go ̀ o ̀ .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ ! Mi ̀ ni do ̀ o ̀ yi Abiraham ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓum ɓɛ zɛy ɓɛ ɓi ̀ ti ɓi ̀ risa ̀ g Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓɔlɛ a ̀ cɛɓ a ̀ nɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ ɓisu wis ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ɓumɓɛ a Yorisalɛm ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɓaa , ɓɛ roo ̀ zɛ ̀ nga ̀ Yeesus , ki ̀ ɓan ki ̀ fog ɓi ri ̀ ren ɗi ɓɛ renga ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ wey nyi , ɓɛ ro ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ kali ̀ ɗi ɓɛkpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɗi ɓɛti ɓɛ ɓaa ̀ yi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ŋwos ɓɛ Saɓa ̀ t ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Nsoo ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ ɓi n ̀ to wu kiɓan wu ɓɛɛ wey nyi mii ̀ , ɓɛ tɔka ̀ Pilat lɛ a kali ɓɛɛ wey Yeesus .
Fɔɔnnɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ le ̀ gsi ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ɓiɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓi ɓagha ̀ ɓi ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ɓi rarɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ nyi , nni ɓɛ kɔsi ̀ gha ̀ y nyi ɓi kɔrɔs ɓɛ ɓom nyi ɓi zɔ ̀ ŋ .
Nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ghe ̀ mzi ̀ gha ̀ y nyi ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓi ̀ loŋ .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ re ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru lɛɛ ̀ gwey a ɓumɓɛ a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ y ri ̀ ɓɔ a Galile ɓɛ ɓɔg a Yorisalɛm n ̀ ɗaŋ , ɓɔ yɛɛ ti ɓɛ ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ tɛɛtɛɛ ̀ zi ̀ ɓumɓɛ a Isirayɛl ki ̀ ɓan kii .
Ɓi ̀ si girig , ti ̀ yu ̀ u mi ̀ ni ri ̀ Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ lɛ , n ̀ ka ̀ g wu wu falɛ ̀ nga ̀ a ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓis ,
Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ roozii wɔ ɓisu wis , ɓɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔn ɓaa , ɓi ri ̀ ghe ̀ mzi ̀ ɗi a ̀ a n ̀ ghe ̀ mzii Yeesus , fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ɓi Sam a ̀ ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ lɛ : U ̀ ri ̀ man wɛm ̀ , mɛ ̀ n ̀ ki ɓa soŋi ̀ a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n gɛɛ ̀ nɛ .
Ri ̀ ghe ̀ mzi ̀ ɗi a ̀ ghe ̀ mzi ̀ gha ̀ nyi a ɓi ̀ loŋ lɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓwɛ ̀ y , ɗi ri lɔŋ kiɓan ki nyimiɗ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : N ̀ ɗi ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ faa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ɓɛ ɓyom ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ tɛnɛn , ɓɛ n ̀ ka ̀ ka ̀ Davit .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki a ̀ kpaatii ja ̀ ŋ idɛŋ ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ wi ̀ i ̀ lɛ : Wa ̀ a ca ̀ ɗ ɓi ̀ mum wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ntɛnɛn lɛ , a ɓwɛy ɓi zɔ ̀ ŋ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ , Davit a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kii nni a ̀ wugha ̀ , ɓɛ ɓom ̀ nyi ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɛ ɓomga ̀ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓii , a ̀ ki ɓwɛ ̀ y ɓi zɔ ̀ ŋ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , roa ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ghe ̀ mzi ̀ gha ̀ , nyii ɓɔla ̀ ɓi ɓi zɔ ̀ ŋ .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ ! Konaaghna ki ̀ yii ̀ lɛ ɓisu wii nnɛ ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ lɛ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ cenɛɛ ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓyaa , a kpaakpaa ̀ rɛ ̀ n a lɔ ̀ ŋkin .
Ɓi Yeesus a ̀ nɛn nnɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ gherɛɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ tɔ ̀ sɛɛ ɓiɓe ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Moyis ɓi ɓagha ̀ ɓi lɛ , ɓi pisi ̀ .
Kɔ ̀ riina ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ! Lɛ kɛ ̀ ɓi tulɛn ɗi ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛkpaagha ̀ , ɓi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ lɛ :
Mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ daŋa ̀ daŋa , ghɛɛna di ɓi kuughrag , ɓi ̀ ki pɛ ̀ sɛn mɛ ɓi mis , ɓisuulɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i rikuu ɗi kiɓan ɗidɛŋ ɓi mɛ ̀ ru min ɗi ɓi ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi lɛ ɓi ̀ gherɛ ̀ n lɛ , ɗi ri lɛ ɗi kilɛ ̀ n di ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ yɛɛ kpaa mi ̀ ni lɛ ɗyaa ki ̀ lɛɛ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Sol ɓɛɛ ̀ Ɓarinaɓas ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ di ɓɛ ti ɓii ̀ kpaŋi ̀ i ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n , ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ tɔg ɓɔ lɛ , ɓɛɛ sugtii ̀ ŋwosi Saɓa ̀ t a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɓka ̀ y , lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓii ̀ ti ɓɔ ki ̀ kalii kiɓan kin ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ gha ̀ da ̀ ɗi leka ̀ , Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n lɛɛ ̀ gwey ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ zɛy ɓɛ ɓɛ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ nɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ Pol ɓɛɛ ̀ Ɓarinaɓas , ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kuu ̀ ku ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ ɓɔ , ɓɛ tee ̀ te ̀ e ̀ si ̀ ɓɔ nyoo di ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa ɓɔ lɛ , ɓɛɛ kɛn asu , ɓɛ ki si ̀ i ̀ rɛn ɓi geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Nni go ̀ n i Saɓa ̀ t i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɓka ̀ foo , ɓaa ̀ yiɓi ba ̀ n bimiɗ yɛ ̀ ɛ taŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ wog jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ gɛ ɓum a ̀ nɛ ̀ n , nni n ̀ ɗem wu ya ̀ aka wu ɓɔka ̀ y ɓɔ , ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ fee ̀ fe ̀ ngi ̀ ɗi Pol di ɓɛɛ ̀ sɛɛsɛ ̀ mgi ̀ nyi .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ -Pol ɓɛɛ ̀ Ɓarinaɓas ɓɛ kpagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ fwa ̀ afwa ̀ a ̀ y lɛ : Ki n ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ , jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll yɛ ̀ ɛ log ki ̀ kpaarɛɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin , nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ ɓe ̀ ni yɔ ̀ yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ , ɓi ̀ ghɛɛ lɛ cɛɓ ki fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ri mi ̀ ni , nni ɓi ̀ sii tiŋ ̀ mɛɛ min a ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n .
Ɓisuulɛ , Kan a kalag ɓisi lɛ : N ̀ ɗɛsi ̀ gha ̀ wɔ ̀ lɛ , u ̀ ɓa fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓimbog u ̀ ki sa ̀ a ̀ ti cɛɓ ɓi zi bimiɗ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ woka ̀ ri ̀ kpaa ɗi ̀ n ɓɛ nyaa ̀ rɛ ̀ n lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ kee ̀ ke ̀ mzi ̀ ɗi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Kan . Nni fɔɔnnɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ nɛn lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓa ri ̀ cɛɓ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ Kan a ̀ sa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ ja ̀ ŋbimiɗ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kin ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ toosi ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ te ̀ ete ̀ ɗ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓi ɓi falɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ri ̀ gi ̀ ni-ɓum yi ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛn lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓigti paa ̀ zi ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ -Pol ɓɛɛ ̀ Ɓarinaɓas ; fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ kpaga ̀ ɓɔ ri ̀ baŋi ̀ , ɓɛ ki na ̀ ɓ ɓɔ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kaa .
Ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kwiɗ ku ̀ ru ̀ ɓu a ̀ nɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ maa ɓi ɓɔ , lɛ a ɓa ki ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ ki lɛ , ɓɛ na ̀ ɓi ɓɔ ; fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ min ɓɛ kɛn ̀ a Ikonyɔm .
Ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ a Aŋtyos , ɓɛ ron ̀ ga ̀ ka ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ ɓi n ̀ ɗem , ɓɛ ki ɓa ti ɓɛ ronɛn ɗi Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay .
A Ikonyɔm , Pol ɓɛɛ ̀ Ɓarinaɓas ɓɛ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ girig ɓi naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n i ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ kurɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ɓum , le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n lɛɛ ̀ gwey ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓenga ̀ dɔgtɛ ̀ n i ̀ Pol , ɓɛ toosi ̀ gha ̀ ɓum ɓɛ zɛy lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓa ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛyiti ̀ ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓis ɓɛ righerɛ ̀ n .
Pol ɓɛɛ ̀ Ɓarinaɓas ɓɛ finɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Ikonyɔm lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ coo n ̀ tyweeyi ri Kan ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ fafa ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ , ɓɛɛ , kiki lɛ ri ̀ da ̀ m , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ koŋnyoo ɓɛ ɓiɓan , a ̀ ki ̀ fɔlɔɔ lɛ a sii ̀ rag ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ ɓi komko ̀ m geesɛ ̀ n yi ̀ i ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛn ɓɛ lanɛ ̀ nga ̀ ga ̀ ɓ yiɓɛɛ ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ sug jɛ ̀ m ɗi ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , ɓɛmbog ɓɛ sug jɛ ̀ m ɗi ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ɓɛ Yeesus .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓumɓɛ zɛy , ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɓaa ɓɛ pee ̀ ghpe ̀ gsɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ ki ɓɔ n ̀ tɔɓ , ɓɛ rogi ̀ ɓɔ gɔ ̀ g ,
Pol ɓɛɛ ̀ Ɓarinaɓas ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ lɛ ɓaa ghɛn fɔlɔɔ , ɓɛ kaa bee inɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ ghɛŋi ki ̀ nya ̀ mzɛɛ a Likawonii ri ̀ a Listirɛ , ri ̀ a Dɛriɓɛ ri ̀ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ yidɛŋ yi yi ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ ja ̀ ŋbog .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ghagsi ̀ gha ̀ Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ wɔɔ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ yin ̀ .
Ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ yɛɛ ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ wɔ ̀ g a Listirɛ . A rɔ ̀ ɓka ̀ ki ̀ sɛkɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ tumɛn a ri ̀ yalɛ ̀ n ɗii , nsoo ̀ ŋwos adɛŋ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi kirɛlii mɛrɛy , a ̀ ɓa ̀ y i ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ .
Nni ŋwos adɛŋ a ̀ nɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ wowo ̀ ka ̀ di Pol a ̀ to ̀ to ̀ g , fɔɔnnɛ Pol a ̀ pɛɓsɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi , a ̀ fiɓi ̀ nyi lɛ fyɛɛɛyi a ̀ ghɛn lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɗi ̀ n ̀ tyweeyi lɛ a wɔɔ ̀ zi nyi .
Nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyoo , u rɛli mɛrɛy wɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ . Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ aɗyoo lɛ fa ̀ tweɗ , a ̀ ghagsɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ gɛ ɓum a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ a ghɛnga ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki Pol a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ kin ̀ , nni ɓɛ la ̀ mɓɛ ̀ nga ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo ɓi ki ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ki ɓumɓɛ a Likawonii lɛ ɓɛ ̀ y yidɛŋ yɛɛ yuu ̀ yi ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkaa , ɓi nghay wu ɓum .
Nni ɓɛ roo ̀ gha ̀ Ɓarinaɓas ɗii ɗi ɓɛ ̀ y i ̀ nɛ lɛ Zes , ɓɛ ro ̀ o ̀ Pol ɗii lɛ Ɛrmɛs , ɓisuulɛ nnyɛɛ toto ̀ ka ̀ .
Nni pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ y i ̀ nɛ lɛ Zes , inɛ naa yi ̀ i ̀ i ɓagha ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ɗigi ̀ ɗi ɓi ba ̀ n , a ̀ yugha ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ lem ɓɛ ɓɛ ̀ sani ̀ nya ɓɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ gakɛn ri zyo ̀ na ̀ yi ɓila ̀ a ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ bog ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛmbog ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m lɛ ɓɛɛ funɛn ɓi ̀ tuwe ɓin ̀ , ɓɛɛ ɓɔgsi ɓɛ ̀ y yi yi yugha ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkaa , yi lɛ ri ̀ Ɓarinaɓas ri ̀ Pol .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ɓɛ lɛ , ri ̀ Pol ri ̀ Ɓarinaɓas ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ fɔlɔɔ , nni ɓɛ ghaska ̀ ka ̀ ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ɓyaa ɓɛ tɔy ɓi gwi ̀ y di ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ :
Ɓi ki ̀ ki fɔlɔɔ lɛ la ? Ɓi ̀ sii ri girig ɓum lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ mi ̀ ni . Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ ti ghaaghagsi ̀ mi ̀ ni a ̀ ri lɛ , ɓi caɗ ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi ɓinu ̀ n ɓi zɛy ri ̀ zɛy , ɓi lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ cencem , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ɗyoo ri ̀ zi , ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n ɗi ̀ ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓi ri mii ̀ .
Ɓi gba ̀ a ̀ yi ajɛ ̀ m , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ca ̀ ɗka ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓyɛɛ nɔɔ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ bee yi ɓi kɔni lɛ ɓyɛɛ nɔɔ ̀ ti .
Nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ , a ̀ re ̀ re ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ lɔŋ riɓa ɗii , ɓi ɓi ̀ rɔɔ ɓi a ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ɓum , a ̀ ti a ̀ nɔsa ̀ g mi ̀ ni bwey , a ̀ ki ̀ lɛ , ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓyɛɛ ɗiŋi mi ̀ ni , a ̀ fa mi ̀ ni ɓyom ɓiɗiyɛn lɛɛ ̀ gwey , a ̀ ki roo ̀ zi mɛrem min ɗi ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ .
Ri ̀ n ̀ tɔɓ lɛɛ ̀ gwey i ̀ nnɛ ri ̀ kpaa ɗyaa ɗin ̀ ɗi ki re ̀ ka ̀ gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ , yɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ fu ̀ nɛn ɓi ̀ tuwe ɓisu waa .
Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ y a Aŋtyos a ̀ nɛ a Pisidii ri ̀ a Ikonyɔm , ɓɛ syoŋ gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum ɓi ga ̀ m ya ̀ a ̀ , ɓɛ rogi ̀ Pol gɔ ̀ g ɓɛ syo ̀ ŋ nyi , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ nyi ki ̀ naŋi ̀ ɓi nwɔŋi ̀ wu ba ̀ n lɛ ɓɛ fefe ̀ ka ̀ lɛ a ̀ mɛ wu .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ taŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi a ̀ nyoo , a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ n aɗyoo , a ̀ sugti ̀ ki ̀ ɗiŋii ɓi ba ̀ n . Ɓi duri tana , ɓɛ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Dɛriɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ Ɓarinaɓas .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pol ɓɛɛ ̀ Ɓarinaɓas ɓɛ ghagsi ̀ gha ̀ Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛ lɛ Dɛriɓɛ , ɓɛ ki syo ̀ ŋ ɓum wɔɔ lɛɛ ̀ gwey , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ sugti ̀ gha ̀ a Listirɛ , ri ̀ a Ikonyɔm , ri ̀ a Aŋtyos a ̀ nɛ a Pisidii .
Ɓɛ fafa ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ wɔɔ ite ̀ ɗ ɓi n ̀ ɗem ɓɛ rere ̀ ɓ ɓɔ lɛ , ɓɛɛ sii ̀ rɛn ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , di ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa lɛ : Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ , ti ka wog mɛtɔɓ lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓi ɗi lɛ ti ɗiŋi ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll .
Nni ɓɛ rɛsa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓi naa yi Bɛ ̀ ll yi ̀ ce ̀ m yi wɔɔ . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ lɛ , i ɓaa ce ̀ li ɓiɗila ̀ g , ɓɛ ɓɔŋzi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓɛ reɓsɛ ̀ n min ɓɔ ri ̀ Kan a ̀ nɛ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ saghi ̀ gha ̀ n ̀ tyweeyi waa ɓi nyi .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ceegha ̀ ɓi kiden ki zi ki lɛ Pisidii , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ a Paŋfilii .
Ɓɛ mɛ ghagsi Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a Pɛrizɛ , ɓɛ sɛn min a Atalii .
Wɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ teri min kikɔm lɛ , ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ a Aŋtyos a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ y wɔɔ , ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɛ reɓsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ geesɛ ̀ n , ɓisuu kisay ki ɓɛ kigha ̀ y kin ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kpaga ̀ a Aŋtyos , ɓɛ taŋzɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓi ki ̀ seŋi ki wɔɔ , ɓɛ kpaa ɓɔ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ ɓɔ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ ɓɛɛ kiki ̀ , a ̀ ɓiisɛ ̀ n ri ̀ nɛm ɗi a ̀ nɛmga ̀ ɓum ɓɛ zɛy bee inɛ ɓɛɛ gherɛn girig nyi .
Ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ Pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ y a Zyude ɓɛ yu a Aŋtyos , ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ re ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ɗi ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n di ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa lɛ : I ̀ ɓi ̀ kɛ ̀ rɛɛ ɓi , yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Moyis ɓyɛɛ ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ , ɓi ̀ yin lɛ ɓi ̀ ghɛn cɛɓ .
Fɔɔnnɛ coo kiyoo ̀ yo ̀ o ̀ ki kpigha ̀ , di ̀ Pol ɓɛɛ ̀ Ɓarinaɓas ɓɛ mɛ teɗ rire ̀ sa ̀ g ɗi ɓumɓɛ ̀ n nyoey , ɓɛ ren min lɛ , ri ̀ Pol ri ̀ Ɓarinaɓas ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ , ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓɔɔ ̀ gh a Yorisalɛm lɛ , ɓɛɛ ghɛn ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ lɛ ɓɛɛ fiɓi ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ .
Ki ̀ seŋi ki ki a Aŋtyos ki fagha ̀ ɓɔ ɓyom ɓi ɓi kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɗyaa : Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ fyeegha ̀ a Fenisii ri ̀ a Samari di ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa ɓɛgeni ɓaa rilɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓum ɓɛ zɛy ɓɛ lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ , ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ n Bɛ ̀ ll . Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ fagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓaa ɓɛn ̀ coo kinya ̀ a ̀ ɓi n ̀ ɗem .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kpaga ̀ a Yorisalɛm nni ki ̀ seŋi ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ ghaɓka ̀ ɓɔ , fɔɔnnɛ Pol ɓɛɛ ̀ Ɓarinaɓas ɓɛ resi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn nnɛ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓi n ̀ ɗaŋ wu Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ ristɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ aɗyoo , ɓɛ kpaa lɛ : Ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ kɛ ̀ raagh , ɓɛ ki ̀ ka ̀ ŋ ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓeŋ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Moyis .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ taŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ fiɓi ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ .
Di ɓaa nyolɛn lɛɛ ̀ gwey , nni Pyɛɛri a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ aɗyoo , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ ! Ɓi ̀ yii lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ nga ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n lɔŋ a ri ̀ tumɛ ̀ n lɛ , nkali Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ɓum ɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , lɛ i ɓɛ woogh Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n , ɓɛɛ gherɛn Bɛ ̀ ll .
Nni Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ yii mɛ ̀ rem mɛ ɓum , a ̀ a n ̀ ɗe ̀ sii lɛ a ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ɓɔ , yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ a n ̀ faa ɓɔ girig Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ fagha ̀ ɓi ̀ si ;
a ̀ a n ̀ ɗe ̀ sii ɓi n ̀ ɗe ̀ e ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ nɛ lɛ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si ri ̀ ɓɔ , a ̀ a n ̀ tɛɛ ̀ zii ɓɔ mɛ ̀ rem lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓɛ n ̀ gherɛɛ nyi .
Nni lannɛ ɓi kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ ɓi fee ̀ ghrɛn Bɛ ̀ ll , yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ki ̀ ki lɛ ɓi tɛgsi ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g n ̀ tɛ ̀ g wu wu kigha ̀ lɛ , wu yag ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓis , wu ki yag ti ɓisi ri ̀ tɛ ̀ g ?
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ sii gherɛɛ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ mɛ ghɛɓsi ɓisi lɛ geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ Kan Yeesus lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɔ girig .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ a ri ̀ gha ̀ da ̀ ɗin ̀ ɓɛ maagha ̀ lɛ fyo ̀ oog , ɓɛ wowo ̀ g yɛ ̀ ɛ Pol ɓɛɛ ̀ Ɓarinaɓas ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ da ̀ m yi ɓiɓan , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ koŋnyoo ɓɛ ɓiɓan ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓum ɓɛ zɛy .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ le ̀ gsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ , nni Zyag a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ aɗyoo , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ ! Wooghna girig ri ̀ kpaa ɗyɛ ̀ m !
Simɔn a ̀ a re ̀ sii ɓi ̀ si yɛ ̀ ɛ ki kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ a ri ̀ tumɛ ̀ n lɛ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ɓɔn ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki kɛɛ ɓa kiŋkii , ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi zɛy .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ gi ̀ ri ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ :
Kan lɛ , ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , n ̀ ɗi sugtii gɛs ̀ m ̀ pɛ ̀ si ̀ mɛɛ mɛ Davit mɛ mɛ kpila ̀ ka ̀ ; fɔɔnnɛ m ̀ pe ̀ gsaagh gɛ ja ̀ ŋ yi yi ri yi ̀ wa ̀ a ̀ rɛn , m ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ mɔ ki ̀ rɛsii .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓum ɓɛmbog ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ kaa gɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ ghɛn ̀ Kan , ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓyɛɛ rereŋi ɗii ɗyɛ ̀ m .
Ri ̀ kali ̀ ɗi Kan a ̀ nɛ a ̀ re ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi ̀ n .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ ghɛɛ lɛ , tyɛ ̀ ki ri ̀ i ̀ si ɓum ɓɛ zɛy ɓɛ ɓɛ lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛɛ mɛ ̀ rem , ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ n Bɛ ̀ ll n ̀ tɛ ̀ g ɓi nyoo .
Ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɔŋ ɓɔ ki ̀ ka ̀ ni kaa ̀ ta ̀ , ti kpaa ɓɔ lɛ , ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ce ̀ lii lɛ : ri ̀ riɗi ɗi ɓituwe ɓi ɓɛ woli ɓisuu riɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi ɓinu ̀ n , ri ̀ ti ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g , ri ̀ ri ̀ ɗi ɗi ɓituwe ɓi ɓi wii lɛ swi ̀ i ̀ ɗ bwaɓ yɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ kpaŋ .
Ɓisuulɛ a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓi gba ̀ a ̀ yi ajɛ ̀ m , ba ̀ n yi ̀ ce ̀ m yi ri ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ re ̀ eresa ̀ g ɓum ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Moyis , lɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ ɓaa ̀ yi ̀ ɓyɔ ɓi naa yi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ ŋwos ɓɛ Saɓa ̀ t .
Nni fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ri ̀ ki ̀ seŋi ki ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓɔn ̀ ɓum ɓɛɗɛŋ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wa ̀ a ̀ , di ɓɛɛ rom ɓɔ nɗaŋ ri Pol ɓɛɛ ̀ Ɓarinaɓas a Aŋtyos . Nni ɓɛ ɓɔnga ̀ min lɛ , ri ̀ Zyuudɛ a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ nɗega ̀ g ti ̀ lɛ Ɓarisaɓas , ri ̀ Silas . Ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ɓum ki ̀ n ki ɓagha ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓaa ɓɛ righerɛ ̀ n ɓɛ keesi ̀ gha ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ romga ̀ ɓɔ ri ̀ kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ ka ̀ nɛn fɛlɛ ̀ : Ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓin ɓɛ lɛ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn , ɓɛ togsaghii ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓaa , ɓɛ ɓi ̀ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ ɓi ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔrii a Aŋtyos , ri ̀ a Sirii , ri a Silisii .
Ti ̀ i nwoogh lɛ , ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ m ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ yi ̀ fɛ , ɓi ̀ si tyɛ ̀ ki rom yi ɓɔ , ɓɛ yu mi ̀ ni ki ̀ ɓu ̀ u ̀ sii , ɓɛ ki syaŋdi mini mɛ ̀ rem ri ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓyaa .
Fɔɔnnɛ ti ̀ i n-yɔɔsii jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ bog lɛ : Ti ɓɔn ̀ ɓumɓɛ ti ̀ romii ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin n ̀ ɗaŋ ɗi Pol ɓɛɛ ̀ Ɓarinaɓas , ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓis ɓɛ n ̀ ɗem .
Ɓɛ ri ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ mɛ ka ̀ ɓɓɛn ɓɔmiɗ ɓisuu kisay ki Yeesus Kiris Kan wi ̀ s .
Nni ti ̀ romii ̀ mi ̀ ni lɛ , ri ̀ Zyuudɛ ri ̀ Silas lɛ ɓɔmiɗ ɓɛɛ kpaa ̀ ti mi ̀ ni ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ti ̀ ka ̀ nii ̀ ɓi .
Lɛ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ sii ̀ ɓɔmi ̀ ɗ ri ̀ Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay , ti ̀ i nghɛɛ lɛ , tyɛ ̀ ki tɛ ̀ gsi ti mi ̀ ni n ̀ tɛ ̀ g wudɛŋ , i ki cee ɓi lɛ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi ̀ ɓi ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi , ɓi ɓi ri lɛ :
Kɛ ̀ ɓi ɗi ɓyɛn ɓi nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ woli ɓi ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi ɓinu ̀ n , ri ̀ bwaɓ , ri ̀ ɓyɛn ɓi nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛ i ̀ wii lɛ swi ̀ i ̀ ɗ , kɛ ̀ ɓi ki ̀ tisɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g , i ɓi ̀ lɛɛgh ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ , di ɓi ̀ konaagh , O ̀ O o ̀ ona ya ̀ a ̀ !
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ romga ̀ ɓɛn ̀ , ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ min a Aŋtyos , ɓɛ taŋzɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ wɔɔ , lɛ ɓɛɛ fa ɓɔ kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ kanga ̀ y ɓɔ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ɓala ̀ nyi , ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ nyaa ̀ rɛ ̀ n , lɛ a ̀ te ̀ e ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ nyo ̀ o ̀ .
Zyuudɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ Silas ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ toka ̀ ka ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓaa ɓɛn ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ tee ̀ si ̀ ɓɔ nyoo , ɓɛ ki si ̀ i ̀ rag ɓɔ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Silas ɓɛɛ ̀ Zyuudɛ ɓɛ kɔri ̀ gha ̀ wɔɔ le ̀ g a ̀ dɛŋ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓaa ɓɛ ghesɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ , ɓɛ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ kɛ ̀ n lɛ fyo ̀ oog ; nni ɓɛ sugti ̀ gha ̀ min a ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓaa ɓɛ ɓɛ romga ̀ y ɓɔ
( Ki ̀ ɓan kifog Silas a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓi a Aŋtyos ) .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ -Pol ɓɛɛ ̀ Ɓarinaɓas ɓɛ rɔ ̀ ɓka ̀ a Aŋtyos , ɓɛ ɓasɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓi ri ̀ re ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ri ̀ kaka ̀ li ̀ ɗi Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ Kan .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ foo , Pol a ̀ kpaa Ɓarinaɓas lɛ : Ti sugtiina ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓis ɓɛ ɓi ba ̀ n yi ti ̀ i nkpaa Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ Kan wɔɔ , lɛ ti ghɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ri ,
Ɓarinaɓas a ̀ kɔ ̀ nkɔ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ , ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ ɗi Zyaŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɗii lɛ Marikus ,
wɔ ̀ lɛ Pol a ̀ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi lɛ ɓɛɛ Kɛn ̀ ɗi ̀ Zyaŋ , ɓisuulɛ , a ̀ rini ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ a Paŋfilii , kɛ ̀ ɛ ki teeti ga ̀ ɓ ɓi ki ̀ say ki ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i .
Ɓɛ nyolɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ , ɓɛ syɔnga ̀ ki ̀ ghasɛɛ , lɛ ri ̀ mum a ̀ ro ̀ ŋi ̀ bee yii ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ Ɓarinaɓas ɓɛɛ ̀ Marikus ɓɛ ɓɔka ̀ ki ̀ kɔm , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ a Siipirɛ .
Pol nyii teka ̀ Silas ɓɔɔ kɛn ̀ , di ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓaa ɓɛ mɛ reɓsɛn ɓɔ ri ̀ geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ Kan .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ fyeegha ̀ a Sirii ri ̀ a Silisii di a te ̀ etee ̀ si ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ wɔɔ nyoo ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
Nni Pol a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ a Dɛriɓɛ , ri ̀ a Listirɛ n-yila ̀ g a ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ ɗii lɛ Timote , jɛɛ wi ̀ i ̀ a ɓagha ̀ n ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , gɔ ̀ n i ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , seŋi muu Gi ̀ rɛg ,
ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ a Listirɛ ri ̀ ɓɛ a Ikonyɔm ɓɛ sɛsɛ ̀ ka ̀ nyi .
Fɔɔnnɛ Pol a ̀ kɔ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ a teɗ nyi , ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ ; yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ki teka ̀ nyi , a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɗ nyi , lɛ a ̀ riri ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ , lɛ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ yigha ̀ lɛ seŋi Timote a ̀ ɓagha ̀ muu Gi ̀ rɛg .
Ɓi ba ̀ n yi ̀ ce ̀ m yi Pol ri ̀ Silas ɓɛ ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ wɔɔ , ɓɛ ghaa ̀ gha ̀ gsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ a Yorisalɛm ɓɛ renga ̀ , ɓɛ ki kpaakpaa ɓum lɛ , ɓɛɛ ɓeŋ ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ seŋi ɓi mɛ tete ̀ ka ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n i ̀ ɓɔɓɔ ̀ g m ̀ ɓɔɓɔghɛn ɓɛŋwos ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ki ̀ reka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ghagsi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ki ̀ den ki zi ki a Azii fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ ba ̀ n i ̀ Firizii , ri ̀ zi i ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ ga ̀ lat ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kpaga ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ Misii , nni ɓɛ kaagha ̀ bee inɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ a Bitinii , ki ̀ ɓan kifog Nghay a ̀ Yeesus kɛ ̀ ɛ gherɛ ̀ n .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ syaa ̀ gha ̀ min zi inɛ a Misii , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ a Tirowas .
Nni ɓi ̀ dɛ ̀ ndɛm ̀ ɓi kigha ̀ Pol ri ̀ i ̀ ru lɛ a ̀ ghɛɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a Masedwan mɛ ̀ rɛy , a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋza ̀ g nyi lɛ : Yu a Masedwan , u ghɛɓsi ɓi ̀ si .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ ɓi ̀ dɛ ̀ ndɛm ɓi Pol ɓin ̀ , nnɛ ti ̀ gha ̀ ska ̀ ki ̀ kaa ̀ bee i ̀ nɛ lɛ ti kɛn ̀ a Masedwan , lɛ ti ̀ kona ̀ ka ̀ ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll yɛɛ regii ɓi ̀ si lɛ , ti kɛn ̀ ki ̀ kalii Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ wɔɔ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ teka ̀ ki ̀ kɔm a Tirowas , ti ̀ kɛ ̀ n lɔŋ kilomi ̀ ɓi ki ̀ ri ̀ ŋ ki riɓa ̀ y ki lɛ , Samotiras , ɓi duri tana ti ̀ kɛ ̀ n a Neyapolis ,
wɔɔnnɛ ti ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ , ti ̀ kɛ ̀ n a Filiɓ , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tonto a ̀ ba ̀ n a ̀ nɛ a Masedwan , a ̀ ki ɓa ti ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛ ɓumɓɛ a Rom ɓɛ lami ̀ i ̀ ; ti ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛn , ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru .
Nni ŋwosi ̀ Saɓa ̀ t , ti ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ba ̀ n , ti ̀ kɛ ̀ n ɓi be ̀ n i ̀ n ̀ syo ̀ m , ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ti ̀ fe ̀ fe ̀ ka ̀ lɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ɓa ri ̀ naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n wɔɔ . Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓi zi , nni ti ̀ to ̀ ka ̀ ka ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ ɓɛtaŋzɛn .
Giɓ a ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ ɗii lɛ Lidyaa a ̀ a m ̀ ɓɔgsa ̀ g Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -du ̀ ne i ̀ ɓi ̀ syeesyee ɓi ɓila ̀ a ̀ ɓi ɓa ̀ ŋ ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ Tyatiir , a ̀ ramga ̀ mɛ ̀ ree ̀ lɛ syeesyee lɛ a wog ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓis , fɔɔnnɛ Kan a ̀ nɛmga ̀ nyi n ̀ ɗem lɛ a konag ki ̀ woo ̀ gh ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓi Pol .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ɓaɓti ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ri ̀ nyi , ri ̀ naa yi ̀ i ̀ i ɓum nni a ̀ tɔka ̀ ɓi ̀ si lɛ , ti kɛn ̀ a mɛɛ mii , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : I ɓi ̀ ghɛɛ lɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ n ̀ gherɛ ̀ n Kan , yu ̀ una ki ̀ kɔ ̀ rii a mɛɛ mɛm ̀ . Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ si ̀ i ̀ rɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ti gherɛn lɛ , ti kɔri a ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋkii .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ kɛ ̀ nkɛ ̀ nga ̀ ŋwos adɛŋ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ i bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n , nni ti ̀ tulɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ gɔ ̀ n i ̀ giɓ idɛŋ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓii ̀ sasali ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ; i ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki nghay , ki ki fafa ̀ gha ̀ yɔ ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ log ki ̀ yii ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ri ɓii ̀ ki ̀ lɛɛ . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ masa ̀ ɓii ɓɛ fɔ ̀ nfɔ ̀ nga ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓi ɓi ̀ fyeŋ ɓii ɓin ̀ .
Nni i ̀ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ̀ si ri ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si ri ̀ Pol , di yɛ ̀ ɛ kpaakpaa jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ teŋmɛɛ a ̀ cee , ɓɛɛ ̀ kakali mini ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ri lɛ ɓi fa mi ̀ ni cɛɓ .
Ɓa ̀ li ̀ i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru i ̀ ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey ŋwutya ̀ a ̀ giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ kɛ ̀ nkɛ ̀ n lɔŋ asu a ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ fɔlɔɔ . Fɔɔnnɛ bim i ̀ ɓagha ̀ lɛ i ̀ mɛ naasag Pol , a ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpaa ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki nghay ki ki ɓagha ̀ ɓi giɓ anɛ ̀ n lɛ : Ɓi ɗii ɗi Yeesus Kiris , n ̀ tɔɔgh wɔ ̀ lɛ , u pɛsɛn ɓi giɓ a ̀ nɛ . Nni ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki nghay ki gha ̀ ska ̀ ki ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi gom yɔ ̀ miɗ inɛ ̀ n .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ masa ̀ ɓɛ giɓ anɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ bee yaa ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ fɔ ̀ n i ̀ nɛn i ̀ simɓɛɛ , nni ɓɛ ɓanga ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ Pol ri ̀ Silas , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓɔ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ m ɓi mis mɛ ɓɛyɔ ̀ mi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ rɛsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ ɓi mis mɛ ɓɛyɔ ̀ mi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ ro ̀ mɛŋ ɓɛ kpaa lɛ : Ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yuu ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓu ̀ u ̀ si ̀ ɓi ba ̀ n yi ̀ s , ɓɛnce ̀ m ɓɛ ki ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ;
ɓɛɛ re ̀ eresa ̀ g ɓum ɓi ̀ syɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓidɛŋ , ɓi ɓi ̀ si Ɓɛ ̀ ro ̀ mɛŋ ti ̀ yin ri i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ , ti ̀ teɗ , nsoo ̀ lɛ ti ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ mii ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ , i ̀ woka ̀ bim ri Pol ɓɛɛ ̀ Silas , ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ mi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ kpaa lɛ , ɓɛɛ kori ɓɔ ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ɓi nyoo ɓɛ ki ɓog ɓɔ ki ̀ to ̀ n .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ɓaa ̀ gh lɛ , ɓɛ mɛ ɓog ɓɔ ki ̀ to ̀ n fɔlɔɔ , ɓɛ pii ̀ g min ɓɔ ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y , ɓɛ kali ̀ m ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -naa ̀ -za ̀ y lɛ , a ɓeŋ ɓɔ , le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ a ̀ dɛŋ kɛ ̀ ɛ ɗim .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ m ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ naa ̀ -za ̀ y a ̀ woka ̀ fɔlɔɔ , a ̀ pi ̀ g ɓɔ ɓi ki ̀ den ki naa ki ki ɓagha ̀ lɔŋ wɔɔ ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y ɓi ɗu ̀ u ̀ m , a ̀ ki pu ̀ rag ɓɔ mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓe ̀ g .
Di n ̀ ɗem-iru ̀ wu ti ja ̀ ŋbog , Pol ri ̀ Silas ɓɛ ɓɔɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋza ̀ ka ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓɛ kɛkɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ gh tyem ti lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓɔgsi Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓi ̀ mbu ̀ ŋ ɓimbog ɓi wowo ̀ g yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kɛkɛ ̀ ghi ̀ gha ̀ .
Nni zi i gha ̀ ska ̀ ki ̀ nyɛ ̀ ŋɗɛɛ ri i ̀ te ̀ ɗ le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ mɛɛ mɛ naa ̀ -za ̀ y mɛ kpikɛ ̀ nga ̀ , ɓi ̀ si ̀ m ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ghas ki ̀ ŋwa ̀ rɛɛ , bɛn yi ɓimbu ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m yi fumɓa ̀ g .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ m ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -naa ̀ -za ̀ y a ̀ fo ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ y ɓi fi ̀ lo , a ̀ ghɛn mɛ ̀ suuna mɛ naa ̀ -za ̀ y ɓi ̀ kpaŋ a ̀ sɔ ̀ ŋi ̀ i ̀ ga ̀ fa ̀ g yi ̀ i ̀ lɛ , a wolɛn ɓisuulɛ a ̀ fe ̀ fe ̀ ka ̀ lɛ , ɓi ̀ mbu ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓyaa la ̀ ngii .
Nni Pol a ̀ kpaagha ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ɔ ki ̀ lɛn com ! ti ̀ ri ̀ fɛ ɓi ̀ si ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
M ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -naa ̀ -za ̀ y a ̀ tɔg min lɛ ɓɛɛ fa nyi ɗuu ; a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ree ɓi ki ̀ den ki naa , di a ni ̀ ighniŋdɛ ̀ n lɛ kpa ̀ g-kpa ̀ g-kpa ̀ g , a ̀ kpi ̀ Pol ɓɛɛ ̀ Silas a mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ ;
fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ , a ̀ tɔg ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓɛ ̀ kan ɓɛ ̀ m ! Cɛ n ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ɓisuulɛ mɓa ri ̀ cɛɓ ?
Ɓɛ ɓaa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Gherɛn Kan Yeesus , fɔɔnnɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ cɛɓ lɛ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ , ri ̀ naa yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ i ̀ ɓum .
Nni ɓɛ kali ̀ gha ̀ min nyi Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ Kan Yeesus , lɛ ri ̀ nyi ri ̀ ri ̀ mɛɛ ɗii .
Ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kɔm ̀ kin ̀ , nnɛ , m ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -naa ̀ -za ̀ y a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ lɛ a soo ̀ ɓɔ beŋ yi ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ yɔ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ gha ̀ ska ̀ ki ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓtii lɛ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓum ɓii ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn nnɛ m ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -naa ̀ -za ̀ y a ̀ teka ̀ lɛ ri ̀ Pol ri ̀ Silas , a ̀ ɓɔg ri ̀ ɓɔ a mɛɛ mii , a ̀ fa ɓɔ ɓyom ɓiɗiyɛn , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n ri ̀ naa yi ̀ i ̀ i ɓum , ɓɛ woka ̀ ki ̀ rɔɔ lɛɛ ̀ gwey , yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ duri i tanga ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ mi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ rom yi ̀ ɓum lɛ ɓɛɛ kali m ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -naa ̀ -za ̀ y lɛ , a ̀ caɗ ɓɛ ̀ -Pol ɓɛɛ ghaa ̀ gh .
Nni m ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -naa ̀ -za ̀ y a ̀ kpaagha ̀ Pol lɛ : Ɓɛ ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɓɛ romii ̀ ɓum lɛ , mɛ ̀ ncaɗ mi ̀ ni , mi ̀ nii ghaa ̀ gh , nni ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki , kpaŋina min , ɓi kɛn ̀ lɛ fyo ̀ oog .
Nni Pol a ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ romga ̀ y ɓɛn ̀ lɛ : Ɓɛ ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɓɛ mɛ ki ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ ɓog ɓi ̀ si ki ̀ to ̀ n ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓum , di ɓɛ ka yɔmzi ɓi ɓisi , kɔlɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ girig Ɓɛ ̀ ro ̀ mɛŋ , ɓɛ ki pi ̀ g ɓisi ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y nni ɓɛ ti ɓigomi ̀ nɛ lɛ , ɓɛɛ kpaŋzi ɓi ̀ si ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y ; a ri ̀ nyam , e ̀ e e ̀ e , ɓi ̀ sii ɓeni ̀ , ɓɔmiɗ ɓɛɛ yu ɓi ̀ si ki ̀ kpaŋzii .
Nni ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ romga ̀ y ɓɛn ̀ ɓɛ sugti ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ kalii ɓɛyɔ ̀ mi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Pol i ̀ nɛ ̀ n , fɔɔnnɛ i ̀ ris wu ɓanga ̀ ɓɔ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ woka ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ -Pol ɓɛ ri Ɓɛ ̀ ro ̀ mɛŋ .
Nni ɓɛ yugha ̀ ɓɔ ki ̀ tɔɔ ̀ gh ri ̀ cenɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ kpaŋzi ̀ ɓɔ ɓi ̀ naa ̀ -za ̀ y , ɓɛ ki ɓɔ ̀ ŋzag ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ pɛsɛn ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛn .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pol ri ̀ Silas ɓɛ kpaga ̀ y naa ̀ -za ̀ y ɓɛ kɛn ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Lidyaa , ɓɛ ghɛn ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓaa ɓɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ tee ̀ si ̀ ɓɔ nyoo , ɓɛ ghaa ̀ gh min .
Pol ri ̀ Silas ɓɛ fyeegha ̀ a Aŋfipolis ri ̀ a Apolonii , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ a Tesalonika , wɔɔnnɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n .
Fɔɔnnɛ Pol a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n i ̀ nɛn lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ a nti a ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g . A ̀ kurɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ wɔɔ , ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , go ̀ n yi Saɓa ̀ t yiraa .
A ̀ tɛɛ ̀ tɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ , a ̀ re ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ɓɔ lɛ , ki ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ , Kiris a wog ri ̀ kɛŋ , a ̀ ki ghe ̀ mɓɛn yi a ɓi ̀ loŋ ; a ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Yeesus a ̀ nɛ nkakali mini a ̀ nɛ yɛɛ ri ̀ Kiris .
Fɔɔnnɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ , ɓɛ ɓasɛ ̀ n n ̀ ɗaŋ ri Pol ri ̀ Silas , ri ̀ Gi ̀ rɛg lɛɛ ̀ gwey i ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ nɗisa ̀ g Bɛ ̀ ll , ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ɓi ̀ te ̀ ete ̀ ɗ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ i ̀ nɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ girig ɓɔ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ya ̀ aka ɓɛ reŋɗɛ ̀ nga ̀ y ɓumɓɛ zɛy ɓɛ ɓɛ yoo ̀ yo ̀ mga ̀ ɓi ba ̀ n , ɓɛ taŋzɛ ̀ n ci ̀ i ̀ ba , ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ ki ̀ ɗi kiyoo ̀ yo ̀ o ̀ ɓi ba ̀ n . Nni ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ ki ̀ kaa ̀ lɛ ri ̀ Pol ri ̀ Silas a mɛɛ mɛ Jazɔŋ , lɛ ɓɛɛ rɛsi ɓɔ ɓi mis mɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ lɛ kɛɛ yɔm ɓɔ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ tanɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓɔ , nni ɓɛ ɓanga ̀ lɛ ri ̀ Jazɔŋ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛdɛŋ , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ a ɓɛ ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛn ɓɛ kpaa jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓuu ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ziinɛ bimiɗ , ɓɛ nkpaŋi girig fɛ ɓi ba ̀ n yi ̀ s ,
Nni Jazɔŋ a ̀ a n ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ɓɔ a mɛɛ mii ; ri ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ɗi ɓiɓan ɗi ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɗi wɛɛsɛɛ ɓi ri ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Kaaza , lɛ ɓɔɔ kalag lɛ : Ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗidɛŋ ɗi ri ̀ wɔɔ , ɗyɛɛ ri ɗii lɛ , Yeesus .
Ri ̀ kpaa ɗi ̀ n ɗi ɓuu ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ri ̀ gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ mɛ ̀ to ɓi le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ ,
ɓɛ kaga ̀ Jazɔŋ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛmbog lɛ , ɓɛɛ pee ̀ la ̀ man ɓi ɗi lɛ ɓɛɛ ca ̀ ɗ ɓɔ .
Lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ i ̀ ru wu finga ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓaa ɓɛ righerɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ghas ki ̀ kaa ̀ bee inɛ lɛ , Pol ɓɛɛ ̀ Silas ɓɛɛ pɛsɛn , ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ a Bere . Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kpaga ̀ wɔɔ , ɓɛ ɗiŋi ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n i ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n .
Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ a Bere ɓɛ rɔɔtɛ ̀ nga ̀ n ̀ ɗem ɓɛ cee ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ a Tesalonika , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ghaɓka ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ coo kinya ̀ a ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ ŋwos ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , ɓɛ fifi ̀ ɓi ̀ gha ̀ kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ ɓɛɛ ghɛn ̀ nko ̀ o ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Pol a ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ , ɓi ri mii ̀ .
Ki ̀ gwey ki ɓi ɓɔ , ki gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ ; ɓi ̀ te ̀ ete ̀ ɗ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓi a Gi ̀ rɛg ri ̀ ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ baŋi ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ i ̀ tɛn , ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ girig .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ a Tesalonika ɓɛ woka ̀ lɛ Pol a ̀ titi ̀ ɓii ̀ ghaaghagsi ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a Bere , nni ɓɛ yugha ̀ y wɔɔ lɛ , ɓɛɛ ɓuu ̀ si ja ̀ ŋ , ɓɛ ki ki ̀ kiyoo ̀ yo ̀ o ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓum ɓɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ .
Ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓaa ɓɛ righerɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ghas min ki ki ̀ i lɛ Pol a kɛn ̀ ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n , Silas ri ̀ Timote ɓɛɛ rɔɓka ̀ lɔŋ a Bere .
Ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ ki ̀ foŋi ̀ Pol , ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ lɔŋ n ̀ ɗaŋ ɗi ̀ nyi a ̀ kpaŋ a Atɛn , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ sugti ̀ gha ̀ y min a Bere , Pol a ̀ romgi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ -Silas ɓɛɛ ̀ Timote jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ , lɛ , ɓɛɛ nɔɔ ̀ tii ̀ nyi lɛ fyɛ ̀ ɗ .
Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki Pol a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓoŋɓoŋi ɓɛ ̀ -Silas a Atɛn , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ -yeesɛ ̀ n ɓi n ̀ ɗem yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ ba ̀ n i ̀ Atɛn i ̀ ronɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ bɛ ̀ ll yi ɓinu ̀ n .
A nyoo ̀ nyo ̀ lɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ri ̀ Gi ̀ rɛg i ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ n ̀ ɗisa ̀ g Bɛ ̀ ll ; ki ɓagha ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n . A ̀ nyoo ̀ nyo ̀ lɛ ̀ n ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ a ̀ a n ̀ tana ̀ g ɓi ki ̀ yan ki ɓum ɓɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ ɓɛ nkura ̀ g wɔɔ ɓɛŋwos ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g dɔgtɛ ̀ n yidɛŋ yi yɛɛ , kpaakpaa lɛ ŋwaa ̀ kee ̀ si ri ̀ yɛ ̀ y ɗi cɛɓ , ri ̀ lɛ , ŋwaa ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓiɓi ̀ nɗem ɓi ri ̀ kɛŋ , ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ girig i ̀ kure ̀ ri ̀ Pol , ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ lɛ : Cɛ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -kɛɛgh anɛ a kpaakpaa kɔmiɗ ? Ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛm ̀ bog ɓɛ ɓaa ̀ g lɛ : Ki pisɛɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ a kakali kiɓan ki bɛ ̀ ll yidɛŋ , yi ti ̀ yii ɓi ; ɓɛ ɓaka ̀ fɔlɔɔ ɓisuulɛ , ɓɛ woka ̀ di Pol a kakali Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ Yeesus , ri ̀ ri ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓiloŋ .
Nni ɓɛ teka ̀ Pol ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ n ̀ taŋzɛn wu a Atɛn wulɛ , aye ̀ ro ̀ paa ̀ zɛ ̀ ɓɛ kpaa nyi lɛ : Ti ̀ ri ̀ nya lɛ ti ̀ yi nyɔɔnyɔn a ̀ dɔgtɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ u re ̀ resi anɛ ?
Ki ri yɛ ̀ ɛ u kakali ɓisi ɓi ̀ ke ̀ neke ̀ ne ̀ ɓi ɓiɓan , nni ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓi ti kɔ ̀ nkɔ ̀ n lɛ di tya ̀ a yii yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ri azi .
Ɓumɓɛ a Atɛn ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ke ̀ n ɓɛ ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛn , ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ syɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ lɛ , i ̀ duri i tani , ɓɛ kɔri ̀ foo lɛ , ɓɛɛ kpaa ̀ kpaa , nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ wowog ɓɛ ̀ ɓɔlɛ ɓɛ nyɔn .
Nni Pol a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ aɗyoo ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ n ̀ taŋzɛn wulɛ , a ̀ ye ̀ ro ̀ paa ̀ zɛ ̀ a kpaa lɛ : Mi ̀ ni ɓumɓɛ a Atɛn , mɛ ̀ n ̀ ka ghɛɛ lɛ , ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ falɛɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi mɛgherɛn lɛ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ nɗerenii ba ̀ n yi ̀ n , n ̀ seese ̀ e ̀ gɛ mɛɛ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ̀ togii bɛ ̀ ll yin ; mɛ ̀ ɛ mɓa ̀ li kɔm ̀ ɓi mɛɛ mɛdɛŋ lɛ : Mɛɛ mɛ , mɛ ri ɓisuu bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ dɛŋ i ̀ nɛ ti ̀ yii ɓi . Nni bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓɔɔɓɔgsi ̀ i ̀ nɛn kɛ ̀ ɓi yi yɔ ̀ , yɛ ̀ ɛnnɛ n ̀ -yu ̀ u mi ̀ ni ki ̀ re ̀ sii .
Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ zi ri ̀ ɗyoo , ri ̀ ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi mii ̀ , nnyɛɛ ri Kan a ̀ nɛ a ̀ la ̀ mii ɓyom ɓi ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m . Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛn a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ ɓi mɛɛ mɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ ̀ toŋi ri ̀ ɓya ̀ g ɓyaa .
Fɔɔnnɛ ki ̀ say kii ki yin ɓii ̀ tɔtɔɔgh ɓya ̀ g ɓi ɓum lɛ kɛɛ ki ̀ lɛn , ɓisuulɛ com kidɛŋ ki kaarɛɛ ɓi nyi ; nnyɛɛ ti a ̀ fala ̀ g ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m cɛɓ , ri ̀ cɔ ̀ ŋzɛn ri ̀ ɓyom ɓimbog ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m .
Nnyɛɛ kigha ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓyɛɛ fuu ̀ yi ̀ ɓi mum bog , a ̀ ki kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ si ɓyɔ ɓi zi bimiɗ ; a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , a ̀ wo ̀ ŋza ̀ g ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓisu waa , a ̀ ki rɛsag mɛre ̀ e ̀ mɛ zi , yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ kɔ ̀ rii .
A ki ̀ gha ̀ fɔlɔɔ lɛ , ɗi ɓum ɓɛɛ kaa ̀ kaa nyi ɓaa ̀ yiɓi , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ ghɛn nyi di ɓɛ mɛ gbɔ ̀ mgbɔ ̀ m , lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ raɓsɛɛ gi ̀ ɓi ri ɓi ̀ si ;
ti ghɛghɛ ̀ ɓ , ti ̀ nyɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ nyɛŋɗɛ ̀ n , ti ̀ ki ɓa ɓum , lɛ nyi . Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓɛ ̀ toŋi ̀ ɓyom ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ sii ri gi ̀ ri ̀ g boo yi ̀ i ̀ i mum .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ lɔɔ boo i ̀ mum i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi kife ̀ egh lɛ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ pisɛ ̀ n gol , nsoo ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni , nsoo ̀ gɔ ̀ g yi ɓum ɓɔ yɛɛ soɓi ri ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗyaa .
Fɔɔnnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ foŋi ɓi n ̀ to ri ̀ ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓi ɓum ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓin ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ɗim , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , a rereŋi ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m nsoo ̀ ɓɛ fe , nsoo ̀ ɓɛ fe , lɛ ɓɛɛ lɔɔghrɛn mɛ ̀ rem .
Ɓisuulɛ a ̀ rɛsi ̀ gha ̀ bimiɗ a ̀ ŋwos a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ yɔ ̀ mi zi bimiɗ mii ̀ , lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ saaɗ a kɔ ̀ nkɔ ̀ n ; a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ nga ̀ mum a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i kisay kin ̀ , a ̀ fa ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ki ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ ki ki resii lɛ , nnyɛɛ ɓɔnga ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nce ̀ m , yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ghe ̀ mzi ̀ gha ̀ y nyi a ɓi ̀ loŋ .
Lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ woka ̀ di Pol a ̀ ti ɓii ̀ kpaakpaa kiɓan ki righe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓiloŋ , ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ kpusɛ ̀ n ɗi tyɛ ̀ y , ɓɛm ̀ bog ɓɛ kpaa nyi lɛ , ti ̀ ri wog kiŋkɔɔ kin ̀ ŋwos adɛŋ .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ Pol a ̀ kpaga ̀ , a ̀ ghaa ̀ gh .
Nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ɓum i ̀ dɛŋ i ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ Pol , i ̀ gherɛ ̀ n . Ɓi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɛn ̀ , Denis ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓumɓɛ n ̀ taŋzɛn wulɛ a ̀ ye ̀ ro ̀ paa ̀ zɛ ̀ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ mii ̀ , ri ̀ giɓ adɛŋ ɗii lɛ Damaris , ri ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ti ̀ foo .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , Pol a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ a ̀ Atɛn a ̀ kɛ ̀ n a Kɔrɛŋt .
A tuusɛ ̀ nga ̀ wɔɔ ri muu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n a ̀ dɛŋ ɗii lɛ Akilas ; ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ yalɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ki ̀ la ̀ na ̀ ki zi ki lɛ Pɔŋ . A pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ y a Italii ɓɛɛ ̀ Pirisilya a ̀ giy , ɓisuulɛ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi lɛ Kiloodɛ ɗi renga ̀ lɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ a Rom ɓɛɛ pɛsɛn wɔɔ . Fɔɔnnɛ Pol a ̀ ra ̀ rɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ kuu ɗi kisay ɗifog , ki ̀ say ki toŋtoŋɛn ɓilaa ri ̀ ta ̀ pot , nni Pol a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkaa ɓɛ sasa ̀ y n ̀ ɗaŋ .
Go ̀ n yi Saɓa ̀ t yi ̀ ce ̀ m , Pol a ̀ a n ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghraagh ɓi naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ nzɛ ̀ n lɛ a ̀ kaaka ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ bee lɛ a syoŋ ̀ lɛ ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ri ̀ Gi ̀ rɛg .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Silas ri ̀ Timote ɓɛ kpaga ̀ a Kɔrɛŋt di ɓɛ pɛsɛɛ yi ̀ a Masedwan , Pol a ̀ naga ̀ ɓɔɔ ɓisay ɓimbog , a ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓ lɔŋ lɛ a kpaa ̀ kpaa ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ kaka ̀ li ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n a ̀ ki si ̀ i ̀ rɛn lɛ , Yeesus yɛɛ ri Kiris .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓee ̀ dɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Pol a ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ , ɓɛ ki sɛmgi nyi , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ sa ̀ ɗka ̀ ku ̀ ru ̀ ɓu a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ nyi ɓi ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : I ̀ ɓi ̀ ɗyaŋi ŋwos yɛ ̀ ɛ gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , di zɛ ̀ ɗ yin ̀ i ̀ mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ , mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yii ̀ di mii ̀ ri ̀ bɛ ̀ lɛn . Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , n ̀ -yu ̀ u ki ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ a ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n .
Nni a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ foo a ̀ kɛ ̀ n a mɛɛ mɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ a n ̀ ɗisa ̀ g Bɛ ̀ ll ɗii lɛ Tityus-Yustus , mɛɛ mii mɛ ɓagha ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog ɗi ̀ naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n .
Nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n , ɗii lɛ Kirispus ɗi gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ Kan , ri ̀ ri ̀ mɛɛ ɗii ɗice ̀ m , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓumɓɛ a Kɔrɛŋt lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ ɓɛ woka ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Pol ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ girig , ɓɛ ki ɓa ̀ ɓtag .
Ɓi-ru wudɛŋ , Kan a ̀ kpaagha ̀ Pol a ɓi ̀ dɛ ̀ ndɛm lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ɔ risi , kɛ ̀ na asu ri ̀ ri ̀ kaka ̀ li ̀ ɗi ɓɔlɛ , kɔ ̀ ɔ mam .
Ɓisuulɛ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ wɔ ̀ ajɛ ̀ m , ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ saa ̀ gh wɔ ̀ ca ̀ g ɓi nyoo lɛ a ki wɔ ̀ ki ̀ ɓe ɓisuulɛ ɓum ɓɛm ɓɛ ronɛɛ fɛ ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛ .
Pol a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ a Kɔrɛŋt be ̀ g bog ri ̀ ki ̀ den di a re ̀ resi ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ Galyɔŋ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ gɔmi ̀ na ̀ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ki ̀ la ̀ na ̀ ki zi ki lɛ Akayi , Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ wɔrɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔɔ ̀ ce ̀ m , ɓɛ ɓigti ̀ paa ̀ zi ̀ ri ̀ Pol ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi ɓi naa ̀ -ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ m .
Ɓɛ kpaa lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a tootoo ̀ si ̀ , ɓum lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓɔgsi Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ri ̀ kuu ɗi riɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi ree ̀ gh .
Lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Pol a ̀ mɛɛ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ a pini ŋwɔm a too ̀ ghrɛn , Galyɔŋ a ̀ kpaa Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛn ̀ lɛ : Mi ̀ ni Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ! I kaa ri ̀ lɛ Pol a ̀ wolii ̀ mum nsoo ̀ lɛ a ̀ sɛ ̀ raaghii ̀ coo kiɓan kidɛŋ , di n ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ lɛ fyo ̀ oog n ̀ kona ̀ g ti ̀ ki ̀ woo ̀ gh sɔmi ̀ na ̀ wi ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri ̀ lɛ ɓi nyoonyolɛ ̀ n ɓi dɔgtɛ ̀ n i ̀ dɛŋ ri ̀ ɓi mii mɛdɛŋ , ri ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓin , mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ yɛɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ pe ̀ gsɛɛ kiɓan kin ; mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yin lɛ n ̀ -yɔ ̀ m ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi fɔlɔɔ .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ ɓi naa ̀ -ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ m .
Nni Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛn ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ sɛnga ̀ ɓi Sostɛn a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ n nyi ri ̀ ɓog ɓi mis mɛ ɓɛyɔ ̀ mi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan , wɔ ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗin ̀ ɗyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ yeesi Galyɔŋ nsoo ̀ lɛsa ̀ g .
Pol a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ti ̀ a Kɔrɛŋt ga ̀ ɓ , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ghesɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓɛ righerɛ ̀ n , a ̀ teɗ min kikɔm lɛ a kɛn ̀ a Sirii . A ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ Pirisilya ɓɛɛ ̀ Akilas . Pol a ̀ kɛ ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ nga ̀ n ̀ to a ̀ Saŋkire ɓisuulɛ , a ̀ ca ̀ rɛ ̀ nga ̀ tyo ̀ ŋ ɓi bɛ ̀ ɗ idɛŋ i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ n ̀ ɗegi lɛ bɛ ̀ ɗ i na ̀ ziryia ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kpaga ̀ a Efɛɛzɛ Pol a ̀ ca ̀ ɗ Pirisilya wɔɔ ɓɛɛ ̀ Akilas , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ɓi naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n a ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n .
Ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ tɔg nyi lɛ a kɔri ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru ri ̀ ɓɔ , a ̀ ɓe ̀ n .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog a ̀ ghasɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ , a ̀ ki ka ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ sugtii yi a lɔ ̀ ŋkaa ŋwos adɛŋ di Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kɔ ̀ ni . Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpagha ̀ lɛ : Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ , nɗi ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ ti ti rii ̀ ti a Yorisalɛm nsoo ̀ kaa ɓaa la . Nni a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Efɛɛzɛ ɓi fi ̀ tima ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ sɛni fi ̀ tima ̀ a ̀ Sezare , a ̀ ɓɔg kito ̀ gsii n ̀ ɗaŋ wu ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n wu a Yorisalɛm , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ sɛnga ̀ min a Aŋtyos .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ wɔɔ ga ̀ ɓ , nni a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ti ̀ , a ̀ reni zi i ̀ Galasi bimiɗ , a ̀ ghaa ̀ gh min a Firizii , di a si ̀ isii ̀ ra ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
Muu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n a ̀ dɛŋ ɗii lɛ Apolos , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ yalɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Alɛgsaŋdirii , a ̀ kpaga ̀ a Efɛɛzɛ . Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , a ̀ yi ri ̀ lɛ ̀ ŋi ̀ ɗi ɓito ̀ ki ̀ , a ̀ ki yi ɓiɓan ɓi ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ di ɓɛ mɛ re ̀ si nyi bee i ̀ Kan n ̀ ɗem wii wu ki falɛn mii ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey . A kaka ̀ li ̀ gha ̀ ɓum , a ̀ ki re ̀ resi ɓɔ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Yeesus yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ba ̀ ɓtis i ̀ Zyaŋ yɛɛ ̀ nɛ nyii yigha ̀ yɔ ̀ riyɔ ̀ .
Nni Apolos a ̀ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ to ̀ to ̀ g ɓi naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ ris , yɛ ̀ ɛ Pirisilya ri ̀ Akilas ɓɛ woka ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓii , nni ɓɛ teka ̀ nyi , ɓɛ kona ̀ g nyi ki ̀ tɛɛ ̀ zaagh bee inɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , Apolos a ̀ fe ̀ ka ̀ lɛ a kɛn ̀ a Akayi , ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓii ɓɛ righerɛ ̀ n ɓɛ tee ̀ si ̀ nyi nyoo lɛ a kɛn ̀ , ɓɛ ki ka ̀ n ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ wɔɔ lɛ , ɓɛɛ ghaɓ nyi lɛ syeesyee . Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kpa ̀ ga ̀ wɔɔ , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ghɛɓsɛn ɓisuu ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , ɓɛɛ ɓa ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ,
lɛ a ̀ a n ̀ ti a ̀ cii ̀ za ̀ g Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n lɛ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ di ɓɛɛ ̀ n ̀ yoonyolɛ ̀ n ɓi gwi ̀ y . A ̀ re ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ɓɔ , di a ɓaaɓaa ̀ zi ̀ ri ̀ kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ , Yeesus a ̀ ri ̀ Kiris .
Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki Apolos a ̀ ɓaa a Kɔrɛŋt , kɛɛ ̀ ki Pol a ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ , a ̀ mɛ rerenii ̀ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ɓi do ̀ n , a ̀ yu ̀ ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ a Efɛɛzɛ , a ̀ tanɛn ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g wɔɔ , a ̀ tɔg ɓɔ lɛ :
Ɓi ̀ teka ̀ nya Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ ? Ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓaa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Ɓi ̀ sii ka woka ̀ ɓi ̀ gi di ɓɛ ɓuŋi com kidɛŋ lɛ Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay .
Nni Pol a ̀ tɔka ̀ min ɓɔ lɛ : Ri ̀ kuu ɗi ba ̀ ɓtis ɗibe ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi ɓɛ ɓaɓti ̀ gha ̀ mi ̀ ni ? Ɓɛ ɓaa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Ba ̀ ɓtis i ̀ Zyaŋ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Pol a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Zyaŋ a ̀ ɓa ̀ a ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓti ̀ gha ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ mɛ ̀ rem , a ̀ kaka ̀ li ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Isirayɛl lɛ , ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ gherɛɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ nyi ɓii ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ , yɛɛlɔɔ lɛ Yeesus .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ woka ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛn , nni ɓɛ ɓaɓti ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ ɓi ɗii ɗi Kan Yeesus .
Fɔɔnnɛ Pol a ̀ saghi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ ɓya ̀ g ɓi nyoo , Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ki sɛn yi ̀ ɓi ɓɔ , ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ to ̀ g ɗi ɓi ̀ ke ̀ neke ̀ ne ̀ ɓi ɓito ̀ ki ̀ di ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa ɓiɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ re ̀ re ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ , ɓɛɛ kpaa ̀ .
Ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ nunu ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ɗi ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ .
Nni Pol a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n , a ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n wɔɔ lɛ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n , a ̀ kurɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ ɓɛ ̀ ŋwii ɓɛraa ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi seesee ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ kaaka ̀ a ̀ bee inɛ a ki lɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ wowo ̀ ka ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓii , ɓɛɛ gherɛn ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi a ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ mɛ ̀ rem mɛ ̀ te ̀ ɗkakɛn ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ n lɛ di ɓaa gherɛɛ , ɓɛ ki feefengi ̀ bee i ̀ Kan ɓi mɛ ̀ ree ̀ mɛ ɓum , fɔɔnnɛ Pol a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wa ̀ a ̀ , a ̀ teɗ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ ɓɔ ja ̀ ŋ i ̀ dɛŋ , a ̀ kuu ̀ ku ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ ɓɔ ɓɛ ̀ ŋwos ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi naa ̀ -su ̀ kuri ̀ i ̀ Tiranus .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki finɛ ̀ nga ̀ be ̀ g yiɓɛɛ ̀ , kɛɛ kigha ̀ lɛ , ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ a Azii , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n lɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpaŋ lɛ Gi ̀ rɛg , ɓɛ woka ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Kan .
Fɔɔnnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ Pol i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ a kiki da ̀ m yi ɓiɓan yi kuurakɛn ,
le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ , ɓum ɓɛ nteki ̀ zyo ̀ na ̀ yi ɓila ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ den ɓi ɓila ̀ a ̀ ɓi ɓi komga ̀ nyoo i ̀ Pol , ɓɛ ɓaɓa ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roroɓ mii ̀ , ti ̀ roɓ tyaa ti wɔnwɔ ̀ n , ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay ɓi ki kpaŋkpaŋ ɓi ɓumɓɛ ̀ n .
Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓɛ kɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ gha ̀ ja ̀ ŋ bimiɗ lɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ na ̀ ɓi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay ɓɛ mɛɛ ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ na ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay ri ̀ ɗii ɗi Kan Yeesus , ɓɛ kpaa ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay ɓi ̀ n lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni ɓi ɗii ɗi Yeesus a ̀ nɛ Pol a ̀ ti a ̀ la ̀ a ̀ la ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n lɛ , ɓi kpaŋ ̀ !
Ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ kiki ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɔn ɓɛ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey a ̀ dɛŋ , muu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɗii lɛ , Seva ; ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki nghay ki ɓaa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yii Yeesus , n ̀ ki yi ghɛn yɛɛ ri ̀ lɛ Pol ; nni mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ , mi ̀ nii ri ɓɛ ̀ ghɛn ?
Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki nghay a ̀ sɛnga ̀ ɓi ɓɔɔ ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ cee ɓɔ ɓi-te ̀ ɗ , a ̀ ki ̀ ɓɔ le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ , ɓɛ faŋɗa ̀ ka ̀ y ɓi naa i ̀ nɛ ̀ n di ɓɛ ti nyoo zɛ ̀ y , beŋ ja ̀ ŋ bimiɗ .
Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ri ̀ Gi ̀ rɛg bimiɗ ɓɛ ɓɛ ghɛghɛ ̀ ɓka ̀ a Efɛɛzɛ , ɓɛ woka ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ , i ̀ ris wu ɓan ɓɔ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ kee ̀ ke ̀ mzi ̀ gha ̀ ɗii ɗi Kan Yeesus .
Ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɛ yuyu ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ kpa ̀ kpaagh ɓi ̀ mis mɛ ɓum , ɓɛ ki re ̀ resi ɓiɓan ɓi ɓeɓtɛn ɓi ɓɛ kigha ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ki ̀ gwey ki ɓum ki ki kiki ̀ gha ̀ maji ̀ g abɛ ̀ y , ki yugha ̀ y ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kaa ̀ ta ̀ ɓaa ɓɛ maji ̀ g , ɓɛ tɔ ̀ n ɓɔ ɓi mis mɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m . Ɓɛ ɓala ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ ̀ kaa ̀ ta ̀ ɓɛn ̀ ɓɛ kpaga ̀ ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ tɔɔsi ̀ m mɛ ̀ tin mɛɓɛɛ ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ kɛ ̀ nkɛ ̀ nga ̀ bee ̀ bɛ ̀ y ɗi ̀ ri ̀ sa ̀ a ̀ sa ̀ a ̀ ɓi-te ̀ ɗ wu Kan .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ , Pol a ̀ ɓeka ̀ lɛ a kɛn ̀ a Yorisalɛm , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ sya ̀ a zi i ̀ Masedwan ri ̀ zi i ̀ Akayi , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ i m ̀ ɓaa wɔɔ , n ̀ kɛ ̀ n girig ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ Rom .
Nni a ̀ romga ̀ min ɓɔɓti ɓii ɓɛ kisay ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ Timote ri ̀ Erast a Masedwan , nyimiɗ a rɔ ̀ ɓti ̀ ki ̀ ghagsii ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru ɓi ki ̀ la ̀ na ̀ ki zi ki a Azii kin ̀ .
Ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ , ɓɛ ɓigti ̀ gha ̀ coo kiyoo ̀ yo ̀ o ̀ ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki ki seesee bee i ̀ Kan .
N ̀ syaa ̀ gh-i ̀ rɛm adɛŋ ɗii lɛ Demetiriyus a ̀ a n ̀ ti a ̀ syaki ̀ ɓɔɔ ɓife ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ɓɛ mɛɛ mɛ bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛ lɛ Aritemis ri ̀ ri ̀ kuu ɗi swiɗ ɗi ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ lag mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɛ tiraŋ ̀ mii ̀ , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ a ̀ le ̀ le ̀ ɓka ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓii lɛ syeesyee .
Nni a ̀ taŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓii , ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓɛ kiki ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ kuu ɗi kisay ɗin ̀ , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ ! Ɓi ̀ yii lɛ , di ̀ gdi ̀ g wi ̀ s a ri ̀ ɓa , a ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ ɓi-rɛm wu ti syasyag wu .
Nni ɓi seese ̀ e ̀ ɓi ̀ ki wowog , yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ lɛ Pol a ̀ nɛ a ̀ mɛ ki ̀ lɛ , a ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g , a ̀ ki syoŋ ̀ ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey , a ̀ a fɛ a Efɛɛzɛ nyi ri ̀ nyi , ɓaa ̀ yiɓi ɓi zii ̀ Azii bimiɗ . A ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ lɛ , bɛ ̀ ll yi ɓum ɓɛɛ kii ri ̀ ɓya ̀ g ɓyaa , yi yin Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ki ̀ ɓan ki ki ɓeɓtɛɛ mii ̀ , ki yin lɔŋ lɛ , ki ̀ say kis ki ri ɓii ̀ so ̀ o , ki ri girig lɛ mɛɛ mɛ coo bɛ ̀ ll yi ̀ s i giɓ inɛ lɛ Aritemis mɛ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ghali ̀ com ki zɛy , nsoo ̀ ri ̀ gwey ɗi bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛn , i ̀ nɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɔɔɓɔgsi ̀ ɓi zii ̀ Azii bimiɗ , ri ̀ ziinɛ n ̀ ce ̀ m ɗi ri ɓii ̀ le ̀ egh .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ woka ̀ fɔlɔɔ , bim i ki ̀ ɓɔ lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ la ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Aritemis a ̀ nɛ a ̀ Efɛɛzɛ a ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ki ̀ yoo ̀ yo ̀ o ̀ ki kpigha ̀ ɓi ba ̀ n bimiɗ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ suu ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɓi naa i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ n ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ mii ̀ , di ɓɛ mɛ ɓan ɓumɓɛ a Masedwan lɛ ri ̀ Gayus , ri Aristarikɛ ɓɛ ɓɛ n ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ gha ̀ g ɗi ̀ Pol .
Pol a ̀ kɔ ̀ nkɔ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ a rɛli ɓi mis mɛ ɓum wɔ ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ree ̀ g lɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ fɔlɔɔ .
Mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m mɛdɛŋ mɛ a Azii mɛ mɛ ɓagha ̀ mɛ ̀ ghan mɛ Pol , mɛ romga ̀ nyi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ lɛ : Kɛ ̀ ɛ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn ki yu ̀ u ɓi naa ̀ -ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ .
Ki ̀ ɓagha ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ syansya ̀ n ɓi ri ̀ syansya ̀ n ɗyaa , ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛmbog , ɓɔɔ syansya ̀ n ɓi ɗiŋka ̀ a ̀ ; ki ̀ yoo ̀ yo ̀ o ̀ ki ɓagha ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓi gwi ̀ y i ̀ nɛn , fɔɔnnɛ ki ̀ gwey ki ɓum ki yigha ̀ ɓi gi ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓɛ taŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ .
Nni ɓɛ sɔŋi ̀ gha ̀ y ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ ɓi gwi ̀ y inɛn ɗii lɛ Alɛgsaŋdirɛ , lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n innɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ tyɔtyɔ ̀ ka ̀ y asu . Fɔɔnnɛ Alɛgsaŋdirɛ a ̀ nɛn a ̀ maasi ̀ gha ̀ ɓum ri ̀ ca ̀ g lɛ a too ̀ ghrɛn .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ muu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n yɛɛ ri , ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m lɔŋ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ bog , ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Aritemis a ̀ nɛ a Efɛɛzɛ a ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ , ɓɛ ɓii ̀ ta ̀ ka ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki ̀ n fɔlɔɔ a ̀ kpaŋ nunu ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ hawo ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kani ̀ -ɓɛ ̀ kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ gɔmi ̀ na ̀ a ̀ maasi ̀ gha ̀ ɓum , nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Mi ̀ ni ɓumɓɛ a Efɛɛzɛ , ghɛn yɛɛ nani lɛ ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ Efɛɛzɛ i ̀ nnɛ mɛɛ mɛ coo bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ giɓ inɛ lɛ Aritemis mɛ ri , ri ̀ ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛn ki ki kpigha ̀ y aɗyo ̀ o ̀ ?
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ nyoey yi yin ɓi ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ , ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ kɔ ̀ rii lɛ fyo ̀ oog , kɛ ̀ ɓi swe ̀ ɗ kiɓan kidɛŋ .
Ɓisuulɛ , ɓumɓɛ ɓya ̀ a yu ̀ u yi ̀ fɛ ri ̀ ɓɔ ɓɛ , ɓɛ komi ɓi com ɓi ɓyom ɓi ɓi ri ɓi naa ̀ -bɛ ̀ ll yi ̀ s i giɓ , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki to ̀ g yɔ ̀ kiɓe ̀ .
Nni i Demetiriyus ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓii ɓɛ ri ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kidɛŋ ki ɓɛɛ see ̀ ghkɛn ɓɛ raɗ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ , go ̀ n yi ɓɛyɔ ̀ m yi ri wɔɔ , ɓɛ ̀ gɔmi ̀ na ̀ girig wɔɔ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki sɔmɛn , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ sɔmɛɛ !
I ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓidɛŋ ɓi ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ɓi tɔg , ɓi ri lɛ ɓɛ pegsɛ ̀ n ŋwos anɛ ɓɛ ̀ gɔmi ̀ na ̀ ɓɛ taŋzɛɛ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ .
Ɓɛ ki ri ̀ lɛ ɓɛ sɔmɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ si lɛ ti syo ̀ ŋsyoŋ yi ki ̀ yoo ̀ yo ̀ o ̀ ɓi ri ̀ taŋzɛ ̀ n ɗi tya ̀ a taŋzɛɛ ɗi gɛɛ ̀ nɛ ɓisuulɛ , ti ̀ yin ɗi com ki ti ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ti kpaa lɛ , ti resi azi anɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ fɛ mii ̀ ɓɛ ̀ taŋzɛn ; lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ fɔlɔɔ a ̀ kpaa ɓum lɛ ɓɛɛ suki .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ yoo ̀ yo ̀ o ̀ kin ̀ ki leka ̀ , Pol a ̀ taŋzɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ɓaa lɛ a ̀ mɛ reɓ ɓɔ , a ̀ ghesɛ ̀ n min ɓɔ , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n a Masedwan .
A reni ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ na ̀ ki zi kin ̀ di a fafa ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n deɓ lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn nnɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ min ki kpaŋi ̀ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Gi ̀ rɛg .
A kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ wɔɔ ɓɛ ̀ ŋwii ɓɛraa , yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ mɛɛ ̀ teka ̀ fi ̀ tima ̀ lɛ a kɛn ̀ a Sirii , nni a ̀ woka ̀ lɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ mɛ tɔ ̀ kɛn nyi , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ teka ̀ min nɗɛli lɛ , a sugti a Masedwan .
Ɓumɓɛ Pol a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ ɗi ɓɔ , ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ lɛ : Sopatɛr , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ man a ̀ Pirus a ̀ nɛ a Bere , ri ̀ Aristarikɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ Sekunɗus ɓumɓɛ a Tesalonika , Gayus a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a Dɛriɓɛ , ri ̀ Timote , ri ̀ Tisig , ri ̀ Tirofim ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓumɓɛ a Azii .
Ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ loka ̀ ki ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ asu , ɓɛ Kɛn ̀ ɓi ̀ si ki ̀ ɓoŋi ̀ a Tirowas .
Ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkis , ɓi ̀ sii ɓɔka ̀ ki ̀ kom a Filiɓ di mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ɓɛ nki ̀ la ̀ g ɓi ̀ rɛsi ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ nwi ̀ ɗ mɛ mɛ ghaa ̀ gh , fɔɔnnɛ ti ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ ki ̀ tanɛɛ a Tirowas ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛtan ̀ , ti ̀ ki kɔ ̀ ri wɔɔ mɛru taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ .
Ɓi ŋwos a n ̀ tonto a ̀ nɛ ɓi ri ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɗi sɔnɗi ̀ nnɛ ti ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ taŋzɛn lɛ ti teɗ ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll . Pol nyii ghɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ ghaghii ɓi duri tana , nni a ̀ to ̀ ka ̀ ka ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ki ra ̀ ɓsi ɓito ̀ ki ̀ a ̀ kpaŋ nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ -ru .
Ɓɛ ̀ lamɓa ̀ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓi ki ̀ den ki naa ki ti ̀ taŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ mii ̀ ɓi mɛɛ mɛ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
Nni dɛli ̀ i ̀ mum i ̀ dɛŋ ɗii lɛ Etig i ̀ nɛ i ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓi wonɗo ̀ i ̀ ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ fi ̀ lo lɛ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ di Pol a ka ra ̀ araɓsi ̀ lɔŋ ɓito ̀ ki ̀ ɓii , yɛ ̀ ɛ fi ̀ lo fi teri nyi fɔlɔɔ , nni a ̀ kɔ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ y ɓi dɛg i ̀ ki ̀ raa , a ̀ kpi ̀ azi ; yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ mɛɛ ̀ pɛ ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ nyi , ɓɛ ghɛn lɛ , a ̀ mɛ wu .
Fɔɔnnɛ Pol a ̀ sɛnga ̀ min a ̀ kɛ ̀ n mɛ ̀ ree a ̀ pɛ ̀ si ̀ dɛli ̀ i ̀ nɛn , a ̀ kpaa ɓum lɛ : Kɔ ̀ riina lɛ fyo ̀ oog , a ̀ ri ̀ cem .
Nni a ̀ sugti ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ ɓɔɔ ̀ gh , a ̀ ɓɛg bi ̀ rɛs a ̀ ɗi ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn nnɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ di ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ lɔŋ ri ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓii asu , duri i ̀ ra ̀ m i ̀ tan , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ki ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ min .
Ɓɛ suka ̀ ri ̀ mutya ̀ a ̀ dɛli ̀ a ̀ nɛn , di a ̀ ri ̀ cem , ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki ki lɛ , mɛ ̀ rem mɛɛ kpi ɓum ɓi mu ̀ m .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ sii lolo ̀ ka ̀ ki ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ bee ̀ bɛ ̀ y ɓi fi ̀ tima ̀ fi fi kɛnkɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Asɔs , wɔɔnnɛ ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ teetii Pol , ɓisuulɛ nyii kɔnkɔ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ , a kpaŋ wɔɔ ɓi zi .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ tanɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ̀ si a Asɔs , ti ̀ teɗ nyi ɓi fi ̀ tima ̀ lɛ , ti kɛn ̀ a Mitilɛn .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ Pɛ ̀ sɛɛ wɔɔ , ti ̀ ghagsi ̀ lɔŋ rikɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɗis ɓi fi ̀ tima ̀ , ti ̀ kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ a Siyos ɓi duri tana , ŋwos anɛ a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɓka ̀ foo , ti ̀ syaa ̀ gha ̀ a Samos , ɓi a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɓti ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ nnɛ ti ̀ kpaga ̀ a Milɛ .
Pol a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ si ̀ i ̀ rɛn lɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ rɛli a Efɛɛzɛ lɛ , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ri nyi ɓii ̀ cee a Azii . A ̀ ɓo ̀ o ̀ ɓo ̀ o ̀ zɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ , a ɓa a Yorisalɛm ɓi ŋwosi Pa ̀ ŋte ̀ kot , di bee i ɓaa .
Pol a ̀ pɛ ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ɓum a Milɛ , a ̀ rom lɛ ɓɛɛ regii ̀ nyi ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ kiseŋi ̀ ɓɛ ɓi ki ̀ seŋi ki a Efɛɛzɛ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ yugha ̀ y , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ yi yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ghɛghɛɓi ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki mɛ ̀ ɛ nɗi ̀ ri ̀ mi ̀ ni , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n lɔŋ ɓi ŋwos a ̀ n ̀ tonto a ̀ nɛ n ̀ kpaga ̀ ɓi ki ̀ la ̀ na ̀ ki zi ki a Azii .
Mɛ ̀ ɛ nki ̀ i Kan ki ̀ say kɛ ̀ ɛ m ̀ ɓɔgsɛn mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ nsoo ̀ lɛsa ̀ g , ri ̀ misi ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ tam ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ mɛ ̀ tɔɓ mɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ nghɛɛ lɛ ɓi ̀ tɔ ̀ kɔ ̀ ɓi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ntɔɔ ̀ tɔ ̀ kɛ ̀ n mɛ ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ yii lɛ , n ̀ nyamga ̀ ɓi mini ki ̀ ɓan kidɛŋ ki ki ri lɛ , ki ghɛɓsi ̀ mi ̀ ni , kɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ki risi mini ri ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ , ɗi ̀ ri ̀ re ̀ e ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɗi ɓiɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum , nsoo ̀ lɛ a ɓɛ ̀ mɛɛ ɓin .
N ̀ ɗere ̀ ŋi ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ri ̀ Gi ̀ rɛg lɛ ɓɛɛ lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛn mɛ ̀ rem , ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ n Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓɛ ki tyweeyi Yeesus a ̀ Kan wi ̀ s .
Nni ɓigominɛ , n ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ a Yorisalɛm lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Nghay a titini mɛ lɛ nkɛn ̀ , n ̀ -yii ɓi com ki kɛɛ ̀ ɓoŋɓoŋ mɛ wɔɔ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , n ̀ -yii lɛ ɓi ba ̀ n bimiɗ i ̀ nɛ n ̀ kpaŋi wɔɔ , Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ki ti ki resa ̀ g mɛ ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ naa ̀ -za ̀ y , ri ̀ n ̀ kulɛ ̀ n ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓoŋɓoŋ mɛ wɔɔ .
Mɛ ̀ m ̀ ɓiisɛɛ gi ̀ ɓi ki foŋi ̀ n ̀ to ɓi cɛɓ kɛ ̀ m ki mɛ ̀ ɛmi ̀ ɗ , com ki nfɔmfɔ ̀ m ki ri lɛ , nkɛnkɛn asu ri ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɗyɛm ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ , n ̀ ki ki ̀ kisay ki Kan Yeesus a ̀ fagha ̀ mɛ ̀ , kɛɛ ri lɛ , n ̀ ghagsi Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ n ̀ ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin di nkakali Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll , n ̀ -yii lɛ syeesyee lɛ , ɓya ̀ a ghɛɛ ̀ di ɓi i ̀ su wɛ ̀ m a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓigomi ̀ nɛ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki n ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni gɛɛ ̀ nɛ lɛ : Bwaɓ yi wa ̀ a ̀ dɛŋ yi yi ̀ n lɛ , yi kɛn ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓi n ̀ to .
Ɓisuulɛ , n ̀ kpa ̀ ka ̀ ka ̀ mi ̀ ni dwi ̀ ɗ i Bɛ ̀ ll bimiɗ , kɛ ̀ ɛ nnyam mini nsoo ̀ maa ki ̀ ɓan adɛŋ .
Fɔɔnnɛ , ɓe ̀ ŋina mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ , ɓi ̀ ki ɓe ̀ ŋ di kituu ki jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yi Bɛ ̀ ll , yi Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ki rɛsi ̀ gha ̀ mi ̀ ni lɛ ɓi ɓeŋ ̀ ɓeŋ . Mɛniina ki ̀ seŋi ki Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ syeesyee , lɛ a ̀ la ̀ ka ̀ kɔ ri ̀ bwaɓ yii .
Mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yii lɔŋ lɛ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ monɗo , ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ ɗiŋii ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n ajɛ ̀ m yɛ ̀ m , ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓaa ke ̀ ŋi ɓi kituu ki jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Nsoo ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n , ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ tumɛɛ gɛ ri ̀ re ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ɗi ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi , lɛ , ɓɛɛ syoŋ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓi bee yaa ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓaana cem , ɓi ̀ ki yiti lɛ , n ̀ ɗeɓi mi ̀ ni be ̀ g yiraa , yɛ ̀ ɛ i ̀ ru yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwos kɛ ̀ ɛ nfɔɛy , ri ̀ misi ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ tam .
Nni ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki , n ̀ ɗeɓsɛɛ mi ̀ ni ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll n ̀ ki reɓsɛnti mi ̀ ni ri ̀ ɓɔlɛ a ̀ geesɛ ̀ n yi ̀ i ̀ ; ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n yɛɛ ri lɛ , a ̀ ki ̀ lɛ ɓi ɓa ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , a ̀ ki fati mini ɓyom ɓi a ̀ nyamga ̀ ɓisuu ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛŋkii .
M ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ri za ̀ y i ̀ nɛ lɛ , mum a fa mɛ ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni , nsoo ̀ gol , nsoo ̀ ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ .
Mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓomiɗ ɓi ̀ yii lɛ , n ̀ sasa ̀ la ̀ ri ̀ ɓya ̀ g ɓyɛm ̀ ɓi , lɛ n ̀ tanɛn ɓyom ɓi ti ghɛɓ mii ̀ lɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ , ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ n ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ .
Mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗe ̀ sii mi ̀ ni bee yice ̀ m lɛ , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓi sasay fɔlɔɔ , kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɓsii ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ yin ɗi i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , ɓi ̀ ki yiti jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ Kan a ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ŋwɔm wii lɛ : Ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ faa , ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓɛ faa com roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ faa yɛɛ ti a ̀ ɓiisa ̀ g ki ̀ woo ̀ gh ki ̀ rɔɔ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ le ̀ gsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓin ̀ fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ɓaka ̀ mɛ ̀ ɗu ɓi zi , a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll n ̀ ɗaŋ ri ̀ ɓɔ .
Fɔɔnnɛ mum bimiɗ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓɔ a ̀ kpusɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ kɛ ̀ gh , a ̀ ki fyuŋ Pol ɓi ki ̀ mi ̀ i ̀ gh lɛ a lɔɛɗ nyi .
Ki ̀ ɓan ki ki ɓiisɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ ki ̀ faa ̀ n ̀ ɗemi-kɛŋɛn ki ɓagha ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ Pol a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ , ɓaa ghɛɛ ̀ di ɓi i ̀ su wii ŋwos adɛŋ . Nni ɓɛ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ min nyi ki foŋi ̀ a fi ̀ tima ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ ghasɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ , ɓi ̀ sii ɓɔg ɓi fi ̀ tima ̀ ti ̀ ro ̀ ŋi ̀ bee inɛ a Kos lɛ saaɗ . Ɓi duri tana ti ̀ kpaŋ a Roodɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ wɔɔ , ti ̀ kɛ ̀ n a Patara .
Ti ̀ tanɛ ̀ nga ̀ fi ̀ tima ̀ fi fi ɓagha ̀ ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ nkɛni a Fenisii , ti ̀ ɓɔg min mii ̀ , ti ̀ kɛ ̀ n .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ ɓagha ̀ di ti ̀ ti ɓii ̀ seesee yi ̀ ki ̀ ri ̀ ŋ ki riɓa ̀ y ki lɛ Siipirɛ , ti ̀ ca ̀ dka ̀ y kɔ ɓi ki ̀ mɛŋ ti ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a Sirii . Ti ̀ kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ rɛlii a Tiir , wɔɔnnɛ fi ̀ tima ̀ fi ghɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ sɛɛ ̀ dii mɛtɛ ̀ g .
Ti ̀ kɔri ̀ gha ̀ wɔɔ mɛru taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , lɛ ti ̀ tanɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n wɔɔ , Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ki tini ̀ bɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓɛɛ kpaa ̀ Pol lɛ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɔg a Yorisalɛm .
Di tya ̀ a ghagsi mɛru taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , nnɛ ti ̀ ru ̀ ɓtɛ ̀ nga ̀ ti ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ ɓi ̀ si ki ̀ fɔŋi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m lɛ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓaa , ri ̀ ɓɔn ɓaa , ɓɛ ceesi ̀ ɓi ̀ si n ̀ de ̀ e ̀ wu ba ̀ n . Nni ti ̀ ɓaka ̀ mɛ ̀ ɗu ɓi zi , ti ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi be ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ ghesɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ , ɓi ̀ sii ɓɔg ɓi fi ̀ tima ̀ , ɓɔɔ sugta ̀ g a ɓɛ ̀ mɛɛ ɓaa .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ y a Tiir ɓi fi ̀ tima ̀ ti ̀ yu ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ lɔŋ ki rɛlii a Pitolemayis , ti ̀ to ̀ gsi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓis ɓɛ righerɛ ̀ n , ti ̀ ki ghagsi bimiɗ a ̀ ŋwos n ̀ ɗaŋ ɗi ɓɔ .
Ɓi duri tana nnɛ ti ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ti ̀ kɛ ̀ n a Sezare , wɔɔnnɛ ti ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ a mɛɛ mɛ Filiɓ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ kali ̀ -ɓɔlɛ , a ̀ ki ɓati kibog ki ɓi ɓum taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛ rɛsi ̀ gha ̀ a Yorisalɛm ; a lɔ ̀ ŋkii nnɛ ti ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ .
A ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gɔ ̀ n ɓɛnin , ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ di ɓɛ ka yi ɓi ɓɛbaŋi ̀ , ɓɛ ki ɓa ti ɓɛkpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ ɓagha ̀ di tya ̀ a ghagsi ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru wɔɔ , fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan a ̀ dɛŋ ɗii lɛ Agaɓus a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ y a Zyude .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ yugha ̀ ɓi ̀ si ki ̀ tanɛɛ a teɗ ka ̀ nɗa a ̀ Pol , a ̀ ka ̀ gi ̀ lɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ mii , ri ̀ ɓya ̀ g ɓii , a ̀ ki kpaa lɛ : Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay kɛɛ ̀ kpaaghi lɛ : Ɓi ̀ ghɛɛ ? Fɛlɛ nnɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ ka ̀ ŋi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ka ̀ nɗa a ̀ nɛ , ɓɛ ki teɗ nyi , ɓɛ fa nyi ɓi ɓya ̀ g ɓi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ woka ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓis ɓɛ a Sezare , ti ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋza ̀ g Pol lɛ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɔg a Yorisalɛm .
Nni Pol a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Cɛ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓi ɗiighɗigsi ̀ mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗem mii ̀ ɗi ̀ mɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ gh ? A ̀ a bɛn yɔ ̀ riyɔ ̀ yɛɛ yi m ̀ ɓoŋɓo ̀ ŋ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ gi ̀ m ̀ pe ̀ gsɛn lɛ nwu a Yorisalɛm ɓi ɗii ɗi Kan Yeesus .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ yaaghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ , nni ɓi ̀ sii caɗka ̀ nyi ti ̀ kpaa lɔŋ nyi lɛ , ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi Kan ɗyɛɛ kilɛn .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɔɔ mɛru ɓɛ ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ , nni ti ̀ ɓu ̀ ŋɛ ̀ nga ̀ ti ̀ ɓɔg a Yorisalɛm .
Ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ a Sezare ɓɛ ti ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ , ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ ɓi ̀ si ki ̀ foŋi ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Nazɔŋ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a Siipirɛ , ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ n ̀ tonto , lɛ ti kɔri wɔɔ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ kpaga ̀ a Yorisalɛm , ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓis ɓɛ righerɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ghaɓ ɓi ̀ si ri ̀ ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ .
Ɓi duri tana nnɛ Pol a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si yɛ ̀ ɛ Zyag . Ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ kiseŋi ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ taŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ girig wɔɔ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pol a ̀ to ̀ gsa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓɔ ri ̀ kpaa ɗi ɓiɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ e ̀ m ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ a n ̀ kii , a ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , ɓi ki ̀ say ki nyii nki ̀ kii .
Nni ɓɛ woka ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ , ɓɛ fa Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ kem ɓɛ ki kpaa Pol lɛ : Maasoŋ ̀ , u ̀ ghɛɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ tɔɔsi ̀ m ɓɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ mɛ gherɛ ̀ n wɔ ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ ki ri ̀ lɔŋ ɓɛsi ̀ i ̀ rɛn ɓi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓis .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛ n ̀ woogh ɓi ɓɔlɛ , lɛ wa ̀ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ a gwe ̀ ɗ lɛ , ɓɛn ̀ ɓɛɛ caɗ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Moyis , ɓɛn ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɗti ɓɔn ɓɛ ɓɛn ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓe ̀ ŋdi ɓisyɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓi ɓɛseŋi ɓaa .
Nni ti ghay la ? Ɓaa ki rɔ ̀ ɓ ɓi lɛ , ɓɛ woogh ɓi lɛ u ̀ ri ̀ fɛ .
U ki lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ kpaa ̀ lɛ u ki . Ti ̀ ri ̀ fɛ ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛnin , ɓɛ ɓɛ n ̀ ka ̀ nɛɛ bɛ ̀ ɗ i na ̀ ziri ̀ ya ̀ .
Tera ɓɔ , ɓi kɛn ̀ a zo ̀ ghɛ ̀ n i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ lɛɛ , u ̀ pee ̀ ɓi ̀ kɔ ̀ tɛn ɓyaa , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ ŋɗɛɛ mɛ ̀ to , i u ̀ ki ̀ i fɔlɔɔ , ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɛ lɛ , ɓɛ ̀ ɓɔlɛ ɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ wowo ̀ g ɓɛ rarɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓɛ yin mii ̀ , ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ wɔ ̀ girig , u ɓe ̀ ŋɓeŋ ɓidɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Moyis , u ̀ ki nɔ ̀ ɔnɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ ɓyɔ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ .
Ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a ɓum ɓɛ zɛy ɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , ti ̀ ka ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ti ̀ renga ̀ lɛ , ɓɛɛ celi ɓyɛn ɓi nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ woli ɓi ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi ɓinu ̀ n ɓi zɛy ri ̀ zɛy , ɓɛ celi ̀ ti ̀ bwaɓ yi nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛ i ̀ wii lɛ swi ̀ i ̀ ɗ , ri ̀ ti ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g .
Nni Pol a ̀ teka ̀ min ɓumɓɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ lɛɛ zo ̀ ghɛ ̀ n n ̀ ɗaŋ ɓi duri tana . Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ min ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ ɓɔ , lɛ a kpaa ̀ ɓɔ go ̀ n inɛ ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ faa ̀ ɓi ̀ kɔ ̀ tɛn ɓisuu mum bimiɗ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓɔ di zo ̀ ghɛ ̀ n i ̀ le ̀ egh ,
Di ɓɛ ti lɛ ɓɛɛ lɔgsi mɛ ̀ ru taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓi zo ̀ ghɛ ̀ n ya ̀ a ̀ , nni Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ a Azii ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ Pol ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓɛ toosa ̀ g ɓum ɓɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ , ɓɛ ɓan Pol
di ɓɛɛ kuukugsɛ ̀ n jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Mi ̀ ni ɓumɓɛ a Isirayɛl , yu ̀ una ɓi ̀ si fɛ ̀ ! Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ja ̀ ŋbimiɗ , di a re ̀ resi ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m lɛ ɓɛɛ ki lɛ , ɓɛ sɛɛti ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kis , ɓɛ sɛɛti ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Moyis , ɓɛ ki sɛɛti naa yi ̀ s i Bɛ ̀ ll . A ̀ a rɛ ̀ ŋii gi ̀ ki ̀ ɗiŋzii ɓumɓɛ zɛy ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll . Ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗin ̀ , ɗi yogsii ri ̀ ɓa ɗi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , i ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ce ̀ li ̀ .
Ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ fɔlɔɔ lɛ , ɓɛ loka ̀ ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ Tirofim a ̀ nɛ a Efɛɛzɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ Pol ɓi ba ̀ n , ɓɛ feki ̀ nya lɛ Pol a ̀ a ɗiŋzii nyi ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ba ̀ n bimiɗ i ̀ nyɛ ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ ghɛ ̀ ŋmɛ ̀ n yi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɓɛg ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , nni ɓɛ ɓanga ̀ Pol , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi ɓi dan , ɓɛ ghas ki ̀ si ̀ mgii mɛ ̀ suunaa mɛ naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kaaka ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ bee inɛ ɓɛɛ wey nyi , nni ɓɔlɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ ree ̀ mɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ gwey lɛ : Ki ̀ yoo ̀ yo ̀ o ̀ ki ti ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ Yorisalɛm bimiɗ .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ gha ̀ s ki ̀ teri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛsa ̀ g , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛdɛŋ a ̀ kɛ ̀ n mɛ ̀ ree ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓagha ̀ . Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ y n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ gwey n ̀ ɗaŋ ɗi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛdɛŋ , ɓɛ ca ̀ ɗ Pol , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓogti nyi .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ gwey a ̀ tyo ̀ ŋdɛ ̀ nga ̀ y a ̀ ɓan Pol , ɓɛ kaŋ ̀ nyi bɛn ɗi mɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ŋi , a ̀ tɔg min ɓum lɛ , ŋwaa ̀ be yɛɛ ri ̀ lɛ , cɛ kɛɛ ̀ ki a ̀ ki ̀ i ?
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ ̀ n i ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ lɛ ki ri fɛlɛ , ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ lɛ , ki ri fɛlɛ ̀ . Yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ gwey a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ bee inɛ lɛ a wog ki ̀ ɓan mii ̀ lɛ syeesyee i ̀ yin lɛ , ki ̀ yoo ̀ yo ̀ o ̀ ki ceegha ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ lɔɔ ̀ gh Pol .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kpaga ̀ ri ̀ nyi ɓi ɓɛ ̀ si ̀ tɛɓ , ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛɛ tɛg nyi n ̀ tɛ ̀ ghɛn , ɓisuulɛ , gwi ̀ y i ̀ nɛn i ̀ nyɛnga ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey
lɛ , ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ nɔɔnɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ nyi di ɓɛɛ kpaakpaa lɛ : Ɓɛɛ wey nyi , ɓɛɛ wey nyi .
Ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓɛ mɛɛ ̀ ɗiŋzi ̀ gha ̀ Pol ɓi gari kɛɛ ̀ ki a ̀ tɔka ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ gwey lɛ : N ̀ ɗi ̀ nya lɛ m ̀ pɔ ̀ s maa jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ? Nni roa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ nyi lɛ : U ̀ yii kɔmiɗ ri ̀ gi ̀ rɛg ?
A ̀ a wɔ ̀ yɛɛ ri kɔm ̀ muu Egiɓtɛn a ̀ nɛ a ̀ a m ̀ ɓigtii wɛ ̀ y fɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ mɛ nghaghii mɛ ? Nnyɛɛ nɗiŋii ɓi ̀ tɔ ̀ mbɔ ̀ ɓi-reɓ , ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ tɔɔsi ̀ m ɓɛnin .
Nni a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ nyi lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ muu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛ a Silisii i ̀ nɛ lɛ Tarisi ; n ̀ ɗi ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛ mum a ̀ yin lɛ , a ̀ co ̀ mɛ ̀ n , ku ̀ ru ̀ g gherɛn ɓa ̀ lɛ n ̀ too ̀ ghrɛn ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ gwey anɛ ̀ n a ̀ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ , Pol a ̀ rɛli ̀ i ̀ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ si ̀ tɛɓ aɗyoo , a ̀ maasi ̀ ɓum ri ̀ ca ̀ g . Nni ɓum ɓɛ maarɛ ̀ nga ̀ , a ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n min ɗi ɓɔ ɓi ri ̀ e ̀ bi ̀ reegh , a ̀ kpaa lɛ :
Mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓɛ ̀ m ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓɛ ̀ m , ɓigomi ̀ nɛ ramina mɛ ̀ ree ̀ , ɓi wog com ki n ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ n ̀ ɗe ̀ si ̀ mi ̀ ni .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ woka ̀ di Pol a ̀ too ̀ ghrɛɛ ɓi ri ̀ ebi ̀ reegh ɓɛ mam lɛ kpaɗ ; nni Pol a ̀ kpagha ̀ lɛ :
N ̀ ɗi ̀ muu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , n ̀ -yalɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Tarisi ɓi ki ̀ la ̀ na ̀ ki zi ki a Silisii . Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , fɛ ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛ nnɛ n ̀ tɔɔ , n ̀ ki yilag ɓisyɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓi ɓɛseŋi ɓis yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ , a mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ mɛ Gamalyɛl ; m ̀ ɓagha ̀ girig n ̀ falɛn ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll lɔŋ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ mi ̀ ni girig ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ falɛn ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m gɛɛ ̀ nɛ .
N ̀ ɗu ̀ u ̀ ɗu ̀ u ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ nɔɔ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ bee i ̀ Kan , wɛ ̀ y a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ wowo ̀ la ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛdɛŋ , n ̀ ki ɓanɓan lɛ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ baŋi ̀ n ̀ fogi ̀ ɓɔ ɓi ɓi ̀ sɔŋ , n ̀ ki pi ̀ ki ɓɔ ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y .
N ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ri mɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ lɛ , ɓɛ fagha ̀ kɔm ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kaa ̀ ta ̀ ɓisuu ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ a Damas . Nni n ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ wɔɔ lɛ , n ̀ sug yi ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ n ̀ tanɛɛ , a Yorisalɛm , ɓɛ ̀ ka ̀ gakɛn ɓi ɓi ̀ sɔŋ di ɓɛɛ pɔnɔ ̀ si ɓɔ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ m ̀ ɓagha ̀ di n ̀ kaka ɓi bee ɓi ri ̀ kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ a Damas , nni n ̀ si ̀ gmɛ ̀ nga ̀ di Coo ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ki mɛ ki ̀ yi aɗyoo lɛ ŋwa ̀ a ̀ ɗ , ki yu ki ceŋzɛ ̀ n mɛ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ kpi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi zi , n ̀ wog di jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ kpaakpaa mɛ lɛ : Sol ! Sol wɔ ̀ , u yeeyee ̀ si ̀ mɛ ̀ lɛ cɛ yɔ ?
Nni m ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ lɛ : Kan , wɔ ̀ yɛɛ ri ghɛn ? Jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ ɓa ̀ g mɛ ̀ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ri Yeesus a ̀ nɛ a Nazarɛt a ̀ nɛ u ̀ ti , u ̀ yee ̀ ye ̀ e ̀ si ̀ .
Ɓumɓɛ m ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ ɗi ɓɔ , ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn , ki ̀ ɓan kifog jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛnɛ ɓɛ woka ̀ ɓi .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ tɔka ̀ min lɛ : Kan , cɛ kɛɛ ̀ ki n ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ? Kan a ̀ ɓa ̀ g mɛ ̀ lɛ : Pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyoo , u kɛn ̀ a Damas , wɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ri wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ re ̀ sii com ki u ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ i .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗɔ ̀ ɓka ̀ kɛ ̀ nghɛnɛn ti lɛ ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ki ̀ n ki ɗiŋzi ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ ti ̀ ɗyaŋ , nni ɓumɓɛ m ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ ɓɛ ɓanga ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓi ca ̀ g , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ɗi ̀ mɛ ̀ a Damas .
Ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ ɗii lɛ Ananyas , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ falɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n a ̀ ki nɔ ̀ ɔnɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓis , Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ a Damas , ɓɛ sɛsɛ ̀ ka ̀ nyi .
Nni a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ , a ̀ kpaa mɛ ̀ lɛ : Geni wɛ ̀ m Sol , ghɛnɛn ti ̀ , ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kɔm ̀ kin ̀ nnɛ mis mɛ ̀ m mɛ ghaska ̀ ki ̀ ŋwa ̀ rɛɛ , n ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ti ̀ ri ̀ ghɛnɛ ̀ n n ̀ ki ghɛn nyi .
Nni Ananyas a ̀ kpaagha ̀ mɛ ̀ lɛ : Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓis a ̀ loka ̀ wɔ ̀ ki ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ni lɛ , u yi ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗii , u ̀ ghɛn m ̀ bobog a ̀ mum a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ saaɗ u ̀ ki wog jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ kpaŋii ̀ ɓi ŋwɔm wi ̀ i ̀ ;
ɓisuulɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ wi ̀ i ̀ , lɛ u ghagsi ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi u ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , u ̀ ghɛn , u ̀ ki wog .
Nni ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , kɔ ̀ ɔ lɛ ̀ mziti , pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyoo u teɗ ba ̀ ɓtis ɓi ɗii ɗi Kan , di ɓiɓe ɓyɔɔ ɓyɛɛ ɓa ɓi ̀ so ̀ o ̀ yɛn .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ sugti ̀ gha ̀ y a Yorisalɛm , nni n ̀ ghay wɛ ̀ m wu faŋi ̀ gha ̀ di m ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɔɓɔŋza ̀ g ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll ,
fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ Kan , a ̀ kpaa mɛ ̀ lɛ : Ki ̀ ya lɛ fyɛ ̀ ɗ , u fyaŋzi ki ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ a Yorisalɛm lɛ ɓumɓɛ wɔɔ ɓaa gherɛn ɓi ɓiban ɓi u ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ ɓii ̀ ghagsii ɓi rarɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ mɛ ̀ .
Nni n ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Kan , ɓɔmiɗ ɓɛ yii lɛ , mɛ ̀ ɛ nkɛ ̀ ngi ̀ ɓi naa yi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n , di mɓanɓan yi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ gherɛɛ wɔ ̀ , m ̀ pi ̀ pi ̀ g ɓɔ ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y , n ̀ ki reereɓsi ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓog ɓɔ ki ̀ to ̀ n .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ wowɔla ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ a ̀ nɛ lɛ Ityɛn mɛɛ ̀ miɗ m ̀ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ , mɛ ̀ m ̀ ɓagha ̀ girig ɓijɛ ̀ m i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ wola ̀ nyi ɓɛ ̀ n , mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ki ɓe ̀ ŋɓe ̀ ŋga ̀ ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ɓyaa .
Nni Kan a ̀ kpaagha ̀ min mɛ lɛ : Kɛ ̀ na ɓisuulɛ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ romi fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ , ɓi ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɛ ka kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ lɛ fyo ̀ oog lɛ ɓɛɛ wog ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓii ɓɛ mɛɛ ̀ woka ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ siito ̀ n inɛ ̀ n , nni ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ syan jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Pisi ɓi ̀ si ŋwaa ̀ nɛ bi ̀ i ̀ bii ̀ , ki ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ti ̀ ɓi lɛ a ghɛghɛɓ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ syansya ̀ nga ̀ fɔlɔɔ di ɓɛɛ ̀ ma ̀ mag ɓila ̀ a ̀ ɓyaa , ɓɛ rara ̀ ɓ ku ̀ ru ̀ ɓu ɓɛ pampa ̀ m aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
Nni n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɗiŋzi Pol ɓi gari , ɓɛ ki ɓog nyi ki ̀ to ̀ n lɛ a kpaa ̀ cɛ kɛɛ kii ̀ lɛ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛɛ wog bim fɔlɔɔ ri nyi , ɓɛ syansya ̀ n ɓi le ̀ g a ̀ nɛn .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ mɛɛ ̀ kuɓsi ̀ gha ̀ Pol lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓog nyi ki ̀ to ̀ n , nni a ̀ tɔka ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ sa ̀ g lɛ : Ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓog muu Ro ̀ mɛŋ di ɓɛ ka yɔ ̀ mzi ɓi nyi ?
Yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ sa ̀ g a ̀ nɛn a ̀ woka ̀ fɔlɔɔ , nni a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ gwey lɛ a kpaa nyi lɛ : U ̀ yii com ki u kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ u ki ? Ŋwaa ̀ nɛnii a ̀ ri ̀ muu Ro ̀ mɛŋ .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ gwey a yugha ̀ ki ̀ tɔɔ ̀ gh Pol lɛ : Ki ri saaɗ lɛ u ̀ ri ̀ muu Ro ̀ mɛŋ ? Pol a ̀ gheri ̀ lɛ : Ki ri saaɗ fɔ ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Nni n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ gwey a ̀ kpaati ̀ gha ̀ min lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ su ̀ u ̀ ghra ̀ ka ̀ ɓyoo mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni a ɓɛ ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ lɛ m ̀ ɓa ɓi nɗɛli wu muu Ro ̀ mɛŋ . Pol a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ muu Ro ̀ mɛŋ a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n a ri ̀ yalɛ ̀ n .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ mɛɛ ̀ ɓoka ̀ nyi ki ̀ to ̀ n lɛ di a too ̀ ghrɛn ɓɛ ghaska ̀ ki ̀ ghaaghraagh , nsoo ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ gwey a ̀ risi ̀ gha ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ woka ̀ lɛ , Pol a ̀ ri ̀ muu Ro ̀ mɛŋ ɓisuulɛ , nnyɛɛ reɓsi ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ kaŋ ̀ nyi bɛn .
Ɓi duri tana , yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ gwey a ̀ kɔ ̀ nkɔ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ , a konag ki ̀ yii ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ sɔmɛ ̀ nga ̀ Pol mii ̀ nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ fumi nyi bɛn , a ̀ ki tɔg ɓɛpi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓi Sa ̀ ne ̀ di ̀ rɛŋ lɛ ɓɛɛ taŋzɛn , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ y ri ̀ Pol a ̀ rɛsi ̀ ɓɔ nyi asu .
Pol a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ mis ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓi Sa ̀ ne ̀ di ̀ rɛŋ a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , a ̀ kpaŋ gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , n ̀ ɗem wu yin mɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ riighriki ̀ nsoo ̀ lɛsa ̀ g , ɓi ri ̀ ba ɗi lɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey a ̀ nɛ lɛ Ananyas a ̀ reɓsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ Pol ja ̀ ŋbog lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓog nyi com ɓi ŋwɔm ; nni Pol a ̀ kpaagha ̀ min nyi lɛ :
Bɛ ̀ ll nnyɛɛ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓoo ̀ gh , wɔ ̀ com ki ba ̀ ŋba ̀ ŋ ki puɓ ki ! U ̀ kɔ ̀ rii foo lɛ , u yɔm ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna aɗyoo , ki ̀ ɓan kifog kɔ ̀ ɔ ki nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti com ki ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓyɛɛ ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ , ɓisuulɛ u ̀ kpaa lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓog mɛ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ Pol ja ̀ ŋbog ɓɛ tɔka ̀ nyi lɛ : U ̀ sɛmgii pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll !
Nni Pol a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , ma ̀ a yii ɓi lɛ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey yɛɛ ri , lɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ , kɔ ̀ ɔ sɛm rifo ̀ m ɗi ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kɔɔ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pol a ̀ yigha ̀ lɛ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ri mɛ ̀ raŋ mɛɓɛɛ ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ sa ̀ du ̀ syɛŋ , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wa ̀ a ̀ lɛ : Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ Fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ , man a ̀ Fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ nni ɓɛɛ ̀ sɔmag mɛ ɓisuulɛ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tyweeyi lɛ ɓi ̀ loŋ ɓi ri ɓii ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛɛ .
Pol a ̀ syɔɔ ̀ di ̀ gha ̀ ɓi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ inɛn di ki ̀ yoo ̀ yo ̀ o ̀ ki mɛ kpi ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ nɛ lɛ , ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ sa ̀ du ̀ syɛŋ , fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ taŋzɛn wu ghasɛ ̀ nga ̀ ga ̀ ɓ yiɓɛɛ ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ Ɓɛ ̀ sa ̀ du ̀ syɛŋ ɓɛɛ ̀ si ̀ i ̀ rag ɓi n ̀ dɛli wulɛ : Com kidɛŋ ki yin lɛ ri ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓilo ̀ ŋ , nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓum ɓɛ titom , nsoo ̀ lɛ n ̀ ghay . Wɔ ̀ lɛ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɔɔ ̀ ghera ̀ g lɛ ɓyom ɓi ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ri wɔɔ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ yoo ̀ yo ̀ o ̀ ki kɛnkɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɔŋ asu ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , nni ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓi n ̀ ɗaŋ wu Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ aɗyoo , ɓɛ rɛli ɓi ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , ɓɛ kpaa lɛ : Ɓi ̀ sii ghɛɛ ɓi kiɓan ki ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki ̀ i , ɓaa ̀ yi ɓi n ̀ ghay wudɛŋ nsoo ̀ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom adɛŋ yɛɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ a ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n ri ̀ nyi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓagha ̀ di ki mɛ ɓa ̀ ŋ , n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ gwey a risi ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ ki pa ̀ kii Pol nsoo ̀ m ̀ pa ̀ kakɛn fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ romga ̀ y ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ yu nyi ki ̀ teri ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ɓumɓɛ ̀ n , ɓɛɛ pɛɛ ̀ zi nyi ɓi gari .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ i ̀ ru wu finga ̀ , Kan a ̀ re ̀ sɛ ̀ n Pol a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Pol , kɔ ̀ ɔ ca ̀ rɛn ! Lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ n ̀ lo ̀ mi ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki ki seesee mɛ ̀ a Yorisalɛm , nnɛ u ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ti ̀ ki ̀ lo ̀ mi ̀ aa ̀ Rom .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ duri i tanga ̀ nni Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ wɔrɛ ̀ nga ̀ , ɓɛ kanɛ ̀ n bɛ ̀ ɗ lɛ , ɓwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓwaa ɗi ɓi com , ɓɔ kɔɔ ̀ ki nɔ nsoo ̀ mɛ ̀ nig di ɓɔɔ ka wey ɓi Pol .
Ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ a dwi ̀ ɗ i m ̀ ɓeɓɛn inɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ceegha ̀ mɛ ̀ tin mɛɓɛɛ ̀ .
Nni ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ ki ̀ tanɛɛ lɛ , ri ̀ ɓɛpi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Tya ̀ a ka ̀ nɛɛ bɛ ̀ ɗ ri ɓi ̀ sii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ lɛ ti ̀ yin lɛ ti ̀ ɗi com di ti ̀ ka wey ɓi Pol .
Nni ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓi Sa ̀ ne ̀ di ̀ rɛŋ , tɔɔghna n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ gwey lɛ a yuiy mi ̀ ni ri ̀ Pol , ɓi pwaa ̀ lɛ ɓi kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ , ɓi konag ki ̀ fiɓii kiɓan kii lɛ syeesyee . Ɓi ɓɛg wi ̀ s , ti ̀ ti ɓɛ ̀ pe ̀ gsɛn lɛ ti wey nyi di a ̀ ka kpaŋ ɓi a lɔ ̀ ŋkin .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ mancɛɛ Pol a ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ woka ̀ dwi ̀ ɗ inɛ ̀ n , nni a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɛ lɔka ̀ Pol , a ̀ wogsi ̀ nyi yɔ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Pol a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ , a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Kɛ ̀ na ki ̀ foŋi ̀ dɛli ̀ i ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ gwey lɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki lɛ a kpaa ̀ nyi .
Nni n ̀ kɔmɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ nɛn a ̀ teka ̀ dɛli ̀ i ̀ nɛn , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ yɔ ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ gwey a ̀ kali ̀ nyi lɛ : Ki ̀ mbu ̀ ŋ ki lɛ Pol , kɛ yaa regii mɛ ̀ , ki kpaa lɛ n ̀ -yuy ri ̀ dɛli ̀ i ̀ nɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɔɔ , ɓisuulɛ i ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kidɛŋ ki yɛ ̀ ɛ kpaa ̀ wɔ ̀ .
Nni n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ gwey a ̀ ɓanga ̀ ŋwɔɓti a ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓi ca ̀ g , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ dwi ̀ ɗ , a ̀ tɔg nyi lɛ : Ki ̀ ɓan aɗi kɛɛ ̀ ki u kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ u ̀ kpaa ̀ mɛ ̀ ?
Dɛli ̀ i ̀ nɛn i ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ mɛ wooghrɛn jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ yu wɔ ̀ ki ̀ tɔɔ ̀ gh lɛ u ̀ kɛn ̀ ɗi ̀ Pol a Sa ̀ ne ̀ di ̀ rɛŋ ri ̀ duri , ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ ɓanɛɛ ɓi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ lɛ , ɓɔɔ ̀ kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ ɓɔɔ konag ti ̀ ki ̀ fiɓii kiɓan ki anɛ ̀ n .
Nni kɔ ̀ ɔ wog com ki ɓɛ ri wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ kpaa ̀ ɓisuulɛ ɓum ɓɛ ceeyɛn mɛtin mɛɓɛɛ ̀ , ɓɛ ri nyi ɓɛ ̀ ranɗamɛn ɓi bee , ɓum ɓɛnce ̀ m ɓɛ n ̀ ka ̀ nɛɛ bɛ ̀ ɗ lɛ , ɓɔɔ yin lɛ ɓɛ ɗi com , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki nɔ nsoo ̀ mɛ ̀ nig di ɓɔɔ ka wey ɓi Pol . Ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , ɓɛ ti ɓɛ ̀ pe ̀ gsɛn nni jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛnɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓoŋɓo ̀ ŋ .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ gwey a ̀ ca ̀ ɗka ̀ ŋwɔɓti a ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ a kɛn ̀ . A ̀ ki siitɛn nyi lɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ kpaa mum lɛ , a ̀ a yu ̀ u nyi ki ̀ kpa ̀ kii dwi ̀ ɗ inɛ ̀ n .
Nni n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ gwey a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛsa ̀ g ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Terina ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ lɛ : ɓɛ zɛy ɓɛ ̀ hɔnɗɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ , ɓɛ ɓi zo ̀ m yi kimbɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ aɗyoo mɛ ̀ tin mɛraa ri ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ , ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ mɛkɔ ̀ ŋ ɓɛ ̀ hɔnɗɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ ; ɓi pegsɛn lɛ , ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ mɛkɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ taa ̀ ni ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ ru , ɓi ri ̀ kɛ ̀ n ɗi a Sezare .
Ɓu ̀ ŋɛɛna girig zo ̀ m i ki ̀ mbɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓisuu Pol , lɛ ɓi kɛn ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi yɛ ̀ ɛ gɔmi ̀ na ̀ Felis lɛ sogha ̀ sogha .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ka ̀ nga ̀ min kaa ̀ ta ̀ lɛ :
Mɛ ̀ Kiloodɛ Lizyas , n ̀ togsii wɔ ̀ Felis gɔmi ̀ na ̀ a ̀ gwey .
Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ mɓani ŋwaa ̀ nɛ n ̀ ɗomii ̀ wɔ ̀ a ̀ nɛ , ɓɛ n ̀ ki ti lɛ ɓɛɛ wes ̀ nyi , nni mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ , m ̀ ɓa ̀ tɛ ̀ n nyi ɓi ɓya ̀ g ɓyaa , di m ̀ mɛ wog lɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ muu Ro ̀ mɛŋ .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ za ̀ y i ̀ nɛ lɛ , di ma ̀ a yii ki ̀ ɓan ki a ̀ a nki ̀ i ɓɔ , nni mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ gherɛɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ yɔmzi nyi ɓi n ̀ taŋ ̀ zɛn waa wulɛ Sa ̀ ne ̀ di ̀ rɛŋ .
Ɓi ɓɛg wɛ ̀ m , mɛ ̀ nghɛɛ lɛ , ɓɛɛ ̀ sɔmag nyi ɓisuu ɓiɓan ɓi ɓi seesee ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓyaa . Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , a ̀ ki ̀ i ɓi bimiɗ a ̀ ki ̀ ɓan anɛ ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ wey nyi mii ̀ , nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓɛ pig nyi ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓaa kɔ ̀ ŋɗɛɛ mɛ ̀ lɛ , Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ mɛ tɔ ̀ kɛn lɛ ɓɛɛ wey nyi , fɔɔnnɛ ma ̀ a gha ̀ si wɔ ̀ nyi ki ̀ romi ̀ i ̀ , n ̀ ki kpaa ɓum ɓii ɓɛ kiɓan lɛ , ɓɛɛ yu nyi ki ̀ sɔmɛɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɔɔ ɓɔmi ̀ ɗ . O ̀ o o ̀ o ̀ yaa ̀ .
Ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ kigha ̀ lɔŋ ɓiɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ ki . Ɓɛ teɗ Pol , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ lɔŋ ɗi nyi ri ̀ i ̀ ru wi ̀ n , ɓɛ kpaŋ a Aŋtipatiris .
Ɓi duri tana , ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi zi ɓɛ caɗka ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓi zo ̀ m yi kimbɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ ghaa ̀ gh ri ̀ nyi bee ̀ bɛ ̀ y , ɓɔɔ sugti ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ jɛ ̀ m ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɛ ka lɔka ̀ Pol .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ ɓi zo ̀ m yi ki ̀ mbɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛ kpaga ̀ a Sezare , ɓɛ fa gɔmi ̀ na ̀ kaa ̀ ta ̀ , ɓɛ ceesi ̀ Pol ɗi ̀ nyi .
Nni gɔmi ̀ na ̀ a ̀ ɓa ̀ la ̀ kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ nɛn a ̀ tɔg min Pol lɛ : Wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓi tum a zi abe ? Ɓɛ resi ̀ nyi lɛ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a Silisii yɛɛri .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ min nyi lɛ : Mɛ ̀ m ̀ ɓii ̀ yii ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kɔɔ di ɓum ɓɔɔ ɓɛ sɔmi ̀ na ̀ ɓɛ mɛ kpaŋ fɛ . A ̀ reɓsi ̀ min ɓum lɛ , ɓɛɛ ka kɛ ̀ n ki lɔɔ ̀ gh Pol ɓi mɛɛ mɛ Eroodɛ .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru mɛtan ̀ , nni pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey a ̀ nɛ lɛ Ananyas a ̀ sɛnga ̀ y a Sezare , n ̀ ɗaŋ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛdɛŋ , ri ̀ loya ̀ a ̀ dɛŋ ɗii lɛ Tɛrityul . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ sɔmɛ ̀ nga ̀ Pol ri ̀ gɔmi ̀ na ̀ .
Nni ɓɛ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ y Pol , Tɛrityul a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ kpaa ɗi kiɓan n ̀ ŋwe ̀ e lɛ :
Gɔmi ̀ na ̀ a ̀ gwey , coo syeesyee wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ a ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ si ̀ , ri ̀ nyɔɔnyɔn a ̀ ri ̀ wo ̀ ŋzi ̀ ɗi ɓiɓan anɛ u ̀ mɛ wo ̀ ŋzi ̀ ɓi ki ̀ rɔɔ ki kilɔ ̀ ŋ kis , ɓi mɛ ki ̀ lɛ , ti ɓa ri ̀ fyo ̀ oog , ti ̀ ki nya ̀ anyaa ̀ rɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ syeesyee ɓɛ ɓiɓan ɓɛn ̀ ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , ja ̀ ŋbimiɗ , ti ̀ ki fafa ti wɔ ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n .
Ɓi ɗi lɛ tyɛ ̀ ki ɓiisɛn wɔ ki ̀ yeesii , m ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzii wɔ ̀ lɛ , u ram ̀ mɛ ̀ ree ̀ , u wog ki ̀ ɓan ki nki ̀ ki lɛ n ̀ ɗesi wɔ ̀ ki ̀ den lɛ cɔs .
Ti ̀ i n ̀ ghɛɛ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ fi ̀ ɓa ̀ g , a ɓiighɓigti ̀ ki ̀ yoo ̀ yo ̀ o ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓi Zi bimiɗ . Nnyɛɛ ki ri ̀ ti ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi righerɛ ̀ n ɗi nyɔn ɗi ɓumɓɛ a Nazarɛt .
A ̀ a mɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ gi lɛ , a yogsi ri ̀ ɓa ɗi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll yi ̀ s , ɗi i ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ce ̀ li ̀ nni ti ̀ i mɓani nyi , ti ̀ fe ̀ g lɛ ti yɔmzi nyi ɓi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓis .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ gwey a ̀ nɛ lɛ Lizyas , a ̀ a n-yu ̀ u yi ̀ ri ̀ coo kigu ̀ g , a ̀ ɓa ̀ tɛ ̀ n nyi ɓi ɓya ̀ g ɓis ,
a ̀ ki kpaa lɛ , ɓumɓɛ anɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kiɓan , ɓɛn ɓɛɛ yuiy fɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɔɔ ; yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ ri ̀ nyi ɓii ̀ tɔɔ ̀ gh mɛ ̀ tɔɔ ́ ghtɔɔgh , nnɛ wɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ u ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ saaɗ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ti ̀ sɔmɛɛ nyi ɓi mii ̀ .
Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɛm ̀ dɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ kpaa ɗi Tɛrityul ɗin ̀ , ɓɛ kpaa lɛ fɔlɔɔ nnɛ kin ̀ ki nɗi ̀ .
Nni gɔmi ̀ na ̀ a ̀ reɓsi ̀ gha ̀ Pol ri ̀ ca ̀ g lɛ , a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a too ̀ ghrɛn , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ min lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yii lɛ ki mɛ finɛn ba ̀ li ̀ yi be ̀ g , yɛ ̀ ɛ waa ̀ yɔ ̀ myɔ ̀ m ɓi ̀ ɓan fɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kis , fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tyweeyi ɓi nɗem ɓi ki ̀ ɓan kɛm ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ti ɓii ̀ kpaasɛɛ lɛ .
U ̀ ri ̀ lɛ u ̀ tɔg ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ n ̀ ko ̀ o ki mɛ cee mɛru ntɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ mɛɓɛɛ ̀ , yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ mɓɔɔgh a Yorisalɛm lɛ mɓɔgsi Bɛ ̀ ll .
Fɔɔnnɛ nsoo ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , nsoo ̀ ɓi naa yi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n , nsoo ̀ ɓi ba ̀ n , ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ tanɛɛ ɓi mɛ di n ̀ nyoonyolɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ɓum , nsoo ̀ ;
ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ , ɓɛ yin ɗi ki ̀ ɓan kidɛŋ ki ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ ɓaa ̀ zi ̀ sɔmi ̀ na ̀ wa ̀ a ̀ mii ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ rɛrɛlii lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan ki mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yii ki ri lɛ , nki ̀ ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓis kisay ɓi bee inɛ ɓɔɔ ̀ rereŋi lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi nyɔ ̀ n . N ̀ gherɛɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓi ri ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓis , ri ̀ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ kanga ̀ ;
n ̀ ɗi ri ̀ dya ̀ ɓɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , nsoo ̀ ɓɔ girig , lɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri lɛ saaɗ , nsoo ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛ yin lɛ saaɗ , ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛɛ ŋwosi righe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓilo ̀ ŋ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin kɛɛ ̀ ki mɛ ̀ girig nte ̀ etee ̀ si ̀ nyoo ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m lɛ , n ̀ ɗem wɛ ̀ m wɛɛ ɓa kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ bɛ ̀ lɛn ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ ɓi mis mɛ ɓum .
Di ki mɛ finɛn be ̀ g lɛɛ ̀ gwey yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ , nnɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ n-yu ̀ u ri ̀ ɓyom lɛ nkaɓsag ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g ɓɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kɛm ̀ , n ̀ ki fu ̀ nɛn ɓituwe ɓi ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll .
Nni fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ntanɛɛ mɛ ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll di n ̀ ti ɓii ̀ le ̀ gsii zo ̀ ghɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ m , nsoo ̀ ci ̀ i ̀ ba ki ɓum , nsoo ̀ ki ̀ yoo ̀ yo ̀ o ̀ , com ɗi ̀ com ki n-yi ̀ n .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ a Azii ɓɔ yɛɛ nghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ mɛ ̀ ki ̀ yu ̀ u ki sɔmɛɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɔɔ , di ɓɛ nki ri ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ ɓa ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓɛɛ cɔɓɛn ɓɛ raɗ ɗi ̀ mɛ ̀ .
I ki yin fɔlɔɔ , ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ kali min kiɓan kiɓeɓtɛn ki ɓɛ nghɛɛ lɛ n ̀ ki ̀ i ŋwos anɛ ɓɛ n-yɔ ̀ mzii mɛ ̀ ɓi Sa ̀ ne ̀ di ̀ rɛŋ .
I ki cee ɓi lɛ , jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ nkalii ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wa ̀ a ̀ lɛ : M ̀ mɛ rɛli ɓɛyɔ ̀ m gɛɛ ̀ nɛ ɓi mis min lɛ , ki ̀ ɓan ki righe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓiloŋ wa ?
Fɔɔnnɛ Felis a ̀ nɛ a ̀ kona ̀ ka ̀ ki ̀ yii ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓi dɔgtɛ ̀ n i ̀ nɛn , a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ ɓan rijɛ ̀ m a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : N ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ yɔ ̀ mi kiɓan kin di n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ gwey a ̀ nɛ lɛ Lizyas a ̀ mɛ kpaŋ fɛ .
Nni a ̀ reɓsi ̀ gha ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ su ̀ ja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ sa ̀ g lɛ , a pɛɛ ̀ zi Pol ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓiisɛn nyi ki ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋɓeŋi , ɓɛ kɛɛ ̀ ki re ̀ g ɓum ɓii lɛ ɓɛɛ ghɛɛ ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɓsi ̀ nyi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɔɔ mɛru ɓɛ ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ , Felis a ̀ yu ̀ y ɓɛɛ ̀ giy anɛ lɛ Durusil , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ gɔ ̀ n i ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ regii ̀ nyi Pol . Nni Pol a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi ki ̀ ɓan ki ki seesee n ̀ tyweeyi wu ɓi Kiris Yeesus .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓi ɓagha ̀ di ɓyaa kɛ ̀ n ki ko ̀ mi saaɗ a ̀ nɛ a kɔ ̀ ngi Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓan ɗi n ̀ ɗem ɗi lɛ mum kɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ ɓiɓan ɓi ɓeɓtɛn , ri ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ren ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓan , nni Felis a ̀ risi ̀ gha ̀ , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Ɓigomi ̀ nɛ u ̀ ri ̀ lɛ , u ̀ ka sugti ̀ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ regii ti di n ̀ ghɛɛ ki ̀ rɔŋiɗ .
A ̀ mi ̀ i ̀ mi ̀ nga ̀ ka ̀ ti ̀ tyɛɛ ̀ lɛ Pol a ̀ ri ̀ nyi ɓii ̀ faa ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni . Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ ŋwos ri ̀ ŋwos a ̀ reŋi ̀ nyi lɛ ɓɛɛ toki ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ be ̀ g yi ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ yiɓɛɛ ̀ , nni ɓɛ romga ̀ y gɔmi ̀ na ̀ a ̀ dɛŋ ɗii lɛ Pɔrisyus-Fɛstus ɓi-kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu Felis . Yɛ ̀ ɛ Felis a ̀ kɔ ̀ nkɔ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ a puɓsi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n n ̀ ɗem , nni a ̀ ca ̀ ɗka ̀ Pol ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru mɛraa a ̀ nɛ gɔmi ̀ na ̀ a ̀ nɛ lɛ Fɛstus a ̀ kpaga ̀ ɓi ki ̀ den ki zi ki a ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ nga ̀ , a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Sezare , a ̀ ɓɔg a Yorisalɛm .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ri ̀ ɓi ̀ te ̀ ete ̀ d ɓi ɓum ɓi a Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ yugha ̀ nyi ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ sɔmɛn Pol .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ɓɔŋza ̀ ka ̀ Fɛstus lɛ , i a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ gherɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓɛɛ yuiy ri ̀ Pol a Yorisalɛm , lɛ ɓɔɔ ɓagha ̀ di ɓɛ mɛ tɔ ̀ kɛn lɛ , ɓɛ ri nyi ɓii ̀ ɓoŋi ̀ ɓi bee lɛ ɓɛɛ wey .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Fɛstus a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ Pol a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ lɔlɔghɛn a Sezare , ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ , nyimiɗ a ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ sugtii wɔɔ lɛ fyɛ ̀ ɗ .
Nni a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɓka ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ lɛ : I ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓi mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ri ri ̀ bee , ɓɛɛ nɔɔ ̀ tii ̀ mɛ ̀ , di ti sɛn ̀ a Sezare n ̀ ɗaŋ , lɛ i ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kiɓeɓtɛn ki a ̀ a nki ̀ i , ɓɛɛ sɔmɛn nyi .
Fɛstus a ̀ ghagsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi mɛru mɛ ceeyɛn taa ̀ raa nsoo ̀ lɛ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ a lɔ ̀ ŋkaa , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ sugti ̀ gha ̀ a Sezare . Ɓi ɗuri tana nnɛ a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ki ̀ kpana ̀ ki ɓɛyɔ ̀ m , a ̀ rom lɛ ɓɛɛ teɗ yi ̀ Pol .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pol a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ y , Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ y a Yorisalɛm , ɓɛ kɔmzɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi , ɓɛ kpaa ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓeɓtɛn lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ rara ̀ ɗ ɗi nyi , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ n ri ̀ ŋwɔm kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ com ki ki resii lɛ ɓi ri saaɗ .
Pol a ̀ yɔ ̀ myɔ ̀ mga ̀ lɛ : N ̀ sɛ ̀ rii ɓi kiɓan kidɛŋ ki rarɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n nsoo ̀ lɛ ri ̀ naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , nsoo ̀ ri ̀ Kaaza .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Fɛstus a ̀ kɔ ̀ nkɔ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ a puɓsi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n mɛ ̀ rem nni a ̀ tɔka ̀ Pol lɛ : U ̀ ri ̀ lɛ , u ̀ gherɛ ̀ n lɛ , u ̀ kɛn ̀ a Yorisalɛm ɓɛɛ yɔm ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kɔɔ wɔɔ di mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔriyɛn ?
Nni Pol a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ lɛ : N ̀ ɗɛrɛlii ɓi ɗi lɛ , nkpaŋ ɓi ki ̀ kpana ̀ ki ɓɛyɔ ̀ m ki Kaaza , wɔɔnnɛ ɓɛɛ ren ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kɛm ̀ ; n ̀ ki ̀ i ɓi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n nsoo ̀ maa ki ̀ ɓan adɛŋ a ̀ m ̀ ɓeɓtɛn lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ wɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ u ̀ yii .
Nko ̀ o ki ri ̀ lɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ zɛ ̀ ɗ , nsoo ̀ lɛ i mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ki ̀ i ki ̀ ɓan ki lɛ ɓɛɛ wey mɛ ̀ mii ̀ , ma ̀ a ɓe ̀ n ɓi riwu ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog i ki ghɛnɛɛ lɛ saaɗ a ̀ yin ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓɛ sɔmɛɛ mɛ ̀ mii ̀ nsoo ̀ lɛsa ̀ g , mum a ̀ yin ri i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ , a ̀ teɗ mɛ ̀ a ̀ fa ri ̀ ɓɔ ; n ̀ ghagsii ki ̀ ɓan kɛm ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Kaaza .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Fɛstus a ̀ tɔka ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ nɗeɓki ̀ nyi , nni a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ min Pol lɛ : Yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ ghagsii ki ̀ ɓan kɔɔ yɛ ̀ ɛ Kaaza , u ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkii .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɔɔ mɛru ɓɛ ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ , nni ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi lɛ Agiripa ɓɛɛ Berenis , ɓɛ yugha ̀ y a Sezare lɛ ɓɛɛ togsi Fɛstus .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ ghagsii ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru wɔɔ , fɔɔnnɛ Fɛstus a ̀ re ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ki ̀ ɓan ki Pol a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Felis , a ̀ a nca ̀ ri ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ fɛ ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ i ̀ a Yorisalɛm , ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ n-yu ̀ u nyi ki ̀ sɔmɛɛ , ɓɛ ki kpaa mɛ lɛ , mɛ ̀ ɛ nfa a ̀ nɛ ̀ n ri ̀ na ̀ n .
Nni mɛ ̀ ɛ mɓa ̀ agh ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓɛ ̀ ro ̀ mɛŋ ɓɛ yin ɗi ki ̀ syɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ki lɛ , i ɓɛ sɔmɛɛ mum ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓɛɛ wes ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n , di a ̀ ka rɛɛsɛn ɓi ri ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ sɔmɛɛ nyi , ɓɛ ca ̀ ɗ nyi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki lɛ a kpaa ̀ sɛn ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓɛ kpaakpaa ɓɛ rara ̀ ɗ ɗi ̀ nyi .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ n-yu ̀ u yi ̀ fɛ , mɛ ̀ mɓoŋi ɓi lɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kɛɛ ghaa ̀ gh , mɛ ̀ ɛ nkɔ ̀ rii ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ m ɓi duri tana , n ̀ ki rom lɛ ɓɛɛ teɗ yi ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nce ̀ m .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ nɗɛlii ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ m , ɓum ɓɛ kiɓan ɓɛ n ̀ kpaa ɓi nsoo ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓeɓtɛn ɓi mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ fe ̀ feegh lɛ , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ lɛ a ̀ ki ̀ .
Paa ̀ zi ̀ wa ̀ a ̀ a ̀ a nɗi ̀ ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki ki seesee ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗyaa , a ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓi ̀ i ̀ sɛ ̀ n ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ lɛ Yeesus , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ wugha ̀ , wɔ ̀ lɛ Pol nyii kala ̀ g lɛ , a ̀ nɛn a ̀ ri ̀ cem .
Ɓi ɓɛg wɛ ̀ m , com ki mɛ ̀ ɛ nɗi lɛ n ̀ kpaa ɓi ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki n ̀ -yeesii mɛ ̀ . Fɔɔnnɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ m ̀ mɛɛ ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ , i a ̀ kɔ ̀ ni a kɛn ̀ a Yorisalɛm , ɓɛɛ yɔm ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kii wɔɔ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Pol a ̀ a ntɔɔgh lɛ ki ̀ ɓan kii kɛɛ ghaa ̀ gh yɛ ̀ ɛ Kaaza . Fɔɔnnɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ nkalii lɛ , ɓɛɛ ka ɓe ̀ ŋ nyi ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y a ̀ kpaŋ ŋwos anɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi ɓii ̀ romi ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Kaaza .
Nni Agiripa a ̀ kpaagha ̀ Fɛstus lɛ : Mɛ ̀ ɛ nkɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ nwog n ̀ kpaa ̀ wu ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n . Fɛstus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ , u ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ woo ̀ gh ri ̀ duri .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ duri i tanga ̀ Agiripa ɓɛɛ ̀ Berenis ɓɛ yugha ̀ y ri coo ri ̀ gwey ɓɛ ɗiŋi ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ m , ɓɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛgwey , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ lem ɓɛ ɓum ɓɛ ɓi ba ̀ n ɓɛ nɔɔ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ y ɓɔ . Fɔɔnnɛ Fɛstus a ̀ romga ̀ min lɛ ɓɛɛ yuis ̀ ri ̀ Pol .
Nni Fɛstus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Ri ̀ fo ̀ m Agiripa ri ̀ mi ̀ nii ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ fɛ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si , n ̀ waa ̀ nɛ ɓi seesee anɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ yugha ̀ mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ lɛ ri ̀ a Yorisalɛm ri ̀ fɛfɛ bisu wii , ɓɛ tɔtɔ ̀ g mɛ ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ , ɓɛɛ wey nyi .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ , mɛ ̀ ɛ nghɛɛ ɓi kiɓan kiɓeɓtɛn ki a ̀ ki ̀ i ki ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ wey nyi mii ̀ , nni yɛ ̀ ɛ nyimiɗ yɛɛ ntɔɔgh lɛ ki ̀ ɓan kii kɛɛ ghaa ̀ gh yɛ ̀ ɛ Kaaza , nni mɛ ̀ ɛ nkpaa lɛ , n ̀ ɗi nyi ɓii ̀ romi ̀ wɔɔ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ n ̀ ka yin ɗi bimiɗ a ̀ ki ̀ ɓan anɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ n ̀ ka ̀ n Kaaza ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki n ̀ waa ̀ nɛ , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ n ̀ ɗɛsii nyi fɛ ɓi mis min , a ɓiisɛ ̀ n ɓi mis mɔɔ , wɔ ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m Agiripa lɛ i tya ̀ a mɔ ̀ ɔmɔmgi ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kii , fɔɔnnɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yi cɛ kɛɛ ̀ ki n ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ n ̀ ka ̀ n Kaaza ;
lɛ ki ri ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ki ̀ di ̀ mi ̀ dimi ki kiɓan , di n ̀ ɗomi ki ̀ mbu ̀ ŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Kaaza kɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗe ̀ si ɓiɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓiɓan ɓi ki nsɛ ̀ raagh lɛ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n .
Nni Agiripa a ̀ kpaagha ̀ Pol lɛ : Ti ̀ faa wɔ ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ , u kpaa ̀ sɛn . Fɔɔnnɛ Pol a ̀ na ̀ mga ̀ ca ̀ g , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n mɛ ̀ kpaa ̀ lɛ :
Ri ̀ fo ̀ m Agiripa , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ lɛ nɗɛli gɛɛ ̀ nɛ ɓi mis mɔɔ , lɛ n-yɔm ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ti ɓɛ sɔɔ ̀ sɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n mɛ ̀ mii ̀
ɓisuulɛ , u ̀ yii ɓi ̀ syɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m lɛ syeesyee , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ti ɓi syoga ̀ g yi ̀ nyoey ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wa ̀ a ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ m ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzaagh wɔ ̀ lɛ , u maa ̀ si n ̀ ɗem , u woo ̀ g ki ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ kɛm ̀ .
Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ yii cɛɓ kɛ ̀ m , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n di n ̀ kaka maa ŋwɔɓti , yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ghɛghɛɓi a Yorisalɛm ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kɛm ̀ .
Ɓɛ yii mɛ ̀ fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ , ɓaa ki ri ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ ɓa ɓɛ ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛm di ɓɛ kɔni ̀ , lɛ n ̀ ghɛghɛ ̀ ɓka ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ci ̀ ɓtaagh ri ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋ ɗi ɓisyɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓi ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗis .
I n ̀ ki rɛrɛlii gɛɛ ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ m , ki ri ɓisuu ntyweeyi wu ɓi n ̀ ka ̀ g wu Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓis .
Nka ̀ g win ̀ wɛɛ ̀ wu mɛ ̀ kuu mis mɛce ̀ m ntɛ ̀ ɗ ɗi ̀ mɛɓɛɛ ̀ rɛn mɛ mɛɛ ̀ ɓɔɔɓɔgsi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ ri ̀ i ̀ ru ri ̀ ŋwos kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ fɔɛy , mɛ tyweetywe ̀ e ̀ yi ̀ lɛ wu ri ɓii ̀ roni ri ̀ fo ̀ m , ɓisuu ntyweeyi win ̀ innɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛɛ ̀ sɔmag mɛ .
Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ mi ̀ nii ̀ teki nyoey lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ ghe ̀ mzi ̀ ɓi ̀ loŋ ?
Ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ n ̀ fe ̀ fe ̀ ka ̀ lɛ , ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ nɗuu ̀ ri ̀ ɗii ɗi Yeesus a ̀ nɛ a Nazarɛt bee yice ̀ m .
Ki ̀ say kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki n ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ a Yorisalɛm lɛ mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ m ̀ pi ̀ ka ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ɓɛ fagha ̀ mɛ ̀ . Mɛ ̀ ɛ nki ti m ̀ ɓɛmda ̀ g fe ̀ g wa ̀ a ̀ di ki kpaŋi lɛ ɓɛɛ wey ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
Mɛ ̀ ɛ nti m ̀ pɔnɔsa ̀ g ɓɔ ɓi naa yi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n yi ̀ ce ̀ m , n ̀ ka ̀ ŋkaŋ ɓɔ lɛ , ɓɛɛ ca ̀ ɗ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗyaa ; bim yɛm ̀ i ̀ nɛ ri ̀ ɓɔ i ̀ te ̀ ghɛ ̀ nga ̀ le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ , mɛ ̀ ɛ nti n ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ g ɓɔ ki ɓangii nsoo ̀ ɓi ba ̀ n yi tira ̀ ɓ .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ŋwos adɛŋ a Damas , di ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ɓɛɛ romi mɛ ̀ , ɓɛ fa mɛ ̀ kaa ̀ ta ̀ lɛ , ɓɔɔ faa mɛ ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ nkɛn ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kɛ ̀ nkɛ ̀ nga ̀ di toroɓ a ̀ tii ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m , fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ di coo kitɛɛtɛn ki kii yi ̀ aɗyoo lɛ ŋwa ̀ a ̀ ɗ , ki yuis ̀ , ki ceŋzɛ ̀ n lɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ , ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ti ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ si ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ti ̀ kpi ̀ la ̀ ka ̀ ɓi zi , n ̀ wog min di jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ dɛŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ kakali mɛ ɓi ri ̀ e ̀ bi ̀ reegh lɛ : Sol wɔ ̀ sol wɔ ̀ , u ̀ yeeyee ̀ si ̀ mɛ ̀ lɛ cɛ ? Ki ri ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ n ̀ tɔɓ lɛ u kɛnkɛn asu , u ̀ yaa ̀ ghya ̀ a ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ Sani ̀ nya a ̀ nɛ a ̀ risii ɓi nkpas wu m ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ wi ̀ i ̀ .
Nni n ̀ tɔka ̀ nyi lɛ : Kan , wɔ ̀ yɛɛ ri ghɛn ? Kan a ̀ ɓa ̀ g mɛ ̀ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ri Yeesus a ̀ nɛ u yeeyee ̀ si ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyoo , u rɛli mɛ ̀ rɛy lɛ ki ̀ ɓan ki n ̀ ɗe ̀ sɛɛ wɔ ̀ mii ̀ ki ri lɛ , nkɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ u ɓa n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say wɛm ̀ , u ̀ ki ɓa wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ wɛ ̀ m lɛ u kakali ɓum yɛ ̀ ɛ wa ̀ a ghɛɛ mɛ ̀ gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , u ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ki kakalii ti ɓɔ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi n ̀ ɗi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ re ̀ sii ti .
N ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ ka ̀ mɛɛ ri wɔ ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓizɛy ɓi n ̀ ɗomi wɔ ̀ wɔɔ , lɛ u ŋwa ̀ ɗ ɓyɔ mis ,
di ɓyɛɛ pɛsɛn yi ̀ ɓi biri ̀ m , ɓyɛɛ yu ɓi ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn , ɓi leg yi ̀ ɓi ri ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɗi Sata ̀ n , ɓi yuiy yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ , i ɓɛ mɛ gherɛn mɛ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ cenɛ ̀ n ɓɔ ɓi ̀ be ɓyaa , a ̀ ki fa ɓɔ i ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓi n ̀ ɗaŋ wu ɓum ɓii .
Ri ̀ fo ̀ m Agiripa , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ n ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ lɔg ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki ki resɛ ̀ nga ̀ y mɛ ̀ kin ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ n ̀ ka loka ̀ ki ̀ kalii ɓumɓɛ a Damas ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll , n ̀ kali ̀ girig ɓumɓɛ a Yorisalɛm ri ̀ ɓɛ ɓi zi i ̀ Zyude bimiɗ , a ̀ kpagi ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓizɛy mii ̀ ; n ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ , ɓɛɛ lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛn mɛ ̀ rem , ɓɛɛ gherɛn Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛ ki ki ̀ ɓiɓan ɓi ɓyɛɛ resi lɛ , cɛɓ kaa ki ti ki ̀ lɔ ̀ gtɛn .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ mɓani mɛ ̀ mii ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓɛ kɔn ̀ lɛ di ɓaa woli mɛ ̀ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll a ɓe ̀ ŋɓeŋ mɛ , ɗyɛɛ kii ̀ lɛ , m ̀ ɓaɓa ɓi cɛɓ a ̀ kpaŋ gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ a ̀ nɛ a kakali lɛ , ri ̀ ɓɔɓti , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn , ɓiɓan ɓii , kɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ki sagti kiɓan kidɛŋ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ri ̀ Moyis ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ lɛ , ɓi ri ɓii ̀ ki ̀ lɛɛ ,
ɓyɛɛ ri lɛ : Kiris a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ wii ̀ , a ̀ ki ɓa ŋwaa ̀ n ̀ tonto a ̀ nɛ a ghemɓɛn yi ̀ a ɓi ̀ loŋ , a ̀ lo ̀ m ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kis ri ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓimbog lɛ ɓyɛɛ yi lɛ ɓi ri ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ri ̀ cɛɓ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pol a ̀ kpaa ̀ kpa ̀ a ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ fɔlɔɔ , nni Fɛstus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Pol , u ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ye ̀ g , coo riyi ɗyɔɔ ɗi ɓiɓan ɗi ghaasii wɔ ̀ ki ̀ ye ̀ g .
Pol a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ nyi lɛ : Coo gi ̀ n i mum Fɛstus , n ̀ -yin kiye ̀ g , ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi nkpaakpa ̀ a ̀ ɓi ri ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi saaɗ , ɓi ki wooghrɛn ,
Ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi yii ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi fɔɔnnɛ nkakali nyi ɓyɔ lɛ fwa ̀ afwa ̀ a ̀ y lɛ n ̀ konaagh ki ̀ yii ̀ lɛ a ̀ co ̀ mɛɛ ɓi kiɓan mii ̀ nsoo ̀ ki ̀ fog , ɓyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓa ɓiɓan ɓi ɓi kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ a ri ̀ nyam .
Ri ̀ fo ̀ m Agiripa , u ̀ gherɛɛ nya ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ ? Mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yii lɛ , u ̀ ghɛrɛɛ ɓyɔ ̀ .
Nni Agiripa a ̀ kpaagha ̀ Pol lɛ : Ki rɔɓi lɛsa ̀ g lɛ , u ki lɛ m ̀ ɓa ki ̀ ristɛ ̀ n .
Pol a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : Nsoo ̀ ki kilɛɛ ɓi fɔlɔɔ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗyɛm ̀ ɗi ri lɛ , nsoo ̀ gɛ fin , Bɛ ̀ ll a gherɛn lɛ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ , ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ wowog ɓito ̀ ki ̀ ɓyɛm ̀ gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , ɓi ɓa ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog kɛ ̀ ɓi ɓa ri ɓɛn yi mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ yi ri ̀ yɔ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ri ̀ fo ̀ m , ri ̀ gɔmi ̀ na ̀ , ri ̀ Berenis , ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ , ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ aɗyoo ,
ɓɛ kɛn ̀ dwi ̀ ɗ ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ wɔɔ ɓɔ ri ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki ̀ i ɓi kiɓan ki ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ wey nyi mii ̀ , nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓɛ foŋ nyi ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y .
Nni Agiripa a ̀ kpaagha ̀ Fɛstus lɛ , i kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ tɔka ̀ lɛ ki ̀ ɓan kii kɛɛ kɛn ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Kaaza , di ɓɛ cari nyi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ renga ̀ lɛ ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ a Italii ɓi fi ̀ tima ̀ , nni ɓɛ teka ̀ lɛ ri ̀ Pol , ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ , ɓɛ fa ɓɔ ri ̀ n ̀ kɔmɛ ̀ n-ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ sa ̀ g a ̀ nɛ ɓi ki ̀ tuu ki ɓɛsuja ̀ a ̀ ki ɓɛ nɗegi ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ Kaaza a ̀ nɛ a Italii ɗii lɛ : Zyulyus .
Nni ti ̀ ɓɔka ̀ fi ̀ tima ̀ fi a Adiramit , lɛ fyɔ yɛɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ so ̀ rii be ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y i ̀ nɛ a Azii , fɔɔnnɛ ti ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , ti ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ ɗi Aristarikɛ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a Tesalonika , ɓi ki ̀ den ki zi ki a Masedwan .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ rɛli ̀ gha ̀ a Sidɔŋ ɓi duri tana fɔɔnnɛ Zyulyus a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓeŋɓe ̀ ŋga ̀ Pol ri ̀ syeesyee a ̀ n ̀ ɗem , a ̀ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ Pol a kɛn ̀ ki ghɛɛ ̀ mɛ ̀ ghan mii , mɛɛ fa nyi ɓyom ɓi ɓi kaa ̀ ka ̀ a ̀ rɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ foo , nni ti ̀ narigha ̀ be ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y i ̀ nɛ a Siipirɛ , ɓisuulɛ , bɛ ̀ ɓ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ y ɓi ̀ si asu , i ̀ fɛɛ ̀ fɛ ̀ ɓsi ̀ i ̀ ɓi ̀ si ɓi nyo ̀ o ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ sya ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ ja ̀ ŋ yi lɛ Silisii , ri ̀ Paŋfilii , nni ti ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ rɛlii a Mira a ̀ nɛ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ lɛ Lisii .
Wɔɔnnɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n-ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ fi ̀ tima ̀ fidɛŋ fi a Alɛgsaŋdirii , fi fi kɛnkɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Italii , a ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ ɓi ̀ si mii ̀ .
Fi ̀ tima ̀ fi kɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ gha ̀ lɛ tɛ ̀ tɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ ti ̀ ghagsi ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ ru lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓi bee , ti ̀ ki kɛ ̀ n ki kpaŋi ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ Kiniidɛ di tya ̀ a ghɛn ntɔɓ . Yɛ ̀ ɛ bɛ ̀ ɓ i ̀ fagha ̀ ɓi ɓisi bee inɛ lɛ ti kɛnkɛn bee ̀ bɛ ̀ y ɓi san a ̀ nɛ ̀ n , fɔɔnnɛ ti ̀ so ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ riŋ ki ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y ki lɛ Kirɛɗɛ , ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a Salmone .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ kɛ ̀ nkɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɔŋ asu ri ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ nni ti ̀ kpaga ̀ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ idɛŋ ɗii lɛ : Bopɔɔr , di tya ̀ a ghɛn ntɔɓ lɛɛ ̀ gwey ; ja ̀ ŋ ince ̀ m i ̀ ɓagha ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛ lɛ Lasee .
Ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru i ̀ ɓagha ̀ di i ̀ mɛ ghaa ̀ gh , fɔɔnnɛ ki ɓagha ̀ di ki ti koŋnyo ̀ o ̀ lɛ mum a kɛɛ ̀ kɛɛ ti ̀ ɓi fi ̀ tima ̀ , ɓisuulɛ ŋ ̀ wos a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ nce ̀ la ̀ g ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ mɛ ghaa ̀ gh .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki Pol a ̀ rɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ rɔ ̀ gsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ a ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ ghɛɛ lɛ , ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɗi ɗyaa syɔn ɓi kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ; ɓisuulɛ , fi ̀ tima ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ tɛ ̀ g mɛ mɛ ri mii ̀ , ɓi ɓii ̀ ɗya ̀ ŋi ̀ , nsoo ̀ ɓi ̀ sii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ , ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓi koŋnyo ̀ o ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n-ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ ɓiisɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ tyweeyii rikpaa ɗi ɓumɓɛ lɛ , ri ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n-fi ̀ tima ̀ , ri ̀ m ̀ pusi ̀ -fi ̀ tima ̀ , a ̀ cee ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Pol a ̀ kpaagha ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ̀ n i ̀ ɓiisɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ki rɔɔtɛɛ lɛ ŋwaa ghagsi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ bu ̀ ma ̀ wɔɔ , nni ki ̀ gwey ki ɓum ki ɓi ɓɔ , ki gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ ruɓtɛn ti ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , lɛ i bee i ɓaa , ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ a Fenis , ɓi ja ̀ ŋ idɛŋ i ̀ nɛ a Kirɛɗɛ , i ̀ nɛ ti ̀ tima ̀ tyɛɛ ̀ rɛlag wɔɔ , i ̀ nɛ i ̀ faa mis ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ ŋwos a kɛ ̀ ngi ki nɔ ̀ ŋii , lɛ ɓɛ kɔnkɔ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ bɛɛ ghagsi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ bu ̀ ma ̀ wɔɔ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ maa fɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ fɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ a ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ y fɛlɛ duŋzi , ɓɛ feki ̀ nya lɛ , ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ kpaŋzɛɛ fe ̀ g wa ̀ a ̀ anɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ a Fenis . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ lɔmzi ̀ gha ̀ y min fitima ̀ , ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ so ̀ so ̀ ri ̀ ɗi kiri ̀ ŋ ki riɓa ̀ y ki lɛ Kirɛɗɛ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ maa ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ mɛɛ ̀ ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ sigmɛ ̀ n di coo bɛ ̀ ɓ i ̀ nɛ ɓɛɛ regi lɛ Rakilon ki mɛ pɛ ̀ sɛn yi n ̀ ko ̀ kwey ɓi ki ̀ ri ̀ ŋ ki riɓa ̀ y .
Bɛ ̀ ɓ i ̀ nɛn i ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ tyɔg ɗi fitima ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ bee inɛ lɛ fyɛɛ nɔɔnɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ ti ̀ be ̀ n i ̀ ki ̀ ri ̀ ŋ ki ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y , fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ sii ca ̀ rɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ fi ̀ tima ̀ fyɛɛ ɓɛnɓɛn ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si m ̀ ɓɛ ̀ mɓɛnɛn ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y .
Fɔɔnnɛ ti ̀ fyeegha ̀ ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ maa ki ̀ ri ̀ ŋ ; adɛŋ ɗii lɛ Koda , ti ̀ ra ̀ m ti ̀ ru ̀ nɛ ̀ n ki ̀ kɔm ki sa ̀ g ri ̀ n ̀ tɔɓ lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ ru ̀ nɛ ̀ nga ̀ kɔ fɔlɔɔ , nni ti ̀ kaagha ̀ bee inɛ lɛ , ti sugi mɛ ̀ ɗig ɓi fi ̀ tima ̀ , lɛ ti ̀ risi ̀ gha ̀ lɛ tyɛ ̀ ki kɛ ̀ n ki ɗiŋii ɓi sɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ anɛ ɓi be ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ nɛ a Liɓii ; nni ɓɛ fumi ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ki fitima ̀ ; fi ̀ tima ̀ fi rɔɓ ki ɓɛ ̀ nɓɛni fɔlɔɔ fyɔmiɗ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ bɛ ̀ ɓ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ di i ̀ mɛ yeesi ɓisi lɛɛ ̀ gwey , nni ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ma ̀ g ɗi ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ mɛ ̀ tɛ ̀ g ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y ɓi duri tana .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru mɛɓɛɛ ̀ rɛn , ɓɔmiɗ ɓɛ maki ̀ ti ̀ ɓyom ɓidɛŋ ɓi ɓɛ nki ̀ la ̀ g ɓi ̀ say mii ̀ ɓi fi ̀ tima ̀ .
Ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru i ̀ ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ , tyɛ ̀ ki ghɛn nsoo ̀ ki ̀ saa ki ŋwos , nsoo ̀ tyɔɛy , bɛ ̀ ɓ i ̀ ki kɛ ̀ nkɛn lɔŋ asu ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , ɓi le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ , ti ̀ ɓati ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ri n ̀ tyweeyi wulɛ , ti ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ti ̀ ghɛɓ .
Ti ̀ ɓagha ̀ di ti ̀ mɛ ghagsi mɛru lɛɛ ̀ gwey , tyɛ ̀ ki ɗi com . Fɔɔnnɛ Pol a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛn ̀ ga ̀ aɗyoo ɓi nyi ̀ innyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓum , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ i nghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ woo ̀ gh yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ nkpaa lɛ , tyɛ ̀ ki pɛ ̀ sɛn a Kirɛɗɛ , lɛ i ɓi ̀ i n ̀ woogh ri ̀ kpaa ɗi ̀ n , di ɓi ̀ yin fɛlɛ ɓi koŋnyoo yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , ɓyɛ ̀ ɓi ki ɗimzi ɓyom yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ mɛ ɗimzi ɓi .
Nni m ̀ ɓɔŋzaagh mi ̀ ni ɓigomi ̀ nɛ lɛ , ɓi sii ̀ ri mɛ ̀ rem , lɛ nsoo ̀ wa ̀ a ̀ dɛŋ , wa ̀ a wu ɓi , lɔŋ fi ̀ tima ̀ fyɔri ̀ fyɔ fyɛɛ ɓii ̀ ɗya ̀ ŋi ̀ .
Ɓi-ru wu gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ la ̀ mii mɛ ̀ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ nki ɓɔɔɓɔgsi ̀ , a ̀ a yu ̀ u mɛ ̀ jaŋ ̀ bog ,
a ̀ kpaa mɛ ̀ lɛ : Pol , kɔ ̀ ɔ risi , ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ , u kpaa ̀ sɛn ɓi mis mɛ Kaaza , wɔ ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ka ̀ mɛɛ ri ɓyɛɓ ɓi ɓumɓɛ ɓi kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛɛ ri ɓɔ ɓi fi ̀ tima ̀ ɓisu wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Mi ̀ ni ɓum ! Fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ si ̀ i ̀ rii mɛre ̀ m , ɓisuulɛ n ̀ tyweeyii Bɛ ̀ ll , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki ɓii ̀ ki ̀ lɛɛ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ a kpaa mɛ ̀ .
Ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ghaatɛɛ ɓi ki ̀ ri ̀ ŋ ki ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y kidɛŋ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ -ru a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ tii ̀ , ɓi ri ̀ ra ̀ ɗ mɛru n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ɗi ̀ mɛnin a ̀ nɛ bɛ ̀ ɓ i ̀ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ ri ̀ yee ̀ ye ̀ e ̀ si ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n , a ̀ nɛ lɛ Mediterane nni ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ si ̀ -fi ̀ tima ̀ ɓɛ woka ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ fi ̀ tima ̀ fi ̀ ti ɓii ̀ wuɓsɛɛ zi i ̀ zɛy .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ pika ̀ n ̀ ɗig wu wu ɓagha ̀ wu ̀ suŋɛn gɔ ̀ g mii ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y , lɛ ɓɛɛ ghɛn ̀ ri ̀ rim ɗi mɛnig , nni ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ ri ̀ rim di mɛnig ɗi ri ɓɛ ̀ mita ̀ ri ̀ tin ɗi ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ɗi ̀ taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ . Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kɛɛdi ̀ gha ̀ lɛsa ̀ g , ɓɛ ghɛn ɓɛ ̀ mita ̀ ri ̀ tin ɗi ̀ taa ̀ raa .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ risi ̀ gha ̀ lɛ fi ̀ tima ̀ fyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki kɛ ̀ n ki roŋɗɛɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ ɓan , nni ɓɛ pika ̀ bɔŋ yi yɛɛ ̀ rɛsag fitima ̀ yinin ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y , ɓɛ ɓoŋ lɛ duri yɛ ̀ ɛ tan ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ pusi ̀ -fi ̀ tima ̀ ɓɛ mɛɛ ̀ fye ̀ e ̀ rɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ , ɓɛɛ naŋ ̀ fi ̀ tima ̀ ɓɛɛ ghaagh , di ɓɛ mɛ pi ̀ g maa ki ̀ kɔm a ̀ sa ̀ g a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ nyi ɓi mɛ ̀ nig ri ̀ n ̀ kpaa ̀ lɛ : Ɓɔɔ kɛɛ ki ̀ suŋi ̀ bɔŋ yi yɛɛ ̀ rɛsag fitima ̀ ɓi n ̀ to wu fitima ̀ ,
Pol a ̀ kali ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n-ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ lɛ : I ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ rɔɓi ɓi fɛ ɓi fi ̀ tima ̀ , di ɓya ̀ a ghɛɓ ɓi .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ renga ̀ ka ̀ mɛ ̀ ɗig mɛ mɛ ɓanɓa ̀ nga ̀ maa ki ̀ kɔm a ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓɛ caɗ lɛ , a ɓɛn ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ɓoŋɓo ̀ ŋga ̀ lɛ duri yɛ ̀ ɛ tan ̀ , nni Pol a ̀ ca ̀ a ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m nyoo lɛ ɓɛɛ ɗi com a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Mɛ ̀ ru n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ mɛnin yɛɛ ti lɛ gɛɛ ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ɓoŋɓoŋ risyɔn , kɛ ̀ ɓi ki ɗi nsoo ̀ maa com .
Fɔɔnnɛ m ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzaagh mi ̀ ni lɛ , ɓi ɗi ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g lɛ ɓi ri mi ̀ ni ri ̀ gɛɓsɛ ̀ n , wa ̀ a ̀ dɛŋ wa ̀ a ɗimzi ɓi nsoo ̀ fyo ̀ ŋ fi ̀ fog fi wɔ ̀ ɓi n ̀ to .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ fɔlɔɔ , nni a ̀ teka ̀ bi ̀ rɛs a ̀ fa Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n ɓi mis mɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ ɓɛg yɔ ̀ , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ɗi .
Fɔɔnnɛ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu yugha ̀ min ɓɛro ɓɛm ̀ bog ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi nyoo , ɓɛ ɗi girig .
Ɓi ̀ si ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ti ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi fi ̀ tima ̀ , ti ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ hɔnɗɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛ ɓum ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ , ri ̀ ɓum mɛ ̀ tin mɛraa ri ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ taa ̀ fog .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ɗigha ̀ ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ maka ̀ ka ̀ fa ̀ rin ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y , lɛ fi ̀ tima ̀ fyɛɛ ki yɛ ̀ ɛ fi fɛmɓɛɛ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ duri i tanga ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ pusi ̀ -fi ̀ tima ̀ ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ di ̀ gha ̀ ɓi kipisɛn ki zi ; yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ pi ̀ ka ̀ mis , ɓɛ ghɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ ɗiŋii ɓi ki ̀ ri ̀ ŋ ki riɓa ̀ y , be ̀ n i ̀ ki ̀ ri ̀ ŋ kin ̀ i ̀ see ̀ se ̀ e ̀ rɛ ̀ nga ̀ y gi ̀ rig ; nni ɓɛ kɔnga ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ ki ̀ rɛsii fitima ̀ wɔɔ di bee i ɓaa .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ fumɓa ̀ ka ̀ bɔŋ yi yɛɛ ̀ rɛsag fitima ̀ , ɓɛ ca ̀ ɗ yɔ wɔɔ ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y , ɓɛ fumɓa ̀ g girig mɛ ̀ ɗig mɛ kikɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ si ̀ -fi ̀ tima ̀ ; yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kigha ̀ fɔlɔɔ , nni ɓɛ kaga ̀ min maa ki ̀ la ̀ a ̀ a ̀ nɛ asu wu fitima ̀ , lɛ bɛ ̀ ɓ yɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ tyɔg fyɔ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ min ɓi be ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ ki roŋɗɛɛ ɓi sɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ , ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ mɛ ̀ nig . Wɔɔnnɛ fi ̀ tima ̀ fi kaɓka ̀ ; ja ̀ ŋ i ̀ nɛ asu i ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ ɓi sɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ bee inɛ i ̀ ɓati ̀ gha ̀ lɛ i ̀ nyɛ ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ n ti ̀ , jaŋ i ̀ nɛ ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ siitɛ ̀ n ki ̀ wa ̀ a ̀ rɛɛ , lɛ ɓi ̀ kus ɓi riɓa ̀ y ɓi roo ̀ ro ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ nga ̀ mii ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ wooghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ lɛ ɓɔɔ cuu ̀ si ɓi ̀ mbu ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , ɓisuulɛ kidɛŋ ki ɓagha ̀ lɛ ki wɔg ki ki la ̀ n .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n-ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ kɔ ̀ nkɔ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ a ghɛɓsi Pol , nni a ̀ re ̀ ka ̀ ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛn ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ fɔlɔɔ . Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ reɓsi ̀ gha ̀ min ɓɛroɓɛ ɓɛ yigha ̀ ki ̀ wɔg lɛ , ɓɛɛ log ki ̀ kpi ̀ i ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y ɓɛɛ wɔg ɓɛɛ kpaŋ ̀ a cɛɗ .
Ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛm ̀ bog ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ ki ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ tii di ɓɛ kɔraagh ɓi mɛ ̀ ɓam , nsoo ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ la ̀ na ̀ ɓi fitima ̀ . Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ a cɛɗ lɛ sogha ̀ sogha .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ ghɛɓka ̀ ka ̀ fɔlɔɔ lɛ sogha ̀ sogha , nni ɓɛ kali ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ si lɛ , ki ̀ ri ̀ ŋ ki riɓa ̀ y kin ̀ ki ɓagha ̀ ɗii lɛ Maltɛ .
Ɓumɓɛ ɓi ki ̀ ri ̀ ŋ kin ̀ ɓɛ ghaɓka ̀ ɓi ̀ si ri ̀ geesɛ ̀ n lɛɛ ̀ gwey ; yɛ ̀ ɛ bwey i ̀ sɛnga ̀ , ki ̀ fɛɓ ki ki ki ̀ ki lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ɓɛ ghɛŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ coo kikaŋi ̀ ki ɗuu , ɓɛ reŋi ̀ ɓi ̀ si lɛ , ti kɛn ̀ ki ̀ woo ̀ gh ɓi ̀ sii ̀ ce ̀ m .
Pol a ̀ raɓka ̀ n ̀ kun wu ti ̀ caa ̀ gh lɛ a foŋ ̀ ɓi ɗuu , nni ki ̀ go ̀ m ki faŋi ̀ gha ̀ y ɓi n ̀ kun wu tiwon wi ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ ɗuu ɗi komga ̀ y kɔ , ki fyuŋ Pol ɓi ca ̀ g .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓi ki ̀ ri ̀ ŋ ki riɓa ̀ y kin ̀ ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ di nyoo i ̀ nɛ ̀ n i ̀ fyufyuŋii Pol fɔlɔɔ ɓi ca ̀ g , nni ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ lɛ : Ki ri lɔŋ saaɗ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ woli ̀ -ɓum . Ɓisuulɛ , ri ̀ ren ɗi ɓiɓan ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ɗi ghɛɛ lɛ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓati ɓi cɛɓ , nsoo ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ghɛɓii ̀ ri ̀ wu ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ Pol a ̀ sa ̀ ɗka ̀ ca ̀ g , nyoo i ̀ kpi ̀ ɓi ɗuu , kɛ ̀ ɛ ki wog nsoo ̀ maa ri ̀ kɛŋ .
Nni ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ pɛɛ ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ mis , lɛ ɓɛɛ ghɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ Pol a ̀ ɓii ̀ mi ̀ kii , nsoo ̀ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ bii ̀ na ̀ rɛɛ a ̀ wu ; ki ̀ ɓan kifog , yɛ ̀ ɛ coo ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ghɛn kire ̀ mzɛna ki ɓeɓtɛn , ɓɛ lɔɔ ̀ gh jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ lɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ dɛŋ .
Ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi ɓi ki ̀ ri ̀ ŋ ki riɓa ̀ y kin ̀ ɗi ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ ri fyo ̀ oma ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog ; ri ̀ fo ̀ m din ̀ ɗi ɓagha ̀ ɗii lɛ Puɓilyus ; ɗi ghaɓka ̀ ɓi ̀ si a mɛɛ mii lɛ syeesyee , ti ̀ lay wɔɔ mɛru mɛraa .
Seŋi Puɓilyus a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ nɔ ̀ nɔŋiyɛn ɓi zi , lɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ba ̀ ɓ-ba ̀ ɓ ɓi nyoo , ɗu ̀ m ɗi bwaɓ ɗi ki ki ̀ ki nyi . Nni Pol a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi naa yɛ ̀ ɛ ta ̀ a ̀ ta a ̀ nɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ saghi ̀ nyi ɓya ̀ g ɓi nyoo , a ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zi ̀ nyi .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn nnɛ ɓɛ ̀ roroɓ ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓi ki ̀ ri ̀ ŋ ki riɓa ̀ y ɓɛ yugha ̀ y , a ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zi ̀ girig ɓɔ .
Ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ nyaasi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ si lɛɛ ̀ gwey ; yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ ɓagha ̀ di ti ̀ ti ɓii ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ , ɓɛ fagha ̀ ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓi kaarɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ̀ si bisuu rikɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɗis .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ ghagsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ŋwii ɓɛraa wɔɔ , nni ti ̀ ɓɔka ̀ fi ̀ tima ̀ fidɛŋ fi a Alɛgsaŋdirii , fi fi ghagsi ̀ gha ̀ bu ̀ ma ̀ wɔɔ ɓi ki ̀ ri ̀ ŋ ki riɓa ̀ y kin ̀ . Fi ̀ tima ̀ fin ̀ fi ɓagha ̀ ɗii lɛ , bɛ ̀ ll yi rifas .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ fi ̀ tima ̀ fin ̀ fi rɛli ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛ lɛ Sirakuuzɛ , nni ti ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ wɔɔ mɛ ̀ ru mɛraa .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ foo , ti ̀ so ̀ ri ̀ be ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y , ti ̀ kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ a Regyo . Bi duri tana , bɛ ̀ ɓ i ̀ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ fɛɓsi ̀ i ̀ duŋzi , ɓi ̀ sii kɛn ̀ min kikpaŋi ̀ a Puzɔl ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛɓɛɛ ̀ .
Ti ̀ tanɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓis ɓɛ righerɛ ̀ n wɔɔ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ tɔg ɓi ̀ si lɛ ti lay mɛ ̀ ru taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkaa , fɔɔnnɛ ti ̀ ki kɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Rom .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓis ɓɛ righerɛ ̀ n ɓɛ a Rom ɓɛ woka ̀ lɛ ti ̀ kpaŋi , ɓɛ yugha ̀ ɓi ̀ si ki ̀ ɓoŋi ̀ a fye ̀ e ̀ fi Apiyus , ri ̀ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɗii lɛ : Naa yi ɓɛ ̀ ke ̀ n yiraa . Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pol a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ɓɔ , a ̀ to ̀ gsa ̀ g Bɛ ̀ ll , nyoo yi ̀ i ̀ i te ̀ e ̀ sɛ ̀ n .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ kpaga ̀ a Rom , n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ sɛdɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓimbu ̀ ŋ ri ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ gwey , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛ caɗ Pol lɛ a kɔri cɛ ̀ ncii , ri ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋɓe ̀ ŋga ̀ nyi .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ̀ ra , Pol a ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ghra ̀ ka ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n . Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ taŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ , nni Pol a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , n ̀ ki ̀ i ɓi ɓumɓɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kis kiɓan kiɓeɓtɛn , kɛ ̀ ɛ nki yogsi ɓi ̀ syɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓi ɓɛseŋi ɓis . Nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ɓɛ ɓanga ̀ mɛ ̀ a Yorisalɛm , ɓɛ kaa ̀ ɓ mɛ ̀ ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ ro ̀ mɛŋ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Ɓɛ ̀ ro ̀ mɛŋ ɓɛ tɔka ̀ ka ̀ mɛ ̀ mɛ ̀ tɔɔ ̀ tɔɔgh ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ghɛn kiɓan kiɓeɓtɛn ki ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i , ki ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ri ̀ n ̀ wolɛ ̀ n , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ mɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , ɓɛɛ caɗ mɛ ̀ ,
ki ̀ ɓan kifog Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓen ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ca ̀ ɗ mɛ , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ n ̀ tiniyɛn lɛ nghagsii ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kɛm ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Kaaza . N ̀ ki yin ri ̀ fe ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ , n ̀ sɔmɛn ɓumɓɛ ɓi kilɔ ̀ ŋ kɛm ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki mɛ ̀ ɛ ntɔɔgh lɛ di ma ̀ a ghɛɛ mi ̀ ni , n ̀ kali ̀ mi ̀ ni lɛ bɛn yi n ̀ ɗi ̀ yi ri ̀ yɔ , yi ri ɓisuu n ̀ tyweeyi wu Isirayɛl a ri ̀ ri ̀ wɔ .
Nni ɓɛ ɓaka ̀ nyi lɛ : Ɓi ̀ sii ghɛɛ ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ a Zyude a ̀ ɓu ̀ ŋ ki ̀ ɓan kɔɔ nsoo ̀ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ yu ̀ u ɓi fɛ , a ̀ kpaa ki ̀ ɓan a ̀ ra ̀ ɗ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ sii ̀ kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ ti wog ɓi ŋwɔm wɔɔ com ki wɔ ̀ ɔ fe ̀ fe ̀ g , ɓisuulɛ ti ̀ yii lɛ bee inɛ ̀ n , ɓum ɓɛɛ ̀ ɗu ̀ u ̀ ɗuu ri yɔ ̀ ja ̀ ŋbimiɗ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ fagha ̀ nyi n ̀ ka ̀ g wulɛ ɓɛɛ ghɛnɛn , nni ɓɛ yugha ̀ y ki ̀ tuu lɛ ɓɛɛ ghɛn ̀ nyi a mɛɛ mii . Ɓi ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓii , Pol a ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ ki ̀ ɓan ki ki taataa ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ ki kaakaa bee lɛ ri ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Moyis , ri ̀ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan , lɛ a ki lɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ teeti nyoey ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki Yeesus . A to ̀ ka ̀ ka ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ fɔlɔɔ a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n sariwa a ̀ kpaŋ cɛŋko ̀ .
Ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ dɛŋ i ̀ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi a ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ , wɔlɛ ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛmbog ɓɛ teɗ nyoey .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ sug , di ɓɛ mɛ rɔ ̀ ɓ kɛ ̀ ɓɛɛ ̀ wooghrɛn jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , com ki Pol a ̀ kpaati ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ ki ɓagha ̀ lɛ : Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ki kpagha ̀ lɔŋ saaɗ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki kali ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓin ɓi ŋwɔm wu n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan Ezayii lɛ :
Kɛ ̀ na u kpaa ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kin ̀ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ soo woogh lɛ syeesyee kɛ ̀ ɓi yi ̀ , ɓi ̀ ri ki seese ̀ e ̀ lɛ syeesyee kɛ ̀ ɓi ghɛn
ɓisuulɛ mɛ ̀ rem mɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki , mɛ tɔgtii ɓi , ɓɛ mɛ simgi dɔm ɓi mɛ ̀ ree ̀ ɓɛ ki ɓuusag mis lɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ghɛnɛn , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ yi kiɓan ɗi nɗem , lɛ i ɓɛ lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛɛ mɛ ̀ rem n ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zi ̀ ɓɔ .
Nni yiina min lɛ , ɓɔlɛ ̀ a ̀ go ̀ ri i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛ , a ̀ mɛ romɓɛn a ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n . Nsoo ̀ ɓɔ , ɓɛ ri nyi ɓii ̀ gha ̀ ɓi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pol a ̀ kpagha ̀ fɔlɔɔ , Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ghaa ̀ gh di ɓɛɛ ̀ nyoonyolɛ ̀ n ɓɔri ̀ ɓɔ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ .
Pol a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ bimiɗ ɓɛ be ̀ g ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ ɓi naa i ̀ nɛ a ̀ rɛnti ̀ gha ̀ . Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ yuyu ̀ gha ̀ y nyi ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ a ̀ tete ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ ri ̀ ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ .
A la ̀ a ̀ la ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ ki re ̀ resi ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi seesee Kan Yeesus Kiris le ̀ g bimiɗ a ̀ nɛ ki ɓagha ̀ lɛ ki kɔ ̀ n nyi , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ntɔɓ .
Pol , n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say a Yeesus Kiris , a ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ lɛ a ɓa n ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom a Yeesus , a ̀ ki ɓa ti nɗɛsiyɛn dɛga ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ghagsi ̀ ɗi Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ka ̀ ka ̀ Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n abɛ ̀ y , ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ ki ka ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ seesee Man wii ̀ , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ yalɛ ̀ nga ̀ mum ɓi boo i ̀ ɓum i ̀ Davit .
Ɓi san a ̀ nɛ a Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay , ki ghɛnɛ ̀ n lɛ a ̀ ri ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , ɓi ri ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi a ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ nga ̀ y a ɓi ̀ loŋ .
Ɓi Yeesus Kiris a ̀ Kan wi ̀ s nnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ nɛ lɛ mɓa n ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ɓi ri ̀ kem ɗi Kiris lɛ nsyoŋ ̀ yi ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m lɛ ɓɛɛ gherɛn nyi , ɓɛ ki nyi mɛ ̀ wog .
Ɓi ̀ ri ̀ girig ɓi ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n , mi ̀ ni ɓɛ Yeesus Kiris a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ y ;
nni mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ keesii yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ , ɓɛ bi ̀ ri ̀ a Rom , mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɛ a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ɓi ɓa ɓum ɓii , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ Seŋi ̀ wi ̀ s ɓɛɛ ̀ Kan Yeesus , ɓɛɛ fa mi ̀ ni lɛ ri ̀ geesɛ ̀ n ri ̀ fyo ̀ oog .
Mɛ ̀ n ̀ ka faa Bɛ ̀ ll wɛ ̀ m ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n lɛ Yeesus Kiris , ɓisu win mɛ ̀ to mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓisuulɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗin ɗyɛɛ ̀ keŋkem zi bimiɗ .
Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ nki ̀ ki kisay ɓi nghay wɛ ̀ m ɓi ri ̀ ghaa ̀ gha ̀ gsi ̀ ɗi Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ Man wii ̀ , a ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ lɛ n ̀ ti mɓu ̀ gi ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ,
ɓi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n yɛm ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ nfɔɛy , n ̀ tɔtɔ ̀ g Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ , i ki ri lɛ ki kɔn ̀ nyi , mɛ ̀ ɛ mɓa ɓa ̀ min ɗi bee inɛ lɛ n-yu a lɔ ̀ ŋkin .
Ɓisuulɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ coo za ̀ y i ̀ nɛ lɛ di ma ̀ a ghɛɛ mi ̀ ni , lɛ n-yuy mi ̀ ni ri ̀ ri ̀ fa ɗi Kitɛntɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ridɛŋ ɗi ɗyɛɛ fati mi ̀ ni i ̀ te ̀ ɗ .
Nsoo ̀ gi ̀ lɛ di ti faa ̀ fa ̀ lɛ ̀ n i ̀ te ̀ ɗ nɗaŋ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi ɗi ri ɓi ̀ si bas lɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ri ̀ mi ̀ ni .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ ni ɓi lɛ ɓi nan ̀ lɛ , mmɛ ɓeg ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓidɛŋ lɛ n-yu mi ̀ ni ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ lɛ di ki ̀ say kɛm ̀ kɛɛ wum ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ɓi ̀ ɗu ̀ n a lɔ ̀ ŋkin , yɛ ̀ ɛ ki fagha ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓimbog . Nni a ̀ kpaŋ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , bee i ̀ ka ghɛnɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi .
Ɓisuulɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ g wulɛ nkɛn ̀ a ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , a ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ yii cɛɓ ri ̀ a ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ ka yi ɓi cɛɓ , a ɓɛ ̀ yii ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan , ri ̀ a ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yii ɓi com .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ coo za ̀ y i ̀ nɛ lɛ nghagsi girig mi ̀ ni Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ , mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ a Rom .
Ɓisuulɛ , n ̀ -yin lɛ n ̀ wog n ̀ too ̀ ri ̀ ɗ ɓi ri ̀ ghagsi ̀ ɗi Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ , lɛ a ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu Bɛ ̀ ll wu wɛɛ ̀ ghɛɛghɛɓsi ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ gherɛɛ , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n lɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpaŋ lɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n .
Ɓisuulɛ Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a re ̀ resi yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ti a ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g lɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ ɓa lɛ saaɗ ɓi mis mii lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ɓisuu righerɛ ̀ n lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ mum a ̀ saaɗ ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , lɛ rgherɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɓi ̀ .
Bim i Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ ti i ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g yi ̀ aɗyoo ɓisuu kiɓe kice ̀ m , ri ̀ ki ̀ tɛ ̀ ŋtɛ ̀ ŋ kice ̀ m ɓi ɓum ɓɛ ri ri ̀ ɓyɔ , ɓyɛɛ ɓanɓani saaɗ ɓi ri ̀ kpa ̀ n ɓi zɛ ̀ ɗ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ ;
ɓisuulɛ , ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓum ɓɛ ri ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ ɓɛ yi ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓi ri lɛ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ɓi mis maa , lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ re ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ ɓyɔ lɛ syeesyee .
A ̀ tumɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ zi , mɛ ̀ ro ̀ ŋa mii mɛ ɓum ɓɛ yin lɛ ɓɛ ghɛn lɛ , ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wii wu wu ri fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ɗii ɗi a ̀ ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓyɛɛ ̀ re ̀ eresɛ ̀ n ɓi ɓyom ɓi a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ; fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓɛ yin ɗi com ki ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ kpaa ki ki ki lɛ ɓɛɛ cenɛn ɓɔ .
Ɓisuulɛ ɓɛ yii Bɛ ̀ ll , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓɔgsi nyi yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓɔgsag nyi , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki fa nyi ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ di ̀ mi ̀ dimi ɓyaa ɓi ɓɛfe ̀ g ɓi mɛ tɔɔsi ɓɔ cog , ɓi ̀ du ̀ ŋdu ̀ ŋ ɓyaa ɓi mɛre ̀ m ɓi sigtɛ ̀ n biri ̀ m .
Ɓɛ sasa ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓɛ wom ̀ zɛɛ , kɔlɛ ɓɛ ri ɓi ̀ ye ̀ g .
Ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ ɓɔgsii Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ Loy ɓi ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ɓi lɛ , ri ̀ mum a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ wula ̀ g , ri ̀ ti ̀ i ̀ li ̀ , ri ̀ nya ̀ m yi mɛko ̀ o ̀ mɛnin , ri ̀ yi wɔwɔghɛn ri mu ̀ m , ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓi ɓɔɔ ɓɔɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ gsi ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ci ̀ tɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi tifin , ɓi mɛ ̀ rem maa mɛ ɓiisɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ kɔ ̀ ni , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ so ̀ osoo ̀ ti ̀ nyoo yaa yi ɓɔmiɗ .
Ɓɛ koɓsɛ ̀ n saaɗ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pwa ̀ a ̀ , ɓɛ ɓɔɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ gsi ̀ ɓyom ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ , ɓɛ kiki ̀ ɓyɔ mɛ ̀ wog ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓaa ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓɔgsii n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ri ̀ ri ̀ kem fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , a ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ tini ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ kiki ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ntoo ̀ ri ̀ ɗ ; ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓaa ɓɛ pɛɛ ̀ zi ̀ ri ̀ ra ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fe ̀ ka ̀ lɛ ri ̀ giɓ ri ̀ baŋi ̀ ɓi bee i ̀ du ̀ ne .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓɛ ̀ baŋi ̀ girig , ɓɛ mɛ ca ̀ ɗ rira ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fe ̀ ka ̀ lɛ baŋi ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ rarag ri ̀ giɓ , ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛ ̀ baŋi ̀ ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛ kɔnkɔ ̀ n lɛ ɓɛɛ rarɛn ɗi ̀ ɓɔ . Ɓɛ ̀ baŋi ̀ ɓɛ kiki ̀ min ɓiɓan ɓi ntoo ̀ ri ̀ ɗ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛ ̀ baŋi ̀ , ri ̀ syɔn ɗi mii ̀ ɗi ɓa lɛ ɓɛɛ teɗ mɛ ̀ le ̀ ɓ mɛ mɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ri ̀ ri ̀ na ̀ n ɗya ̀ a ɗin ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ ɓi kirɔɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ yiti lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ wɔɔ , nni Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ naga ̀ ɓɔ ri ̀ ki ̀ ye ̀ g kaa ki ɗyomzɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓɛɛ kiki ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓaa ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi kiki ̀ i .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ ronɛn ɗi mɛ ̀ be ̀ e mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , ɗi ̀ ri ̀ gɛn , ri ̀ za ̀ y i ̀ i ̀ kum , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ghe ̀ y ; ɓɛ ɓa ti ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ronɛn ri ya ̀ aka , ɓɛɛ woowoo ̀ sɛ ̀ n , ɓɔ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ paa ̀ zi ̀ , ri ̀ wii wu mɛghe ̀ y , ɓɛ keesi ̀ cɛɓ ki tisɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g ,
ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɓɔlɛ , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ wɔ ̀ wɔri ̀ , ɓɛ ɓa ɓɛ ̀ be ̀ na ̀ bena ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓɔ ɓɛ ̀ kaa ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan , ɓɔ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ daŋa ̀ ri ̀ kalɛn , ɓɛ womzɛ ̀ n ɓi ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗi kiɓe , ɓɛ ki ɓa ri ntoo ̀ te ̀ ɗ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yali ̀ ɓaa .
Ɓɔ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓa ɓumɓɛ mum a ̀ tyweeya ̀ g , ɓɔ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗem wu woghɛn romum nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g .
Nsoo ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ yii lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ renga ̀ lɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki mɛkuu mɛ ɓiɓan mɛn ̀ , ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ di ̀ ri ̀ wu , ɓɔɔ kɛnkɛ ̀ n lɔŋ asu ɓɛ kiki ̀ ɓyɔ , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki sugtɛn foo , ɓɛ kɛɛ ̀ di ̀ asu ɓɛ sɛsɛ ̀ g ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki girig ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi fɔ ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ wɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ anɛ u yɔ ̀ myɔm ɓum , u ̀ yin ɗi com ki kpaayɛn ɓisuulɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki u yɔ ̀ myɔm ɓɛro , kɛɛ ̀ ki u faafa ̀ lɛ ̀ n wɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ bɛ ̀ lɛn , lɛ wa ̀ a ̀ nɛ u yɔ ̀ myɔm ɓum u ̀ ti u ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g girig ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓɔɔ ti ɓɛ kila ̀ g .
Ɓi ̀ sii yii lɛ ri ̀ yɔ ̀ m ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓii ̀ yɔ ̀ mi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki mɛkuu mɛ ɓiɓan mɛ fɔlɔɔ ɗi ri ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ saaɗ a ̀ ri ̀ .
Wa ̀ a ̀ nɛ u ̀ ti u ̀ yɔ ̀ mgi ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kila ̀ g fɔlɔɔ , wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ki ki ̀ ki ɓiɓan ɓyɔm ̀ ɓin ̀ , u fe ̀ ki nya lɛ u ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɓi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ m ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ?
Gi ̀ n wɔ ̀ ɔ sɛɛsɛɛ ̀ ti ̀ lɛ ri ̀ coo ki ̀ rɔɔ-n ̀ ɗem a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓi kii ki nɗem , ri ̀ ki ̀ puɓi ̀ -n ̀ ɗem wi ̀ i ̀ ? U ̀ yii ɓi lɛ ki ̀ rɔɔ-n ̀ ɗem a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ghɛ ̀ sɛɛ wɔ ̀ ki ̀ tinii lɛ u lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛn n ̀ ɗem ?
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ri ̀ ɓa ɗi n ̀ ɗem wɔɔ wu ri wu ̀ te ̀ rɛn , ri ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ kɔ ̀ ni ɓi lɛ u lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛn n ̀ ɗem , u taataŋza ̀ g wɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ coo bim i Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi nyo ̀ o ̀ ; bim inɛ ̀ n i ̀ ri re ̀ sɛn ŋwos anɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri sa ̀ ɗ bim yii ̀ ; ŋwos anɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ren ɗii ɗi ɓiɓan ɗi ɗi ri lɛ saaɗ ɗi ri yilɛ ̀ n ,
yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ri le ̀ ɓ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗii ɗi ri .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ sii ̀ rɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗi kirɔɔ , ɓɛ kaaka ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ kem ɗi yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ n ̀ nya ̀ asɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ cɛɓ ki kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ le ̀ g , Bɛ ̀ ll fa ɓɔ cɛɓ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kila ̀ g nyi n ̀ too ̀ te ̀ ɗ , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ n lɛ ɓɛɛ wog com ki saaɗ a kaka ̀ li ̀ , lɔŋ ki ̀ tɛ ̀ ŋtɛ ̀ ŋ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓɔɔ nɔɔ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ɓɔ lɛ , ri ̀ bim yii ̀ , ɗi ̀ ri ̀ baŋi ̀ ɗii .
Ri ̀ kɛŋ ɗi ̀ mɛ ̀ riighriki ̀ ɓi ri ɓii ̀ sɛni ̀ ɓi mum bimiɗ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓeɓtɛn , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n lɛ muu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpaŋ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yin muu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ , a ̀ kemzi ̀ , a ̀ ki nyaasi mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g ki ̀ rɔɔ , a ̀ fa nyi fyo ̀ oog , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n lɛ muu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpaŋ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yin muu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n .
Ɓisuulɛ n ̀ la ̀ nag wu yin yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ kigha ̀ ki ̀ ɓe , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ yi ɓidɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ Moyis , ɓɛ ɓii ̀ cuu ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓince ̀ m . Ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ kigha ̀ ki ̀ ɓe di ɓɛ ti ri ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna , ɓɛ ri ɓɔ ɓii ̀ yɔ ̀ mi ri ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓyɔm ̀ ɓin ̀ .
A ̀ a ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ wowog ɓidɔ ̀ gsɛna ri mɛ ̀ ree ̀ ɓɛɛ ri lɛ saaɗ ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , lɔŋ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kila ̀ g yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓyɛɛ ̀ kaka ̀ li ̀ , ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ a ̀ ri ghɛn lɛ ɓɛ ri lɛ saaɗ .
I ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , ɓɔ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ faagha ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ɓiɓan ɓi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓyɛɛ ̀ tɔtɔg lɔŋ ɓɔmiɗ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ com ki ki resii ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ ki fɔlɔɔ , di ɓɛ ti fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna , ɓisu waa wu ɓɔmiɗ , nsoo ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ yin ɗi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna .
Ɓi ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗin ̀ , ɓɛ resii yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi ri ɓɔ ɓi ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ɓi nɗem ; fɔlɔɔ nnɛ n ̀ ɗem waa wu ɓi ɗu ̀ m wɛɛ ̀ re ̀ resi girig ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ . Mɛ ̀ yiti ̀ maa mɛ kiki ̀ lɛ , ɗi ɗi yii mɛ fa ɓɔ zɔɔ , ɗi ɗi yii , mɛ kamɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ɓɔ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ri ghɛnɛn ŋwos anɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri yɔm ̀ ɓi Yeesus Kiris ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓum ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kila ̀ g a ri ̀ nyam ; fɔlɔɔ nnɛ Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ nghaaghagsi ̀ ɓum a re ̀ re ̀ si ̀ .
Wa ̀ a ̀ nɛ u reeghreŋ ̀ ɗɛ ̀ n lɛ muu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , u ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ ghɛ ̀ gmɛ ̀ n ɓi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna , u ̀ saa ̀ sa ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ghan ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ,
u ̀ yii ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓii ɓi mɛ re ̀ sag wɔ yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ ri ̀ lɛ u ̀ yi lɛ ki ̀ ɓan ki kɛɛ ɓiisɛɛ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ ri ̀ gɛɓsɛ ̀ n .
Wɔ ̀ ɔ fe ̀ feg lɛ wɔ ̀ yɛɛ ri ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓanɓani ɓɛ ̀ ɗyaŋɗya ̀ ŋ ɓi ki ̀ geŋ , u ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ si ̀ ɓɔ wɔ ̀ ti ̀ ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ki ɓɛroɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓi ɓiri ̀ m ,
u ̀ ri ̀ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ reɓka ̀ g ɓi ̀ du ̀ ŋdu ̀ ŋ ɓi ɓum , u ̀ ki ɓa nɗe ̀ sa ̀ g a ̀ ɓɔɔɓɔɓti ɓisuulɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ com ki kɛɛ ̀ re ̀ resi wɔ ri ̀ yi ɗi ɓiɓan ɗyɔmiɗ , ri ̀ saaɗ ɓi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓiɗu ̀ m .
Wa ̀ a ̀ nɛ u ̀ ti u ̀ re ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓi ̀ ɓan , kɔ ̀ ɔ ka re ̀ si ɓaa ̀ wɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ ? U ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ ɓum lɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ yii com , wɔ ̀ yiiyi ̀ i ̀ ɓyom .
U ̀ re ̀ re ̀ g ɓum ti ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g , ki ̀ ɓan kifog wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ; u ̀ ɓe ̀ e ̀ zɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ nu ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ nni lannɛ u pye ̀ epyee ̀ zɛ ̀ n mis ri ̀ za ̀ ŋ ɓi naa yi ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɔɔɓɔgsi ̀ ɓi ̀ nu ̀ n mii ̀ ?
U ̀ kaa ̀ ka ̀ lɛ ̀ n lɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll , ki ̀ ɓan kifog u ̀ so ̀ o ̀ so ̀ o ̀ ti ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ɗi ɓiɓan ɓi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓii ɓi gherɛɛ ɓi lɛ ɓɛɛ kilag .
Ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi zɛy ɓyɛɛ ̀ sɛɛsɛɛ ̀ ti ̀ ɗii ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗin , lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn .
Ki ri saaɗ lɛ kɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ n a ̀ ghɛɓsii , di u ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , uu ̀ sɛɛtii ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna , kɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ n wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ a ̀ ɓa lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ ka kɛrɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi .
Nni i ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ka yin nkɛ ̀ rɛn a ɓe ̀ ŋɓeŋ mɛsiŋdɛn mɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ ɓa ɗi a ̀ yin nkɛ ̀ rɛn ɗi yin nya lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ teɗ ɗyɔ ɓi si ̀ g a ̀ kɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ n ?
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ yin nkɛ ̀ rɛn , ki ̀ ɓan kifog a ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋɓe ̀ ŋ mɛ ̀ siŋdɛn mɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna , a ̀ ɓii ̀ reni ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki wa ̀ a ̀ nɛ u sɛɛsɛɛ ̀ ti ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna nsoo ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna , u ̀ ki ɓa nkɛ ̀ rɛn .
Ɓisuulɛ muu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n a ̀ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ yin lɔŋ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a seesee ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɓi mis lɛ a ̀ ri ̀ muu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , nsoo ̀ lɛ a ̀ ɓa nkɛ ̀ rɛn kɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ seesee ɓi nyo ̀ o ̀ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ muu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ri ̀ ri ̀ nɗem wu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n . Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ syeesyee a ̀ kɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ ɓi nɗem , a ̀ nɛ a ki ̀ ikilɛ ̀ n ri ̀ N ̀ ghay a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa anɛ a ̀ ri ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri ki ka ̀ nɛn ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna . Mɛ ̀ sɛɛ ̀ ghsɛɛgh mɛ rikuu ɗi muu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɗi fɔlɔɔ mɛ ti mɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓayi a ɓum , mɛ ti mɛ ɓala ̀ g yi ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ki ̀ rɔɔ ki muu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ min ɗi kɔ ki ri lɛ cɛ ? Nsoo ̀ lɛ , kɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ min ɗi gɛɓsɛ ̀ n aɗi ?
Ki ̀ rɔɔ kaa ki te ̀ ghɛɛ bee lɛɛ ̀ gwey ; ri ̀ ɓɔ nnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ka loka ̀ ki ̀ reɓsɛɛ ɓiɓan ɓii .
Nni la ! I ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wa ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ gherɛɛ ɓi , ri ̀ ɓa ɗyaa ɗi kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗin ̀ ɗyɛɛ ri ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a rɔɓ kɛ ̀ ɛ roo ̀ zi ti mɛ ̀ ka ̀ g mii ?
Ɓi saaɗ ki yin fɔlɔɔ ! Ɓum ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ gherɛɛ lɛ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ kpaaghi ̀ saaɗ , ɓum ɓɛɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ pwa ̀ a ̀ pwaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛce ̀ m ; lɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ yi lɛ u ̀ ri ̀ mum a ̀ saaɗ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi u ̀ kalii , u ̀ ki yagsag ɓɛyɔ ̀ m di ɓɛ sɔmɛɛ wɔ ̀ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ i ki ri lɛ ri ̀ ɓa ɗis ɗi ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ tɛ ̀ ŋtɛ ̀ ŋ ɓi ɓum ɗyɛɛ ̀ re ̀ resi ɓi ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ saaɗ , cɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ min lɛ ti ̀ kpaa ? Ti kpaa nya lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ ɗi ̀ ki ̀ tɛ ̀ ŋtɛ ̀ ŋ di a ̀ paa ̀ zii ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si ? N ̀ kpaa fɔlɔɔ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kpaaghi ̀ .
Ki yin fɔlɔɔ ! I Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ a ri ̀ fɔlɔɔ di a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ yɔ ̀ m ziinɛ la ?
I pwa ̀ a ̀ wɛ ̀ m a ki ̀ ki lɛ saaɗ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a konag ki ̀ ghɛnɛɛ , fɔlɔɔ a ɓa ɓisuu rikem ɗii , ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ti ̀ mɛ ̀ ki ̀ yɔ ̀ mi yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe ?
I ki ri fɔlɔɔ , ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ti ̀ yin min lɛ ti ̀ kpaa lɛ ti kiki ki ̀ ɓe di ki ̀ rɔɔ kɛɛ kpaŋ yi ̀ mii ̀ ? Fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓɛɛ to ̀ tog ɓisi ki ̀ ɓe ɓi nyoo ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kpaakpaa ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ sii ti ti ̀ kala ̀ g fɔlɔɔ ; ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ri ki teɗ deɓ yi yi ghɛsɛɛ ri ̀ ɓɔ .
Nni la min ? Ɓi ̀ si Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ti ̀ cee nya ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓimbog ? Ti ̀ cee ɓi ɓyɔ nsoo ̀ lɛsa ̀ g ! Ɓisuulɛ ti ̀ mɛ re ̀ si lɛ ki ̀ ɓe ki lamii ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , nsoo ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , nsoo ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n .
Lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ saaɗ a ̀ yin lɔŋ nsoo ̀ bog ,
Ŋwaa ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa , nsoo ̀ ŋwaa ̀ n ̀ kaakaayɛn Bɛ ̀ ll kɛ ̀ ɛ ghɛnɛn . Ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ ɗimɛn bee , ɓɔɔ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓa ɓɛ ̀ ɓu ̀ u ̀ sɛn .
Ŋwaa ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ kiyɛn kirɔɔ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa lɔŋ , nsoo ̀ bog .
Ɓoŋ waa ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ zɔ ̀ ŋ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ bwaŋ , ri ̀ lema ̀ g ɗyaa ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi ɓɛ ti ɓɛ pwaa ̀ ghi ̀ ɓum mii ̀ , i ̀ rɔg wu nyoo wɛɛ ti wu kpagi ̀ i ̀ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ ɓeeɓee ɓaa ɓɛ ŋwɔ ̀ m .
Myɔm maa mɛ roni ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ nyɔ ̀ ma ɓɛ lo ̀ lolɛn .
Mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ maa mɛ fɛmɓɛ ̀ n ɓi ri ̀ kɛ ̀ n ɗi wolɛn mum .
Bee bimiɗ i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ fyee mii ̀ , ɓɛ ca ̀ ɗ wɔɔ lɛ , ri ̀ cuu , ɗi ̀ ri ̀ kɛŋ .
