Ɓisuulɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ke ̀ ŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi myaɓ mɛ kite mɔmiɗ , a ̀ a ke ̀ ŋi ɓi girig wɔ ̀ ,
Kuurag ki ̀ puɓi ̀ -n ̀ ɗem a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ ki ̀ nyɛn kii ; a ̀ re ̀ sii ki ̀ nyɛn ɓisuu ɓɛroɓɛ ɓɛ kpigha ̀ , a ̀ re ̀ si ̀ wɔ ̀ ki ̀ puɓi ̀ -n ̀ ɗem , wɔ ̀ lɛ kɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔkɔnɛ ̀ n lɛ u ɓaɓa lɔŋ ɓi ki ̀ puɓi ̀ -n ̀ ɗem wi ̀ i ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ fɔlɔɔ ɓɛ pisi ̀ girig wɔ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ i ɓɔ girig ɓɛ kɛn ̀ kɛni ɓi asu ɓɛ ɓenɓe ̀ n ki ̀ gherɛɛ , ɓɛ ɓii ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zii ɓɔ ki ̀ ɓaatii ɓi n ̀ ɗye ̀ m , lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ ɓɔ ki ̀ ɓaatii ɓi n ̀ ɗye ̀ m .
Wa ̀ a ̀ nɛ u ̀ yin muu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , u ̀ ri ̀ ( fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ) ŋwaɓ wu o ̀ li ̀ vyee a ̀ nɛ ɓi cog , ŋwaɓ wii wɛɛ ̀ wu ɓɛ renii ̀ , ɓɛ yu ki ̀ ɓaatii ɓi n ̀ ɗye ̀ m wu o ̀ li ̀ vyee a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ɓɛla ̀ m ̀ ɓɛ ̀ lɛn , ki ̀ ɓan ki lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓaati ŋwaɓ wu kite ɓi n ̀ ɗye ̀ m wu kite kidɛŋ , ki ri ki mum kɛ ̀ ɛ wog ; Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɔ yɛɛ ri myaɓ mɛ o ̀ li ̀ vyee a ̀ m ̀ ɓɛ ̀ lɛn , fɔɔnnɛ ki ri ɓii ̀ pɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zii ki ɓaa ̀ lɛ fɛnfɛn lɛ ɓɛɛ pɛɛ ̀ zi ɓɔ ki ̀ ɓaatii ɓi n ̀ ɗye ̀ m waa .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan kidɛŋ ki a ri ̀ nyam ki ri wɔɔ , kɛɛ ̀ ki n ̀ kɔ ̀ ni ɓi lɛ ɓi comɛn lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ghɛnɛɛ minii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛ ɗyom ̀ zɛ ̀ n ; ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ri lɛ , ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ a Isirayɛl i ̀ yii ̀ di ri i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ i ̀ wog , wɔ ̀ lɛ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki ri ɓii ̀ finɛɛ a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓimbog ɓi ɓi yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓii ̀ ɗiŋii ɓi go ̀ ri i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ Isirayɛl bimiɗ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ cɛɓ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : N ̀ ko ̀ ri-bum a ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ yi ̀ a Siyon , a ̀ pisi ̀ n ̀ too ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu do ̀ o ̀ yi Yakɔɓ .
Bee inɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ reni ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ yɛ ̀ ɛnɛ ̀ n lɔɔ , di ma ̀ a pisi ɓiɓe ɓyaa .
Ɓi san a ̀ nɛ a Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ɓenga ̀ , Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ be ̀ na ̀ bena ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , fɔlɔɔ a ̀ ki ɓa ɓi ki ̀ rɔɔ kin , wɔ ̀ lɛ i ti ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ tii ri ̀ ɓɔ ̀ n ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ , Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ keesii ɓisuu ɓɛseŋi ɓaa ɓɛ ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ ri ̀ ɓo ̀ o ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ti ̀ a ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g ɓum kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ azi adɛŋ , ri ̀ n ̀ ɗee ̀ ghreŋi wii , ɓi yin lɛ ɓi lɔgtɛ ̀ n .
Fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ mi ̀ nii kigha ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll n ̀ too ̀ te ̀ ɗ ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ abɛ ̀ y , ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ mɛ wog mini nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g lɛ n ̀ too ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ nkii nyi .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓɔ girig ɓɛ mɛ re ̀ si n ̀ too ̀ te ̀ ɗ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , lɛ di Bɛ ̀ ll a wog ɓɔ girig nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ a ncenɛɛ mi ̀ ni .
Ɓisuulɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ghaasi ̀ gha ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ̀ kpa ̀ n ɓi n ̀ too ̀ te ̀ ɗ , ɓi ɗu ̀ m , lɛ di a wog ɓɔ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g .
Ri ̀ kuu ɗi coo nɗem wu nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɗyɔ ! Ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗii , ri ̀ ri ̀ yi ɗii ɗi ɓiɓan , ɓi rimi yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ . Mum a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ yi ɓɛ ̀ fe ̀ g ɓii , mɛ ̀ yiti ̀ mii mɛ yin lɛ mum a ̀ wog .
Ɓi saaɗ ghɛn yɛɛ ɓagha ̀ lɛ a ̀ yi fe ̀ g a ̀ Kan , ghɛn yɛɛ ki ɓagha ̀ lɛ a ̀ reɓ nyi ?
Ghɛn yɛɛ ka loka ̀ nyi ki ̀ faa ̀ com ki a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ ɓoŋɓo ̀ ŋ mɛ ̀ le ̀ ɓ mɛ mii ̀ ?
Lɛ ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi fuuyi ̀ ɓi nyi , ɓi ri lɛ nyi , ɓi ki ri ̀ ɓisu wi ̀ i ̀ , nnyɛ ̀ ɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ri ̀ ri ̀ kem fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ . A ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , ɓisuu nɗem wu nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g wu Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ re ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ɓɛg wi ̀ s , n ̀ tɔɔgh mi ̀ ni lɛ ɓi funɛn mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ tuwe ki mum a ̀ ti a ̀ weeyi ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ; ɓi funɛn mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ rifunɛ ̀ n ɗi ɗi ri cem , ɗyɔ ri ̀ tɛnɛn , ɗi ki ɓa ɗi ɗi rɔɔ Bɛ ̀ ll . Fɔlɔɔ yɛɛ ri ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ syeesyee a ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓɔgsii Bɛ ̀ ll .
Kɛ ̀ bi nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti cɛɓ ki ɓumɓɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ghɛghɛ ̀ ɓ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ca ̀ rɛɛna ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a lɔgti mi ̀ ni di a ̀ koɓsɛɛ mɛ ̀ yiti ̀ mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m mɛ mɛ ri mi ̀ ni ɓi mɛ ̀ rem , i ̀ suu ̀ ce ̀ m , ri ̀ mɛ nyɔn , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓi ri ̀ min ɓii ̀ yii ̀ ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi rɔɔtɛɛ , ri ̀ ɓi ɓyɛɛ ̀ rɔɔghi nyi , ri ̀ ɓi ɓi ri kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓɛ fen mii ̀ .
Lɛ geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kigha ̀ mɛ ̀ , n ̀ kpaa mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ ɓi mi ̀ ni lɛ : Kɛ ̀ ɓi rɛsag minii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ ɓi nɗɛli wu wu cee ri ̀ ɓa ɗin , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓaana lɔŋ ri mɛ ̀ yiti ̀ mɛ lɛ ɓi sɛɛ ̀ di mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ ɓi zi , mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ rɛsɛ ̀ n ɓi nɗɛli wu wu ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ri ̀ ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n i ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ nyi .
Lɛ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɓ lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɓ ɓin ̀ ɓi ki ɓa ɓika ̀ ɓ ɓi nyoo bog , ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓa rikuu ɗi kisay ɗifog ,
fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓi ̀ si ɓɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ tuu , ti ̀ ri nyoo bog ɓi Kiris ɓi ɗu ̀ m ; ti ̀ ki ɓa ti ɓika ̀ ɓ ɓi ɓi nyoo bog ,
le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ ghɛnɛ ̀ nga ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkis , ti ̀ ri lɛ ri ̀ mum , ri ̀ ri ̀ kuu ɗi kiɓan ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ nyi lɛ a kilag , fɔɔnnɛ roa ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ a kpaa ̀ kpa ̀ ŋzi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ re ̀ sii nyi , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ i kisay kin ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
Roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ɗeŋiyɛn lɛ a ɓa n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛmbog , a sii ̀ rɛn ɓi ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗi kisay ; roa ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ lɛ a ɓa n ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ falɛɛ ɓi ri ̀ re ̀ re ̀ si ̀ .
Roa ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ lɛ a tee ̀ te ̀ e ̀ si ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni nyoo ri ̀ deɓ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ si ̀ i ̀ rɛɛ ɓi ri ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ɗi fɔlɔɔ ; roa ̀ nɛ a ka ̀ aka ̀ ɓsi ̀ i ̀ kum wii , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ i kiɓan kin ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ̀ ka ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ n ; roa ̀ nɛ a kɛ ̀ ɛkɛɛ ̀ si ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ wɔ ki ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sii ri ti ̀ kɛɗ ; roa ̀ nɛ a ghɛɛghɛɓsi ̀ ɓum ɓɛ nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ i kiɓan kin ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ .
Nkɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛ ̀ ghe ̀ y azi , ɓi ̀ ɓe ̀ e ̀ zɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ɓe , ɓi ̀ ki si ̀ i ̀ rɛn ɓi ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗi kirɔɔ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ .
Ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ re ̀ sii , kirɔɔrɛɛ ki n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ geni ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n ; lɛ nnyaasɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ , re ̀ siina bɔgsɛ ̀ n lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m win ̀ .
Ɓaana ri ̀ ki ̀ si ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɓi ki ̀ iɓwɛɗ ; ki ̀ ina Kan ki ̀ say ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ ɓi nɗem .
Ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ nyaa ɓi dya ̀ ɓɛn inɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ yɔ ̀ , ɓi ̀ ni ̀ ɗ n ̀ ɗem ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓi ̀ tulɛɛ ri mɛ ̀ tɔɓ , ɓi ̀ ki si ̀ i ̀ rɛn bi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n .
Ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ghɛɓsaagh ɓɛgeni ɓin ɓɛ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓyɛɛ ̀ yeeyee ̀ si ̀ ɓɔ , ɓi ̀ ki yi ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓ ɗi ɓɛ ̀ ke ̀ n lɛ syeesyee .
Ma ̀ ŋina ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ yeeyee ̀ si ̀ mi ̀ ni , kɛ ̀ ɓi cɛ ̀ m ɓɔ .
Nya ̀ a ̀ rɛɛna nɗaŋ ɗi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓi ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ , ɓi ̀ re ̀ n nɗaŋ ɗi ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ re ̀ nɗe ̀ n .
Ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ wooghrɛɛ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n , kɛ ̀ ɓi ɓɔɔɓɔgsɛ ̀ n , lɔŋ ca ̀ rɛɛna ̀ lɛ ɓi ki ɓi ̀ say ɓi ɓyɛ ̀ ɛ tɔtɔg lɛ mum a sɛɛ ̀ di nyimiɗ ɓi zi , kɛ ̀ ɓi ghɛn minii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ lɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n .
Kɛ ̀ ɓi le ̀ ɓ mum ki ̀ ɓe ri ki ̀ ɓe , kaana lɔŋ lɛ ɓi ki ki ̀ rɔɔ ɓi mis mɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
I bee i ̀ ri ̀ lɛ i ̀ ɓa , le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ win wu ri lɛ wu kpaŋ , ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ghɛɓi ̀ lɛ fyo ̀ oog ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓɛ ̀ m ɓɛ nɗem , kɛ ̀ ɓi rɔ ̀ ŋ kiɓan kin minii ̀ ɓɔmi ̀ ɗ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ca ̀ rina lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a saɗ bim yii ̀ , lɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : Kan lɛ : Mɛ ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ri ̀ rɔ ̀ ŋɗɔ ̀ ŋ , mɛ ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛɛ ki ̀ le ̀ ɓi .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ , i be ̀ na ̀ bena wɔɔ ̀ a wowog za ̀ y , faa nyi ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g , i a wowog kinɔli , faa nyi mɛ ̀ nig mɛnɔyɛn , lɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki u ̀ ki ̀ i fɔlɔɔ , di u ̀ ku ̀ nii nyi ɓɛ ̀ ra ̀ ŋ ɓɛ ɗuu ɓɛ ghɛ ̀ g-ghɛ ̀ g ɓi nto .
Kɔ ̀ ɔ ca ̀ rɛn lɛ ki ̀ ɓe kɛɛ lami wɔ ̀ , kaaya lɔŋ lɛ u lami ki ̀ ɓe ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗi kirɔɔ .
Mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ woo ̀ gh ɓɛ ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛkɛɛ ̀ si ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓisuulɛ ri ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɗi ti ɗyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ kpi ̀ yi n ̀ lɛŋlɛŋ ̀ di Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ faa ɓi , ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ , Bɛ ̀ ll yɛɛ rɛsa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɛ ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓi ziinɛ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki , mum a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ rami ̀ wɛ ̀ y ɗi ri ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ , a yi lɛ a ̀ rami wɛ ̀ y ri ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , nni ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ ri fɔlɔɔ ri n ̀ too ̀ te ̀ ɗ , ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ syoŋii ̀ ɓɔmi ̀ ɗ n ̀ cɛ ̀ m ɓi nyo ̀ o ̀ .
Ɓɛ ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɓɛ yin ɓumɓɛ lɛ mum a ̀ ni ̀ ŋ di a ki ̀ ki ɓiɓan ɓi syeesyee , lɔŋ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ɓiɓan ɓi ɓeɓtɛn , ɓɛɛ ti ɓɛ risa ̀ g ɓɔ . I u ̀ kɔ ̀ ni lɛ kɔ ̀ ɔ ririsi rila ̀ mi ̀ , u ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ kii ɓiɓan ɓi syeesyee fɔɔnnɛ ri ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɗi sɛg wɔ ̀ .
Ri ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɗyɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki Bɛ ̀ ll ki ̀ say lɛ ɗyɛɛ toni wɔ ̀ lɛ u ki ki ̀ rɔɔ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog i u ̀ ki ̀ i ki ̀ ɓe , u ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɗyɔ ki ̀ risii lɛ a ̀ a zɛy nnɛ ɗi ri ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ ɗyɛɛ pɔnɔ ̀ sag ɓum ; ɗyɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki kisay ki Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ ɗyɛɛ resi bim yii ̀ ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki ̀ i ki ̀ ɓe .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ mum a ki ɓɛ ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ mɛ ̀ wog , a ̀ a lɔŋ ɓaa ̀ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ririsi ribaŋi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , ki ̀ ɓan kifog a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓɔ ki ̀ ki ̀ i mɛwog ri ̀ nɗem wulɛ com ki a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ i kɛɛ ri .
Ɓisu wi ̀ n mii ̀ nnɛ ɓi ̀ ti ɓi ̀ peeghi ̀ girig ɓɛ ̀ la ̀ mpoŋ ̀ ; ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ teki ̀ la ̀ mpoŋ ̀ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ ɓɛɛ kilag ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ .
Le ̀ ɓkiina mum n ̀ ce ̀ m com ki ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ri ̀ nyi , ɓi ̀ peeghi ̀ la ̀ mpoŋ ̀ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a tɔtɔg mini la ̀ mpoŋ ̀ , ɓi ̀ peeghi ̀ tikis ri ̀ n ̀ tɔɔ ̀ gh-tikis , ɓi ̀ risa ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ risii , ɓi ̀ ki nyaasag ɓɛroɓɛ ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ nyaasii .
Kɛ ̀ ɓi ɓa mum ri ̀ pon i ki yin lɛ pon anɛ lɛ ɓi kɔnɛn mi ̀ ni ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ; lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ keesii romum , a ̀ mɛ roozi ɓidɔ ̀ gsɛna yɛ ̀ ɛ kɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ nkɔ ̀ n .
Ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ki ̀ fisɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g , kɔ ̀ ɔ wey mum , kɔ ̀ ɔ yii com ki mum , kɔ ̀ ɔ lem com ki mum , ri ̀ ɓimbog ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , ɓi ri ɓi ̀ ɓasɛn ɓi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ lɛ : U ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ keesii romum a ̀ nɛ wɔ ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog yɛ ̀ ɛ wɛ ̀ ɛmi ̀ ɗ .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ti kɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ romum ki ̀ ɓe , n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ syeesyee a ̀ ri ̀ roo ̀ zi ̀ ɗi ɓidɔ ̀ gsɛna .
Lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ yii ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ti ̀ ri ̀ mii ̀ ki , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓi ghemɓɛn min ɓi fi ̀ lo kɛɛ ti lɛ , ɓisuulɛ go ̀ ri i ̀ ti ɓi ̀ si ja ̀ ŋbog ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , a ̀ cee le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ti ̀ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ .
Iru waa rim , duri i kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi ̀ , nni ti riniina ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi biri ̀ m , ti ̀ woti ̀ ɓyom ɓi ribaŋi ̀ ɓi mum a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ ɗu ̀ u ̀ ri ̀ ɓyɔ ɓi ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn .
Ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ghɛɓi ̀ cɛɓ ki ki ri lɛ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ri ̀ ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ki ŋwos , ti ̀ womzɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ dili , ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki riceesi ̀ ɗi rinɔ ɗi mɛrɔ ̀ g ɗi ̀ ti ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g , ri ̀ cɛɓ ki sa ̀ a ̀ saa , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ paa ̀ zi ̀ , ri ̀ ya ̀ aka .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , waatɛɛna Kan Yeesus Kiris kɛ ̀ ɓi ca ̀ ɗ mɛrem min lɛ mɛɛ ɓɔm ̀ ɓɔm ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi mɛ ̀ mu ̀ u ̀ , lɛ di ɓi kaa ̀ kaa ri ̀ yɛ ̀ y ɗi ɓiɓan ɓin ̀ .
Gha ̀ ɓkiina ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ kpɔ ̀ gkpɔ ̀ g ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , kɛ ̀ ɓi nyolɛn ri nyi ɓi mom ̀ zɛ ̀ n mɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ mɔ ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki righerɛ ̀ n .
Ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ ɗi ri lɛ ɗi tini ̀ nyi lɛ a ɗiɗi ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m kɔlɛ ŋwaa ̀ mbog a ̀ nɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗii ɗi tee ̀ sɛɛ ɓi , nyii ɗiɗi ̀ lɔŋ lɛ ɓi ̀ nya ̀ a .
Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ɗiɗi ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi lɛ a ̀ sɛɛti ̀ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yin ɓii ̀ ɗiɗii , roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki yin ɓii ̀ ɗiɗii ɓyom lɛ ɓus ɓu ̀ s ɓus a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi lɛ a ̀ sɛɛti ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ɗiɗi ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓisuulɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ gha ̀ ɓka ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ɗiɗi ɓyom a ̀ nɛ ̀ n .
Wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ri ̀ ghɛn anɛ u ̀ ri ̀ lɛ u ̀ yɔ ̀ m n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say a ɓɛ ̀ gan ? A ̀ a soo ri ̀ n ̀ si ̀ i ̀ rɛn ɓi ki ̀ say kii , a ̀ a soo kpi ̀ i ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki seesee masa ̀ wi ̀ i ̀ , nni a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ki si ̀ i ̀ rɛɛ ɓi ki ̀ say kii kɛ ̀ ɛ kpi ̀ , lɛ Kan a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ a ̀ le ̀ nle ̀ m nyi .
Ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ ti a ̀ ghɛngi ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ ŋwos ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ceerɛɛ ri ̀ ɓɛm ̀ bog , ŋwaa ̀ mbog nyii ghɛngi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ŋwos ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m lɛ ɓɛ ri lɔŋ com ki ̀ fog , mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ konaagh ki yii ̀ com ki a fe ̀ feg ɓi nɗem wi ̀ i ̀ .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ghaghasi go ̀ n a ki ̀ ki fɔlɔɔ ɓisuu Kan , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ɗiɗi ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m a ɗiɗi ɓyɔ ɓisuu Kan , lɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ fala ̀ g Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n ; ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti kɛ ̀ ɛ ɗi , a ̀ ti kɛ ̀ ɛ ɗi ɓisuu Kan , nyi girig a ̀ ti a ̀ fala ̀ g Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n .
Kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ si a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ ghɛɓki ̀ ɓi ki ̀ rɔɔ kii ki nyimiɗ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ wula ̀ g ɓisuu nyimiɗ .
Fɔlɔɔ yɛɛ lɛ i ti ghɛghɛ ̀ ɓ , ti ghɛghɛɓ ɓisuu Kan , i ti ̀ ki wii , ti ̀ wii ɓisuu Kan , nni fɔɔnnɛ tya ̀ a soo ghɛghɛ ̀ ɓ , tya ̀ a ki soo cuu , ti ̀ wooghrɛɛ lɔŋ ɗi Kan .
Lɛ Kiris a ̀ wugha ̀ , a ̀ ki ghemɓɛn lɛ di a ɓa Kan a ̀ nɛ a ̀ la ̀ mii lɛ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ loŋ ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ cem .
Nni wɔ ̀ ɔ yɔmgi goni ɓisuucɛ ? Nsoo ̀ lɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ sɛɛtag goni lɛ la ? Ɓi ̀ si ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ rɛlii ɓɛyɔ ̀ m ɓi ki ̀ kpana ki ɓɛyɔ ̀ m ki Bɛ ̀ ll .
Lɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : Kan a kpaaghi lɛ : N ̀ ɗi ̀ cem , ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ri mɛ ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ gh mɛ ̀ ɗu asu , mum bimiɗ a ̀ la ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ , Bɛ ̀ ll a teɗ ri ̀ kem .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ si nyimi ̀ ɗ yɛɛ ɓii ̀ re ̀ sii Bɛ ̀ ll cɛɓ ki a ̀ ghɛɓka ̀ .
Ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ min ki ca ̀ ri kiɓan ki rifii ̀ fi ̀ ɓɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ ri ̀ faa ̀ fa ̀ lɛ ̀ n , ɗi zɔɔ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ s ; n ̀ ɗɛli wu ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ teri ̀ wu ri lɛ ; kɔ ̀ ɔ ki ̀ kiɓan ki ki ri lɛ ki kɛɓti ̀ goni fi ̀ ɓa ̀ g nsoo ̀ lɛ ki tini ̀ nyi lɛ a kpi ɓi ki ̀ ɓe .
Mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yii kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ yi lɛ ɓi Yeesus Kiris com kidɛŋ ki yin ɗi ki ̀ syeg ɓi kɔmiɗ , wɔ ̀ lɛ i ŋwaa ̀ ghɛɛ lɛ com kidɛŋ ki ri ri ̀ ki ̀ syeg , com ki ̀ n ki ghay lɛ ki ti ri ̀ ki ̀ syeg ɓisu wi ̀ i ̀ .
I u ̀ ɓeɓsii goni n ̀ ɗem ɓi ri ̀ kuu ɗi ɓiɗila ̀ g ɗidɛŋ ɗi u ɗiɗi , di u ̀ re ̀ sii ti ̀ ɓi n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ; u ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ kɔ ̀ rii ɗyomzɛ ̀ n lɛ kɔ ̀ ɔ ki ̀ lɛ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ Yeesus Kiris a ̀ wugha ̀ ɓisu wii a ɗyaŋ ̀ lɛ ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓiɗila ̀ g .
Com ki mi ̀ nii ghɛɛ lɛ ki ri lɛ syeesyee , ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ki ɓaa ̀ com ki kɛɛ ki lɛ ɓi totog ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓin kiɓe mii ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll ki yin kiɓan ki riɗi ri ̀ ri ̀ nɔ , ki ri lɛ ri ̀ saaɗ ri ̀ fyo ̀ oog , ri ̀ ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ ɓi Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ki ti ki fala ̀ g .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ki ̀ ki Kiris ki ̀ say ɓiko ̀ o ̀ wi ̀ n , Bɛ ̀ ll a woki kirɔɔ ri ̀ nyi , ɓum ɓɛ ki sɛki nyi .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ min kikaa ̀ lɛ ti ki ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓyɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki lɛ fyo ̀ oog a ɓa , ɓi ki fa ti ɓisi ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m i ̀ te ̀ ɗ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
Kɔ ̀ ɔ yogsi kisay ki Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓiɗila ̀ g . Ki ri lɔŋ saaɗ lɛ ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ri kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ syeg , wɔ ̀ lɛ ki ɓeɓtɛɛ lɛ mum a ɗi com di ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki ri lɛ ki kɛɓti ̀ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ fi ̀ ɓa ̀ g .
Ki ̀ ɓan ki ki ri syeesyee a ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki ri lɛ , kɔ ̀ ɔ ɗi ɓyɛn , kɔ ̀ ɔ nɔ mɛrɔ ̀ g , u ̀ lɛg com ki ki ri lɛ ki kɛɓti ̀ goni fi ̀ ɓa ̀ g .
Fe ̀ g a ̀ nɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗyɔɔ ɗi faa wɔ ̀ ɓi ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ , ɓeŋa nyi ɓisu wɔɔ , ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll . Ma ̀ a ̀ gh ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ falɛn nyimiɗ zɔɔ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki a ̀ teri n ̀ ɗɛli lɛ a ki ki ̀ ɓan .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ i ŋwaa ̀ ɗii ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓidɛŋ ri ̀ i ̀ ris ɓi nɗem , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fa nyi bɛ ̀ lɛn ɓisuulɛ a ̀ ki ̀ i ɓi kiɓan kin ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓi nɗem ; fɔɔnnɛ ki ̀ ɓan kice ̀ m ki mum a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ ki ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓi nɗem ki ri ki ̀ ɓe .
Ɓi ̀ si ɓɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ghɛɓsii ɓɛroɓɛ ɓɛ ri kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , lɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ca ̀ rɛn ɓi-ɓwɛɗ waa ; tyɛ ̀ ki kaa lɛ ti ki ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓyɛɛ puɓsi ɓi ̀ si nɗem .
Mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ si a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ puɓsii geni nɗem ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki ki rɔɔtɛɛ , lɛ a sii ̀ rag nyi ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
Ɓisuulɛ Kiris a ̀ kaagha ̀ ɓi com ki lɛ kɛɛ puu ̀ pu ̀ ɓsi ̀ nyi n ̀ ɗem , wɔ ̀ lɛ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : Ti ̀ fena ti ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ feefengi ̀ wɔ ̀ ti syɔnga ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ .
Kɔlɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓɛ loka ̀ ki ̀ ka ̀ ni , ɓi kanɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓisuulɛ ɓyɛɛ fa ɓi ̀ si ɗyomzɛ ̀ n , lɛ di ti ɓa ri ̀ dya ̀ ɓɛn ɓi bee i ̀ ri ̀ ni ̀ ɗ ɗi nɗem , ri ̀ ri ̀ fɔɔsi ̀ ɗi nɗem ɗi mɛ ̀ ka ̀ ni ̀ mɛ ti mɛ fala ̀ g .
Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a falag kini ̀ ri ki nɗem , a ̀ ki fɔɔsag mɛrem , a ̀ fa mi ̀ ni i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ ɓi woo ̀ ghrɛn ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m win ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ kɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ngi Yeesus Kiris .
Lɛ di mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓasɛn jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ bog lɛ ɓi kemzi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ Seŋi Kan wi ̀ s Yeesus Kiris .
Fɔɔnnɛ gha ̀ agha ̀ ɓɓɛɛna mi ̀ ni ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ri ̀ syeesyee a ̀ nɗem fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Kiris a ̀ gha ̀ ɓka ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓisuu rikem ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll .
Mɛ ̀ n ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni lɛ Kiris a ̀ ti n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say a Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n lɛ a resi lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a roozag mɛka ̀ g mii , a ̀ ki si ̀ i ̀ rag mɛka ̀ g mɛ a ̀ fagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓaa ɓɛ ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ .
