Geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ Kan wi ̀ s Yeesus Kiris yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m . A ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n .
Roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ a ̀ si ̀ i ̀ rag mi ̀ ni lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ nghaaghagsi ̀ di nla ̀ alamɓɛ ̀ n Yeesus Kiris a ̀ ri ̀ , ri ̀ le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ teka ̀ fe ̀ g a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ nyamɛn fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ,
ki ̀ ɓan kifog nnyɛɛ mɛ re ̀ sɛn ɓigomi ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ kanga ̀ , lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ a tɔka ̀ lɛ kɛɛ kilɛ ̀ n , fe ̀ g a ̀ nɛ ̀ n innɛ ɓɛ mɛ re ̀ si ɓilɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m lɛ ɓyɛɛ gherɛn Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ki ki ̀ nyi mɛ ̀ wog .
Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n cɛ ̀ ncii , a teɗ ri ̀ kem fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ lɛ Yeesus Kiris . A ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n .
Mɛ ̀ Pol a ̀ nɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ n ̀ ɗeŋiyɛn lɛ mɓa n ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom a Yeesus Kiris lɛ ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ Sostɛn a ̀ geni wi ̀ s .
Ti ̀ ka ̀ ni ki ̀ seŋi ki Bɛ ̀ ll ki ki ri a Kɔrɛŋt , ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ tɛnɛn ɓi Yeesus Kiris ɓi ɗu ̀ m ɓɔ yɛɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ reŋiyɛn lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓa ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ rereŋi ɗii ɗi Kan wi ̀ s Yeesus Kiris ɓaa soo ri ̀ fe , lɛ Yeesus a ̀ ri ̀ Kan wa ̀ a ̀ , nyi ti ̀ Kan wi ̀ s .
Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ Seŋi wi ̀ s ɓɛɛ ̀ Kan Yeesus Kiris ɓɛɛ fa mi ̀ ni lɛ ri ̀ geesɛ ̀ n ri ̀ fyo ̀ oog .
Mɛ ̀ ɛ nfafa Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n kɛ ̀ ɛ nfɔy ɓisu win , lɛ geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛ i ̀ falɛ ̀ nga ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin ɓi Yeesus Kiris .
Ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ ɓi Kiris , ɓi ̀ mɛ teɗ ɓɛma ̀ a ̀ gh ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ ɓiisɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɛ seesee ki ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ , ri ̀ ri ̀ yi ɗi ɓiɓan .
Lɛ ri ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ɗi ɓiɓan ɓi ɓi seesee cɛɓ ki Kiris ɗi mɛ ɓag ga ̀ ŋ ri i ̀ te ̀ ɗ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ com kidɛŋ ki kaarɛɛ ti ̀ ɓi mini ɓi ri ̀ ɓoŋ ɗi ɓi ɓoŋɓoŋ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki Yeesus Kiris a ̀ Kan wi ̀ s a ̀ ri re ̀ sɛn ti .
Nyi yɛɛ ri mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ si ̀ i ̀ raagh a ̀ kpaŋ a ri ̀ sugtɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓi ɓa kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ ɓɛy mi ̀ ni mii ̀ , ɓi ŋwos a Yeesus Kiris a ̀ Kan wi ̀ s .
Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ mi ̀ ni lɛ ɓi ghɛɓ ɓɛ ̀ ra ̀ rɛn ri Man wii ̀ Yeesus Kiris a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ Kan wi ̀ s , a ̀ ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ roo ̀ za ̀ g mɛ ̀ ka ̀ g mii .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , n ̀ tɔɔgh mi ̀ ni ɓi ɗii ɗi Kan wi ̀ s Yeesus Kiris lɛ , wooghrɛɛna jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , yɛ ̀ ɛ gasɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ɓaana ɓɛ ̀ ra ̀ rɛn kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ ra ̀ rɛ ̀ n , ɓi ̀ ɓa nɗem wufog ri ̀ fe ̀ g bogtɛ ̀ n .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , ɓisuulɛ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓi naa i ̀ Kilowee ɓɛ nkpaa mɛ ̀ lɛ , ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ paa ̀ zi ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n .
Nkɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ nkpaa ̀ yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ , ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ : Ri ̀ wa ̀ a ̀ nɛn mii ̀ u ̀ kpaa lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ŋwaa ̀ Pol ; roa ̀ nɛ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ŋwaa ̀ Apolos , roa ̀ mbog lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ŋwaa ̀ Sefas , roa ̀ dɛŋ ti ̀ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ŋwaa ̀ Kiris .
Kiris a ̀ ti nya n ̀ la ̀ ngakɛn ? Gi ̀ n Pol a ̀ wugha ̀ nya ɓi kɔrɔs ɓisu win ? Nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ɓaɓta ̀ ka ̀ nya mi ̀ ni ɓi ɗii ɗi Pol gi ̀ n ?
N ̀ faa Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n lɛ m ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓti ̀ gha ̀ ɓi kibog ki ɓi mi ̀ ni i ki cee ɓi lɛ ɓɛ ̀ Kirispus ɓɛɛ ̀ Gayus .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ wa ̀ a ̀ dɛŋ u ̀ yin lɛ u ̀ kpaa lɛ ɓɛ ɓaɓti ̀ gha ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓi ɗii ɗyɛ ̀ m .
M ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓti ̀ gha ̀ ti ̀ girig naa i ̀ ɓum i ̀ Sitefanas ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛmbog , n ̀ -yii ɓi nko ̀ o m ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓti ̀ gha ̀ ti ̀ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ .
Ɓisuulɛ Kiris a ̀ romga ̀ y ɓi mɛ lɛ mɓa ̀ a ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓti ̀ ɓum , wɔ ̀ lɛ a ̀ romga ̀ y mɛ ̀ lɛ nkakali Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ , n ̀ ki ki ̀ kiɓan kin ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓito ̀ ki ̀ , lɛ di kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa yɛ ̀ ɛ kɔrɔs a ̀ Kiris a ̀ ri ̀ com ki zɛy .
Ɓisuulɛ ri ̀ la ̀ a ̀ la ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi kɔrɔs ɗi ri ki ̀ ɓan ki kiye ̀ g ɓisuu ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɗyaŋi ̀ , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓisuu ɓisi ɓɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ cɛɓ , ɗi ri i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu Bɛ ̀ ll .
Lɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : N ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ yogsii ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ wom ̀ zɛɛ , n ̀ ki ti ̀ i ̀ si riyi ɗi ɓɛyii ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan .
Nni ŋwaa ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n im ̀ be ? N ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna im ̀ be ? Nni n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -nyoey anɛ ɓi ziinɛ a ̀ ri ̀ fe ? Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ re ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓumɓɛ ɓi ziinɛ ɗi ri ki ̀ ye ̀ g .
Lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓi ziinɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi lɛ ɓɛ yi Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗyaa ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ɗyɛɛ ̀ re ̀ eresɛ ̀ n , nni Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kɔ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ a ghɛɓsi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ gherɛɛ nyi , ri ̀ ki ̀ ye ̀ g ki kiɓan ki ɓi ̀ sii ̀ la ̀ alamɓɛ ̀ n .
Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛɛ ̀ tɔtɔg da ̀ m yi ɓiɓan , Gi ̀ rɛg yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ tɔtɔ ̀ g ɗyomzɛ ̀ n .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ sii ̀ la ̀ alam ̀ ɓɛ ̀ n Kiris a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ kpanga ̀ ɓi kɔrɔs aɗyoo , ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki ri ki ̀ ɓan ki kɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛkɛɓti ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n fi ̀ ɓa ̀ g , ki ɓa ki ̀ ɓan ki kiye ̀ g ɓisuu ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ reŋigha ̀ , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n lɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpaŋ lɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , Kiris a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ nyi i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu Bɛ ̀ ll , nyi ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ɓisuulɛ ki ̀ ɓan kice ̀ m ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ i ki pisɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ye ̀ g ki kiɓan , ɓi ri ̀ ghɛn ɗi ɓum , ki cee ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓum , ki ɓɛ ghɛɛ i ̀ kɔ ̀ g wu Bɛ ̀ ll mii ̀ , ki cee i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu ɓum .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , ghɛɛna lɛ , ɓi mi ̀ ni ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ , ɓum ɓɛ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɓɛ tɔɔ ɓi , ɓi ri ̀ ghɛn ɗi ɓum , ɓɛ ̀ te ̀ teɗ ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ tɔɔ , ɓum ɓɛ mii ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki tɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ziinɛ yɛɛ ̀ seesee lɛ ɓi ̀ ye ̀ g ɓi ɓiɓan , lɛ a fa ɓum ɓɛ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n n ̀ too ̀ ri ̀ ɗ , a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ n ɓyom ɓi ɓi ri kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , lɛ a fa ɓɛ ̀ te ̀ teɗ n ̀ too ̀ ri ̀ ɗ .
Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ nga ̀ ɓyom ɓi nnyuŋi ̀ ɓi ɓi ziinɛ , ri ̀ ɓyom ɓi ɓum ɓɛɛ ̀ sɛɛsɛɛ ̀ ti ̀ , ɓi ɓi yin ɓɛ bimiɗ ɓɛ ɓyom lɛ , a ghaasi ɓyom ɓi ɓi ri lɛ gi ̀ n i ɓyom , ɓyom ɓi zɛy .
Lɛ di mum kɛ ̀ ɛ nyi ̀ nɛn ca ̀ g ɓi dwey ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ra ̀ ɗka ̀ mi ̀ ni ri ̀ Yeesus Kiris a ̀ ki ki ̀ lɛ Kiris a ɓa ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗis , fɔɔnnɛ ti ̀ ti ɓum ɓɛ saaɗ ɓi mis mii lɛ Kiris ; ti ̀ ti ɓi nɗɛli wulɛ ti ghɛɓ cɛɓ ki tɛnɛn , ti ̀ ki ɓa ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ ̀ ko ̀ rɛn ɓi ki ̀ ɓe .
Fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ kɔ ̀ ni kalɛn , a kaa ̀ ka ̀ lɛ ̀ n ɓi Kan ɓi ɗu ̀ m .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ n ̀ -yu ̀ gha ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin lɛ nghagsi mi ̀ ni kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ ki ̀ ɓan a Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ a ri ̀ nyam , m ̀ ɓagha ̀ y ɓi ri ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓi ɓi yeesɛɛ ri ̀ wog , nsoo ̀ lɛ coo ɗyomzɛ ̀ n .
Lɛ n ̀ ɗenga ̀ ɓi nɗem wɛ ̀ m lɛ ma ̀ a yi ɓi kiɓan kidɛŋ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki n ̀ ɗi ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin , i ki cee ɓi lɛ Yeesus Kiris , ki ki ɓa lɛ Yeesus Kiris a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ kpanga ̀ ɓi kɔrɔs .
Fɔɔnnɛ m ̀ ɓagha ̀ foo a lɔ ̀ ŋkin lɛ ri ̀ i ̀ kɔ ̀ g , ri ̀ i ̀ ris , n ̀ ki ni ̀ niŋi lɛ kpa ̀ g kpa ̀ g kpa ̀ g .
Ri ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɗyɛm ̀ , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi n ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ , ɓi ɓagha ̀ ɓi ri ɓɛ ̀ syeesyee ɓɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ ɓala ̀ g yi ̀ ɓi ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓum , ɗi ki syo ̀ gi ɓɔ mɛ ̀ rem , ɓi ɓagha ̀ lɔŋ ɓiɓan ɓi N ̀ ghay a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll yɛɛ rere ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ saaɗ a ̀ nɛ mii ̀ , ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wii .
Lɛ di ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗin ɗyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ saagh n ̀ to ɓi ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓum , ɗyɛɛ saagh lɔŋ n ̀ to ɓi-te ̀ ɗ wu Bɛ ̀ ll .
Kɔlɛ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗidɛŋ ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi ɓi ̀ sii ̀ re ̀ resi ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ ristɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɛ mɛ kadɛ ̀ n ; ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗin ̀ ɗi yin ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓi ziinɛ , nsoo ̀ lɛ ɗi mɛfo ̀ m mɛ ɓi ziinɛ , mɛ mɛɛ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ mɛ ̀ ti ̀ i ̀ siyɛn .
Ɓi ̀ sii ̀ kakali ɓum ki ̀ ɓan ki ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ɗi ɗi rimi ɗi ki ɓa ɗi nyamɛn ; ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗin ̀ ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ loka ̀ ki ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ni abɛ ̀ y ɓisuu rikem ɗis , di zii ̀ ka kilɛn ɓi .
Nsoo ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗifog ɗi ɓi mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m mɛ ɓi ziinɛ ɗi yigha ̀ ɓi ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗin ̀ ; i ki lɛ mɛɛ yi ɗyɔ , di mɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi lɛ mɛ ghɛri ̀ Kan a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ kemi ̀ ɓi kɔrɔs .
Fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : Com ki ɗis ɗi ghɛnga ̀ ɓi , com ki i ̀ ree ̀ wu woka ̀ ɓi , ki n ̀ ɗem wu mum wu feka ̀ ɓi , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ pe ̀ gsɛ ̀ nga ̀ kɔ ɓisuu ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ keesii nyi .
Ɓi ̀ si ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ mɛ re ̀ si ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗin ̀ ri ̀ N ̀ ghay , ɓisuulɛ N ̀ ghay a ̀ ti a ̀ timgi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , nsoo ̀ ɓɛ ̀ fe ̀ g ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ rimɛn lɛ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ .
Ghɛn yɛɛ ri lɛ a ̀ yi com ki ki ri ɓi nɗem wu mum , i ki yin lɛ nghay wu mum a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ wɔ ; fɔlɔɔ nnɛ fe ̀ g a ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ nyi , ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ yi i ki yin lɛ N ̀ ghay a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkis , a ̀ a n ̀ ghay wu ɓi ziinɛ wɛɛ ̀ wu ti ̀ teka ̀ , lɔŋ Nghay a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ di ti yi ɓyom ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ ɓi ̀ si ɓi geesɛ ̀ n yi ̀ i ̀ .
Nni ɓi ̀ sii yin ɓii ̀ kpaakpaa kiɓan ki ri ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi ti ̀ terii ̀ ɓi ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓum ; ti kpaakpaa lɔŋ kɔ ri ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi N ̀ ghay a re ̀ resi ɓisi , ti ̀ ki re ̀ resi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ri ̀ N ̀ ghay a ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ saaɗ ɓɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi Nghay lɛ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yin ɗi N ̀ ghay a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ teɗ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi N ̀ ghay a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ri ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ ɓyɔ ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi ri ɓi ̀ ye ̀ g ɓi ɓiɓan ɓi ri ̀ ghɛn ɗii , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ yi ɓyɔ ̀ , lɛ ɓi ri ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓɛɛ ̀ fiɓɓag ri N ̀ ghay .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ Nghay a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ti a ̀ yɔ ̀ mgi ̀ ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ; mum a ̀ ki yin lɛ a ̀ yɔ ̀ m nyi .
Lɛ ghɛn yɛɛ yigha ̀ fe ̀ g a ̀ Kan , lɛ a resi nyi ? Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ sii ri ri ̀ fe ̀ g a ̀ Kiris .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ ! Ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ , n ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ri mi ̀ ni yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ti ri ̀ N ̀ ghay a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , wɔ ̀ lɛ n ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɔŋ ri mi ̀ ni yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓumɓɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ mu ̀ u ̀ , lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ kaka ɓɔn ɓɛsa ̀ g ɓi Kiris .
Milig mɛɛ ̀ mɛ n ̀ fagha ̀ mi ̀ ni a ̀ a ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓi ɓi teri ̀ , ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi lɛ ɓi ̀ cenɛ ̀ n ɓyɔ ri ̀ ɗi , nsoo ̀ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , ɓi ̀ ka yin gi lɛ ɓi ̀ cenɛ ̀ n ɓyɔ ri ̀ ɗi , ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ kaka ɓumɓɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ mu ̀ u ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ kaka lɛ ri ̀ ya ̀ aka , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ paa ̀ zi ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n , fɔlɔɔ a yin nya ɓii ̀ re ̀ resii lɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ mu ̀ u ̀ , ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ , ɓi ghɛghɛɓ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ?
I ki ̀ bog ki ɓi mi ̀ ni ki kpaa lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ŋwaa ̀ Pol , roa ̀ mbog lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ŋwaa ̀ Apolos , ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗin ɗi ri ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗi ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ ki ̀ !
Cɛ kɛɛ ri min lɛ Apolos ? Cɛ kɛɛ ri lɛ Pol ? Ti ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛ ɓɛ kigha ̀ lɛ ɓi gherɛn Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗi mum n ̀ ce ̀ m ɗi ɓa lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Kan a ̀ fagha ̀ nyi i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ a ki .
Mɛ ̀ m ̀ ɓɛ ̀ la ̀ boo i ̀ ɓyom , Apolos a ̀ yu ̀ ki ̀ tu ̀ ɓii , ki ̀ ɓan kifog Bɛ ̀ ll yɛɛ kigha ̀ lɛ ɓyom ɓyɛɛ roo ̀ .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ li boo i ̀ ɓyom a ̀ yin com nsoo ̀ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ tu ̀ ɓii yɔ ̀ , lɔŋ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g lɛ ɓyom ɓyɛɛ roo ̀ , nnyɛɛ ri com .
Lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ li boo , ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ tu ̀ ɓii ɓɛ ri com ki ̀ fog , nni mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ teri ̀ mɛ ̀ le ̀ ɓ mɛ mɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ri ̀ ki ̀ say ki a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ .
Lɛ ɓi ̀ sii ̀ ki ̀ ki kisay ki Bɛ ̀ ll n ̀ ɗaŋ , mi ̀ ni yɛɛ ri dɛm i Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓi ̀ ki ɓa mɛɛ mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a toŋto ̀ ŋ .
Ɓi le ̀ g a ̀ geesɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ , nnɛ n ̀ -ya ̀ ghɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ gɔ ̀ ŋgɔ ̀ m ki mɛɛ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ syeesyee a ̀ n ̀ toŋi ̀ -ɓi ̀ toŋ , nni ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ toŋi ̀ ɓi ki ̀ gɔ ̀ ŋgɔ ̀ m kin ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ ; wɔ ̀ lɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ kɔ ̀ rii ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ ri ̀ kuu ɗi kitoŋ ɗi a toŋtoŋ mii ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ yin ɗi i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ a ̀ ya ̀ ghɛ ̀ n ki ̀ gɔ ̀ ŋgɔ ̀ m kidɛŋ ki ki yin ki ki ti ki ̀ ya ̀ ghɛn , kɔ yɛɛ ri lɛ Yeesus Kiris .
Nsoo ̀ mum a ̀ a toŋi ɓi ki ̀ gɔ ̀ ŋgɔ ̀ m kin ̀ ɗi ̀ gol , nsoo ̀ ri ̀ swiɗ a ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni , nsoo ̀ ri ̀ gɔ ̀ g yi lo ̀ nlomɛn , nsoo ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ geŋ , nsoo ̀ ri ̀ baɓ , nsoo ̀ ri ̀ zyoe ̀ y ;
ki ̀ say ki mum n ̀ ce ̀ m ki ri lɔŋ ɓii ̀ re ̀ sɛɛ . Ɓisuulɛ ŋwosi ɓɛyɔ ̀ m a ̀ ri ki ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ yi ki ̀ say kin ̀ , lɛ ŋwos anɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ re ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ɗuu ; fɔɔnnɛ ɗuu ɗyɛɛ ri bii ̀ re ̀ sii riɓa ɗi kisay ki mum n ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ki ̀ toŋ kii ki ri ɓii ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓi kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɗig , a ̀ ɓii ̀ teri ̀ mɛ ̀ le ̀ ɓ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ki ̀ toŋ kii ki ɗiigh , a ̀ ɓii ̀ mɛ ̀ mi mɛle ̀ ɓ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , nyimiɗ a ghɛɓ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ faŋii yi ̀ ɓi ɗu ̀ u ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ yii ɓi lɛ mi ̀ ni yɛɛ ri naa i ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔrii mii ̀ , ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ N ̀ ghay a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi mi ̀ ni .
I ŋwaa ̀ wa ̀ a ̀ ghii naa i ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔrii mii ̀ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ wa ̀ agh gɛ girig nyi ; lɛ naa i ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔrii mii ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tɛnɛn , nni mi ̀ ni yɛɛ ki ri ̀ naa i ̀ nɛ ̀ n .
Mum kɛ ̀ ɛ pwa ̀ a ̀ rɛn , i ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ ɓi mi ̀ ni a fe ̀ feg lɛ nyii ri ri ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓi ziinɛ , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ghali ̀ ki ̀ ye ̀ g lɛ di a ɓa min ɗi ɗyomzɛ ̀ n .
Ɓisuulɛ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓi ziinɛ ɗi ri ki ̀ ye ̀ g ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , fɔɔnnɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ti a ̀ wɔɔsa ̀ g ɓum ɓɛ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɓi mɛ ̀ ghe ̀ y maa mɛ ɓɔmiɗ ɓɔ yɛɛ kpaŋii ̀ ri ̀ mɔ .
Ri ̀ ti lɛ : Kan a ̀ yii ɓɛ ̀ fe ̀ g ɓɛ ɓum ɓɛ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ri ri ̀ ɓɔ , a ̀ ki yi lɛ ɓɛ ̀ fe ̀ g ɓɛn ̀ ɓɛ yin com .
Fɔɔnnɛ mum a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ki foŋi ̀ ri ̀ kem ɗii ɓi ɓum , ɓisuulɛ ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ri ɓiŋki ̀ n .
Nsoo ̀ Pol , nsoo ̀ Apolos , nsoo ̀ Sefas , nsoo ̀ ziinɛ , nsoo ̀ cɛɓ , nsoo ̀ ri ̀ wu , nsoo ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki , nsoo ̀ ɓi ɓi cɛɓ ki kɛɛ ̀ yu ̀ yuiy , ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ri lɛ ɓyom ɓin .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ mi ̀ nii wooghrɛɛ ri ̀ Kiris , Kiris nyii wooghrɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ min ɓisi ki ̀ seesee yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛ Kiris , ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛkɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ ɓɛ ɓiɓan ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nyamga ̀ .
Nni com ki ɓum ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓoŋɓoŋ a ɓɛ ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -ɓyom ki ri lɛ , ɓɛɛ resi lɛ ɓɛ ri ɓumɓɛ ɓum ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ tyweeyii .
Ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ , n ̀ tɔɔgh ɓi com nsoo ̀ lɛsa ̀ g lɛ mi ̀ ni yɛɛ yɔm ̀ mɛ ̀ , nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ yɔm ̀ mɛ ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɛ nki yɔ ̀ m mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ
lɛ n ̀ -yin ɗi bɛ ̀ lɛn ɓi nɗem . Ki ̀ ɓan kifog a ̀ a fɔlɔɔ yɛɛ kii lɛ mɓa lɛ sɛɛghi sɛɛghi , n ̀ -yɔ ̀ mi ̀ mɛ ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ Kan .
Ɓisu wi ̀ n mii ̀ nnɛ kɛ ̀ ɓi yɔ ̀ m kiɓan kidɛŋ di ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ka kpaŋ ɓi , di Kan a ̀ ka yu ɓi , nnyɛɛ ri ɓii ̀ tɛɛ ̀ zii ɓiɓan ɓi ɓi ri ɓi ̀ nyamɛn a biri ̀ m , a ̀ ki ki ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ yi mɛ ̀ yiti ̀ mɛ ɓum ɓɛ ri ri ̀ mɔ ɓi mɛ ̀ rem , fɔɔnnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ faa mum n ̀ ce ̀ m mɛ ̀ sɛɛ ̀ ghsɛɛgh mɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ri ̀ mɔ .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , ɓisu win nnɛ ma ̀ a teri da ̀ ɗki ̀ yin ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ɓi Apolos ri ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ , lɛ i ɓi ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ tii ki ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ kis , fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ ɓii ̀ yilaagh yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓ kɛ ̀ ɓi ceesi nɗe ̀ e ̀ wu ɓiɓan ɓi ɓi ri ɓi ̀ ka ̀ nɛn , kɛ ̀ ɓi faafa ̀ lɛ ̀ n mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ rikem lɛ ɓi ̀ i nsuugh ɓi jɛ ̀ m i ̀ tɛɛnɛ a ̀ tɛɛnɛ , ɓi ̀ sɛɛti ̀ tɛɛnɛ a ̀ mbog .
Ɓisuulɛ ghɛn yɛɛ kpaa wɔ ̀ lɛ u ̀ ceeghii ɓum ɓɛmbog ? Cɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ kɔ ki ki yin com ki ɓɛ fagha ̀ wɔ ̀ n ̀ fayɛn ? I ɓɛ ki fagha ̀ wɔ ̀ n ̀ fayɛn , ɓisuucɛ nnɛ u kaakalɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ kali lɛ ɓɛ fagha ̀ ɓi wɔ kɔ n ̀ fayɛn ?
Ɓi ̀ mɛ wura ̀ g , ɓi ̀ ki ti ɓɛ ̀ guŋgum ; mi ̀ nii mɛ ɓɔg mɛfo ̀ m , ɓi ̀ si kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ ɓɔɔ ̀ gh , i ɓya ̀ a ri ̀ kɔm ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓa mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m mɛnce ̀ m lɛ ɓi ̀ si girig ti lami nɗaŋ ri mi ̀ ni .
Lɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ nfe ̀ ki lɛ , ɓi ̀ si ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ɓɛ Yeesus Kiris , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ ɓi ̀ si i ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu siito ̀ n fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓumɓɛ ki ̀ ɓan kaa ki ti ki ̀ renɛn lɛ ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓɔ ki ̀ woli ̀ . Ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ rɛsi ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ziinɛ , ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ titom ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓum ɓɛɛ see ̀ see yɛ ̀ ɛ ti yɛɛyɛɓɛ ̀ n .
Ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ghalɛn ɓiye ̀ g lɛ Kiris , wɔ ̀ lɛ mi ̀ nii ri ri ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɓi Kiris ɓi ɗu ̀ m ; ɓi ̀ sii ri ɓɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔg , mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ te ̀ teɗ ; ɓum ɓɛ nyaa ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ si ̀ mi ̀ ni , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛ sɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ti ̀ ɓi ̀ si .
Ɓi ̀ sii wowog lɛ ri ̀ za ̀ y , ri ̀ ki ̀ nɔli , ɓi ̀ si nyoo zɛy , ɓɛ kukwi ̀ y ɓi ̀ si , ti ̀ ki rereni zi , a ̀ kpaŋ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki .
Ti woowolɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ sii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ ri ntɔɓ lɛ ti say ri ̀ ɓya ̀ g ɓis , ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ ̀ sɛɛsɛmgi ̀ ɓi ̀ si , ɓi ̀ sii maŋma ̀ ŋ ɓɔ , ɓɛ ri yeeyeesi ̀ ɓisi , ti ̀ si ̀ i ̀ si ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ nɗem .
Ɓɛ ri to ̀ tog ɓisi ki ̀ ɓe ɓi nyoo , ɓi ̀ sii fɔɔfɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ si ̀ ɓɔ mɛ ̀ rem , a ̀ kpaŋ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , ɓi ̀ sii mɛ ghay fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ so ̀ gtɛ ̀ n ɓi ziinɛ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ gham ɓi ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Nsoo ̀ n ̀ ka ̀ nii ̀ mi ̀ ni fɔlɔɔ , ki yin lɛ nfa mi ̀ ni n ̀ too ̀ ri ̀ ɗ , ki ri lɔŋ lɛ nɗeɓ mi ̀ ni yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɔn ɓɛm ɓɛ nɗem .
Ɓisuulɛ nsoo ̀ ɓya ̀ a ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ tɔɔsi ̀ m n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ɓi cɛɓ ki ɓi ghɛghɛɓ ɓi Kiris ɓi ɗu ̀ m , ɓi ̀ yin lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓa ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ki ̀ tuu , lɛ mɛ ̀ yɛɛ yali mi ̀ ni ɓi Yeesus Kiris ɓi ɗu ̀ m , ri ̀ Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ n ̀ ghagsi ̀ gha ̀ mi ̀ ni .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ tɔɔgh min mini lɛ , ɓi pisɛn mɛ ̀ .
Ɓisuu kiɓan kin ̀ nnɛ n ̀ ɗomga ̀ y mi ̀ ni Timote a ́ man wɛm ̀ a ̀ n ̀ ɗem a ̀ nɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tyweeyi ri nyi ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ; nnyɛɛ ri mi ̀ ni bii ̀ yitii ɓiɓan ɓi mɛ ̀ ɛ nnɔ ̀ ɔnɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ ɓi cɛɓ kɛ ̀ m ki ɓi Kiris , ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi nki re ̀ resi ja ̀ ŋ bimiɗ ɓi ɓi ̀ seŋi ɓi Kiris ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n ɓɛ ntumɛɛ ri ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ɗi ɓidaŋa ̀ ri ̀ fe ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ ma ̀ a kpaŋdi ɓi a lɔ ̀ ŋkin .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ i ki kɔni Kan , di n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ fyaŋzii foo ki kpaŋi ̀ ; fɔɔnnɛ ma ́ a yi ɓi lɔŋ lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓɛ ̀ daŋa ̀ daŋa ɓɛn ̀ ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ girig ɓii ̀ yii ̀ com ki ɓɛ ri ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ ɓɛ ki .
Ɓisuulɛ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll ki yin kiɓan ki ɓito ̀ ki ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ŋwɔm , ki ri lɔŋ kiɓan ki mɛki ̀ ki ̀ .
Cɛ ɓi kɔ ̀ ŋkɔn kɔm ̀ lɛ twiɗ ? Ɓi kɔ ̀ ŋkɔn lɛ n-yu a lɔ ̀ ŋkin ri nkpas gi ̀ n n-yuiy lɛ ri ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n ri ̀ nɗem wu tɛ ̀ tɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ?
Ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa ja ̀ ŋ bimiɗ lɛ ki ̀ tɔɓi ̀ kin ̀ ki ri ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n ; kiŋce ̀ m ki ki ɓa le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ ki ti kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ghɛnɛn nsoo ̀ a ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n . Lɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaaghi lɛ , ki ̀ bog ki ɓi nɗaŋ win ki nteri gili seŋi ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ daŋa ̀ ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɓi waatɛn ɓilɛ ̀ ɓi ̀ lɛ di ɓɛɛ pisi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ a nki ̀ i ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n .
Ɓi san a ̀ nɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ , nsoo ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ mi ̀ ni fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ ri nyoo yɛ ̀ m , n ̀ ɗi ̀ lɔŋ mini ja ̀ ŋbog ɓi nghay wɛ ̀ m ; fɔɔnnɛ m ̀ mɛ yɔ ̀ m ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ a nki ̀ i ri ̀ kuu ɗi kiɓan ɗin ̀ , lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ kali lɛ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ wɔɔ foo ja ̀ ŋbog .
Lɛ ɓi ɗii ɗi Kan Yeesus , ri ̀ ɓi-te ̀ ɗ wii , ti ̀ ri taŋzɛ ̀ n , mɛ ̀ m ̀ ɓa ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n ɓi nghay ;
ri ̀ kuu ɗi mum ɗin ̀ ɗi ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ kaɓ ɗyɔ ri ̀ Sata ̀ n , lɛ mɛ ̀ mu ̀ u ̀ mii mɛɛ ɗyaŋ di fɔɔnnɛ nghay wii wɛɛ ghɛn ̀ cɛɓ ɓi ŋwos a Kan Yeesus .
Ɓi ki ̀ ki ɓidaŋa ̀ ɓi zɛy ! ɓi ̀ yii ɓi lɛ maa nwi ̀ ɗ lɛsa ̀ g a ̀ ti a ̀ ɓɔgsa ̀ g n ̀ ku ̀ ŋ wu ɓɛ tɔɓi ?
Pisiina fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ fi nwi ̀ ɗ fi ɓi ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ fyɔ abɛ ̀ y di fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ɓa n ̀ ku ̀ ŋ wu nyɔn wu ɓɛ tɔɓi , lɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ nwi ̀ ɗ ɓisuulɛ , ɓɛ mɛ wey Kiris a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ maa jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wi ̀ s a Paska ̀ .
Nni ti ki ̀ ina min tica ̀ ɓ tin ̀ , wɔ ̀ lɛ tyɛ ̀ ki ki ̀ tyɔ ri ̀ fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ fi nwi ̀ ɗ , nsoo ̀ lɛ nwi ̀ ɗ a ki ̀ ɓu ̀ u ̀ si ̀ , ri ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ gɛn , ti ki ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ tis tin ̀ ri ̀ bi ̀ rɛs i ̀ nɛ i ̀ yin ɗi nwi ̀ ɗ , ɓi ri ̀ tɛn , ri ̀ ɓi saaɗ ɓi ɗu ̀ m .
Mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ka ̀ nii ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ wɛ ̀ m lɛ , kɛ ̀ ɓi ra ̀ rɛn ri ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ti ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g ,
nni a ̀ a ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ti ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g ɓɛ ɓi ziinɛ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ri ̀ ki ̀ see ki-kum , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ wiiwi ̀ i ̀ , nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ nu ̀ n ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ kpaa lɛ kɛ ̀ ɓi ra ̀ rɛn ɗi ɓɔ ; i fɔɔnnɛ kaa ri ̀ , ɓi ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ n nya min yɛɛ ri ɓi ziinɛ .
Com ki mɛ ̀ ɛ nkɔ ̀ ngi lɛ nkpaa ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ wɛ ̀ m ki nɗi ̀ lɛ , ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi kira ̀ rɛɛ ri ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ , a ̀ ree ̀ ghre ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ n lɛ Ki ̀ ristɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ɓan kifog a ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ti ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g , a ̀ fa nɗem ri ̀ i ̀ kum , a ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ɓi ̀ nu ̀ n , a ̀ keesi ̀ ɓɔlɛ , nyi ki ̀ nɔɔ ̀ -mɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ g nsoo ̀ lɛ wiiwi ̀ i ̀ ; ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi gi ki ̀ ɗisɛɛ ri ri ̀ kuu ɗi mum ɗi ̀ n .
Ki ̀ ɓan ki lɛ n-yɔm ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n ki seesee gi ̀ ɓi mɛ , mɛ ̀ ɛ nti ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓi ɗu ̀ m ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ yɔ ̀ mi ?
Ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓi dan , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ yɔ ̀ mi gɛ ɓɔ ; lɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : Pisiina ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki mum ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n .
Ɓi cɛ nnɛ ɓi ̀ ti ɓi ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g lɛ , i wa ̀ a ̀ dɛŋ u ̀ paa ̀ zii ri ̀ go ̀ ni , u ̀ kɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ a ɓumɓɛ zɛy lɛ ɓɔ yɛɛ yɔm ̀ mi ̀ ni kɔ , kɛ ̀ ɓi reŋi ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓɔ yɛɛ yɔm ̀ ?
Yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ ɓi ̀ yii ɓi lɛ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɔ yɛɛ ri ɓii ̀ yɔ ̀ mi ziinɛ ? I mi ̀ ni yɛɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ yɔ ̀ mi ziinɛ lannɛ ɓɔɔ ɓiɓan ɓɛ zɛy ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ yag mi ̀ ni ri ̀ pe ̀ gsɛ ̀ n ?
Ɓi ̀ yii ɓi lɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ yɔ ̀ mi ɓum ɓɛ titom ? Bɔ ̀ ɓ yaŋ min ɗi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi cɛɓ ki fɛ ?
Nni la yɛɛ ri min lɛ , i ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ paa ̀ zi ̀ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ko ̀ mi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi cɛɓ ki fɛ , ɓumɓɛ ki ̀ seŋi ki Kiris ki tɔɔgh ɓi com ri ̀ ɓɔ ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ ɓi ̀ rɛsi ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ yɔm ̀ ?
N ̀ kpaa ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ lɛ ɓi wog n ̀ too ̀ ri ̀ ɗ . Fɔlɔɔ a re ̀ sii yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ mum a ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n a ̀ yin ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n nsoo ̀ bog , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ a ̀ pe ̀ gsɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓɛgeni wa ?
Nni geni ɓɛɛ ̀ geni ɓɛ ti ɓɛ rɛɛsa ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ m ɓɛ ki rɛli ɓɛnce ̀ m ɓi mis mɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n !
Ki ka ti zɛ ̀ ɗ ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin , lɛ ɓi ɓa ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kpaaghi-kpaaghi ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n ; ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓi ̀ yin kɔm ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ ni ̀ ɗ nɗem lɛ ɓi caɗ kɛ ̀ ɓi nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti kiɓan ki ŋwaa ̀ sɛ ̀ raagh ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ? Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓi yin kɔm ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ ca ̀ ɗ lɛ ɓɛɛ pumzi mi ̀ ni ?
I u ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ gi ̀ ki ̀ fiɓii , lɔŋ mi ̀ ni yɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ɓiɓan ɓi ɓi ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi , ɓi ̀ yiiyi ̀ i ̀ ɓyom ɓi ɓum , ɓum ɓɛ ̀ nce ̀ m lɛ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓin .
Ɓi ̀ yii ɓi lɔŋ lɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ɓiɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓiɓan , ɓaa ɓa ɓi ri i ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll ? Kɛ ̀ ɓi pwa ̀ a ̀ rɛn , a ̀ tumɛɛ lɛ , ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ghɛghɛɓ cɛɓ ki tifin , a ̀ kpaŋ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ nu ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ti ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g ,
ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kɔra ̀ g ri ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ baŋi ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kɔra ̀ g ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛ ̀ baŋi ̀ , a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ di ̀ ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ wiiwi ̀ i ̀ , ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ri ̀ ki ̀ see ki-kum , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ nɔɔ ̀ -mɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ g ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ti ̀ fena , a ̀ kpaŋ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ zyaa ̀ zyaa , ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓaa ɓa ɓi ri ga ̀ ɓ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ɓum i ̀ dɛŋ i ̀ nɛ ɓi mi ̀ ni , i ̀ ɓagha ̀ mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ ɓum mɛ ̀ n ; wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛ soogha ̀ mi ̀ ni , ɓɛ tɛɛ ̀ zi ̀ mi ̀ ni , ɓɛ ki ki ̀ lɛ ɓi ɓa lɛ saaɗ ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓi ɗii ɗi Kan Yeesus Kiris , ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu N ̀ ghay a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll wi ̀ s .
N ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ n ̀ ki ̀ com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki n ̀ kɔ ̀ ni , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , a ̀ a ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓyɛɛ ri mɛ ̀ ri ̀ gɛɓsɛ ̀ n ; n ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ n ̀ ki ̀ com ki n ̀ kɔ ̀ ni , nni ma ̀ a ca ̀ rɛn ɓi lɛ mɓa n ̀ kpa ̀ n a com .
Ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓi ri ɓisuu ɗu ̀ m , ɗu ̀ m ɗi ki ɓa ɓisuu ɓiɗila ̀ g , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ki yogsii ɓyom ɓi kiɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓin ̀ ; wɔ ̀ lɛ nyoo i ̀ mum i ̀ yin nki ̀ yɛn ɓisuu cɛɓ ki tifin , i ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ yɛn ɓisuu Kan , Kan a ̀ ki ɓa ɓisuu nyoo i ̀ mum .
Nni Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghe ̀ mzi ̀ gha ̀ Kan a ɓi ̀ loŋ , a ̀ ghe ̀ mzii gɛ girig ɓi ̀ si ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wii .
Ɓi ̀ yii ɓi lɛ nyoo yin yi ri ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɓ ɓi Kiris ? Nni n ̀ ɗi ̀ nya lɛ n ̀ teɗ ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɓ ɓi Kiris lɛ nghaasi ɓyɔ ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɓ ɓi giɓ a ri ̀ ɓa ̀ mɓa ̀ ?
Nsoo ̀ ŋwos bog ! Ɓi ̀ yii lɛ syeesyee lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ra ̀ rɛɛ ri ̀ giɓ a ri ̀ ɓa ̀ mɓa ̀ , a ̀ ti nyoo bog ri ̀ giɓ anɛ ̀ n , ɓisuulɛ ki ri ki ̀ kaliyɛn lɛ : Ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ɓum ki ri ɓii ̀ ghali ̀ ri ̀ mu ̀ u ̀ ɗi ̀ fog .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ra ̀ rɛɛ ri ̀ Kan ɓɛ ɓii ̀ ɓaa nghay wu ̀ fog ɓɛɛ ̀ nyi .
Lɛɛghna cɛɓ ki tisɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g ! Lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓimbog ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi mum a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ ki ̀ , ɓi ti ɓyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ko ̀ m nyoo yi ̀ i ̀ , wɔ ̀ lɛ i ŋwaa ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ tii cɛɓ ki tisɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g , di a ̀ ki ̀ i ki ̀ ɓe ki kɛɛ yogsi nyoo yi ̀ i ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ yii ɓi lɛ , nyoo yi ̀ n i ri ̀ naa i ̀ Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ki ki ri ɓi mi ̀ ni , ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ mi ̀ ni ? Fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ la ̀ mii ti ̀ ɓi mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ .
Ɓisuulɛ ɓɛ kweɗka ̀ mi ̀ ni du ̀ ne n ̀ kɛŋɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ; fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ kemzii Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ ri ̀ nyoo yin , ri ̀ n ̀ ghay win lɛ ɓi ri ɓyom ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ti ̀ cee min ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ̀ i ntɔghii ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ wi ̀ n ; ki ri ki ̀ rɔɔ lɛ , mum a kɔri kɛ ̀ ɛ wɛy giɓ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ɓi ɗi lɛ cɛɓ ki tisɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ sa ̀ a ̀ , baŋi ̀ bimiɗ i ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ ri ̀ giɓ wii ̀ a ̀ nyimi ̀ ɗ , giɓ bimiɗ a ̀ ɓa ri ̀ yii wii ̀ .
Baŋi ̀ i ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ roo ̀ zii ɓiɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ i giɓ wii ̀ , giɓ a roo ̀ zi ̀ girig ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ i yii .
Giɓ a la ̀ mii ɓi nyoo yi ̀ i ̀ nyimi ̀ ɗ , lɔŋ yii yɛɛ lamii yɔ ̀ , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ baŋi ̀ i ̀ la ̀ mii ɓi girig nyoo yi ̀ i ̀ nyimi ̀ ɗ , lɔŋ giy yɛɛ lamii yɔ ̀ .
Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi lɛ bog a celi roa ̀ mbog di ki yin lɛ ɓi ̀ ka wooghrɛɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ lɛ ɓi celɛn ɓi maa ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓi falɛn ɓi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n , ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ sugtii ki ra ̀ rɛɛ , lɛ Sata ̀ n kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa lɛ a ̀ ghɛn ki ̀ rɔŋiɗ ki lɛ a fee ̀ ghrɛn mi ̀ ni ɓisuulɛ mɛ ̀ rem min mɛ ɓanɛɛ ɓi .
Ki ̀ ɓan ki n ̀ kpaa ki ̀ n , ki yin kiɓan ki ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ka ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ n , ki ri lɔŋ kiɓan ki ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g .
Ɓi mɛ ̀ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ n lɛ di ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓaa ɓaa yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ ; nni wɔ ̀ lɛ mum nce ̀ m a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ nyi lɛ a kila ̀ g ; a ̀ fa roa ̀ nɛ ri ̀ kuu ɗi kiɓan ɗi , a ̀ fa roa ̀ mbog ri ̀ kuu ɗi kiɓan ɗidɛŋ .
Mɛ ̀ n ̀ kpaa ɓɛ ̀ kwɛ ̀ y ri ̀ mɛ ̀ kpɔɓ mɛ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ lɛ , ki ri ki ̀ rɔɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ kɔri fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog i mɛ ̀ rem maa mɛ ɓanɛɛ ɓi , ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ wɔlɛɛ , lɛ ki pɔɔzii ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ ki ̀ rɔɔ lɛ mum a wɔlɛn , a ̀ cee lɛ a wuwu dudug .
Ɓi ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ wɔlɛn , n ̀ faa ɓɔ n ̀ siŋdɛn - nni a ̀ a mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ki faa n ̀ siŋdɛn wunce ̀ m , lɔŋ Kan yɛɛ faa : Giɓ kɛ ̀ ɛ ghasɛn ri yii wii ̀ ;
i a ̀ ki ghasɛɛ ri ̀ nyi , a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ di riwɛy , nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓɛ pegsɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ɓan ki ki ghasi ̀ gha ̀ nyi ri ̀ yii , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ baŋi ̀ i ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ki na ̀ ɓi giy .
Com ki mɛ ̀ n ̀ kpaa ɓum ɓɛmbog ki yin lɛ Kan yɛɛ kalii , lɔŋ mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ yɛɛ kpaa , ki ri lɛ : I ki ̀ ristɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ giɓ anɛ a ̀ yin ngherɛ ̀ n , nni giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ gherɛɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ asu ɓɛ ghɛghɛ ̀ ɓ n ̀ ɗaŋ , nyii ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ki na ̀ ɓi giɓ anɛ ̀ n .
I ki ̀ ristɛ ̀ n a ̀ giɓ a ri ̀ ri ̀ yii a ̀ nɛ a ̀ yin ngherɛ ̀ n , yii a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ki gherɛn lɛ ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ asu ɓɛ ghɛghɛ ̀ ɓ naa bog , giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ki ɓe ̀ ni yii a ̀ nɛ ̀ n .
Ɓisuulɛ baŋi ̀ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ yin ngherɛ ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tɛnɛn lɛ giɓ wii ̀ , giɓ anɛ a ̀ yin ngherɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ ntɛnɛn lɛ yii wii ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ristɛ ̀ n ; kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ fɔlɔɔ di ɓɔn ɓin ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ ɓa yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɔn ɓɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ gherɛɛ ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll , kɔm ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ tɛnɛn ɓi syeesyee a ̀ ri ̀ kali ̀ .
I ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yin ngherɛ ̀ n a ̀ kɔ ̀ ni lɛ a ghasɛn ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ri ɓi ri ̀ wɛy ɗi ̀ nyi , ɓɛ caɗ nyi a ̀ ghasɛ ̀ n ; i ki ghɛnɛɛ fɔlɔɔ , n ̀ gherɛ ̀ n a ̀ baŋi ̀ nsoo ̀ lɛ a ̀ giɓ , a ̀ yii ̀ di nka ̀ ŋɛn ɓi ri ̀ wɛy ɗi ̀ n ; lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ si lɛ ti ghɛɓ ɓi fyo ̀ oog ɓi ɗu ̀ m .
Wɔ ̀ ki ̀ ristɛ ̀ n a giɓ u ̀ yii la nko ̀ o wɔ ̀ yɛɛ ghɛɓsii gɛ yii wɔɔ , nsoo ̀ lɛ wɔ ̀ baŋi ̀ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ristɛ ̀ n , u ̀ yii la nko ̀ o wɔ ̀ yɛɛ ghɛɓsii gɛ giɓ wɔɔ ̀ ?
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ghɛɓ lɔŋ ɓi nɗɛli wu Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ foga ̀ nyi mii ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ nyi ; n ̀ siŋdɛn wu nfafa ɓi ɓi ̀ seŋi ɓi Kiris ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m wɛɛ ri lɔɔ .
I mum a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ kɛ ̀ rɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ nyi , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɔŋ ki rɔ ̀ ɓi ɓi kɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ n wi ̀ i ̀ ; i ŋwaa ̀ ɓagha ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ kɛ ̀ rɛɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ nyi , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ki kɛ ̀ rɛɛ .
Ki ̀ ɓan ki lɛ ŋwaa ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ kɛ ̀ rɛn nsoo ̀ lɛ a ̀ yin n ̀ kɛ ̀ rɛn , ki ghɛɓsii ɓi com , lɔŋ ri ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋ ɗi ɓidɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ɗyɛɛ ghɛɓsii .
Fɔɔnnɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓi ɓi nɗɛli wu a ̀ ɓagha ̀ mii ̀ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ nyi .
I Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ wɔ ̀ di u ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ kpa ̀ n , n ̀ ɗem wɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ cɛɛcɛɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ n wɔ ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ɗi ̀ n , wɔ ̀ lɛ i u ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ bee inɛ lɛ u pɛsɛn ɓi ri ̀ kpa ̀ n , u ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ n , kɔ ̀ ɔ ki ̀ wa ̀ ŋ .
Ɓisuulɛ n ̀ kpa ̀ n anɛ Kan a ̀ mɛ reŋi ̀ a ̀ yii ̀ di ɓi ri ̀ kpa ̀ n , a ̀ ti ŋwaa ̀ zɛy a ̀ nɛ a ̀ wooghrɛɛ ri ̀ Kan , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ Kan a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ di a ̀ yin n ̀ kpa ̀ n , a ̀ ti n ̀ kpa ̀ n a Kiris .
Du ̀ ne i ̀ go ̀ ri yi ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ kɛŋɛn fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ki ɓaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kpa ̀ n ɓɛ ɓum .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ghɛɓ lɔŋ ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi nɗɛli wu a ̀ ɓagha ̀ mii ̀ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ nyi .
Ɓi san a ̀ nɛ a ɓɔɓti ɓɛ ɓɛ ka wɛɛyi ɓi , n ̀ -yin ɗi bimiɗ a ̀ n ̀ siŋdɛn a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Kan , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ɗi n ̀ ɗi ̀ mum a ̀ nɛ ki ̀ rɔɔ ̀ -n ̀ ɗem a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ mɓa mum a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ tyweeyii , n ̀ kpaa le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ yɛɛ ri ̀ ghɛn ɗyɛ ̀ m ɗi ri .
Com ki n ̀ ghɛɛ lɛ ki rɔɔtɛɛ ki ri lɛ : Yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ tɔɓ mɛ ri lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓigomi ̀ nɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ ghɛɛ lɛ , ki ri ki ̀ rɔɔ lɛ ŋwaa rɔɓ lɔŋ ɓi nɗɛli wu a ̀ ri ̀ mii ̀ .
I u ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ giɓ kɔ ̀ ɔ kaa lɛ u ghasɛn ɗi ̀ nyi ; i u ̀ yin nwɔlɛn , kɔ ̀ ɔ kaa giɓ a ̀ nɛ u wɛy .
Kaa soo ri ̀ fɔlɔɔ , u ̀ ki ̀ i ɓi kiɓe di u ̀ wɔlɛɛ . I gɔ ̀ n i ̀ giɓ inɛ i ̀ yii ɓi baŋi ̀ i ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ wɛy , i ̀ ki ̀ i ɓi kiɓe . Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ wɔlɛn ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ tɔɓ ɓi cɛɓ kaa , nni mɛ ̀ tɔɓ mɛ ̀ n mɛɛ ̀ mɛ nkɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ ɓi lɛg .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , com ki nkɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ nkpaa ̀ ki ri lɛ , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ri ki ̀ den , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ , ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ri kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ;
ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛɛ re ̀ nɗe ̀ n ɓɛ ɓa yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ yin ɓii ̀ re ̀ nɗeni , ɓɛ ɓɛɛ nya ̀ a ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ ɓa yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ yin ɓii ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ nyaa ; ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ la ̀ lag ɓyom ɓɛ ɓa yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ yin ɗi ɓyɔ ;
ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ghɛnghɛn kirɔɔ ɓi ziinɛ , ɓɛ ɓa yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ghɛɛ ɓi kirɔɔ , ɓisuulɛ ri ̀ ɓa ɗi ziinɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ seesee ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɗi mii ̀ ɗyaa finɛn ti ɓi ̀ .
Mɛ ̀ ɛ nkɔ ̀ nkɔn kɔm ̀ lɛ , ɓi ɓa kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki kɛɛ ̀ ɗiɗi mini mɛ ̀ rem ; lɛ nɗem wu ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yin nwɔlɛn , wɛɛ ̀ cɛɛrag ri ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Kan ; ŋwaa ̀ nce ̀ m a ̀ nɛn a ̀ ki kaakaa lɛ a ki ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ri lɛ ɓi puɓsi ̀ Kan n ̀ ɗem .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ nɗem wu ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ wɔlɛn wɛɛ ̀ ɓɔmɓɔm ɓiɓan ɓi ɓi ziinɛ , a ̀ ki kaakaa lɛ a puu ̀ pu ̀ ɓsi ̀ nɗem wu giy ,
a ̀ ri ̀ yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ nɗem fɛ , nɗem fɛnii ; fɔlɔɔ yɛɛ ri girig lɛ giɓ anɛ a ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yii , nsoo ̀ lɛ gɔ ̀ n i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ka yi ɓi ɓɛbaŋi ̀ , ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ foŋi ̀ nɗem ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Kan , lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓa ɓɛ ̀ tenɛn lɛ ri ̀ ɓi nyoo yaa , ri ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ ghay maa ; wɔ ̀ lɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ wɔlɛn a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ fe ̀ feegh ɓiɓan ɓi ɓi ziinɛ , ri bee yi a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ puɓsi ̀ yii wii ̀ n ̀ ɗem mii ̀ .
N ̀ kpaa fɔlɔɔ ɓisuu kirɔɔ kin , ki yin lɛ fi ̀ ram fyɛɛ ̀ fi n ̀ ɗami mi ̀ ni , ki ri lɔŋ ɓisuulɛ di ɓi ki ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ syeesyee , ɓi ̀ ki ɓa ɓɛra ̀ rɛn ɗi Kan kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki ki ri lɛ ki yee ̀ ye ̀ e ̀ si ̀ mi ̀ ni .
I mum a ̀ ghɛɛ lɛ ki ri n ̀ too ̀ ri ̀ ɗ lɛ gɔ ̀ n yi ̀ i ̀ yɛɛ ghay i ̀ cee gba ̀ a ̀ i ̀ nɛ giɓ a ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ mii ̀ ki ̀ wɔlɛɛ , nni a ̀ ghɛɛ lɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ yɔ ̀ ki faa ̀ ɓi ri ̀ wɛy , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ i com ki a ̀ kɔ ̀ ni ; fɔlɔɔ a yin kiɓe ; ɓum ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ wɔlɛɛ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ teri bimiɗ a ̀ nɗɛli kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ̀ ka ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ n , ki ɓa lɔŋ lɛ ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗii ɗi nyimiɗ a ̀ ki ren ɓi nɗem wii lɛ a ɓeŋ gɔ ̀ n yi ̀ i ̀ nkwɛ ̀ y , di a ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ syeesyee .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ faa gɔ ̀ n yi ̀ i ̀ ɓi ri ̀ wɛy , a ̀ ki ̀ i syeesyee a ̀ ki ̀ ɓan , wɔ ̀ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ faa ɓi gɔ ̀ n yi ̀ i ̀ ɓi ri ̀ wɛy yɛɛ raŋ ̀ zii ki ̀ ki ̀ i syeesyee a ̀ ki ̀ ɓan .
I giɓ a ri ̀ n ̀ wɔlɛn , nsiŋdɛn wu riwɛy wu ka ̀ ŋi nyi ri ̀ yii ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki yii a ̀ kaka n ̀ to ɓi ki ̀ mi ̀ i ̀ gh ; wɔ ̀ lɛ i yii a ̀ wii , giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ri ̀ wɛy ɗi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ kɔ ̀ ni ; ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ lɛɛ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓi ɗu ̀ m .
Nni wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ri ̀ ghɛn ɗyɛ ̀ m , giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓiisɛɛ ki ɓaa ̀ lɛ syeesyee , di a ̀ kɔ ̀ rii fɔ ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ; nni mɛ ̀ ɛ nfe ̀ ki lɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ girig ri ̀ N ̀ ghay a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a ɓyɛn ɓi nya ̀ m yi ɓɛ funɛɛ ɓi ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi ɓinu ̀ n , ɓi ̀ sii ̀ ce ̀ m ti ̀ yii lɛ , ti ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ti ̀ konaagh ki ̀ yii ̀ , nni ri ̀ yi ɗi ti ɗi fala ̀ g mum n ̀ ca ̀ ŋa ̀ wɔ ̀ lɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ fala ̀ g i ̀ te ̀ ɗ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
I mum a fe ̀ feg lɛ a ̀ yii com , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ka konag ɓi ki yii ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ i ŋwaa ̀ keesii Bɛ ̀ ll , di ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ yii .
Nni ɓi ntɔɔ ̀ tɔɔgh wu lɛ ŋwaa ̀ ri ̀ nya lɛ a ̀ ɗi ɓyɛn ɓi nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ funɛɛ ɓi ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi ɓinu ̀ n , ɓi ̀ sii yii lɛ ki ̀ nu ̀ n ki yin ɓi ziinɛ nsoo ̀ ki ̀ fog ; Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ bog .
Nsoo ̀ ɓyom ɓidɛŋ ɓyaa ri ̀ ɓi ɗyoo , nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓi ziinɛ ɓi ɓɛɛ ̀ rereŋi lɛ bɛ ̀ ll , ɓi saaɗ a ̀ ri ̀ kpaa , ɓyom ɓi lɛ ri ̀ bɛ ̀ ll yidɛŋ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kan ɓɛdɛŋ ɓi teghɛɛ lɛɛ ̀ gwey ,
nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkis , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ bog , nnyɛɛ ri Seŋi a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , ɓisu wii nnɛ ɓi ̀ sii ̀ ghɛghɛ ̀ ɓ . Fɔɔnnɛ Kan a ̀ ri ̀ girig bog lɛ Yeesus Kiris , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g lɛ ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓyɛɛ ɓa , ɓi ̀ sii ki ghɛghɛɓ lɛ nyi .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ a ̀ a ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛɛ yi fɔlɔɔ , lɛ ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ kaka ɓɛ ̀ mɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ tɛn ri ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓinu ̀ n ɓi le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ , ɓɛ ti ɓɛ ɗila ̀ g ɓyɛn ɓi fɔlɔɔ , yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ kali lɛ ɓyɛn ɓi ̀ n ɓi ri ɓyɛn ɓi ɓinu ̀ n ; yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗem waa wu ri kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓin ̀ ɓi caɗ ɓɔ ti ̀ fin ɓi mɛ ̀ rem .
