Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ki ̀ gwey ki ɓi ɓɔ ki kigha ̀ ɓi ɓiɓan ɓi ɓyɛɛ rɔɔ ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll . Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓɛ raa ̀ rɛ ̀ nga ̀ mii ̀ ɓi ̀ loŋ ɓi-reɓ .
Ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi ri ɓi ̀ si ɓi ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ ɓi ɓiɓan , lɛ di tyɛ ̀ ki ɓa ri za ̀ y i ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓiɓan yɛ ̀ ɛ i ̀ nɛ ɓɔɔ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ yɔ ̀ .
Kɛ ̀ ɓi ghay ɓɛki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ nu ̀ n fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓi nɗaŋ waa ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ , lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : Ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki kɔri ̀ gha ̀ ɓi zi lɛ kɛɛ ɗi , ki nɔ , ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛ ̀ n nnɛ ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ aɗyoo lɛ ɓɛɛ nyuŋzɛn .
Nni tyɛ ̀ ki falɛn ɓi cɛɓ ki tisɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wa ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ falɛ ̀ nga ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ loŋ ɓi kpigha ̀ ŋwos bog ɓum ɓɛ ̀ tɔɔsi ̀ m ri ̀ tin ɗi ̀ ɓɛraa .
Tyɛ ̀ ki fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn Kan fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wa ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ feeghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi , ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ cuugha ̀ di nyoo yi taɓkii ɓɔ .
Kɛ ̀ ɓi ŋwɔ ̀ ŋwɔŋi Bɛ ̀ ll yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wa ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ ŋwɔŋwɔ ̀ ŋi ̀ gha ̀ nyi ; ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a ri ̀ wu a ̀ cuusi ̀ gha ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi kiki ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ fɔlɔɔ , lɛ ɓyɛɛ ɓa ɓi ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ ɓisuu ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ kanga ̀ ɓyɔ ɓisuulɛ ɓyɛɛ reɓ ɓi ̀ si lɛ ti ̀ mɛ wuɓsɛn ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki risugtɛ ̀ n .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yii lɛ a ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ rɛy , a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n lɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ kpi ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ ka tulɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ri mɛ ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn mɛdɛŋ , mɛ mɛ cee i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu mum . Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ti a ̀ roo ̀ za ̀ g mɛ ̀ ka ̀ g mii , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ a ca ̀ ɗ ɓi lɛ ɓi tulɛn ri ̀ mɛ ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn mɛ mɛ cee mi ̀ ni ɓi-te ̀ ɗ ; wɔ ̀ lɛ i mɛ ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn mɛ kpaŋi mi ̀ ni , a ̀ ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ re ̀ sii bee inɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ cee mɔ mii ̀ , a ̀ ki fa mini i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ ɓi cenɛn mɔ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki , mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓɛ ̀ m ɓɛ nɗem , ce ̀ liina ɓi ̀ nu ̀ n .
Nto ̀ tog ri mi ̀ ni yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n , mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ fiɓiina ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi nkpaakpa ̀ a ̀ .
Ɓeŋ a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ma ̀ a ̀ gh a ̀ nɛ ti ̀ ti ti ̀ fala ̀ g Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n lɛ nyi , a ̀ ti kɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ nya lɛ ti ɓa ɓɛ ̀ ra ̀ rɛn ɗi bwaɓ yi Kiris ? Bi ̀ rɛs i ̀ nɛ ti ̀ ti ti ̀ ɓɛki ̀ , i ̀ ti yɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ nya lɛ ti ɓa ɓɛ ̀ ra ̀ rɛn ɗi nyoo i ̀ Kiris ?
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ bi ̀ rɛs i ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ bog , tya ̀ a soo te ̀ ghɛɛ , ti ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ nyoo bog ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ sii ̀ ce ̀ m ti teteɗ ga ̀ ɓ ɓi m ̀ bobog a ̀ bi ̀ rɛs a ̀ nɛ ̀ n .
Ghɛɛna ɓɔn ɓɛ Isirayɛl ; ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ ɗila ̀ g ɓi ̀ tuwe ɓi ɓɛ woli ɓi ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛ yin nya ɓɛ ̀ ra ̀ rɛn ɗi ri ̀ ku ̀ na ɗi ɓɛ ti ɓɛ tɔngi ̀ ɓyom ɓi ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɔɔɓɔgsi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll mii ̀ ?
Fɔlɔɔ a re ̀ sii nya yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ nkɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ ɓyɛn ɓi ɓɛ funɛɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ nu ̀ n , nsoo ̀ ɓi ̀ nu ̀ n ɓyɔmiɗ , ɓi ri nya ri ̀ bimiɗ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓa a ̀ dɛŋ ?
A ̀ g ! Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓi ɓɛ ti ɓɛ funa ̀ g ɓyom ɓi ̀ n ɓisu waa a ̀ a ɓisuu Bɛ ̀ ll . Nni mɛ ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ ni ɓi lɛ ɓi ɓa ɓɛ ̀ ra ̀ rɛn ɗi ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay .
Ɓi ̀ yin lɛ ɓi ̀ ki ̀ lɛ : di ɓi nɔ ɓeŋ a ̀ Kan , di ɓi nɔ ɓeŋ a ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ yin lɛ ɓi ̀ ki ̀ lɛ : ɓi ̀ ɗi ɓi teɓe ̀ re ̀ a ̀ Kan , ɓi ̀ ɗi ɓi teɓe ̀ re ̀ a ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay .
Ti kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ ti tini Kan lɛ a ki yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ gi ̀ n ? Ɓi ̀ si yɛɛ cee nyi ɓi-te ̀ ɗ ?
Ti ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ ti ̀ ki ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ti ̀ kɔ ̀ ni , nni a ̀ a ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓyɛɛ ri ri ̀ gɛɓsɛ ̀ n . Ti ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ ti ̀ ki com ki ̀ ce ̀ m wɔ ̀ lɛ a ̀ a ki ̀ ce ̀ m kɛɛ ki ̀ ki lɛ ŋwaa sii ̀ rɛn ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
Mum kɛ ̀ ɛ kaaghi ki ̀ rɔɔ kii ki nyimiɗ , a ̀ kaa lɔŋ ki ɓɛro ɓɛm ̀ bog .
Ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ , ɓi ɗi com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ɓɛɛ ̀ ka ̀ kaɓ a fye ̀ e ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛ ̀ riighriki ̀ ɓi nɗem ɓisuu kiɓan ki righerɛ ̀ n .
Ɓisuulɛ , zi ri ̀ ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi mii ̀ , ɓi wooghrɛɛ ri ̀ Kan .
I ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yin ngherɛ ̀ n a ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ghraagh mi ̀ ni , ɓi ̀ ki gherɛn lɛ ɓi kɛn ̀ , ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɗii ̀ com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ɓɛ faa mi ̀ ni , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛ ̀ riighriki ̀ ɓi nɗem ɓisuu kiɓan ki righerɛ ̀ n .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , i ŋwaa ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni lɛ , ɓyom ɓi , ɓi ri ɓyom ɓi ɓɛ nfu ̀ nɛɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ nu ̀ n , ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ɓyɔ ki ̀ ɗii ̀ , lɛ kɛ ̀ ɓi kɛ ̀ ɓti ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ a kalii mi ̀ ni fɔlɔɔ fiɓa ̀ g ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ , nɗem wɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ fa mini bɛ ̀ lɛn .
Ki ̀ ɓan ki nkpaakpaa ki , ki seesee ɓi nɗem win wu righerɛ ̀ n wɔmiɗ , ki ri ɓisuu nɗem wu righerɛ ̀ n wu ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n . Nni ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ri ̀ ɓa ɗyɛ ̀ m ɗi n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu ki ̀ yɛn com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki n ̀ kɔ ̀ ni ɗi ri lɛ ɗi ɓa ri ̀ mɛ ̀ re ̀ e ̀ lɛ nɗem wu righerɛ ̀ n wu ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ ?
I mɛ ̀ n ̀ faa Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n ɓisuu com ki nɗiɗi ̀ , ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ toto ̀ g mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ɓe ɓi ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓi m ̀ mɛ fa Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n mii ̀ ?
Ɓya ̀ a soo ɗiɗi ̀ , ɓya ̀ a soo nɔnɔ , nsoo ̀ cɛ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓya ̀ a ki ̀ ki ̀ , ki ̀ ina ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓisuu rikem ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll .
Kɛ ̀ ɓi ɓa gɔ ̀ g i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ lɛ i ̀ kɛ ̀ ɓti ̀ nsoo ̀ muu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n nsoo ̀ muu Gi ̀ rɛg nsoo ̀ ki ̀ seŋi ki Bɛ ̀ ll fi ̀ ɓa ̀ g .
Fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ nte ̀ etee ̀ si ̀ nyoo lɛ mpuɓsi ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m mɛ ̀ rem ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓice ̀ m ; mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yin ɓii ̀ kaakaa kirɔɔ kɛ ̀ m ki mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ , nkaakaa lɔŋ kirɔɔ ki ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey lɛ di ɓɛɛ ghɛn ̀ cɛɓ .
Ɓaana ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔnɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ kɛm ̀ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ mɛ ̀ ɛ nnɔ ̀ ɔnɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ ki Kiris .
N ̀ sɛɛgh mi ̀ ni yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi yiiyita ̀ g mɛ ̀ ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , ri ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ɓe ̀ ŋɓeŋ deɓ yɛm ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ fagha ̀ mi ̀ ni yɔ .
Nni nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ , kɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ nkɔn mɛ lɛ di ɓya ̀ a yii ki ̀ ɓan ki : Kiris a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi baŋi ̀ bimiɗ , baŋi ̀ i ̀ ɓa ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi giɓ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ɓa rifo ̀ m ɗi Kiris .
Baŋi ̀ bimiɗ i ̀ nɛ yɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n nsoo ̀ lɛ i ̀ nɛ yɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaŋzi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ re ̀ sii nyi , di i ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ta ̀ m ɓi nto i ̀ yin ɗi bɔgsɛ ̀ n ɓi san a ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ rifo ̀ m ɗii .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ giɓ bimiɗ a ̀ nɛ a ki ̀ ki bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n , nsoo ̀ lɛ a kpaakpaŋzi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ re ̀ sii nyi , di a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ to zɛy , a ̀ sɛɛtii ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗii ; ki ri lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ giɓ anɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ kɛ ̀ ŋɗɛn kpuu .
Lɛ i giɓ a yin ɗi yeŋkesi ̀ ɓi nto , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ kɛ ̀ ŋɗɛɛ nto ; nni i ki ri n ̀ too ̀ ri ̀ ɗ lɛ giɓ a caa ̀ tyo ̀ ŋ tii , nsoo ̀ lɛ a kɛŋɗɛn kpuu , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ min ki waatɛɛ yeŋkesi ̀ .
Baŋi ̀ i ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi lɛ i ̀ lɔɔghrɛ ̀ n nto ɓisuulɛ , i ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki Bɛ ̀ ll , yɔ ̀ ti ̀ ri ̀ kem ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , kɔlɛ giɓ a ri ̀ ri ̀ kem ɗi baŋi ̀ .
Lɛ a ̀ a ɓi giɓ innɛ ɓɛ teka ̀ y com ki ɓɛ kigha ̀ baŋi ̀ ri ̀ kɔ , lɔŋ ɓi baŋi ̀ innɛ ɓɛ teka ̀ com ki ɓɛ kigha ̀ giɓ mii ̀ .
Ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ kigha ̀ ɓi baŋi ̀ ɓisuu giɓ , lɔŋ giɓ innɛ ɓɛ kigha ̀ ɓisuu baŋi ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki giɓ a ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ waatɛɛ com ɓi nto , ki kɛɛ ̀ re ̀ resi lɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ri ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɗi yii , lɛ ɓum ɓɛ titom .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi Kan ɓi ɗu ̀ m , giɓ a yin lɛ ɓɛ ghasi ̀ nyi ri ̀ baŋi ̀ , yɛ ̀ ɛ baŋi ̀ i ̀ yin lɛ ɓɛ ghasi ̀ yɔ ̀ ri giɓ
ɓisuulɛ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ giɓ a ki ̀ lɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ com ki ɓɛ teka ̀ y ɓi baŋi ̀ , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ baŋi ̀ i ̀ ti i ̀ yala ̀ g yi ̀ ɓi ɗu ̀ m ɗi giɓ , ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ti ɓi ɓala ̀ g yi ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ fiɓiina ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ; ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ nya lɛ giɓ a ɓɔŋzi Bɛ ̀ ll di a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ to zɛy ?
Ri ̀ ɓa ɗi ɓum ɗyɔmiɗ ɗyɛɛ ̀ re ̀ resi mini lɛ , ki ri ntoo ̀ ri ̀ ɗ lɛ baŋi ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ raɓsi tyo ̀ ŋ .
Kɔm ̀ lɛ fɔlɔɔ a ri ̀ ri ̀ kem ɗi giɓ , ɓisuulɛ tyo ̀ ŋ ti ra ̀ ɓ ti falɛ ̀ nga ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ giɓ lɛ tyɛɛ ɓa nyi fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ki kɛɛ gheg nyi n ̀ to .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ i mum a ̀ kɔ ̀ ni ɓi lɛ a nyolɛn ɓi ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ yii ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ sii yin ɗi ki ̀ syɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ kin ̀ , nsoo ̀ ɓi ̀ seŋi ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi yin girig ri ̀ kɔ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ cee ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki n ̀ ɗɔ ̀ gsɛɛ mi ̀ ni ki , n ̀ -yin ɗi i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ n ̀ sɛg mi ̀ ni ɓisuulɛ mɛ ̀ gha ̀ da ̀ min mɛ maa ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ ɓi koɓsɛn ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓin ɓi ɓisyɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , mɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ti com ki lɛ ɓi ɗyoŋ ̀ a ̀ cee fɔlɔɔ .
Ki ̀ ɓan ki asu ki ri lɛ , nwoki lɛ ɓi ̀ ti lɛ , i ɓi ̀ taŋzɛɛ ri ̀ gha ̀ da ̀ , n ̀ la ̀ nag wu ɓa ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n , mɛ ̀ nki gherɛɛ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ga ̀ ɓ .
Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ kɔmiɗ lɛ mɛ ̀ la ̀ nag mɛɛ ɓa ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n , lɛ di ɓumɓɛ ɓi nɗaŋ win ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ si ̀ i ̀ rɛn ɓɛɛ yilɛn .
Ɓi ̀ ti lɛ i ɓi ̀ taŋzɛɛ , a ̀ a ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ ti ɓi ̀ teki ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ ti a ̀ ru ̀ na ̀ g ki ̀ ɗii ̀ ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓii ɓi nyimiɗ ɓi le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ wowo ̀ g za ̀ y , roa ̀ mbog n ̀ ŋwaŋɛn mɛrɔ ̀ g .
Ɓi ̀ yin gi ri mɛɛ mɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ ki ̀ lɛ , ɓi ̀ ɗi , ɓi ̀ nɔ wɔɔ ? Gi ̀ n ki ̀ seŋi ki Bɛ ̀ ll kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓi sɛɛsɛɛ ̀ ti ̀ , ɓi ̀ ki kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ ɓi woo ̀ wo ̀ gsi ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ com n ̀ too ̀ ri ̀ ɗ ? Nni cɛ kɛɛ ̀ ki nkpaa min mini ! N ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ nya lɛ nsɛg mi ̀ ni ? A ̀ g ! Mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yin lɛ n ̀ sɛg mi ̀ ni ɓi ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ , ri ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɗi mɛ ̀ n ̀ teka ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Kan ɗyɛɛɗi mɛ ̀ n ̀ ghagsi ̀ gha ̀ mi ̀ ni . Lɛ Kan Yeesus , ɓi-ru wu ɓɛ tɔkɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi , a ̀ teka ̀ bi ̀ rɛs
fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ lɛ , a ̀ mɛ fa Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n nni a ̀ ɓɛka ̀ yɔ ̀ , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Nyoo yɛ ̀ m yɛ ̀ ɛ ri lɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ ri n ̀ fayɛn ɓisu win , ki ̀ laaghna ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓi ̀ yita ̀ g mɛ ̀ .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ a ̀ teka ̀ girig ɓeŋ di ɓaa le ̀ gsi ki ɗii ̀ , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Ɓeŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ nyɔɔnyɔn a ̀ ri ̀ ra ̀ rɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ lɛ ri ̀ ɓum ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi bwaɓ yɛm ̀ ; ɓi ̀ yita ̀ g mɛ ̀ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ɓi ̀ nɔɔ nyi .
Ɓisuulɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ɓi ̀ ɗii bi ̀ rɛs i ̀ nɛ , ɓi ̀ ki nɔ ɓeŋ a ̀ nɛ , ɓi kakali riwu ̀ ɗi Kan , a ̀ kpaŋ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ri yu ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɗii ̀ bi ̀ rɛs nsoo ̀ lɛ a ̀ nɔ beŋ a ̀ Kan yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi , a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ teri ̀ bɛ ̀ lɛn ɓi nyoo , ri ̀ bwaɓ yi Kan .
Nni mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a fiɓɓɛn nyimiɗ di fɔɔnnɛ a ɗi bi ̀ rɛs , a ̀ nɔ ɓeŋ ,
ɓisuulɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɗii ̀ , nsoo ̀ lɛ a ̀ nɔ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ fiɓii nyoo i ̀ Kan , a ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ , a ̀ ɗi , a ̀ ki nɔ ncɛ ̀ m wi ̀ i ̀ a nyimi ̀ ɗ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓɛ ̀ roroɓ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ lɛnlɛm ɓɛ teghɛɛ mii ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n ; kɛɛ ̀ ki ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey i ̀ mɛ ki cuu .
I tya ̀ a ti ti ̀ fiɓɓa ̀ g ɓi ̀ sii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ , di Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ yin ̀ lɛ a ̀ yɔ ̀ mdi ̀ ɓi ̀ si .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Kan a ̀ ti a ̀ yɔ ̀ mgi ̀ ɓi ̀ si lɛ a reɓ ɓi ̀ si , lɛ di tyɛ ̀ ki teɗ bɛ ̀ lɛn nɗaŋ ri ziinɛ .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , fɔlɔɔ yɛɛ ri lɛ , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓi ̀ taŋzɛɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓooɓoŋ ̀ ɗɛ ̀ n mi ̀ ni ri ̀ mi ̀ ni .
I mum a wowog za ̀ y , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɗii ̀ a mɛɛ mii , lɛ di kɛ ̀ ɓi syo ̀ ŋ yi mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ ncɛ ̀ m ɓi nyoo , di ɓi ̀ taŋzɛɛ . N ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ pe ̀ gsɛɛ ɓiɓan ɓimbog yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki ki seesee ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ki ti ki fala ̀ g ɓum i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu ki ̀ yɛn , mɛ ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ ni ɓi lɛ ɓi rɔɓ lɛ du ̀ ŋdu ̀ ŋ .
Ɓi ̀ yii lɛ , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓi ̀ ɓagha ̀ di ɓi ̀ ka yi ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓɛ syoŋsyo ̀ ŋga ̀ mi ̀ ni lɔŋ lɛ duri yaa tani , a ɓi ̀ nu ̀ n ɓi ɓi yin lɛ ɓi too ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki n ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni lɛ , mum a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ kpaa ̀ lɛ : Yeesus a teɗ n ̀ cɛ ̀ m di ki ri lɛ a to ̀ tog ri i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu Nghay a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , mum a ̀ ki yin lɛ a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Yeesus a ̀ ri ̀ Kan , di ki yin lɛ Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay kɛɛ tinii nyi lɛ a kpaa ̀ fɔlɔɔ .
Mɛ ̀ faa ̀ mɛ Nghay mɛ ri mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ ̀ kuu , ki ̀ ɓan kifog N ̀ ghay a ̀ nɛ a fafa mɔ , a ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ bog .
Ɓi ̀ say ɓi ri mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ ̀ kuu , ki ̀ ɓan kifog Kan bog innɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ sasa ̀ y .
Ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ki ̀ yɛn ɓi ri mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ ̀ kuu , wɔ ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll bog yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ ki ɓiɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ki ti ki ghɛna ̀ g yɛ ̀ ɛ mum bimiɗ ɓi bimiɗ a ̀ ri ̀ fa a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ki ̀ rɔɔ ki ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Lɛ Nghay a ̀ ti a ̀ fala ̀ g ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n , m ̀ bobog a ̀ N ̀ ghay a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ fa roa ̀ mbog ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓi riyi ɗi ɓiɓan .
M ̀ bobog a ̀ N ̀ ghay a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ fa roa ̀ dɛŋ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , a ̀ fa roa ̀ mbog i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu wɔ ̀ ɔwɔɔ ̀ zi ̀ yɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ roroɓ .
A ̀ fa ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu ki ̀ kiyɛn da ̀ m , a ̀ fa roa ̀ mbog i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu kpaakpaŋzi ̀ yɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ re ̀ sii nyi ; a ̀ fa roa ̀ dɛŋ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ a yi ri ̀ ghasi ̀ ɗi lɛ , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay , ri ̀ syeesyee a ̀ N ̀ ghay , a ̀ fa ti ̀ roa ̀ dɛŋ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu to ̀ toghɛn ɓi ̀ ke ̀ neke ̀ ne ̀ ɓi ɓito ̀ ki ̀ a ̀ ki fa roa ̀ dɛŋ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ a tɛɛ ̀ zi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓyɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɓi ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓin ̀ .
Lɔŋ m ̀ bobog a ̀ Nghay a ̀ nɛ ̀ n nnyɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ɓiɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ ki ka ̀ aka ̀ ɓsi ̀ ɓyɔ lɛ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n mii ̀ a ̀ fa com ki a ̀ kɔ ̀ ni .
Ɓisuulɛ nyoo i ̀ mum i ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ bog , wɔ ̀ lɛ i ̀ teghɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɓ ; ki ̀ ɓan kifog , nsoo ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɓ ɓin ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi teghɛɛ ba ̀ li ̀ , ɓyɛɛ toŋi lɔŋ mbobog a ̀ nyoo , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ Kiris a ̀ ri ̀ girig .
Lɛ ɓi ̀ si ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , ti ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓtɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi mbobog a ̀ Nghay , lɛ ti ɓa nyoo bogtɛ ̀ n nsoo ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , nsoo ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , nsoo ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kpa ̀ n , nsoo ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin ɓɛkpa ̀ n , fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ sii ̀ ce ̀ m ti ̀ nɔgha ̀ m ̀ bobog a ̀ Nghay a ̀ nɛ ̀ n .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ nyoo i ̀ mum i ̀ yin lɔŋ kika ̀ ɓ ki ̀ fog , i ̀ te ̀ ghɛɛ ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɓ .
I i ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ waa ri ̀ lɛ wu kpaa lɛ : Yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yin ca ̀ g , n ̀ -yin kika ̀ ɓ ki nyoo , fɔlɔɔ a yin lɛ a ̀ re ̀ g wɔ lɛ wɛɛ ɓa lɔŋ kika ̀ ɓ ki nyo ̀ o ̀ .
I i ̀ ree ̀ wu kpaa lɛ : Yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yin ɗis , n ̀ -yin kika ̀ ɓ ki nyoo , fɔlɔɔ a yin lɛ a ̀ re ̀ g wɔ lɛ wɛɛ ɓa lɔŋ ki ̀ ka ̀ ɓ ki nyo ̀ o ̀ .
I nyoo bimiɗ ya ̀ a ri ̀ lɔŋ lɛ ɗis , di mum a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ wog ɓi ̀ ɓan la ? Gi ̀ n i nyoo bimiɗ ya ̀ a ri ̀ lɔŋ lɛ i ̀ ree ̀ , di lannɛ mum a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ wog mɛ ̀ ru ̀ u ̀ mɛ ɓyom ?
Ɓi saaɗ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ foga ̀ ki ̀ ka ̀ ɓ ki ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi nyoo lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki kɔnga ̀ nyi .
I ki ̀ ka ̀ ɓ kɛɛ ɓa lɔŋ kifog di nyoo i ̀ yin gi lɛ i ̀ ɓa .
Nni ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɓ ɓi ri ɓi ̀ te ̀ ghɛn , nyoo i ̀ ɓa lɔŋ bog .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɗis ɗi yin lɛ ɗi kpaa ca ̀ g lɛ : N ̀ tɔɔgh ɓi com ri ̀ wɔ ̀ ; nsoo ̀ n ̀ to , wu yin lɛ wu kpaa mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ yin mɛ ri ̀ gɛɓsɛ ̀ n .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɓ ɓi ɓi nyoo ɓi ɓyɛɛ ̀ seesee ̀ rɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ri kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , ɓi ri ri ̀ coo gɛɓsɛ ̀ n .
Ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɓ ɓi ti ̀ ɓiisɛɛ ɓi ki kuughraagh lɛ ɓi ri bimiɗ a ̀ com , ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓi ti ̀ ti ti ̀ ɓiisa ̀ g ki ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi lɛ syeesyee ; ɓi ̀ sii ri lɔŋ lɛ , ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɓ ɓi ɓi yin loo ̀ ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɓ ɓi lɛ ɓɛ ɓuŋɓu ̀ ŋ ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ sii ɓiisɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋɓeŋi ri ɓyoo tikɛɗ .
Kɔmiɗ lɛ ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɓ ɓi ɓi ri ɓyoo ɓika ̀ ɓ ɓyɔɔ tɔɔgh ɓi lɛ ɓɛɛ nyaa ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ si ̀ ɓyɔ fɔlɔɔ ; ki ̀ ɓan kifog Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ nyoo le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ ɓyom ɓi ɓi yin ɗi ri ̀ kem , a ̀ fa ɓyɔ coo rikem ,
lɛ di gasɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa ɓi nyoo i ̀ mum , ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɓ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓyɛɛ ɓa lɔŋ ɗi za ̀ y i ̀ nɛ lɛ ɓyɛɛ ɓee ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ n ɓyɔ ri ̀ ɓyɔ .
I ki ̀ ka ̀ ɓ ki ̀ fog ki ɓi nyoo i ̀ mum kɛɛ ̀ wowog rikɛŋ , ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɓ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi wog ri ̀ kɛŋ nɗaŋ ri ki ̀ ka ̀ ɓ kin ̀ . I ɓɛɛ ̀ nyaanyaa ̀ si ̀ ki ̀ ka ̀ ɓ ki ̀ fog ɓi nyoo i ̀ mum , ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɓ ɓimbog ɓi kaɓɓɛ ̀ n ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ ki ki ̀ ka ̀ ɓ kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ wowo ̀ g .
Ɓi ̀ ri ̀ nyoo i ̀ Kiris , mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ ɓi mi ̀ ni a ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ka ̀ ɓ kii lɛ ri ̀ mum , a ̀ ɓa ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ɗii .
Nni Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ rɛsa ̀ ka ̀ ɓum ɓi ki ̀ seŋi kii fɛlɛ ̀ : Asu ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom , ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ ɓɔ ̀ ɓ , ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɓɛ yuiy ɓi nɗɛli wu kiraa , ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , ri ̀ fa ɗi lɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ kiki da ̀ m ɗi nɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ , mɛ ̀ faa ̀ mɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ riwɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zi ̀ ɗi ɓɛ ̀ roroɓ , ri ̀ ri ̀ ghɛɛghɛ ̀ ɓsi ̀ ɗi ɓum ɓɛ nyi ̀ inyi ̀ g , ri ̀ ɗi ̀ yi ɗi rila ̀ mi ̀ , ri ̀ ri ̀ to ̀ to ̀ g ɗi ɓito ̀ ki ̀ mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ ̀ kuu .
Ɓi ̀ ghɛɛ foo di ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ? Gi ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ? Ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ri nya ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ? Gi ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛɛ ti ɓɛ kila ̀ g da ̀ m ?
Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ri nya ri ̀ ri ̀ fa ɗi lɛ ɓɛɛ wɔɔ ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zi ̀ ɓum ? Ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛɛ ̀ to ̀ tog nya ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ ̀ kuu ? Gi ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛɛ ri nya ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ ɓɛ tɛɛ ̀ zi ̀ ɓum ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓin ̀ ?
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ za ̀ y ri ̀ mɛ ̀ faa ̀ mɛ mɛ ɓiisɛɛ ki ̀ rɔɔtɛɛ . N ̀ ki ri ̀ ti ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ re ̀ sii bee inɛ i ̀ ɓɛghɛɛ ki ̀ rɔɔ .
Nsoo ̀ ma ̀ a to ̀ to ̀ g ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ɓi ɓum , ri ̀ ɓi ɓum ɓɛ titom , i n ̀ -yin ɗi n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n n ̀ ɗi ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ keŋ wu wɛɛ ̀ to ̀ to ̀ g , nsoo ̀ lɛ jeŋi inɛ yɛɛ ̀ yooyo ̀ o ̀ .
Nsoo ̀ ma ̀ a ri ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ fa ɗi Nghay ɗi lɛ nkpaa ̀ kpa ̀ ŋzi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll , ma ̀ a soo yii da ̀ m yi ɓiɓan yice ̀ m yi a ri ̀ nyam , n ̀ ki yi ɓiɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , nsoo ̀ ma ̀ a ri ̀ kɔm ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi ɗi ri lɛ ɗi pɛsi ̀ do ̀ n lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ , pɛsɛn ja ̀ ŋ inɛ i ̀ ri ̀ , i n ̀ -yin ɗi n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n , di n ̀ ɗi ̀ lɔŋ com ki zɛy .
Ma ̀ a soo teri i ̀ kum wɛm ̀ wu ̀ ce ̀ m , n ̀ ka ̀ ɓsa ̀ g ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sogha ̀ sogha lɛ ɓɛɛ ɗiɗi mii ̀ , ma ̀ a soo ki faa kɔm ̀ nyoo yɛ ̀ m lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɗig ɓi ɗuu , i n ̀ -yin ɗi n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n , fɔlɔɔ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ a ghɛɓsi ɓi mɛ com .
N ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ni ̀ ɗ ɗi nɗem , nyi ri ̀ ki ̀ puɓi ̀ -n ̀ ɗem , kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa ri m ̀ mi ̀ i ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n ; n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ yin ɗi kalɛn , kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa ri ki ̀ re ̀ eresɛ ̀ n .
N ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ti kɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ kiɓan ki kitɛ ̀ ŋtɛ ̀ ŋ , n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ti kɛ ̀ ɛ pa ̀ g ɓi kaagh , kɛ ̀ ɛ wog bim , kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa ri mɛ ̀ nyaa ̀ ka ̀ ,
n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ti kɛ ̀ ɛ wog kirɔɔ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ mɛ ̀ ɓe ̀ e mɛ ri , a ̀ ti a ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ ra ̀ g lɔŋ ri ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ri lɛ saaɗ .
N ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a cenag ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ ghera ̀ g ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ ki ni ̀ ɗki nɗem ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m .
N ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ yin ɗi ri ̀ le ̀ g ; ri ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ ɗi ɓiɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ɗi ri le ̀ g , ri ̀ to ̀ to ̀ g ɗi ɓi ̀ ke ̀ neke ̀ ne ̀ ɓi ɓito ̀ ki ̀ ɗi leg , ri ̀ yi ɗi ɓiɓan ɗi sugtɛ ̀ n ,
ɓisuulɛ ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan yɛ ̀ ɛnɛ ti ̀ yii , ti ̀ ki kpaakpaŋzi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ dɛŋ yɔ ̀ riyɔ ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , yɛ ̀ ɛ com ki ki rɔɔtɛɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki lɛ ɓɛ fen mii ̀ ki ɓii ̀ kpaŋi ̀ , ki ki ri ta ̀ ta ̀ ki leg .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ m ̀ ɓagha ̀ ŋwɔɓti , ki ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ kɛm ̀ , fe ̀ g wɛ ̀ m ri ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗyɛm ̀ , ɓi ɓagha ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi riŋwɔɓti nni wɔ ̀ lɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kpaga ̀ mum , n ̀ ca ̀ ɗ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi riŋwɔɓti ɓi ̀ n .
Ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , ti seesee ɓyom lɛ ri ̀ ii ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ ghɛnɛ ̀ n ɗi ŋwaa ̀ ti a ̀ ghɛna ̀ g ɓi ŋwii wɔ ̀ lɛ , ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ , ti ̀ konaagh gɛ ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ lɛ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n . Ɓigomi ̀ nɛ n ̀ -yii ki ̀ den , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ n ̀ konaagh gɛ nyi ki ̀ yii ̀ , lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ nyii yigha ̀ mɛ ̀ .
Ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi kaka ɓi ri ɓiraa lɛ , ri ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ dya ̀ ɓɛn , ri ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n yɛɛ cee .
Kaana n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n ; ɓi ̀ keesi ̀ girig mɛ ̀ faa ̀ mɛ Kitɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay , a ̀ ɓiisɛ ̀ n ri ̀ fa ɗi lɛ ɓi kpaa ̀ kpa ̀ ŋzi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ re ̀ sii mi ̀ ni .
Ɓisuulɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a to ̀ tog ɓi ̀ ke ̀ neke ̀ ne ̀ ɓi ɓito ̀ ki ̀ , a ̀ yin ɓii ̀ to ̀ toogh ri ɓum , lɔŋ ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll nnɛ a to ̀ to ̀ g ɓisuulɛ a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ wog com ki a kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ ; ri ̀ n ̀ ghay innɛ a kpaakpaa ɓiɓan ɓi rim .
Kɔm ̀ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a kpaakpaŋzi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a to ̀ tog ri ɓum , a ̀ fafa ̀ ɓɔ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , a ̀ fee ̀ ghfe ̀ gsi ̀ ɓɔ , a ̀ ki fɔɔfɔɔ ̀ si ̀ ɓɔ mɛ ̀ rem .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a to ̀ tog ɓi ̀ ke ̀ neke ̀ ne ̀ ɓi ɓito ̀ ki ̀ , a faafa ̀ lɛ ̀ n nyimiɗ ite ̀ ɗ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , roa ̀ nɛ a kpaakpaŋzi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ki ̀ ki lɛ ki ̀ seŋi ki Bɛ ̀ ll kɛɛ ɓa ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
Nkɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ di mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓya ̀ a to ̀ toogh ɓi ̀ ke ̀ neke ̀ ne ̀ ɓi ɓito ̀ ki ̀ , wɔ ̀ lɛ m ̀ ɓiisɛɛ ti ̀ ki ̀ kɔ ̀ ni lɛ ɓi kpaa ̀ kpa ̀ ŋzi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a kpaa ̀ kpa ̀ ŋzi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ cee ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a to ̀ tog ɓi ̀ ke ̀ neke ̀ ne ̀ ɓi ɓito ̀ ki ̀ , di ki cee ɓi lɛ roa ̀ nɛ a to ̀ tog ɓi ̀ ke ̀ neke ̀ ne ̀ ɓi ɓito ̀ ki ̀ a ̀ ghagsii ɓum com ki a ̀ kpaa , lɛ kɛɛ fa ki ̀ seŋi ki ̀ ce ̀ m i ̀ te ̀ ɗ .
Nni ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ gɛɓsɛ ̀ n aɗi yɛɛ ̀ nɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ mɓay mi ̀ ni ri ̀ yɔ ̀ , di n ̀ -yu ̀ u mi ̀ ni ki ̀ to ̀ toogh ɓi ̀ ke ̀ neke ̀ ne ̀ ɓi ɓito ̀ ki ̀ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ma ̀ a ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ n ̀ -yu ̀ y mi ̀ ni ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki N ̀ ghay a ̀ re ̀ sii , nsoo ̀ lɛ ri ̀ yi ɗidɛŋ , nsoo ̀ lɛ ki ̀ ɓan ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ re ̀ sii mɛ ̀ lɛ nkpaŋzi , nsoo ̀ lɛ bimiɗ a ̀ ri ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g a ̀ dɛŋ ?
I ɓyom ɓi zɛy ( ɓi ɓi yin lɛ ɓi nyɛŋɗɛ ̀ n ɓi ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ rɔŋ ) fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ za ̀ ro ri ̀ fi ̀ loŋ ɓyaa yin mɛto ̀ o ̀ gh dɛŋ dɛ ̀ ŋ dɛŋ , di lannɛ ŋwaa ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ yi ri ̀ ghasi ̀ ɗi rito ̀ g ɗi za ̀ ro ri ̀ ɗi fi ̀ loŋ ?
I ɗyam ɗi too ̀ ghrɛɛ ɓi lɛ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ghɛn yɛɛ ɓuŋɛ ̀ n wɛ ̀ y ?
Fɔlɔɔ yɛɛ ri girig ɓi ɓɛg wi ̀ n , lɛ i ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓi ̀ kpaa ɓi ki ̀ ke ̀ neke ̀ ne ̀ ki kito ̀ ki ̀ ki resii ɓi com , lannɛ ɓum ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ yii ̀ com ki ɓi kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ ? Fɔlɔɔ a ɓa lɛ ɓi ma ̀ mag jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓi zi .
Nsoo ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓyaa te ̀ ghɛɛ ɓi ziinɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ cɛ , kidɛŋ ki yin wɔɔ ki ɓɛ kpaa lɛ ki resii ɓi com .
Nni fɔlɔɔ yɛɛ ri min lɛ , i ma ̀ a rɔ ̀ ɓ kɛ ̀ ɛ nwog kito ̀ ki ̀ ki ɓɛɛ ̀ to ̀ tog mɛ mii ̀ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ki ̀ gbɔ ̀ mgbɔ ̀ m ɓi mis mɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a to ̀ tog ri mɛ ̀ , nyii ɓa girig ki ̀ gbɔ ̀ mgbɔ ̀ m ɓi mis mɛ ̀ m .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi kaakaa mɛfaa ̀ mɛ Nghay , ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ kaa ̀ lɛ di ɓya ̀ a ɓaa ri ̀ mɔ lɛɛ ̀ gwey wɔ ̀ lɛ kɛɛ ɓa fɔlɔɔ ɓisuulɛ ki ̀ seŋi ki Kiris kɛɛ ɓa ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a to ̀ tog kike ̀ neke ̀ ne ̀ ki kito ̀ ki ̀ , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzaagh Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ , a yi ri ̀ ghagsi ̀ ɗi ɓum com ki a kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ ɓi ki ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ kin ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki mɓɔ ̀ ɔɓɔŋza ̀ g ɓi ki ̀ ke ̀ neke ̀ ne ̀ ki kito ̀ ki ̀ , lɔŋ nghay wɛ ̀ m wɛɛ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɔɓɔŋza ̀ g , ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗyɛm ̀ ɗyɔɔ maama ̀ a ̀ ɗyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ com .
N ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ min ki ki ̀ i la ? N ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzaagh Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ nghay wɛ ̀ m , ki ̀ ɓan kifog m ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋza ̀ g girig ri ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗyɛm ̀ ; n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ kɛɛghraagh tyem ri ̀ nghay wɛ ̀ m ki ̀ ɓan kifog n ̀ kɛɛghra ̀ g girig ri ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗyɛm ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ i u fafa Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n ɓi nghay wɔ ri ̀ wɔ , lannɛ ŋwaa ̀ zɛ ̀ y a ̀ nɛ a ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔrii n ̀ ɗaŋ ri ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ wowo ̀ g a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ kpaa lɛ a ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓi ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n ɓi u ̀ faa Bɛ ̀ ll kɔlɛ a ̀ yii ɓi com ki u ̀ kpaa ?
Ki ri lɔŋ saaɗ lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi u kakali Bɛ ̀ ll ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki u fafa nyi ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n fɔlɔɔ ɓi rɔɔtɛɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ɓi yin ɓii ̀ fafaa goni i ̀ te ̀ ɗ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
N ̀ faa Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n lɛ , nto ̀ tog ɓi ̀ ke ̀ neke ̀ ne ̀ ɓi ɓito ̀ ki ̀ , n ̀ cee mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓi ntaŋzɛn wu ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n , n ̀ ti m ̀ ɓiisa ̀ g ki ̀ kɔ ̀ ni lɛ nkpaa jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yitan ̀ ri ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗyɛm ̀ , a ̀ cee lɛ nkpaa jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ tɔɔsi ̀ m n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ɓi ki ̀ ke ̀ neke ̀ ne ̀ ki kito ̀ ki ̀ .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɓi ɓa yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɔɓti ɓi ri ̀ fifi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɗi ɓiɓan , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ki ̀ ɓe nnɛ ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɔɓti ; ɓi ̀ ri ̀ fifi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɗi ɓiɓan , ɓi ̀ ɓa ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn .
Ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna lɛ : Ɓi myɔm mɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ to ̀ tog ɓito ̀ ki ̀ ɓidɛŋ , ri ̀ ɓi myɔm mɛ ɓɛ ̀ ke ̀ n , innɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛɛ ri ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki ; nni nsoo ̀ ɓi bee inɛ ̀ n , ɓaa wog ɓi mɛ . Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ Kan a kala ̀ g .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ri ̀ to ̀ to ̀ g ɗi ɓi ̀ ke ̀ neke ̀ ne ̀ ɓi ɓito ̀ ki ̀ ɗi resii com , a ̀ a ɓisuu ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓisuu ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n , kɔlɛ ri ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ ɗi ɓiɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll , ɗi resii com , wɔ ̀ lɛ a ̀ a ɓisuu ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n lɔŋ ɓisuu ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n .
I ki ri min lɛ , ɓi ntaŋzen wu kiseŋi ki ̀ ce ̀ m ɓum ɓɛ ̀ cɛ ̀ m ɓɛɛ ̀ to ̀ tog ɓi ɓito ̀ ki ̀ , nni nnɛ ɓum ɓɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ , nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓe yin ɓɛgerɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ ɗiŋii yi ̀ wɔɔ , ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ kpaa lɛ ɓi ̀ ghali ɓi ̀ yɛ ̀ g di ki ɓaa la ̀ ?
Wɔ ̀ lɛ i ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaŋzi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll , nni nnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yin ngherɛ ̀ n nsoo ̀ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yu ̀ u lɛ a wog a ̀ ɗiŋii yi ̀ , ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ri nyi ɓii ̀ tinii lɛ a gherɛn ki ̀ ɓe kii , ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓii ̀ yɔ ̀ mi nyi .
Ɓɛ ̀ fe ̀ g ɓɛ ɓɛ ri nyi ɓɛ ̀ nyamɛn ɓi nɗem ɓɛ ɓii ̀ kpagii dan , a ̀ kpi ̀ ɓi zi ri i ̀ su , a ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kali ̀ lɛ : Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n a ta ̀ a ̀ kaa ̀ .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ nni cɛ ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ min lɛ ɓi ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g ? Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓi ̀ taŋzɛɛ , wa ̀ a ̀ nɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ fyem , nsoo ̀ lɛ com ki re ̀ siyɛn , nsoo ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki Nghay a ̀ re ̀ sii wɔ ̀ , nsoo ̀ lɛ u too ̀ ghrɛn ki ̀ ke ̀ neke ̀ ne ̀ ki kito ̀ ki ̀ , nsoo ̀ lɛ ri ̀ tɛɛ ̀ zi ̀ ɗi ɓiɓan ɓi ɓi kparɛɛ ɓi ki ̀ ke ̀ neke ̀ ne ̀ ki kito ̀ ki ̀ kin ̀ , ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ faa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m i ̀ te ̀ ɗ ɓi nghay .
