Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ re ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ mɛ ̀ girig , mɛ ̀ a ̀ nɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ man a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ yali ɗyem ki ̀ ɓwɛɗ ,
ɓisuulɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ŋwaa ̀ siito ̀ n ɓi nɗaŋ wu ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ; n ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi lɛ ɓɛ reŋi ̀ mɛ ̀ lɛ n ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ɓisuulɛ n ̀ -yeesi ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ seŋi ki ɓɔn ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Lɛ geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , nnɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ com ki n ̀ ɗi ̀ , nni geesɛ ̀ n yi ̀ i ̀ ɓi ɓɛg wɛ ̀ m i ̀ wugha ̀ ɓi zɛy , n ̀ sala ̀ gi ̀ kɔm ̀ n ̀ cee ɓɔ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , wɔ ̀ lɛ , a ̀ a mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ yɛɛ sala ̀ , lɔŋ geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ , yɛ ̀ ɛ kigha ̀ ki ̀ say .
Nni fɔlɔɔ nnɛ , kaa soo ri ̀ lɛ mɛ ̀ , kaa soo ri ̀ lɛ ɓɔ , com ki ti kpaakpaa ɓum kɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ n , kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓi ̀ ki gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ .
