Bɛ ̀ ll yɛɛ fagha ̀ ɓi ̀ si ki ̀ say ki ɓi ki ̀ puɓi ̀ -nɗem wi ̀ i ̀ , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ mu ̀ m mis mɛ yin mii ̀ lɛ mɛ fɔy .
