Nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ riighriki ̀ lɛ , fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ nyoo i ̀ ye ̀ gsi ̀ gha ̀ Ɛɛvɛ ri ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗi i ̀ ɓagha ̀ y ri ̀ ɗyɔ , mɛ ̀ yiti ̀ min mɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa lɛ mɛ ɓuu ̀ sɛ ̀ n ɓi le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ ɓi rini lɛ ri ̀ ri ̀ sɛɛ ̀ di ̀ ɗi mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ ɓi zi , ri ̀ ri ̀ tɛn , lɛ ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ ri ̀ ɓyɔ , ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Kiris .
Ɓisuulɛ ki yeesii ɓi mini lɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a yu mi ̀ ni ki ̀ kalii kiɓan ki Yeesus a ̀ dɛŋ , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ yin anɛ ɓi ̀ sii kali ̀ gha ̀ mi ̀ ni , nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓi teɗ N ̀ ghay a ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ yin N ̀ ghay a ̀ nɛ ɓi ̀ ɓagha ̀ di ɓi ̀ mɛ teɗ , nsoo ̀ lɛ Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ yin anɛ ɓi ̀ teka ̀ .
Mɛ ̀ ɛ nfe ̀ feg lɛ ɓum ɓin ɓɛ ɓi seesee lɛ ɓɔ yɛɛ ri ɓyoo ɓɛkɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ɓɛ cee ɓi mɛ ɓi com kidɛŋ nsoo ̀ lɛsa ̀ g .
