Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ nya lɛ mum a kalɛn ? Ki ghɛɓsii ɓi com nsoo ̀ lɛsag . Nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ m ̀ ɓii ̀ kpaŋi ̀ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ mɓuŋ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Kan a ̀ re ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ , ri ̀ ɓi a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ n-yi .
N ̀ -yii ki ̀ ristɛ ̀ n a ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓɔka ̀ aɗyoo , a ̀ kpaŋ ɓi ɗyoo ɗi kiraa , ki ti gɛɛ ̀ nɛ be ̀ g n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ɗi ̀ yinin , wɔ ̀ lɛ com ki n ̀ -yii ɓi ki ri lɛ : n ̀ -yii ɓi nko ̀ o a ̀ ɓɔka ̀ ri ̀ nyoo yi ̀ i ̀ bimiɗ , nko ̀ o ki lɛ n ̀ ghay wii wɔ yɛɛ ɓɔka ̀ , lɔŋ Bɛ ̀ ll yɛ ̀ ɛ yii .
N ̀ ki yii lɛ nko ̀ o ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓagha ̀ fɔlɔɔ ri nyoo yi ̀ i ̀ gi yɔ ̀ , nko ̀ o a ̀ ɓagha ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ , Bɛ ̀ ll yɛ ̀ ɛ yii , mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yii ɓi .
