Ɓi ̀ sii nɛmga ̀ ɓi ɓɔ bee , tyɛ ̀ ki ki wog rikpaa ɗyaa nsoo ̀ lɛsa ̀ g , lɛ ti ̀ kɔ ̀ nkɔ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ saaɗ a ̀ Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a rɔɓ lɔŋ zi ̀ ŋ ɓi-kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n .
Ɓi san a ̀ nɛ a ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ si ̀ ɓaa , mɛ ̀ n ̀ tɔɔgh ɓi com ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ɗyaa ɗin ̀ , lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ti kɛ ̀ ɛ fiɓi riɓa ɗi mum , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ si ̀ ɓɛn ̀ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ri com ki ɓɛ sagti ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi n ̀ ɗe ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ mɛ ̀ Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ lɛ nghagsi a ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ fagha ̀ Pyɛɛri lɛ a ghagsi a Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ,
lɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ Pyɛɛri a ɓa n ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom a Yeesus ɓisuu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , nnyɛɛ kigha ̀ mɛ ̀ lɛ mɓa girig fɔlɔɔ ɓisuu ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ geesɛ ̀ n ; ɓɛ ̀ -Zyag , ri ̀ Sefas ri ̀ Zyaŋ ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ n ̀ tɔn ɓaa , ɓɛ tuka ̀ ka ̀ ɓi ̀ si ɓya ̀ g lɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ri ̀ Ɓarinaɓas , lɛ ɓɛɛ resi lɛ , ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɓu ̀ tɛn ɗi ɓɔ ; fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ sii ghɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ a ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , ɓɔɔ kɛn ̀ a Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog ki ɓɛ tɔka ̀ ɓi ̀ si ki ɓagha ̀ lɛ , ɓi ̀ sii yita ̀ g lɛ ti ghɛɓsi ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sogha ̀ sogha a Yorisalɛm ; ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki n ̀ si ̀ i ̀ rɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ki ̀ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Pyɛɛri a ̀ kpaga ̀ a Aŋtyos , nni n ̀ fagha ̀ nyi ri ̀ na ̀ n ɓi mis mɛ ɓum ɓisuulɛ a ̀ sɛ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ .
Lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kpaga ̀ wɔɔ , a ̀ a nti a ̀ ɗila ̀ g n ̀ ɗaŋ ri ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , wɔ ̀ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓumɓɛ Zyag a ̀ romga ̀ y ɓɛ kpaga ̀ ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛn , Pyɛɛri a ̀ sɔ ̀ ŋi ̀ i ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗin ̀ , a ̀ porɛ ̀ n kɛ ̀ ɛ ɗi ti nɗaŋ ri ɓɔ , lɛ a ̀ riri ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n .
Nni ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛmbog ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ nɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ i ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ wu Pyɛɛri win ̀ , a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ syoga ̀ girig Ɓarinaɓas , ɓi mɛ ̀ ghe ̀ y mɛ ɓɛ kiki ̀ gha ̀ mɛn ̀ .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ ɓɛ yin ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi saaɗ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ , nni n ̀ kpaagha ̀ ri ̀ Pyɛɛri ɓi mis mɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m lɛ : I wa ̀ a ̀ nɛ u ̀ ri ̀ muu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n u ghɛghɛɓ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , kɔ ̀ ɔ ghɛɓ cɛɓ ki Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , lannɛ u kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ u kaŋ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓɛɛ ghɛɓ yɛ ̀ ɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ?
Ɓi ̀ sii ri ɓi ̀ yali ̀ ɓi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , ti ̀ yin ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe ɓɛ ɓɛ pɛsɛɛyi ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓidɛŋ .
Nni wɔ ̀ lɛ ti ̀ yii lɛ mum a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ ɓa lɛ saaɗ ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ a nɔ ̀ ɔnɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , lɔŋ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ gherɛɛ Yeesus Kiris nnyɛɛ ri lɛ saaɗ ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ si girig ti ̀ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ Yeesus Kiris lɛ di ti ghɛnɛn ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ lɛ saaɗ lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi ti ̀ gherɛɛ Kiris , a ̀ a ɓisuulɛ ti nɔ ̀ ɔnɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ; lɛ ri ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋ ɗi ɓidɔ ̀ gsɛna ɗi yin lɛ ɗi ki lɛ mum a ɓa lɛ saaɗ ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ , i ki kpaŋi lɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ti kaakaa lɛ ti ɓa lɛ saaɗ ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi ti ̀ gherɛɛ Kiris , ki ghɛnɛɛ lɛ ɓi ̀ si girig ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe , fɔlɔɔ a re ̀ si ̀ nya lɛ Kiris a sasay ɓisuu kiɓe ? A ̀ g ! Ki yin fɔlɔɔ .
I n ̀ tumɛɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ toŋ ɗi ɓyom ɓi n ̀ wa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ , di n ̀ ɗe ̀ sii lɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yin ɓii ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔnɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna .
Ɓi san a ̀ nɛ a ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna , mɛ ̀ n ̀ tigha ̀ ki ̀ loŋ lɛ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna , lɛ di nghɛɓ ɓisuu Bɛ ̀ ll .
N ̀ wugha ̀ ɓi Kɔrɔs n ̀ ɗaŋ ɗi Kiris , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ a mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ̀ ghɛghɛɓti , lɔŋ Kiris yɛɛ ̀ ghɛghɛɓ ɓi mɛ ̀ ; cɛɓ ki nghɛghɛɓ gɛɛ ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ mum , nghɛghɛɓ kɔ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi n ̀ gherɛɛ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ keesi ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ , a ̀ ki fa cɛɓ kii ɓisu wɛ ̀ m .
Mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yin lɛ m ̀ ɓe ̀ n geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ ; lɛ i kaa ri ̀ lɛ mum a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ ɓa lɛ saaɗ ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll di a ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ tii ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Moyis , di ri ̀ wu ɗi Kiris ɗi yin min ɗi gɛɓsɛ ̀ n nsoo ̀ lɛsa ̀ g .
Mi ̀ ni , ɓumɓɛ a Galasi , lannɛ ɓi ̀ ye ̀ ghii fɛlɛ ? Ghɛn yɛɛ yogsii mi ̀ ni mɛ ̀ rem , mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ɓɛ resi ̀ gha ̀ Yeesus Kiris a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ kpanga ̀ ɓi Kɔrɔs .
Ɓa ̀ ghina mɛ ̀ n ̀ tɔɔ ̀ tɔɔgh wu ; Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ mi ̀ ni Nghay wi ̀ i ̀ ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ ɓe ̀ ga ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna gi ̀ n ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , ɓi ̀ wog , ɓi ̀ ki gherɛn Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ ?
Ɓi ̀ ri ̀ kɔm ̀ ɓiye ̀ g ? Ɓi ̀ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ y ri ̀ Nghay a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , lannɛ ɓi kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ ɓi kɛn ̀ ki ̀ wɔmɓɛɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ fe ̀ g ɓɛ ɓum ?
Gɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan anɛ ɓi ̀ mɛ ghɛn anɛ a ̀ wii yɛɛlɔɔ zɛy ? Di ɓi ki ri ̀ lɛ ɓi wu zɛy . Roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ fala ̀ g mi ̀ ni Nghay a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ,
a ̀ ki ki ̀ ki da ̀ m ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n , a ̀ ti a ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g nya fɔlɔɔ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi nɔ ̀ ɔnɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna gi ̀ n ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ ti ɓi ̀ woki ̀ , ɓi ̀ ki gherɛn Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ ?
Abiraham a ̀ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ nyi lɛ a ̀ ri ̀ saaɗ a ̀ mum .
Nni yiina lɛ : mum bimiɗ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ foŋi n ̀ tyweeyi ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ do ̀ o ̀ yi ̀ Abiraham .
Kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ yiti ̀ gha ̀ abɛ ̀ y lɛ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ i gɛ lɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛɛ ɓa lɛ saaɗ ɓi mis mii lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , nni a ̀ loka ̀ ki ̀ kpaa ̀ Abiraham Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi teri gɛ ɓɛ ̀ ma ̀ a ̀ gh ɓisu wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Ɓisu wi ̀ n nnɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ gherɛɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ ma ̀ ŋɛn nɗaŋ ɗi Abiraham a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
Lɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ saghii n ̀ to ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋ ɗi ɓidɔ ̀ gsɛna , ɓɛ ti ɓi ncɛ ̀ m ɓi ɗu ̀ m ɓisuulɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ɓi ɓiɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓi ri ɓi ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna , kɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓyɛɛ ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ teri ̀ n ̀ cɛ ̀ m .
Ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ , mum a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ki ɓaa ̀ lɛ saaɗ ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ ri ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋ ɗi a ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna . Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki ri lɔŋ fɔlɔɔ ɓisuulɛ saaɗ a ̀ mum a ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɓi ̀ lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
Bee i ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna i ̀ ghasɛɛ ri ̀ bee i ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , lɛ , mɛ ̀ ka ̀ ni ̀ mɛɛ ̀ re ̀ sag lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna , a ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɓi ̀ lɛ ɓyɔ .
Kiris a ̀ kwe ̀ ɗka ̀ ɓi ̀ si ɓi ncɛ ̀ m a ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna , lɛ a ̀ ghala ̀ mum a ̀ n ̀ cɛ ̀ m ɓisu wis , - lɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : Mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ surii ɓi mɓa ̀ g a ̀ ti n ̀ cɛ ̀ mɛn .
Ki kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ fɔlɔɔ lɛ di ɓɛ ̀ ma ̀ a ̀ gh ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ka ̀ ka ̀ Abiraham ɓɛɛ kom ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n lɛ Yeesus Kiris , ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ , di ɓi ̀ sii teɗ N ̀ ghay a ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ka ̀ ka ̀ lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , nteɗ mi ̀ ni da ̀ ɗki ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓyɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ikilɛ ̀ n ɓi ri ̀ ghɛghɛ ̀ ɓ ɗi ɓum ; i mum a ̀ reɓsaagh ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓii syeesyee a ̀ ri ̀ reɓsa ̀ g di a ̀ ka wu ɓi , ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ ɓa ri ̀ com ki pisiyɛn , nsoo ̀ ki fɔŋdiyɛn ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Abiraham innɛ ɓɛ fagha ̀ mɛ ̀ ka ̀ g lɛ ri ̀ nyi ri ̀ boo yi ̀ i ̀ i mum , ki yin ki kaliyɛn lɛ , ri ̀ boo i ̀ ɓum i ̀ dɛŋ , yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ kali lɛ boo yi ɓum yi ɓagha ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey . Ri ̀ kpaa ɗi lɛ , ri ̀ boo yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ i mum ɗi seesee lɔŋ boo i ̀ mum bogtɛ ̀ n , yɛ ̀ ɛ ri lɛ Kiris .
Com ki nkɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ nkpaa ̀ ki ri lɛ , bimiɗ a ̀ ri ̀ wo ̀ ŋzi ̀ ɗi ɓiɓan anɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ mɛ pe ̀ gsɛ ̀ n a ̀ yin lɛ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi yogsi ̀ lɛ ɓyɔɓi ɓi kpaŋii ̀ fɛ ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ be ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ hɔnɗɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛnin ri ̀ be ̀ g ri ̀ tin ɗi ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ; i ki kilɛɛ fɔlɔɔ , di n ̀ ka ̀ g wu Bɛ ̀ ll wu ri kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ su .
I ɓaa teki ̀ mɛ ̀ wus mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ ri ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋ ɗi ɓidɔ ̀ gsɛna , di mɛ yin lɛ mum a ̀ teɗti ̀ lɛ n ̀ ka ̀ g wu Bɛ ̀ ll ; kɔlɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ Abiraham geesɛ ̀ n ɓi nka ̀ g wu a ̀ fagha ̀ nyi .
Nni ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi ghɛɓsii min cɛ ? Ɓi foŋɗɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ɓyɛɛ reresi mɛ ̀ na ̀ ni ̀ mɛ ɓum a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ do ̀ o ̀ yi ̀ Abiraham i ̀ nɛ n ̀ ka ̀ g win ̀ wu seese ̀ e ̀ gha ̀ i ̀ kpaŋi gɛ ; ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓɔ yɛɛ ghagsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓin ̀ , di bimiɗ a ̀ mum a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ nɛ lɛ , ri ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ri ̀ ɓɔ .
Mum a ̀ gagsi ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ gɛɓsɛ ̀ n di ɓum ɓɛ ri lɛɛ ̀ gwey , wɔ ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ cɛ ̀ ncii .
Fɔlɔɔ a re ̀ sii nya lɛ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi wɛɛsɛɛ ɓi ri mɛ ̀ ka ̀ g mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ? A ̀ g ! Ki yin fɔlɔɔ ; i ki ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna kidɛŋ ki ki ri lɛ ki fa cɛɓ kɛɛ ɓa wɔɔ , di ri ̀ ɓa ɗi mum a ɓa lɛ saaɗ ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ɗi ri lɛ ɗi ghɛnɛ ̀ n a ta ̀ a ̀ kaa ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a re ̀ sag lɛ , ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ri ɓi ri ̀ kpa ̀ n ɗi kiɓe , lɛ di n ̀ ka ̀ g wu Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ wɛɛ ron ɓi san a ̀ nɛ a ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓɛ gherɛɛ Yeesus Kiris .
Di ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi ka yin , ɓi ̀ sii ɓagha ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y i ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna , ti ̀ ɓoŋɓo ̀ ŋ lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi nce ̀ m ɗyɛɛ resɛ ̀ n .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi ɓagha ̀ ɓi ̀ si fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g wi ̀ s anɛ a kɛ ̀ ɛkɛɛ ̀ si ̀ ɓi ̀ si a ̀ kpaŋ ɓi ri ̀ yu ̀ ɗi Kiris , lɛ di ti ɓa ɓɛ ̀ tɛnɛn ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki righerɛ ̀ n ki mɛ kpaŋ , ɓi ̀ yii ̀ di ɓi ri ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɗi n ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g a ̀ nɛn ,
ɓisuulɛ mi ̀ nii ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔn ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓi ̀ gherɛɛ Yeesus Kiris .
Mi ̀ nii ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓaɓti ̀ gha ̀ ɓi Kiris , ɓi ̀ waatɛ ̀ nga ̀ Kiris .
Fɔɔnnɛ gasɛ ̀ n i ̀ yii ̀ di ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ nɛ lɛ ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓidɛŋ , yɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa ti ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ nɛ lɛ ri ̀ n ̀ kpa ̀ n ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yin n ̀ kpa ̀ n , nsoo ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ nɛ lɛ ri ̀ baŋi ̀ ri ̀ giɓ ɓisuulɛ mi ̀ nii ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ̀ ti com ki ̀ fog ɓi Yeesus Kiris .
Nni mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ Kiris , yiina min lɛ , ɓi ̀ ri ̀ boo i ̀ mum yi ̀ Abiraham , i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ga ̀ ɓ ɓi ɓyom ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ka ̀ ka ̀ .
Fe ̀ g wɛ ̀ m a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓi ri ̀ mɛ ̀ wus a kaka ŋwɔɓti , nsoo ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ wus mɛn ̀ mɛ wooghrɛɛ ri ̀ nyi , a ̀ ceerɛɛ ɓi ɓi com ɓɛɛ ̀ n ̀ kpa ̀ n .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki a ̀ kaka ŋwɔɓti , a ̀ kaka ɓi ri ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɗi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ tɔɔtɔɔ ̀ si ̀ nyi , ɓɛ ki kɛ ̀ ɛkɛɛ ̀ si ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓii , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ ɓi zi ̀ ŋɛn inɛ seŋi a ̀ fagha ̀ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛnɛ a ̀ ri teri gɛ mɛ ̀ wus mɛn ̀ mii ̀ .
Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ti ̀ ɓagha ̀ di ti ̀ kaka ɓɔɓti ti ̀ ɓagha ̀ girig ɓɛ ̀ kpa ̀ n ɓɛ ɓi ɓɔɔ ɓyom ɓɛ zɛy ɓɛ ɓi ziinɛ .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki Bɛ ̀ ll nyimiɗ a fe ̀ ka ̀ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ , nni a ̀ romga ̀ y Man wii ̀ , a ̀ yalɛ ̀ n ɓi ɗu ̀ m ɗi giɓ , a ̀ ghɛɓ ɓi ri ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɗi ɓidɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ,
lɛ di a kweɗ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ri ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɗi ɓidɔ ̀ gsɛna , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓi ̀ sii ghay min ɓɔn ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Com ki ki resii lɛ ɓi ̀ ti ɓɔn ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ki ri lɛ : Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ romga ̀ y N ̀ ghay a ̀ Man wii ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ rem mis , N ̀ ghay a ̀ nɛ ̀ n yɛɛ ̀ la ̀ alamɓɛ ̀ n jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Aba , yɛɛlɔɔ lɛ Ta ̀ a ̀ ta .
Fɔɔnnɛ u ̀ yii ̀ di n ̀ kpa ̀ n , u ̀ ti lɔŋ man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ; nni yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ ti man wii ̀ , u ̀ ri ̀ girig ri ̀ ga ̀ ɓ ɓi ɓyom ɓii lɛ geesɛ ̀ n yi ̀ i ̀ .
Ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ abɛ ̀ y , ɓi ̀ yigha ̀ ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ; ɓi ̀ i mɓɔgsa ̀ g ɓinu ̀ n ɓi ɓi yin kɔm ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Nni ɓigomi ̀ nɛ ɓi ̀ mɛ yi Bɛ ̀ ll , n ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ n ̀ kpaa gi ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ mɛ yi mini , nni lannɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ sugti ̀ ri ̀ jɛ ̀ m ɓi ɓɔɔ ɓyom ɓɛ zɛy ri ̀ zɛy ɓɛ ɓɛ ri kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , ɓi ̀ ki kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ di ɓya ̀ a ɓatii ɓɛ ̀ kpa ̀ n ɓɛ ɓyom ɓi ̀ n ?
Ɓi ̀ ti ɓi ̀ ɓɔgsa ̀ g lɛ ri ̀ go ̀ n yidɛŋ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ŋwii ɓɛdɛŋ , ri ̀ ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓidɛŋ ri ̀ be ̀ g yidɛŋ .
Mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ riighriki ̀ lɛ ki ̀ say ki n ̀ wugha ̀ n ̀ tɔɓ n ̀ ki ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin , kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ɓa lɛ ki wu zɛ ̀ y .
Ɓaana yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ , lɛ mɛ ̀ girig n ̀ ɗi ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ mi ̀ ni , m ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzaagh mi ̀ ni , ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ !
Ɓi ̀ ki ̀ i ɓi mɛ ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓeɓtɛn nsoo ̀ kifog , ɓi ̀ yii lɛ n ̀ ghagsigha ̀ mi ̀ ni Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ ɓi gɛ ̀ n i n ̀ tonto yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗoro ̀ ɓka ̀ .
Fi ̀ roɓ fi m ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ fyɔ ɓi nyoo fi ɓagha ̀ ɓi ̀ te ̀ ete ̀ ɗ ɓi mɛfe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn ɓisu win , nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ɓi ̀ sɛɛti ̀ gha ̀ ɓi mɛ , ri ̀ ɓa ɗyɛ ̀ m ɗyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ mini ti ̀ min , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ gha ̀ ɓka ̀ mɛ ̀ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a Bɛ ̀ ll , nsoo ̀ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus Kiris nyimiɗ .
