Yeesus a ̀ nɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ regi lɛ Yustus , a ̀ to ̀ gsii yi ̀ girig mi ̀ ni ; lɔŋ ki ̀ raa ki ɓum ki ̀ n kɔ ri ̀ kɔ , kɛɛ ri Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ sasay nɗaŋ ri mɛ ̀ ɓisuu kilɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓɛ ki ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ fati ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ ɓi nɗem .
Epafiras a ̀ maaseŋi wi ̀ n a ̀ to ̀ gsii yi ̀ mi ̀ ni , a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say a Yeesus Kiris a ̀ nɛ a ̀ fɔli ɓi riɗu ̀ u ̀ ɓi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n ɓisu wi ̀ n , lɛ ɓi ɓa ɓɛ ̀ si ̀ i ̀ rɛn , ɓi ̀ ɓa ɓɛ ̀ syeesyee ɓɛ ɓum , ɓi ̀ ki gherɛn rikɔ ̀ n ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll syeesyee a ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
N ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ lɛ a woowolɛ ̀ n lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓisu win , ri ̀ ɓisuu ɓumɓɛ a Lawodise ri ̀ ɓɛ a Iyerapolis .
Lukas a ̀ reŋka ̀ ŋ wi ̀ s a nɗem , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ dɔgta ̀ ɓɛɛ ̀ Demas ɓɛ togsii yi ̀ mi ̀ ni .
Ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsa ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓis ɓɛ ɓɛ ri a Lawodise , ri ̀ Nɛmfa , ri ̀ ki ̀ seŋi ki Kiris ki ki ri ɓi naa yi ̀ i ̀ .
I ɓɛ mɛ ɓa ̀ y kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ nɛ foo a lɔ ̀ ŋkin , ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓay girig ki ̀ seŋi ki a Lawodise nyi ; fɔɔnnɛ mi ̀ ni girig ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓa ̀ li kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ yi ̀ mi ̀ ni a Lawodise .
Kaliina Arisip lɛ : U ̀ kona ̀ g ri ̀ ki ̀ say ki Kan a ̀ fagha ̀ wɔ ̀ , te ̀ e ̀ si nyoo lɛ u konag kɔ ki ̀ ki ̀ i .
Mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ Pol yɛɛ kanii ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓi ̀ tɔki ̀ ri ̀ ca ̀ g kɛm ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɓi ɗimzɛn lɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y . Geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa ri ̀ mi ̀ ni !
Mɛ ̀ Pol , ɓɛɛ Silas ri ̀ Timote , ti ̀ ka ̀ ni ɓumɓɛ ɓi Ki ̀ seŋi ki a Tesalonika ki ki ri ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll Seŋi ri ̀ ɓi Yeesus Kiris Kan . Geesɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ fyo ̀ oog ɓyɛɛ ɓa ɓi ̀ fayɛn a lɔ ̀ ŋkin .
Ɓisii ̀ fafa lɔŋ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ɓisu win ̀ mi ̀ nii ̀ ce ̀ m , ti ̀ ki ɓu ̀ ŋɓuŋ mini ɓi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n yis .
Ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ Seŋi wi ̀ s ti ̀ ti ti ̀ yita ̀ g ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ min mɛ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ ki ̀ say ki n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n win ̀ a ki ̀ ki ̀ , ri ̀ ri ̀ si ̀ i ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɗin ɓi dya ̀ ɓɛn inɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ yɔ ̀ ɓi ̀ Kan wi ̀ s Yeesus Kiris .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , ti ̀ yii lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ keesi ̀ gha ̀ mi ̀ ni , a ̀ ki ɓɔ ̀ n mini .
Ɓisuulɛ ti ̀ ghagsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi mini Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ ti ̀ ɓagha ̀ y ri ̀ nyi ri ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ ŋwɔm yɔ ̀ ri yɔ ̀ , ti ̀ ghagsi ̀ gha ̀ girig nyi ɓi da ̀ m yi ti ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ teɗ wu Kitɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay , ti ̀ ki konag kiyii ̀ saaɗ bimiɗ a ̀ nɛ ɓi Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n . Ɓi saaɗ , ɓi ̀ yii cɛɓ ki ti ̀ ghɛɓka ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n ; fɔlɔɔ a ɓagha ̀ ɓi ki ̀ rɔɔ kin .
Ɓi ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ mis , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ mɛ Kan , ɓi ̀ ki tulɛn ri ̀ mɛ ̀ tɔɓ lɛɛ ̀ gwey yɛ ̀ ɛ bi ̀ gha ̀ ɓka ̀ Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ ri ̀ ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ ki Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay kɛɛ ̀ fala ̀ g .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ ti ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ɓisuu ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ a Masedwan , ri ̀ ɓɛ a Akayi .
Lɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Kan i ̀ mɛ pɛ ̀ sɛn yi a lɔ ̀ ŋkin , i ̀ kpaŋ a ̀ Masedwan ri ̀ a Akayi , nni a ̀ a lɔŋ foo nyi ri ̀ nyi , gom i ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗin ɗi ɓi ̀ gherɛɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , i ̀ mɛ sa ̀ a ̀ ja ̀ ŋ bimiɗ a ̀ kpaŋ ɓi le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ ti ̀ yin gi lɛ ti ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ .
Ɓum ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa righa ̀ ɓ ɗi ɓi ̀ gha ̀ ɓka ̀ ɓi ̀ si yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ kpaga ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin ri ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ ca ̀ ɗka ̀ ka ̀ y ɓi ̀ nu ̀ n , ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ ɓi ɓɔgsi nyi , lɛ nnyɛɛ ri kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ri ̀ cem ,
ɓi ̀ ɓoŋɓo ̀ ŋ lɛ Man wii ̀ Yeesus , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghe ̀ mzi ̀ gha ̀ y a ɓi ̀ loŋ , a sɛn ̀ yi ̀ aɗyoo , di a kweɗ ɓi ̀ si ɓi ri ̀ baŋi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ɗi ɗi rii ̀ .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ ɓi ̀ yii lɛ , ri ̀ yu ̀ ɗi ti ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin ɗi wugha ̀ ɓi zɛy .
Di ti ̀ ka kpaŋ ɓi a lɔ ̀ ŋkin , ti ̀ ghɛnga ̀ mɛ ̀ tɔɓ , ɓum ɓɛ ki yeesi ɓisi a Filiɓ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ yii , wɔ ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ ɓi ̀ si i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ ti ghagsi mi ̀ ni Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ wi ̀ i ̀ nsoo ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ɓagha ̀ bimiɗ a ̀ wɛ ̀ y .
Ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ti ̀ kaka ̀ li ̀ gha ̀ ɓum ɓi roogha ̀ y ɓi n ̀ ɗuŋ ɓi ri ̀ na ̀ n n ̀ soo ̀ lɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi tifin , fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ki yin ɗi n ̀ -ye ̀ gsɛ ̀ n .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ timga ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ɗis a ̀ ki fa ɓisi ki ̀ say ki Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ . Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ti ̀ yin ɓii ̀ kpaakpaa ɓiɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ ti puɓsi ɓum mɛ ̀ rem , ki ̀ ɓan ki ̀ fog , ti kpaakpaa ɓi ɓyɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ngi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ ghɛngi ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ rem mɛ ɓum , mɛ ri ɓi ɗu ̀ m .
Ɓi ̀ yii lɛ ti ̀ ka ɓagha ̀ ɓi ri jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ fi ̀ ɗyɛɓi , nsoo ̀ ri ̀ yiti ̀ ɗi lɛ ti fɔn ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni ŋwos adɛŋ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ .
Ti ̀ kaagha ̀ ɓi lɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ kemzi ɓisi , nsoo ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin , nsoo ̀ a ɓum ɓɛm ̀ bog , kɔlɛ ti ̀ ɓagha ̀ lɛ ti ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓi-te ̀ ɗ ɓi ɗii ɗi lɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ɓɛ Kiris .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ti ̀ ghɛɓka ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n ri ̀ nɗem wu tɛ ̀ tɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ jɛɛ ɓɔn a ̀ ti a ̀ ɓe ̀ gi ̀ ɓɔn ɓii .
Ɓi ri ̀ keesi ̀ ɗi ti ̀ keesi ̀ gha ̀ mi ̀ ni , a ̀ a Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll nyi ri ̀ nyi innɛ ti ̀ ɓagha ̀ lɛ ti ̀ kɔ ̀ n lɛ ti fa mi ̀ ni , ti ɓagha ̀ lɛ ti fa mi ̀ ni lɔŋ lɛ ri ̀ ɓyɛɓ ɓis mii ̀ , lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓagha ̀ di ɓi ̀ ti ɓum ɓis ɓɛ nɗem lɛ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ yiti ̀ ki ̀ say ki ti ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ , ri ̀ n ̀ tɔɓ wu ti ̀ woka ̀ ; ti ̀ ghagsi ̀ gha ̀ mi ̀ ni Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ti ̀ ki sasay lɛ ri ̀ i ̀ ru ri ̀ ŋwos lɛ n ̀ tɛ ̀ g wis wɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ siŋ wa ̀ a ̀ dɛŋ ɓi nyo ̀ o ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ ɓis , nsoo ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ girig wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ lɛ cɛɓ ki ti ̀ ghɛɓka ̀ ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ki ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ tɛnɛn , kɔ ti ̀ lɛ saaɗ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kifenɛn mii ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ yii girig lɛ ti ̀ ghɛɓka ̀ ri ̀ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ ɓi mi ̀ ni fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ seŋi a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ ghɛɓ ri ̀ ɓɔn ɓii .
Ti ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ti ̀ reɓ mi ̀ ni , ti ̀ fɔɔsi ̀ mi ̀ ni mɛ ̀ rem , ti ̀ ki ɓɔ ̀ ɔɓɔ ̀ ŋzi ̀ mi ̀ ni lɛ ɓi ghɛɓ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ kɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ngi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a regi mini lɛ ɓi ɓa ri ̀ ga ̀ ɓ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kii , ri ̀ ɓi ri ̀ kem ɗii .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ti ̀ fafa Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m lɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ bi ̀ gha ̀ ɓka ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi ̀ i ̀ i ̀ nɛ ti ̀ wogsi ̀ gha ̀ mi ̀ ni , ɓi ̀ gha ̀ ɓka ̀ ɓi yɔ ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ mum ; ɓi ̀ gha ̀ ɓka ̀ lɔŋ yɔ ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ i ̀ ri ̀ a ta ̀ a ̀ kaa ̀ , lɛ i ̀ ri ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ ki kisay ɓi mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , ɓi ̀ mɛ pisɛn Ɓiseŋi ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ɓi ri a Zyude ɓi Yeesus Kiris , ɓisuulɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kin ɓɛ yeesi ̀ gha ̀ mi ̀ ni lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛroɓɛ a Zyude ɓɛ yeesi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛn ̀ ɓɛɛ wola ̀ Kan Yeesus , ɓɛ ki cuusi ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan , ɓɛɛ yeeye ̀ e ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ si ; ɓɛ ti ɓɛ ɓeɓki ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓɛ ki ɓe ̀ e ̀ zag ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ɓɛ ti ɓɛ reki ̀ ɓi ̀ si lɛ tyɛ ̀ ki ghagsi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓa ri ̀ cɛɓ . Ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗin ̀ ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi ɓɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ nkɛn bee ̀ bɛ ̀ y ɓɛ tee ̀ te ̀ gsi ̀ ki ̀ ɓe kaa ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ri ̀ ɗyɔ ̀ ; wɔ ̀ lɛ ri ̀ baŋi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ɗi mɛ syɔn ɓɔ ki ̀ ko ̀ mi .
Ɓi san wi ̀ s , yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ ghasɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ mi ̀ ni tyɛ ̀ ki ghɛnɛn ti a mɛ ̀ su ɓi maa ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n , fɔlɔɔ kɛ ̀ ɛ ki re ̀ si lɛ ti ̀ ti tyɛ ̀ ki fe ̀ gti mini , ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , ti ̀ i nɗi ̀ ri ̀ coo za ̀ y i ̀ nɛ lɛ ti ghɛnɛn ti ̀ ri ̀ mi ̀ ni , fɔɔnnɛ ti ̀ i n ̀ te ̀ e ̀ sii nyoo lɛɛ ̀ gwey lɛ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ kilɛn .
Ti ̀ kɔ ̀ nga ̀ lɔŋ lɛ di tya ̀ a yu ̀ u foo , a lɔ ̀ ŋkin mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ Pol n ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛɛ gɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ yiɓɛɛ ̀ , wɔ ̀ lɛ Sata ̀ n a re ̀ g ɓi ̀ si ri ̀ yu ̀ .
Ghɛn yɛɛri ̀ min ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ dya ̀ ɓɛn yi ̀ s , ri ̀ ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ kis nsoo ̀ lɛ ta ̀ m wi ̀ s a ri ̀ kem ɓi mis mɛ Kan wi ̀ s Yeesus , ŋwosi risugti ̀ i ̀ ɗii ? A ̀ a lɔŋ mi ̀ ni yɛɛ ri ̀ ɓa wa ?
Ɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , mi ̀ ni yɛɛ ri ri ̀ kem ɗis , ri ̀ ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ kis .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ i n-yiidi lɛ ti ̀ cenɛ ̀ n lɛ ti ɓoŋɓoŋ ti ̀ , nni ti ̀ i nghɛɛ ki ̀ rɔɔ lɛ , ti rɔɓ a Atɛn ɓi ̀ si cɛ ̀ ncis .
Fɔɔnnɛ ti ̀ i nɗomii ̀ mi ̀ ni geni wi ̀ s Timote , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say a Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ri ̀ ghagsi ̀ ɗi Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ Kiris lɛ a fa mi ̀ ni i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , a ̀ ki fegsi mi ̀ ni ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗin ;
lɛ di mum kɛ ̀ ɛ ca ̀ rɛn lɛ mɛ ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn mɛ mɛ ri ɓigomi ̀ nɛ mɛɛ ɓigti nyi , ɓisuulɛ mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ ɓi ̀ yii lɛ mɛ ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn mɛn ̀ mɛ ɓagha ̀ mɛ ̀ pe ̀ gsɛn ɓisu wis .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ ɓagha ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin , ti ̀ loka ̀ mi ̀ ni ki re ̀ sii lɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ tanɛɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn , fɔɔnnɛ ki ki ki ̀ lɛ ̀ nga ̀ fɔlɔɔ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ yii .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ m ̀ ɓati ̀ gha ̀ ɓi lɛ m ̀ ɓoŋɓo ̀ ŋ ti ̀ nni n ̀ ɗomga ̀ y Timote lɛ a yu ki ̀ woo ̀ gh lannɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗin ɗyɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , lɛ n ̀ ɗiri ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ lɛ kɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa lɛ n ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n-ɓum a ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ mi ̀ ni lɛ ki ̀ say kis kɛɛ wu zɛy .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ nnɛ Timote a ̀ sughii ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɗi a ̀ a nɗi ̀ i ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin ; a ̀ sughii ̀ ɓi ̀ si ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɓɔlɛ ɓɛsyeesyee ɓɛ ɓɛ komi lɛ ri ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗin , ri ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ nyi . A ̀ kpaa ɓi ̀ si yɛ ̀ ɛ mi ̀ nii ̀ ka yiiyita ̀ g lɔŋ ɓisi ri ̀ nkɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m , ɓi ̀ ki ɓa ri za ̀ y i ̀ nɛ lɛ ɓi ghɛn ̀ ɓi ̀ si , yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ si girig ti ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ za ̀ y i ̀ nɛ lɛ ti ghɛnɛn .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ i nfaa ɓi ̀ si i ̀ te ̀ ɗ ɓi nyoo ri ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗin , ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ mɛ ̀ tɔɓ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn mɛce ̀ m mɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ mɔ .
Nni ɓigomi ̀ nɛ ki ri yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ teetii ti ̀ cɛɓ yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ woogh lɛ ɓi ̀ kaka lɔŋ ɓɛsi ̀ i ̀ rɛn ɓi Kan .
Ti ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ti ̀ to ̀ gsa ̀ g Bɛ ̀ ll wi ̀ s ɓisu win a ̀ kpaŋ fe , ɓi ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ti ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ kɔ ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓisuu righerɛ ̀ n ɗin !
Ti ɓɔ ̀ ɔɓɔ ̀ ŋzi ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ i ̀ ru yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwos , ti ̀ ki si ̀ i ̀ rɛn ɓi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n lɛ a ki lɛ ti ghɛnag ti ̀ a mɛ ̀ su , a ̀ ki roozi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi kaarɛɛ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗin ?
Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ Seŋi wi ̀ s nyimiɗ , ri ̀ Kan wi ̀ s Yeesus , ɓɛɛ ɓaa ̀ ɓi ̀ si bee i ̀ nɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ti ̀ kpaŋ mii ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin .
Kan a tegsi n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ nyi , lɛ a ron ̀ a ̀ so ̀ so ̀ ɓ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n , a ̀ ko ̀ m ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ ki ɓa fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ ɓisii ri ri ̀ nyi ɓi san wi ̀ n .
A ki lɛ mɛ ̀ rem min mɛɛ sii ̀ rɛn , mɛ ɓa mɛ ̀ tɛnɛn , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓɛ ri ̀ lɛ ɓɛ fen mii ̀ ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ Seŋi wi ̀ s , ŋwosi risugti ̀ i ̀ ɗi Kan wi ̀ s Yeesus n ̀ ɗaŋ ri ̀ ɓum ɓii ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ tɛnɛn .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , ti sii ̀ tɛn ki ̀ kpaa ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ yila ̀ ka ̀ ri ̀ kuu ɗi cɛɓ ɗi ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ghɛɓi ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a wog ki ̀ rɔɔ ri ̀ mi ̀ ni , a lɔ ̀ ŋkis nni cɛɓ ki ̀ n kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓi ghɛghɛ ̀ ɓ ; ti ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzaagh mi ̀ ni , ti ̀ ki yɛ ̀ gsi mini ɓya ̀ g ɓi ɗii ɗi Kan Yeesus lɛ ɓi tee ̀ si ti ̀ nyoo ri ̀ ri ̀ kuu ɗi cɛɓ ɗi ̀ n a ̀ cee fɔlɔɔ .
Ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ yii ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ti ̀ siita ̀ ka ̀ mi ̀ ni ; ɓi ɓagha ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi rii ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Kan Yeesus .
Ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ɗi ri lɛ ɓi ghɛɓ cɛɓ ki tɛnɛn , ɓi ̀ ce ̀ li ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi tifin .
Mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ ɓi mi ̀ ni , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ yii ̀ ri ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋ ɗi nyoo yi ̀ i ̀ ɓi ri ̀ tɛn , a ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ n lɛ a ɓa mum a ̀ saaɗ , ɗi ̀ ri ̀ mum ;
kɛ ̀ ɛ ca ̀ rɛn lɛ ɓiɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓiɓan ɓyɛɛ syo ̀ ŋ nyi n ̀ ɗem , yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ti ki ɓala ̀ g ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki yi Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ɓi ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ŋwaa ̀ ɗɛŋ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ki ye ̀ gsii ̀ geni , nsoo ̀ lɛ a ̀ ki ̀ nyi ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki nɗem , lɛ Kan a ̀ ti a ̀ rɔ ̀ gi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ mɛ ki ̀ lɛ , ti ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni , ti ̀ ki re ̀ si mini .
Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ɓisi lɛ ti ghɛɓ cɛɓ ki kitɔɓi ̀ , wɔ ̀ lɛ a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ si lɛ ti ghɛɓ cɛɓ ki tɛnɛn .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓe ̀ ni ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi nsiisii ̀ ta ̀ g ɓi , a yi lɛ , a ̀ a mum i ̀ nnɛ a ̀ ɓe ̀ ni , lɔŋ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ mɛ fa mini girig Kitɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n kii ki Nghay .
Ki ghɛɓsii ɓi com lɛ ti kan ̀ mi ̀ ni ki ̀ ɓan ki n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ geni , ɓisuulɛ Bɛ ̀ ll nyimiɗ a re ̀ sa ̀ ka ̀ mi ̀ ni ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓi n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n .
N ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛn innɛ ɓi re ̀ resi ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓin ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ri Masedwan bimiɗ . Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , ɓisii yɛgsii lɔŋ mini ɓya ̀ g lɛ ɓi kɛɛ ̀ di bee ̀ bɛ ̀ y ri ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗin ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ foŋ n ̀ ɗem ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki lɛ ɓi ghɛ ̀ ɓ lɛ fyo ̀ oog , ɓi ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ɓi mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmi ̀ ɗ , ɓi ̀ ki sasay ri ɓya ̀ g ɓin lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ siŋdɛ ̀ nga ̀ mi ̀ ni ;
di fɔɔnnɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n ɓɛɛ teɗ mi ̀ ni ri ̀ ri ̀ mum , n ̀ tɛ ̀ g win wɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ri ̀ ɗ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , ti ̀ kɔ ̀ ni ɓi lɛ ɓi ɓa lɛ du ̀ ŋdu ̀ ŋ ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki ki seesee ɓɛroɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓi ̀ loŋ lɛ di kɛ ̀ ɓi ɓa lɛ mɛ ̀ rem min mɛ ɓeɓtɛ ̀ n ɓi mu ̀ m yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ɓum ɓɛm ̀ bog ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ dya ̀ ɓɛn .
Lɛ i ti ̀ gherɛɛ lɛ Yeesus a ̀ wugha ̀ , a ̀ ki ghe ̀ mɓɛn , ti gherɛɛna girig lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ghe ̀ mzii n ̀ ɗaŋ ri Yeesus , ɓɛroɓɛ ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi ɓɛ ɓaa wu .
Ɓisuulɛ com ki ti kpaaghi ̀ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Kan i ̀ ri ̀ ki ri lɛ : Ɓi ̀ si ɓɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ di ti ̀ kaka cem ɓi ri ̀ sugti ̀ i ̀ ɗi Kan , tya ̀ a syo ̀ ŋ ɓi ɓɛroɓɛ ɓaa wu bee .
Ɓisuulɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ i ̀ too ̀ ghrɛɛ , jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ coo ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom , ɗyam ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ɗi rɔŋ , Kan nyimiɗ a ɓii ̀ sɛni ̀ i ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ ; fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ loŋ ɓi ɓi Kiris ɓi ɓii ̀ loo ̀ gh ki ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛɛ .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , ɓi ̀ si ɓumɓɛ ti ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ di ti ̀ kaka cem , ɓɛ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si ɓii ̀ teri ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ ri ɓɔ , ti ̀ ɓɔg ɓi ɓi ̀ kwi ̀ ɗ lɛ ti ̀ tuu ̀ sɛn ri ̀ Kan ɓi nlɛŋlɛŋ ̀ . Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ti ̀ ɓii ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔrii ri Kan ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ ɓi ̀ fɔɔ ̀ fɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ sɛ ̀ n mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ mɛrem ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan ki ki seesee ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n , nsoo ̀ lɛ go ̀ n inɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi ri ɓii ̀ ki ̀ lɛɛ , ki yii ̀ di lɛ ɓɛ kan ̀ mi ̀ ni kɔ .
Ɓisuulɛ mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ ɓi ̀ konaagh ki ̀ yii ̀ lɛ ŋwos a Kan a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ kpaŋi ̀ fɛlɛ yɛɛ wiiwi ̀ i ̀ a ̀ ti a ̀ yu ̀ la ̀ g ri ̀ i ̀ ru .
Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛ ɓii ̀ kpaakpaa lɛ fyo ̀ oma ̀ fi ri lɛ fyo ̀ oog kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki risiyɛn kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓɛ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ si ̀ gmɛɛ lɛ cuu ki mɛ sɛn ɓi ɓɔ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ kɛŋ ɗi riyay ɗi ti ɗi siɗki ̀ giɓ a ɗyem . Ɓaa ɓa ɓi ri bee i ̀ n ̀ lɛghɛn cuu ki ̀ n .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , mi ̀ nii yin ɓi biri ̀ m , fɔɔnnɛ ŋwos anɛ ̀ n a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi mini ki ̀ si ̀ ri yɛ ̀ ɛ wiiwi ̀ i ̀ .
Mi ̀ nii ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔn ɓɛ ɓi ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn , ɓi ̀ ɓa ti ɓɔn ɓɛ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ ŋwos ; ɓi ̀ sii ̀ yin ɓɔn ɓɛ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ i ̀ ru , nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ɓi biri ̀ m .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi min kilali ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛro ɓɛm ̀ bog ; ti kɔ ̀ riina lɔŋ cem , ti ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ n ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki mɛrɔ ̀ g .
Ɓisuulɛ , ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ lala ̀ y , ɓɛ ti ɓɛ laayi ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ ru , ɓɛ ̀ ŋwaŋi ̀ mɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ g , ɓɛ ŋwagi ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ ru .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ si ɓɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔn ɓɛ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ ŋwos , ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋɗɛɛ ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki mɛrɔ ̀ g , ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ pu ̀ rɛɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ri ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n fɛ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ki bɔŋ ti ̀ waatɛ ̀ n girig dya ̀ ɓɛn inɛ ɓi go ̀ ri yi ̀ s fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ta ̀ m .
Ɓisuulɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fe ̀ ka ̀ ɓi lɛ ti ɓa ɓumɓɛ bim yii ̀ i ̀ ɓii ̀ re ̀ sɛɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkaa , wɔ ̀ lɛ a ̀ fe ̀ ka ̀ lɛ ti ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ go ̀ ri i ̀ cɛɓ lɛ Kan wi ̀ s Yeesus Kiris ,
a ̀ nɛ a ̀ wugha ̀ ɓisu wis lɛ ti ghɛɓ ɓɛ ̀ ra ̀ rɛn ɗi ̀ nyi , nsoo ̀ tya ̀ a mɛ wu , nsoo ̀ tya ̀ a kaka cem yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ risugti ̀ i ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ faafa ̀ lɛ ̀ n mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , ɓi ̀ ki ̀ fee ̀ fe ̀ gsɛ ̀ n mi ̀ ni ri ̀ mi ̀ ni yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ ti ɓii ̀ ki ̀ kii .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , ti ̀ tɔɔgh mi ̀ ni lɛ ɓi ɓalag ri ̀ bɔgsɛ ̀ n ɓi san a ̀ nɛ a ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ sasay ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ n wi ̀ n , ɓɛ kɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ si ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓi cɛɓ ki Kan , ɓɛ ki rereɓ mini .
Terina ɓɔ ri ̀ coo nyaasɛ ̀ n lɛɛ ̀ gwey ri ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓisuu ki ̀ say ki ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ . Ghɛbina lɛ fyo ̀ oog ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ ! ti ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzaagh mi ̀ ni lɛ , ɓi rɔgsɛn ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ghɛghɛɓ ɓi ki ̀ ɓu ̀ u ̀ si ̀ , ɓi ̀ ca ̀ a ̀ si ̀ ɓɛ ̀ riris nyoo , ɓi ̀ le ̀ nle ̀ m ɓɛroɓɛ ɓɛ yin ɗi i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , ɓi ̀ yi ri ̀ ni ̀ ɗ ɗi n ̀ ɗem ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ɓi ̀ kona ̀ g lɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa lɛ a ̀ rɔ ̀ ŋ kiɓe ri ki ̀ ɓe ; wɔ ̀ lɛ kaana lɔŋ lɛ ɓi kiki ki ̀ rɔɔ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m , lɛ ri ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a ɓum ɓɛm ̀ bog ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Nya ̀ a ̀ nyaana ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ɓi ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll kɛ ̀ ɓi fɔy .
Faana Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓi tanɛɛ mi ̀ ni , lɛ fɔlɔɔ yɛɛ ri ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗii ɓi cɛɓ kin ki ri ̀ Yeesus Kiris .
Kɛ ̀ ɓi ɓuɓsi Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay .
Kɛ ̀ ɓi sɛɛti ɓiɓan ɓi ɓum ɓɛ kpaŋzii ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu Nghay a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , fiɓɓaaghna ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m lɛ syeesyee , ɓi ɓi rɔɔtɛɛ ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋ .
Lɛɛghna ki ̀ ɓe mɛkuu mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a falag fyo ̀ oog a tɛɛ ̀ zi mi ̀ ni nyimiɗ bee yice ̀ m , fɔɔnnɛ a ɓeŋ ri ̀ ɓa ɗin ɗice ̀ m ɗi lɛ : ri ̀ Nghay win , ri ̀ n ̀ ɗem win , ri ̀ nyoo yi ̀ n , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ti ̀ fin ɓisuu ri ̀ sugti ̀ i ̀ ɗi Kan wi ̀ s Yeesus Kiris .
Roa ̀ nɛ a regag mi ̀ ni a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i kiɓan kin ̀ ɓisuulɛ , a ̀ ti a ̀ roo ̀ za ̀ g mɛ ̀ ka ̀ g mii .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , ɓi ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋza ̀ g girig ɓisu wis .
Ɓi to ̀ gsag ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓis ɓɛ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , ɓi ̀ lwɛ ̀ ɗki ̀ ɓɔ yɛ ̀ ɛ kɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ngi Bɛ ̀ ll .
M ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzaagh mi ̀ ni ɓi ɗii ɗi Kan lɛ , ɓi ɓa ̀ y kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ nɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ ree ̀ mɛ ɓɛgeni ɓis ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
Geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ Kan wi ̀ s Yeesus Kiris yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa ri ̀ mi ̀ ni .
Mɛ ̀ Pol , ɓɛɛ ̀ Silas , ri ̀ Timote , ti ̀ ka ̀ nii ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓi Ki ̀ seŋi ki ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n ki a Tesalonika , ki ki ri ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ Seŋi wi ̀ s , ɓi Yeesus Kiris a ̀ Kan wi ̀ s .
Bɛ ̀ ll Seŋi ri ̀ Kan Yeesus Kiris ɓɛɛ fa mi ̀ ni lɛ ri ̀ geesɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ fyo ̀ oog .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ fafaa Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n ɓisu win tyɛ ̀ ki fɔy ; ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ kii fɔlɔɔ ɓisuulɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗin ɗyɛɛ ̀ tɔɔtɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n a te ̀ e ̀ ghte ̀ ghɛ ̀ n .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ti kaakalɛ ̀ n Ɓi ̀ seŋi ɓi ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ ɓa ɗin , ɓisuu kisi ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ kin , ri ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗin ɓi mɛ ̀ tɔɓ mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , ri ̀ ri ̀ kɛŋ ɗi ̀ ce ̀ m ɗi ɓi wowo ̀ g ɓi ̀ ki ni ̀ niɗ mɛrem .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ re ̀ resi lɛ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ti a ̀ yɔ ̀ mgi ̀ ɓum yɛ ̀ ɛ saaɗ a ̀ ri ̀ . Fɔlɔɔ yɛɛ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ ɓi ɓa ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ teri ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll ki ɓi wuwu mɛtɔɓ mii ̀ .
Lɛ ɓi san a ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ki ri lɛ saaɗ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a yee ̀ si girig ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ yeeyee ̀ si ̀ mi ̀ ni ,
a ̀ fa mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ɓi wowog rikɛŋ ri ̀ fɔɔsɛ ̀ n n ̀ ɗaŋ ri ɓi ̀ si ; a ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i fɔlɔɔ yɛ ̀ ɛ Kan Yeesus a ̀ ɓii ̀ re ̀ sɛɛ yi aɗyoo , nɗaŋ ri ɓum ɓii ɓɛ titom ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ ,
ɓi nɗo ̀ o ̀ wu ɗuu , lɛ a pɔnɔsi lɛ , ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yii ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ wog rikpaa ɗi Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ Kan wi ̀ s Yeesus .
Pɔnɔsi ̀ a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ teri ̀ , a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɗyaŋ ɗi fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ɓɛ kɛɛ ̀ wuɓsɛn i ̀ su wu Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki wuɓsɛn kitɛɛtɛn ki rikem ɗii ,
yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ri yu ̀ ɓi ŋwos anɛ ̀ n lɛ a kem ̀ ɓi ɓum ɓii , ɓɛ ki sɛsɛg nyi ri ̀ mis ɓi ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ; mi ̀ nii gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ gi ̀ kɔm ̀ ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ ti ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ mi ̀ ni .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓi ̀ sii ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɔɓɔ ̀ ŋzi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ɓisu win lɛ , di Bɛ ̀ ll wi ̀ s a ki lɛ ɓi ɓa ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ri ̀ n ̀ ɗee ̀ ghreŋi wii ; a ̀ ki ̀ ti ̀ lɛ ɓi ɓa ri ̀ bee i n ̀ ki ̀ yɛn ɓiɓan ɓi syeesyee ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓi kɔ ̀ nkɔ ̀ n , a ̀ ki ki ̀ lɛ ki ̀ say ki ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗin ɗyɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ kɛɛ ɓa lɛ syeesyee .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɗii ɗi Kan wi ̀ s Yeesus ɗi ɓii ̀ kemi ̀ ɓi mi ̀ ni , mi ̀ nii kem ɓi nyi , lɛ geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll wi ̀ s , ri ̀ i ̀ Kan Yeesus Kiris .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ ! ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki ki seesee ri ̀ sugti ̀ i ̀ ɗi Kan Yeesus Kiris , ri ̀ ri ̀ taŋzɛ ̀ n ɗi ti ̀ ri taŋzɛn nyi a nyoo , ti ̀ tɔɔgh mi ̀ ni lɛ ,
kɛ ̀ ɓi ca ̀ rɛn lɛ mum a fyaŋzi mi ̀ ni ki ̀ nyɛ ̀ ŋi ɓi syeesyee a ̀ n ̀ ɗɛli anɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ mii ̀ , nsoo ̀ lɛ a syaŋdi mi ̀ ni bwaɓ ɗi ri ̀ kuu ɗi ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗidɛŋ ɗi n ̀ ghay wudɛŋ wu ri lɛ wu fa nyi , nsoo ̀ ri ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ dɛŋ , nsoo ̀ ri ̀ kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ pwaa ̀ mi ̀ ni lɛ ɓi ̀ si yɛɛ kani , ki pisɛ ̀ n fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwos a Kan a ̀ mɛ kpaŋ .
Ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ kɛ ̀ ɛ ye ̀ gsi mini , nsoo ̀ ɓi-ghe ̀ y wu la , ɓisuulɛ ŋwos anɛ ̀ n a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ kpaŋ di ɓum ɓɛ ka resi ɓi lɛ ɓɛ naŋi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , Ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki mum ki ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɗyaŋi ̀ , ki resɛ ̀ n .
Ki ri ɗu ̀ u ̀ ri com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɔɔɓɔgsi ̀ ɓɛ rere ̀ ŋi ̀ lɛ bɛ ̀ ll , ki ra ̀ m ki kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ kɔ ̀ rii ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ki ri ̀ lɛ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , ki rɛsɛ ̀ n kɔmiɗ lɛ kɔ yɛɛ ri Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ɓi ̀ yitii ɓi lɛ n ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ mi ̀ ni ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki m ̀ ɓagha ̀ di n ̀ kaka a lɔ ̀ ŋkin ?
Wɔ ̀ lɛ , ɓi ̀ yii lɔŋ com ki ki ka ghegheegh nyi lɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ ka resɛn ɓigomi ̀ nɛ ; lɔŋ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kii i ̀ nnɛ ki ̀ ɓeta ̀ g ki mum ki ̀ n ki ɓii ̀ re ̀ sɛɛ .
Lɛ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu kiɓe wu a ri ̀ nyam wu ti ɓii ̀ ki ̀ kii kisay ; kɛɛ ̀ tɔtɔg lɔŋ lɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ka ghegheegh mɔ a ɗim ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ di nyi .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn innɛ Ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki mum ki ɓii ̀ re ̀ sɛɛ yi , Kan a ̀ wey kɔ ri ̀ cɔ ̀ ŋzɛn ki ki kpaŋii ̀ nyi ɓi ŋwɔm , a ̀ ti ̀ i ̀ si ̀ kɔ ri ̀ ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ki ɓi ri ̀ sugti ̀ i ̀ ɗii .
Ri ̀ yu ̀ y ɗi Kiɓeɓta ̀ g ki mum ɗi ki ̀ lɛɛ gɛ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu Sata ̀ n ; a ̀ ki ̀ i gɛ lɛ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ koŋnyoo ɓɛ ɓiɓan , ri ̀ da ̀ m yi ɓiɓan yi ɓɛpwa ̀ a ̀ ;
a ̀ ki ̀ i gɛ ki ̀ say ri ki ̀ ɓe mɛkuu mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m lɛ a ɓɔŋ ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɗyaŋi ̀ ɓisuulɛ ɓɛ ghaɓka ̀ ɓi n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ ɓi saaɗ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ lɛ a ̀ ghɛɓsi ̀ ɓɔ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ romii ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu wɛɛ naa ̀ zi ɓɔ bee , lɛ ɓɛɛ gherɛn ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓɛpwa ̀ a ̀ ,
di fɔɔnnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a yɔm ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi saaɗ , ɓɛ ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ kaa ki ɓagha ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗi kiɓe .
Ɓi san a ̀ nɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkis , ɓɔɔseŋi ɓis ɓɛ Kan a keesag lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ fafaa Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ɓisuu kiɓan kin , ɓisuulɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ nga ̀ mi ̀ ni a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n a ri ̀ tumɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓi ɓa ɓɛ ̀ ko ̀ rɛn ɓi ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗi Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay kɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki lɛ ɓi ɓa ɓɛ ̀ tɛnɛn , ri ̀ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓi ̀ gherɛɛ saaɗ .
Ki ̀ ɓan ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ ti ̀ mi ̀ ni mii ̀ , ri ̀ Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ ti ̀ ghagsi ̀ gha ̀ mi ̀ ni ki ri lɛ , ɓi ɓa ri ̀ ga ̀ ɓ ɓi ri ̀ kem ɗi Kan wi ̀ s Yeesus Kiris .
Fɔɔnnɛ si ̀ i ̀ rɛɛna lɔŋ ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , ɓi ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ti ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ ka ̀ mi ̀ ni , ri ̀ ŋwɔm nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ nɛ ti ̀ i nka ̀ nii ̀ mi ̀ ni .
Kan wi ̀ s Yeesus Kiris nyimiɗ , ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ Seŋi wi ̀ s anɛ a ̀ keesi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ si , a ̀ fa ɓi ̀ si fɔɔy a ̀ nɛ ɓi nɗem a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ri ̀ dya ̀ ɓɛn i syeesyee ,
ɓɛɛ fɔɔ ̀ si mi ̀ ni mɛ ̀ rem , ɓɛ fa mi ̀ ni i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu ki ̀ yɛn ɓiɓan ɓi syeesyee , ɓi mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ min mɛce ̀ m , ri ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓin ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ ! n ̀ siitɛɛ mi ̀ ni ki ̀ kpaa ̀ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋza ̀ g Bɛ ̀ ll ɓisu wi ̀ s , di jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Kan yɛ ̀ ɛ kɛn asu i ̀ sa ̀ a ̀ sa ̀ a ̀ , i ̀ ki keŋkem , fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ yɛɛ ̀ keŋkem a lɔ ̀ ŋkin .
Ɓi ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋza ̀ g girig Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ a kweɗ ɓi ̀ si ɓi ɓya ̀ g ɓi ɓiɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓum ɓi ɓi ri ri ̀ ri ̀ gɛn , ɓisuulɛ a ̀ a ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛɛ ri ri ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Kan a ̀ ti a ̀ roo ̀ za ̀ g mɛ ̀ ka ̀ g mii ; a ̀ ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ faa ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , a ̀ lɛgsi ̀ mi ̀ ni ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki mum .
Ti ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tyweeyi ri Kan ɓisu win lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ti ̀ tɔɔgh mi ̀ ni , ɓi ̀ ti ɓi ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g ɓyɔ ɓi ̀ ki ri ̀ ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ asu , ɓi ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ɓyɔ .
Kan a ki lɛ mɛ ̀ rem min mɛɛ tiŋi ɓi nkɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ ri ̀ ni ̀ ɗ ɗi nɗem ɗi Kiris a fala ̀ g .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ ! ti ̀ tɔɔgh mi ̀ ni ɓi ɗii ɗi Kan wi ̀ s Yeesus Kiris lɛ : Kɛ ̀ ɓi wuɓsɛn ɓɛgeni ɓin ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ ɓɔɓwɛɗ , ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓeni ki ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ tii ɓiɓan ɓi ti ̀ re ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ mi ̀ ni .
Mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ ɓi ̀ yii lannɛ ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ ɓi nɔɔ ̀ ti mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ mis , lɛ ɓi ̀ sii ɓagha ̀ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ ɓɔɓwɛɗ yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ ghɛɓka ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin .
Mum a ̀ fagha ̀ ɓi ɓisi ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓi ti ɗi zɛy , ti ̀ sasa ̀ la ̀ lɔŋ lɛ ri ̀ i ̀ ru ri ̀ ŋwos , ti ̀ wowo ̀ g mɛ ̀ tɔɓ ri ̀ ki ̀ fɔli lɛ n ̀ tɛ ̀ g wis wɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ siŋ wa ̀ a ̀ dɛŋ ɓi nyo ̀ o ̀ .
I ti ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ki yin lɛ ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi lɛ ti ̀ tɔg mi ̀ ni n ̀ ghɛɓsɛn , ti ̀ kɔ ̀ nga ̀ lɔŋ yɛɛri lɛ ti fa mi ̀ ni ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ .
Lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ ɓagha ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin , ti ̀ siŋdɛ ̀ nga ̀ mi ̀ ni lɛ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ kɔ ̀ ni ɓi lɛ a say , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi girig lɛ a ̀ ɗi .
Ti ̀ kpaa fɔlɔɔ ɓisuulɛ ti wowog lɛ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ foo ɓɛɛ ̀ ghɛghɛɓ cɛɓ ki iɓwɛɗ , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ko ̀ m com ki ki ̀ yɛn , ɓɛ roo ̀ ro ̀ o ̀ tɛ ̀ n ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ .
Ti ̀ tɔɔgh ɓumɓɛ ̀ n , ti ̀ ki reɓ ɓɔ ɓi ɗii ɗi Kan Yeesus lɛ , ɓɛɛ say ɓi fyo ̀ oog , ɓɛ ɗi ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓi ɓɔmiɗ ɓɔ yɛɛ reni ki ̀ ɗi ̀ g mii ̀ .
Ɓi san wi ̀ n , ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɓi fɔy riki ̀ ɗi kirɔɔ .
I mum a ̀ ɓe ̀ ni ki ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ tii ɓiɓan ɓi ti ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ nɛ ɓi , ɓa ̀ lina ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ , ɓi ̀ lɛg ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n mii ̀ , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ woo ̀ gh n ̀ too ̀ ri ̀ ɗ ɗi ri ̀ ɓa ɗii ɗin ̀ .
Kɛ ̀ ɓi teɗ nyi yɛ ̀ ɛ be ̀ na ̀ bena win ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog rɔ ̀ gsɛɛna nyi fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ geni win ̀ .
Kan a ̀ nɛ a falag fyo ̀ oog , nnyɛɛ fa mi ̀ ni fyo ̀ oog nyimiɗ ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , bee yice ̀ m ; Kan a ɓa ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ Pol yɛɛ kanii ̀ ɓi ̀ tɔki ̀ ɓi , ri ̀ ca ̀ g kɛm ̀ ; fɔlɔɔ nnɛ n ̀ ti n ̀ sangi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kaa ̀ ta ̀ ɓɛm ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , ri ̀ ka ̀ n ɗyɛm ɗyɛɛ ri lɔɔ .
Geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ Kan wi ̀ s Yeesus Kiris yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Mɛ ̀ Pol , n ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom a Yeesus Kiris lɛ ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ghɛɓsi ̀ wi ̀ s , ri ̀ Yeesus Kiris a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ dya ̀ ɓɛn yis .
N ̀ ka ̀ ni Timote , a ̀ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ wɛ ̀ m a ̀ man ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , Bɛ ̀ ll Seŋi ri ̀ Kan wi ̀ s Yeesus Kiris ɓɛɛ fa wɔ ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ geesɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ ri ̀ cenɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ fyo ̀ oog .
Fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ tɔka ̀ wɔ ̀ di n ̀ ti lɛ nkɛn ̀ a Masedwan , ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɔŋ lɛ , u kɔkɔri a Efɛɛzɛ lɛ u sii ̀ tɛn ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ re ̀ resi dɔgtɛ ̀ n yidɛŋ ,
ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki mɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ tɛn ɓi mɛ ̀ ka ̀ nka ̀ n ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ a ̀ ɓa ̀ a ̀ si ̀ ɗi boo ɗi kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sugtag , ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓyɛɛ ̀ titini ɓum lɛ ɓɛɛ nyoonyo ̀ lɛ ̀ n , ɓyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ghɛɓsi lɛ fe ̀ g a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ lɛ a ghɛɓsi ɓum lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n a kɛn asu .
Ri ̀ syɔn ɗi ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki n ̀ tɔɔgh wɔ ̀ kin ̀ ɗi ri lɛ , n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ ɓi nɗem wu wu ri wu ̀ tɛnɛn , ri ̀ ɓi nɗem wu wu ri lɛ sɛɛghisɛɛghi , ri ̀ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ti ̀ fye ̀ e ̀ rɛna ̀ .
Ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ naga ̀ bee inɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ nɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ bee i n ̀ kpaakpaayɛn ɓiɓan ɓi kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ su .
Ki kɔnkɔ ̀ n ɓɔ lɛ di ɓaa ɓaa ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ pɔɔ ̀ zii ki ̀ yii ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ yi nsoo ̀ com kɔm ̀ ki ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ , nsoo ̀ ki ɓɛɛ ̀ si ̀ isii ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ ri ̀ kaka ̀ li ̀ lɛ ki ri yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɔɔ ̀ kpaaghi ̀ .
Ti ̀ yii lɛ syeesyee lɛ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi rɔɔtɛɛ , di mum a ̀ ki ̀ i ki ̀ say ri ɓyɔ yɛ ̀ ɛ kɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ nkɔ ̀ n ;
ti ̀ ki yii lɛ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi yin ɓifalɛn ɓisuu ŋwaa ̀ saaɗ , ɓi ri lɔŋ ɓisuu ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ri ̀ ri ̀ gɛn , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ wooghrɛn , ɓɛ ̀ ɓe ̀ ni ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe , ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ risi nsoo ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , nsoo ̀ ɓyom ɓi ɓi ri ki ̀ ce ̀ li ̀ , ri ̀ ɓisuu ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ weeyi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓaa , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ jɛɛ ɓaa , ri ̀ ɓisuu ɓɛwoli ̀ -ɓum ,
ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ zyaa , ɓɛ ̀ baŋi ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kɔra ̀ g ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛ ̀ baŋi ̀ ( n ) ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -dune i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kpa ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pwa ̀ a ̀ pwaa ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ ka ̀ nɛ ̀ n bɛ ̀ ɗ yi ɓɛpwa ̀ a ̀ , ri ̀ com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ki yin yɛ ̀ ɛ syeesyee a ̀ dɔgtɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tɛnɛn a kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓi Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ n ̀ keŋke ̀ mi ̀ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tin wu ɓɛma ̀ a ̀ gh a re ̀ re ̀ si ̀ . Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n nnɛ ɓɛ reɓsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ .
N ̀ to ̀ gsaagh Yeesus Kiris a ̀ Kan wi ̀ s , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ fagha ̀ mɛ ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ ɓisuulɛ , a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ mum a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ tyweeyi ̀ , yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ nga ̀ mɛ ̀ lɛ nki nyi ki ̀ say .
Ma ̀ a ̀ nɛ n ̀ fee ̀ fe ̀ nga ̀ ka ̀ nyi abɛ ̀ y , n ̀ -yee ̀ ye ̀ e ̀ si ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , n ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ri ̀ baŋi ̀ , mɛ ̀ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n innɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ woka ̀ nyi ̀ inyi ̀ g ɓisuulɛ n ̀ -yigha ̀ ɓi com ki n ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ , lɛ m ̀ ɓagha ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ gherɛɛ .
Fɔɔnnɛ geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ Kan wi ̀ s i ̀ ronga ̀ i ̀ so ̀ so ̀ ɓ , ɓi mɛ ̀ bas ɗi ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ri ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi Yeesus Kiris .
Jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ a ̀ nɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɔŋ kiteri ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tyweeyi wuce ̀ m yɛ ̀ ɛ ri lɛ Yeesus Kiris a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ziinɛ lɛ a ghɛɓsi ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe , nni ɓi ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe ɓɛn ̀ , mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ri lɛ ɓog .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ woka ̀ mɛ ̀ nyi ̀ inyi ̀ g lɛ di Yeesus Kiris a resi ri ̀ ni ̀ ɗ ɗii ɗi nɗem ɓi mɛ ̀ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe a ̀ n ̀ tonto , fɔɔnnɛ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ki ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ ɓisuu ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ gherɛɛ nyi lɛ ɓɛɛ teɗ cɛɓ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Roa ̀ nɛ a maa ̀ la ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ wu , roa ̀ nɛ ɓum ɓɛ yin lɛ ɓɛ ghɛn , nyi yɛɛ ri m ̀ bobog a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ ri ̀ n ̀ nyaasɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ ri ̀ kem fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ . A ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n .
Man wɛm ̀ Timote , ki ̀ ɓan ki mɛ ̀ n ̀ siŋ ̀ dɛɛ wɔ ̀ ki rarɛɛ yi ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Nghay a ̀ re ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ɓi san wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ; ɓi ɗi yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓyɛɛ ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ , ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ u ɗu ̀ u syeesyee a ̀ wɛ ̀ y ,
u ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ri ̀ syeesyee a ̀ n ̀ ɗem . Syeesyee a ̀ n ̀ ɗem a ̀ nɛ ̀ n , ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ mɛ naŋ nyi , ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗyaa ɗi ɓɛn ̀ mɛ ̀ nig yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓumɓɛ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ teri .
Imenee ri ̀ Alɛgsaŋdirɛ ɓɛ n ̀ fagha ̀ ri ̀ Sata ̀ n lɛ ɓɛɛ yilag ri ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋ ɗi myɔm maa lɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ to ̀ gti Bɛ ̀ ll ki ̀ ɓe , ɓɛ ri ɓi ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n .
Ki ̀ ɓan ki asu ki ntɔki ki ri lɛ , ɓum ɓɛɛ tɔtɔg Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ ɓan , ɓɛ ɓɔɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzi ̀ nyi , ɓɛ ren ̀ ɗe ̀ n nyi mɛ ̀ tɔɓ di ɓɛɛ ̀ fafa nyi ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n ɓisuu ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ,
ɓisuu mɛfo ̀ m , ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ , lɛ di ti ghɛɓ cɛɓ ki fyo ̀ oog ri ̀ tɛ ̀ tɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , ti ̀ falɛ ̀ n ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ti ̀ ɓa ɗi ̀ ri ̀ mum .
Fɔlɔɔ yɛɛ kii ̀ lɛ , a ̀ rɔɔtɛ ̀ n a ̀ ki yɛ ̀ lɛn ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ghɛɓsi ̀ wi ̀ s ,
a ̀ nɛ a kɔ ̀ ngi lɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛɛ ghɛn cɛɓ , ɓɛ kpaŋ ɓi nɗɛli wulɛ ɓɛɛ yi saaɗ .
Ɓisuulɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ bogtɛ ̀ n , mum a ̀ ki ɓa girig bog ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ nɛ lɛ ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ ɓum , nnyɛɛ ri Yeesus Kiris a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ mum ;
nnyɛɛ falɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyimiɗ lɛ a leɓ pon anɛ ɓi go ̀ ri i ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ; fɔlɔɔ a ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki ki kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ , ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ki ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ siŋdɛn ,
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓɛ rɛsi ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ mii ̀ lɛ mɓa n ̀ ghagsi ̀ -ɓɔlɛ ri ̀ n ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom anɛ mii ̀ . Nkpaakpaa saaɗ , m ̀ pwa ̀ a ɓi , n ̀ ɗi ̀ n ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g a ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , a ̀ nɛ a re ̀ resi ɓɔ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ saaɗ .
Ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗyɛm ̀ ɗi ri min lɛ ɓɛ ̀ baŋi ̀ ɓɛɛ ɓɔɔɓɔ ̀ ŋza ̀ g ja ̀ ŋ bimiɗ , ɓɛ pɛpɛ ̀ si ̀ ɓya ̀ g ɓi ɓi ri ɓi ̀ tɛnɛn aɗyoo , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ bim nsoo ̀ paa ̀ zi ̀ .
Ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ girig ki ̀ waataagh yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ , ɓɛ ɓa ri ̀ ntoo ̀ ri ̀ ɗ ; n ̀ waa ̀ waa wɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ yeesɛn , ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ki ɓaaghraagh tyo ̀ ŋ ti ti yeesɛɛ ri ̀ ɓag , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ waatɛn mɛrɛ ̀ ŋ mɛ gol nsoo ̀ lɛ mɛ mɛ ri mɛ ̀ syaghɛn ri ɓyom ɓi ɓi ciɓtaagh ki ̀ rɔɔ , nsoo ̀ ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ɓi ɓi kɛŋi lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Lɔŋ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi syeesyee ɓi ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ , ɓyɛɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ mɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ ŋ maa , lɛ fɔlɔɔ yɛɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔnɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
Giɓ a ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ a maa ̀ rɛn lɛ fyo ̀ oog ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓɛɛ ̀ re ̀ resi nyi , a ̀ ɓa ri ̀ mɛ ̀ wog lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Mɛ ̀ n ̀ faa ɓi ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ite ̀ ɗ wulɛ ɓɛɛ reresi nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ lami ɓɛ ̀ baŋi ̀ , ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɔŋ ki si ̀ mi myɔm maa ,
ɓisuulɛ Adam nnɛ ɓɛ loka ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i , ɓɛ ɓɔ ̀ ɓ min Ɛɛvɛ ,
ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ a ̀ a Adam nnɛ ɓɛ yegsi ̀ gha ̀ , lɔŋ giɓ innɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ mɛ ye ̀ gsi ̀ , a ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ɓe .
Nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ , a ̀ ki ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɛ cɛɓ , lɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔn , ɗi ̀ lɛ a ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ghɛɓ ɓi nkɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ n n ̀ tɛnɛn ɓi nghay , a ̀ ki sɛɛ ̀ dɛn nyimiɗ ɓi zi .
Jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ lɛ , i kɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ nkɔn mum lɛ a ɓa ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a kɛɛ ̀ si Ki ̀ seŋi , di ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n mii ̀ a kɔ ̀ nkɔn syeesyee a ̀ ki ̀ saay .
Nni ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ , n ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ si ̀ -ki ̀ seŋi a ɓa ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yin ɗi ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓum ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ cɛɛ ̀ cɛ ̀ mdɛ ̀ n . A ̀ ɓa giɓ bog , kɛ ̀ ɛ keesi ɓinɔɔ ̀ nɔɔ ̀ , a ̀ ɓa ŋwaa ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n , a ̀ yi ri ̀ ghɛɓ ri ̀ ɓum , a ̀ ɓe ̀ gi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ke ̀ n a mɛɛ mii lɛ syeesyee , a ̀ ki ɓa ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ yi ri ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɗi ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓan .
Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi lɛ a ɓa ki ̀ nɔɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ g nsoo ̀ lɛ mum a ̀ ɓi ̀ gu ̀ g , ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɔŋ lɛ a ɓa ki ̀ fyo ̀ oog ki mum , kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa mum a ̀ ɓɛsaaka nsoo ̀ lɛ a ̀ keesi ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni .
Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ si ̀ naa yi ̀ i ̀ i ɓum lɛ syeesyee , a ̀ yi ri ̀ ki ̀ lɛ ɓɔn ɓii ɓɛɛ ɓa ri ̀ mɛ ̀ wog , ɓɛ fala ̀ g nyi bɔgsɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ .
Ɓisuulɛ i mum a ̀ yii ɓi rikɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ si ̀ ɗi naa yi ̀ i ̀ i ɓum lannɛ a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ yi ri ̀ fiɓi ̀ ɗi Ki ̀ seŋi ki Bɛ ̀ ll ?
Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi lɛ a ̀ ɓa ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛɛ n ̀ ɗen nyɔn , lɛ ɓi ̀ daŋa ̀ ɓi ri lɛ ɓi ɓɔg nyi ɓi nto , a ̀ ki ghay lɛ a ̀ teri zɔɔ yi Sata ̀ n .
Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ girig lɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓi dan ɓɛɛ sɛg nyi di ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ sɛɛti nyi , fɔlɔɔ a ki ̀ nyi lɛ a kpi ɓi fi ̀ ram fi Sata ̀ n .
Ɓɛ ̀ dyaaki ̀ rɛ ̀ girig ɓɛɛ ɓa ri ̀ ri ̀ mum , ɓɛ ɓa ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin ɓii ̀ ghe ̀ eghelɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ falɛn ɓi mɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ g lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓa ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin ɓii ̀ kaakaa rifɔ ̀ n ɗi mɛso ̀ o ;
ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ ɓiɓan ɓi ɓi ri ɓi ̀ nyamɛn ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ri ̀ nɗem wu wu ri wu ̀ tɛnɛn .
Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ ɓɛ ka fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n ɓɔ fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ teɗ min mɛkɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ mɛ ɓɛdyaaki ̀ rɛ ̀ di ɓɛ ghɛɛ ɓi kiɓan ki ɓeɓtɛn a lɔ ̀ ŋkaa .
Ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ girig ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ ɓɛ ɓa ri ̀ ri ̀ mum , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa ri mɛ ̀ wɔ ̀ wɔri ̀ , ɓɛ kɛɛ ̀ falɛn ɓi mɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ g , ɓɛ ɓa ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ tyweeyi ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m .
Dyaaki ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ giɓ bog , a ̀ ki kɛ ̀ ɛkɛɛ ̀ si ̀ ɓɔn ɓii , ri ̀ ri ̀ mɛɛ ɗii lɛ syeesyee .
Ɓisuulɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki kisay ki dyaaki ̀ rɛ ̀ lɛ syeesyee , ɓɛ ti ɓɛ ɓala ̀ g ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓaa ɓɛɛ ̀ nyaanyaa ̀ si ̀ , ɓɛ ki ri ̀ lɛ ɓɛ toto ̀ g kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ ris ɓi nɗem ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki wu ti ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ wɔ ɓi Yeesus Kiris .
N ̀ ka ̀ nii ̀ wɔ ̀ kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ nɛ ki ̀ ɓan kifog , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tyweeyi lɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u ki ghɛɛ ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ̀ mɛtii ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , nsoo ̀ ma ̀ a lɛ ̀ mzii yi ̀ , ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi nkpaa ɓi ri wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ re ̀ sii lannɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ u ghɛɓ ɓi naa i ̀ ɓum i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ seŋi ki ɓɔn ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ cem a ̀ ki ɓa rikwi ̀ y ɗi ̀ ki ̀ le ̀ mi ̀ ki saaɗ .
Ki ri girig saaɗ lɛ ki ̀ ɓan ki ki ri ki ̀ nyamɛn ɓi ntyweeyi wis ki rimi yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki yugha ̀ y yɛ ̀ ɛ mum a ̀ mɛ ̀ mu ̀ u ̀ , ki ghɛnɛ ̀ n lɛ ki ri lɛ saaɗ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu Kitɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay , ki resɛ ̀ n a ɓum ɓɛ titom , ki kaa ̀ ka ̀ lɛ ̀ n ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ , ɓɛ ki gherɛn kɔ ɓi ziinɛ , ki ɓɔg aɗyoo ɓi ri ̀ gwey ɓi ɗu ̀ m .
N ̀ ghay a kpaaghi lɛ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n lɛ , ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ siito ̀ n , ɓum ɓɛɗɛŋ ɓɛ naŋigɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ nɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ mɛ ̀ ghay mɛ mɓɔ ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ n ri ̀ dɔgtɛ ̀ n yi ɓiɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay ;
ɓi fyɛɛ ̀ -fyɛɛ ̀ ɓi ŋwɔm i ̀ ghe ̀ y ɓi ɗu ̀ m a ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ re ̀ resi ɓiɓan ɓi ɓɛpwa ̀ a ̀ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ mɛ ̀ rem maa mɛ ri mɛ ̀ tɔ ̀ nɛn ɗi swiɗ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓa ̀ ŋii ̀ ɓi ɗuu lɛ pɔɔŋ .
Ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ rere ̀ g lɛ mum kɛ ̀ ɛ wɔlɛn , kɛ ̀ ɛ ki ɗi ɓiɗila ̀ g ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɛ yii saaɗ ɓɛɛ ɗiɗi di ɓɛɛ ̀ fafa nyi ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n .
Kɔlɛ ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ɓi rɔɔtɛɛ , fɔɔnnɛ com ki ma ̀ ghɛn ki yin ; kɛɛ ̀ tɔtɔg yɛɛri lɛ mum a ɗi com ki ̀ ce ̀ m di a fafa Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n ,
ɓisuulɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n ɓi ti ɓi kila ̀ g lɛ ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓyɛɛ ɓa ɓi ̀ tɛnɛn .
U ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ syeesyee a ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say a Yeesus Kiris di u kakali ɓɛgoni ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ u ̀ ki re ̀ resi lɛ u mɛmɛni wɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ ɓi nghay ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi righerɛ ̀ n ri ̀ syeesyee a ̀ dɔgtɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ u ̀ yila ̀ ka ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , u ̀ ca ̀ ɗ da ̀ ɗki ̀ yi zɛy ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ka ̀ nka ̀ n mɛ ɓitu ̀ g ɓi ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ .
Mɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi nyoo yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓi ri ̀ falɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ; ɓisuulɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ ɗi nyoo ɓi ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ ti tyɛɛ ̀ fafa ite ̀ ɗ ɓi mɛ ̀ mu ̀ u ̀ ɗi ɓiisɛɛ ɓi kiɓaa ̀ ri ̀ gɛɓsɛ ̀ n kɔm ̀ lɛ ri ̀ falɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi ghɛɓsii bee lɛɛ ̀ gwey ; ɗi ri ri ̀ n ̀ ka ̀ g wu cɛɓ ki gɛɛ ̀ nɛ ri ̀ ki kɛɛ ̀ yu ̀ yuiy .
Jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛn i ̀ ri ̀ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ a ̀ nɛ ɓum ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ teri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ nywey .
Ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓi ̀ sii ̀ kpuukputɛ ̀ n , ti ̀ ki ɗu ̀ u ̀ ɗuu mii ̀ ki ri lɛ , ti ̀ foga ̀ dya ̀ ɓɛn yis ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ cem , a ̀ ki ɓa nghɛɓsi ̀ -ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ ɓiisɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
Ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓi u ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ siŋɗɛɛ ɓum lɛ ɓɛɛ ki , u ̀ ki re ̀ eresa ̀ g ɓɔ ɓyɔ ̀ .
Mum kɛ ̀ ɛ sɛɛti riɓa ɗyɔɔ ɗi u ̀ ri ̀ ŋwɔɓti , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ɓaya ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ɓisuu ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n ɓi ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓyɔɔ , ɗi ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɗyɔɔ , ri ̀ ɓi nkɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓi ri ̀ tɛn .
A ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u , si ̀ i ̀ rɛn ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓa ̀ y ɗi ɓiɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ ri ̀ rere ̀ ɓ ɗi ɓum , ɗi ̀ ri ̀ re ̀ e ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɗi ɓɔ .
Kɔ ̀ ɔ sɛɛti rifa ɗi Nghay ɗi u ̀ ri ̀ ri ɗyɔ , ɗi u ̀ teka ̀ ɓi ri ̀ kpaa ɗi ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan , ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ Kiseŋi ɓɛ saghi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓya ̀ g ɓi nyo ̀ o ̀ .
Falɛn wɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ bimiɗ u ̀ ki foŋ n ̀ ɗem ɓi ki ̀ say kin ̀ di fɔɔnnɛ kɛɛ ghɛnɛn ɓi mis mɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m lɛ ri ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ɗyɔɔ ɗi kisay ɗyɛɛ ̀ ceecenɗɛ ̀ n .
U ̀ kona ̀ g lɛ ri ̀ wɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi u re ̀ resi ɓum , u ̀ ki si ̀ i ̀ rɛn mii ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ ; ɓisuulɛ i u ki ̀ ki fɔlɔɔ , u ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɓsii lɛ ri ̀ wɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ , ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ wowog rikpaa ɗyɔɔ .
Kɔ ̀ ɔ fwa ̀ a ̀ dag kitu ̀ g ki mum , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ u ̀ reɓ nyi lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ soŋi ; u ̀ reɓki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ dɛli ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ goni ,
u ̀ reɓki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ ri ̀ lɛ u ̀ reɓ ɓɛ ̀ gaa , u ̀ reɓki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛɓwɛɗ yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ ri ̀ lɛ u ̀ reɓ ɓɛ ̀ goni ɓɛ ɓɛyi ̀ ɓ ; ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗin ̀ ɗi ̀ ce ̀ m ɗi ɓa ɗi ̀ tɛnɛn lɛ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ .
Nyaasag mɛ ̀ kpɔɓ mɛ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ mɛ mɛ ri lɛ mɛ ̀ kpɔɓ .
I n ̀ kpɔɓ wu giɓ wu ri ri ̀ ɓɔn nsoo ̀ lɛ do ̀ o ̀ , ɓɔɓti ɓɛ ka ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ loo ̀ gh ki ̀ yilaagh lannɛ ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ ghɛɓ ɓi naa ya ̀ a ̀ i ɓum yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ fa ɓɛ ̀ yali ̀ ɓaa ɓyom ɓi ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓɔ ki ̀ faa ̀ lɛ fɔlɔɔ yɛɛ ti a ̀ rɔɔghi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
N ̀ kpɔɓ wu wu ri lɛ n ̀ kpɔɓ , wu wu rɔɓi nlɛŋlɛŋ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mum , wu ri nkpɔɓ wu wu ri ri ̀ dya ̀ ɓɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , wɔ yɛɛ ti wɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ fwɛy ritɔtɔ ̀ g ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll n ̀ ghɛɓsɛn ɓi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ i ̀ ru yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwos .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , n ̀ kpɔɓ wu wɛɛ ̀ ka nɔ ̀ ɔnɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ ri ̀ yɛ ̀ y ɗi cɛɓ wu ri ki ̀ loŋ nsoo ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ wu kaka cem ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ u siŋɗag mɛ ̀ kpɔɓ ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓi ̀ n , lɛ di ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛɛ ɓa kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓum ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ cɛmdɛ ̀ n mɔ mii ̀ .
I mum a ̀ yii ɓi ri ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋ ɗi ɓum ɓii , a ̀ ɓiisɛ ̀ n ri ̀ mɛɛ ɗii , di a ̀ roo ̀ zɛɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ; ri ̀ kuu ɗi mum ɗi fɔlɔɔ ɗi ɓeɓtɛɛ ɗi cee ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yin ngherɛ ̀ n .
Ɓi ɗi lɛ ɓɛɛ kan ̀ n ̀ kpɔɓ wu giɓ ɓi ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ mɛ ̀ kpɔɓ , wu ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi kiɓaa ̀ giɓ anɛ a ̀ ka kpaŋ ɓi be ̀ g mɛ ̀ tin mɛraa , wu ki ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ giɓ anɛ a ̀ wɔla ̀ lɔŋ yii bog .
Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ a ɓa giɓ anɛ ɓum ɓɛ yii ɓi ̀ syeesyee ɓii ɓi mɛki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ mɛ tɔɔsag ɓɔn , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ a ngha ̀ ɓki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ke ̀ n lɛ syeesyee , a ̀ so ̀ o ̀ ghi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ , a ̀ ghɛɓsa ̀ g ɓum ɓɛ nyi ̀ inyi ̀ g , a ̀ ki kaakaa lɛ a ki ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi syeesyee .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog u ̀ ɓe ̀ n mɛ ̀ kpɔɓ mɛ mɛ kaka ɓi ̀ ɓwɛɗ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓisuulɛ i ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi mɛ ̀ rem maa mɛɛ ̀ ka kɔ ̀ nkɔn ɓi mɛ ghasi ɓɔ ri ̀ Kiris ɓɛ ɓa ri ̀ za ̀ y i ̀ nɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ kɛngi ti ̀ mɛ ̀ wɛy ,
ɓɛ ɓa ri ̀ bɛ ̀ lɛn ɓisuulɛ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗin ̀ ɗi yogsii n ̀ siŋdɛn waa wu n ̀ tonto wu ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ di ɓɛ mɛ teɗ .
A ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ di ̀ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ lɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ri kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ say , ɓɛ yila ̀ g n ̀ de ̀ ŋi ̀ wulɛ , ri ̀ naa i ̀ nɛ ̀ n mii ̀ ɓɛ ɗiŋi ̀ , ɓɛ teeti ̀ cɛɓ ki ɓɛ ̀ ɓɔlɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ wɔ ̀ wɔri ̀ , ɓɛ sagtɛ ̀ n ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ɗi ɓɛ ri kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ say , ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓaa ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ki kpaa ̀ .
Ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗyɛm ̀ ɗi ri lɛ mɛ ̀ kpɔɓ mɛ mɛ kaka ɓɔɓti , mɛɛ kɛngi ti ̀ mɛ ̀ wɛy , mɛ yay ɓɔn , mɛ ɓeŋ ̀ naa yaa , di fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ nɛm be ̀ na ̀ bena bee inɛ a totog ɓi ̀ si ki ̀ ɓe .
Ɓisuulɛ ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ti gi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɗimɛn bee , ɓɛ nɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ Sata ̀ n .
I giɓ adɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ gherɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ kpɔɓ mɛ mɛ rii ̀ ɓi boo yi ̀ i ̀ i mum , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ mɔ ki ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi , lɛ n ̀ tɛ ̀ g wu mɛkpɔɓ mɛn ̀ wɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ siŋ ɗi Ki ̀ seŋi ki Kiris , fɔɔnnɛ Ki ̀ seŋi ki ri lɛ ki teɗ n ̀ tɛ ̀ g wu mɛkpɔɓ mɛ mɛ ri kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mum .
Ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ Kiseŋi ɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛkɛɛ ̀ si ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan lɛ syeesyee , a ̀ ɓiisɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ teeteki ̀ n ̀ tɔɓ lɛ ɓɛɛ kakali ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛ ki re ̀ resi ɓyɔ , ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ri ̀ n ̀ yaasɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ a ̀ cee a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛmbog gɛ ̀ n yiɓɛɛ ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : Ɓaa ka ̀ ŋ ɓi ŋwɔm wu sani ̀ nya a ̀ nɛ a ki ̀ ki kisay , fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say a ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ le ̀ ɓ .
