Com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ri ki ̀ tɛnɛn ɓisuu ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ tɛnɛn , wɔ ̀ lɛ com kidɛŋ ki yin ki tɛnɛn ɓisuu ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri lɛ tɔɔtɔɓki , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n , ɓisuulɛ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ri ̀ nɗem waa , ɓi ri lɛ tɔɔtɔɓki .
Ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kpaaghi ̀ lɛ ɓɔɔ yii Bɛ ̀ ll , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓɛ roo ̀ ro ̀ o ̀ zɛ ̀ n nyi ɓi mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ maa , ɓum ɓɛ ɓee ̀ zɛɛ ri ̀ ɓa ɗyaa ɗin ̀ , ɓɛ ri ri ̀ n ̀ too ̀ te ̀ ɗ , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓa ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ ki syeesyee a ̀ ki ̀ ɓan nsoo ̀ bog .
Ɓi san wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , re ̀ resi ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ri lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ syeesyee a ̀ dɔgtɛ ̀ n a kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ .
U ̀ kpaa ɓi ̀ tu ̀ g ɓi ɓum lɛ ɓyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ nɔnɔ mɛrɔ ̀ g lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ mum , ri ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ ki ɓa ri i ̀ te ̀ ɗ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓi nkɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓ ɗi nɗem .
U ̀ kpaa ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ lɛ ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ girig ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ ri ̀ cɛɓ ki ɓum ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ ghɛn lɛ ki ri cɛɓ ki ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa ri mɛ ̀ wɔ ̀ wɔri ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa ɓɛkpa ̀ n ɓɛ mɛrɔ ̀ g , ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ fafaa ɓɛsyeesyee ɓɛ deɓ ,
lɛ di ɓɛɛ resag ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛ ɓwɛ ̀ ɗ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛɛ kee ̀ si lɛ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yii ɓaa , ri ̀ ɓɔn ɓaa ,
ɓɛ ɓa ri ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ ɓeŋɗɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ nde ̀ ŋi ̀ wu ɓidan , ɓɛ ɓa ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛ ɓɛ foŋi n ̀ ɗem ri ̀ gi ̀ lɛ ̀ n i ̀ nɛ ɓi naa lɛ syeesyee , ɓɛ rɔɔta ̀ g mɛ ̀ rem ɓɛ wog ɓɛ ̀ yii ɓaa , fɔɔnnɛ ɓum ɓaa fen ɓi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Rereɓ girig ɓɛ ̀ dɛli ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓa ri ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m .
Wɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ u ̀ ɓa ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗi ɓiɓan ɓi syeesyee , u ̀ re ̀ e ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɓum dɔgtɛ ̀ n inɛ i ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tɛnɛn , ɗi ̀ ri ̀ mum .
Ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓyɔɔ ɓyɛɛ ɓa lɛ sɛɛghi sɛɛghi , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ com ki ɓɛ fen mii ̀ , lɛ di ɓɛ ̀ be ̀ na ̀ bena ɓis ɓɛɛ wog n ̀ too ̀ ri ̀ ɗ , ɓɛ rɔɓ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓeɓtɛn ki ɓɛ fen a lɔ ̀ ŋkis .
U ̀ kpaa ɓɛ ̀ kpa ̀ n lɛ ɓɛɛ wog ɓɛ ̀ masa ̀ ɓaa ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , ɓɛ puu ̀ pu ̀ ɓsi ɓɔ mɛ ̀ rem , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ tu ̀ u ̀ zi kiɓan ki ɓɛ ̀ masa ̀ ɓaa ɓɛ kpaa ,
ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ fyaasi com , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ re ̀ sii ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m lɛ ɓɛ ri ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ tyweeyii lɛ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ nyaa ̀ si dɔgtɛ ̀ n i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ghɛɓsi ̀ wi ̀ s .
Ɓisuulɛ geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ sim a ̀ cɛɓ ɓisuu ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , i ̀ mɛ re ̀ sɛ ̀ n ,
geesɛ ̀ n yi ̀ i ̀ inɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ re ̀ resi ɓisi lɛ ti roo ̀ zɛn cɛɓ ki kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓiɓan ɓi ɓyɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ngi ɓum ɓi ziinɛ , ti ̀ ghɛɓ ɓi ziinɛ ri ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n , ti ̀ ɓa lɛ saaɗ ti ̀ ki falɛn ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ,
ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ti ka ɓoŋɓoŋ coo ŋwos a ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ dya ̀ ɓɛn yis , ti ̀ ki ɓoŋɓoŋ ti ri ̀ kem ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll wi ̀ s anɛ a ̀ teŋmɛɛ , ri ̀ n ̀ ghɛɓsi ̀ wi ̀ s Yeesus Kiris ,
a ̀ nɛ a ̀ falɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyimiɗ ɓisu wis lɛ a pwaŋ ̀ yi ̀ ɓi ̀ si ɓi ki ̀ ɓe mɛkuu mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ ki ̀ lɛ ti ɓa ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kitɛnɛn ki kɛɛ woo ̀ ghrɛn ɗi ̀ nyi ; ki falɛ ̀ n ɓi ri ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ɗi ɓiɓan ɓi syeesyee .
Ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi u ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ kakalii ɓum ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓi ̀ n lɔɔ , u ̀ te ̀ e ̀ te ̀ e ̀ si ̀ ɓɔ nyoo , u ̀ ki fwa ̀ a ̀ dag ɓɔ ɗi ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ wu ̀ ce ̀ m wu u ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ wɔ . Kɔ ̀ ɔ gherɛn lɛ mum a sɛɛ ̀ ti wɔ ̀ .
Yiti ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ ki ɓɛ ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gɔmi ̀ na ̀ mɛ ̀ wog ; ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ i com ki ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ tɔɔgh ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ ki , ɓɛ ki fɛmɓɛn ɓi ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗi kiɓan kice ̀ m ki ki ri lɛ syeesyee .
Ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ wɛ ̀ ɗ mum , ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ ɓum ɓɛ fyo ̀ oog , ɓɛ ɓa ri ̀ syeesyee a ̀ nɗem , ɓɛ ghɛɓ lɔŋ lɛ fyo ̀ oog ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ si girig ti ̀ ɓagha ̀ abɛ ̀ y kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n , ɓi ̀ si ri ̀ ntoo ̀ te ̀ ɗ , ɓi ̀ si ɓi ri ̀ ɗim ; ti ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kpa ̀ n ɓɛ ɓiɓan mɛkuu mɛ ̀ kuu , ɓi mɛ ̀ rem mɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ngi ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ɓyɛɛ ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi mɛmu ̀ u ̀ , ti ̀ ghɛghɛ ̀ ɓ ɓi ri ̀ gɛn ri ̀ ɓi m ̀ mi ̀ i ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n , ti ̀ ɓeɓe ̀ ɓ ɓum , ti ̀ ki ɓe ̀ eɓee ̀ zɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ si ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ rɔɔ-nɗem a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ghɛɓsi ̀ wi ̀ s , ri ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ nyi ɓisuu ɓum , ɓi resɛ ̀ nga ̀ ,
nni a ̀ ghɛɓsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ si , a ̀ a ɓisuu ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi saaɗ , ɓi ti ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ , lɔŋ a ̀ ghɛɓsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ si lɛ nɗem wu nyi ̀ inyi ̀ g wu a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ wɔ , ri ̀ ɗu ̀ u ̀ ɗu ̀ u ̀ ɗi ɗi ti ɗi kila ̀ g lɛ mum a ɓii ̀ ti ki ̀ yalɛɛ , ri ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗi Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay kɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ lag lɛ mum a ghay nyɔɔnyɔn a ̀ mum .
Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ romga ̀ y Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ki ̀ n ɓi ɓi ̀ si lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓi go ̀ o ̀ i ̀ Yeesus Kiris a ̀ n ̀ ghɛɓsi ̀ wi ̀ s ,
lɛ di ti ɓa ri ̀ ga ̀ ɓ ɓi dya ̀ ɓɛn i cɛɓ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , yɛ ̀ ɛ geesɛ ̀ n yi ̀ i ̀ i mɛ ki ̀ lɛ ti ɓa lɛ saaɗ ɓi mis mii ̀ .
Jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ nkɔ ̀ ngi lɛ u sii ̀ rɛn ɓi ri ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ ɗi yɔ ̀ di fɔɔnnɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛɛ tee ̀ si nyoo lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ɗi ɓiɓan ɓi syeesyee ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ rɔɔtɛɛ ki ki ɓa ri gɛɓsɛ ̀ n ɓisuu ɓum .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , lɛgha nyoey yi kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ -su ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ a ̀ ɓa ̀ a ̀ si ̀ ɗi boo , ri ̀ ɓɛsaaka , ri ̀ ri ̀ ka ̀ a ̀ ka ̀ da ̀ g ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓidɔ ̀ gsɛna , ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ghɛɓsii ɓi , ɓyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓa com .
I ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ yu ̀ u ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓu ̀ u ̀ si ̀ ki lɛ gasɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ kpi ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , rɔ ̀ gsɛn nyi gɛ ̀ n yiɓɛɛ ̀ , ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , foŋa nyi ɓi nwɔŋi ̀ .
U ̀ yii lɛ ri ̀ kuu ɗi mum ɗi fɔlɔɔ ɗi ri ɓi ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki bee , ɗi kiki ̀ ki ̀ ɓe , di ɗyɛɛ ̀ faafa ̀ lɛ ̀ n ɗyɔmiɗ zɔɔ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗi rom yi wɔ ̀ Aritemas nsoo ̀ lɛ Tisig , u ̀ fyaŋzi ̀ i ̀ mɛ ̀ ki ̀ yu ̀ u ki tanɛɛ a Nikopolis lɛ wɔɔ nnɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ nkpaa lɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ ghagsii bu ̀ ma ̀ .
Pe ̀ gsɛn ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɗi Zenas a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ coo n ̀ ɗe ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna , ri ̀ Apolos ɓi le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ com kidɛŋ kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ kaarɛn ɓɔ .
Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓi nɗaŋ wis ɓɛɛ yilɛn ri ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ɗi ɓiɓan ɓi syeesyee lɛ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ ki ̀ kii ɓɛ ̀ gɛni-ɓiɓan ɓɛ ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ lɛɛ lɛ fyɛ ̀ ɗ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓi ̀ ɗu ̀ n .
Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ri fɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓɛ togsaagh yi ̀ wɔ ̀ . Wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ to ̀ gsi ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ keesa ̀ g ɓi ̀ si ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n . Geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Mɛ ̀ Pol a ̀ nɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ki ̀ mbu ̀ ŋ ɓisuu Yeesus Kiris ɓɛɛ ̀ geni wɛ ̀ m a ̀ nɛ lɛ Timote , ɓi ̀ si yɛɛ kani lɛ ri ̀ Filemɔŋ a ̀ reŋka ̀ ŋ wi ̀ s a n ̀ ɗem , a ̀ nɛ ti ki ̀ ki kisay kifog ri ̀ nyi ,
ri ̀ geni wi ̀ s a giɓ anɛ lɛ Apya , ri ̀ reŋka ̀ ŋ wi ̀ s anɛ lɛ Arisip a ̀ nɛ ti ɗu ̀ u ̀ ɗuu nɗaŋ ɗi nyi , ri ̀ Ki ̀ seŋi ki Kiris ki ki ti ki taŋza ̀ g ɓi naa yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ Seŋi wi ̀ s ri ̀ Kan Yeesus Kiris ɓɛɛ fa mi ̀ ni lɛ ri ̀ geesɛ ̀ n ri ̀ fyo ̀ oog .
N ̀ ti n ̀ fafa ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll wɛ ̀ m ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m , n ̀ ki yiiyiti ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n yɛm ̀ ,
lɛ n ̀ ti n ̀ wowo ̀ g di ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa nkɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ ntyweeyi , ɓi u re ̀ resi ɓi san a ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Kan Yeesus ri ̀ ɓisuu ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
N ̀ ti n ̀ tɔki ̀ nyi lɛ , ri ̀ ɓa ɗi u ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ɗa ̀ rɛn ri ɓi ̀ si ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗyɛɛ ki lɛ u konag ki ̀ yii ̀ ki ̀ rɔɔ ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ti ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ kɔ ɓi cɛɓ ki ti ghɛghɛɓ nɗaŋ ri Kiris .
Lɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ nwoogh ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey nɗem wu ki kpi ̀ mɛ ɓi ɗu ̀ m lɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ nyi ; ɓisuulɛ mɛ ̀ rem mɛ ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n mɛ mmaa lɛ fyo ̀ oog lɛ ki ̀ say kɔɔ , geni wɛ ̀ m .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki , nsoo ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Kiris a ̀ mɛ fa mɛ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ lɛɛ ̀ gwey lɛ nsiŋdɛn wɔ ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi u ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ u ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ,
ki mɓiisɛɛ mɛ ̀ ki ̀ kɔ ̀ ni lɛ mɓɔŋzi wɔ ̀ ɓi nkɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n . Ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ɗi mɛ ̀ Pol n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɗi ki ̀ tu ̀ g ki mum , a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ di ̀ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ lɛ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ki ̀ mbu ̀ ŋ ɓisuu Yeesus Kiris .
M ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzaagh wɔ ̀ ɓisuu Onezim a ̀ man wɛm ̀ a ̀ nɛ n ̀ -yali ɓi Kiris di n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y .
Nnyɛɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ la ̀ g wɔ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ gɛɓsɛ ̀ n abɛ ̀ y ; wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , a ̀ ti ɓi ̀ si ri ̀ gɛɓsɛ ̀ n lɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ .
M ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zii yi ̀ wɔ ̀ nyi ki ̀ romi ̀ i ̀ ; nyii ri fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ ka ̀ ɓ kɛm ̀ ki nyoo kidɛŋ .
Mɛ ̀ m ̀ mɛɛ ̀ ɓa ri za ̀ y i ̀ nɛ lɛ nɗɔɓ fɛ ri ̀ nyi , lɛ a ghɛɛ ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɓsi ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓi si ̀ g wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki n ̀ kaka ri ̀ bɛn ɓisuu Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ ni ɓi lɛ nki fɔlɔɔ di n ̀ ka wog ɓi fe ̀ g wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , lɛ ki ̀ rɔɔ ki u ̀ ri ̀ lɛ u ̀ ki ̀ mɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ ki ̀ i kɔ ɓi ka ̀ ŋbɛn , kɛɛ ɓa ki ̀ ɓan ki wɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ u ̀ ɓekii ri ̀ syeesyee wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ a n ̀ ɗem .
Ɓaa ̀ yi ɓi Onezim a ̀ a nɗi ̀ lɛ a ̀ ghasɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓi maa ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n lɛ di a sugtii ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓi ɓya ̀ g ri ̀ sugti ̀ i ̀ ɗi isuu ̀ ce ̀ m ,
kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa ti n ̀ kpa ̀ n , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ri ̀ ɓa ɗii ɗi cee ɗi n ̀ kpa ̀ n a zɛy , a ̀ ɓa maaseŋi wi ̀ s a n ̀ ɗem ; i a ̀ ki ti maaseŋi wɛ ̀ m a ̀ n ̀ ɗem , a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ girig aŋkɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ a ̀ cee fɔlɔɔ , lɛ ri ̀ ɓi bee inɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ mu ̀ u ̀ ri ̀ ɓi i ̀ nɛ ɓi ri ̀ geni ɗi ɓi Kan ɓiɗu ̀ m .
I ki ri lɛ , u seesee mɛ lɛ roŋka ̀ ŋ , gha ̀ ɓa nyi yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ ri ̀ lɛ u ̀ gha ̀ ɓ mɛ ̀ .
I a ̀ sɛ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kidɛŋ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ nsoo ̀ lɛ a ̀ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ ri ̀ pon , foŋa ɓi nɗem lɛ ntɛ ̀ g wu mii ̀ wu seesee mɛ ̀ .
Mɛ ̀ Pol yɛɛ kanii ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ri ̀ ca ̀ g kɛm ̀ lɛ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓyɔ ɓii ̀ le ̀ ɓi ; yɛ ̀ ɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ n-yiti wɔ lɛ u ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ri ̀ pon , pon anɛ ̀ n yɛɛ ri lɛ cɛɓ kɔɔ kɔmiɗ .
Ɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ geni wɛ ̀ m , ki ̀ ya mɛ ̀ ki ̀ say kin ̀ ɓi nkɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ Kan , fɔɔsi mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗem ɓi Kiris ɓiɗu ̀ m .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tyweeyi lɛ u ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i com ki n ̀ tɔɔgh , fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ka ̀ nii ̀ wɔ ̀ ; n ̀ ki yii lɛ u ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i com ki n ̀ kpaa , u ̀ ceesa ̀ g .
N ̀ kpaatii wɔ ̀ lɛ u pegsɛn mɛ ̀ ki ̀ den ki naa ɓisuulɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ dya ̀ ɓɛn lɛ bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n yin yi ri ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ ɓɛɛ pɛɛ ̀ zii ̀ mɛ ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin .
Epafiras a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ reŋka ̀ ŋ wɛ ̀ m a ̀ nɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y ri ̀ nyi , ɓisuu Yeesus Kiris
a ̀ tɔkii yi ̀ wɔ ̀ , Marikus ri ̀ Aristarikɛ ri ̀ Demas , ri ̀ Lukas ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ reŋka ̀ ŋ ɓɛm ɓɛ kisay ɓɛ togsaagh yi ̀ girig wɔ ̀ .
Geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ Kan Yeesus Kiris yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa ri ̀ mi ̀ ni .
Ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ajɛ ̀ m , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓis gɛ ̀ n lɛɛ ̀ gwey , bee lɛ bee ɓi ŋwɔm wu ɓɛkpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ,
nni ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ siito ̀ n mɛ , a ̀ a nto ̀ o ̀ ghrɛɛ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si ɓi ŋwɔm wu Man wii ̀ , man a ̀ nɛ ̀ n innɛ a ̀ rɛsi ̀ gha ̀ lɛ a teɗ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓice ̀ m ; ri ̀ nyi nnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ɗyoo ri ̀ zi .
Man a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ ci ̀ i ̀ ghziŋ ki rikem ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ ɓa ti ̀ syeesyee a ̀ ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ɗi yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ , a ̀ le ̀ nlemi ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ri ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi ̀ i ̀ inɛ i ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ . Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ le ̀ gsi ̀ gha ̀ zo ̀ ghɛ ̀ n i ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓi ɓum , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ɗyoo ɓiɗu ̀ m , ɓi wee ̀ lem a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ la ̀ ŋi mɛ ̀ te ̀ ɗ mɛce ̀ m .
Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ mɛ cee ɓum ɓɛ titom le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ mɛ fa nyi ɗii ɗi ɗi laŋi ɗi nkaa .
Ɓisuulɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ka kpaagha ̀ ɓi ŋwaa ̀ fi ̀ tom adɛŋ lɛ : U ̀ ri ̀ Man wɛm ̀ , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , n ̀ ti soŋi ̀ , nsoo ̀ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ Seŋi , nyii ɓa mɛ ̀ Man .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓagha ̀ a ̀ ti ɓii ̀ romi ̀ i ̀ Man a ̀ n ̀ tonto wii ̀ ɓi ziinɛ , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ nyi ki ̀ ɓɔgsii .
Ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a ɓum ɓɛ titom , a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Bɛ ̀ ll a ki ̀ lag lɛ : A ̀ ghaasi ̀ ɓum ɓii ɓɛ titom bɛ ̀ ɓ , a ̀ ki ghaasi ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓii nɗoo ̀ wu ɗuu .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Man , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : wɔ ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wɔɔ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ wu ri fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ki ̀ geŋ kɔɔ ki rila ̀ mi ̀ , ki ri ki ̀ geŋ ki rila ̀ mi ̀ ɗi saaɗ .
U ̀ keesi ̀ gha ̀ saaɗ , u ̀ ɓe ̀ e ̀ zɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ɓe ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki wɔ ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , Bɛ ̀ ll wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ a mɛ ɓɔ ̀ n wɔ , a ̀ siŋi ̀ wɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ mɛ nnyaasɛ ̀ n a ̀ ca ̀ ɗ ɓɛ ̀ roŋka ̀ ŋ .
A ̀ kpaati ̀ gha ̀ lɛ : Kan , wɔ ̀ yɛɛ kigha ̀ zi a ri ̀ tumɛ ̀ n , nsoo ̀ ɗyoo ɗi ri girig ki ̀ say ki ɓya ̀ g ɓyɔɔ ɓyɛɛ kii ̀ .
Ɓyom ɓi ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ri ɓii ̀ ɗyaŋi ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kifog wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓ ; ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ri ɓii ̀ ru ̀ ni yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ;
u ̀ tag ɓyɔ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ taki rɛ ̀ ŋkweɗ , ɓɛ koɓsɛ ̀ n ɓyɔ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔrii lɔŋ zi ̀ ŋ ɓi-kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , cɛɓ kɔɔ kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa ri n ̀ ɗe ̀ e ̀ .
Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ka kpaagha ̀ ɓi ŋwaa ̀ fi ̀ tom adɛŋ lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ri mɛ ̀ fɛ ɓi wee ̀ lem a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ ghaasii ɓɛ ̀ be ̀ na ̀ bena ɓɔɔ kiɓoŋ ki u rɛsag mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ mii ̀ .
Ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ yin nya mɛ ̀ ghay mɛ mɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki Bɛ ̀ ll ki ̀ say ? Mɛ ki ɓa lɛ , nyi yɛɛ romi mɔ lɛ mɛɛ kɛn ̀ ki ̀ ghɛɓsii ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ teri ̀ ga ̀ ɓ ɓi go ̀ ri i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ?
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓiisɛɛ ki ɓaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ si ̀ i ̀ rɛn ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ti ̀ woka ̀ di ti ̀ kɔ ̀ ni ɓi lɛ , ti ɗyaŋ .
Ɓisuulɛ ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ ki kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ ; fɔɔnnɛ mum bimiɗ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ foga ̀ ɓi nɗem ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ nsoo ̀ lɛ , a ̀ ɓe ̀ n ki ̀ woo ̀ gh com ki ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ , a ̀ teka ̀ deɓ inɛ i ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗii .
Nni lannɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ tyɛ ̀ ki teɗ deɓ di ti ̀ sɛɛtii coo go ̀ ri yɛ ̀ ɛ i ̀ nɛ ? Kan nyimiɗ a loka ̀ ki ̀ kpaa ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki go ̀ ri i ̀ nɛ ̀ n , fɔɔnnɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ woka ̀ di a kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ sii ̀ ra ̀ ka ̀ ɓi ̀ si ki ̀ re ̀ sii saaɗ a ̀ nɛ mii ̀ .
Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki si ̀ isii ̀ ra ̀ g ri ̀ kali ̀ ɗyaa lɛ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ koŋnyoo ɓɛ ɓiɓan ri ̀ da ̀ m mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ ̀ kuu , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ fafa ̀ a ̀ mɛ Kitɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay mɛ a ka ̀ aka ̀ ɓsi ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki kɔni nyi .
Ɓisuulɛ , a ̀ a ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ nyɔnyɔn a ̀ zi anɛ a yu ̀ yuiy lɛ ɓɛɛ lami ; nyɔnyɔn a ̀ zi anɛ ̀ n nnɛ ti ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ .
Kɔlɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ja ̀ ŋ idɛŋ ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ : Mum innɛ cɛ , ɓi ɗi lɛ wɔ ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll u yitag nyi ? Nsoo ̀ man a ̀ mum , a ̀ ri ̀ cɛ lɛ u teki ntɔɓ ɓisu wi ̀ i ̀ ?
U ̀ sɛɛ ̀ di ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ɗii ɓi maa ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n , lɛ ɗyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ kpaŋdi yɛ ̀ ɛ ɗi ɓum ɓɛ titom , u ̀ waasi ̀ nyi lɛ , ri ̀ ri ̀ kem , ri ̀ nnyaasɛ ̀ n fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ta ̀ m a ̀ mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m .
U ̀ foga ̀ nyi ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m a mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ lɛ a lami ɓyɔ ̀ . Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ kalag lɛ : A ̀ fagha ̀ nyi i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ , a lami ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m fɔlɔɔ a re ̀ sii lɛ : A ̀ fagha ̀ mum i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ a lami ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ki lɔɔ ̀ sɛɛ . Nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ɓi ̀ sii ka ghɛn ɓi ɓigomi ̀ nɛ lɛ , ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ti ɓi ri ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɗi mum .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , roa ̀ nɛ ɓɛ sɛɛ ̀ di ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ɗii ɓi maa ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n lɛ ɗyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ kpaŋdi yɛ ̀ ɛ ɗi ɓum ɓɛ titom yɛɛ ri Yeesus , nyi nnɛ ti seesee yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ mɛ waasi ri ̀ kem , ri ̀ n ̀ nyaasɛ ̀ n ɓisuu riwu ̀ ɗi a ̀ wugha ̀ ; lɛ a ̀ wugha ̀ ɓisuu ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m lɛ geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ɓisuulɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , nnyɛɛ ̀ ki ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ɓɔn lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛɛ teɗ ga ̀ ɓ ɓi ri ̀ kem ɗii , ɓi bee i ̀ ri ̀ kɛŋ , a ki lɛ Yeesus a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ to wu go ̀ ri ya ̀ a ̀ , a kpaŋ ɓi nɗɛli wu , kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa ri ki ̀ ɓan ki fenɛn a lɔ ̀ ŋkii .
Ɓisuulɛ ri ̀ n ̀ tɛɛ ̀ zi ̀ ɓum , ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ a ̀ tɛɛ ̀ zii ɓɛ fuu yi ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ mum bog , ɓisu wi ̀ n mii ̀ nnɛ ki yeesii ɓi nyi lɛ a regi ɓɔ lɛ , ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓii ,
yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : N ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ ghagsii ɓɛgeni ɓɛ ̀ m ɗii ɗyɔɔ , n ̀ kemzi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ n ̀ taŋzɛ ̀ n .
Ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ : N ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ faa ̀ n ̀ tyweeyi wɛm ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi . Ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ : Ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔn ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ mɛ ̀ , ɓi ̀ si ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ lɛ ̀ .
Nni fɔlɔɔ nnɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɔn ɓɛ ri lɛ , ri ̀ nyoo i ̀ mɛ ̀ mu ̀ u ̀ , ri ̀ bwaɓ , nyi girig a ̀ teka ̀ nyoo i ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ , di a ghaa ̀ si Sata ̀ n a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu riwu ̀ com ki zɛy , ɓi ri ̀ wu ɗi a ̀ wugha ̀
a ̀ ki ghɛɓsi ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ i ̀ ris wu riwu ̀ wu foga ̀ ɓi ri ̀ kpa ̀ n cɛɓ kaa kice ̀ m .
Ɓisuulɛ , a ̀ a ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ a ̀ yu ̀ u ɓa ̀ ki ̀ ghɛɓsii , lɔŋ do ̀ o ̀ yi Abiraham .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ pisɛɛ ɓɛgeni bee yice ̀ m lɛ , di a ɓa ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi ɓɛpi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɗi ɗi ri ri ̀ nɗem wu nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g , ɗi kiki ̀ ki ̀ say ki Bɛ ̀ ll lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ , lɛ ɗyɛɛ soo ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓi ɓum ɓɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ .
Lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ nyimiɗ a tulɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn , a ̀ wog ri ̀ kɛŋ a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ ghɛɓsi ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓi mɛ ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn .
Nni fɔlɔɔ nnɛ , mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓɛ ̀ m ɓɛ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓi ri ̀ ri ̀ ga ̀ ɓ ɓi nɗee ̀ ghreŋi wu Bɛ ̀ ll , seeseena Yeesus a ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ romga ̀ y lɛ a ɓa ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi ɓɛpi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɗi ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓi ̀ sii ̀ la ̀ alam ̀ ɓɛ ̀ n .
Yeesus a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ fagha ̀ nyi ki ̀ say kin ̀ mɛ ̀ wog , lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ Moyis a ̀ kigha ̀ , ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll bimiɗ .
Lɛ ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ teri ̀ ri ̀ kem ɗi ɗi cee ɗi Moyis , fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ toŋi mɛɛ , a ̀ ti a ̀ kemgi ̀ a ̀ cee mɛɛ mɔmiɗ mɛ a ̀ toŋi .
Mɛɛ mɛce ̀ m mɛ ri ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ toŋi mɔ , nni n ̀ toŋi ̀ ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m yɛɛ ri lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Moyis , a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ wog yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ , ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll bimiɗ , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say anɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ ghagsii ɓiɓan ɓi ɓi ghɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ kalɛɛ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Kiris a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ wog fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Man a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ bee ̀ bɛ ̀ y ɓi naa yi ̀ i ̀ ; naa i ̀ nɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ ri lɛ ɓi ̀ si , i ti ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi a ̀ kpaŋ a ri ̀ sugtɛ ̀ n lɛ ri ̀ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ n ̀ tyweeyi ri ̀ dya ̀ ɓɛn inɛ ti saasanɛ ̀ n .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki , i ɓi ̀ woogh jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi ̀ i ̀ gɛɛ ̀ nɛ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ki ti ki kala ̀ g ,
kɛ ̀ ɓi te ̀ e ̀ si mɛrem min fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɗi ɓi ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ nyi ntoo ̀ te ̀ ɗ ŋwos anɛ ɓi ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi ɓireɓ ,
ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓin ɓɛ fee ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ mɛ ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ ghɛn ̀ com ki n ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ n ̀ ki ̀ , nsoo ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi n ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ɓi be ̀ g mɛ ̀ tin mɛɓɛɛ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ woka ̀ bim ri gba ̀ a ̀ i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ ̀ n , n ̀ kpaa lɛ : mɛ ̀ rem maa mɛɛ ̀ pwa ̀ a ̀ pwaa ɓɔ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m , ɓɛ woka ̀ ɓi ɓiɓan ɓi n ̀ tɔtɔ ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ ki .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ka ̀ nɛ ̀ nga ̀ bɛ ̀ ɗ ɓi bim inɛ n ̀ woka ̀ , n ̀ kpaa lɛ : Ɓaa ɗiŋi ɓi ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ m ̀ pe ̀ gsɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ri fɔɔsɛn wɔɔ , nsoo ̀ ŋwos .
Ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓɛ ̀ m , konaaghna lɛ , ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ ɓi mi ̀ ni kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa ri nɗem wu ɓeɓtɛn , wu wu ri kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓi le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ a ghasɛn ɗi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ cem .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , reere ̀ ɓɓɛɛna ɓɛ ̀ ŋwos ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ kpaŋ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ kali ̀ lɛ gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , di fɔɔnnɛ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi mi ̀ ni kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ca ̀ rɛn lɛ nɗem wii wɛɛ teɗ ɓiɗu ̀ m di ki ̀ ɓe kaa ye ̀ gsi nyi .
Lɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛɛ nɗaŋ ri Kiris , di ti ̀ si ̀ i ̀ rɛɛ lɛ , ti ɓeŋ ̀ n ̀ tyweeyi wu ti ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ wɔ a ri ̀ tumɛ ̀ n .
Lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri ki ̀ kaliyɛn lɛ : I ɓi ̀ woogh jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi ̀ i ̀ gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , kɛ ̀ ɓi te ̀ e ̀ si mɛrem fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɗi ɓi ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ nyi n ̀ too ̀ te ̀ ɗ .
Ɓɛ ̀ ghɛn ɓɛɛ woka ̀ kɔm jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛ ki ki ̀ nyi ntoo ̀ te ̀ ɗ ? Lɔŋ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ Moyis a ̀ kpaŋzigha ̀ y a Egiɓtɛn .
Ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ be ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ a ̀ woka ̀ bim ri ɓɔ a ̀ kpaŋ be ̀ g mɛ ̀ tin mɛɓɛɛ ̀ ? A ̀ woka ̀ bim ɗi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ kigha ̀ ki ̀ ɓe , ɓɔ yɛɛ wuwu ̀ gha ̀ di ɓɛɛ ̀ kpi ̀ kpi wɔɔ ɓireɓ .
Ɓɛ ̀ ghɛn ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ a ̀ ka ̀ nɛ ̀ nga ̀ bɛ ̀ ɗ lɛ ɓaa ɗiŋi ɓi ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ a ̀ pe ̀ gsɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ri fɔɔsɛn wɔɔ ? Lɔŋ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ kigha ̀ nyi n ̀ too ̀ te ̀ ɗ ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ sii ghɛɛ gi ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi lɛ ɓɛ ɗiŋi ̀ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ i ri ̀ fɔɔsɛ ̀ n i ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓisuulɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ri ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
Nni ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ka ̀ g wulɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ ɗiŋi ɓi ri ̀ fɔɔsɛ ̀ n ɗii wu kaka , ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ konaagh lɛ , ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ ɓi mi ̀ ni kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa ri fe ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ nyii kpaŋi di ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kaa cee ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ mɛ kalɛn a lɔ ̀ ŋkis lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kalɛ ̀ nga ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkaa . Wɔ ̀ lɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ woka ̀ , i ̀ ghɛɓsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi com , ɓisuulɛ ɓɛ woka ̀ yɔ ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ teɗ yɔ ̀ ri ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
Ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a ɓi ̀ siɓɛ ti ̀ gherɛɛ , ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɗiŋii ɓi ri ̀ fɔɔsɛ ̀ n ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ka ̀ nɛɛ bɛ ̀ ɗ ɓi bim inɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ nwoogh , n ̀ kpaa lɛ : Ɓaa ɗiŋi ɓi ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ m ̀ pe ̀ gsɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ri fɔɔsɛn wɔɔ . A ̀ kpaagha ̀ fɔlɔɔ nsoo ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri lɛ ki ̀ say kii ki ɓagha ̀ di ki mɛ le ̀ g , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ɗyoo , ri ̀ zi .
Lɛ ki ri ki ̀ kaliyɛn ja ̀ ŋ idɛŋ ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki ŋwos a ki ̀ taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ lɛ : Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fɔɔsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ say kii ki ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ŋwos a ki ̀ taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ,
a ̀ kpaa ti ̀ fɛ lɛ : Ɓaa ɗiŋi ɓi ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ m ̀ pe ̀ gsɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ri fɔɔsɛn wɔɔ .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri ki ̀ siŋdɛn lɛ , ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ ɗiŋii ɓi ri ̀ fɔɔsɛ ̀ n ɗin ̀ ki ki ɓa ti lɛ , ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ loka ̀ ki ̀ teri ̀ Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ rɔɓka ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɗiŋi wɔɔ lɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ,
fɔɔnnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ mɛ rɛsi ti bimiɗ a ̀ ŋwos adɛŋ lɛ : Gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓi ŋwɔm wu Davit di ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kaa ghaa ̀ gh lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ tya ̀ a mɛ wog lɛ : Gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , i ɓi ̀ woogh jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi ̀ i ̀ . Kɛ ̀ ɓi te ̀ e ̀ si mɛrem .
Ɓisuulɛ , i Yooswa a fa ɓɔ ri ̀ fɔɔsɛ ̀ n , di Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi lɛ , a ̀ ka ̀ gti ̀ ɓum ŋwos adɛŋ , ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ri ̀ fɔɔsɛ ̀ n ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fɔɔsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi Saɓa ̀ t ɗi ri wɔɔ ɓisuu ɓum ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ɓisuulɛ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɗiŋii ɓi ri ̀ fɔɔsɛ ̀ n ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ mɛ fɔɔsɛn ɓisay ɓii fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ nyii fɔɔsɛ ̀ nga ̀ girig ɓi nki ̀ i ̀ .
Ti te ̀ e ̀ siina nyoo lɛ ti ɗiŋi ɓi ri ̀ fɔɔsɛ ̀ n ɗin ̀ , di fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa lɛ a ̀ kpi ̀ , di a ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ tii ri ̀ kuu ɗi ntoo ̀ te ̀ ɗ ɗi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓireɓ ɓɛ resi ̀ gha ̀ .
Lɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ ri ̀ cencem , i ̀ ki ɓa ri i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , i ̀ poo i ̀ cee ga ̀ fa ̀ g i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ghɛliyɛn ɓɛɓɛg ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m . Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɗiɗiŋi mum ɓi nɗem a ̀ kpaŋ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ cɛɓ ki mum ri ̀ nghay wii ɓi rarɛɛ ; i ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ i ̀ kpaŋ ɓi ri ̀ ra ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɗi go ̀ ga ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋ ɓɛ ɓiwoɓ . Yɛ ̀ ɛ re ̀ resi nko ̀ o ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi mum ri ̀ mɛ ̀ yiti ̀ mɛ mɛ ri nyi ɓi nɗem , ɓi ri lɛ syeesyee .
Ɓi ɓyom ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ , com kidɛŋ ki yin nyi ki ̀ nyamɛn , ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ri ɓi ̀ ghaniyɛn lɛ kpee ̀ nye-kpe ̀ e ̀ nye ̀ e ̀ ɓi mis mɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ̀ si ki ̀ tɔɔ ̀ gh ki ̀ say ki ti ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ min ri nkɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n-ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey lɛ Yeesus a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓɔka ̀ aɗyoo yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ si ̀ i ̀ rɛɛ lɛ syeesyee ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ti ̀ gherɛɛ ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓi ti ̀ ti ti ̀ kaka ̀ li ̀ ɓum .
Ɓisuulɛ n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ wi ̀ s a ̀ gwey a yin rikuu ɗi ɗi ri lɛ , ɗi taŋ ̀ n ̀ ɗem wu nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ɗi ti ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , lɛ a ̀ tulɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn mɛkuu mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ si , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ɓi kiɓe .
Ti tyoŋdɛn min ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ i ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ wu Bɛ ̀ ll , ja ̀ ŋ inɛ geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ , ti ̀ ɓa ri ̀ n ̀ tyweeyi , di fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛɛ wog ɓi ̀ si nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g , ti ̀ ki ghɛn geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si ɓii ̀ ghɛɓsii ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ .
Lɛ n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ -ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ teri ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓum , a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ rɛsɛn ɓisuu ɓum , lɛ a ki ki ̀ say ki Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ fafa ̀ nyi ɓyom , a ̀ ki fu ̀ ufunɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ tuwe ɓisuu ɓiɓe ɓi ɓum .
A ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ ɓa ri ̀ ri ̀ cenɛ ̀ n ɓisuu ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ nana ̀ g lɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ yi , lɛ nyimiɗ a ri ̀ mum a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ na ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓa kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ .
Ri ̀ ɓa ɗi a ̀ ri ̀ ɗin ̀ ɗi ̀ i ̀ kɔ ̀ g , ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ lɛghii Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ , ri ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓii ɓi nyimiɗ , ri ̀ ɓi ɓum ɓɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ .
Mum a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ falɛ ̀ n m ̀ ɓɔg wi ̀ n nyimiɗ , di Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ reŋii ɓi nyi fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ Arɔn .
Nsoo ̀ Kiris a ̀ falɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi nyimiɗ ri ̀ gwey ɗi lɛ , a ɓa n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ -ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ . Ki ̀ ɓan kifog a ̀ teka ̀ ɗyɔ ri ̀ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : U ̀ ri ̀ Man wɛm ̀ , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n gɛɛ ̀ nɛ n ̀ ti wɔ ̀ seŋi .
Fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kpaati ̀ gha ̀ ja ̀ ŋ idɛŋ lɛ : U ̀ ri ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ , ri ̀ ɓa ɗi isuu ̀ ce ̀ m , ɓi nɗɛli wu Mɛlkisedɛg .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ghɛghɛ ̀ ɓka ̀ ɓi ziinɛ , a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋza ̀ ka ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ghyɛ ̀ gsi ̀ nyi ɓya ̀ g , ri ̀ ɓyoo ɓikiŋ , ri ̀ misi ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ tam , lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll yɛɛ ɓagha ̀ lɛ a ̀ ghɛɓsi ̀ nyi ɓi ri ̀ wu ; nni Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ woka ̀ bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n yii lɛ mɛ ̀ wog mɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ mɔ .
Nsoo ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ yila ̀ ka ̀ com ki lɛ mɛ ̀ wog , ɓi mɛ ̀ tɔɓ mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m mɛ a ̀ woka ̀ ;
fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ lɛ a ̀ mɛ teŋzi nyi ɓi nɗɛli wu kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa ti ri ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓɛ fen a lɔ ̀ ŋkii , nni a ̀ ghala ̀ n ̀ faa ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ woogh nyi , go ̀ ri i ̀ fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ,
lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ -ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓi nɗɛli wu Mɛlkisedɛg .
Ti ̀ te ̀ ghɛɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi kpaayɛn ɓi ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ wɔ ̀ lɛ ri ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ɗi ti resi mi ̀ ni ɓyɔ lɛ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓi konag ki ̀ woo ̀ gh ɗi yeesɛɛ ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ ti kɛ ̀ ɓi wog ti kiɓan lɛ fyɛ ̀ ɗ .
Lɛ mi ̀ niɓɛ ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɓɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi fiɗya ̀ ɓ , ɓi ̀ kaka ri ̀ za ̀ y i ̀ nɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ resag mi ̀ ni mɛ ̀ to mɛ ɓiɓan mɛ bee ̀ bɛ ̀ y mɛ ɓi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll . Ɗi ɓya ̀ a ri ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ ɗi ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓi te ̀ ɗ , ɓi ̀ kaka ri ̀ za ̀ y i ̀ nɛ lɛ ɓi nyɔŋnyɔŋ mɛli ̀ .
Kɔlɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ kaka ɓi mɛli ̀ , a ̀ ka yi ɓi righasi ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ saaɗ , ri ̀ pwa ̀ a ̀ ɓisuulɛ a ̀ kaka man .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ , ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓi te ̀ ɗ ɓi ri ɓisuu ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ mɛ si ̀ i ̀ rɛn ɓum , ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗi mɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ tɛn ɗi ri ̀ ghasi ̀ ɗi lɛ , ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓe ri ̀ ki ̀ rɔɔ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ti ca ̀ rina ri ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ɗi a ri ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki Kiris , ti ɓeg ̀ mɛn ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi konaagh ki ̀ rɔɔtɛɛ , tyɛ ̀ ki sugti tii ̀ ri ̀ jɛ ̀ m ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi a ri ̀ ya ̀ ghɛ ̀ n ɓi ɓi ri lɛ : Mum a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ca ̀ ri ɓiɓan ɓi kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ su ,
a ̀ gherɛ ̀ n Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g mɛ mɛ koŋ ̀ komi ba ̀ ɓtis mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ ̀ kuu , ɗi ̀ ri ̀ saa ̀ gh ɗi mum ɓya ̀ g ɓi nyoo lɛ ɓɛɛ maŋ ̀ nyi , ri ̀ ri ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓiloŋ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ m ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri yɔ ̀ m ɓum gɛ ̀ n bog ɓi gɛ ̀ n yice ̀ m .
Ki ̀ ɓan ki ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i di Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ gherɛɛ kɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ n .
Ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki ki seesee ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ki Bɛ ̀ ll ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kidɛŋ , ɓɛ ɓoɓti ̀ ri ̀ fa ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓɛ ki teɗti ga ̀ ɓ ɓi Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ,
ɓɛ ɓoɓti ̀ ri ̀ yɛ ̀ y ɗi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛ ki ghɛn mɛte ̀ ɗ mɛ ɓi cɛɓ ki ki rii ̀
ɓɛ ki sugti ki kpi ̀ i ɓi ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki cɛɓ , bee inɛ ŋwaa ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ ki ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛn ti ̀ nɗem i ̀ yii ̀ di ɓisuulɛ , ɓɔɔ ̀ ɓi ̀ iɓii ̀ ti ̀ ki ̀ kpani ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi Kɔrɔs aɗyoo , ɓɛ ki so ̀ osoo ̀ ti ̀ nyi ɓi mis mɛ ɓum .
Lɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki zi yɛ ̀ ɛ nɔnɔ mɛnig di bwey yɛ ̀ ɛ nɔnɔ mii ̀ lɛ fyɛ ̀ ɗ fyɛ ̀ ɗ , zi inɛ ̀ n i ̀ ki fafa ɓyaɓi ɓi ɓi ri ri ̀ gɛɓsɛ ̀ n ɓisuu ɓumɓɛ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ̀ n i ̀ salɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓisu waa , zi inɛ ̀ n i ̀ ti i ̀ teki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ma ̀ a ̀ gh yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ i zi inɛ ̀ n yɛɛ ̀ fafa lɛ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓyaaɓi , ri ̀ keŋ , di i ̀ yin syeesyee a ̀ zi , i ̀ ki ɓa ja ̀ ŋbog lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ teɗ n ̀ cɛ ̀ m , ki ki syɔn lɛ ɓɛɛ tɔn ̀ yɔ ̀ .
Mi ̀ ni ɓum ɓɛm ɓɛ nɗem , nsoo ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ti kpaakpaa lɔɔ , ti ̀ konaagh ki ̀ yii ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ rɛrɛlii ɓi syeesyee a ̀ bee , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ bee i ̀ cɛɓ .
Lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ saaɗ , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ ɗimzɛ ̀ n ki ̀ say kin , nsoo ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ ɓi ̀ re ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ nyi ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ̀ ghɛɓsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ kaka ɓi ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɓsi ̀ ɓɔ .
Ti kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ ɓi mi ̀ ni a ɓa ri ̀ ri ̀ kuu ɗi rifalɛ ̀ n ɗin ̀ a ̀ kpaŋ a ri ̀ sugtɛ ̀ n , fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ɓoŋɓo ̀ ŋ ɓi ri ɓii ̀ ki ̀ lɛɛ lɛ syeesyee ,
ɓi le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ kɛ ̀ ɓi rɛ ̀ gsi nyoo , ɓi nɔɔ ̀ ti lɔŋ iko ̀ o ̀ wu ɓɛroɓɛ ɓɛ gherɛɛ , ɓɛ ki ɓa ri ki ̀ si ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ ; ɓɛɛ ti ɓɛ teki ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ka ̀ ka ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗyaa ɗin ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ Abiraham n ̀ ka ̀ g , a ̀ ka ̀ nɛ ̀ nga ̀ bɛ ̀ ɗ ri myimi ̀ ɗ , lɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi lɛ a ̀ ka ̀ nɛ ̀ n bɛ ̀ ɗ ri ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ cee nyi .
Nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : N ̀ ka ̀ nɛɛ bɛ ̀ ɗ lɛ : N ̀ ɗi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ ma ̀ ŋi , n ̀ te ̀ gsi ̀ boo yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ i mum .
Abiraham a ̀ si ̀ i ̀ rɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ɓoŋ ɗi nka ̀ g win ̀ , nni a ̀ ki teka ̀ com ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ka ̀ ka ̀ nyi .
Ɓum ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kana ̀ g bɛ ̀ ɗ ri mii mɛ ɓɛroɓɛ ɓɛ ceetii ɓɔ ; ri ̀ ka ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɗi bɛ ̀ ɗ ɗyɛɛti ɗi rengi ̀ nywey ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wa ̀ a ̀ , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓɛɛ ̀ nyoonyolɛ ̀ n .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kɔ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ a konag ki ̀ re ̀ sii ɓumɓɛ a ̀ fagha ̀ mɛ ̀ ka ̀ g lɛ nyaa lɔ ̀ gtiigɛ ɓi rikali ̀ ɗii , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ka ̀ nɛ ̀ nga ̀ bɛ ̀ ɗ .
Ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ri min ɓiɓɛɛ ̀ ɓi ɓi yin lɛ ɓi lɔgtɛ ̀ n , ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ yin ɗi i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu lɛ a ̀ foŋ pwa ̀ a ̀ mii ̀ . Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓi ̀ siɓɛ ti ̀ mɛ tanɛn n ̀ nyamzɛn a lɔ ̀ ŋkii , ɓi mɛ fati ɓisi ite ̀ ɗ lɛɛ ̀ gwey , lɛ ti sii ̀ ri ki ̀ ɓani ̀ dya ̀ ɓɛn inɛ i ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si n ̀ fayɛn .
Dya ̀ ɓɛn inɛ ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si yɛ ̀ ɛ com ki ki lenlemi cɛɓ kis , ki ɓa ki ̀ bɛ ̀ lɛn lɛ kpeg-kpeg , kɔ yɛɛ ɗiŋii ki syaa ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ki ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , ki kpaŋzɛ ̀ n ɓi ja ̀ ŋ i ki ̀ ce ̀ li ̀ i ̀ nɛ wɔɔ ɓiɗu ̀ m ,
ja ̀ ŋ inɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓisu wis , fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si n ̀ syo ̀ ŋɛn bee , lɛ ɓɛ rɛsi ̀ gha ̀ nyi n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey isuu ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi nɗɛli wu Mɛlkisedɛg .
Mɛlkisedɛg a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi kilɔ ̀ ŋ ki lɛ Salɛm , nyi ti ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ teŋmɛn a ̀ cee , nnyɛɛ kɛnga ̀ ki ̀ tulɛɛ ri Abiraham , di roa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a susug yi wɛ ̀ y wu a ̀ yaka ̀ y mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m mɛdɛŋ mii ̀ a ̀ ki ma ̀ ŋ nyi .
Ri ̀ nyi nnɛ Abiraham a ̀ fagha ̀ ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ki ̀ ntɛ ̀ ɗ i ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓyom ɓii ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m . Ɗii ɗi lɛ Mɛlkisedɛg a ̀ nce ̀ m ɗi ka re ̀ sii lɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi saaɗ , a ̀ ki ɓa ti lɛ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi Salɛm yɛɛlɔɔ lɛ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi fyo ̀ oog .
A ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ seŋi , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ jɛɛ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ fuuyi ̀ ; ɓɛ ɓuŋi ɓi kiɓan ki riyalɛ ̀ n ɗii , nsoo ̀ ki riwu ̀ ɗii ja ̀ ŋ idɛŋ , a ̀ pisɛɛ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ ghɛn lɛ , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ coo gi ̀ n i mum , Abiraham a ̀ seŋi wi ̀ s a ̀ nsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ a fagha ̀ nyi ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ki ̀ ntɛ ̀ ɗ i ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓyom ɓi a ̀ suka ̀ y wɛ ̀ y ri ɓyɔ .
Ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛ ɓi boo i ̀ Levi ɓɛɛ ri ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu lɛ ɓɛɛ tɔki ɓumɓɛ a Isirayɛl ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ki ̀ ntɛ ̀ ɗ i ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓyɛɛ ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ . Yɛɛlɔɔ lɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ tɔki ̀ ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ki ̀ ntɛ ̀ ɗ i ̀ nɛn ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓaa , ɓɛ ɓɛ ki ri ̀ girig lɛ do ̀ o ̀ yi Abiraham .
Mɛlkisedɛg a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ɓi boo i ̀ mum i ̀ Levi ki ̀ ɓan kifog a ̀ teka ̀ ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ki ̀ ntɛ ̀ ɗ i ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓyom ɓi Abiraham a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɓyɔ , a ̀ ki ma ̀ ŋ roa ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ mɛ ̀ ka ̀ g .
Kɔlɛ mum bimiɗ a ̀ yii lɛ , ri ̀ ɓa ɗi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓɛ maŋi ɗi wuɓsɛɛ ɓi ɗi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ma ̀ ŋi nyi .
Ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ teki ̀ ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ki ̀ ntɛ ̀ ɗ fɛ , ɓɛ ri ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ wula ̀ g ; ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Mɛlkisedɛg , nyii ri ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ki ̀ ntɛ ̀ ɗ , kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ si ̀ i ̀ raagh ki ̀ kpaa ̀ lɛ a ̀ ri ̀ cem .
Nni ti ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ti ̀ kpaa lɛ : Levi a ̀ nɛ do ̀ o ̀ yii yi ti yi teki ̀ ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ki ̀ ntɛ ̀ ɗ a ̀ fagha ̀ girig ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ki ̀ ntɛ ̀ ɗ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki Abiraham a ̀ fagha ̀ ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ki ̀ ntɛ ̀ ɗ .
Ɓisuulɛ nsoo ̀ Levi a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ ka yalɛn ɓi , ti ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ti ̀ kpaa lɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ kakay ɓi bwaɓ yi seŋi a ̀ nsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ anɛ lɛ Abiraham , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki Mɛlkisedɛg a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ tulɛɛ ri nyi .
Ki ̀ say ki pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ki ɓɔn ɓɛ Levi kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi ɓɛ fagha ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Isirayɛl ɓi sasa ̀ ghi ̀ gha ̀ mii ̀ ; i ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛ ɓi boo i ̀ Levi ɓɛɛ ki ki ̀ say ki kɛɛ rɔɔtɛn , kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa ri ki ̀ ɓan ki fenɛn , di ki ghɛɓsi ̀ gha ̀ ti ̀ ɓi com lɛ ri ̀ kuu ɗi pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɗidɛŋ ɗyɛɛ ghɛnɛn ɗi ɗi ɓa ɓi nɗɛli wu Mɛlkisedɛg , ɗyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa ti ɓi nɗɛli wu Arɔn .
Ɓisuulɛ i ki ̀ say ki pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ki ti ki ̀ cenɗɛn , ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ girig lɛ ɓi koɓsɛ ̀ n .
Nni roa ̀ nɛ ki ̀ ɓan kii ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ti kpaakpaa inɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓi ri ̀ pwi ̀ ɗ ɗidɛŋ , ɗi mum a ̀ ka ɓagha ̀ ɓi pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ mii ̀ .
Lɛ ɓɛ yii lɛ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n lɛ Kan wi ̀ s a ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yalɛɛ ɓi ri ̀ pwi ̀ ɗ ɗi Zyuda ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi Moyis a ̀ ɓu ̀ ga ̀ ɓi ɓi ki ̀ say ki pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki konaagh ti ̀ ki ̀ ghɛnɛɛ fɔlɔɔ , yɛ ̀ ɛ pirɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ adɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ki ̀ pisɛn ki Mɛlkisedɛg a ̀ mɛ kpaŋ .
A ̀ teka ̀ ɓi ikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu Pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓi ri ̀ kpaa ɗi ̀ ɓidɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi ɓum ɓɛɛ faa , a ̀ ɓɔka ̀ lɔŋ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu cɛɓ ki ki ri kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sugtag .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a kalag lɛ : U ̀ ri ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓi nɗɛli wu Mɛlkisedɛg fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ mɛ pisi kidɔ ̀ gsɛna ki abɛ ̀ y lɛ ki ɓagha ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ghɛɓsi com .
Lɛ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Moyis ɓi kigha ̀ ɓi lɛ com kidɛŋ kɛɛ kpaŋ ɓi nɗɛli wulɛ ki ̀ ɓan ki fenɛn mii ̀ kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa ti , ki ̀ ɓan kifog dya ̀ ɓɛn inɛ i ̀ cee i ̀ mɛ ɗiŋi ̀ , yɛ ̀ ɛ ti i ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g lɛ ti kɛn ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ja ̀ ŋbog .
Ki kɛɛ ̀ di ̀ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ka ̀ nɛ ̀ nga ̀ bɛ ̀ ɗ ɓi ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ,
kɔlɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓi boo i ̀ Levi ɓɛ mɓɔkaagh ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ a nka ̀ naagh ɓi bɛ ̀ ɗ fɔlɔɔ ; ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓi ri ̀ ɓɔg ɗi Yeesus a ̀ ɓɔka ̀ Pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ka ̀ nɛ ̀ nga ̀ bɛ ̀ ɗ , a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Kan a ̀ a n ̀ ka ̀ nɛɛ bɛ ̀ ɗ , a ̀ a ki lɔ ̀ gti ɓi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ : U ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ Pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛn i ̀ re ̀ sii lɛ : Yeesus a ̀ ri ̀ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ren bee i ̀ nɛ i ̀ rɔɔtɛɛ i ̀ cee i ̀ nɛ abɛ ̀ y ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si .
Ki ki ɓa ti lɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓaa ̀ ɓɔɓɔ ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛ teghɛɛ ; ri ̀ wu ɗyɛɛ reka ̀ ɓɔ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ nkɛ ̀ n ɗi ri ̀ ki ̀ say asu , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus , nyii ̀ ghɛghɛɓ fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ ceesi ̀ ki ̀ say kii ki pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ a ̀ ghɛɓsi ̀ lɛ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ tyoŋdɛɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ja ̀ ŋbog , di ɓɛ fyee a lɔ ̀ ŋkii ɓisuulɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ cem ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ ki ɓɔ ̀ ɔɓɔŋ ̀ za ̀ g Bɛ ̀ ll ɓisu wa ̀ a ̀ .
Ri ̀ kuu ɗi nla ̀ mi ̀ -ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey ɗi ɗi ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si ɗyɛɛ ri Yeesus , lɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tɛnɛn , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ti ̀ fin , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ na ̀ n , ɓɛ ghasi ̀ gha ̀ nyi ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe , a ̀ ki teŋmɛɛ a ̀ cee ɗyoo .
Ɓɛ ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ fu ̀ nɛɛ ɓituwe ɓɛŋwos ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ri ̀ lɛɛghra ̀ g ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ɓisuu ɓiɓe ɓyaa ɓi ɓɔmiɗ , ri ̀ ɓisuu ɓiɓe ɓi ɓum ɓɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ . Wɔ ̀ lɛ Yeesus a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ki ki ̀ kii yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɔ , ɓisuulɛ nyii lɛɛghra ̀ ka ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll gɛ ̀ n bog ɓi gɛ ̀ n yice ̀ m yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ fagha ̀ nyimiɗ ɓi si ̀ g a ̀ ki ̀ tuwe ki mɛlɛɛ ̀ ghlɛɛgh .
Ɓumɓɛ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Moyis ɓi nfala ̀ g i ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ -ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey , ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ lɔŋ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ ki ki ̀ ɓe ; wɔ ̀ lɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ ɓi bɛ ̀ ɗ inɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ka ̀ nɛ ̀ nga ̀ ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Moyis , i ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ gha ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ -ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti ɓi nɗɛli wulɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ na ̀ a ̀ di isuu ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ti kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ , ki ki cee kɛɛ ri lɛ , ti ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ -ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey a ̀ nɛ , a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ kɔ ̀ rii ɓi wee ̀ lem a ̀ ri ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓi ɗyoo ɓi ɗu ̀ m ,
a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say anɛ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ i ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ce ̀ li ̀ , ri ̀ ɓi kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ ki ̀ nuugh a ̀ nɛ a ̀ yin lɛ mum yɛɛ toga ̀ , lɔŋ Kan yɛɛ toga ̀ .
N ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ -ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey bimiɗ a ̀ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ɗɛsɛn lɛ , a resi Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ ri ̀ ɓyom ɓi ɓum ɓɛ faa , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ tuwe ɓi ɓum ɓɛ funɛɛ ɓi ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ; fɔɔnnɛ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ nyii ɓa girig ri ̀ com ki nyimiɗ yɛɛ faa ɓi ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll .
I Yeesus a ɓa ɓi ziinɛ , di a ̀ yin gi lɛ a ̀ ɓa pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓisuulɛ , ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛ ri wɔɔ ɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ re ̀ resi Bɛ ̀ ll ɓyom ɓi ɓum ɓɛ faa ɓi ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ , fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓyɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ nkɔ ̀ n .
Ki ̀ say ki ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛn ̀ ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ , ki ri ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ , ri ̀ ci ̀ i ̀ ziŋ ki ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ri ɓi ɗyoo ɓi ɗu ̀ m , fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ Moyis di a ̀ ti lɛ a toŋ ki ̀ laa lɛ : U ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ kɔ ki ̀ toŋi ̀ ɓi ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki kilaa ki n ̀ ɗe ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓi do ̀ n .
Nni ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki , Yeesus a ̀ ti ri ̀ ki ̀ say ki ki cee ki nkaa ɓisuulɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ren syeesyee a ̀ bee ri ɓum ; bee inɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ sasaghii ɓi mɛ ̀ ka ̀ g mɛ mɛ rɔɔtɛɛ mɛ cee .
I bee inɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ loka ̀ ki ̀ reni ̀ ri ̀ ɓum yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓeɓtɛn ki ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ , di ki ghɛɓsi ̀ gha ̀ ti ̀ ɓi com lɛ , ɓɛɛ koɓsɛn yɔ ̀ ri bee idɛŋ .
Ɓisuulɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi a fenfen a ɓum ɓii , fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : Kan a kpaaghi lɛ : Mɛ ̀ ru mɛɛ ̀ yu ̀ yuiy mɛɛ ̀ mɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ reni ̀ nyɔɔnyɔn a ̀ bee lɛ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ a Isirayɛl , ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ a Zyuda .
Ya ̀ a ɓa ti ɓi yɛ ̀ ɛ bee inɛ n ̀ ɗenga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓaa ɓɛ ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn , ŋwos anɛ m ̀ ɓanga ̀ ɓɔ ɓi ca ̀ g lɛ nkpaŋzii ̀ ɓɔ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Egiɓtɛn . Ɓɛ ɓega ̀ ɓi bee inɛ n ̀ ɗenga ̀ i ̀ nɛn ri ̀ ɓɔ , fɔɔnnɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ ghɛ ̀ righa ̀ ɓi girig nɗem aɗyoo ri ̀ ɓɔ , ri ̀ kpaa ɗi Kan ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi ̀ n .
Nni bee inɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ reni ̀ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ a Isirayɛl yɛɛ ̀ nɛ : Kan lɛ : Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ̀ n , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ foŋi ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓyɛm ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ yiti ̀ maa n ̀ ka ̀ n ɓɔ ɓyɔ ɓi mɛ ̀ rem , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll wa ̀ a ̀ , ɓɔɔ ɓa ɓum ɓɛm .
A ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ a ɓa ti ɓi lɛ a ̀ re ̀ si ̀ maaseŋi a ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ , nsoo ̀ lɛ geni lɛ , a yi lɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ Kan ; ɓisuulɛ , ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ri mɛ ̀ ɓii ̀ yii ̀ , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓi ɓɔɔ ɓɔɓti a ̀ kpaŋ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn .
N ̀ ɗi cenɛn ɓɔ mɛ ̀ na ̀ ni ̀ maa kɛ ̀ ɛ nki yiti ɓiɓe ɓyaa .
Ɓi ri ̀ kpaa ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kpaa lɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ reni ̀ bee i ̀ nyɔn ri ̀ ɓum , a ̀ ghaasi ̀ bee i n ̀ tonto bee inɛ abɛ ̀ y . Nni com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ki mɛ finɛ ̀ n ki ki ru ̀ n , kaa rɔ ̀ ɓ lɛsa ̀ g lɛ kɛɛ sili ̀ .
Bee i n ̀ tonto i ̀ nɛ lɛ ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ ɓum i ̀ ɓagha ̀ girig ri ̀ mɛ ̀ siŋdɛn mɛ mɛ seesee ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi riɓɔgsi ̀ , ri ̀ naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛ fɛ ɓi ziinɛ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ toga ̀ ki ̀ nuugh ; ɓi ki ̀ den ki asu ki ɓɛ nɗegi ̀ lɛ ja ̀ ŋ i ki ̀ ce ̀ li ̀ ; ɓyom ɓi ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ lɛ : ri ̀ ki ̀ rɛsi ̀ ki lamɓa ̀ ri ̀ teɓe ̀ re ̀ , ri ̀ bi ̀ rɛs yi ɓɛ fafaa ɓisuu riɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ki kiɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , nnɛ ki ̀ den ki ɓɛ nkala ̀ g lɛ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ i ̀ pɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zii ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ ki ̀ ce ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ .
Wɔɔ nnɛ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɛ ntɔ ̀ ngi ̀ ɓyom ɓi nu ̀ nnumɛn i ɓagha ̀ ; ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ̀ n i ̀ ɓagha ̀ gol ri ̀ gol ; fi ̀ kɔrɔŋ fi rira ̀ rɛ ̀ n fi ɓagha ̀ girig wɔɔ , fince ̀ m fi ̀ pa ̀ mɛn ri gol ; ki ̀ bɔkɔ ̀ ki gol ki ɓagha ̀ ɓi fi ̀ kɔrɔŋ fin ̀ ; ɓyom ɓi ɓagha ̀ ɓi ki ̀ bɔkɔ ̀ , kin ̀ lɛ : ri ̀ mana ̀ , ri ̀ ki ̀ geŋ ki Arɔn ki ki sam ̀ ga ̀ , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓoŋ ɓi ɓi ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi ɓi bee inɛ lɛ , ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ ɓum .
Ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓɛ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ sye ̀ ru ̀ ɓɛŋ ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ gwey ɓi nyoo ɓɛ rɛrɛ ̀ li ̀ gha ̀ ɓi fi ̀ kɔrɔŋ fi rira ̀ rɛ ̀ n aɗyoo , ki ̀ fi ̀ i ̀ kaa ki gheg ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɛ nti ɓɛ weeyi ̀ ɓi ̀ tuwe ɓi riso ̀ ghɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓiɓe . Nni a ̀ a ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki kpaakpaayɛn ɓiɓan ɓin ̀ lɛ tintɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ŋ kɛɛ ri lɛ ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓyom ɓi ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓagha ̀ fɔlɔɔ ɓi woŋzakɛn , ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛɛ nti ɓɛ ɗiŋɗa ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ ŋwos ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ki ̀ den ki asu lɛ ɓɛɛ ki ki ̀ say kaa .
Ɓi ki ̀ den ki kiɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , lɔŋ n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ nyi cɛ ̀ ncii yɛɛ nti a ̀ ɗiga ̀ g wɔɔ , gɛ ̀ n bog ɓi be ̀ g ; a ̀ ki ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ wɔɔ ki ɗiŋii ri bwaɓ yi kituwe ki a ̀ faa Bɛ ̀ ll ɓisu wii wu nyimiɗ ri ̀ ɓisuu ɓiɓe ɓi kilɔ ̀ ŋ ki ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ki kɔnkɔ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ kɛɛ resi ɓi ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗin ̀ lɛ , bee inɛ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ i ̀ pɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zii ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ ki ̀ ce ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ di i ̀ ka yin kikpaŋ , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ nuugh ki abɛ ̀ y ki ɓagha ̀ di ki kaka .
Ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗin ̀ ɗi ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ti ̀ ri ̀ ki mii ̀ , ki resii lɛ : Ɓyom ɓi mum a ̀ faa , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ tuwe ɓi a ̀ cuusii ɓi ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓi yin ɗi i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ ɓi kona ̀ g ki ̀ tɛɛ ̀ zii nɗem wu ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ɓɔɔɓɔgsi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi bee inɛ ̀ n .
Bee i ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ i ̀ nɛ ̀ n i ̀ ɓiisɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ mi ɓiɓan ɓi ɓiɗila ̀ g , ri ̀ ɓyom ɓi nɔnɔyɛn , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ syɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓi zo ̀ ghɛ ̀ n mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ ̀ kuu ; ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi mii ̀ ɓi komko ̀ mga ̀ lɔŋ ɓyom ɓi zɛy , fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ghɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ a ̀ kpaŋ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki rilɔ ̀ gta ̀ g ɗi ɓiɓan .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Kiris a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey a ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi syeesyee ɓi ɓi ri ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ; a ̀ sya ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ y ki ̀ nuugh ki ki kii lɛ , ki teghɛ ̀ n ki cee , ki ki rɔɔtɛn ki cee , kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓa kinuugh ki ɓum ɓɛɛ toŋi , yɛɛlɔɔ lɛ ki yin ɓi ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɓyom ɓi ɓi kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ziinɛ .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ gɛ ̀ n bog ɓi gɛ ̀ n yice ̀ m , ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ i ̀ pɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zii ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ ki ̀ ce ̀ li ̀ ; a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi wɔɔ ri bwaɓ yi ɓipii ̀ , nsoo ̀ lɛ yi ɓɔn ɓɛ sani ̀ nya , a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ wɔɔ lɛ a ɓɔgsi Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ bwaɓ yii yi nyimiɗ , a ̀ ki fɔ ̀ n yi ɓi ̀ si go ̀ ri i ̀ fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Lɛ i bwaɓ yi ɓɛ ̀ lem ɓɛ sani ̀ nya ri ̀ yi ɓipii ̀ , ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓu ki jɛɛ a ̀ sani ̀ nya a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ tɔni , ɓɛ ɗyɛɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ri ̀ ɓi ̀ syeg , ɓi ti ɓi pisa ̀ g ɓɔ ɓi ̀ syeg ɓi nyoo ,
bɔ ̀ ɓ yaŋ min ɗi bwaɓ yi Kiris a ̀ nɛ a ̀ falɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyimiɗ ri Bɛ ̀ ll , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ fi ̀ fin , ɓi Nghay a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ . Bwaɓ yii yi ri ɓii ̀ tɛɛ ̀ zii mɛrem mis ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ri kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ gɛɓsɛ ̀ n , lɛ ti ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ cem kisay .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki Kiris a ̀ rɛrɛlii ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ nɛ ɓi bee i nyɔn i ̀ nɛ lɛ , ri ̀ ɓum ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , lɛ di ɓumɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ mɛ reŋi ɓɛɛ teɗ ɓi ̀ rɔɔ ɓi fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ɓi a ̀ ka ̀ ka ̀ ɓumɓɛ abɛ ̀ y ; ɓɛ ri ɓyɔ ɓii ̀ teri ̀ lɛ ri ̀ wu ɗi mum bog ɗyɛɛ mɛ kwe ̀ ɗ ɓum ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓɛ kigha ̀ di ɓɛ kaka ɓi fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ fi bee .
Ɓisuulɛ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ nɛ mum a ̀ reɓsa ̀ ka ̀ ri ̀ wu ɗii mii ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ , ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ yi lɛ mum nyimiɗ anɛ a ̀ reɓsa ̀ ka ̀ ri ̀ wu a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ mɛ wu .
Lɛ kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ nɛ mum a ̀ reɓsaagh ri ̀ wu ɗii mii ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ di mum a ̀ nce ̀ m a ̀ mɛ wu , ɓisuulɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki mum a ̀ nce ̀ m a ̀ kaka cem , kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ nɛn a ̀ yin ɗi i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wudɛŋ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki nsoo ̀ bee i n ̀ tonto i ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ renga ̀ ri ̀ ɓum , i ̀ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ bwaɓ yi yi kpaŋi ̀ ;
lɛ Moyis a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , a ̀ mɛ la ̀ mɓɛn mɛsiŋdɛn mɛce ̀ m mɛ mɛ ri ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi mis mɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ ki ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ teɗ min bwaɓ yi ɓɔn ɓɛ ɓɛ ̀ sani ̀ nya , ri ̀ yi ɓipii ̀ , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ nig , a ̀ mi ̀ si ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna , ri ̀ ɓi ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , ri ̀ ki ̀ vu ̀ ree ki kite ki lɛ i ̀ zoɓ , ri ̀ ɓi n ̀ fi ̀ ŋga wu ɓa ̀ ŋ lɛ pɔɔŋ .
A ̀ kpaa lɛ : Bwaɓ yi yi sii ̀ raagh bee inɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ a n ̀ siŋ ̀ dɛɛ mi ̀ ni lɛ , ɓi ɓeŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ri lɛ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Moyis a ̀ mi ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ girig bwaɓ ɓi ki ̀ nuugh , ri ̀ ɓi ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓɛ nki ̀ la ̀ g ki ̀ say mii ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ɓi ɗi yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓyɛɛ ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ , ɓɛ ti ɓɛ sogha ̀ g ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ri ̀ bwaɓ , nsoo ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓe , ɓi ti ɓi ɓala ̀ g ɓi ̀ cenɛn di bwaɓ yi kpaŋi .
Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ min lɛ , ɓi ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ɓi ɓɛkɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ ɓɛ ɓyom ɓi ɓi ri aɗyoo ɓyɛɛ teɗ ri ̀ kuu ɗi zo ̀ ghɛ ̀ n ɗin ̀ , ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ , nsoo ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ ɓɛ ɓyom ɓɛ aɗyoo ɓɛnce ̀ m ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ teri ̀ zo ̀ ghɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ɓi ̀ fu ̀ na ɓi ɓi cee ɓin ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ Kiris a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ toŋi , i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ lɛ i ̀ ɓa ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ , a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ lɔŋ ɓi ɗyoo ɗyɔmiɗ lɛ di a rɛli ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki , ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓisu wis .
A ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi wɔɔ lɛ di a funɛn nyimiɗ gɛ ̀ n lɛ gɛ ̀ n fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ nla ̀ mi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ a nti a ̀ ɗiga ̀ g be ̀ g bimiɗ ri ̀ bwaɓ yi nya ̀ m .
I kɛɛ ɓa fɔlɔɔ , di ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ min lɛ Kiris a wog ri ̀ kɛŋ gɛ ̀ n lɛ gɛ ̀ n a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ zi i ki ̀ lɛ ̀ nga ̀ . Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki , a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ gɛ ̀ n bog ɓi gɛ ̀ n yice ̀ m , di mɛ ̀ ru mɛ siito ̀ n mɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛɛ yi lɛ a legsi ki ̀ ɓe di a ̀ fu ̀ nɛɛ nyimiɗ .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri ki ̀ siŋdɛn lɛ mum a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ wii gɛ ̀ n bog , ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn innɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ yɔ ̀ mzi ̀ nyi ,
fɔlɔɔ nnɛ Kiris a ̀ nɛ a ̀ falɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyimiɗ gɛ ̀ n bog ɓi gɛ ̀ n yice ̀ m lɛ a tɛg ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓi ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓi ̀ i ̀ tii ti ki ̀ re ̀ sɛɛ ɓi gɛ ̀ n i ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ ɓe a ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓoŋɓoŋ nyi lɛ a kweɗ ɓɔ .
Ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi konaagh ɓi ki ɓaa ̀ syeesyee a ̀ ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ ɓɛ ɓyom , ɓi ri lɔŋ ci ̀ i ̀ ghziŋ ki ɓi ɓi ̀ rɔɔ ɓi ɓyɛɛ ̀ yu ̀ yuiy ; ɓi yin ɗi i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ ɓi kona ̀ g ki ̀ tɛɛ ̀ zii ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kɛ ̀ ngi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ja ̀ ŋbog ɓi bee inɛ ̀ n , ɓi ki yin lɛ ɓi tɛɛ ̀ zi ̀ ɓɔ ri ̀ ri ̀ kuu ɗi ɓifu ̀ na ̀ ɗi fɔlɔɔ , ɗi ɗi ri lɔŋ be ̀ g yi ̀ ce ̀ m ri ̀ kuu ɗi ̀ fog , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ lɔ ̀ gtɛ ̀ n .
I ɓyɛɛ ɓa ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu tɛɛ ̀ ziyɛn mum , di ɓɛ mɛ le ̀ ka ̀ ri ̀ wewe ̀ y ɗi ɓituwe ɓi ri ̀ so ̀ o ̀ so ̀ ghɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓum , ɓisuulɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɔɔɓɔgsi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ri ̀ kuu ɗi riɓɔgsi ̀ ɗin ̀ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ lɛ ɓɛ teɗ zo ̀ ghɛ ̀ n gɛ ̀ n bog ɓi gɛ ̀ n yice ̀ m , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa ti ri fe ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ ɓɛ ri ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓe .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi saaɗ a ̀ ri ̀ kpaa , ɓi ̀ tuwe ɓi ɓɛ ti ɓɛ weeyi ̀ ɓi zo ̀ ghɛ ̀ n i ̀ ɓum ɓi ti ɓi kila ̀ g lɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ yiyiti ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓyaa be ̀ g yi ̀ ce ̀ m .
Lɛ bwaɓ yi ɓɛ ̀ lem ɓɛ ɓɛ ̀ sani ̀ nya ri ̀ yi ɓipii ̀ yi yin lɛ yi pisi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓe ŋwos adɛŋ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki , yɛ ̀ ɛ Kiris a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ ti ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u ɓi ziinɛ , a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ : U ̀ kɔ ̀ ni ɓi kifu ̀ na , nsoo ̀ lɛ com ki mum a ̀ faa wɔ ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , u ̀ fagha ̀ mɛ ̀ nyoo .
U ̀ ti kɔ ̀ ɔ wog kirɔɔ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ tuwe ɓi ɓɛ tɔni lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓɔgsi wɔ ̀ ri ̀ ɓyɔ , nsoo ̀ ɓi ɓɛ funɛɛ ɓisuu zo ̀ ghɛ ̀ n i ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓe .
Nni fɔɔnnɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ nkpaaghi lɛ : wɔ ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , mɛ ̀ ɛnɛ , n ̀ -yu ̀ u lɛ nki ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗyɔɔ , lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ ɓan kɛm ̀ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna .
A ̀ loogh ki ̀ kpaa lɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ kɔ ̀ ni ɓi nsoo ̀ ɓi ̀ fu ̀ na , nsoo ̀ mɛ ̀ fafa ̀ a ̀ mɛ zɛy , nsoo ̀ ɓi ̀ tuwe ɓi ɓɛ tɔni lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓɔgsi wɔ ̀ ri ̀ ɓyɔ , nsoo ̀ ɓi ɓɛ funɛɛ ɓisuu zo ̀ ghɛ ̀ n i ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓe , ɓyom ɓi ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi rɔɔ ɓi wɔ , kɔlɛ ɓi ̀ fu ̀ na ɓi ̀ n ɓyɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ikilɛ ̀ n lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓyɛɛ ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ .
A ̀ ki ɓɔ ̀ ɓti lɛ wɔ ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ! Mɛ ̀ ɛnɛ , n ̀ -yu ̀ u lɛ nki ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗyɔɔ , fɔlɔɔ a ri ̀ lɛ , a ̀ pisii bee i ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔgsa ̀ g ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ n ̀ tonto , a ̀ re ̀ si ̀ bee i ̀ nyɔn .
Ɓisuulɛ Yeesus Kiris a ̀ roo ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ sii ti ri ̀ zo ̀ ghɛ ̀ n i ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓis lɛ ri ̀ fa ɗi a ̀ fagha ̀ nyoo yi ̀ i ̀ gɛ ̀ n bog ɓi gɛ ̀ n yice ̀ m .
Pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ bimiɗ a ̀ ti a ̀ rɛla ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ ŋwos ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ja ̀ ŋ yii ̀ i ̀ ki ̀ say a ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ ɓifu ̀ na mɛ ̀ fog mɛ mɛ yin lɛ mɛ pisi ɓi ̀ ɓe ŋwos adɛŋ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Kiris a ̀ fagha ̀ ki ̀ fu ̀ na kifog ɓisuu ɓiɓe , a ̀ ki kɔ ̀ ri min ɓi wee ̀ lem a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ɓoŋɓoŋ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ be ̀ na ̀ bena ɓii ɓɛɛ ɓa ki ̀ ɓoŋ ki a rɛsag mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ mii mii ̀ .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓi ri ̀ fa ɗi ̀ fog , a ̀ mɛ ki ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ tɛɛ ̀ ziyɛn ɓɛɛ ɓa lɛ syeesyee i ̀ suu ̀ ce ̀ m kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ com ki ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ fen a lɔ ̀ ŋkaa .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay kɛɛ ̀ re ̀ resi girig ɓi ̀ si ; lɛ a ̀ loogh ki ̀ kpaa ̀ lɛ ,
Kan lɛ : Bee inɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ reni ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ nɛ lɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ , ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ fɛlɛ : N ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ foŋi ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓyɛm ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ rem maa , n ̀ ka ̀ n ɓɔ ɓyɔ ɓi nto . A ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɓ min lɛ :
Fɔɔnnɛ ma ̀ a yititi ɓi ɓiɓe ɓyaa , nsoo ̀ mɛ ̀ na ̀ ni ̀ maa .
Ɓisuulɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓi ti ɓi ̀ cenɛn , ki ghɛɓsii ti ̀ ɓi com lɛ ɓɛɛ fa ɓi ̀ fu ̀ na ɓisuu riso ̀ ghɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓiɓe ɓin ̀ .
Nni fɔɔnnɛ mi ̀ ni ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , ti ̀ ti lɛ ti ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ i ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ce ̀ li ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ ris lɛ bwaɓ yi Yeesus .
A ̀ nɛmga ̀ ɓi ̀ si nyɔɔnyɔn a ̀ bee , bee inɛ i ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ cɛɓ ɓi ki ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ki ki ɓagha ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , yɛɛlɔɔ lɛ ɓi nyoo yi ̀ i ̀ i nyimi ̀ ɗ .
Ti ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey anɛ ɓɛ rɛsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ti tyo ̀ ŋdɛɛna min Bɛ ̀ ll ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ n ̀ ɗem wu wu ri lɛ sɛɛghi sɛɛghi , ri ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi ɗi ri ɗi ̀ ronɛn , n ̀ ɗem wu ̀ tɛnɛn ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ri lɛ ɓi fa wɔ ̀ bɛ ̀ lɛn , nyoo i ̀ ɓa n ̀ wu ̀ ɓsiyɛn ɓi mɛ ̀ nig mɛ mɛ ri mɛ ̀ tɛnɛn .
Ti ɓe ̀ ŋina dya ̀ ɓɛn inɛ ti la ̀ alam ̀ ɓɛ ̀ n , ti ̀ si ̀ i ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɓisuulɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ fagha ̀ n ̀ ka ̀ g roo ̀ zag mɛka ̀ g mii .
Ti ɓe ̀ eghɓe ̀ ŋɗɛɛna ɓi ̀ si ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si , ti ̀ fee ̀ fe ̀ gsɛ ̀ n lɛ ti ɓa ri ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n , ti ̀ ki ki ̀ ki ɓiɓan ɓi syeesyee .
Tyɛ ̀ ki le ̀ g rikɛ ̀ ngi ̀ ɗi a mɛ ̀ taŋzɛn mis yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kila ̀ g , ti faa ̀ fa ̀ lɛ ̀ n lɔŋ ɓi ̀ sii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ ite ̀ ɗ , a ̀ ɓiisɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi seesee lɛ ŋwos a Kan a kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛɛ yi .
Ɓisuulɛ , i ti ̀ kɛ ̀ nkɛni asu ti ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ɓe ɓi ri ̀ fee , di ti ̀ mɛ yi saaɗ , ki ̀ fu ̀ na kidɛŋ ki yii ̀ di ɓisuu zo ̀ ghɛ ̀ n i ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓe .
Ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓi lɔŋ lɛ ti ɓoŋɓoŋ lɛ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ m ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ ɗuu ɗi ɗi ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɗigsii ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki Bɛ ̀ ll n ̀ too ̀ te ̀ ɗ ri coo iris ɓi nɗem .
Ɓɛ ti ɓɛ weeyi ̀ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ yogsii ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Moyis , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ wog nyi nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g di ɓum ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ , nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓɛraa ɓɛ resii ri ̀ na ̀ n ɗii .
Ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ fe ̀ g lɛ ri ̀ kuu ɗi ntɔɓ aɗi ɗyɛɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ a ̀ sɛɛti ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ ghɛn bwaɓ yi rira ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɗi lɛ ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ ɓum , yi yi kii lɛ a ɓa n ̀ tɛnɛn , yɛ ̀ ɛ zɛy ri ̀ zɛy a ̀ com , a ̀ ki fen Nghay a ̀ geesɛ ̀ n .
Ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ sii yii roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ rɔ ̀ ŋi mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ le ̀ ɓi a ̀ kpaa ti ̀ lɛ : Kan a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ yɔ ̀ mzii ɓum ɓii .
Ki ri koŋnyoo lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ cem , a raɗ mum ɓi ɓya ̀ g ɓii .
Yitiina lɔŋ cɛɓ ki ɓi ̀ ghɛɓka ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ n ̀ tonto mɛ ɓi ̀ teka ̀ ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ki Bɛ ̀ ll ; ɓi ̀ woka ̀ mɛ ̀ tɔɓ lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ̀ n ; wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ ki ca ̀ rɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ɓi za ̀ a ̀ i ̀ nɛn .
Ki mɓala ̀ g lɛ ɗi ɗi yii , ɓɛ sɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ mgi ̀ mi ̀ ni , nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓɛ yeeyee ̀ si ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓum , ɗi ɗi yii , ɓi ̀ sug ɓi ga ̀ m i ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yee ̀ ye ̀ e ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ fɔlɔɔ .
Ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɓɓɛ ̀ nga ̀ mɛ ̀ tɔɓ mɛ ɓimbu ̀ ŋ , ɓi ̀ ki woki kirɔɔ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ɓɛ nti ɓɛ ɓata ̀ g mi ̀ ni ɓyom , ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ yigha ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɓyom ɓi ɓi cee ɓin ̀ lɛ , ɓyɔɔ ri ɓi ɓi ri ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m .
Fɔɔnnɛ kɛ ̀ ɓi ca ̀ ɗ ntyweeyi win ɓisuulɛ wu ri ri ̀ ɓyoo mɛle ̀ ɓ .
Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ ɓi ɓa ri ̀ ki ̀ si ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ , di fɔɔnnɛ ɓi roo ̀ zi ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓi ̀ teɗ min com ki a ̀ ka ̀ ka ̀ mi ̀ ni .
Lɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kaa rɔ ̀ ɓ kiden lɔŋ lɛsa ̀ g lɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ yu ̀ u a kpaŋ , a ̀ a lɛ ̀ mzii ɓi .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ saaɗ ɓi mis mɛ ̀ m a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ghɛɓi ̀ lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , wɔ ̀ lɛ i a ̀ sugtii ri ̀ jɛ ̀ m , n ̀ ɗem wɛ ̀ m wɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ wogti kirɔɔ ri ̀ nyi .
Ɓi ̀ sii yin ɓɛroɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ sugta ̀ g ri ̀ jɛ ̀ m lɛ ɓɛɛ ɗyaŋ , ɓi ̀ sii ri ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ gherɛɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ ghɛɓsi ɓyɛɓ ɓya ̀ a ̀ .
Ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi ri ri ̀ yi ɗi mum a ̀ yii saaɗ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi a ̀ tyweeyii , ɗi ɓa ti ̀ com ki kɛɛ ̀ re ̀ resi mum ɓɛ ̀ saaɗ ɓɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi a ̀ ghɛɛ ɓi ̀ .
Ɓumɓɛ abɛ ̀ y ɓɛ teka ̀ mɛ ̀ sɛɛ ̀ ghsɛɛgh lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗyaa .
Lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n nnɛ ti ̀ ti ti ̀ yila ̀ g lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ zi ri jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi ̀ i ̀ , ɓi le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ti seesee ɓi kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ com ki ŋwaa ̀ ghɛɛ ɓi ̀ .
Lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n nnɛ Aɓɛl a ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ gha ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ ɓi ̀ fu ̀ na ɓi ɓi cee ɓi Kaɛŋ ; lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗii , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kpaagha ̀ Aɓɛl lɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ saaɗ , Bɛ ̀ ll nyimiɗ a sɛka ̀ ri ̀ fa ɗii , ɗyɛɛ kii lɛ a ɓaɓa a ̀ to ̀ to ̀ g , nsoo ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ mɛ wu .
Lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n nnɛ Enɔg a ̀ ɓɔka ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll cem , kɛ ̀ ɛ yi com ki lɛ ri ̀ wu ; ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ di ̀ gha ̀ ɓi nyi ɓisuulɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓɔka ̀ ri ̀ nyi aɗyoo ; di ɓɛ ka ɓɔg ɓi ri nyi aɗyoo , Enɔg a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a wog ki ̀ rɔɔ ri ̀ nyi .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ i mum a ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ rɔɔ Bɛ ̀ ll ; ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ tyɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ tɛɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ja ̀ ŋbog , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ gherɛɛ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ wɔɔ , a ̀ ki gherɛn ti lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ti a ̀ le ̀ ɓki ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kaaghi ̀ nyi .
Lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n nnɛ Nowe a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ loka ̀ nyi ki ̀ kpaa ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ di ɓɛ ka ghɛn ɓi , nni a ̀ risi ̀ gha ̀ , a ̀ wog ri ̀ kpaa ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ toŋ ki ̀ kɔm lɛ a ghɛɓsi naa yi ̀ i ̀ i ɓum ; fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi kigha ̀ Nowe lɛ a fa ziinɛ bɛ ̀ lɛn , a ̀ fɔ ̀ n ri ̀ ɓa ɗi mum a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ ɓa lɛ saaɗ ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
Lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n innɛ Abiraham a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll mɛ ̀ wog yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ nyi , a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ n ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kii lɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ nyi ɓii ̀ faa ̀ . A ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ fɔlɔɔ kɛ ̀ ɛ yi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ .
Lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , nnɛ a ̀ ghɛghɛ ̀ ɓka ̀ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ke ̀ n ɓi ziinɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ siŋdɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ a ̀ ri ̀ nyi ɓii ̀ faa ̀ . A ̀ a nkɔ ̀ ra ̀ g ɓi ɓi ̀ laa , lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ -Isag ɓɛɛ ̀ Yakɔɓ ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ girig n ̀ ka ̀ g wɔm win ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ Abiraham a ̀ ɓoŋɓo ̀ ŋga ̀ ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll yɛɛ feka ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ i ̀ ri ̀ lɛ i ̀ toŋɗɛ ̀ n , nyimiɗ yɛɛ ki toŋ , yɔ ̀ lɛ kpegkpeg .
Lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n innɛ , nsoo ̀ Sara a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ mɛ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ a kiti boo i ̀ mum , ɓisuulɛ a ̀ tyweeya ̀ ka ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ roo ̀ zii nka ̀ g wii .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ki ̀ bog ki mum ki ki ɓagha ̀ di kaa tɔ ̀ gti kin ̀ , ki kigha ̀ boo i ̀ nɛ i ̀ te ̀ ghɛɛ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ tyɔɛy ti aɗyoo , nsoo ̀ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ sɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ anɛ ɓi be ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ yin lɛ ɓɛ ɓay .
Lɔŋ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n innɛ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ cuugha ̀ di ɓɛ ka teɗ ɓi ɓyom ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ka ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ ; ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ y ɓyɔ , ɓɛ ki nya ̀ a ̀ rɛn ri ɓyɔ di ɓi kakay fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ , ɓɛ ki kpaa lɛ ɓɔɔ ri ɓɛ ̀ ke ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓi ri ̀ ghaa ̀ gh fɛ ɓi ziinɛ .
Ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ to ̀ tog ɓɛn ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ɓɛɛ ̀ re ̀ resi lɛ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n lɛ : Ɓɛɛ ̀ kaakaa kilɔ ̀ ŋ kidɛŋ .
I kɛɛ ɓa lɛ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ y wɔɔ kɛɛ ɗiɗi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ ɓi nɗem , di ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ɓa ri ̀ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki lɛ ɓɛɛ sugti wɔɔ .
Ɓi saaɗ a ̀ ri ̀ kpaa , ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki ki cee kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓɛ kɔnkɔ ̀ nga ̀ , yɛɛlɔɔ lɛ , ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyoo ; ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ wog n ̀ too ̀ ri ̀ ɗ lɛ ɓɛɛ reŋi nyi lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll wa ̀ a ̀ , ɓisuulɛ a ̀ pe ̀ gsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ bimiɗ a ̀ ba ̀ n .
Lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n innɛ Abiraham a ̀ fu ̀ nɛ ̀ nga ̀ Isag di Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛɛ nyi ; m ̀ bobog wi ̀ i ̀ a man nnɛ a ̀ fu ̀ nɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɔɔ , kɔlɛ ri ̀ nyi nnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ n ̀ ka ̀ g .
A ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Ɓi Isag nnɛ u ̀ ɓaagɛ ri ̀ boo i ̀ mum i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ɓɛsa ̀ g ri ̀ wɔ ̀ .
Abiraham a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ fe ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ , nsoo ̀ mum a ̀ a wii , a ̀ ghe ̀ mzi ̀ nyi , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ pɛɛ ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ nyi man wii ̀ ; ri ̀ kuu ɗi kife ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki righe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓiloŋ , kɛɛ ri lɔɔ .
Lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n innɛ Isag a ̀ ma ̀ ga ̀ lɛ ri ̀ Yakɔɓ , ri ̀ Eso ɓisuu ɓiɓan ɓi ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ bee ̀ bɛ ̀ y .
Lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n innɛ Yakɔɓ a ̀ ma ̀ ga ̀ ɓɔn ɓɛ Yoosɛɓ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m lɛ bog bo ̀ g bog , di a ̀ ti ɓii ̀ wii ̀ , a ̀ tuŋi ̀ ɓi nto wu kigeŋ ki a ̀ a mɓe ̀ mda ̀ g mii ̀ , a ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n innɛ Yoosɛɓ a ̀ ɓu ̀ ga ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki ri ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓɔn ɓɛ Isirayɛl a Egiɓtɛn , di a ̀ ti ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ ri ̀ wu , a ̀ ki reɓsɛn com ki ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ri ɓi ̀ woɓ ɓii .
Lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n innɛ ɓɛ ̀ yali ̀ ɓɛ Moyis ɓɛ nyamga ̀ nyi ɓi naa ɓɛ ̀ ŋwii ɓɛraa ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ ri ̀ yalɛ ̀ n ɗii , ɓisuulɛ ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ man a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ rɔɔtɛ ̀ nga ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ risi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi kidɔ ̀ gsɛna ki rifo ̀ m ɗi fagha ̀ .
Lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n innɛ Moyis a ̀ ɓe ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ regi nyi lɛ man a ̀ gɔ ̀ n i ̀ Farawɔŋ di a ̀ ti n ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ,
a ̀ ɓii ̀ sɛ ̀ n ki ̀ kɔ ̀ ni lɛ ɓɛɛ kiki nyi mɛ ̀ tɔɓ n ̀ ɗaŋ ɗi ɓumɓɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ rɔ ̀ tɛ ̀ nga ̀ , a ̀ cee lɛ a wog ki ̀ rɔɔ ɓi ki ̀ ɓe ɓiɗu ̀ m maa ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n .
A ̀ ghɛn lɛ n ̀ too ̀ ri ̀ ɗ wu Kiris a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ woo ̀ gh wu cee coo ikum wu Egiɓtɛn kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ve ̀ g ɓisuulɛ mis mii mɛ ɓagha ̀ lɔŋ ri mɛ ̀ le ̀ ɓ mɛ mɛ ɓoŋɓo ̀ ŋga ̀ nyi asu .
Lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n innɛ a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ y a Egiɓtɛn , kɛ ̀ ɛ risi bim inɛ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi ɓagha ̀ lɛ ɗi wog , a ̀ si ̀ i ̀ rɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɔŋ ɓi nɗɛli wii yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ kali lɛ , a seesee Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ ɓaa ̀ ghɛn ɓi .
Lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n innɛ a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ Paska ̀ , a ̀ tɔg lɛ ɓɛɛ misi bwaɓ ɓi mɛ ̀ suunaa di fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom anɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ cuusii ɓɔn ɓɛ n ̀ tonto , a rɔɓ kɛ ̀ ɛ cuusi ɓɛroɓɛ a Isirayɛl .
Lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n innɛ ɓɔn ɓɛ Isirayɛl ɓɛ syaa ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ m ̀ ɓa ̀ ŋ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ zi i zɛy ; yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓumɓɛ a Egiɓtɛn ɓɛ mɛɛ ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ girig , mɛ ̀ nig mɛ ghaa ̀ gh ri ̀ ɓɔ .
