ɓisuulɛ ki ri ma ̀ a ̀ gh di mum a ̀ cenɛɛ mɛ ̀ tɔɓ mɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki nyi ɓi mɛ ̀ ɓe ̀ e lɛ a ki Bɛ ̀ ll mɛ ̀ wog .
Lɛ ri ̀ kem ɗidɛŋ ɗi yin ɓisuu ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ cena ̀ g mɛ ̀ ɓi ̀ i ̀ mɛ ɓi ki ̀ ɓe ki nyi yɛɛ kii ̀ . Wɔ ̀ lɛ i ɓi ̀ cenɛɛ ri ̀ kɛŋ di ɓi ki ̀ i kirɔɔ , fɔlɔɔ a ri ̀ ma ̀ a ̀ gh ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Lɛ ri ̀ ɓa ɗi ̀ n ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ mi ̀ ni mii ̀ ɓisuulɛ Kiris girig a ̀ woka ̀ ri ̀ kɛŋ ɓisu win , a ̀ ki ca ̀ ɗ mini ki ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ ki lɛ ɓi nɔɔ ̀ ti ɓi ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɓ ɓii .
Nyi a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ɓi kiɓe , kɛ ̀ ɛ ki kpaa kiɓan ki pwa ̀ a ̀ nsoo ̀ ŋwos bog ;
nyi a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ soo sɛmi nyi , kɛ ̀ ɛ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi mum ki ̀ sɛmi ̀ , a ̀ a soo wowo ̀ g ri ̀ kɛŋ kɛɛ ̀ tam mum , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , a ̀ fa ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ yɔ ̀ mgi ̀ ɓum lɛ saaɗ ;
nyi a ̀ nɛ a ̀ tɛ ̀ ka ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓis ɓi nyoo yi ̀ i ̀ ɓi ki ̀ te aɗyoo lɛ di kɛɛ ɓa lɛ , i ti ̀ mɛ wu ɓi san a ̀ nɛ a ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓis , ti ̀ ghɛɓ cɛɓ ki ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri lɛ saaɗ . Mɛ ̀ ɓi ̀ i ̀ mii mɛɛ kigha ̀ lɛ ti wɔn ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ ɓagha ̀ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yi yɛɛ de ̀ ŋde ̀ ŋ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ m ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , ɓi ̀ mɛ sugti yɛ ̀ ɛ mɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ a ̀ nɛ a ɓe ̀ ŋɓeŋ mɛghay min .
Nsoo ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ , ɓaana girig ri ̀ mɛ ̀ wog , giɓ bimiɗ a wog yii wii ̀ , di fɔɔnnɛ kɛɛ ɓa lɛ i ɓɛ ̀ baŋi ̀ ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ gherɛɛ ɓi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ kuu ɗi cɛɓ ɗi ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓaa ɓɛɛ ̀ ghɛghɛɓ ri ɓɔ ɗyɛɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓɔ ki ̀ syo ̀ ŋi ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n nsoo ̀ mum a ̀ a to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛɛ ɓi ri ɓɔ .
Lɛ ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ cɛɓ ki ̀ n ki ri ki ̀ tɛnɛn , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ wog .
Mɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ ŋ min mɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa mɛrɛ ̀ ŋ mɛ seesee ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɓi dan ; fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ tyo ̀ ŋ ti ɓaghrɛn , ti ̀ caka ri ̀ mɛkpe ̀ y mɛ ɓɛ kii ri ̀ gol , ri ̀ n ̀ waa ̀ wu syeesyee ,
ki ̀ ɓan kifog n ̀ ɗɛ ̀ ŋ wu ɓi ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ ri ̀ wɔ wu ri wu wu ri wu ̀ nyamɛn ɓi nɗem , wɛɛ ri n ̀ ɗɛ ̀ ŋ wu wu yin lɛ wu ɗyoŋ , lɛ wu ri n ̀ ɗɛ ̀ ŋ wu nghay wu wu ri lɛ tɛ ̀ tɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , wɔ ti ̀ lɛ fyo ̀ oog , ri ̀ kuu ɗi ̀ n ɗyɛɛ ri gi ̀ n i com ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛ abɛ ̀ y , ɓɛ dya ̀ ɓɛn yaa ̀ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛ nti ɓɛ rɛŋɗa ̀ g , lɛ ɓɛ nti ɓɛ woki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yii ɓaa ;
fɔlɔɔ nnɛ Sara a ̀ a nti a ̀ woki ̀ Abiraham a ̀ ki regi nyi lɛ kan wi ̀ i ̀ . Sara a ̀ nɛn nnɛ ɓi ̀ ti do ̀ o ̀ yii , di ɓi ki ̀ ki kirɔɔ kɛ ̀ ɓi ca ̀ rɛn lɛ com kidɛŋ kɛɛ niŋzi mi ̀ ni nyo ̀ o ̀ .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ baŋi ̀ , ɓi ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ girig lɛ mum bimiɗ a ghɛɓ ri ̀ giɓ wii ̀ , a ̀ yi lɛ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛ ri ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin ɗi i ̀ te ̀ ɗ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ baŋi ̀ ; terina ɓɔ ri ̀ nyaasɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ girig ki ̀ teri ̀ ma ̀ a ̀ gh a ̀ cɛɓ bas ɗi ̀ mi ̀ ni , di fɔlɔɔ nnɛ com kidɛŋ kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ gheŋɗɛn ɓi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n yi ̀ n .
N ̀ siitɛɛ mi ̀ ni ki ̀ kpaa ̀ lɛ , ɓaana ɓɛ ̀ fe ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ fog , n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n bog , ɓaana ɓɛ ̀ ronɛn ɗi n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ geni , ɓi ̀ ɓa ri ̀ nɗem wu nyi ̀ inyi ̀ g ri ̀ nɗem wu sɛɛ ̀ dɛn mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ ɓi zi .
Kɛ ̀ ɓi rɔ ̀ ŋ kiɓe ri ki ̀ ɓe , nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓi pɛɛ ̀ zi fi ̀ sɛm ri fi ̀ sɛm , lɔŋ com ki ɓi ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ kii ̀ ki ri lɛ ɓi maŋ ̀ maŋ ɓum , lɛ ki ̀ ɓan ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ mi ̀ ni mii ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ n , lɛ ɓi teɗ mɛ ̀ wus mɛ ɓɛma ̀ a ̀ gh .
Ɓisuulɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ a keesi cɛɓ , a ̀ ghɛn mɛ ̀ ru mɛ kinya ̀ a ̀ , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ŋwɔm wii lɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ kpaakpaa ɓiɓan ɓi ɓeɓtɛn kɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pwa ̀ a ̀ ;
a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ghii jɛ ̀ m ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓe , ki ̀ rɔɔ kɛɛ ̀ ki a ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ , a ̀ falɛ ̀ n ɓi ri ̀ kaaka ̀ a ̀ ɗi fyo ̀ oog .
Ɓisuulɛ mis mɛ Kan mɛɛ ̀ seesee ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri lɛ saaɗ , mɛ ̀ ree ̀ mii mɛramɛn ri ̀ bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n yaa , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , Kan a ̀ ti a ̀ paa ̀ za ̀ g ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki kiɓe .
Ghɛn yɛɛ ri min lɛ a ̀ tɔɓ mi ̀ ni di ɓi ̀ falɛɛ ɓi ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗi kirɔɔ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ ?
I ki kpaŋi gi kɔm ̀ lɛ ɓi wog n ̀ tɔɓ ɓisuu saaɗ , di ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ma ̀ a ̀ gh ; kɛ ̀ ɓi risi ɓum nsoo ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɓi ki ɓu ̀ u ̀ sɛn ;
wɔ ̀ lɛ kemziina ̀ Kiris ɓi mɛ ̀ rem min fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Kan wi ̀ n . Ɓaana ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ̀ pe ̀ gsɛn lɛ ɓi ɓag mum bimiɗ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ tɔɔgh mi ̀ ni azi anɛ ɓi dya ̀ ɓɛn inɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ yɔ ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog ki ̀ ina fɔlɔɔ ri n ̀ ɗem wu tɛ ̀ tɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , ri ̀ bɔgsɛ ̀ n ; n ̀ ɗem win wu ɓa wu ̀ tɛnɛn ɓi le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ to ̀ tog mini ki ̀ ɓe , ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ feefengi ̀ syeesyee wi ̀ n a ri ̀ ghɛɓ ɓi Kiris ɓi ɗu ̀ m ɓɛɛ wog n ̀ too ̀ ri ̀ ɗ .
Lɛ ki ri ki ̀ rɔɔ lɛ mum a wog n ̀ tɔɓ lɛ a ki ̀ ki kirɔɔ , di fɔlɔɔ yɛɛ ri ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ cee lɛ a wog n ̀ tɔɓ lɛ a ki ̀ ki ki ̀ ɓe .
Ɓisuulɛ Kiris girig a ̀ wugha ̀ gɛ ̀ n bog ɓi gɛnice ̀ m ɓisuu ɓiɓe ɓi ɓum , nyi a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ syeesyee a ̀ mum , a ̀ wu ɓisuu ɓiɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓum lɛ di a kɛn ̀ ɗi ̀ mi ̀ ni yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll . Ɓɛ wola ̀ nyi ri ̀ wu ɗi ɓi mɛ ̀ mu ̀ u ̀ a ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu Nghay .
Ri ̀ Nghay a ̀ nɛ ̀ n innɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ kɔm ̀ ki ̀ kakalii Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a mɛ ̀ ghay mɛ mɛ ri ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y ,
yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ mɛ ̀ ghay mɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ kigha ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛ ̀ lɔg ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ajɛ ̀ m , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ si ̀ i ̀ si ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ nɗem , a ̀ ɓoŋɓo ̀ ŋ ; ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ Nowe a ̀ soso ̀ ɓka ̀ ki ̀ kɔm ; ki ̀ kɔm ki ̀ n kɛɛ kigha ̀ lɛ ɓɔɔ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ taa ̀ raa ɓɛ ghɛɓka ̀ lɛ mɛ ̀ nig .
Mɛ ̀ nig mɛn ̀ mɛ ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki ba ̀ ɓtis i ̀ nɛ yɛɛ ̀ ghɛɛghɛɓsi ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , ba ̀ ɓtis i ̀ nɛ ̀ n i ̀ yin ɓii ̀ so ̀ o ̀ soo tifin ti ɓi nyoo , ki ̀ ɓan kifog i ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ falɛ ̀ n ɗi mum a ̀ falɛɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ syeesyee a ̀ nɗem . A ghɛɛghɛɓsi ̀ mi ̀ ni lɛ ri ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi Yeesus Kiris a ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ nga ̀ ,
a ̀ ɓɔg aɗyoo , a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi wee ̀ lem a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ; wɔɔ a la ̀ lami lɛ ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ titom , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ te ̀ ɗ mɛ ɓi ɗyoo mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ Kiris a ̀ woka ̀ ri ̀ kɛŋ ɗi ɓi mɛ ̀ mu ̀ u ̀ , mi ̀ nii ̀ rig ɓanɛɛ na ri ̀ ri ̀ yiti ̀ ɗin ̀ ɓisuulɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ mɛ wog rikɛŋ ɗi ɓi mɛ ̀ mu ̀ u ̀ , a ̀ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ mɛ ghasɛn ɗi ki ̀ ɓe
lɛ di fɔɔnnɛ a ghɛɓ yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ɗi ri , ɓi ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru i ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ti ̀ ki ̀ ghagsii ɓi ziinɛ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ghɛɓ ti cɛɓ ki n ̀ ɗem wii wɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ a ghɛɓ .
Ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ roo ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ gherɛɛ ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ ghɛghɛ ̀ ɓka ̀ ɓi ki ̀ ɓu ̀ u ̀ si ̀ , ɓi ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi n ̀ ɗem win wɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ nkɔ ̀ n , ɓi ̀ nɔnɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ g , ɓi ̀ ɗiɗi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ri ̀ ɗi ɗi kiɓe , ɓi ̀ ŋwaŋŋwa ̀ ŋ mɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ g , ɓi ̀ ki ɓɔɔɓɔgsi ̀ ɓi ̀ nu ̀ n ɓi ɓi ri ki ̀ ɓan ki ki ɓeɓtɛɛ ki ciɓ .
Nni ɓigomi ̀ nɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n ɓɛɛ ̀ kuukuu ̀ ghra ̀ g yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ tii ti ̀ ɓi ɓɔ ɓi coo kiɓeɓta ̀ g ki cɛɓ ki ̀ n , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ wɔmwɔm mini .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓɛ ɓa ̀ agh gɛ ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki kin ̀ ɓi mis mɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti ja ̀ ŋbog lɛ a yɔm ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ cem ri ̀ ɓi ̀ loŋ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ kalɛ ̀ nga ̀ girig a ɓi ̀ loŋ , a ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ mɛn ɓi cɛɓ kaa ki mɛmu ̀ u ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , lɛ di ɓɛɛ ɓa ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ ɓɛɛ ghɛɓ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu Nghay .
Ri ̀ sugtɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɗi ti ja ̀ ŋbog , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ ri ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n , kɛ ̀ ɓi falɛn ɓi ɓi ̀ nɔɔ ̀ nɔɔ ̀ , di ɓi kiki bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n .
Ki ̀ ɓan ki asu ki ri lɛ : Ɓaana ri ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ lɔ ̀ gtɛn ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n , lɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ti a ̀ lɔki ̀ n ̀ kun wu ɓiɓe .
Ɓaana ri ̀ n ̀ ɗem wulɛ ɓi ghaɓki ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓin di ɓɛ yuu a lɔ ̀ ŋkin kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ti ̀ ru ̀ ru ̀ mi ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ ɓi mi ̀ ni a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ fa ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ nyi , ki ̀ ina ki ̀ say ri ri ̀ fa ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓi ki ̀ rɔɔ ki ɓum ɓɛmbog fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ syeesyee ɓɛ ɓum ɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛkɛɛ ̀ si ̀ geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ti i ̀ ghɛna ̀ g bee lɛ bee .
I mum a ̀ pinii ŋwɔm lɛ a kali ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll , a ghagsi lɔŋ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ghɛɛghɛɓsi ̀ ki ̀ say , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ kɔ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ri i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ faa nyi , di fɔlɔɔ nnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a teɗ ri ̀ kem ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m lɛ Yeesus Kiris a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ ri ̀ kem , ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ . A ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n .
Mi ̀ ni ɓum ɓɛm ɓɛ nɗem , ri ̀ ɓa ɗi ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ gɛn ɓɛ mɛfe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn ɓɛ ɓɛ ri yɛ ̀ ɛ ɗuu ɗi ghɛ ̀ g-ghɛ ̀ g , ɗyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ si ̀ ɗ mini yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ kali lɛ ki ̀ ke ̀ neke ̀ ne ̀ ki kiɓan kidɛŋ kɛɛ tanɛɛ mi ̀ ni .
Ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɔŋ lɛ ɓi ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ rɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓi teteɗ ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ mɛ ̀ tɔɓ mɛ Kiris , di fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ɓii ̀ rongii girig ri ̀ ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ kem ɗii ɗi ri ɓii ̀ ghɛnɛɛ .
I ɓɛɛ ̀ sɛɛsɛmgi ̀ mi ̀ ni lɛ ɗii ɗi Kiris , di ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ma ̀ a ̀ ghmaagh ɓisuulɛ N ̀ ghay a ̀ ri ̀ kem , N ̀ ghay a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi mi ̀ ni .
Wa ̀ a ̀ dɛŋ kɔ ̀ ɔ ɓa lɛ u ̀ wowo ̀ g mɛ ̀ tɔɓ lɛ u ̀ woli mum , nsoo ̀ lɛ u ̀ yii com , nsoo ̀ lɛ u ̀ ki ̀ i coo kiɓeɓta ̀ g ki kiɓan kidɛŋ , nsoo ̀ lɛ u ̀ pu ̀ rii ŋwɔm ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ;
wɔ ̀ lɛ i ki ri lɛ ɓi wowog ntɔɓ ɓi ɗii ɗi lɛ ki ̀ ristɛ ̀ n , kɛ ̀ ɓi wog ntoo ̀ ri ̀ ɗ , ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɔŋ ki kemzii Bɛ ̀ ll ɓisuu ɗii ɗi ̀ n .
Ɓisuulɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓɛyɔ ̀ m ki kpaŋi , nni ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ m ɓɛn ̀ ɓɛ tumɛɛ ɓi naa i ̀ ɓum ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll . I ɓi ɓi ̀ si nnɛ ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ m ɓɛ tumɛɛ , ri ̀ syɔn ɗi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ ɓengi ̀ ki ̀ gherɛɛ Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ ɗi ri ɓa la ̀ ?
I ri ̀ ghɛɓ ɗi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ saaɗ a ghɛɓ ɗi ka ti fɔlɔɔ ri ntɔɓ , ki ɓa min la ɓi san a ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ kiɓeɓta ̀ g ki mum ri ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe ?
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ wowog mɛtɔɓ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll yɛɛ kɔni , ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ faa ̀ ɓyɛɓ ɓyaa ri n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ roo ̀ za ̀ g mɛ ̀ ka ̀ g mii , ɓi ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗi ɓɛɛ ̀ kiki kirɔɔ .
N ̀ tɔɔgh min ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ Kiseŋi ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n , mɛ ̀ a ̀ nɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ girig N ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn a Ki ̀ seŋi yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɔ , n ̀ ki ɓa ti wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ a ̀ nɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ tɔɓ mɛ Kiris , mɛ ti ri ̀ ga ̀ ɓ ɓi ri ̀ kem ɗi ɗi ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ re ̀ sɛɛ ,
lɛ mɛniina ki ̀ tuu ki jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ki Bɛ ̀ ll ki ɓɛ reɓsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ; kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ka ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ n , mɛniina yɔ ri ̀ syeesyee a ̀ ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ kɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ngi Bɛ ̀ ll , kɛ ̀ ɓi ki ̀ kisay kin ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ɗem wulɛ ɓi fɔn ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni , ki ̀ i ̀ na lɔŋ kɔ ri ̀ syeesyee a ̀ nɗem .
Kɛ ̀ ɓi tuturi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ fagha ̀ mi ̀ ni lɛ ɓi ɓeŋ ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓaana ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yi Bɛ ̀ ll yi ri lɛ yi nɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ ;
fɔlɔɔ nnɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ a ̀ ɓii ̀ kpaŋi ̀ , ɓi ̀ ɓii ̀ teri ̀ ta ̀ m a ̀ ri ̀ kem a ̀ nɛ a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ ɗyoŋ .
Mi ̀ ni ɓi ̀ ɓwɛɗ ɓi ɓum , ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ girig lɛ ɓi ki ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn mɛwog . Nni mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , ɓi cɛɓ ki ɓi ghɛghɛɓ mini ri ̀ mi ̀ ni , sɛɛ ̀ dɛɛna mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ ɓi zi , ɓisuulɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ti kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa nkɔɔ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ daŋa ̀ daŋa , lɔŋ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ sɛɛ ̀ dɛɛ ɓɔmiɗ ɓi zi ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ a re ̀ sag geesɛ ̀ n yi ̀ i ̀ .
Nni sɛɛ ̀ dɛɛna min mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ ɓi zi ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ ucem lɛ nyi yɛɛ pɛsi mi ̀ ni aɗyoo ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki a ̀ siŋdɛ ̀ nga ̀ .
Sɛɛ ̀ dɛɛna ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɗiɗi mini mɛ ̀ rem a lɔ ̀ ŋkii ɓisuulɛ nyimiɗ a ɓeŋ ̀ ɓeŋ mini .
Ɓaana cem , ɓi ̀ kona ̀ g ɓisuulɛ be ̀ na ̀ bena win ̀ a ̀ nɛ lɛ Sata ̀ n a ŋwɔŋ-ŋwɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ monɗo ki kɛɛ ̀ kaakaa com ki kɛɛ sokɛn .
Ɓaana ɓɛ ̀ si ̀ i ̀ rɛn ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , kɛ ̀ ɓi ca ̀ rɛn lɛ a ɓigti mi ̀ ni , ɓi ̀ ki yi lɛ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓin ɓɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛɛ ̀ tuutulɛ ̀ n ri ̀ mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ mɛtɔɓ mɛ ̀ n ɓi ziinɛ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ki ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ lɛ i ɓya ̀ a wog rikɛŋ ɓi maa ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ geesɛ ̀ n bimiɗ , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ mi ̀ ni lɛ ɓi teɗ ga ̀ ɓ ɓi ri ̀ kem ɗii ɗi fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓi Kiris ɓi ɗu ̀ m , a ̀ ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ konagh ki rɛsii lɛ syeesyee nyimiɗ , a ̀ si ̀ i ̀ ra ̀ g mi ̀ ni , a ̀ fa mi ̀ ni i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , a ̀ ki ̀ lɛ ɓi ɓa ɓumɓɛ com ki yin lɛ ki ɓigti ̀ .
Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛn yɛɛ ri ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ A ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n .
N ̀ ka ̀ nii ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓɔɔ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ri ̀ Silvɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ geni wi ̀ s a n ̀ tyweeyi lɛ nfa mi ̀ ni deɓ , n ̀ ki tɛɛ ̀ zi mini ki ̀ re ̀ sii lɛ fɔlɔɔ nnɛ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ geesɛ ̀ n i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ nɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ mii ̀ ɓɛ ̀ si ̀ i ̀ rɛn lɛ tiŋtiŋ , a ̀ ri ̀ .
Ki ̀ seŋi ki ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ nɛn ki a Baɓilon ki togsaagh yi ̀ mi ̀ ni , Marikus a ̀ man wɛm ̀ a ̀ to ̀ gsi ̀ girig mi ̀ ni .
To ̀ gsɛɛna mi ̀ ni ri ̀ mi ̀ ni , di ɓi lɔ ̀ ɔlɔrɛ ̀ n ɓi nkɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ geni . Fyo ̀ oog a ɓa ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓi Kiris ɓi ɗu ̀ m .
Mɛ ̀ Simɔn Pyɛɛri a ̀ nɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say , n ̀ ki ɓa ti nkɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom a Yeesus Kiris , n ̀ ka ̀ ni ɓumɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ ri ̀ kuu ɗi ntyweeyi ɗifog ri ̀ ɗinkis , ɓisu saaɗ a ̀ Yeesus Kiris a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll wi ̀ s ri ̀ n ̀ ghɛɓsi ̀ wi ̀ s .
Geesɛ ̀ n ri ̀ fyo ̀ oog ɓyɛɛ teghɛn a lɔ ̀ ŋkin lɛɛ ̀ gwey lɛ ri ̀ yi ɗi ɓi ̀ yii lɛ ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ Yeesus Kiris a ̀ Kan wi ̀ s .
I ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu Kan wu wu rii ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll wu fagha ̀ ɓi ̀ si com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ki ri lɛ ki ghɛɓsi ̀ ɓi ̀ si lɛ ti ghɛɓ cɛɓ ki lɛ ti falɛn ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗi a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ti yi roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ si lɛ ti kaɓɓɛn ri ̀ kem ɗii , ri ̀ syeesyee wi ̀ i ̀ a ki ̀ syɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ a ̀ fagha ̀ ɓi ̀ si ɓyoo ɓisyeesyee ri ̀ gi ̀ n yi mɛka ̀ g lɛ , i ɓi ̀ teri ɓyom ɓi a ̀ ka ̀ ka ̀ , ɓi ̀ ɓa ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ ɓi ghɛŋi ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓiɓan ɓi ɓyɛɛ ̀ yooyogsi ̀ ɓum ɓyɛɛ ri ɓi ̀ cakɛn ɗi ziinɛ , ɓi yu ki ̀ teri ̀ ga ̀ ɓ ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ɗii ɗi a ̀ ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ɓisu wi ̀ n mii ̀ nnɛ ɓi ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ foŋi ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ win wuce ̀ m lɛ , ɓi ɓɔɓtɛn syeesyee a ̀ ki ̀ syɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗin , ɓi ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɓtɛ ̀ n ri ̀ yi ɓi syeesyee a ̀ ki ̀ syɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ,
ɓi ri ̀ yi ɗi ̀ n aɗyoo , ɓi ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɓtɛ ̀ n ti ̀ ri ̀ ni ̀ ɗ ɗi nɗem ; ɓi ri ̀ ni ̀ ɗ ɗi nɗem ɗi ̀ n , ɓi ̀ sagtɛ ̀ nti ̀ ki ̀ si ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ ; ɓi ki ̀ si ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ kin ̀ , ɓi ̀ foŋdi ̀ ri ̀ falɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ;
ɓi ri ̀ falɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , ɓi ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɓtɛ ̀ nti ̀ ki ̀ rɔɔrɛɛ ki ɓi ri ̀ geni ; ɓi ki ̀ rɔɔrɛɛ ki ɓi ri ̀ geni ki ̀ n , ɓi ̀ foŋ ̀ di ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n .
Ɓisuulɛ i ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ , nni ɓi ghɛnɛɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ɓi ̀ yin lɛ ɓi ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓ lɛ ɓi ̀ ki ̀ i ɓi lɛ ɓi ɓa ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ sasa ̀ y ɓɛ ki wumwum ɓiɗu ̀ n , ɓi ri ̀ yi ɗi ɓi ̀ yii Kan wi ̀ s Yeesus Kiris .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ta ̀ ŋi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ ɗyaŋɗya ̀ ŋ a ̀ nɛ a mɔmɔɓ m ̀ mɔmɔɓɛn , a ̀ ɗimzɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓii ɓi abɛ ̀ y ɓi ti ɓi ̀ so ̀ o ̀ yɛn .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓɛ ̀ m , ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ te ̀ e ̀ sii nyoo lɛ ɓi sii ̀ rag n ̀ ɗee ̀ ghreŋi win ɗi ri ̀ ɓɔ ̀ n ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ nga ̀ mi ̀ ni ; i ɓi ̀ ki ̀ i fɔlɔɔ , ɓya ̀ a kpi ̀ ɓi ɓi ki ̀ ɓe .
Fɔlɔɔ anɛ ̀ n nnɛ ri ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ ɗin ɗi ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ki Kan wi ̀ s ri ̀ n ̀ ghɛɓsi ̀ wi ̀ s Yeesus Kiris , ɗi ri ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ maa ntɔɓ nsoo ̀ lɛsa ̀ g .
