Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓyom ɓi ̀ n , ri ̀ kuu ɗi com ɗi ɓagha ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ mum . A ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ coo jɔmpa ̀ s , nyi ti ̀ n ̀ waatɛn ka ̀ nɗa a ̀ gol ɓi dwey .
