mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ mii lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ kuu ɗi swiɗ ɗiɗɛŋ ɗi ɓɛ ɓaŋzii ɓi ɗuu ɗi ghɛ ̀ g-ghɛ ̀ g , jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi ̀ i ̀ i wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ coo boɓ i ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y .
A ̀ ɓanɓa ̀ nga ̀ tyɔɛy taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓi ca ̀ g kii ki wee ̀ lem , fɔɔnnɛ ga ̀ fa ̀ g i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ ghɛliyɛn ɓɛɓɛg ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , i ̀ kpaŋkpa ̀ ŋga ̀ y nyi ɓi ŋwɔm , i ̀ su wii wu ɓa yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwos a ɓala ̀ g , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki a lo ̀ nlom ri i ̀ te ̀ ɗ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ nyi , nni n ̀ kpi ̀ gha ̀ nyi a mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ loŋ . A ̀ saghi ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ ca ̀ g kii ki wee ̀ lem ɓi nyoo , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ɔ risi !
Mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ri ŋwaa ̀ n ̀ tonto , mɛ ̀ ti ̀ ŋwaa ̀ siito ̀ n , roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ cem . N ̀ wugha ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog n ̀ ɗi ̀ cem fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ . N ̀ wowotii ti ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓa ̀ ti riwu ̀ ri ̀ ti a tɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ .
Nni ka ̀ na min com ki wa ̀ a ghɛɛ , com ki ki ri , ri ̀ ki ki ri ɓii ̀ ki ̀ lɛɛ ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn .
Ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a ɓɛ ̀ azi ɓɛ a ri ̀ nyam ɓɛ ɓi tyɔɛy ti kitaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ti wa ̀ a ghɛɛ mɛ ̀ ri ̀ tyɔ ɓi ca ̀ g ki wee ̀ lem , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ rɛsi ̀ ɓi lamɓa ̀ ɓi gol taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , tyɔɛy ti kitaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ti ri ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓɛ Ɓiseŋi ɓi kitaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , ɓi ̀ rɛsi ̀ ɓi lamɓa ̀ ɓi kitaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓyɔɔ ri Ɓi ̀ seŋi ɓi kitaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓince ̀ m .
Ka ̀ na ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom anɛ ɓi Ki ̀ seŋi ki Kiris ki a Efɛɛzɛ lɛ : Roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ wowotii tyɔɛy ti kitaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓi wee ̀ lem wi ̀ i ̀ , roa ̀ nɛ a kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛɛ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓi ̀ rɛsi ̀ ɓi lamɓa ̀ ɓi gol taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ a kalag fɛlɛ ̀ :
N ̀ -yii mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ mɔɔ , n ̀ -yii ki ̀ say kɔɔ ri ̀ ki ̀ si ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ kɔɔ . N ̀ -yii lɛ u ̀ yin lɛ u ̀ cenɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓum , wɔ ̀ ɔ nfe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛ ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ nkpaakpaa lɛ ɓɔɔ ri ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom , kɔm ̀ lɛ ɓɛ yin ɓɛkɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom , fɔɔnnɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ nghɛɛ lɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ pwa ̀ a ̀ pwaa ̀ .
U ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ si ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ , wɔ ̀ ɔ n ̀ woogh mɛ ̀ tɔɓ ɓisuu ɗii ɗyɛ ̀ m , kɔ ̀ ɔ ki ca ̀ rɛn .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ki ̀ ɓan ki n ̀ ɗi ̀ wɔ ̀ ri ̀ kɔ ki ri lɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ nca ̀ ri n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ u ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ nyi n ̀ tonto .
Yiti min ja ̀ ŋ inɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ nkpi ̀ i , u lɔgti ri ̀ ki ̀ , u ̀ tumɛn ri ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ɗi ɓiɓan ɓi u ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ n ̀ tonto , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ fɔlɔɔ di n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u a lɔ ̀ ŋkɔɔ , m ̀ pisi ̀ ki ̀ rɛsi ̀ ki lamɓa ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ki ri , di u ̀ ɓe ̀ ni ki ̀ cenɗɛɛ .
Nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ ki ̀ ɓan ki syeesyee ki u ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ kɔ ki ri lɛ , u ̀ ɓe ̀ e ̀ zɛɛ mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ mɛ Nikolayit mɛ mɛ ti mɛ ɓeɓki ̀ girig mɛ ̀ .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ree ̀ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ woo ̀ gh com ki N ̀ ghay a kakali Ɓiseŋi ɓi Kiris , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ yagsaagh innɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ faa ̀ ki ̀ ɗu ̀ n ki kite ki cɛɓ ki ki ri ɓi pa ̀ ra ̀ ɗis a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ka ̀ na ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom anɛ ɓi Ki ̀ seŋi ki a Simirinɛ lɛ : Mum a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ nyi ŋwaa ̀ n ̀ tonto , nyi ŋwaa ̀ siito ̀ n , mum a ̀ nɛ a ̀ wugha ̀ a ̀ ki ghe ̀ mɓɛn , a kpaaghi fɛlɛ :
N ̀ -yii n ̀ tɔɓ wu ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki wɔ , ri ̀ ki ̀ sowa ̀ kɔɔ , kɔm ̀ lɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ kum ; n ̀ -yii lɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ reereŋɗɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓɛ ri Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓa Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , ɓɛɛ yooyogsi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɗii ; ɓɛ ri lɔŋ ntaŋzɛn wu Sata ̀ n .
Kɔ ̀ ɔ risi ntɔɓ wu u ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ tulɛɛ ri wɔ . Ghɛna lɛ Sata ̀ n a ri ̀ ɓii ̀ pi ̀ igh kigwey ki ɓi mi ̀ ni ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y lɛ a fee ̀ ghrɛn mi ̀ ni , fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ tulɛɛ ri n ̀ -yeesɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ finɛɛ mɛru n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ . Si ̀ i ̀ rɛn ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpaŋ a ri ̀ wu , fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ faa ̀ ta ̀ m a ̀ cɛɓ .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ree ̀ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ woo ̀ gh com ki Nghay a kakali ɓiseŋi ɓi Kiris , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ yagsaagh innɛ ri ̀ wu ɗi kiɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɗyaa ko ̀ m ɓi .
Ka ̀ na ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom anɛ ɓi ki ̀ seŋi ki a Pɛrigam lɛ , fɛlɛ nnɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ga ̀ fa ̀ g i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ to lɛ pyɔŋpyɔŋ , yɔ ̀ mpooyɛn ɓɛɓɛg ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m a kala ̀ g :
N ̀ -yii ja ̀ ŋ inɛ u ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔrii , ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ̀ n yɛɛ ̀ nnɛ i ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu Sata ̀ n wu rila ̀ mi ̀ wu ri , ki ̀ ɓan kifog u ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ n ̀ si ̀ i ̀ rɛn ɓi ɗii ɗyɛ ̀ m , u ̀ roo ̀ zɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ntyweeyi wu u ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ wɔ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ , nsoo ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ɓɛ wola ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ wɛ ̀ m a ̀ n ̀ tyweeyi a ̀ nɛ lɛ Antipas a lɔ ̀ ŋkin ja ̀ ŋ inɛ Sata ̀ n a kɔ ̀ kɔrii .
Nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓidɛŋ ɓi ɓi ɓeɓi mɛ ̀ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ ; u ̀ ri ̀ foo ri ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔnɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ dɔgtɛ ̀ n i ̀ Balam ; Balam a ̀ a nɗe ̀ sa ̀ g Balag lɛ a ki com ki lɛ ɓɔn ɓɛ Isirayɛl ɓɛɛ kɛɓtɛn fi ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ ɓɛ ɗii ɓyɛn ɓi nya ̀ m yi ɓɛ funɛɛ ɓi ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi ɓinu ̀ n , ɓɛ ki ɗiŋi ɓi ri ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ɗi tisɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g .
Fɔɔnnɛ u ̀ ri ̀ girig foo ri ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ sii ̀ rɛɛ ɓi dɔgtɛ ̀ n i ̀ Nikolayit .
Lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛn min nɗem , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ fɔlɔɔ di nkpaŋkpaŋ wɔ a nyoo lɛ fyɛ ̀ ɗ , n ̀ ki ɗu ̀ u ̀ zi ɓumɓɛ ̀ n wɛ ̀ y ri ga ̀ fa ̀ g i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓi ŋwɔm .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ree ̀ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ woo ̀ gh com ki N ̀ ghay a kakali ɓiseŋi ɓi Kiris . Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ yagsaagh n ̀ fa nyi mana ̀ mɛ mɛ ri mɛ ̀ nyamɛn , ri ̀ gɔ ̀ g i ̀ mpuɓ ; gɔ ̀ g i ̀ nɛn i ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɗii ɗi nyɔn mii ̀ ɗi ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ɗi ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ yii ɓi , i ki cee ɓi lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓɛ faa gɔ ̀ g i ̀ nɛn .
Ka ̀ na ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom anɛ ɓi Ki ̀ seŋi ki a ̀ Tyatiir lɛ : Fɛlɛ nnɛ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ mis mɛ ri yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗo ̀ o ̀ wu ɗuu , mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ kuu ɗi swiɗ ɗiɗɛŋ , a kala ̀ g :
N ̀ -yii mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ mɔɔ , ri ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ɗi ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗyɔɔ , ri ̀ ca ̀ g kɔɔ ki kisay , ri ̀ ki ̀ si ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ kɔɔ , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ mɔɔ mɛ siito ̀ n mɛ mɛ teghɛɛ mɛ cee mɛ n ̀ tonto .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog ki ̀ ɓan ki ki ɓeɓi mɛ ̀ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ ki ri lɛ , u ̀ ti u ̀ ca ̀ ɗki ̀ giɓ anɛ lɛ Zyezaɓɛl a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ kala ̀ g lɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan lɛ a reresi , a ̀ ki syo ̀ ŋsyoŋ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛm lɛ ɓɛɛ ɗiŋi ɓi ti ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g ti ki ̀ kiyɛn , ɓɛ ki ɗiɗi ɓyɛn ɓi nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ funɛɛ ɓi ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi ɓinu ̀ n .
N ̀ fagha ̀ nyi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki lɛ a lɔɔghrɛn n ̀ ɗem , ki ̀ ɓan kifog a ̀ kɔ ̀ ni ɓi lɛ di a ̀ a lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛɛ nɗem lɛ a caɗ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi tifin ɓi a ki ̀ ki ̀ .
Ghɛna , n ̀ -yu ̀ u nyi ki ̀ nɔ ̀ ŋzii ɓi ɓyom ɓilɔ ̀ ŋ lɛ a wog ri ̀ kɛŋ lɛɛ ̀ gwey kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓ , lɛ ri ̀ nyi ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g fi ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g ri ̀ ɓɔ ; i ɓɛ lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛɛ nya mɛ ̀ rem ɓɛ caɗ mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ maa mɛn ̀ , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ki lɔɔ ̀ sɛ ̀ n .
N ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ cuusii ɓɔn ɓii , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓi ̀ seŋi ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ri ɓii ̀ yii ̀ lɛ mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ri roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ sɔ ̀ gi ̀ mɛ ̀ yiti ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ri ɓum ɓi mɛ ̀ rem ɓiɗu ̀ m , fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ le ̀ ɓi mum bimiɗ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ mii mɛ ri .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin , ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛmbog ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ a Tyatiir ɓɛ ɓi ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ ɓi dɔgtɛ ̀ n i ̀ nɛ ̀ n , kɛ ̀ ɓi ki tim lɛ ɓi yi com ki ɓɛ ti ɓɛ regi ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Sata ̀ n ɓi rim , mɛ ̀ n ̀ foŋdii ɓi mini n ̀ tɛ ̀ g wudɛŋ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , com ki ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ kɔ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓanina ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ yagsaagh a ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋ mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ mɛ mɛ ti mɛ kɔngi ̀ mɛ ̀ a ̀ kpaŋ a ri ̀ sugtɛ ̀ n innɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ faa ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu a lami ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓyɔ ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛkɛɛ ̀ si ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ kpas wu bɔŋ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ weeyi be ̀ e ̀ yi ɓɛ yeŋi ri ̀ fyo ̀ o ̀ , lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ n ̀ teka ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ win ̀ ɗi ̀ Seŋi wɛ ̀ m ,
fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi ɓii ̀ faa ̀ fyɛy fi fi ti fi lomgi ̀ sariwa .
Mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ree ̀ , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ woo ̀ gh com ki N ̀ ghay a kakali Ɓiseŋi ̀ .
Ka ̀ na ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom anɛ ɓi Ki ̀ seŋi ki a Saridɛ lɛ , fɛlɛ nnɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ghay mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll mɛ kitaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ tyɔɛy ti kitaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ a kpaaghi ̀ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yii mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ mɔɔ , u keŋkem lɛ u ̀ ri ̀ cencem kɔm ̀ lɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ loŋ .
Kɔ ̀ ri ɗyomzɛ ̀ n u ̀ ki si ̀ i ̀ rag righerɛ ̀ n ɗi ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ u ̀ kaka ri ̀ yɔ ̀ , ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ja ̀ ŋbog ɗi ̀ ri ̀ wu , ɓisuulɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ nghɛɛ lɛ mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ mɔɔ mɛ ɓiisɛɛ ɓi kirɔɔtɛɛ ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Yiti min ɓiɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi u ̀ teka ̀ ri ̀ ɓi u ̀ woka ̀ , ɓe ̀ ŋa ɓyɔ u ̀ ki lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛn nɗem ; i u ̀ kɔ ̀ rii ɓi cem , di n ̀ ɗi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u ki si ̀ ri kɔ ̀ ɔ ki yi ŋwos anɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , u ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ a Saridɛ ɓɛ ɓɛ nsiŋɗɛɛ ɓi tifin ɓi ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ɓyaa ; ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛɛ nɗaŋ ɗi mɛ ̀ , ɓisuulɛ ɓɛ ri ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ɗyɛ ̀ m .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ yagsaagh yɛɛ ri ɓii ̀ waatɛɛ ɓila ̀ a ̀ ɓi puɓ ; ma ̀ a ti ̀ i ̀ si ɓi ɗii ɗii ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ cɛɓ . N ̀ ɗi ̀ lɔŋ ɓii ̀ gherɛɛ lɛ a ̀ ri ̀ mum wɛm ̀ ɓi mis mɛ Seŋi wɛ ̀ m ri ̀ mɛ ɓum ɓɛ titom .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ree ̀ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ woo ̀ gh com ki N ̀ ghay a kakali Ɓiseŋi ̀ .
Ka ̀ na ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom anɛ ɓi Ki ̀ seŋi ki a Filadɛlfii lɛ : Roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ nyi n ̀ tɛnɛn , nyi lɛ saaɗ , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki ɓanɓani fi ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓa ̀ fi Davit , nyi yɛɛ ri lɛ , i a ̀ ŋwa ̀ ri , ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ si ̀ m , i a ̀ ki si ̀ mi , ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ kɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwa ̀ ɗ , a kpaaghi lɛ :
N ̀ -yii mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ mɔɔ . Ghɛna , mɛ ̀ yɛɛ foŋi i ̀ suunaa wu wu ri ki ̀ kpaŋ asu wɔɔ , wɛɛ ̀ wu ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ si ̀ m ɓisuulɛ u ̀ ɓiisɛɛ ɓi ki ɓaa ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , kɔm ̀ lɛ u ̀ ɓe ̀ ga ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yɛ ̀ m kɔ ̀ ɔ ki roo ̀ zɛn mɛ .
Ghɛna mɓii ̀ faa ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓi nɗaŋ wu Sata ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ pwa ̀ a ̀ pwa ̀ a ̀ , ɓɛ ree ̀ ghre ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓɛ ri Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓa Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , lɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ pwa ̀ a ̀ pwa ̀ a ̀ . Ghɛna , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ ɓɛɛ yu wɔ ̀ ki ̀ kuŋii a mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ , ɓɛ ki yi lɛ n ̀ keesi ̀ gha ̀ wɔ ̀ .
Lɛ u ̀ ɓe ̀ ga ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yɛ ̀ m ɗi ̀ ki ̀ si ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ mɛ ̀ girig n ̀ ɗi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ mɛ ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn mɛ mɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ yu ̀ u ɓi ziinɛ bimiɗ lɛ mɛɛ fee ̀ ghrɛn ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓi ziinɛ .
Mɛ ̀ yɛɛ tii ̀ lɔɔ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , si ̀ i ̀ ri ki ̀ ɓani ̀ com ki u ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ kɔ , di ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ kɛ ̀ ɛ teɗ ta ̀ m wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ a ri ̀ kem .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ yagsaagh n ̀ ki ̀ nyi lɛ a ɓa ri ̀ kwi ̀ y ɗi ɓi naa i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll wɛ ̀ m , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ a kpaŋdii gɛ ti ̀ ɓi ɓi naa i ̀ nɛ ̀ n . N ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ ka ̀ ni ɗii ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll wɛ ̀ m ɓi nyi , ɗii ɗi ba ̀ n i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll wɛ ̀ m , ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ ri myɔɔnyɔn a ̀ Yorisalɛm a ̀ nɛ a sɛnsɛn yi aɗyoo , di a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ yi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll wɛ ̀ m ja ̀ ŋbog , n ̀ ki ka ̀ n irig ɗii ɗyɛ ̀ m ɗi nyɔn ɓi nyi .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ree ̀ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ woo ̀ gh com ki N ̀ ghay a kakali Ɓiseŋi ̀ .
Ka ̀ na ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom anɛ ɓi Ki ̀ seŋi ki a Lawodise lɛ : ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɗii lɛ A ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ a ̀ n ̀ tyweeyi , roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ a kpaaghi lɛ :
N ̀ -yii mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ mɔɔ , u ̀ ri ̀ lɛ , kɔ ̀ ɔ ke ̀ ŋmɛn , kɔ ̀ ɔ ki tɔ ̀ n . I wa ̀ a ka ri ̀ ɓa ̀ lɛ u ̀ ke ̀ ŋmɛ ̀ n , nsoo ̀ lɛ u ̀ tɔ ̀ n .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ ri ̀ lɛ yaɓi ̀ yaɓi ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ke ̀ ŋmɛn , kɔ ̀ ɔ ki tɔ ̀ n , n ̀ ɗi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ loghii a ŋwɔm .
Ɓisuulɛ u kpaakpaa lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ guŋgum , m ̀ mɛ kum , com ki kaarɛɛ ti ̀ ɓi mɛ , kɔ ̀ ɔ ki yi lɛ u ̀ ri ̀ nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g i ̀ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ , wɔ ̀ sogha ̀ sogha , wɔ ̀ ɗyaŋɗya ̀ ŋ , wɔ ̀ ki ̀ to ̀ n zɛy ;
nni n ̀ ɗeɓi wɔ ̀ lɛ u lag gol i ̀ nɛ ɗuu ɗi ghaŋzii a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ , di fɔɔnnɛ u ɓa ri ̀ i ̀ kum , u ̀ la ̀ g girig ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ɓi puɓ lɛ u waa ̀ tɛn ɓyɔ , di n ̀ too ̀ ri ̀ ɗ wɔɔ wulɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ to ̀ n zɛy wɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ghɛnɛn ; u ̀ ki la ̀ g boo ̀ boo i ̀ nɛ lɛ u foŋɗɛn ɓi mis di fɔɔnnɛ u ghɛnɛn .
Lɛ n ̀ ti n ̀ fwa ̀ a ̀ da ̀ g , n ̀ ki ɓoki ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ n ̀ keesii , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ falɛn ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , u ̀ ki lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛn nɗem .
Ghɛna , n ̀ ɗɛrɛlii asuunaa , m ̀ ɓoɓo ̀ g ki ̀ si ̀ m , nni i mum a ̀ woogh jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yɛ ̀ m , a ̀ nɛm mɛ ̀ i ̀ suunaa , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ ɗiŋii a lɔ ̀ ŋkii ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ri ̀ nyi ti ̀ ɗi n ̀ ɗaŋ .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ yagsaagh n ̀ ki ̀ lɛ a kɔri n ̀ ɗaŋ ri mɛ ̀ ɓi-kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wɛm ̀ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yagsa ̀ ka ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ ri Seŋi wɛ ̀ m ɓi-kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wii wu rila ̀ mi ̀ .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ree ̀ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ woo ̀ gh com ki N ̀ ghay a kakali Ɓiseŋi ̀ .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn nnɛ m ̀ pɛ ̀ ɓsɛ ̀ nga ̀ , n ̀ ghɛn i ̀ suunaa ki ̀ kpaŋ ɓi ɗyoo ɓi ɗu ̀ m , jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ n ̀ tonto i ̀ nɛ n ̀ woka ̀ di i ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɗyam ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi ɓɛɛ ̀ rɔŋɗɔ ̀ ŋ i ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ lɛ : Ɓɔghay fɛ di nɗesi wɔ ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ri ɓii ̀ ki ̀ lɛɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ asu .
Fɔɔnnɛ N ̀ ghay a ̀ gha ̀ ska ̀ ki ̀ sɛni ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ , n ̀ ghɛn i ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ wɔɔ ɓi ɗyoo , mum mii ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔriyɛn .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ a ̀ nɛn ɓi-kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi mis yɛ ̀ ɛ gɔ ̀ g yi lo ̀ nlomɛn yi lɛ ri ̀ Zyaspɛ ̀ ri ̀ Sa ̀ ri ̀ dwana ̀ ; fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ sye ̀ ɗ wu wu lonlo ̀ mga ̀ ɓi mis yɛ ̀ ɛ gɔ ̀ g i ̀ nɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ regi lɛ e ̀ me ̀ roo ̀ dɛ ̀ wu ceŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ i ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ wunce ̀ m .
Mɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ mɛ rila ̀ mi ̀ mɛdɛŋ ri ̀ tin ɗi ̀ mɛnin mɛ ceŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ i ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ wu n ̀ tonto ; ɓi ̀ tu ̀ g ɓi ɓum ri ̀ tin ɗi ̀ ɓinin ɓi ɓagha ̀ ɓi ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔriyɛn ɓi mɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ mɛn , ɓi waatɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ɓi puɓ , ɓyɔ ti ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ta ̀ m ɓɛ gol ɓi mɛ ̀ to .
Ɓi-kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ win ̀ , ŋwa ̀ aŋwa ̀ ɗ a ̀ ŋwa ̀ ŋwa ̀ ɗka ̀ , gom , ri ̀ baa ̀ ba ̀ n ɓi fafa ̀ ŋi ̀ gha ̀ y mii ̀ . Ɓɛ ̀ lamɓa ̀ taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ roo ̀ ro ̀ o ̀ lɛ pa ̀ ŋ pa ̀ ŋ asu wu ikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ lamɓa ̀ ɓɛn ̀ ɓɛ ri mɛ ̀ ghay mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll mɛ kitaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ .
Ti ̀ ti ̀ fɛlɛ asu wu ikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ , ja ̀ ŋ i ghay lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ŋwii ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ŋwii , i ̀ lo ̀ nlo ̀ m yɛ ̀ ɛ maa ki ̀ pɛsa ̀ a ̀ ŋwii . Ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ i ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ ri ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ wɔŋi ̀ , nya ̀ m yi ɓagha ̀ yinin , yɔ yi ̀ ronɛn ri mis ja ̀ ŋ bimiɗ lɛ , ri ̀ asu ri ̀ ajɛ ̀ m .
Nya ̀ m i ̀ n ̀ tonto i ̀ pisɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ monɗo , i ̀ ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ rɛn i ̀ pisɛ ̀ n man a ̀ sani ̀ nya , i ̀ ki ̀ raa i ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ su yɛ ̀ ɛ wu mum , nya ̀ m i ̀ ki ̀ ni ̀ n i ̀ ɓa yɛ ̀ ɛ be ̀ e ̀ i fi ̀ i ̀ li ̀ i ̀ nɛ yɛɛ ̀ lɛŋlɛ ̀ ŋ .
Nya ̀ m yi kini ̀ n yin ̀ yi ɓala ̀ ka ̀ lɛ , nya ̀ m bog mɛ ̀ keɓ taa ̀ fog , yɔ ̀ mis nyoo bimiɗ lɛ ri ̀ ɓi ɗu ̀ m , ri ̀ ɓi ɓya ̀ s . Fɔɔnnɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ i ̀ ru yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwos , ɓɛ fɔli ɓi rikaka ̀ li ̀ lɛ : Kan Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wuce ̀ m a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tɛnɛn , a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tɛnɛn , a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tɛnɛn , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛn yɛɛ , ɓagha ̀ nnyɛɛ ri nnyɛɛ ̀ ki yu ̀ yuiy .
Nni ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki nya ̀ m yin ̀ yi fafa ̀ gha ̀ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔrii ɓi-kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ cem fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ ri ̀ kem , ri ̀ bɔgsɛ ̀ n ,
ɓi ̀ tu ̀ g ɓi ɓum ɓi ritin ɗi ̀ ɓinin ɓi nti ɓi kuŋɗa ̀ g roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔrii ɓi-kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ asu , ɓi ɓɔɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ gsi ̀ roa ̀ nɛ a ghɛghɛɓ fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ɓi nagi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ta ̀ m ɓaa asu wu ikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ di ɓyɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa lɛ :
Wɔ ̀ Kan wi ̀ s , Bɛ ̀ ll wi ̀ s , u ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ , ɗi ̀ ri ̀ kem , ri ̀ bɔgsɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , ɓisuulɛ wɔ ̀ yɛɛ kigha ̀ ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , yɛ ̀ ɛ ki kɔnga ̀ wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓyom ɓi ̀ n ɓyɛɛ ɓa , nnɛ ɓi kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ .
Nni n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ɓi wee ̀ lem a ̀ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓi-kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ , kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ ri ̀ ɓi ɗu ̀ m ri ̀ ɓi ɓya ̀ s , ɓɛ ̀ si ̀ tam ̀ mii ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɓaatiyɛn taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ .
Nni n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ki ̀ te ̀ ete ̀ ɗ ki ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom di kɛɛ ̀ la ̀ alamɓɛ ̀ n jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Ghɛn yɛɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ a ̀ ŋwa ̀ ɗ kaa ̀ ta ̀ , a ̀ ɓɛki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ si ̀ tam ̀ ɓɛ mii ̀ ?
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog nsoo ̀ ɓi ɗyoo ɓi ɗu ̀ m , nsoo ̀ ɓi ziinɛ , nsoo ̀ ɓi ziinɛ a zi , ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ri i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ a ̀ ŋwa ̀ ɗ kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ nɛn nsoo ̀ lɛ a ̀ seese ̀ e ̀ nyi .
