N ̀ tɔɓ wu n ̀ tonto wu mɛ ghaa ̀ gh , nni wɔ ̀ lɛ mɛ ̀ tɔɓ mɛdɛŋ mɛɓɛɛ ̀ mɛ ri ti ̀ i ̀ ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ win ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a ki ̀ taa ̀ fog a ̀ rɔga ̀ ɗyam , n ̀ wog di jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ yi ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ tɔŋ mɛ kini ̀ n mɛ ɓi com ki gol ri ̀ gol ki ɓɛ ntɔ ̀ ngi ̀ ɓyom mii ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , com ki ̀ n kɛɛ rɛrɛ ̀ li ̀ gha ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll asu .
Jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ kpaa ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a ki ̀ taa ̀ fog anɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɗyam lɛ : Fu ̀ mi ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓɛ kini ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ ka ̀ gakɛn bɛn ɓi coo riɓa ̀ y a ̀ nɛ lɛ Efirat .
Nni ɓɛ fumi ̀ gha ̀ ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓɛ kini ̀ n ɓɛn ̀ , ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ di ɓɛ mɛ ɓu ̀ ŋɛn ɓisuu ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ , ri ̀ go ̀ n inɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ ŋwii a ̀ nɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ be ̀ g i ̀ nɛn , lɛ ɓɛɛ cuu ̀ si ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ki ̀ raa i ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓi ziinɛ .
Ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɗu ̀ u ̀ wɛ ̀ y inɛ ɓi nɗaŋ wu ɓɛsuja ̀ a ̀ wu wu ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ zo ̀ m yi kimbɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ mi ̀ li ̀ yɔŋ ɓɛ ̀ hɔnɗɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ , n ̀ woka ̀ di ɓɛ faa ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛn ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi n ̀ seese ̀ e ̀ gha ̀ ɓin ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ dɛ ̀ ndɛm , n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ zo ̀ m yi kimbɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ mii ̀ aɗyoo ; ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pa ̀ mɓɛn dwey ri ̀ bɔŋ yi yi ɓagha ̀ lɛ yɔ yi ̀ ɓa ̀ ŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɗuu , yɔ bu ̀ rum ɓi mis yɛ ̀ ɛ gɔ ̀ g i ̀ nɛ lɛ ya ̀ sɛŋtɛ ̀ , yɔ ti ̀ ɓi mis yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ du ̀ si . Mɛ ̀ to mɛ zo ̀ m yi kimbɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ yin ̀ mɛ ɓagha ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ to mɛ ɓimonɗo , fɔɔnnɛ ɗuu ri ̀ fi ̀ sili ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ du ̀ si ɓi fafa ̀ ŋi ̀ gha ̀ y yɔ ɓi myɔm .
Ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓyom ɓi kiraa ɓi lɛ ri ̀ ɗuu ri ̀ fi ̀ sili ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ du ̀ si ɓi ɓi kpaŋkpa ̀ ŋga ̀ y ɓi myɔm mɛ zo ̀ m , ɓi cuusi ̀ gha ̀ ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ki ̀ raa i ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓumɓɛ ɓi ziinɛ .
Ɓisuulɛ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu zo ̀ m yin ̀ wu ri lɛ ri ̀ ɓi myɔm ri ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ ghey ; mɛ ̀ ghey mɛ yɔ mɛ ri yɛ ̀ ɛ nyoo , mɔ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ to , mɛ ̀ to mɛ ̀ n mɛɛ ̀ mɛ mɛ ̀ ghey mɛ ̀ n mɛ ri lɛ mɛ ki ki ̀ ɓe mii ̀ .
Ɓum ɓɛmɓog ɓɛ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓyom ɓi ̀ n ɓi cuusi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi , ɓɛ ɓenga ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛɛ mɛrem lɛ ɓɛɛ caɗ ɓi ̀ nu ̀ n ɓi ɓɔmiɗ ɓɔ yɛɛ syaagh ri ̀ ɓya ̀ g ɓyaa ; fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ lɔŋ bee ̀ bɛ ̀ y ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ gsi ̀ ɗi ɓiɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ nu ̀ n ɓi ɓi ri ɓi ̀ syaghɛn ri gol nsoo ̀ lɛ ri ̀ swiɗ a ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni , nsoo ̀ lɛ ri ̀ bɔŋ idɛŋ , nsoo ̀ lɛ ri ̀ gɔ ̀ g , nsoo ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ki ̀ te ; ɓi ̀ nu ̀ n ɓin ̀ ɓyɛɛ yin lɛ ɓi ghɛnɛ ̀ n , ɓyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ wooghrɛn , ɓyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ghi .
Ɓɛ ɓenga ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛɛ mɛrem lɛ ɓɛɛ caɗ ri ̀ wowe ̀ y ɗi ɓum , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi kifuu ri ̀ ti ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g , ri ̀ wii .
Nni n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ki ̀ te ̀ ete ̀ ɗ ki ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom kidɛŋ di kɛɛ ̀ sɛnsɛn yi aɗyoo , ki ̀ waatɛn kikwi ̀ ɗ , n ̀ sye ̀ ɗ wu ɓagha ̀ nyi wu gheniyɛn ɓi nto , i ̀ su wu lonlo ̀ m yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwos , mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ mii mɛ ɓa yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ kwi ̀ y mɛ ɗu ̀ u ̀ .
A ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ maa kaa ̀ ta ̀ n ̀ ŋwa ̀ rɛn ɓi ca ̀ g ; a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , a ̀ rɛsi ̀ i ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ wii wu wee ̀ lem ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n , wu kimɛŋ ɓi zi i ̀ zɛy ,
nni a ̀ nya ̀ mga ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ monɗo kɛɛ ̀ nya ̀ mgi ̀ , lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ nya ̀ mga ̀ fɔlɔɔ , baa ̀ ba ̀ n yi kitaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi ɓog , gom i ̀ ghaa ̀ gh .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ baa ̀ ba ̀ n yi kitaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi ɓoka ̀ fɔlɔɔ , m ̀ mɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ nkan ̀ , nni n ̀ woka ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ dɛŋ di i ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Nyama ki ̀ ɓan ki baa ̀ ba ̀ n yi kitaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi kpaa ki ̀ n , kɔ ̀ ɔ ka ̀ n kɔ .
Nni ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ ɗɛrɛliyɛn lɛ i ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ wu ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y , wumbog a cɛɗ , a ̀ pɛ ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ wee ̀ lem wi ̀ i ̀ aɗyoo ;
fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ka ̀ nɛ ̀ nga ̀ bɛ ̀ ɗ ɓi ɗii ɗi roa ̀ nɛ a ghɛghɛɓ fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ɗyoo ri ̀ ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓi ri mii ̀ , a ̀ ki ̀ lɛ ri ̀ zi ri ̀ ɓyom ɓi ɓi ri mii ̀ , a ̀ ki ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓyom ɓi ɓi ri mii ̀ ; a ̀ ka ̀ nɛ ̀ nga ̀ bɛ ̀ ɗ lɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki lɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ ɓuŋɛn kaa ɓa ti ɓi ,
ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a ki ̀ taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ wooghrɛɛ , di a ̀ ti lɛ a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ rɔŋ ɗi ɗyam , innɛ fe ̀ g a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ɓalag nyamɛn a ̀ ɓii ̀ roni ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ wogsi ̀ gha ̀ Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ ɓi fe ̀ g a ̀ nɛn ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓii .
Nni jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ n ̀ woka ̀ di i ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ aɗyoo i ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ ti ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ fɛlɛ ̀ : Kɛ ̀ na , u teɗ maa kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ŋwa ̀ rɛn ɓi ca ̀ g ki ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom anɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ɗɛrɛliyɛn lɛ ri ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n ri ̀ a cɛɗ .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom anɛ ̀ n n ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ a fa mɛ ̀ maa kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ nce ̀ m ; nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ mɛ ̀ lɛ : Tera nyi , u min ̀ , a ̀ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ lo ̀ loli ɓi mɛ ̀ ɗyɔɔ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog a ̀ yɛ ̀ yɛ ̀ y wɔ ̀ ɓi ŋwɔm yɛ ̀ ɛ mɔ ̀ ɔ mɛ ilo ̀ o ̀ .
Nni n ̀ teka ̀ maa kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓi ca ̀ g ki ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom m ̀ mi ̀ n nyi ; a ̀ ɓagha ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓi ŋwɔm yɛ ̀ ɛ mɔ ̀ ɔ mɛ ilo ̀ o ̀ , nni yɛ ̀ ɛ m ̀ mi ̀ nga ̀ nyi , mɛ ̀ ɗyɔɔ mɛ ̀ m mɛ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ lo ̀ lo ̀ e ̀ y .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ mɛ ̀ lɛ : Ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ u kpaŋzi ti ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ɓi seesee mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Nni ɓɛ fagha ̀ min mɛ ki ̀ syo ̀ ŋ ki ki ɓagha ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ geŋ , ɓɛ kpaa mɛ ̀ lɛ : Kɛ ̀ na u feg lɛ ri ̀ naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ com ki ɓɛ ti ɓɛ tɔngi ̀ ɓi ̀ tuwe mii ̀ , u ̀ ɓa ̀ y ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɔɔɓɔgsi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll wɔɔ ɓi naa i ̀ nɛ ̀ n .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a nlɛmɓog wu ɓi dan , ca ̀ ra wɔ , kɔ ̀ ɔ fe ̀ g ɓisuulɛ ɓɛ fagha ̀ wɔ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi zɛy ; ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓin ̀ ɓyɛɛ ri ɓɛɛ ̀ dag ba ̀ n i ̀ n ̀ tɛnɛn ɓɛ ̀ ŋwii mɛ ̀ tin mɛɓɛɛ ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ faa gɛ ɓɛ ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛm ɓɛ kiɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ ɓɛɛ kpaŋzi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll mɛ ̀ ru tɔɔsi ̀ m ɓɛ ̀ hɔnɗɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ̀ tin mɛraa .
Ɓɛ ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛ kiɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛn ̀ ɓɔ yɛɛ ri mɛ ̀ ɗye ̀ m mɛ oli ̀ vi ̀ yee mɛ kiɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ rɛsi ̀ ɓi lamɓa ̀ ɓi kiɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓi ɓi rɛrɛlii ɓi mis mɛ Kan a ̀ ziinɛ .
Nni i mum a ̀ kɔ ̀ ni lɛ a ki ɓɔ ki ̀ ɓe , ɗuu ɗi kpaŋ yi ̀ ɓɔ ɓi myɔm , ɗi ɗigsi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ be ̀ na ̀ bena ɓaa . Ri ̀ kuu ɗi riwu ̀ ɗi ̀ n ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ kɔ ̀ ni lɛ a ki ɓɔ ki ̀ ɓe a ri ̀ ɓii ̀ wii ̀ .
Ɓɛ ri ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ ɓɛɛ sim ɗyoo lɛ bwey yɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ nɔ , ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m mɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaŋzi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ; ɓɛ ki ɓa ri i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ ɓɛɛ ghaa ̀ si mɛ ̀ nig bwaɓ , ɓɛ ki ɓa ri i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ ɓɛɛ rom yi ̀ ri ̀ kuu ɗi ntɔɓ ɗi ̀ ce ̀ m ɗi ɓɛ kɔni ɓi ziinɛ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ɓaa gɛ di ɓaa le ̀ gsi ki re ̀ sii ɓiɓan ɓi ɓɛ yu ̀ u gɛ ki ̀ re ̀ sii , fɔɔnnɛ nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛ i ̀ kpaŋii ̀ gɛ ɓi ri ̀ ɓee ɗi rim i ̀ faa gɛ ɓɔ ri ̀ baŋi ̀ , i ̀ cee ɓɔ ɓi-te ̀ ɗ , i ̀ ki cuusi ɓɔ .
Nni ɓi ̀ loŋ ɓyaa ɓi cɛnɛɛ gɛ ɓi nlɛmɓog wu coo ba ̀ n i ̀ gwey inɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ regi ɓi mɛ ̀ ghe ̀ y lɛ Sɔdɔm nsoo ̀ lɛ Egiɓtɛn ɓi ja ̀ ŋ yɔ ̀ miɗ inɛ ɓɛ kpanga ̀ Kan wa ̀ a ̀ ɓi kɔrɔs .
Ɓumɓɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ pwi ̀ ɗ mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ri seesee gɛ ɓi ̀ loŋ ɓyaa a ̀ kpaŋ mɛ ̀ ru mɛraa ri ̀ ki ̀ den , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ gherɛn lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓom ̀ ɓyɔ ɓi zɔ ̀ ŋ .
Ɓumɓɛ ɓi ziinɛ ɓɛ ri nya ̀ a ̀ rɛɛ gɛ ri ̀ ri ̀ wu ɗyaa , ɓɛ wog ki ̀ rɔɔ ; ɓɛ roo ̀ ro ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɓyom ɓisuulɛ ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ kiɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛn ̀ ɓɛ tɔɓka ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓi ziinɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru mɛ kiraa ri ̀ ki ̀ den mɛ ̀ n , n ̀ ghay a ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ nghay a ̀ cɛɓ a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ y yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ ɓi ɓɔ , ɓɛ ki pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyoo , ɓɛ rɛli ̀ mɛ ̀ rɛy , fɔɔnnɛ coo iris wu ɓanga ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ seese ̀ e ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ .
Nni ɓɛ woka ̀ di coo jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ i aɗyoo , i ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓɔɔghnay fɛ . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ɓɔka ̀ aɗyoo ɓi ɓi ̀ kwi ̀ ɗ ɓi mis mɛ ɓɛ ̀ be ̀ na ̀ bena ɓaa .
Ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kɔm ̀ kin ̀ , zi i nyɛ ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ ; ki ̀ la ̀ na ̀ ki ba ̀ n ki ̀ fog ki ɓi ɓi ̀ la ̀ na ̀ ɓi kintɛ ̀ ɗ ɓi ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛn ki waa ̀ rɛ ̀ n , ɓum ɓɛ ̀ tɔɔsi ̀ m taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ cuu , ɓi ri ̀ nyɛ ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ n ɗi zi i nyɛ ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɗin ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛmbog ɓɛ risi ̀ , ɓɛ fa Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ aɗyoo ri ̀ kem .
N ̀ tɔɓ wu kiɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ wu mɛ ghaa ̀ gh , nni n ̀ tɔɓ wu kiraa wɔ yɛɛ nɔ ̀ ɔnɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ i ̀ lɔŋ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ .
Nni ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a ki ̀ taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ a rɔga ̀ ɗyam ; fɔɔnnɛ ɓyoo jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓi ɓagha ̀ y ɓi ɗyoo ɓi ɗu ̀ m , ɓi kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ lɛ : Ki ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ki zi ki cee ɓi ɓya ̀ g ɓi Kan wi ̀ s , ri ̀ Me ̀ sii wi ̀ i ̀ . A ̀ ɓii ̀ la ̀ mii fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ ritin ɗi ̀ ɓɛnin ɓɛ ɓɛ kɔkɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll asu ɓi mɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ maa mɛ rila ̀ mi ̀ , ɓɛ kpila ̀ ka ̀ , ɓɛ ɓaki ̀ mɛ ̀ su maa ɓi zi , ɓɛ ɓɔgsi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Di ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa lɛ : Ti ̀ faa wɔ ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n Kan Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wuce ̀ m , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki ɓagha ̀ , wɔ ̀ ɔ nɗe ̀ sii coo ite ̀ ɗ wɔɔ , u ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ kɔɔ .
Ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi woka ̀ bim , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki lɛ bim yɔɔ ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ghɛnɛn ki yuu ̀ , ri ̀ ki lɛ u yɔm ̀ ɓi ̀ loŋ ; ri ̀ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki lɛ u leɓ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɔɔ ɓɛ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ nigi ̀ ɗii ɗyɔɔ , lɛ ri ̀ ɓɔɓti ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ; ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki lɛ u cuu ̀ si ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ yooyogsi ̀ ziinɛ ki kpaŋi .
Nni naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ɗyoo ɓi ɗu ̀ m i ̀ ŋwa ̀ rɛ ̀ nga ̀ , fi ̀ kɔrɔŋ fii fi rira ̀ rɛ ̀ n fi see ̀ se ̀ e ̀ rɛ ̀ n yi ̀ ɓi naa yi ̀ i ̀ ɓi ɗu ̀ m . Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwa ̀ aŋwa ̀ ɗ a ̀ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ŋwa ̀ ŋwa ̀ ɗ , ɓyoo gom ɓi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓi ghagha ̀ a ̀ gh , baa ̀ ba ̀ n i ̀ ɓoɓo ̀ g , zi i nyɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ nyɛ ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ n , bol i ̀ gɔ ̀ g i ̀ su ̀ u ̀ su ̀ u ̀ rɛ ̀ n .
Coo kife ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki resɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ɗyoo ɓi ɗu ̀ m ; giɓ ŋ ̀ waatɛn ŋwos yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ la ̀ a ̀ , ŋwii a ̀ lo ̀ nlo ̀ m nyi a mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ -zi , ta ̀ m a ̀ ri ̀ kem a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ tyɔɛy ntɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ tiɓɛɛ ̀ nyi ɓi nto .
Giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɗyem , a ̀ ki kuukugsɛ ̀ n lɛ ɗyem ɗi kiki ̀ gha ̀ nyi a ̀ wowo ̀ g ri ̀ kɛŋ ɗi giɓ a woki ɓi ri ̀ yay .
Fɔɔnnɛ ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ kidɛŋ ki resɛ ̀ nga ̀ ti ̀ ɓi ɗyoo ɓi ɗu ̀ m ; coo kina ̀ a ̀ gɔ ̀ n kɛɛ ɓagha ̀ , ki ɓaŋɓa ̀ ŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɗuu , kɔ mɛ ̀ to taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , mɛ ̀ tɔŋ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ; nni ɓi mɛ ̀ to mɛ kitaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ ta ̀ m ɓɛ rikem ɓɛ ɓala ̀ ka ̀ mii ̀ .
N ̀ ghey wu kina ̀ a ̀ gɔ ̀ n kin ̀ wu wɔɔwɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ rɛ ̀ nga ̀ y ri ̀ ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ki ̀ raa i ̀ nɛ ɓi tyɔɛy tice ̀ m ti aɗyoo , wu suu ̀ su ̀ u ̀ ri ̀ tyɔ ɓi zi . Ki ̀ na ̀ a ̀ gɔ ̀ n ki rɛli ̀ gha ̀ giɓ anɛ a ̀ ɓoŋɓo ̀ ŋga ̀ ri ̀ yay a ̀ nɛ ̀ n asu lɛ i a ̀ yali , kɛɛ sokɛn man .
Giɓ a yala ̀ man a ̀ baŋi ̀ , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛkɛɛ ̀ si ̀ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ri ̀ gban ̀ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ yɛn ɗi bɔŋ . Nni ɓɛ ki ɓɔka ̀ ri ̀ man wii ̀ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ ɓi kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wii wu rila ̀ mi ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ ghɛŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi-reɓ , wɔɔnnɛ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ pe ̀ gsɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi i ̀ ɓagha ̀ , lɛ a ̀ ri ̀ wɔɔ ɓii ̀ ɗiɗii a ̀ kpaŋ mɛ ̀ ru tɔɔsi ̀ m ɓɛ ̀ hɔnɗɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ̀ tin mɛraa .
Fɔɔnnɛ wɛ ̀ y wu ɗuurɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ɗyoo ɓi ɗu ̀ m ; Mikaɛl ri ̀ ɓum ɓii ɓɛ titom ɓɛ ɗu ̀ u ̀ gha ̀ ri ki ̀ na ̀ a ̀ gɔ ̀ n . Ki ̀ na ̀ a ̀ gɔ ̀ n girig , ki ɗuugha ̀ wɛ ̀ y win ̀ ri ̀ ɓum ɓii ɓɛ titom ,
ki ̀ ɓan kifog , a ̀ a ki ̀ na ̀ a ̀ gɔ ̀ n kɔ yɛɛ ceegha ̀ ɓi-te ̀ ɗ ; fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ɓati ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ri ja ̀ ŋ i n ̀ kɔ ̀ riyɛn aɗyoo .
Nni ɓɛ tyɔka ̀ y coo kina ̀ a ̀ gɔ ̀ n kin ̀ , fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ fi nyoo fi ̀ n , fi fi ri ɗii lɛ n ̀ ɗe ̀ m nsoo ̀ lɛ Sata ̀ n , nnyɛɛ ri n ̀ -ye ̀ gsi ̀ zi bimiɗ i ̀ nɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ ̀ ghɛghɛɓ mii ̀ , ɓɛ tyɔka ̀ y nyi ɓi zi , ɓɛ ki tyɔg yi girig ɓum ɓii ɓɛ titom n ̀ ɗaŋ ri nyi .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ woka ̀ di coo jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa yi ɓi ɗyoo lɛ : Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki go ̀ ri ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , ri ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ki Bɛ ̀ ll , kɛɛ ti lɛ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ ɗi Kiris wi ̀ i ̀ , ɓisuulɛ ɓɛ mɛ tyɔg roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ sɔma ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓis , lɛ nnyɛɛ nti a ̀ sɔma ̀ g ɓɔ yɛ ̀ ɛ i ̀ ru yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwos , ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ɓɛ mɛ yag nyi ɓi wɛ ̀ y lɛ bwaɓ yi Man a ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ri ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ nɗe ̀ resii saaɗ a ̀ nɛ mii ̀ ; ɓɛ nki keesii ɓi ɓyɛɓ ɓyaa a ̀ kpaŋ le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ risi ri ̀ wu .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɗyoo , ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓumɓɛ ɓi ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔrii aɗyoo , ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ nyaa ! Nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g ri ̀ ziinɛ , ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n , ɓisuulɛ Sata ̀ n a mɛ sɛn yi a lɔ ̀ ŋkin , n ̀ woghɛn coo bim lɛ a ̀ yii lɛ , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kii ki mɛ rɔ ̀ ɓ lɛsa ̀ g .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ na ̀ a ̀ gɔ ̀ n ki ghɛnga ̀ lɛ ɓɛ tyɔghii ̀ kɔ ɓi ziinɛ , nni ki ɓɛɓsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ giɓ anɛ a ̀ yala ̀ man baŋi ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ fagha ̀ giɓ anɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki mɛkeɓ ki coo be ̀ e ̀ i fi ̀ i ̀ li ̀ , lɛ a lɛŋ ɓi-reɓ , ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɛ ri nyi ɓii ̀ mɛnii be ̀ g yiraa ri ̀ ki ̀ den , fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ ri nyoo .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ nyoo i ̀ loogha ̀ y giɓ anɛ ̀ n mɛ ̀ nig ajɛ ̀ m yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y lɛ di ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ɓɛn ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog zi i ru ̀ nɛ ̀ nga ̀ giɓ , i ̀ ghasi ̀ ŋwɔm i ̀ mi ̀ n ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ nɛ ki ̀ na ̀ a ̀ gɔ ̀ n kin ̀ ki loogha ̀ y a ŋwɔm ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ki ̀ na ̀ a ̀ gɔ ̀ n ki woka ̀ bim ri giɓ anɛ ̀ n ki ki kɛ ̀ n ki kpaŋi ̀ do ̀ o ̀ yii wɛ ̀ y , ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ ɓegi ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ saaɗ a ̀ nɛ Yeesus a ̀ re ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ di nya ̀ m i ̀ dɛŋ yɛɛ ̀ kpaŋkpaŋ yi ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n ; i ̀ ɓagha ̀ mɛ ̀ tɔŋ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ to taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , mɛ ̀ tɔŋ mɛ yɔ ̀ mɛn ̀ mɛ ɓala ̀ ka ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ta ̀ m ɓɛ rikem , mii mɛ tifena ɓisuu Bɛ ̀ ll mɛ ɓala ̀ ka ̀ mɛ ̀ ka ̀ ngakɛn ɓi mɛ ̀ to mɛ nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛn .
Nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛ n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ i ̀ nɛn i ̀ pisɛ ̀ nga ̀ n ̀ gɔn , mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ mɛ yɔ ̀ mɛ ɓa yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ mɛ kpao ̀ , ŋwɔm wu yɔ ̀ wu ɓa yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwɔm wu kimonɗo . Ki ̀ na ̀ a ̀ gɔ ̀ n ki teka ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu ki ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ wɔ , ri ̀ i ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ , ri ̀ coo ite ̀ ɗ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ , ki fa nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛn .
Nni n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ kibog ki ɓi mɛ ̀ to mɛ nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛn ri ̀ coo beŋ i nfin , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓɛ wɔɔ ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ coo beŋ inɛ ̀ n . Zi bimiɗ i ̀ kuu ̀ ku ̀ u ̀ ghra ̀ g nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , i ̀ ki nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti yɔ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ gh mɛ ̀ ɗu ɓi mis mɛ kina ̀ a ̀ gɔ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɔgsi ̀ kɔ , ɓisuulɛ ki fagha ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ ri ̀ nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛn ; nni ɓɛ ɓaka ̀ girig nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛn mɛ ̀ ɗu asu di ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa lɛ : Ghɛn yɛɛ ri lɛ a ̀ ɓa yɛ ̀ ɛ yɔ ̀ ? Ghɛn yɛɛ ki ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ ɗu ̀ u ̀ ri ̀ yɔ ̀ ?
Nni ɓɛ fagha ̀ nya ̀ m i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ kpaa ̀ kpaa ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi mɛ ̀ ca ̀ ŋa ̀ , i ̀ fee ̀ fe ̀ ngi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll . Ɓɛ ki fa ti yɔ ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ lami ɓɛ ̀ ŋwii mɛ ̀ tin mɛɓɛɛ ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ŋwii ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ .
Nni i ̀ pini ̀ gha ̀ ŋwɔm lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ fengi Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ ɗii ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ ki ̀ nuugh ki Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓi ɗyoo ɓiɗu ̀ m .
Ɓɛ ki fa nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛn i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɗuu ̀ zi ɓɔ wɛ ̀ y , i ̀ yag ɓɔ . Ɓɛ fa yɔ ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu yɛ ̀ ɛ lami ɓumɓɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ pwi ̀ ɗ mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ri ̀ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓi ziinɛ , ɓɛ mii maa mɛ ka ɓagha ̀ ɓi mɛ ka ̀ nɛn ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ cɛɓ a ̀ Man a ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ wola ̀ , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n a ri ̀ ya ̀ ghɛ ̀ n ɗi zi , ɓɛ ɓaagh gɛ mɛ ̀ ɗu ɓi zi ɓɛ ɓɔgsi ̀ nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛn .
I ŋwaa ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ree ̀ a ̀ wog .
I mum a ̀ yalɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ gɛ ri ̀ kpa ̀ n , a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ , i ŋwaa ̀ woli mum ri ̀ gafa ̀ g , ɓɛ woli gɛ nyi ri ̀ ga ̀ fa ̀ g . Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ si ̀ i ̀ rɛɛ , ɓɛ ki ɓa ri n ̀ tyweeyi kɛɛ ̀ ki .
Nni n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ nya ̀ m i ̀ dɛŋ di yɛɛ ̀ kpaŋkpaŋ yi ɓi zi , Nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛn i ̀ ɓagha ̀ mɛ ̀ tɔŋ mɛɓɛɛ ̀ rɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ tɔŋ mɛ man a ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , i ̀ ki to ̀ tog yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ na ̀ a ̀ gɔ ̀ n .
I ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ say ri i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ wu nya ̀ m i ̀ n ̀ tonto , ɓi mis mɛ nya ̀ m i ̀ nce ̀ m i ̀ nɛn . I ̀ ki ka ̀ ŋkaŋ zi , ri ɓumɓɛ mii ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓɔgsi nya ̀ m i ̀ n ̀ tonto i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ coo beŋ i n ̀ fin i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ɓoogha ̀ i ̀ wɔ ̀ n .
I ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ koŋnyoo ɓɛ ɓiɓan , a ̀ kpaŋ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ kɔsag yi ̀ ɗuu ɓi ɗyoo , ɗyɛɛ sɛn ̀ yi ̀ ɓi ziinɛ , ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ seese ̀ e ̀ .
I ̀ ye ̀ gsi ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓi ziinɛ ri ̀ da ̀ m yi ɓɛ fagha ̀ yɔ ̀ ite ̀ ɗ wulɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ kiki ɓi mis mɛ nya ̀ m i ̀ n ̀ tonto di yɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa ɓumɓɛ ɓi ziinɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ ki ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ kpɛɛ ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ ga ̀ fa ̀ g i ̀ ki ghɛɓ .
Ɓɛ fagha ̀ nya ̀ m i ̀ mbog i ̀ nɛ ̀ n i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki lɛ ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki nya ̀ m i ̀ n ̀ tonto kɛɛ nyɛɛ ̀ nyɛ ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ n lɛ di kɛɛ too ̀ ghrɛn ki ki lɛ , ɓɛɛ cuusi ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓeni ki ̀ ɓɔgsii kife ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki nce ̀ m kin ̀ .
Nya ̀ m i ̀ ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ inɛ ̀ n i ̀ ka ̀ ŋka ̀ ŋga ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ɓɔɓti ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ guŋgum ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sogha ̀ sogha , ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin ɓɛkpa ̀ n ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ kpa ̀ n , lɛ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛɛ ɓalag ri ̀ ki ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ ɓi ca ̀ g ki wee ̀ lem , ri ̀ ɓisu ̀ ,
ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ mum kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa ri bee inɛ lɛ a lag com nsoo ̀ lɛ a kaɓ , di a ̀ yin ɗi ki ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ kin ̀ , kɛɛ ri ɗii ɗi nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , nsoo ̀ lɛ ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɗii ɗi nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛn .
Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki lɛ mum a womzɛn kɛɛ ̀ ki , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ wom ̀ zɛɛ , a kaa ̀ lɛ a ̀ tanɛ ̀ n ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , ɓisuulɛ ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ nɛn i ̀ ri ̀ ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɗii ɗi mum . Ba ̀ li ̀ yi ̀ i ̀ inɛ ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ hɔnɗɛ ̀ ɗ taa ̀ fog ri ̀ mɛ ̀ tin mɛraa ri ̀ taa ̀ fog .
Nni n ̀ seese ̀ e ̀ gha ̀ , n ̀ ghɛn Man a ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ n ̀ ɗɛrɛliyɛn ɓi do ̀ n i ̀ Siyon , n ̀ ɗaŋ ri ɓum ɓɛ ̀ tɔɔsi ̀ m mɛ ̀ tin taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ tɔɔsi ̀ m ɓɛnin ; ɓi mɛ ̀ su mɛ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɗii ɗii , ri ̀ ɗii ɗi Seŋi mɛ ɓagha ̀ mɛ ̀ ka ̀ nɛn .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ woka ̀ y jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo di yɛɛ ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wɔɔ yi yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ kus ɓi riɓa ̀ y , i ̀ pisɛ ̀ n ti ̀ coo gom i ̀ baa ̀ ba ̀ n ; gom i ̀ nɛ n ̀ woka ̀ i ̀ nɛ ̀ n i ̀ ɓagha ̀ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ fi ̀ loŋ fyɛɛ ̀ fi ɓum ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓoɓo ̀ g .
Ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kɛkɛ ̀ ghi ̀ gha ̀ fyem fi nyɔn di ɓɛ rɛrɛlii asu wu ikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ , ri ̀ nya ̀ m yi kini ̀ n , ri ̀ asu wu ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ ɓum . Ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi lɛ a ̀ yila ̀ g fyem fi ̀ n , i ki yin lɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ tɔɔsi ̀ m mɛ ̀ tin taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ tɔɔsi ̀ m ɓɛnin ɓɛ a ̀ kwe ̀ ɗka ̀ ɓi ziinɛ .
Ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛɛ tɔɓɓɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi tifin ri ̀ ɓɛyi ̀ ɓ ; ɓɛ ri ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yii ɓi ɓɛyi ̀ ɓ ; ɓɛɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔnɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ Man a ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ja ̀ ŋ bimiɗ i ̀ nɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ . Ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ko ̀ rɛn ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓum lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓa fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓi ̀ ɗu ̀ n ɓi n ̀ tonto ɓisuu Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ ɓisuu Man a ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ,
fɔɔnnɛ ŋwɔm wu roa ̀ dɛŋ wu kpaagha ̀ ɓi kiɓan ki ɓɛpwa ̀ a ̀ ; ɓɛ ri ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ bɛ ̀ lɛn .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom adɛŋ di a lɛŋlɛŋ ɓi ɗyoo ɓi ɗu ̀ m , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ a ̀ nɛ lɛ a ghagsi ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓi ziinɛ , ɓumɓɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ pwi ̀ ɗ mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
A ̀ la ̀ a ̀ la ̀ mɓɛ ̀ nga ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Risiina Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓi ̀ fa nyi ri ̀ kem ɓisuu ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓɛyɔ ̀ m ɓii ki ki kpaŋi ; ɓaaghna mɛ ̀ ɗu ɓi zi ɓi mis mɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ɗyoo ri ̀ zi , ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ n ̀ sim ɓɛ mɛnig ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Nni ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom adɛŋ , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɓka ̀ y roa ̀ n ̀ tonto , a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ di a kpaakpaa lɛ : Baɓilon a ̀ gwey a kpi ̀ i , Baɓilon a ̀ gwey a kpi ̀ i ; nnyɛɛ nɔsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m mɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ g mɛ ɓi cɛɓ kii ki tifin ki ki ri koŋnyo ̀ o ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a ki ̀ raa a ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ y di a kpaakpaa jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : I mum a ̀ ɓɔgsii nya ̀ m ri ̀ ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki yɔ ̀ nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓɛ teɗ nyi ki ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ ki nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛn ɓisu nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓi ca ̀ g ,
di a ̀ ri ̀ girig ɓii ̀ nɔɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ g mɛ ribaŋi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , mɛ mɛ ri mɛ ̀ ɓe ̀ niyɛn ɓi ɓeŋ a ̀ bim yii ̀ , mɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa mɛ ɓu ̀ tɛn ɗi com kidɛŋ ; a ̀ ki ri ̀ ɓii ̀ wowoogh ntɔɓ ɓi ɗuu , ri ̀ ɓi n ̀ du ̀ si , ɓi mis mɛ ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ tɛnɛn , ri ̀ ɓi mis mɛ Man a ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Fi ̀ sili ̀ fi ɗuu ɗi ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗiighɗigsi ̀ ɓɔ fyɛɛ ̀ syoosyoo fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ . Yɛ ̀ ɛ i ̀ ru yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwos , ri ̀ fɔɔsɛ ̀ n ɗyaa ɓa ɓi ɓisuu ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓɔgsi ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ri ̀ nya ̀ m ri ̀ ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki yɔ ̀ , ri ̀ ɓisuu mum bimiɗ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ teka ̀ ki ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ ki ɗii ɗi nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛn .
Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋɓeŋ ɓidɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ n ̀ tyweeyi wu yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus , ɓɛɛ sii ̀ rɛn kɛɛ ri lɛ ̀ .
Nni n ̀ woka ̀ di jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ aɗyoo i ̀ kpaa lɛ : Ka ̀ na ki ̀ ɓan ki ! Ma ̀ a ̀ gh ri ̀ ɓi ̀ loŋ ɓi ɓi wii ɓi ki ̀ say ki Kan , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓigomi ̀ nɛ . N ̀ ghay a kpaaghi lɛ : Ki ri fɔlɔɔ saaɗ , lɛ di ɓɛɛ fɔɔ ̀ sɛn ɓi ̀ say ɓyaa , ɓisuulɛ mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ maa mɛɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔnɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ ɓɔ .
Nni n ̀ seese ̀ e ̀ gha ̀ , n ̀ ghɛn ki ̀ kwi ̀ ɗ ki puɓ ; ɓi ki ̀ kwi ̀ ɗ kin ̀ mum a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔriyɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ man a ̀ mum , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ tam a ̀ ri ̀ kem ɓi nto , a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ kii ̀ ri ̀ gol , a ̀ ki ɓanɓan zɛ ̀ m i mpooyɛn ɓi ca ̀ g .
Nni ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom adɛŋ a ̀ kpaga ̀ y ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ kpaa ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔriyɛn ɓi ki ̀ kwi ̀ ɗ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Pi ̀ gha zɛ ̀ m , u saŋ ɓyom , lɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ mɛ ̀ saŋ yɛɛ kpaŋi lɛ ̀ , ɓisuulɛ ɓyom ɓi ɓi ziinɛ ɓi mɛ te ̀ ɗ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a saŋ ̀ ɓyɔ .
Fɔɔnnɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔriyɛn ɓi ki ̀ kwi ̀ ɗ a ̀ pi ̀ ka ̀ zɛ ̀ m , a ̀ saŋ ɓyom ɓi ɓi ziinɛ .
Nni ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom adɛŋ a ̀ kpaga ̀ y ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛ aɗyoo , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ girig ri ̀ zɛ ̀ m i mpooyɛn ɓi ca ̀ g ;
fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom adɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ gha ̀ ɗuu , a ̀ kpaga ̀ y ɓi com ki ɓɛɛ ̀ tɔ ̀ ngi ɓyom mii ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ kpaa roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ zɛ ̀ m i mpooyɛn ɓi ca ̀ g jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Pi ̀ gha zɛ ̀ m yɔɔ ̀ , u syaŋ ɓi ̀ jug ɓi vii ̀ nyɛ ̀ , ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ ɗu ̀ n ɓi mɛ ɓa ̀ ŋ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a pi ̀ ka ̀ zɛ ̀ m , a ̀ syagi ̀ vii ̀ nyɛ ̀ bimiɗ i ̀ nɛ ɓi ziinɛ , di a su ̀ usuu ̀ ri ̀ yɔ ̀ ɓi coo wayɗ wu bim i Bɛ ̀ ll .
Nni ɓɛ saɓka ̀ ɓi ̀ ɗu ̀ n ɓin ̀ ɓi wayɗ wu wu ɓagha ̀ fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ ri ba ̀ n ; fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ rɛm ɓi bwaɓ ɓi ɓɛnga ̀ ka ̀ y ɓi wayɗ , ɓi riɓi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ko ̀ do ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ ko ̀ do ̀ , ɓi ki rim , nunu ̀ g mɛɛtɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ bog ri ̀ ki ̀ den .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ki ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ kidɛŋ aɗyoo , ki ki ɓagha ̀ coo gɛn a ̀ ki ̀ ɓan a n ̀ kuurakɛn ; ɓum ɓɛ titom taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ; ɓɛ ɓanɓa ̀ nga ̀ mɛ ̀ tɔɓ taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , mɛ ̀ tɔɓ mɛ siito ̀ n . Ɓi mɔ innɛ bim i Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ tulii .
Nni n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ di ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yaka ̀ lɛ ri ̀ nya ̀ m , ri ̀ ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki yɔ ̀ , ri ̀ ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɗii ɗi nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛn . Ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ rɛrɛ ̀ li ̀ gha ̀ ɓi com ki ke ̀ leŋ ̀ ŋ ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ŋwii ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ŋwii , m ̀ ɓu ̀ takɛn ɗi ɗuu , ɓɛ ɓanɓa ̀ n ti ̀ loŋ ti Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ ɓɔ .
Ɓɛ kɛkɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ gh lɛ ri ̀ fyem fi Moyis a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say a Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ fi Man a ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , lɛ Kan Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wuce ̀ m , mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ mɔɔ mɛ kii lɛ , mɛ teghɛ ̀ n , mɛ ki ɓa com ki kuurakɛn ! Rifo ̀ m ɗi ɓilɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , bee yɔɔ yi ri lɛ saaɗ , yi ki ɓa ɓɛkɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ ɓɛ bee .
Kan ghɛn yɛɛ ri lɛ a ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓ lɛ a ̀ risii ɓi ɗii ɗyɔɔ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ki kemzi ɗyɔ ? Ɓisuulɛ , lɔŋ wɔ ̀ cɛ ̀ ncɔɔ yɛɛ ri n ̀ tɛnɛn . Ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ri ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u , ɓi ɓag wɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ ɗu asu , lɛ saaɗ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ a mɛ re ̀ sɛ ̀ n .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn nnɛ n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ di naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ ŋwa ̀ rɛɛ aɗyoo ; ɓi na-Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛn innɛ ki ̀ nuugh ki rira ̀ rɛ ̀ n ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ki ri .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓɛ kitaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓanɓa ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki mɛtɔɓ , ɓɛ kpaga ̀ y ɓi na-Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛn , ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ waatakɛn ɓisyeesyee ɓi ɓila ̀ a ̀ ɓi puɓ , ɓi ɓi lonlo ̀ mga ̀ n ̀ lo ̀ nlomɛn , ɓɛ ŋira ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ ka ̀ nɗa ɓɛ gol ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓon .
Ki ̀ bog ki ɓi nya ̀ m yi kini ̀ n ki fala ̀ ka ̀ ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓɛ kitaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɓeŋ ɓɛ gol , ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓala ̀ ka ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ronɛn ɗi bim i Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ fi ̀ sili ̀ fi ronga ̀ naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ ri ̀ kem ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wii . Mum a ̀ ki ɓagha ̀ ɓi lɛ a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ ɓi na-Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛn , a ̀ kpaŋ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ tɔɓ mɛ kitaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛ ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓɛ kitaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛ ri ɓii ̀ le ̀ egh .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ woka ̀ di coo jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , i ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ ɓum ɓɛ titom lɛ : Kɛ ̀ ɛna ki ̀ su ̀ u ̀ rii kitaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ɓɛɓeŋ ɓɛ bim i ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi zi .
Nni ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a n ̀ tonto a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ , a ̀ su ̀ u ̀ ri ̀ ɓeŋ wi ̀ i ̀ ɓi zi ; fɔɔnnɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ ki nya ̀ m , ɓɛ ki ɓɔɔɓɔgsi ̀ ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki yɔ ̀ , ɓɛ roɓka ̀ ka ̀ ri ̀ kuu ɗi kiɓɛɛ ɗiɗɛŋ ɗi mum kɛ ̀ ɛ yi yɛ ̀ ɛ ɗi kɛɛ ̀ kɛɛ yi ̀ , ɗi ki kɛŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ .
Nni ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ a su ̀ u ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓeŋ wi ̀ i ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n bwaɓ , yɛ ̀ ɛ bwaɓ yi kiloŋ ki mum , fɔɔnnɛ ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓi ghɛghɛ ̀ ɓka ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n ɓi cuugha ̀ .
Ŋwaa ̀ fi ̀ tom a ki ̀ raa a ̀ su ̀ u ̀ ri ̀ ɓeŋ wi ̀ i ̀ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y ɓɛ zɛy ri ̀ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ n ̀ sim ɓɛ mɛnig , ɓyom ɓi ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n bwaɓ .
Nni n ̀ woka ̀ di ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a mɛ ̀ nig a kpaa lɛ : U ̀ ri ̀ lɛ saaɗ , yɛ ̀ ɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ nɗeni lɛ kɛɛ ɓa fɔlɔɔ , wa ̀ a ̀ nɛ u ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tɛnɛn , u ̀ ri ̀ , u ̀ ki ɓagha ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ ɓɛ yogsi ̀ gha ̀ bwaɓ yi ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n ri ̀ yi ɓɛkpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan , nni wɔ ̀ ɔ nfaa ɓɔ bwaɓ lɛ ɓɛɛ nɔ , ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ ki ɓɔ fɔlɔɔ .
Nni n ̀ woka ̀ di com ki ɓɛɛ ̀ tɔ ̀ ngi ɓyom mii ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ki kpaa lɛ : Ɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ Kan Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wuce ̀ m , ri ̀ ren ɗyɔɔ ɗi ɓiɓan ɗi ri mii ̀ , ɗi ki ɓa lɛ saaɗ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a ki ̀ ni ̀ n a ̀ su ̀ u ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓeŋ wi ̀ i ̀ ɓi ŋwos , ŋwos a teɗ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ a ɗigsi ɓum ri ̀ ɗuu ,
nni coo ritɔ ̀ n ɗi sya ̀ n ɗin ̀ ɗi ɗigsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓum , ɓɛ tum ri ̀ fengi ̀ ɗi ɗii ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ la ̀ mii mɛ ̀ tɔɓ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛn mɛrem lɛ ɓɛɛ fa nyi ri ̀ kem .
Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a ki ̀ tan ̀ a ̀ su ̀ u ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓeŋ wi ̀ i ̀ ɓi-kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ wu nya ̀ m , biri ̀ m i ̀ sigtɛ ̀ n ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , ɓum ɓɛ kaŋka ̀ m mɛ ̀ lema ̀ g lɛ ri ̀ kɛŋ ɗi cee ɓɔ ,
ɓɛ ki feefengi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ aɗyoo ɓisuu rikɛŋ ɗi ɓɛ wowo ̀ ka ̀ ri ̀ ɓisuu ɓiɓɛɛ ̀ ɓyaa , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛn mɛrem lɛ ɓɛɛ caɗ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓyaa ɓi mɛki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ .
Nni ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a ki ̀ taa ̀ fog a ̀ su ̀ u ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓeŋ wi ̀ i ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ nɛ lɛ Efirat , mɛ ̀ nig mɛ mii ̀ mɛ ghemi ̀ lɛ mɛɛ nɛm ̀ mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m mɛ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ŋwos a ti a ̀ kpagi ̀ i ̀ bee .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ di ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay ɓiraa ɓyɛɛ ̀ kpaŋkpaŋ yi lɛ ri ̀ ɓi ŋwɔm wu kina ̀ a ̀ gɔ ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓi ŋwɔm wu nya ̀ m , ri ̀ ɓi ŋwɔm wu n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓɛpwa ̀ a ̀ ; mɛ ̀ ghay mɛ ̀ n mɛ ɓagha ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ gbo ̀ ri .
Ɓi ri ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay ɓi ɓyɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki da ̀ m , ɓi ki kɛ ̀ ngi a mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m mɛ ɓi ziinɛ bimiɗ , lɛ ɓyɛɛ taŋzɛn mɔ ɓisuu wɛ ̀ y wu wu ri ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ɓi coo go ̀ n i Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wuce ̀ m .
Ghɛna , n-yu ̀ yuy yɛ ̀ ɛ wiiwi ̀ i ̀ . Ma ̀ a ̀ gh ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ cem , a ̀ ki ɓe ̀ ŋɓeŋ ɓila ̀ a ̀ ɓii lɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ghi kito ̀ n zɛy lɛ a wog n ̀ too ̀ ri ̀ ɗ di ɓum ɓɛ ghɛɛ nyi ki ̀ to ̀ n zɛy .
Mɛ ̀ ghay mɛ ̀ n mɛ taŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ regi ɓi ri ̀ Ebi ̀ reegh lɛ Arimagedɔŋ .
Nni ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a ki ̀ taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ a su ̀ u ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓeŋ wi ̀ i ̀ ɓi bɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ bɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ . Fɔɔnnɛ coo jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki kpaga ̀ y ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , di ki rii ̀ ɓi-kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ ki kpaa lɛ : Ki lee ̀ gh !
Fɔɔnnɛ ki kigha ̀ lɛ ŋwa ̀ aŋwa ̀ ɗ a ̀ ŋwa ̀ ŋwa ̀ ɗ , gom yi woo ̀ ghwo ̀ o ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n , baa ̀ ba ̀ n i ̀ ɓoɓo ̀ g , zi i ki nyɛ ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ n lɛɛ ̀ gwey le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ i ̀ ka nyɛŋɗɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi rikuu ɗi ̀ n , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓaa ̀ ɓa ɓi ziinɛ .
Ba ̀ n i ̀ gwey i la ̀ nɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ̀ la ̀ na ̀ ɓiraa , ba ̀ n yi ɓilɔ ̀ ŋ ɓimbog ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m yi waa ̀ rɛ ̀ n , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ yiti ̀ Baɓilon a ̀ gwey lɛ a nɔsi nyi ɓeŋ a ̀ mɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ g mɛ ɓi coo bim yii ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ŋ ɓi riɓa ̀ y ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ghɛŋɗa ̀ ka ̀ , do ̀ n yɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ghɛnɛn ti nsoo ̀ bog .
Coo bol i ̀ gɔ ̀ g i ̀ kɔ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ y aɗyoo i ̀ nɔ ɓum ɓi nyoo , gɔ ̀ g yi bol i ̀ nɛ ̀ n yi ɓala ̀ ka ̀ nunu ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ kilo ̀ mɛ ̀ tin mɛɓɛɛ ̀ ; nni ɓum ɓɛ fenga ̀ ka ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓisuu ntɔɓ wu ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ win ̀ ɗi ̀ bol i ̀ gɔ ̀ g , n ̀ tɔɓ wi ̀ n wu tee ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ wu ciɓ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓum ɓɛ titom taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓanɓa ̀ nga ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɓeŋ ɓɛ kitaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ , ki yugha ̀ y ki kpaa mɛ ̀ lɛ : Yu , nɗesi wɔ ̀ lannɛ ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ pɔnɔsii coo giɓ a ri ̀ ɓa ̀ mɓa ̀ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔri ɓi be ̀ n yi ɓɛri ̀ ɓa ̀ y ɓɛgwey .
Ri ̀ nyi nnɛ mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m mɛ ɓi ziinɛ mɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi fi ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g , ɓumɓɛ ɓi ziinɛ ɓɛ ŋwaŋ ri ̀ nɔ ɗi mɛrɔ ̀ g mɛ ɓi cɛɓ kii ki tifin ki ̀ n .
Nni ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom anɛ ̀ n a ̀ teka ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓi nghay a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓireɓ . - Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ giɓ adɛŋ n ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔriyɛn ɓi nya ̀ m i ̀ dɛŋ fɛlɛ m ̀ ɓa ̀ ŋ , nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛn ri ̀ mii mɛ mɛɛ ̀ feefengi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll nyoo bimiɗ , i ̀ ki ɓa ri mɛ ̀ to taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , mɛ ̀ tɔŋ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ .
Giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ waatɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ ɓi ɓa ̀ ŋ lɛ pɔŋŋ , ri ̀ ɓi ɓa ̀ ŋ lɛ ɓu ̀ lu ̀ g-ɓu ̀ lu ̀ g , a ̀ ki waatɛn lɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ ŋ mɛ gol , ri ̀ mɛ ɓɛ kii ̀ ri ̀ gɔ ̀ g yi ŋwe ̀ rim ŋwe ̀ rim , ri ̀ ti ̀ caka . A ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɓeŋ a ̀ gol ɓi ca ̀ g , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓiɓan , ri ̀ ti ̀ fin ti kiɓeɓta ̀ g kii ki cɛɓ .
Ɗii ɗidɛŋ ɗi ɓagha ̀ nyi ɗi ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ɓisu ; azi anɛ ɓi ɗii ɗi ̀ n a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki a ri ̀ nyam ; ɗii ɗi ̀ n ɗi ɓagha ̀ lɛ Baɓilon a ̀ gwey , a ̀ jɛɛ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛ riɓa ̀ mɓa ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓeɓtɛn ɓi ɓi ziinɛ .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ giɓ anɛ ̀ n n ̀ ŋwaŋɛn lɛ ri ̀ bwaɓ yi ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ yi ɓɛwusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛ Yeesus . Yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ nyi , n ̀ kuura ̀ g lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Ŋwaa ̀ fi ̀ tom a tɔg mɛ ̀ lɛ ɓisuucɛ nnɛ u ̀ kuuraagh ? N ̀ ɗi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ kalii ɓɛ ̀ azi ɓɛ a ri ̀ nyam ɓɛ ɓi giɓ anɛ ̀ n ri ̀ nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛ i ̀ tɛ ̀ tɛɛgh nyi , i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ to taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ tɔŋ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ .
Nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛ wa ̀ a ghɛɛ , i ̀ ɓagha ̀ nni i ̀ yii ̀ di . I ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ kpaŋi ̀ i ̀ ɓi coo riɓee ɗi rimɛn , i ̀ kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ɗyaŋi ̀ . Nni ɓumɓɛ ɓi ziinɛ , ɓɛ mii maa mɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi mɛ ka ̀ nɛn ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ cɛɓ , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ ziinɛ i ̀ ki ̀ lɛ ̀ nga ̀ , ɓɛ ri kuura ̀ g di ɓɛ ghɛɛ nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , ɓisuulɛ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ , nni i ̀ yii ̀ di , nni i ̀ ki ri ̀ ɓii ̀ sugtii yi ti ̀ .
Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki lɛ mum a ɓa ri ̀ fe ̀ g a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n kɛɛ ̀ ki . Mɛ ̀ to mɛ nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛn mɛ kitaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , mɛ ri do ̀ n taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔrii mii ̀ .
Mɛ ri girig mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ; mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m mɛtan ̀ mɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m mɛn mɛ mɛ kpi ̀ , ɗi ̀ fog ɗi kaka ɗi lala ̀ mi , ɗimbog ɗi ka kpaŋ ɓi . Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɗi ri kpaŋ , ɗi ri kɔ ̀ ri maa ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n lɛsa ̀ g .
Nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ , i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ki yii ̀ di inɛ ̀ n , yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi kitaa ̀ raa , i ̀ ɓa ti ̀ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi mɛfo ̀ m mɛ kitaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , i ̀ ki ri ̀ ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ki ɗyaŋi ̀ .
Mɛ ̀ tɔŋ mɛ kin ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ mɛ wa ̀ a ghɛɛ , mɛ ri mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ mɛ mɛ ka tumɛn ɓi rila ̀ mi ̀ ; ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ rɛsɛɛ mɛfo ̀ m ɓɛ lami ̀ hawo ̀ bog nɗaŋ ɗi nya ̀ m .
Mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m mɛn ̀ mɛ ri lɔŋ riyiti ̀ ɗi ̀ fog , lɛ ɓɛɛ teɗ lɛ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ waa , ri ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ kaa , ɓɛɛ fa ri ̀ nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛn .
Ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ ɗu ̀ u ri Man a ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , Man a ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ a ̀ ki yag ɓɔ ɓi wɛ ̀ y ɓisuulɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ Kan a ̀ nɛ a ɓɛ ̀ kan , a ̀ ki ɓa ti rifo ̀ m ɗi mɛfo ̀ m . Man a ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ ɓii ̀ yaa ̀ gh ɓi wɛ ̀ y , n ̀ ɗaŋ ɗi ɓumɓɛ a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ nɛn , ɓɛɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓii ɓɛ ntyweeyi .
Nni ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a kpaati ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ nig mɛ wa ̀ a ghɛɛ di giɓ a ri ̀ ɓa ̀ mɓa ̀ a ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔrii wɔɔ , mɛ ri ɓumɓɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ kuu lɛ mɛ ̀ kuu , ɓi ̀ tuu lɛ ɓi ̀ tuu , ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ lɛ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ .
Mɛ ̀ tɔŋ mɛ kin ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ mɛ wa ̀ a ghɛɛ ri ̀ nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , ɓi ri ɓii ̀ ɓe ̀ e ̀ zɛɛ giɓ a ri ̀ ɓa ̀ mɓa ̀ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n , ɓi pumzi ̀ nyi , ɓi caɗ nyi ki ̀ to ̀ n zɛy , ɓi ɗi mɛ ̀ mu ̀ u ̀ mii , ɓi ki tɔ ̀ n nyi ɓi ɗuu .
Ɓisuulɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ foga ̀ ɓɔ fe ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ roo ̀ zi ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗii ɓi mɛ ̀ rem ; ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi ̀ fog ɗyɛɛri lɛ , ɓɛɛ teɗ ri ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɗyaa , ɓɛɛ fa ri ̀ nya ̀ m a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓi ri ɓii ̀ ki ̀ lɛɛ .
Nni giɓ anɛ wa ̀ a ghɛɛ , nnyɛɛ ri ba ̀ n i ̀ gwey inɛ i ̀ la ̀ mii mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m mɛ ɓi ziinɛ .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn nnɛ n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ di ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom adɛŋ a sɛnsɛn yi aɗyoo , nyi ri ̀ coo ite ̀ ɗ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ , ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ki ɓi ri ̀ kem ɗii ki kpeŋzi ̀ zi bimiɗ .
Nni a ̀ la ̀ mɓɛ ̀ nga ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Baɓilon a ̀ gwey a kpi ̀ i , Baɓilon a ̀ gwey a kpi ̀ i ! A ̀ ghali mɛɛ mɛ ɓiɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay , ri ̀ n ̀ nyamzɛn wu mɛghay mɛ ɓeɓtɛn mɛkuu mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , ri ̀ wu ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ti ̀ i ̀ li ̀ ɓi ɓi ti ɓi ɓeɓki ̀ ɓum ,
ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi nnɔɔ mɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ g mɛ cɛɓ kii ki tifin ki ki ri koŋnyoo ; ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m mɛ ɓi ziinɛ mɛ nki ̀ kii ti ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g ri nyi , ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -du ̀ ne ɓɛ ɓi ziinɛ ɓɛ kum , lɛ coo gɛn a ̀ i ̀ kum wii ̀ .
Nni fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ woka ̀ di jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ dɛŋ i ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Mi ̀ ni ɓɔn ɓɛm , pɛ ̀ sɛɛna ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛn , di kɛ ̀ ɓi teɗ ga ̀ ɓ ɓi ki ̀ ɓe ki yɔ ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓya ̀ a ɓa ɓi ri ga ̀ ɓ ɓi mɛ ̀ tɔɓ mɛ yɔ ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ ɓe ɓi yɔ ̀ ɓi mɛ saɓta ̀ g a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ aɗyoo , nni Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ a n-yitii mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ mɛ yɔ ̀ mɛ ɓeɓtɛn .
Ki ̀ ina nyi yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ mi ̀ ni , ɓi ̀ le ̀ ɓ nyi ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗii gɛ ̀ n yiɓɛɛ ̀ ɓi ɓeŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ foga ̀ mi ̀ ni mɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ g mii mii ̀ ; ca ̀ ɓina nyi mɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ g mii ̀ gɛ ̀ n yiɓɛɛ ̀ .
Faana ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛn n ̀ tɔɓ , ɓi ̀ ki cuusi yɔ ̀ le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ kem ɗi kɔnga ̀ yɔ ̀ , bas ri ̀ i ̀ kum , ɓisuulɛ ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛn yɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa ɓi nɗem ɓi ɗu ̀ m lɛ : N ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔrii lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ giɓ anɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m a kɔ ̀ ra ̀ g , n ̀ -yin nkpɔɓ , ri ̀ wu ɗyaa tanɛɛ gɛ ɓi mɛ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki mɛ ̀ tɔɓ mii mɛ ri yu ̀ lɔŋ ŋwos bog , mɛ ɓa lɛ : ɗi ̀ ri ̀ wu , ɗi ̀ ɓi ̀ lɛ ̀ ɓi ̀ , ri ̀ za ̀ y , ɗuu ɗi ki ri ̀ nyi ɓii ̀ ɗigsii . Ɓisuulɛ Kan Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ a n-yɔ ̀ mi ki ̀ ɓan kii a ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ .
Mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m mɛce ̀ m mɛ ɓi ziinɛ , mɛ mɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi fi ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g ɗi ̀ nyi , mɛ ki nɔ ̀ ɔnɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ i ̀ kum wii , mɛ ri ɓii ̀ re ̀ nɗeni , mɛ ki seeghsee ̀ ghkɛ ̀ n ɓisuu kiɓan kii , yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ri ghɛn di fi ̀ sili ̀ fi ɗuu ɗi ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗiighɗigsi ̀ nyi fyɛɛ ̀ syoosyo ̀ o ̀ .
Mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m mɛn ̀ mɛ ri rɛlag yi fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ lɛ mɛɛ ̀ ririsi ntɔɓ wu ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛn , mɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ lɛ : Nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g , nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g ɗi ̀ coo ba ̀ n i ̀ Baɓilon , ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ te ̀ ete ̀ ɗ ki ba ̀ n ; ki ̀ ɓan kɔɔ ki yɔm ̀ ɓɛɛ lɔŋ ɓi hawo ̀ bog .
Ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -du ̀ ne ɓɛ ɓi ziinɛ ɓɛ re ̀ nɗe ̀ n , ɓɛ ki waatɛn ɓilɛ ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓisu wii , lɛ mum a ̀ la ̀ gtii ti ̀ ɓi du ̀ ne ya ̀ a ̀ ,
du ̀ ne i ̀ nɛ ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ ɓyom mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ ̀ kuu , lɛ ri ̀ gol , ri ̀ swiɗ a ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni , ri ̀ gɔ ̀ g yi ŋwe ̀ rim-ŋwe ̀ rim , ri ̀ ti ̀ caka , ri ̀ syeesyee a ̀ ki ̀ rimiti ̀ , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ɓi ɓa ̀ ŋ lɛ pɔŋŋ , ri ̀ silig , ri ̀ ɓi ɓi ri ɓi ̀ ɓa ̀ ŋ lɛ ɓu ̀ lu ̀ g-ɓu ̀ lu ̀ g ; ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓam mɛ ɓite ɓi ɓi kaarɛɛ ri ̀ ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓɛ syaagh ri ̀ mam mɛ zo ̀ g , ri ̀ ɓi ɓɛ soɓi ri ̀ ɓi ̀ te ɓi syeesyee , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓɛ kii ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ kuu ɗi swiɗ ɗidɛŋ nsoo ̀ lɛ ri ̀ bɔŋ nsoo ̀ lɛ ri ̀ gɔ ̀ g yi ɗyɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɗyɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ gh ;
ɓi ̀ ɓaaɓaa ɓi kite ki lɛ kane ̀ li ̀ yee ri ̀ ɓyom ɓi nu ̀ nnumɛn , ri ̀ ti ̀ ra ̀ a ̀ re , ri ̀ ri ̀ kuu ɗi firu ɗi lɛ mii ̀ r , ri ̀ fi ̀ ru fi lɛ a ̀ ŋsaŋ , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ rɔ ̀ g , ri ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ , ri ̀ fa ̀ rin ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ kuu ɗi ge ̀ ŋ ɗi ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ lag bi ̀ rɛs mii ̀ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sani ̀ nya , ri ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ri ̀ zo ̀ m yi kimbɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ , ri ̀ ɓyalig , ri ̀ ɓɛkpa ̀ n ri ̀ ɓyɛɓ ɓi ɓum .
Ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi n ̀ ɗem wɔɔ wu kɔnkɔ ̀ nga ̀ , ɓi mɛ ra ̀ ɓsɛn wɔ ; i ̀ kum wɔɔ , ri ̀ gi ̀ n yi ɓyom yi wɔ ̀ ɔ nɗi ri ̀ yɔ , ɓi ti ɓi ̀ ɗimɛn ɓi san a ̀ nɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɔɔ , wa ̀ a ki ghɛɛ ̀ dii gɛ ɓi ɓyɔ .
Ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -du ̀ ne ɓɛ ɓɛ kumga ̀ lɛ ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛn , ɓɛ ri rɛlii fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ , lɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ririsi ntɔɓ wu ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛn ; ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ re ̀ ni , ɓɛ waatɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ lɛ ̀ ɓi ̀ ;
ɓɛ kpaa gɛ lɛ : Nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g , nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g ri ̀ coo ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛ i ̀ i nɗi ̀ n ̀ waatɛn lɛ ri ̀ syeesyee a ̀ ki ̀ rimiti ̀ , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ɓi ɓa ̀ ŋɓaŋɛn lɛ pɔŋŋ ri ̀ ɓi ɓa ̀ ŋ lɛ ɓu ̀ lu ̀ g-ɓu ̀ lu ̀ g , yɔ ̀ lɛ ri mɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ ŋ mɛ gol , ri ̀ mɛ ŋwe ̀ rim-ŋwe ̀ rim ri ̀ ti ̀ caka , coo ikum win ̀ wu ̀ ce ̀ m wu ɗyoŋi ɓi bimiɗ a ̀ hawo ̀ .
Ɓɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ti ̀ tima ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pusi ̀ ti ̀ tima ̀ ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ sasay ɓi ti ̀ tima ̀ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛɛ mii ̀ , ɓɛ rɛla ̀ ka ̀ y fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ ,
ɓɛ kuu ̀ ku ̀ gsɛ ̀ n di ɓaa ghɛn fisili ̀ fi ɗuu ɗi ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗiighɗigsi ̀ ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛn , ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ lɛ ba ̀ n i ̀ be yɛ ̀ ɛ kpaga ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ coo ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛ ?
Ɓɛ ɗyɛɛɗyɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ nga ̀ ku ̀ ru ̀ ɓu ɓi mɛ ̀ to , di ɓɛɛ ̀ re ̀ eree ̀ dɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ waatɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ lɛ ̀ ɓi ̀ , di ɓɛɛ ̀ kuukugsɛ ̀ n jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g , nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g ri ̀ coo ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛ ; ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ri ̀ ti ̀ tima ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n , ɓɛ mmɛ kum lɛ i ̀ kum wu ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛn , yɛ ̀ ɛ ghali i ̀ reɓ ɓi maa hawo ̀ bog !
Wɔ ̀ ɗyoo , u ̀ ri ̀ lɛ u ̀ sa ̀ msa ̀ m ɓi ri ̀ ɗyaŋ ɗi ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛn i ̀ ɗyaŋi , ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan girig , ɓisuulɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ rɔ ̀ ŋi ki ̀ ɓan kin yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ pɔnɔsii yɔ ̀ .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ki ̀ te ̀ ete ̀ ɗ ki ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom ki pɛsi ̀ gha ̀ gɔ ̀ g i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ coo rikem ɗi kipɛn , a ̀ pi ̀ g yɔ ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n di a kpaakpaa lɛ : Fɛlɛ nnɛ ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ pi ̀ igh coo ba ̀ n i ̀ Baɓilon fɛlɛ azi ri i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , ɓum ɓaa ghɛɛ ̀ dii gɛ ti ̀ ɓi yɔ ̀ .
Ɓɛ ri wogtii gɛ ɓi gom i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɓoo ̀ gh-fi ̀ loŋ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɓoo ̀ gh-ɓyom , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ rɔŋi ̀ -za ̀ ro , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ rɔŋi ̀ -mam a lɔ ̀ ŋkɔɔ . Ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki tanɛn ti ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yii ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗi rikuu ɗi kisay ɗiɗɛŋ nsoo ̀ ɗi ̀ fog ; ɓɛ wogtii gɛ ɓi gom i ̀ ri ̀ kem ɗi kipɛn foo ,
ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn ki lamɓa ̀ kaa ghɛnɛɛ gɛ ti ̀ ɓi foo , ɓɛ ki wogtii gɛ ɓi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ n ̀ wɔli ̀ giɓ ri ̀ gil foo . Ɓisuulɛ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -du ̀ ne ɓɔɔ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi ̀ te ̀ ete ̀ ɗ ɓi ɓi ziinɛ , ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ , u ̀ ye ̀ gsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ghe ̀ y mɔɔ mɛ kifuu ,
ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ tanɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ri ̀ bwaɓ yi ɓɛkpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan , ri ̀ yi ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ yi ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ cuusi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ziinɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɔɔ .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn n ̀ woka ̀ coo jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , i ̀ pisɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ coo kituu ki ɓum kɛɛ ri ɓi ɗyoo ɓi ɗu ̀ m ki kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ lɛ : Ale ̀ luya ̀ ! Go ̀ ri , ri ̀ kem , ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , ɓi ri ɓyom ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll wi ̀ s .
Ɓisuulɛ ri ̀ ren ɗii ɗi ɓiɓan ɗi ri mii ̀ , ɗi ki ɓa lɛ saaɗ . A ̀ a m ̀ pɔnɔsii coo giɓ a ri ̀ ɓa ̀ mɓa ̀ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ a n-yooyo ̀ gsi ̀ zi ri ri ̀ ɓa ̀ mɓa ̀ ɗii , a ̀ ki rɔ ̀ ŋ bwaɓ yi ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓii ɓɛ a ̀ wowo ̀ la ̀ .
Nni ɓɛ ɓii ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ ti ̀ ki ̀ kpaa ̀ lɛ : Ale ̀ luya ̀ . Fɔɔnnɛ fi ̀ sili ̀ fi fyɛɛ ̀ ɗiighɗigsi ̀ ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛn , fyɛɛ ̀ syoosyoo fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ ɓum ɓɛ ritin ɗi ̀ ɓɛnin , ɗi ̀ nya ̀ m yi kini ̀ n , ɓɛ ɓaka ̀ mɛ ̀ ɗu ɓi zi , ɓɛ ɓɔgsi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔrii ɓi-kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ di ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa lɛ : A ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n Ale ̀ luya ̀ !
Nni jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ faŋi ̀ gha ̀ y ɓi-kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ lɛ : Ɓɔgsiina Bɛ ̀ ll wi ̀ s , mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓii ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ɓi ̀ ti ɓi ̀ risa ̀ g nyi lɛ ri ̀ ɓɔɓti ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ woka ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ di yɛɛ ̀ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wɔɔ yɛ ̀ ɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ coo kituu ki ɓum , i ̀ pisɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ gom i ̀ ɓyoo ɓikus ɓi riɓa ̀ y , nsoo ̀ lɛ gom i ̀ baa ̀ ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛ yɛɛ ̀ ɓoɓog ri i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nce ̀ m i ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ lɛ : Ale ̀ luya ̀ ! Lɛ Kan Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wuce ̀ m a ̀ mɛ re ̀ si kila ̀ mi ̀ kii .
Ti nya ̀ a ̀ rɛɛna , ti ̀ sa ̀ msa ̀ m , ti ̀ fafa ̀ nyi ri ̀ kem ɓisuulɛ ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ ti ɓi ri ̀ wɛy ɗi Man a ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti kpaŋi , gil a mɛ ki pe ̀ gsɛ ̀ n .
Ɓɛ nfaa nyi i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ a waa ̀ tɛn syeesyee a ̀ ki ̀ rimiti ̀ a ̀ nɛ a lo ̀ nlo ̀ m , a ̀ ki ɓa ntɛnɛn . Syeesyee a ̀ ki ̀ rimiti ̀ a ̀ nɛn yɛɛ ri ɓi ̀ syeesyee ɓi ɓiɓan ɓi ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kila ̀ g .
Nni ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom anɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpaagha ̀ mɛ ̀ lɛ ka ̀ na lɛ : Ma ̀ a ̀ gh ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ la ̀ a ̀ ghrakɛn a dina ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ wɛy ɗi Man a ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ; fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpati ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ lɛ : Jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi , yi ri ɓɛ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ ɓɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Nni n ̀ kpi ̀ gha ̀ nyi a mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ lɛ mɓɔgsi nyi ki ̀ ɓan kifog , a ̀ kpaa mɛ ̀ lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ɔ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn ki ki ̀ i com kidɛŋ fɔlɔɔ ; mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ mɛ ̀ reŋka ̀ ŋ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ a ki ̀ say , n ̀ ki ɓa ti reŋka ̀ ŋ a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ goni ɓɛ ɓɛ teka ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Yeesus a ̀ tɛɛ ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ . Bɛ ̀ ll innɛ ɓɔgsi , lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Yeesus a ̀ re ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ɓyɛɛ ri n ̀ ghay a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan , com ki ɓɛɛ kpaa ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ɗyoo ɗi ̀ nɛmɓɛn n ̀ ghɛn zo ̀ m i ki ̀ mɓɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ i ̀ mpuɓ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi zo ̀ m inɛ ̀ n aɗyoo , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɗii lɛ , Ŋwaa ̀ -n ̀ tyweeyi , ri ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ a ̀ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ , a yɔ ̀ myɔm ɓiɓan , a ̀ ki ɗu ̀ u ̀ ɗuu wɛ ̀ y ɓi ɓɛ ̀ saaɗ .
Mis mii mɛ ri n ̀ ɗo ̀ o ̀ wu ɗuu ; ɓɛ ̀ ta ̀ m ɓɛ rikem ɓɛ ɓa nyi ɓi nto ki ̀ tuu ; a ̀ ri ̀ ɗii ɗi ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ɓi nyoo , ɗi ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ yii ɓi , i ki cee ɓi lɛ nyimiɗ ,
a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ waatɛn ri ̀ ga a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ bwaɓ ri bwaɓ , a ̀ ki ri ̀ ɗii lɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Mɛ ̀ raŋ mɛ ɓɛsuja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ aɗyoo mɛ nɔɔ ̀ nɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ nyi ɓi zo ̀ m yi kimbɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ yi puɓ , ɓɛ waata ̀ g ɓi ̀ syeesyee ɓi ɓɛki ̀ rimiti ̀ ɓɛ puɓ , ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ tɛnɛn .
Ga ̀ fa ̀ g i ̀ mpooyɛn i kpaŋ yi ̀ nyi ɓi ŋwɔm lɛ a ɓog ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ri yɔ ̀ ; a ̀ ri ̀ ɓyɔ ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sii ri n ̀ kpas wu bɔŋ , a ̀ ki saɓ ɓiɗu ̀ n ɓi vii ̀ nyɛ ̀ ɓi wayɗ wu mɛrɔ ̀ g mɛ coo bim i Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wuce ̀ m .
Ɓi ri ̀ ga wi ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ y wii , ɗii ɗi ri mii ̀ ɗi ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi mɛfo ̀ m , ri ̀ Kan a ̀ nɛ a ɓɛ ̀ kan .
Nni n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom adɛŋ di a ̀ rɛrɛlii ɓi ŋwos ; a ̀ la ̀ mɓɛ ̀ nga ̀ ti ̀ i ̀ li ̀ ti ̀ ce ̀ m ti ti lɛŋlɛ ̀ ŋga ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Yu ̀ unay , ɓi taŋzɛn ɓi coo dina ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ,
lɛ di ɓi ɗi lɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ mu ̀ u ̀ mɛ mɛfo ̀ m , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ te ̀ ete ̀ ɗ ɓi ɓum , ri ̀ mɛ zo ̀ m yi kimbɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓi zo ̀ m yin ̀ aɗyoo , ri ̀ mɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m lɛ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kpa ̀ n ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ yin ɓɛkpa ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓɔɓti ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ ri ̀ nya ̀ m ( i ̀ mɛ ̀ to taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ) , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m mɛ ɓi ziinɛ , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ raŋ maa mɛ ɓɛsuja ̀ a ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ taŋzɛn lɛ ɓɛɛ ɗuu wɛ ̀ y ɗi roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi zo ̀ m i mpuɓ aɗyoo , ri ̀ nɗaŋ wii wu ɓɛsuja ̀ a ̀ .
Nni ɓɛ ɓanga ̀ nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛn nɗaŋ ri n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓɛpwa ̀ a ̀ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ da ̀ m yi yi syoga ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ ki nya ̀ m , ɓɛ ki ɓɔɔɓɔgsi ̀ ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki nya ̀ m i ̀ nce ̀ m . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ pika ̀ ɓyom ɓi kiɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓin ̀ cem ɓi ki ̀ ra ̀ a ̀ ki ɗuu , ki n ̀ du ̀ si a lɔŋlɔŋ mii ̀ .
Ga ̀ fa ̀ g i ̀ nɛ i ̀ kpaga ̀ y ɓi ŋwɔm wu roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi zo ̀ m aɗyoo , i ̀ cuusi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛm ̀ bog ; fɔɔnnɛ ti ̀ i ̀ li ̀ ti ̀ ce ̀ m ti ɗigha ̀ mɛ ̀ mu ̀ u ̀ maa , ti wura ̀ g .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ di ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom adɛŋ a sɛnsɛn yi aɗyoo , a ̀ ɓanɓa ̀ n lɛ ri ̀ fi ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓa ̀ fi riɓee ɗi rimɛn , ri ̀ coo nsɛ ̀ ŋi ɓi ca ̀ g .
A ̀ ɓanga ̀ ki ̀ na ̀ a ̀ gɔ ̀ n ki ki ri lɛ fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ fi nyoo fi lɛ nɗe ̀ m , ri ̀ Sata ̀ n , a ̀ ka ̀ ŋ kɔ bɛn lɛ kɛɛ kɔri fɔlɔɔ be ̀ g tɔɔsi ̀ m .
Nni a ̀ pi ̀ ka ̀ kɔ ɓi coo riɓee ɗi rim , a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ ɗyɔ ki ̀ si ̀ mi , a ̀ ki roŋ ɗyɔ , lɛ ki ̀ na ̀ a ̀ gɔ ̀ n kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ye ̀ gsi ti ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ tɔɔsi ̀ m a ̀ be ̀ g a ̀ nɛn a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ roni ̀ . Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn , ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ ka ca ̀ ɗ kɔ ɓi maa ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n .
Nni n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ mɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ mɛ rila ̀ mi ̀ , ɓɛ fagha ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ kɔra ̀ ka ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ mɛn ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu yɔ ̀ myɔmɛn ɓiɓan ; fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ di ̀ gha ̀ mɛ ̀ ghay mɛ ɓum ɓɛ ɓɛ wowo ̀ la ̀ ɓisuulɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛ Yeesus ri ̀ ɓɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ ɓɔgsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi nya ̀ m i ̀ mɛ ̀ to taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , nsoo ̀ lɛ ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki yɔ ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓa ri ki ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ ki nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛn ɓisu nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓi ca ̀ g . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ghemɓɛ ̀ nga ̀ , ɓɛ ki la ̀ mi nɗaŋ ɗi Kiris be ̀ g tɔɔsi ̀ m .
Ɓi ̀ loŋ ɓimbog ɓi ghemɓɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ be ̀ g tɔɔsi ̀ m yin ̀ yi ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ . Ri ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓiloŋ ɗi n ̀ tonto ɗyɛɛ ri lɔɔ .
Ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ri ̀ ga ̀ ɓ ɓi ri ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓiloŋ ɗi n ̀ tonto , ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ ma ̀ a ̀ ghmaagh , ɓɛ ki ɓa ɓɛtɛnɛn ; ri ̀ wu ɗi kiɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɗi yii ̀ di ri i ̀ te ̀ ɗ ɓi ɓɔ ; ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ ɓɛ Kiris , ɓɛ ki la ̀ mi nɗaŋ ɗi nyi be ̀ g tɔɔsi ̀ m .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ be ̀ g yi ri ghaagh fɔlɔɔ tɔɔsi ̀ m , ɓɛ kpaŋzi ̀ Sata ̀ n ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y yi ̀ i ̀ ,
fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ri kɛ ̀ n kiye ̀ gsii ɓilɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓi ziinɛ ɓi ̀ la ̀ na ̀ ɓinin lɛ ri ̀ Gɔ ̀ g ri ̀ Magɔ ̀ g , lɛ di a taŋzɛn ɓyɔ ɓisuu wɛ ̀ y . Ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓin ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ sɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ a ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n .
Nni ɓɛ riɓi ̀ gha ̀ zi bimiɗ , ɓɛ ghegsɛ ̀ n ba ̀ n i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ti a ̀ keesa ̀ g ; ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɗuu ɗi sɛnga ̀ y aɗyoo , ɗi ɓugsi ̀ ɓɔ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ pika ̀ Sata ̀ n anɛ a ̀ ye ̀ gsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ ɓi ki ̀ ra ̀ a ̀ ki ɗuu ri ̀ n ̀ du ̀ si , ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɛ ri lɛ , ri ̀ nya ̀ m ri ̀ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓɛpwa ̀ a ̀ . Ɓɛ ri wowoogh gɛ mɛ ̀ tɔɓ yɛ ̀ ɛ i ̀ ru yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwos fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Nni n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ i ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ wu puɓ , ɗi ̀ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ mii ̀ . Zi ri ̀ ɗyoo ɓi ghɛŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi mis mii ɓyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa ti ri i ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ɓi ̀ loŋ lɛ ri ̀ ɓi ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ri ̀ ɓi ɓɔɓti , di ɓi rɛrɛlii asu wu ikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ . Ɓɛ ŋwaɗka ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kaa ̀ ta ̀ , ɓɛ ŋwaɗti ̀ kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ cɛɓ . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ yɔmga ̀ ɓi ̀ loŋ ɓin ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ maa mɛ ɓagha ̀ , le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn ɓi ɓɛ ̀ kaa ̀ ta ̀ ɓɛn ̀ .
Ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ loŋ ɓi a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɓyɔ , ri ̀ wu ri ̀ tɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , ɓi fa ɓi ̀ loŋ ɓi ɓyɔɔ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɓyɔ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ yɔmga ̀ mum bimiɗ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ mii mɛ ɓagha ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ pika ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ri ̀ wu , ri ̀ tɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓi ki ̀ ra ̀ a ̀ ki ɗuu ; ki ̀ ra ̀ a ̀ ki ɗuu ki ̀ n kɛɛ ri ri ̀ wu ɗi kiɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ .
Nni mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ ɗii ɗii ɗi ɓagha ̀ ɓi ɗika ̀ nɛn ɓi kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ cɛɓ , ɓɛ pika ̀ nyi ɓi ki ̀ ra ̀ a ̀ ki ɗuu ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ nyɔɔnyɔn a ̀ ɗyoo ri ̀ nyɔɔnyɔn a ̀ zi , lɛ ɗyoo ɗi n ̀ tonto ri ̀ zi i n ̀ tonto ɓi sili ̀ gha ̀ , nsoo ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ ki ̀ ko ̀ n kɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa ti .
Nni n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ba ̀ n i ̀ n ̀ tɛnɛn , nyɔɔnyɔn a ̀ Yorisalɛm , m ̀ pe ̀ gsɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ gura ̀ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ rɛ ̀ ŋɗɛɛ ɓisuu yii wii ̀ , di a sɛnsɛn yi aɗyoo , di a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ yi ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ woka ̀ di coo jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki rii ̀ ɓi-kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ , ki kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ lɛ : Ki ̀ nuugh ki Bɛ ̀ ll kɛɛ ̀ ki , n ̀ ɗaŋ ɗi ɓum ɓii ; a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ kɔ ̀ rii nɗaŋ ɗi ɓɔ , ɓɔɔ ɓa ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kii ; fɔɔnnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll nyimiɗ a ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ ɗi ɓɔ .
A ̀ ɓii ̀ tɔ ̀ saagh misi ̀ mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m mɛ ɓɔ ɓi mis ; fɔɔnnɛ ri ̀ wu ɗyaa ɓa ti ɓi nsoo ̀ ɓi ̀ lɛ ̀ ɓi ̀ , n ̀ soo ̀ ɓi ̀ kiŋ , nsoo ̀ ri ̀ kɛŋ , ɗyɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa ti , ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi n ̀ tonto ɓi ̀ n ɓi mɛ ghaa ̀ gh .
Fɔɔnnɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔriyɛn ɓi-kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu rila ̀ mi ̀ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓi m ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zii lɛ nyɔn ; a ̀ ki kpaa lɛ : Ka ̀ na ! ɓisuulɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yi yi ri mii ̀ , yi ki ɓa saaɗ .
Nni a ̀ kpagha ̀ mɛ ̀ lɛ ki lee ̀ gh . N ̀ ɗi ̀ Alfa ̀ ri ̀ O ̀ mega ̀ , ri ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ ri ̀ sugtɛ ̀ n . Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a wowog kinɔli , nnɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ faa ̀ n ̀ sim a ̀ mɛ ̀ nig mɛ cɛɓ zɛy ri ̀ zɛy , kɛ ̀ ɛ ko ̀ o ̀ sɛn .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ yagsaagh nnyɛɛ ri ɓii ̀ fɔ ̀ ni mɛwus mɛn ̀ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll wi ̀ i ̀ , nyii ɓa mɛ ̀ man .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a ɓɛ ̀ riris , ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ gherɛɛ ɓi , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓeɓtɛn , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ woli ̀ ɓum , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ti ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -maji ̀ g , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ nu ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pwa ̀ a ̀ pwaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , ga ̀ ɓ ya ̀ a ̀ i ɓaa gɛ ɓi ki ̀ ra ̀ a ̀ ki ɗuu ɗi ghɛ ̀ g-ghɛ ̀ g ri ̀ n ̀ du ̀ si , kɛɛ ri ri ̀ wu ɗi kiɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓɛ kitaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɓeŋ ɓɛ ̀ rongakɛn ɗi mɛ ̀ tɔɓ mɛ kitaa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛ siito ̀ n , ki yugha ̀ mɛ ̀ ki ̀ kpaa lɛ : Yu nɗesi wɔ ̀ gura ̀ , gili Man a ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
